":doc:`Ustvarite in prilagodite poročila <accounting/reporting/customize>` z "
"motorjem poročil Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:256
msgid ""
"In the :ref:`Tax return <accounting/tax-returns/report>`, Odoo computes all "
"accounting transactions for the specific tax period and uses these totals to "
"calculate the tax obligation."
msgstr ""
"V :ref:`Davčnem obračunu <accounting/tax-returns/report>` Odoo izračuna vse "
"računovodske transakcije za določeno davčno obdobje in uporabi te vsote za "
"izračun davčne obveznosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:260
msgid ""
"Depending on the country's localization, an XML version of the tax report "
"can be generated to be uploaded to the VAT platform of the relevant taxation "
"authority."
msgstr ""
"Glede na lokalizacijo države je mogoče ustvariti XML različico davčnega "
"poročila za nalaganje na platformo DDV pristojnega davčnega organa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:266
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:5
msgid "Bank synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija banke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:268
msgid ""
"The bank synchronization system directly connects with banking institutions "
"to automatically import all transactions into the database. It gives an "
"overview of the cash flow without logging into an online banking system or "
"waiting for paper bank statements."
msgstr ""
"Sistem sinhronizacije bank se neposredno povezuje z bančnimi institucijami "
"in samodejno uvozi vse transakcije v bazo podatkov. Zagotavlja pregled "
"denarnega toka brez prijave v spletni bančni sistem ali čakanja na papirnate "
"bančne izpiske."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:273
msgid ":doc:`Bank synchronization <accounting/bank/bank_synchronization>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Sinhronizacija bank <accounting/bank/bank_synchronization>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:278
msgid "Inventory valuation"
msgstr "Vrednotenje zalog"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:280
msgid ""
"Both periodic (manual) and perpetual (automated) inventory valuations are "
"supported in Odoo. The available methods are Standard Price, Average Cost "
"(AVCO), and First In First Out (FIFO)."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo sta podprti periodična (ročna) in stalna (avtomatizirana) vrednotenja "
"zaloge. Na voljo so metode standardna cena, povprečni stroški (AVCO) in prvi "
"vstop prvi izstop (FIFO)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:284
msgid ":doc:`../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet`"
msgstr ":doc:`../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:289
msgid "Retained earnings"
msgstr "Nerazporejeni dobiček"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:291
msgid ""
"Retained earnings are the portion of income retained by a business. Odoo "
"calculates current year earnings in real-time, so no year-end journal or "
"rollover is required. The profit and loss balance is automatically reported "
"on the balance sheet report."
msgstr ""
"Nerazporejeni dobiček je delež dohodka, ki ga podjetje zadrži. Odoo v "
"realnem času izračunava dobiček tekočega leta, zato ni potrebna knjižba ob "
"koncu leta ali prenos stanja. Bilanca uspeha se samodejno prikaže na "
"poročilu bilance stanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:301
msgid "Fiduciaries"
msgstr "Fiduciarji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:303
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Accounting Firms` mode can be activated by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. When enabled:"
msgstr ""
"Način :guilabel:`Računovodska podjetja` lahko aktivirate tako, da odprete "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. Ko je "
"omogočen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:306
msgid "The document's sequence becomes editable on all documents;"
msgstr "Zaporedje dokumenta postane uredljivo na vseh dokumentih;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:307
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Total (tax incl.)` field appears to speed up and control the "
"encoding by automating line creation with the right account and tax;"
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Skupaj (z DDV)` se prikaže za pospeševanje in nadzor vnosa "
"s samodejnim ustvarjanjem vrstic s pravilnim kontom in davkom;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:309
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice Date` and :guilabel:`Bill Date` are pre-filled when "
"encoding a transaction."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum računa` in :guilabel:`Datum računa dobavitelja` sta vnaprej "
"izpolnjena pri kodiranju transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:310
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Quick encoding` option is available for customer invoices and "
"vendor bills."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :guilabel:`Hitro kodiranje` je na voljo za račune strankam in račune "
"dobaviteljev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:315
msgid "Share invoices with external accountants"
msgstr "Deljenje računov z zunanjimi računovodji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:317
msgid ""
"Odoo offers multiple ways to share invoices and bills with an external "
"accountant, including the abilities to :ref:`grant access rights <accounting/"
"accountant-access-rights>` to your database, to :ref:`automatically send "
"copies of a journal's invoices or bills <accounting/send-copy>` to a "
"specified email address, and to :ref:`download ZIP files <accounting/zip>` "
"containing all invoices and all bills."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ponuja več načinov za deljenje računov in prejemkov z zunanjim "
"računovodjem, vključno z možnostmi :ref:`dodelitve pravic dostopa "
"<accounting/accountant-access-rights>` do vaše podatkovne baze, "
":ref:`samodejnega pošiljanja kopij računov ali prejemkov dnevnika "
"<accounting/send-copy>` na določen e-poštni naslov in :ref:`prenosa ZIP "
"datotek <accounting/zip>`, ki vsebujejo vse račune in vse prejemke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:326
msgid "Accountant access rights"
msgstr "Dostopne pravice računovodje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:328
msgid ""
"To grant access to the company's accountant, :ref:`add the accountant as a "
"new user <users/add-individual>` and configure the appropriate :doc:`access "
"rights <../general/users/access_rights>` in the :guilabel:`Accounting` "
"section to enable access to the company's financial data:"
msgstr ""
"Za odobritev dostopa računovodji podjetja :ref:`dodajte računovodjo kot "
"novega uporabnika <users/add-individual>` in konfigurirajte ustrezne "
":doc:`dostopne pravice <../general/users/access_rights>` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Računovodstvo`, da omogočite dostop do finančnih podatkov "
"podjetja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:333
msgid ":guilabel:`Accounting`: Select :guilabel:`Administrator`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Računovodstvo`: Izberite :guilabel:`Skrbnik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:334
msgid ":guilabel:`Bank`: Allow bank account validation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Banka`: Omogoči potrjevanje bančnega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:337
msgid ""
"Adding an accountant as a new user in :doc:`Odoo Online <../../"
"administration/odoo_online>` is free if the accountant has an Odoo account "
"registered with the same email address as the one listed for the company "
"user. However, :doc:`Odoo.sh <../../administration/odoo_sh>` and :doc:`Odoo "
"On-premise <../../administration/on_premise>` may involve extra charges for "
"each additional user. For more pricing information, see `Odoo's pricing "
"<https://www.odoo.com/pricing-plan>`_."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje računovodje kot novega uporabnika v :doc:`Odoo Online <../../"
"administration/odoo_online>` je brezplačno, če ima računovodja račun Odoo "
"registriran z enakim e-poštnim naslovom kot tisti, ki je naveden za "
"uporabnika podjetja. Vendar pa :doc:`Odoo.sh <../../administration/odoo_sh>` "
"in :doc:`Odoo On-premise <../../administration/on_premise>` lahko "
"vključujeta dodatne stroške za vsakega dodatnega uporabnika. Za več "
"informacij o cenah glejte `Odoo cenik <https://www.odoo.com/pricing-plan>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:344
msgid ""
"For a multi-company environment, set the appropriate :ref:`access <users/"
"multi-companies>`."
msgstr ""
"Za večpodjetniško okolje nastavite ustrezen :ref:`dostop <users/multi-"
"companies>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:349
msgid "Send copies of a journal's invoices or bills"
msgstr "Pošiljanje kopij računov ali nabavnih računov dnevnika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:351
msgid ""
"Sales and purchase type journals can be used to send all of their invoices "
"and bills to external email addresses. These records are sent in XML format."
msgstr ""
"Dnevniki tipa prodaje in nabave lahko uporabite za pošiljanje vseh njihovih "
"računov in nabavnih računov na zunanje e-poštne naslove. Ti zapisi se "
"pošiljajo v formatu XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:354
msgid ""
"To configure a journal to automatically send its records to a specified "
"email address, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti dnevnik za samodejno pošiljanje njegovih zapisov na "
"določen e-poštni naslov, sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:357
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:145
msgid "Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:358
msgid "Open the desired journal."
msgstr "Odprite želeni dnevnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:359
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab, enter an email address in "
"the :guilabel:`Send Copy To` field."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Napredne nastavitve` vnesite e-poštni naslov v polje "
":guilabel:`Pošlji kopijo na`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:363
msgid ""
"Multiple email addresses can be entered. Separate them with `;` without a "
"space (i.e.: `sample1@example.com;sample2@example.com`)."
msgstr ""
"Vnesete lahko več e-poštnih naslovov. Ločite jih s `;` brez presledka (npr.: "
"`primer1@example.com;primer2@example.com`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:369
msgid "ZIP file export"
msgstr "Izvoz ZIP datoteke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:371
msgid ""
"Groups of invoices and bills can be exported in ZIP files. To export "
"invoices or bills in ZIP files, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Skupine računov in nabavnih računov lahko izvozite v ZIP datoteke. Če želite "
"izvoziti račune ali nabavne račune v ZIP datoteke, sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:374
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices` "
"or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Bills`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Kupci --> Računi` ali "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Nabavni računi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:376
msgid "Select the invoices or bills to be included in the ZIP file."
msgstr ""
"Izberite račune ali nabavne račune, ki jih želite vključiti v ZIP datoteko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:377
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Print` menu, and click :guilabel:`Export "
"ZIP`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Natisni` in nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Izvozi ZIP`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting.rst:379
msgid ""
"Once the ZIP file is exported, it can be sent to an external accountant to "
"provide them with all the information of your invoices and bills."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ZIP datoteka izvožena, jo lahko pošljete zunanjemu računovodji, da mu "
"posredujete vse informacije o vaših računih in nabavnih računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:7
msgid ""
"You can manage as many bank or cash accounts as needed on your database. "
"Configuring them correctly allows you to have all your banking data up-to-"
"date and ready for :doc:`reconciliation <bank/reconciliation>` with your "
"journal entries."
msgstr ""
"V svoji bazi podatkov lahko upravljate toliko bančnih ali gotovinskih "
"računov, kot jih potrebujete. Pravilna konfiguracija omogoča, da so vsi vaši "
"bančni podatki posodobljeni in pripravljeni za :doc:`uskladitev <bank/"
"reconciliation>` z vašimi knjižili."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:11
msgid ""
"In Odoo Accounting, each bank account has a dedicated journal set to post "
"all entries in a dedicated account. Both the journal and the account are "
"automatically created and configured whenever you add a bank account."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo Računovodstvu ima vsak bančni račun namenski dnevnik, nastavljen za "
"knjiženje vseh vnosov na namenski kont. Tako dnevnik kot kont sta samodejno "
"ustvarjena in konfigurirana, kadarkoli dodate bančni račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:16
msgid ""
":ref:`Cash journals <accounting/journals/cash>` and accounts must be "
"configured manually."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dnevniki gotovine <accounting/journals/cash>` in računi morajo biti "
"konfigurirani ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:18
msgid ""
"Bank journals are displayed by default on the :guilabel:`Accounting "
"Dashboard` in the form of cards which include action buttons."
msgstr ""
"Bančni dnevniki so privzeto prikazani na :guilabel:`Nadzorni plošči "
"računovodstva` v obliki kartic, ki vključujejo akcijske gumbe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:None
msgid ""
"Bank journals are displayed on the Accounting Dashboard and contain action "
"buttons"
msgstr ""
"Bančni dnevniki so prikazani na nadzorni plošči računovodstva in vsebujejo "
"gumbe za dejanja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:27
msgid "Manage bank and cash accounts"
msgstr "Upravljanje bančnih in denarnih računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:30
msgid "Connect a bank for automatic synchronization"
msgstr "Povežite banko za samodejno sinhronizacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:32
msgid ""
"To connect your bank account to your database, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` and on the kanban card of an "
"unconnected bank, click :guilabel:`Search over 26000 banks`. Select your "
"bank from the list, click on :guilabel:`Connect`, and follow the "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"Če želite povezati svoj bančni račun s svojo podatkovno bazo, pojdite na "
":guilabel:`Nadzorno plošč računovodstva` in na kartici kanban nepovezane "
"banke kliknite :guilabel:`Išči med več kot 26000 bankami`. Izberite svojo "
"banko s seznama, kliknite na :guilabel:`Poveži` in sledite navodilom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started.rst:183
msgid ":doc:`bank/bank_synchronization`"
msgstr ":doc:`bank/bank_synchronization`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:42
msgid "Create a bank account"
msgstr "Ustvari bančni račun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:44
msgid ""
"If your banking institution is not available in Odoo, or if you don't want "
"to connect your bank account to your database, you can configure your bank "
"account manually."
msgstr ""
"Če vaša bančna institucija ni na voljo v Odoo ali če ne želite povezati "
"svojega bančnega računa z bazo podatkov, lahko bančni račun konfigurirate "
"ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:47
msgid ""
"To manually add a bank account, go to the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` "
"and on the kanban card of an unconnected bank, click :guilabel:`Search over "
"26000 banks`. Then, click on :guilabel:`Record transactions manually` (at "
"the bottom right), fill out the bank information, and "
"click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ročno dodati bančni račun, pojdite na :guilabel:`Nadzorno plošč "
"računovodstva` in na kartici kanban nepovezane banke kliknite "
":guilabel:`Išči med več kot 26000 bankami`. Nato kliknite na "
":guilabel:`Ročno zabeleži transakcije` (spodaj desno), izpolnite bančne "
"podatke in kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:53
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically detects the bank account type (e.g., IBAN) and enables "
"some features accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Odoo samodejno zazna vrsto bančnega računa (npr. IBAN) in ustrezno omogoči "
"nekatere funkcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank.rst:55
msgid ""
"A default :ref:`bank journal <accounting/journals/bank>` is available and "
"can be used to configure your bank account by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Accounting: Journals --> "
"Bank`. Open it and edit the different fields to match your bank account "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti :ref:`bančni dnevnik <accounting/journals/bank>` je na voljo in ga "
"lahko uporabite za konfiguracijo svojega bančnega računa tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Računovodstvo: "
"Dnevniki --> Banka`. Odprite ga in uredite različna polja, da se ujemajo s "
"podatki vašega bančnega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo synchronizes directly with your bank institution to automatically "
"import all bank transactions into the database. It supports over 26,000 "
"financial institutions worldwide and relies on multiple :ref:`third-party "
"providers <accounting/bank-synchronization/third-party-providers>` to "
"connect with banks."
msgstr ""
"Odoo se sinhronizira neposredno z vašo bančno institucijo, da samodejno "
"uvozi vse bančne transakcije v podatkovno bazo. Podpira več kot 26.000 "
"finančnih institucij po vsem svetu in se zanaša na več :ref:`ponudnikov "
"tretjih oseb <accounting/bank-synchronization/third-party-providers>` za "
"povezavo z bankami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:13
msgid "To use this service, a valid Odoo Enterprise subscription is required."
msgstr "Za uporabo te storitve je potrebna veljavna naročnina Odoo Enterprise."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:16
msgid ""
"To check if your bank is compatible with Odoo, go to `Odoo Accounting "
"Features <https://www.odoo.com/app/accounting-features#part_5>`_, and "
"click :guilabel:`See list of supported institutions` in the :guilabel:`Bank "
"& Cash` section."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preveriti, ali je vaša banka združljiva z Odoo, pojdite na `Odoo "
"Accounting Features <https://www.odoo.com/app/accounting-features#part_5>`_ "
"in kliknite :guilabel:`See list of supported institutions` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Bank & Cash`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:21
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:22
msgid ":doc:`transactions`"
msgstr ":doc:`transactions`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:26
