#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:31
msgid "First synchronization"
msgstr "Prva sinhronizacija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:33
msgid ""
"To synchronize the database with a bank, go to the Accounting Dashboard, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, and select the :guilabel:`Bank` card. In "
"the :guilabel:`Add a Bank Account` window, select the relevant bank and "
"click :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Za sinhronizacijo baze podatkov z banko pojdite na Nadzorno ploščo za "
"računovodstvo, kliknite :guilabel:`New` in izberite kartico "
":guilabel:`Bank`. V oknu :guilabel:`Add a Bank Account` izberite ustrezno "
"banko in kliknite :guilabel:`Connect`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:38
msgid ""
"Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical "
"ellipsis)` icon of the :guilabel:`Bank` journal, and :guilabel:`Connect "
"bank`, or click :guilabel:`Search over 26000 banks` in the Accounting "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Lahko pa kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)"
"` dnevnika :guilabel:`Bank` in :guilabel:`Connect bank` ali kliknite "
":guilabel:`Search over 26000 banks` na Nadzorni plošči za računovodstvo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:41
msgid ""
"Depending on your bank and country, you can select the :guilabel:`Type of "
"account` and/or choose another :ref:`third-party provider <accounting/bank-"
"synchronization/third-party-providers>` to connect with the bank if needed "
"before clicking :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Glede na vašo banko in državo lahko izberete :guilabel:`Type of account` in/"
"ali izberete drugega :ref:`ponudnika tretje osebe <accounting/bank-"
"synchronization/third-party-providers>`, če je to potrebno za povezavo z "
"banko, preden kliknete :guilabel:`Connect`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:44
msgid ""
"If your bank is not listed in the :guilabel:`Search for an institution` "
"window, scroll down the list and click :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add new "
"bank` to create a bank account manually. Fill in the :guilabel:`Account "
"Number`, :guilabel:`Bank`, and :guilabel:`SWIFT Code`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Connect`. A bank journal is then created and named using "
"the account number. Note that in this case, the bank is not synchronized."
msgstr ""
"Če vaše banke ni na seznamu v oknu :guilabel:`Search for an institution`, se "
"pomaknite navzdol po seznamu in kliknite :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add new "
"bank`, da ročno ustvarite bančni račun. Izpolnite :guilabel:`Account "
"Number`, :guilabel:`Bank` in :guilabel:`SWIFT Code` ter kliknite "
":guilabel:`Connect`. Ustvari se bančni dnevnik, poimenovan po številki "
"računa. Upoštevajte, da v tem primeru banka ni sinhronizirana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:49
msgid ""
"If issues occur during the first synchronization, check that no firewall or "
"proxy is blocking the address https://production.odoofin.com/. Make sure "
"your web browser allows pop-ups and that any ad-blocker is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Če pride do težav med prvo sinhronizacijo, preverite, da noben požarni zid "
"ali posredniški strežnik ne blokira naslova https://production.odoofin.com/. "
"Prepričajte se, da vaš spletni brskalnik dovoljuje pojavna okna in da je "
"onemogočen morebitni zaviralec oglasov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:54
msgid ""
"When setting up bank synchronization, accounting transactions are "
"automatically recorded from the date of the last transaction +1 day (e.g., "
"if the last transaction date is 31/12/2025, the recording starts on "
"01/01/2026). If the journal contains no transactions, all available past "
"transactions are retrieved. To limit the retrieval period, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Lock Dates`, and set a date "
"in the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` field."
msgstr ""
"Pri nastavitvi bančne sinhronizacije se računovodske transakcije samodejno "
"zabeležijo od datuma zadnje transakcije +1 dan (npr. če je datum zadnje "
"transakcije 31. 12. 2025, se beleženje začne 1. 1. 2026). Če dnevnik ne "
"vsebuje nobenih transakcij, se pridobijo vse razpoložljive pretekle "
"transakcije. Za omejitev obdobja pridobivanja pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Lock Dates` in nastavite datum "
"v polju :guilabel:`Lock Everything`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:61
msgid ""
"Some banks are in a :guilabel:`Beta` status, meaning they're not yet fully "
"supported by third-party providers. This may lead to bugs or other issues. "
"Although they can be used, Odoo does not provide technical support in this "
"case."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere banke imajo status :guilabel:`Beta`, kar pomeni, da jih ponudniki "
"tretjih oseb še ne podpirajo v celoti. To lahko povzroči napake ali druge "
"težave. Čeprav jih je mogoče uporabljati, Odoo v tem primeru ne zagotavlja "
"tehnične podpore."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:64
msgid ""
"The :ref:`third-party provider <accounting/bank-synchronization/third-party-"
"providers>` may request more information to connect with a bank. This "
"information is not stored on Odoo's servers."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Ponudnik tretje osebe <accounting/bank-synchronization/third-party-"
"providers>` lahko zahteva dodatne informacije za povezavo z banko. Te "
"informacije niso shranjene na strežnikih Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:67
msgid ""
"To view all past synchronizations, activate the :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>` and go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Online Synchronization`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled vseh preteklih sinhronizacij aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način "
"<developer-mode>` in pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Online Synchronization`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:73
msgid "Manual synchronization"
msgstr "Ročna sinhronizacija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:75
msgid ""
"After the :ref:`first synchronization <accounting/bank-synchronization/first-"
"synchronization>`, bank journals are synchronized by default every twelve "
"hours. To manually trigger synchronization, go to the Accounting dashboard "
"and click :guilabel:`Fetch Transactions` on the relevant bank journal."
msgstr ""
"Po :ref:`prvi sinhronizaciji <accounting/bank-synchronization/first-"
"synchronization>` se bančni dnevniki privzeto sinhronizirajo vsakih dvanajst "
"ur. Za ročno sprožitev sinhronizacije pojdite na Nadzorno ploščo za "
"računovodstvo in kliknite :guilabel:`Fetch Transactions` pri ustreznem "
"bančnem dnevniku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:80
msgid ""
"Alternatively, activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Online Synchronization`, "
"select the relevant bank, and click :guilabel:`Fetch transactions`."
msgstr ""
"Lahko pa aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>`, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Online Synchronization`, "
"izberite ustrezno banko in kliknite :guilabel:`Fetch transactions`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:85
msgid ""
"Some banks do not support automatic transaction fetching. For these "
"institutions, an error message appears during the automatic account "
"synchronization, prompting the user to disable the automatic "
"synchronization. This message is also logged in the chatter of the online "
"synchronization. In such cases, disable the :guilabel:`Automatic "
"synchronization` option in the corresponding bank's :guilabel:`Online "
"Synchronization` and make sure to perform manual synchronizations by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Fetch Transactions` on the relevant bank journal."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere banke ne podpirajo samodejnega pridobivanja transakcij. Pri teh "
"institucijah se med samodejno sinhronizacijo računa prikaže sporočilo o "
"napaki, ki uporabnika pozove k onemogočitvi samodejne sinhronizacije. To "
"sporočilo je zabeleženo tudi v pogovoru spletne sinhronizacije. V takih "
"primerih onemogočite možnost :guilabel:`Automatic synchronization` v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Online Synchronization` ustrezne banke in poskrbite, da "
"izvajate ročne sinhronizacije s klikom na :guilabel:`Fetch Transactions` pri "
"ustreznem bančnem dnevniku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:91
msgid ""
"For some bank institutions, transactions can only be fetched up to three "
"months in the past. If older transactions are needed, they can "
"be :ref:`imported <accounting/transactions/import>`."
msgstr ""
"Pri nekaterih bančnih institucijah je transakcije mogoče pridobiti le do tri "
"mesece v preteklost. Če so potrebne starejše transakcije, jih je mogoče "
":ref:`uvoziti <accounting/transactions/import>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:97
msgid "Update synchronization credentials"
msgstr "Posodobitev poverilnic za sinhronizacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:99
msgid ""
"To update bank credentials, activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Online "
"Synchronization`. Open the connection that needs to be updated, "
"click :guilabel:`Update Credentials`, and follow the steps."
msgstr ""
"Za posodobitev bančnih poverilnic aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način "
"<developer-mode>` in pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Online Synchronization`. Odprite povezavo, ki jo je treba "
"posodobiti, kliknite :guilabel:`Update Credentials` in sledite korakom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:104
msgid ""
"The steps may vary depending on the third-party provider, as each provider "
"follows its own process."
msgstr ""
"Koraki se lahko razlikujejo glede na ponudnika tretje osebe, saj vsak "
"ponudnik sledi svojemu postopku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:106
msgid ""
"When updating bank credentials, make sure all accounts are selected for "
"synchronization, including those from other banking institutions if "
"applicable."
msgstr ""
"Pri posodabljanju bančnih poverilnic se prepričajte, da so vsi računi "
"izbrani za sinhronizacijo, vključno s tistimi iz drugih bančnih institucij, "
"če je primerno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:112
msgid "Third-party providers"
msgstr "Zunanji ponudniki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:114
msgid ""
"Odoo relies on third-party providers to securely connect to your bank "
"accounts and automatically import transactions and financial data into the "
"database. The following providers are used:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo se za varno povezavo z vašimi bančnimi računi in samodejni uvoz "
"transakcij ter finančnih podatkov v bazo podatkov zanaša na zunanje "
"ponudnike. Uporabljeni so naslednji ponudniki:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:117
msgid ""
"`Plaid <https://plaid.com/discover-apps/>`_ (supported in the `United States "
"of America and Canada <https://plaid.com/docs/institutions/>`_)"
msgstr ""
"`Plaid <https://plaid.com/discover-apps/>`_ (podprto v `Združenih državah "
"Amerike in Kanadi <https://plaid.com/docs/institutions/>`_)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:119
