#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:145
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:60
msgid "Duplicate transactions"
msgstr "Podvojene transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:147
msgid ""
"When importing transactions, some may appear :ref:`duplicated <accounting/"
"transactions/duplicate>` due to the same online transaction identifier or "
"the same currency, amount, account number, and date."
msgstr ""
"Pri uvozu transakcij se lahko nekatere prikažejo kot :ref:`podvojene "
"<accounting/transactions/duplicate>` zaradi enakega identifikatorja spletne "
"transakcije ali enake valute, zneska, številke računa in datuma."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:154
msgid "Missing transactions"
msgstr "Manjkajoče transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:156
msgid ""
"Missing or pending transactions are entries that the bank has not yet "
"validated."
msgstr ""
"Manjkajoče ali čakajoče transakcije so vnosi, ki jih banka še ni potrdila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:158
msgid ""
"To find missing and pending transactions, access the :ref:`bank "
"reconciliation view <accounting/reconciliation/access>`, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon, and select :guilabel:`Find Missing "
"Transactions`."
msgstr ""
"Za iskanje manjkajočih in čakajočih transakcij odprite :ref:`pogled "
"usklajevanja banke <accounting/reconciliation/access>`, kliknite ikono "
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(zobnik)` in izberite :guilabel:`Najdi manjkajoče "
"transakcije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:162
msgid ""
"To import a posted missing transaction, select it and "
"click :guilabel:`Import Transactions`."
msgstr ""
"Za uvoz knjižene manjkajoče transakcije jo izberite in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Uvozi transakcije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:165
msgid ""
"Make sure the connection with the bank is active to find missing "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Za iskanje manjkajočih transakcij se prepričajte, da je povezava z banko "
"aktivna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:166
msgid ":guilabel:`Pending` transactions cannot be imported."
msgstr "Transakcij s statusom :guilabel:`V teku` ni mogoče uvoziti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:171
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:102
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:174
msgid ""
":ref:`Bank synchronization troubleshooting - Ponto <accounting/bank-"
"synchronization/ponto/troubleshooting>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odpravljanje težav s sinhronizacijo banke - Ponto <accounting/bank-"
"synchronization/ponto/troubleshooting>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:180
msgid "Synchronization errors or disconnections"
msgstr "Napake pri sinhronizaciji ali prekinitve povezave"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:182
msgid ""
"To report a connection error to `Odoo support <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_, "
"activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Online Synchronization`, "
"select the failed connection, and copy the error description and the "
"reference."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prijaviti napako pri povezavi `podpori Odoo <https://www.odoo.com/"
"help>`_, aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>`, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> Spletna sinhronizacija`, "
"izberite neuspešno povezavo in kopirajte opis napake ter referenco."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:187
msgid ""
"If the connection with the proxy is lost and reconnection using "
"the :guilabel:`Reconnect` option isn't successful, contact `support <https://"
"www.odoo.com/help>`_ directly. Provide the client ID or the error reference "
"from the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Če je povezava s proxyjem izgubljena in ponovna povezava z možnostjo "
":guilabel:`Ponovno poveži` ni uspešna, se obrnite neposredno na `podporo "
"<https://www.odoo.com/help>`_. Navedite ID odjemalca ali referenco napake iz "
"klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:194
msgid "Why is the synchronization not working in real-time?"
msgstr "Zakaj sinhronizacija ne deluje v realnem času?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:196
msgid ""
"Synchronization is not designed to work in real time, as third-party "
"providers synchronize accounts at different intervals. To manually trigger "
"synchronization and retrieve bank transactions, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, and click :guilabel:`Fetch "
"Transactions`."
msgstr ""
"Sinhronizacija ni zasnovana za delovanje v realnem času, saj zunanje "
"storitve sinhronizirajo račune v različnih intervalih. Za ročno sprožitev "
"sinhronizacije in pridobitev bančnih transakcij pojdite na "
":guilabel:`Nadzorno plošča računovodstva` in kliknite :guilabel:`Pridobi "
"transakcije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:200
msgid ""
"Alternatively, to synchronize and fetch transactions, activate "
"the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Online Synchronization`."
msgstr ""
"Alternativno lahko za sinhronizacijo in pridobitev transakcij aktivirajte "
":ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>` in pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> Spletna sinhronizacija`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:204
msgid ""
"Some providers restrict refreshes to once per day. If transactions have "
"already been fetched, clicking :guilabel:`Fetch Transactions` again may not "
"retrieve the latest data."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri ponudniki omejujejo osvežitev na enkrat na dan. Če so bile "
"transakcije že pridobljene, ponovni klik na :guilabel:`Pridobi transakcije` "
"morda ne bo pridobil najnovejših podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:207
msgid ""
"Transactions may appear on a bank account, but cannot be fetched if they "
"have a :guilabel:`Pending` status; only transactions with "
"a :guilabel:`Posted` status are retrieved."
msgstr ""
"Transakcije se lahko prikažejo na bančnem računu, vendar jih ni mogoče "
"pridobiti, če imajo status :guilabel:`V teku`; pridobljene so samo "
"transakcije s statusom :guilabel:`Objavljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:213
msgid "Why do my transactions only synchronize when I refresh manually?"
msgstr "Zakaj se moje transakcije sinhronizirajo le, ko jih ročno osvežim?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:215
msgid ""
"Some banks implement additional security measures and require extra steps, "
"such as an SMS or email authentication code, or another type of :abbr:`MFA "
"(multi-factor authentication)`. As a result, the third-party provider cannot "
"retrieve transactions until the security code is provided."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere banke izvajajo dodatne varnostne ukrepe in zahtevajo dodatne "
"korake, kot so avtentikacijska koda prek SMS ali e-pošte ali druga vrsta "
":abbr:`MFA (večfaktorska avtentikacija)`. Posledično zunanji ponudnik ne "
"more pridobiti transakcij, dokler ni zagotovljena varnostna koda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:222
msgid "Why are no transactions visible?"
msgstr "Zakaj ni vidnih transakcij?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:224
msgid "There are a few possible reasons for this issue:"
msgstr "Za to težavo obstaja več možnih razlogov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:226
msgid ""
"No bank accounts were synchronized during the :ref:`first synchronization "
"<accounting/bank-synchronization/first-synchronization>`."
msgstr ""
"Med :ref:`prvo sinhronizacijo <accounting/bank-synchronization/first-"
"synchronization>` ni bilo sinhroniziranih nobenih bančnih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:228
msgid "There may be no new transactions available to fetch."
msgstr "Morda ni na voljo novih transakcij za pridobitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:230
msgid ""
"If the bank account is correctly linked to a journal, but posted "
"transactions still aren't visible in the database, contact `support <https://"
"www.odoo.com/help>`_."
msgstr ""
"Če je bančni račun pravilno povezan z dnevnikom, a objavljene transakcije še "
"vedno niso vidne v bazi podatkov, se obrnite na `podporo <https://"
"www.odoo.com/help>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:236
msgid "Why are no accounts shown after synchronization?"
msgstr "Zakaj po sinhronizaciji ni prikazanih računov?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:238
msgid ""
"During the synchronization process, a bank institution was selected, but no "
"bank accounts from this institution were authorized during the :ref:`first "
"synchronization <accounting/bank-synchronization/first-synchronization>`."
msgstr ""
"Med postopkom sinhronizacije je bila izbrana bančna institucija, vendar med "
":ref:`prvo sinhronizacijo <accounting/bank-synchronization/first-"
"synchronization>` ni bil avtoriziran noben bančni račun te institucije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:245
msgid "Saltedge troubleshooting"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav s Saltedge"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:250
msgid "Why is there an error when deleting a synchronization in Odoo?"
msgstr "Zakaj pride do napake pri brisanju sinhronizacije v Odoo?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:252
msgid ""
"Odoo can't permanently delete the connection established with the banking "
"institution. However, it revokes consent, which prevents Odoo from accessing "
"the account. The error message indicates that the consent has been revoked, "
"but the record could not be deleted as it remains in Salt Edge."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ne more trajno izbrisati povezave, vzpostavljene z bančno institucijo. "
"Vendar prekliče soglasje, kar prepreči Odoo dostopu do računa. Sporočilo o "
"napaki označuje, da je bilo soglasje preklicano, vendar zapisa ni bilo "
"mogoče izbrisati, ker ostaja v Salt Edge."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:256
msgid ""
"To delete the connection, connect to the `Salt Edge account <https://"
"www.saltedge.com/dashboard>`_ and manually remove the synchronization. Once "
"this is done, the record can be deleted in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Za brisanje povezave se povežite na `račun Salt Edge <https://"
"www.saltedge.com/dashboard>`_ in ročno odstranite sinhronizacijo. Ko je to "
"storjeno, je zapis mogoče izbrisati v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:262
msgid "I have an error saying that this account has already been synchronized"
msgstr "Imam napako, ki pravi, da je bil ta račun že sinhroniziran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:264
msgid ""
"The bank account has already been synchronized with Salt Edge. Access the "
"Salt Edge `dashboard <https://www.saltedge.com/dashboard>`_ to check if a "
"connection with the same credentials exists. There are two options:"
msgstr ""
"Bančni račun je bil že sinhroniziran s Salt Edge. Dostopite do `nadzorne "
"plošče <https://www.saltedge.com/dashboard>`_ Salt Edge, da preverite, ali "
"obstaja povezava z enakimi poverilnicami. Obstajata dve možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:268
msgid ""
"If a connection with the same credentials exists in Salt Edge but has not "
"been synchronized with Odoo, delete the existing connection and create a new "
"one from the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Če povezava z enakimi poverilnicami obstaja v Salt Edge, vendar ni bila "
"sinhronizirana z Odoo, izবrišite obstoječo povezavo in ustvarite novo iz "
"podatkovne baze Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization.rst:270
msgid ""
"If a connection with the same credentials exists in Salt Edge and has "
"already been synchronized with Odoo, :ref:`update the synchronization "
"credentials <accounting/bank-synchronization/update-credentials>` to "
"reactivate the connection."
msgstr ""
"Če povezava z enakimi poverilnicami obstaja v Salt Edge in je bila že "
"sinhronizirana z Odoo, :ref:`posodobite poverilnice sinhronizacije "
"<accounting/bank-synchronization/update-credentials>`, da ponovno aktivirate "
"povezavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:3
msgid "Ponto"
msgstr "Ponto"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Ponto <https://myponto.com/>`_ is a paid third-party service that enables "
"companies and professionals to connect multiple bank accounts to a single "
"platform. It provides a unified view of all transactions within a single "
"interface. When integrated with Odoo, it automatically synchronizes bank "
"transactions directly into its database."
msgstr ""
"`Ponto <https://myponto.com/>`_ je plačljiva storitev tretje osebe, ki "
"podjetjem in strokovnjakom omogoča povezavo več bančnih računov na eno "
"platformo. Zagotavlja enoten pogled na vse transakcije znotraj enega "
"vmesnika. Ko je integriran z Odoo, samodejno sinhronizira bančne transakcije "
"neposredno v njegovo podatkovno bazo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:11
msgid "Using Ponto is subject to applicable fees."
msgstr "Uporaba Ponto je predmet veljavnih pristojbin."

