#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:94
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Batch Payments` "
"and :ref:`create a batch <accounting/batch/creation>`. Select the same "
"bank :guilabel:`Journal` and :guilabel:`Payment Method`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` to select the payment created in the previous "
"step."
msgstr ""
"Přejděte do :menuselection:`Účetnictví --> Dodavatelé --> Dávkové platby` a "
":ref:`vytvořte dávku <accounting/batch/creation>`. Vyberte stejný bankovní "
":guilabel:`Deník` a :guilabel:`Platební metodu` a klikněte na "
":guilabel:`Přidat řádek`, abyste vybrali platbu vytvořenou v předchozím "
"kroku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:97
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Initiate Payment` to connect to Ponto and follow the steps "
"to sign the payment."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Zahájit platbu`, připojte se k Ponto a dokončete "
"kroky k podepsání platby."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:110
msgid "Why has the authorization expired?"
msgstr "Proč vypršela autorizace?"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:112
msgid ""
"Every six months (180 days), the connection between a bank account and Ponto "
"must be re-authorized via the `Ponto website <https://myponto.com>`_. "
"Failure to do so will result in synchronization stopping for those accounts."
msgstr ""
"Každých šest měsíců (180 dní) musí být propojení mezi bankovním účtem a "
"Ponto znovu autorizováno prostřednictvím `webové stránky Ponto <https://"
"myponto.com>`_. Pokud k tomu nedojde, synchronizace pro tyto účty se zastaví."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:3
msgid "Manage a bank account in a foreign currency"
msgstr "Upravljanje bančnega računa v tuji valuti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo, every transaction is recorded in the default currency of the "
"company, and reports are all based on that default currency. When you have a "
"bank account in a foreign currency, for every transaction, Odoo stores two "
"values:"
msgstr ""
"V Odoo je vsaka transakcija zabeležena v privzeti valuti podjetja in vsa "
"poročila temeljijo na tej privzeti valuti. Ko imate bančni račun v tuji "
"valuti, Odoo za vsako transakcijo shrani dve vrednosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:9
msgid "The debit/credit in the currency of the *company*;"
msgstr "Bremenitev/dobropisa v valuti *podjetja*;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:10
msgid "The debit/credit in the currency of the *bank account*."
msgstr "Bremenitev/dobropisa v valuti *bančnega računa*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:12
msgid ""
"Currency rates are updated automatically using the web services of a banking "
"institution. By default, Odoo uses the European Central Bank's web services "
"but other options are available."
msgstr ""
"Valutni tečaji se posodablja samodejno z uporabo spletnih storitev bančne "
"institucije. Privzeto Odoo uporablja spletne storitve Evropske centralne "
"banke, na voljo pa so tudi druge možnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:19
msgid "Activate multi-currencies"
msgstr "Aktivirajte več valut"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:21
msgid ""
"To work with multiple currencies, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings --> Currencies` and tick :guilabel:`Multi-"
"Currencies`. Under :guilabel:`Post Exchange difference entries in:`, provide "
"a :guilabel:`Journal`, a :guilabel:`Gain Account`, a :guilabel:`Loss "
"Account`, and then click on :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za delo z več valutami pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve --> Valute` in označite :guilabel:`Več valut`. "
"Pod :guilabel:`Knjižite razlike v menjavi v:` vnesite :guilabel:`Dnevnik`, "
":guilabel:`Račun dobička`, :guilabel:`Račun izgube` in nato kliknite na "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:27
msgid "Configure currencies"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte valute"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:29
msgid ""
"Once Odoo is configured to support multiple currencies, they are all created "
"by default, but not necessarily active. To activate the new currencies, "
"click on :guilabel:`Activate Other Currencies` under the :guilabel:`Multi-"
"Currencies` setting or go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Accounting: Currencies`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je Odoo konfiguriran za podporo več valut, so vse ustvarjene privzeto, "
"vendar niso nujno aktivne. Za aktivacijo novih valut kliknite na "
":guilabel:`Aktivirajte druge valute` pod nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Več valut` "
"ali pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Računovodstvo: Valute`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:34
msgid ""
"When the currencies are activated, you can choose to **automate** the "
"currency rate update, or leave it on **manual**. To configure the rate "
"update, go back to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings "
"--> Currencies`, check :guilabel:`Automatic Currency Rates`, "
"set :guilabel:`Interval` to your desired frequency, and then click "
"on :guilabel:`Save`. You also have the option to choose "
"the :guilabel:`Service` you wish to obtain currency rates from."
msgstr ""
"Ko so valute aktivirane, lahko izberete **samodejno** posodabljanje valutnih "
"tečajev ali pa to pustite na **ročno**. Za konfiguracijo posodabljanja "
"tečajev se vrnite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve --> Valute`, označite :guilabel:`Samodejni valutni tečaji`, "
"nastavite :guilabel:`Interval` na želeno frekvenco in nato kliknite na "
":guilabel:`Shrani`. Imate tudi možnost izbire :guilabel:`Storitve`, iz "
"katere želite pridobiti valutne tečaje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:40
msgid ""
"Click on the Update now button (:guilabel:`🗘`) besides the :guilabel:`Next "
"Run` field to update the currency rates manually."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na gumb Posodobi zdaj (:guilabel:`🗘`) poleg polja "
":guilabel:`Naslednji zagon`, da ročno posodobite valutne tečaje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:44
msgid "Create a new bank account"
msgstr "Ustvarite nov bančni račun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:46
msgid ""
"In the accounting application, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals` and create a new one. Enter a :guilabel:`Journal "
"Name` and set the :guilabel:`Type` to `Bank`. In the :guilabel:`Journal "
"Entries` tab, enter a **short code**, a **currency**, and then finally click "
"on the :guilabel:`Bank Account` field to create a new account. In the pop-up "
"window of the account creation, enter a name, a code (ex.: 550007), set its "
"type to `Bank and Cash`, set a currency type, and save. When you are back on "
"the **journal**, click on the :guilabel:`Account Number` field, and in the "
"pop-up window, fill out the :guilabel:`Account Number`, :guilabel:`Bank` of "
"your account, and save."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji za računovodstvo pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki` in ustvarite novega. Vnesite :guilabel:`Ime "
"dnevnika` in nastavite :guilabel:`Vrsta` na `Banka`. V zavihku "
":guilabel:`Vnosi dnevnika` vnesite **kratko kodo**, **valuto** in nato "
"končno kliknite na polje :guilabel:`Bančni račun`, da ustvarite nov račun. V "
"pojavnem oknu ustvarjanja računa vnesite ime, kodo (npr.: 550007), nastavite "
"vrsto na `Banka in gotovina`, nastavite vrsto valute in shranite. Ko ste "
"ponovno na **dnevniku**, kliknite na polje :guilabel:`Številka računa` in v "
"pojavnem oknu izpolnite :guilabel:`Številka računa`, :guilabel:`Banka` "
"vašega računa in shranite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:None
msgid "Example of a created bank journal."
msgstr "Primer ustvarjenega bančnega dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:59
msgid ""
"Upon creation of the journal, Odoo automatically links the bank account to "
"the journal. It can be found under :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Accounting: Chart of Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Po ustvaritvi dnevnika Odoo samodejno poveže bančni račun z dnevnikom. "
"Najdete ga lahko pod :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Računovodstvo: Kontni načrt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:63
msgid "Vendor bill in a foreign currency"
msgstr "Račun dobavitelja v tuji valuti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:65
msgid ""
"To pay a bill in a foreign currency, simply select the currency next to "
"the :guilabel:`Journal` field and register the payment. Odoo automatically "
"creates and posts the foreign **exchange gain or loss** as a new journal "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"Za plačilo računa v tuji valuti preprosto izberite valuto poleg polja "
":guilabel:`Dnevnik` in registrirajte plačilo. Odoo samodejno ustvari in "
"knjižil devizni **dobiček ali izgubo** kot nov dnevniški vnos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:None
msgid "How to set a bill currency."
msgstr "Kako nastaviti valuto računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:74
msgid ""
"Note that you can pay a foreign bill with another currency. In that case, "
"Odoo automatically converts between the two currencies."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko plačate tuji račun z drugo valuto. V tem primeru Odoo "
"samodejno pretvori med obema valutama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:78
msgid "Unrealized Currency Gains/Losses Report"
msgstr "Poročilo o nerealiziranih valutnih dobičkih/izgubah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:80
msgid ""
"This report gives an overview of all unrealized amounts in a foreign "
"currency on your balance sheet, and allows you to adjust an entry or "
"manually set an exchange rate. To access this report, go "
"to :menuselection:`Reporting --> Management: Unrealized Currency Gains/"
"Losses`. From here, you have access to all open entries in your **balance "
"sheet**."
msgstr ""
"To poročilo podaja pregled vseh nerealiziranih zneskov v tuji valuti v vaši "
"bilanci stanja in vam omogoča prilagoditev vnosa ali ročno nastavitev "
"menjalnega tečaja. Za dostop do tega poročila pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Poročanje --> Upravljanje: Nerealizirani valutni dobički/"
"izgube`. Od tu imate dostop do vseh odprtih vnosov v vaši **bilanci stanja**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:None
msgid "View of the Unrealized Gains/Losses journal."
msgstr "Pogled dnevnika nerealiziranih dobičkov/izgub."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:89
msgid ""
"If you wish to use a different currency rate than the one set "
"in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings --> "
"Currencies`, click the :guilabel:`Exchange Rates` button and change the rate "
"of the foreign currencies in the report."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti drug valutni tečaj od tistega, ki je nastavljen v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve --> Valute`, "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Menjavalni tečaji` in spremenite tečaj tujih valut "
"v poročilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:None
msgid "Menu to manually change exchange rates."
msgstr "Meni za ročno spreminjanje menjalnih tečajev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:97
msgid ""
"When manually changing **exchange rates**, a yellow banner appears allowing "
"you to reset back to Odoo's rate. To do so, simply click on :guilabel:`Reset "
"to Odoo's Rate`."
msgstr ""
"Pri ročnem spreminjanju **menjalnih tečajev** se prikaže rumeni pasic, ki "
"omogoča ponastavitev na Odoo tečaj. Za to preprosto kliknite "
":guilabel:`Ponastavi na Odoo tečaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:None
msgid "Banner to reset back to Odoo's rates."
msgstr "Pasic za ponastavitev na Odoo tečaje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:104
msgid ""
"In order to update your **balance sheet** with the amount of "
"the :guilabel:`adjustment` column, click on the :guilabel:`Adjustment Entry` "
"button. In the pop-up window, select "
"a :guilabel:`Journal`, :guilabel:`Expense Account` and :guilabel:`Income "
"Account` to calculate and process the **unrealized gains and losses**."
msgstr ""
"Za posodobitev **bilance stanja** z zneskom iz stolpca "
":guilabel:`prilagoditev` kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Vnos prilagoditve`. V "
"pojavnem oknu izberite :guilabel:`Dnevnik`, :guilabel:`Konto odhodkov` in "
":guilabel:`Konto prihodkov` za izračun in obdelavo **nerealiziranih dobičkov "
"in izgub**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:109
msgid ""
"You can set the date of the report in the :guilabel:`Date` field. Odoo "
"automatically reverses the booking entry to the date set "
"in :guilabel:`Reversal Date`."
msgstr ""
"Datum poročila lahko nastavite v polju :guilabel:`Datum`. Odoo samodejno "
"stornira knjiženje na datum, nastavljen v :guilabel:`Datum storna`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:112
msgid ""
"Once posted, the :guilabel:`adjustment` column should indicate `0.00`, "
"meaning all **unrealized gains/losses** have been adjusted."
msgstr ""
"Ko je knjiženje objavljeno, bi moral stolpec :guilabel:`prilagoditev` "
"prikazovati `0,00`, kar pomeni, da so bili vsi **nerealizirani dobički/"
"izgube** prilagojeni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/foreign_currency.rst:None
msgid "Unrealized Currency Gains/Losses report once adjusted."
msgstr "Poročilo o nerealiziranih valutnih dobičkih/izgubah po prilagoditvi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:3
msgid "Internal transfers"
msgstr "Interni prenosi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:5
msgid ""
"Internal money transfers can be handled in Odoo. At least two bank or cash "
"accounts are needed to make internal transfers."
msgstr ""
"Notranji prenosi denarja se lahko obravnavajo v Odoo. Za notranje prenose "
"sta potrebna vsaj dva bančna računa ali računa za gotovino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:9
msgid ":ref:`How to add an additional bank account <accounting/bank/create>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Kako dodati dodaten bančni račun <accounting/bank/create>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:14
msgid ""
"An internal transfer account is automatically created in your database based "
"on your company's :doc:`localization <../../fiscal_localizations>` and "
"depending on your country’s legislation. To modify the "
"default :guilabel:`Internal Transfer` account, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"down to the :guilabel:`Default Accounts` section."
msgstr ""
"Račun za notranje prenose je samodejno ustvarjen v vaši bazi podatkov na "
"podlagi :doc:`lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>` vašega podjetja in "
"glede na zakonodajo vaše države. Za spremembo privzetega računa "
":guilabel:`Notranji prenos` pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in se pomaknite navzdol do razdelka "
":guilabel:`Privzeti računi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:19
msgid ""
"While it is possible to manually :ref:`write off <accounting/reconciliation/"
"set-account>` internal transfers to this internal transfers account, it is "
"recommended to instead use the :guilabel:`Internal "
"Transfers` :doc:`reconciliation model <reconciliation_models>`. If "
"the :guilabel:`Internal Transfers` reconciliation model does not exist, "
"create it manually:"
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je mogoče :ref:`odpisati <accounting/reconciliation/set-account>` "
"interne prenose na ta račun internih prenosov ročno, priporočamo, da namesto "
"tega uporabite :guilabel:`Interni prenosi` :doc:`model uskladitve "
"<reconciliation_models>`. Če :guilabel:`Interni prenosi` model uskladitve ne "
"obstaja, ga ustvarite ročno:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:24
msgid ""
":ref:`Create a new reconciliation model <accounting/rec-models/config>`, and "
"fill in the :guilabel:`Name` field (e.g., `Internal Transfers`)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Ustvarite nov model uskladitve <accounting/rec-models/config>` in "
"izpolnite polje :guilabel:`Naziv` (npr. `Interni prenosi`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:26
msgid ""
"Do not select specific :ref:`matching conditions <accounting/rec-models/"
"conditions>`, and leave the model set to :guilabel:`Manual` to ensure the "
"model is available to be selected for all transactions."
msgstr ""
"Ne izbirajte določenih :ref:`pogojev ujemanja <accounting/rec-models/"
"conditions>` in pustite model nastavljen na :guilabel:`Ročno`, da "
"zagotovite, da je model na voljo za izbiro pri vseh transakcijah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:29
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Counterpart Items` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Postavke nasprotne strani` kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"vrstico`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:30
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Account` to the internal transfer account (the specific "
"account name and code vary by localization)."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite :guilabel:`Račun` na račun internega prenosa (specifično ime in "
"koda računa se razlikujeta glede na lokalizacijo)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:32
msgid ""
"Leave the :guilabel:`Amount Type` and :guilabel:`Amount` as their default "
"values of :guilabel:`Percentage of balance` and :guilabel:`100`."
msgstr ""
"Pustite :guilabel:`Vrsta zneska` in :guilabel:`Znesek` pri njunih privzetih "
"vrednostih :guilabel:`Odstotek stanja` in :guilabel:`100`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:34
msgid ""
"Add a :guilabel:`Label` to identify transactions that are matched using this "
"reconciliation model (e.g., `Internal Transfers`)."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte :guilabel:`Oznako`, da identificirate transakcije, ki so usklajene z "
"uporabo tega modela uskladitve (npr. `Interni prenosi`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:38
msgid "Register an internal transfer from one bank to another"
msgstr "Registriranje notranjega prenosa iz ene banke v drugo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:40
msgid ""
"When money is transferred from one bank or cash account to another, that "
"amount appears as two transactions on the corresponding journals, whether "
"the transactions are created manually, via import, or via :doc:`bank "
"synchronization <bank_synchronization>`. When :ref:`reconciling the "
"transaction <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>`, select "
"the :guilabel:`Internal Transfers` :doc:`reconciliation model "
"<reconciliation_models>` button. This action writes the transaction off to "
"the :guilabel:`Internal Transfer` account."
msgstr ""
"Ko je denar prenesen iz enega bančnega ali gotovinskega računa na drugega, "
"se ta znesek prikaže kot dve transakciji na ustreznih dnevnikih, ne glede na "
"to, ali so transakcije ustvarjene ročno, z uvozom ali prek :doc:`bančne "
"sinhronizacije <bank_synchronization>`. Pri :ref:`uskladitvi transakcije "
"<accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` izberite gumb :guilabel:`Interni "
"prenosi` :doc:`model uskladitve <reconciliation_models>`. To dejanje odpiše "
"transakcijo na račun :guilabel:`Interni prenos`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:48
msgid ""
"Remember to reconcile both the outgoing transaction (on the journal that "
"sends the payment) and the incoming transaction (on the journal that "
"receives the payment) with the internal transfers account using "
"the :guilabel:`Internal Transfers` reconciliation model button."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite uskladiti tako odhodne transakcije (v dnevniku, ki pošlje "
"plačilo) kot dohodne transakcije (v dnevniku, ki prejme plačilo) z računom "
"internih prenosov z uporabo gumba modela uskladitve :guilabel:`Interni "
"prenosi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:52
msgid ""
"Once each bank journal's transaction is reconciled using "
"the :guilabel:`Internal Transfers` reconciliation model, the internal "
"transfer account is balanced, and the balances of both bank accounts are "
"updated to reflect the transfer."
msgstr ""
"Ko je transakcija vsakega bančnega dnevnika usklajena z uporabo modela "
"uskladitve :guilabel:`Interni prenosi`, je račun internega prenosa "
"uravnotežen in stanja obeh bančnih računov so posodobljena tako, da odražajo "
"prenos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:57
msgid ""
"When transferring $1,000 from Bank Account A to Bank Account B, each of the "
"two bank journals has one journal entry:"
msgstr ""
"Pri prenosu 1.000 $ z Bančnega računa A na Bančni račun B ima vsak od dveh "
"bančnih dnevnikov en dnevniški zapis:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:60
msgid "The outgoing transaction in the Bank Account A journal:"
msgstr "Odhodna transakcija v dnevniku Bančnega računa A:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:66
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:83
msgid "**Account**"
msgstr "**Konto**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:67
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:68
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:82
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:99
msgid "**Debit**"
msgstr "**Breme**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/internal_transfers.rst:68
