"click the :guilabel:`x to reconcile` button to display only unreconciled "
"transactions. To include previously reconciled transactions, remove "
"the :guilabel:`Not Matched` filter from the search bar."
msgstr ""
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`x za uskladitev`, da prikažete samo neusklajene "
"transakcije. Če želite vključiti prej usklajene transakcije, odstranite "
"filter :guilabel:`Ni ujemanja` iz iskalne vrstice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:None
msgid "Reaching the bank reconciliation tool from the accounting dashboard"
msgstr ""
"Dostop do orodja za uskladitev bančnih izpiskov z nadzorne plošče "
"računovodstva"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:40
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Bank Matching` view is composed of lines for each transaction "
"of the journal with the newest displayed first. Each transaction has a date, "
"a label, a partner (if set), :ref:`action buttons <accounting/reconciliation/"
"action-buttons>`, and the transaction amount. Each line has additional "
"actions available through the :icon:`oi-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Pogled :guilabel:`Ujemanje bank` je sestavljen iz vrstic za vsako "
"transakcijo dnevnika, pri čemer so najnovejše prikazane prve. Vsaka "
"transakcija ima datum, oznako, partnerja (če je nastavljen), :ref:`gumbe za "
"dejanja <accounting/reconciliation/action-buttons>` in znesek transakcije. "
"Vsaka vrstica ima dodatna dejanja na voljo prek gumba :icon:`oi-ellipsis-v` "
":guilabel:`(tri pike)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:None
msgid "The user interface of the bank matching view of a bank journal."
msgstr "Uporabniški vmesnik pogleda bančnega ujemanja bančnega dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:49
msgid ""
"Once a :doc:`transaction <transactions>` is reconciled, the suggested action "
"button(s) is replaced with the counterpart entry/entries it was matched with "
"or the account(s) it was written off to."
msgstr ""
"Ko je :doc:`transakcija <transactions>` usklajena, se predlagani gumb(i) "
"dejanja nadomesti z vnosom/vnosi nasprotne strani, s katerim je bil "
"usklajen, ali z računom/računi, na katerega je bil odpisan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:56
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avalara_portal.rst:32
msgid "Transactions"
msgstr "Transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:58
msgid ""
"Every :doc:`transaction <transactions>` is linked to a journal entry that "
"debits/credits the journal's main account and its suspense account until it "
"is fully reconciled. At that point, the suspense account is replaced with "
"the account of the counterpart item or, in the case of :ref:`manual matching "
"<accounting/reconciliation/set-account>`, the selected account."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka :doc:`transakcija <transactions>` je povezana z dnevniškim vnosom, ki "
"bremeni/odobri glavni račun dnevnika in njegov prehodnega račun, dokler ni v "
"celoti usklajen. Na tej točki se prehodnega račun zamenja z računom "
"nasprotnega postavke ali, v primeru :ref:`ročnega ujemanja <accounting/"
"reconciliation/set-account>`, z izbranim računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:64
msgid ""
":ref:`Duplicate transactions <accounting/bank-synchronization/duplicate-"
"transactions>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Podvojene transakcije <accounting/bank-synchronization/duplicate-"
"transactions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:65
msgid ""
":ref:`Missing transactions <accounting/bank-synchronization/missing-"
"transactions>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Manjkajoče transakcije <accounting/bank-synchronization/missing-"
"transactions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:70
msgid "Possible actions"
msgstr "Možna dejanja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:72
msgid ""
"Depending on the transaction, up to two suggested actions are available as "
"buttons while other actions can be accessed by clicking the :icon:`oi-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` button:"
msgstr ""
"Glede na transakcijo sta na voljo do dve predlagani dejanji kot gumba, "
"medtem ko je do drugih dejanj mogoče dostopati s klikom na gumb :icon:`oi-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(tri pike)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:75
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Set Partner`: Open a search view to add a partner to the "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nastavi partnerja`: odpre iskalni pogled za dodajanje partnerja k "
"transakciji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Set Account`: Open a search view to manually select an account to "
"write off the full amount of the transaction with this account. If "
"necessary, :ref:`edit the line <accounting/reconciliation/edit>` to change "
"the amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nastavi račun`: odpre iskalni pogled za ročno izbiro računa, na "
"katerega se odpiše celoten znesek transakcije. Po potrebi :ref:`uredite "
"vrstico <accounting/reconciliation/edit>`, da spremenite znesek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Receivable`: Write off the transaction to the receivable account "
"of the partner."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Terjatve`: odpiše transakcijo na račun terjatev partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales`: Open a list view of sales orders belonging to the "
"transaction's :guilabel:`Partner` (or proceed directly to the form view if "
"only one relevant sales order exists). Select the relevant sales order(s) "
"and click :guilabel:`Create Invoices`, then return to the :guilabel:`Bank "
"Matching` view and match the invoice(s) using the :guilabel:`Reconcile` "
"action button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prodaja`: odpre seznamski pogled prodajnih nalogov, ki pripadajo "
":guilabel:`Partnerju` transakcije (ali neposredno nadaljuje v pogled "
"obrazca, če obstaja samo en ustrezni prodajni nalog). Izberite ustrezne "
"prodajne naloge in kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari račune`, nato se vrnite v "
"pogled :guilabel:`Bančno ujemanje` in uskladite račun(e) z gumbom dejanja "
":guilabel:`Uskladi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payable`: Write off the transaction to the payable account of the "
"partner."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Plačljivo`: Odpišite transakcijo na plačljiv račun partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reconcile`: Open a search view of existing items from records "
"such as customer invoices, vendor bills, and payments. Select one or "
"multiple items to add counterpart items with the corresponding accounts of "
"those items."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uskladi`: Odprite iskalni pogled obstoječih postavk iz zapisov, "
"kot so računi strankam, računi dobaviteljev in plačila. Izberite eno ali več "
"postavk, da dodate nasprotne postavke z ustreznimi računi teh postavk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Batches`: Open a short list of :doc:`batch payments <../payments/"
"batch>`. To view all batch payments, click :guilabel:`Search More ...`. "
"Select a batch payment to add a counterpart item for each payment of the "
"batch with the corresponding account of each payment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Serije`: Odprite kratek seznam :doc:`serijskih plačil <../"
"payments/batch>`. Za ogled vseh serijskih plačil kliknite :guilabel:`Iskanje "
"več ...`. Izberite serijo plačil, da dodate nasprotno postavko za vsako "
"plačilo v seriji z ustreznim računom vsakega plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:92
msgid ""
":doc:`reconciliation_models`: Each manual reconciliation model that could "
"apply to the transaction is displayed. Click the reconciliation model's "
"action button to generate the counterpart items defined on the "
"reconciliation model."
msgstr ""
":doc:`reconciliation_models`: Prikazan je vsak ročni model usklajevanja, ki "
"bi se lahko uporabil za transakcijo. Kliknite gumb akcije modela "
"usklajevanja, da ustvarite nasprotne postavke, določene v modelu "
"usklajevanja."

