"nasprotnem primeru uskladite transakcije ročno tako, da sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:136
msgid ""
"Expand the desired line among unmatched bank transactions to display all "
"available action buttons."
msgstr ""
"Razširite želeno vrstico med neusklajenim bančnimi transakcijami, da "
"prikažete vse razpoložljive gumbe akcij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:138
msgid ""
"Define the counterpart. There are several options for defining a "
"counterpart, including :ref:`matching existing items <accounting/"
"reconciliation/existing-items>`, :ref:`manually setting the account "
"<accounting/reconciliation/set-account>`, matching with :doc:`batch payments "
"<../payments/batch>`, and using :ref:`reconciliation model buttons "
"<accounting/reconciliation/model>`."
msgstr ""
"Določite protikonto. Na voljo je več možnosti za določitev protikonta, "
"vključno z :ref:`usklajevanjem obstoječih postavk <accounting/reconciliation/"
"existing-items>`, :ref:`ročnim nastavljanjem konta <accounting/"
"reconciliation/set-account>`, usklajevanjem s :doc:`paketnimi plačili <../"
"payments/batch>` in uporabo :ref:`gumbov modelov usklajevanja <accounting/"
"reconciliation/model>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:143
msgid ""
"If the resulting entry is not fully balanced, add another existing "
"counterpart item or write it off by :ref:`setting the account <accounting/"
"reconciliation/set-account>` of the remaining amount."
msgstr ""
"Če nastali vnos ni v celoti uravnotežen, dodajte še eno obstoječo postavko "
"protikonta ali ga odpišite z :ref:`nastavitvijo konta <accounting/"
"reconciliation/set-account>` za preostali znesek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:150
msgid "Existing items"
msgstr "Obstoječe postavke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:152
msgid ""
"To reconcile transactions with existing items related to records such as "
"customer invoices, vendor bills, and payments, click "
"the :guilabel:`Reconcile` action button, select the matching journal item(s) "
"in the list, and click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""
"Za usklajevanje transakcij z obstoječimi postavkami, povezanimi z zapisi, "
"kot so računi strankam, računi dobaviteljev in plačila, kliknite gumb "
"dejanja :guilabel:`Uskladi`, na seznamu izberite ustrezno postavko dnevnika "
"(ali več njih) in kliknite :guilabel:`Izberi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:157
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Partner` is set, this list is automatically filtered to "
"only include items related to that partner."
msgstr ""
"Če je nastavljen :guilabel:`Partner`, je ta seznam samodejno filtriran tako, "
"da vključuje samo postavke, povezane s tem partnerjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:161
msgid ""
"Use the search bar within the :guilabel:`Search: Journal Items to Match` "
"window to search for specific journal items."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite iskalno vrstico v oknu :guilabel:`Iskanje: Postavke dnevnika za "
"ujemanje`, da poiščete določene postavke dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:164
msgid ""
"If a transaction amount is lower than the invoice or bill it is reconciled "
"with, the transaction is fully reconciled, but the difference remains open "
"on the counterpart item. The remaining amount can be left open to be "
"reconciled later or the invoice or bill can be marked as fully paid. To mark "
"the invoice or bill as fully paid, :ref:`edit <accounting/reconciliation/"
"edit>` the line, click :guilabel:`fully paid`, and :guilabel:`Save`. To "
"reverse this, :ref:`edit <accounting/reconciliation/edit>` the line again, "
"click :guilabel:`partial payment`, and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Če je znesek transakcije nižji od računa ali dobaviteljevega računa, s "
"katerim je usklajen, je transakcija v celoti usklajena, vendar razlika na "
"postavki protikonta ostane odprta. Preostali znesek lahko ostane odprt za "
"kasnejše usklajevanje ali pa je račun lahko označen kot v celoti plačan. Za "
"označitev računa kot v celoti plačan :ref:`uredite <accounting/"
"reconciliation/edit>` vrstico, kliknite :guilabel:`v celoti plačano` in "
":guilabel:`Shrani`. Za razveljavitev tega postopka :ref:`uredite <accounting/"
"reconciliation/edit>` vrstico znova, kliknite :guilabel:`delno plačilo` in "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:172
msgid ""
"If a transaction amount is greater than the invoice or bill it is reconciled "
"with, the transaction is only partially reconciled. The remaining balance "
"can be reconciled as any other transaction amount."
msgstr ""
"Če je znesek transakcije večji od računa, s katerim je usklajen, je "
"transakcija samo delno usklajena. Preostalo stanje lahko uskladite kot "
"katerikoli drug znesek transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:177
msgid ""
"Existing items of draft entries can be matched. Eventual automatic moves "
"(like currency exchange or cash basis moves) are created in draft "
"simultaneously with the reconciliation. Posting the original entry also "
"posts the automatic move."
msgstr ""
"Obstoječe postavke osnutkov vnosov je mogoče uskladiti. Morebitne samodejne "
"knjižbe (kot so knjižbe menjave valut ali gotovinskega načela) se ustvarijo "
"v osnutku hkrati z usklajevanjem. Knjiženje izvirnega vnosa hkrati knjiži "
"tudi samodejno knjižbo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:184
msgid "Set account"
msgstr "Nastavi konto"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:186
msgid ""
"If no existing item matches the selected transaction, you can still write "
"off the transaction manually: Click :guilabel:`Set Account`, then choose the "
"appropriate account. To write off only part of the transaction, :ref:`edit "
"the line <accounting/reconciliation/edit>` to reflect the correct value and "
"reconcile the remaining amount as desired."
msgstr ""
"Če nobena obstoječa postavka ne ustreza izbrani transakciji, lahko "
"transakcijo še vedno odpišete ročno: kliknite :guilabel:`Nastavi konto`, "
"nato izberite ustrezen konto. Za odpis samo dela transakcije :ref:`uredite "
"vrstico <accounting/reconciliation/edit>`, da odraža pravilno vrednost, in "
"uskladite preostali znesek po želji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:192
msgid ""
"If the partner is set, write the amount off to their receivable or payable "
"account directly by clicking the :guilabel:`Receivable` "
"or :guilabel:`Payable` :ref:`action button <accounting/reconciliation/action-"
"buttons>`."
msgstr ""
"Če je partner nastavljen, odpišite znesek neposredno na njegov konto "
"terjatev ali obveznosti s klikom na gumb dejanja :guilabel:`Terjatve` ali "
":guilabel:`Obveznosti` :ref:` <accounting/reconciliation/action-buttons>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:199
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:3
msgid "Reconciliation models"
msgstr "Modeli usklajevanja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:201
msgid ""
"Use :doc:`reconciliation models <reconciliation_models>` to create custom "
"rules that can be applied automatically or manually via custom buttons for "
"operations that are frequently repeated. These custom buttons allow you to "
"quickly reconcile bank transactions manually and can also be combined with "
"other reconciliation models and with counterpart items when reconciling "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite :doc:`modele usklajevanja <reconciliation_models>`, da ustvarite "
"pravila po meri, ki se lahko uporabijo samodejno ali ročno prek gumbov po "
"meri za operacije, ki se pogosto ponavljajo. Ti gumbi po meri vam omogočajo "
"hitro ročno usklajevanje bančnih transakcij in jih je mogoče kombinirati "
"tudi z drugimi modeli usklajevanja in s postavkami protikonta pri "
"usklajevanju transakcij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:207
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:141
msgid ""
"An outgoing bank transaction for $103 is partially matched with a vendor "
"bill for $100, leaving $3 of the transaction still unreconciled. Use "
"the :guilabel:`Bank Fees` reconciliation model to create a new counterpart "
"item for $3 and reconcile it with the remaining $3 of the bank transaction."
msgstr ""
"Odhodna bančna transakcija za 103 $ je delno usklajena z dobaviteljevim "
"računom za 100 $, pri čemer 3 $ transakcije ostanejo neusklajeni. Uporabite "
"model usklajevanja :guilabel:`Bančne provizije`, da ustvarite novo postavko "
"protikonta za 3 $ in jo uskladite s preostalimi 3 $ bančne transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:215
msgid "Edit lines and unreconcile transactions"
msgstr "Urejanje vrstic in razveljavitev usklajevanja transakcij"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:217
msgid ""
"To edit a counterpart item, expand the line, click the :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon, and edit the necessary fields "
"in :guilabel:`Edit Line` window."
msgstr ""
"Za urejanje postavke protikonta razširite vrstico, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(svinčnik)` in uredite potrebna polja v oknu "
":guilabel:`Uredi vrstico`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:221
msgid ""
"When the counterpart item is an existing journal item, some fields are read-"
"only."
msgstr ""
"Ko je postavka protikonta obstoječa postavka dnevnika, so nekatera polja "
"samo za branje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:223
msgid ""
"If a transaction is partially matched with a counterpart item, use the link "
"to mark the invoice as :guilabel:`fully paid` or to switch back to "
"a :guilabel:`partial payment`."
msgstr ""
"Če je transakcija delno usklajena s postavko protikonta, uporabite povezavo "
"za označitev računa kot :guilabel:`v celoti plačan` ali za vrnitev na "
":guilabel:`delno plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:226
msgid ""
"To unreconcile a transaction, delete all counterpart items associated with "
"the transaction by clicking on the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Za razveljavitev usklajevanja transakcije izbrišite vse postavke protikonta, "
"povezane s transakcijo, tako da kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`"
"(koš)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:232
msgid "Netting"
msgstr "Mreža"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:234
msgid ""
"Netting (also known as AP/AR offsetting) is the process of balancing "
"incoming debts from and outgoing debts to the same partner. Reconciling the "
"incoming and outgoing debts creates a new journal entry that balances the "
"debts. Two main scenarios exist:"
msgstr ""
"Pobotanje (znano tudi kot izravnava AP/AR) je postopek uravnoteženja "
"dohodnih dolgov od in odhodnih dolgov do istega partnerja. Uskladitev "
"dohodnih in odhodnih dolgov ustvari nov dnevniški zapis, ki uravnoteži "
"dolgove. Obstajata dva glavna scenarija:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:238
msgid ""
":ref:`A bank transaction balances <accounting/reconciliation/net-"
"transaction>` (either fully or partially) the incoming and outgoing debts."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Bančna transakcija uravnoteži <accounting/reconciliation/net-"
"transaction>` (bodisi v celoti bodisi delno) dohodne in odhodne dolgove."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:240
msgid ""
":ref:`No bank transaction balances <accounting/reconciliation/net-no-"
"transaction>` the incoming and outgoing debts. This situation can occur "
"either when the debts balance each other completely or when the debts remain "
"unbalanced."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Nobena bančna transakcija ne uravnoteži <accounting/reconciliation/net-"
"no-transaction>` dohodnih in odhodnih dolgov. Ta situacija se lahko pojavi "
"bodisi, ko se dolgovi popolnoma uravnotežijo med seboj, bodisi ko dolgovi "
"ostanejo neuravnoteženi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:247
msgid "Netting with bank transactions"
msgstr "Pobotanje z bančnimi transakcijami"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:249
msgid ""
"When a bank transaction balances (either fully or partially) the incoming "
"and outgoing debts, reconcile the bank transaction from the :guilabel:`Bank "
"Matching` view like any other :ref:`existing items <accounting/"
"reconciliation/existing-items>`:"
msgstr ""
"Ko bančna transakcija uravnoteži (bodisi v celoti bodisi delno) dohodne in "
"odhodne dolgove, uskladite bančno transakcijo iz pogleda :guilabel:`Ujemanje "
"bank` kot katero koli drugo :ref:`obstoječo postavko <accounting/"
"reconciliation/existing-items>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:253
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Reconcile` on the transaction."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Uskladi` pri transakciji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:254
msgid ""
"Select all the relevant counterpart items on both the payable and receivable "
"side."
msgstr ""
"Izberite vse ustrezne protiknjižbe na strani obveznosti do dobaviteljev in "
"terjatev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:255
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Izberi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:256
msgid ""
"If a balance remains, depending on the details, the following situations are "
"possible:"
msgstr "Če ostane stanje, so glede na podrobnosti možne naslednje situacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:258
msgid ""
"An invoice, bill, or other item is not fully reconciled, and the remaining "
"balance can be :ref:`reconciled <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` with "
"other bank transactions."
msgstr ""
"Račun, dobaviteljski račun ali druga postavka niso v celoti usklajeni in "
"preostalo stanje je mogoče :ref:`uskladiti <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` z drugimi bančnimi transakcijami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:260
msgid ""
"The bank transaction itself is not fully reconciled, and the remaining "
"balance can be :ref:`reconciled <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` as in "
"any other situation."
msgstr ""
"Bančna transakcija sama ni v celoti usklajena in preostalo stanje je mogoče "
":ref:`uskladiti <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` kot v kateri koli "
"drugi situaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:266
msgid "Netting without bank transactions"
msgstr "Pobotanje brez bančnih transakcij"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:268
msgid ""
"When no bank transaction balances the incoming and outgoing debts, there is "
"nothing to reconcile from the :guilabel:`Bank Matching` view. However, the "
"debt amount is visible in both the account receivable and the account "
"payable. To balance these debts so that they no longer appear on the partner "
"ledger, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Ko nobena bančna transakcija ne uravnoteži dohodnih in odhodnih dolgov, ni "
"ničesar za uskladitev v pogledu :guilabel:`Ujemanje bank`. Vendar je znesek "
"dolga viden tako na računu terjatev kot na računu obveznosti do "
"dobaviteljev. Sledite tem korakom, da uravnotežite te dolgove, tako da se "
"več ne pojavljajo na knjigi partnerja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:273
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Reconcile`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Uskladi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:274
msgid ""
"Select the journal items that debit or credit the account receivable and "
"account payable and represent the debts to be netted."
msgstr ""
"Izberite dnevniške postavke, ki bremeni ali odobri račun terjatev in "
"obveznosti do dobaviteljev ter predstavljajo dolgove, ki jih je treba "
"pobotati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:276
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:279
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Reconcile`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Uskladi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:277
msgid ""
"If the debts don't balance each other perfectly, a :guilabel:`Write-Off "
"Entry` popup window appears, allowing you to decide how to resolve the "
"remaining balance:"
msgstr ""
"Če dolgovi niso popolnoma uravnoteženi, se prikazno pojavno okno "
":guilabel:`Vpis odpisa`, ki vam omogoča odločitev, kako razrešiti preostalo "
"stanje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:280
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Allow partials` to only partially reconcile the account "
"receivable and account payable and leave the remaining balance open."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Dovoli delne`, da delno uskladite račun terjatev in "
"obveznosti do dobaviteljev ter pustite preostalo stanje odprto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:282
msgid ""
"Use a :doc:`reconciliation model button <reconciliation_models>` to write "
"off the balance."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite :doc:`gumb modela uskladitve <reconciliation_models>`, da odpišete "
"stanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:283
msgid ""
"Manually choose an :guilabel:`Account`, and optionally adjust "
"the :guilabel:`Tax`, :guilabel:`Journal`, :guilabel:`Label`, :guilabel:`Date`, "
"and :guilabel:`To Check` fields."
msgstr ""
"Ročno izberite :guilabel:`Račun` in po želji prilagodite polja "
":guilabel:`DDV`, :guilabel:`Dnevnik`, :guilabel:`Oznaka`, :guilabel:`Datum` "
"in :guilabel:`Za preveriti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:286
msgid ""
"The items are then matched, and their balance is removed from the partner "
"ledger, representing that no payment is due for these debts."
msgstr ""
"Postavke se nato uskladijo, njihov saldo pa je odstranjen iz knjige "
"partnerja, kar pomeni, da za te dolgove ni treba plačati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation.rst:290
msgid ""
"The workflow is the same whether there are only two equal debts in the "
"receivable and payable accounts or multiple debts in each account."
msgstr ""
"Potek dela je enak, ne glede na to, ali sta v kontih terjatev in obveznosti "
"samo dva enaka dolga ali več dolgov v vsakem kontu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:5
msgid ""
"Reconciliation models are custom rules that complement the :ref:`default set "
"of matching rules <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` and enable more "
"advanced automation of the :doc:`bank reconciliation <reconciliation>` "
"process. These models are especially useful when dealing with recurring "
"flows like writing off bank fees or :doc:`cash discounts <../"
"customer_invoices/cash_discounts>`."
msgstr ""
"Modeli usklajevanja so pravila po meri, ki dopolnjujejo :ref:`privzeti nabor "
"pravil za ujemanje <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` in omogočajo bolj "
"napredno avtomatizacijo procesa :doc:`usklajevanja bančnih izpiskov "
"<reconciliation>`. Ti modeli so še posebej uporabni pri obravnavi "
"ponavljajočih se tokov, kot so odpis bančnih provizij ali :doc:`popusti pri "
"plačilu v gotovini <../customer_invoices/cash_discounts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:12
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Reconciliation models <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"reconciliation-models-6858>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Vodniki Odoo: Modeli usklajevanja <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"reconciliation-models-6858>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:19
msgid ""
"To access reconciliation models, go to the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, "
"click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(dropdown menu)` menu on the bank "
"journal, and select :guilabel:`Models` under the :guilabel:`Reconciliation` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dostopati do modelov usklajevanja, pojdite na :guilabel:`Nadzorna "
"plošča`, kliknite meni :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(spustni meni)` na "
"bančnem dnevniku in izberite :guilabel:`Modeli` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Usklajevanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:23
msgid "To create a new reconciliation model, click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr "Če želite ustvariti nov model usklajevanja, kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:25
msgid ""
"Reconciliation models can be either :guilabel:`Manual` "
"or :guilabel:`Automated`. Manual reconciliation models appear "
"as :ref:`possible action buttons <accounting/reconciliation/action-buttons>` "
"when :doc:`reconciling <reconciliation>`. Automatic reconciliation models "
"apply automatically to transactions that meet the reconciliation "
"model's :ref:`matching conditions <accounting/rec-models/conditions>`."
msgstr ""
"Modeli usklajevanja so lahko :guilabel:`Ročni` ali :guilabel:`Samodejni`. "
"Ročni modeli usklajevanja se pojavijo kot :ref:`gumbi za možne ukrepe "
"<accounting/reconciliation/action-buttons>` pri :doc:`usklajevanju "
"<reconciliation>`. Samodejni modeli usklajevanja se samodejno uporabijo za "
"transakcije, ki izpolnjujejo :ref:`pogoje ujemanja <accounting/rec-models/"
"conditions>` modela usklajevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:31
msgid ""
"Each reconciliation model is configured with :ref:`matching conditions "
"<accounting/rec-models/conditions>` to identify the relevant bank "
"transactions and :ref:`Counterpart Items <accounting/rec-models/"
"counterpart>` to be generated during reconciliation."
msgstr ""
"Vsak model usklajevanja je konfiguriran s :ref:`pogoji ujemanja <accounting/"
"rec-models/conditions>`, ki identificirajo ustrezne bančne transakcije, in "
":ref:`protikonta <accounting/rec-models/counterpart>`, ki se ustvarijo med "
"usklajevanjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:36
msgid ""
"To create an activity on the transaction, select which type of activity to "
"create in the :guilabel:`Next Activity` field."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti aktivnost na transakciji, v polju :guilabel:`Naslednja "
"aktivnost` izberite vrsto aktivnosti, ki jo želite ustvariti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:40
msgid ""
"If a record matches with several *automated* reconciliation models, the "
"first one in the sequence of models is applied. Rearrange the order by "
"dragging and dropping the :icon:`oi-draggable` :guilabel:`(handle)` icon "
"next to the name."
msgstr ""
"Če zapis ustreza več *avtomatiziranim* modelom uskladitve, se uporabi prvi v "
"zaporedju modelov. Preuredite vrstni red z vlečenjem in spuščanjem ikone "
":icon:`oi-draggable` :guilabel:`(ročica)` ob imenu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:0
msgid "Rearrange the sequence of models in the list view."
msgstr "Preurejanje zaporedja modelov v pogledu seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:50
msgid "Matching conditions"
msgstr "Pogoji ujemanja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:52
msgid ""
"A reconciliation model's matching conditions determine to which transactions "
"it applies."
msgstr ""
"Pogoji ujemanja modela usklajevanja določajo, za katere transakcije se "
"uporablja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:54
msgid ""
"The following fields can be used to restrict the reconciliation model's "
"availability to transactions that meet the conditions:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednja polja se lahko uporabijo za omejitev razpoložljivosti modela "
"usklajevanja na transakcije, ki izpolnjujejo pogoje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:57
msgid ":guilabel:`Journals`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Dnevniki`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:58
msgid ":guilabel:`Partners`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Partnerji`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount`: Select :guilabel:`Is lower than or equal "
"to`, :guilabel:`Is greater than or equal to`, or :guilabel:`Is between` and "
"enter the amount(s)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Znesek`: Izberite :guilabel:`Je nižji ali enak`, :guilabel:`Je "
"višji ali enak` ali :guilabel:`Je med` in vnesite znesek(-ke)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:61
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Label`: Select :guilabel:`Contains`, :guilabel:`Not Contains`, "
"or :guilabel:`Match Regex` and enter the transaction label's matching "
"condition."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oznaka`: Izberite :guilabel:`Vsebuje`, :guilabel:`Ne vsebuje` ali "
":guilabel:`Ujemanje z regularnim izrazom` in vnesite pogoj ujemanja oznake "
"transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:65
msgid ""
"`Regular expressions <https://regexone.com/>`_, often abbreviated as "
"**regex**, can be used in Odoo in various ways to search, validate, and "
"manipulate data. Regex can be powerful but also complex, so it's essential "
"to use it judiciously."
msgstr ""
"`Regularni izrazi <https://regexone.com/>`_, pogosto okrajšani kot "
"**regex**, se lahko v Odoo uporabljajo na različne načine za iskanje, "
"preverjanje in manipulacijo s podatki. Regex je lahko močan, vendar tudi "
"zapleten, zato ga je pomembno uporabljati preudarno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:69
msgid ""
"To use regular expressions in a reconciliation model, set "
"the :guilabel:`Label` to :guilabel:`Match Regex` and add an expression. Odoo "
"automatically retrieves the transactions that match the regex expression and "
"the conditions specified in the reconciliation model."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti regularne izraze v modelu usklajevanja, nastavite "
":guilabel:`Oznaka` na :guilabel:`Ujemanje z regularnim izrazom` in dodajte "
"izraz. Odoo samodejno pridobi transakcije, ki se ujemajo z izrazom regex in "
"pogoji, določenimi v modelu usklajevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:74
msgid ""
"A transaction must meet all conditions for the reconciliation model to be "
"available for it. If no condition is defined (i.e., if all fields are left "
"blank), the reconciliation model will be available for all transactions."
msgstr ""
"Transakcija mora izpolnjevati vse pogoje, da je model usklajevanja na voljo "
"zanjo. Če pogoj ni določen (tj. če so vsa polja prazna), bo model "
"usklajevanja na voljo za vse transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:81
msgid "Counterpart items"
msgstr "Postavke protiknjižb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:83
msgid ""
"Each line in the :guilabel:`Counterpart items` tab creates a journal item "
"with the specified details:"
msgstr ""
"Vsaka vrstica v zavihku :guilabel:`Postavke protiknjižb` ustvari knjižbo s "
"podanimi podatki:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partner`: Select the partner, if any, to set on the journal item."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Partner`: Izberite partnerja, če obstaja, ki bo nastavljen na "
"knjižbi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account`: Select the account, if any, to set on the journal item."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Konto`: Izberite konto, če obstaja, ki bo nastavljen na knjižbi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount Type`: Select how the amount of the journal item should be "
"calculated:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta zneska`: Izberite, kako naj se izračuna znesek knjižbe:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:90
msgid ":guilabel:`Fixed`: Use a fixed amount."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Fiksno`: Uporabi fiksni znesek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Percentage of balance`: Use a percentage of the remaining balance "
"of the transaction, regardless of the transaction total."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Odstotek salda`: Uporabi odstotek preostalega salda transakcije "
"ne glede na skupni znesek transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Percentage of statement line`: Use a percentage of the "
"transaction total, regardless of the remaining balance of the transaction."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Odstotek vrstice izpiska`: Uporabi odstotek skupnega zneska "
"transakcije ne glede na preostali saldo transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`From label`: Use a percentage from the transaction's label using "
"regex."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Iz oznake`: Uporabi odstotek iz oznake transakcije z uporabo "
"regularnega izraza."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:97
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount`: Enter the amount to be used on the journal item. This "
"field will be either a fixed amount, percentage amount, or regex depending "
"on the :guilabel:`Account Type`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Znesek`: Vnesite znesek, ki bo uporabljen na knjižbi. To polje bo "
"bodisi fiksni znesek, odstotni znesek ali regularni izraz, odvisno od "
":guilabel:`Vrste konta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Taxes`: Select a tax, if any, to set on the journal item. This "
"field is hidden behind the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(settings "
"adjust)` icon by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Davki`: Izberite davek, če obstaja, ki bo nastavljen na knjižbi. "
"To polje je privzeto skrito za ikono :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`"
"(prilagoditve nastavitev)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Analytic`: Select an analytic distribution, if any, to set on the "
"journal item."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Analitika`: Izberite analitično porazdelitev, če obstaja, ki bo "
"nastavljena na knjižbi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:102
msgid ":guilabel:`Label`: Enter a label, if any, to set on the journal item."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oznaka`: Vnesite oznako, če obstaja, ki bo nastavljena na knjižbi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:105
msgid ""
"While neither the :guilabel:`Partner` nor :guilabel:`Account` fields are "
"mandatory, at least one of the two must be set for the reconciliation model "
"to work correctly."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav niti polje :guilabel:`Partner` niti :guilabel:`Konto` nista obvezni, "
"mora biti nastavljena vsaj ena od njiju, da model usklajevanja deluje "
"pravilno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:107
msgid ""
"The reconciliation model can be used for :ref:`partner mapping <accounting/"
"rec-models/partner>` if the :guilabel:`Counterpart Items` include "
"a :guilabel:`Partner` but no :guilabel:`Account`."
msgstr ""
"Model usklajevanja se lahko uporabi za :ref:`preslikavo partnerjev "
"<accounting/rec-models/partner>`, če :guilabel:`Postavke protiknjižb` "
"vključujejo :guilabel:`Partnerja`, vendar ne :guilabel:`Konta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:113
msgid "Default reconciliation models"
msgstr "Privzeti modeli usklajevanja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:115
msgid ""
"In Odoo, different models are available by default depending on the "
"company's :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`. These can "
"be updated if needed. The following reconciliation models exist across most "
"fiscal localizations."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo so privzeto na voljo različni modeli, odvisno od :doc:`davčne "
"lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>` podjetja. Ti se lahko po potrebi "
"posodobijo. Naslednji modeli usklajevanja obstajajo v večini davčnih "
"lokalizacij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:120
msgid "Internal Transfers"
msgstr "Interni prenosi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:122
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Internal Transfers` reconciliation model is used for "
"making :doc:`internal transfers <internal_transfers>` from one bank or cash "
"account to another by moving the entire transaction's balance to a liquidity "
"or internal transfer account. To fully transfer the amount from one account "
"to another, this reconciliation model must be used on both the incoming "
"journal's transaction and the outgoing journal's transaction."
msgstr ""
"Model usklajevanja :guilabel:`Notranji prenosi` se uporablja za izvajanje "
":doc:`notranjih prenosov <internal_transfers>` z enega bančnega ali "
"denarnega konta na drugega s prenosom celotnega salda transakcije na konto "
"likvidnosti ali notranjih prenosov. Za popoln prenos zneska z enega konta na "
"drugega mora biti ta model usklajevanja uporabljen tako na transakciji "
"dnevnika za prejemke kot na transakciji dnevnika za izdatke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:129
msgid ":doc:`internal_transfers`"
msgstr ":doc:`internal_transfers`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:132
msgid "Bank Fees"
msgstr "Bančne preovizije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:134
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Bank Fees` reconciliation model generates a counterpart item "
"that moves the remaining balance of a transaction to a bank fees account "
"(that varies by :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`) and "
"includes \"Bank Fees\" in the :guilabel:`Label` of the new item that it "
"creates. This reconciliation model is only applicable to transactions whose "
"label contains \"Bank Fees\" due to its :ref:`matching conditions "
"<accounting/rec-models/conditions>`."
msgstr ""
"Model usklajevanja :guilabel:`Bančne provizije` ustvari protiknjižbo, ki "
"prenese preostali saldo transakcije na konto bančnih provizij (ki se "
"razlikuje glede na :doc:`davčno lokalizacijo <../../fiscal_localizations>`) "
"in vključuje \"Bančne provizije\" v :guilabel:`Oznaki` nove postavke, ki jo "
"ustvari. Ta model usklajevanja se uporablja samo za transakcije, katerih "
"oznaka vsebuje \"Bančne provizije\" zaradi svojih :ref:`pogojev ujemanja "
"<accounting/rec-models/conditions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:147
msgid "Cash Discount"
msgstr "Popust pri plačilu v gotovini"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:149
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Cash Discount` reconciliation model generates a counterpart "
"item that moves the remaining balance of a transaction to a cash discount "
"account (that varies by :doc:`fiscal localization <../../"
"fiscal_localizations>`) and includes \"Cash Discount\" in "
"the :guilabel:`Label` of the new item that it creates."
msgstr ""
"Model uskladitve :guilabel:`Popust pri plačilu v gotovini` ustvari postavko "
"nasprotne strani, ki prenese preostalo stanje transakcije na račun popusta "
"pri plačilu v gotovini (ki se razlikuje glede na :doc:`davčno lokalizacijo "
"<../../fiscal_localizations>`) in vključi \"Popust pri plačilu v gotovini\" "
"v :guilabel:`Oznako` nove postavke, ki jo ustvari."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:155
msgid ":doc:`../customer_invoices/cash_discounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../customer_invoices/cash_discounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:160
msgid "Partner mapping"
msgstr "Preslikava partnerja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:162
msgid ""
"Partner mapping allows you to establish rules for automatically matching "
"transactions to the correct partner account, saving time and reducing the "
"risk of errors that can occur during manual reconciliation. For example, you "
"can create a partner mapping rule for incoming payments with specific "
"reference numbers or keywords in the transaction description. When an "
"incoming payment meets these criteria, Odoo automatically maps it to the "
"corresponding customer's account."
msgstr ""
"Preslikava partnerja vam omogoča, da vzpostavite pravila za samodejno "
"usklajevanje transakcij s pravilnim računom partnerja, s čimer privarujete "
"čas in zmanjšate tveganje napak, ki se lahko pojavijo med ročnim "
"usklajevanjem. Na primer, ustvarite lahko pravilo za preslikavo partnerja za "
"dohodno plačilo s specifičnimi številkami sklicevanja ali ključnimi besedami "
"v opisu transakcije. Ko dohodno plačilo izpolnjuje ta merila, ga Odoo "
"samodejno preslika na račun ustreznega kupca."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/reconciliation_models.rst:168
msgid ""
"To create a partner mapping rule, configure any :ref:`matching conditions "
"<accounting/rec-models/conditions>`, such as a specific transaction label, "
"and then configure the :guilabel:`Partner` and any other relevant fields in "
"the :ref:`Counterpart Items <accounting/rec-models/counterpart>` tab. "
"Setting an :guilabel:`Account` is not mandatory for partner mapping."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje pravila za preslikavo partnerja konfigurirajte poljubne "
":ref:`pogoje ujemanja <accounting/rec-models/conditions>`, kot je specifična "
"oznaka transakcije, nato pa konfigurirajte :guilabel:`Partnerja` in vsa "
"druga ustrezna polja v zavihku :ref:`Postavke nasprotne strani <accounting/"
"rec-models/counterpart>`. Nastavitev :guilabel:`Računa` ni obvezna za "
"preslikavo partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:5
msgid ""
"Importing transactions from your bank statements allows keeping track of "
"bank account transactions and reconciling them with the ones recorded in "
"your accounting."
msgstr ""
"Uvoz transakcij iz vaših bančnih izpiskov omogoča sledenje transakcijam na "
"bančnem računu in njihovo usklajevanje s tistimi, zabeleženimi v vašem "
"računovodstvu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:8
msgid ""
":doc:`Bank synchronization <bank_synchronization>` automates the process. "
"However, if you do not want to use it or if your bank is not yet supported, "
"other options exist:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Sinhronizacija banke <bank_synchronization>` avtomatizira postopek. "
"Vendar, če je ne želite uporabiti ali če vaša banka še ni podprta, obstajajo "
"druge možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:11
msgid ""
":ref:`Import bank transactions <accounting/transactions/import>` delivered "
"by your bank;"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Uvozite bančne transakcije <accounting/transactions/import>`, ki jih "
"dostavi vaša banka;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:12
msgid ""
":ref:`Register bank transactions <accounting/transactions/register>` "
"manually."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Zabeležite bančne transakcije <accounting/transactions/register>` "
"ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:15
msgid ""
":ref:`Grouping transactions by statement <accounting/transactions/"
"statements>` is optional."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Združevanje transakcij po izpisu <accounting/transactions/statements>` "
"je izbirno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:20
msgid "Transaction view"
msgstr "Pogled transakcij"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:22
msgid ""
"The list of transactions for the bank journal is displayed in "
"the :guilabel:`Bank Matching` view. To access it, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, then either:"
msgstr ""
"Seznam transakcij za bančni dnevnik je prikazan v pogledu "
":guilabel:`Ujemanje banke`. Za dostop do njega pojdite na "
":guilabel:`Nadzorno ploščo računovodstva`, nato pa:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:30
msgid ""
"Unreconciled transactions display the following information while collapsed:"
msgstr ""
"Neusklajene transakcije prikazujejo naslednje informacije, ko so stisnjene:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:32
msgid "The date of the transaction"
msgstr "Datum transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:33
msgid "A button linked to the chatter. The icon of this button can vary:"
msgstr "Gumb, povezan s klepetom. Ikona tega gumba se lahko razlikuje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:35
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-comments-o` :guilabel:`(comments)` icon displays only on hover "
"and indicates that there are no attachments or activities for the "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
"Ikona :icon:`fa-comments-o` :guilabel:`(komentarji)` se prikazuje samo ob "
"prehodu z miško in označuje, da za transakcijo ni prilog ali dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:37
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(attachments)` icon indicates that there "
"is an attachment on the journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Ikona :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(priloge)` označuje, da je na knjižbi "
"prisotna priloga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:39
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`(activities)` icon indicates that there is "
"an activity scheduled on the journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Ikona :icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`(dejavnosti)` označuje, da je na knjižbi "
"načrtovana dejavnost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:42
msgid "The label of the transaction"
msgstr "Oznaka transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:43
msgid "The partner of the transaction (if one is set)"
msgstr "Partner transakcije (če je nastavljen)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:44
msgid ""
"Up to two :ref:`action buttons <accounting/reconciliation/action-buttons>`, "
"depending on the details of the transaction"
msgstr ""
"Do dva :ref:`akcijska gumba <accounting/reconciliation/action-buttons>`, "
"odvisno od podrobnosti transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:46
msgid "The balance of the transaction"
msgstr "Saldo transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:49
msgid ""
"When the chatter of a transaction is open, a blue tag highlights the related "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
"Ko je klepet transakcije odprt, modra oznaka označi povezano transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:50
msgid ""
"The chatter can be opened and closed by clicking the :icon:`fa-comments-"
"o` :guilabel:`(comments)` icon and the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(close)` "
"icon in the top right of the view."
msgstr ""
"Klepet lahko odprete in zaprete s klikom na ikono :icon:`fa-comments-o` "
":guilabel:`(komentarji)` in ikono :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(zapri)` v "
"zgornjem desnem delu pogleda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:53
msgid ""
"Once a transaction is :doc:`reconciled <reconciliation>`, its action buttons "
"are replaced with the labels of the item(s) it was reconciled with or the "
"account if it was reconciled with the :guilabel:`Set Account` action button."
msgstr ""
"Ko je transakcija :doc:`usklajena <reconciliation>`, se njeni akcijski gumbi "
"zamenjajo z oznakami postavk, s katerimi je bila usklajena, ali s kontom, če "
"je bila usklajena z akcijskim gumbom :guilabel:`Nastavi konto`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:62
msgid ""
"Duplicate transactions occur when either by human error or :doc:`bank sync "
"<bank_synchronization>` error, the same transaction is created multiple "
"times. The duplicate transaction view identifies potential duplicate "
"transactions so they can be selected and deleted. To access the duplicate "
"transaction view, first access the :guilabel:`Bank Matching` view by going "
"to the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` and clicking the bank journal's "
"name, then open the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` menu and "
"click :guilabel:`Find Duplicate Transactions`."
msgstr ""
"Podvojene transakcije nastanejo, ko je zaradi človeške napake ali napake "
":doc:`bančne sinhronizacije <bank_synchronization>` ista transakcija "
"ustvarjena večkrat. Pogled podvojenih transakcij identificira potencialno "
"podvojene transakcije, da jih lahko izberete in izbrišete. Za dostop do "
"pogleda podvojenih transakcij najprej dostopite do pogleda :guilabel:`Bančno "
"ujemanje` tako, da greste na :guilabel:`Nadzorna plošča` in kliknete ime "
"bančnega dnevnika, nato odprite meni :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Najdi podvojene transakcije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:69
msgid ""
"Potential duplicate transactions are identified based on their amount, date, "
"and account number, or (if the transaction is created via :doc:`bank sync "
"<bank_synchronization>`) the transaction ID."
msgstr ""
"Potencialno podvojene transakcije so identificirane na podlagi njihovega "
"zneska, datuma in številke računa ali (če je transakcija ustvarjena prek "
":doc:`bančne sinhronizacije <bank_synchronization>`) ID-ja transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:72
msgid ""
"Select a :guilabel:`Starting Date` to view the corresponding potential "
"duplicate transactions, then select the transactions to delete and "
"click :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Delete Selected`."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Začetni datum`, da si ogledate ustrezne potencialno "
"podvojene transakcije, nato izberite transakcije za brisanje in kliknite "
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Izbriši izbrane`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:76
msgid ""
"Any transactions created by :doc:`bank sync <bank_synchronization>` that the "
"bank sync provider determines to be potential duplicates are displayed in "
"the :guilabel:`Provider Duplicates` tab. This tab is only visible if there "
"are any potential duplicates according to the provider."
msgstr ""
"Vse transakcije, ustvarjene prek :doc:`bančne sinhronizacije "
"<bank_synchronization>`, za katere ponudnik bančne sinhronizacije ugotovi, "
"da so potencialno podvojene, so prikazane v zavihku :guilabel:`Podvojeni "
"ponudnika`. Ta zavihek je viden samo, če obstajajo potencialno podvojene "
"transakcije po mnenju ponudnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:83
msgid "Import transactions"
msgstr "Uvozi transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:85
msgid "Odoo supports multiple file formats to import transactions:"
msgstr "Odoo podpira več formatov datotek za uvoz transakcij:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:87
msgid "SEPA recommended Cash Management format (CAMT.053)"
msgstr "Priporočeni format SEPA za upravljanje gotovine (CAMT.053)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:88
msgid "Comma-separated values (CSV)"
msgstr "Vrednosti ločene z vejicami (CSV)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:89
msgid "Excel (XLSX)"
msgstr "Excel (XLSX)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:90
msgid "Open Financial Exchange (OFX)"
msgstr "Odprta finančna izmenjava (OFX)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:91
msgid "Quicken Interchange Format (QIF)"
msgstr "Format izmenjave Quicken (QIF)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:92
msgid "Belgium: Coded Statement of Account (CODA)"
msgstr "Belgija: kodirani izpisek računa (CODA)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:94
msgid ""
"To import a file, go to the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon on "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` journal, and select :guilabel:`Import file`. Next, "
"select the file and upload it."
msgstr ""
"Za uvoz datoteke pojdite na :guilabel:`Nadzorna plošča`, kliknite ikono "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(tri pike)` na dnevniku :guilabel:`Banka` "
"in izberite :guilabel:`Uvozi datoteko`. Nato izberite datoteko in jo "
"naložite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:101
msgid "Alternatively, access the transaction list by:"
msgstr "Alternativno dostopajte do seznama transakcij tako, da:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:100
msgid ""
"clicking on the :guilabel:`Bank` journal's name, then "
"clicking :guilabel:`Upload`"
msgstr ""
"kliknete na ime dnevnika :guilabel:`Banka`, nato pa kliknete "
":guilabel:`Naloži`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:101
msgid ""
"dragging and dropping a file on the bank journal on "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`"
msgstr ""
"povlečete in spustite datoteko na bančni dnevnik na :guilabel:`Nadzorni "
"plošči računovodstva`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:102
msgid "dragging and dropping a file on the :guilabel:`Bank Matching` view"
msgstr "povlečete in spustite datoteko na pogled :guilabel:`Ujemanje s banko`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:104
msgid ""
"Certain file types such as CSV and XLSX, then require setting the necessary "
"formatting options and mapping the file columns with their related Odoo "
"fields, after which you can run a :guilabel:`Test` and :guilabel:`Import` "
"your bank transactions. Other file types are mapped automatically."
msgstr ""
"Določene vrste datotek, kot sta CSV in XLSX, nato zahtevajo nastavitev "
"potrebnih možnosti oblikovanja in preslikavo stolpcev datoteke z njihovimi "
"povezanimi polji Odoo, po tem pa lahko zaženete :guilabel:`Test` in "
":guilabel:`Uvozite` svoje bančne transakcije. Druge vrste datotek se "
"preslikajo samodejno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:109
msgid ":doc:`/applications/essentials/export_import_data`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/essentials/export_import_data`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:114
msgid "Register bank transactions manually"
msgstr "Ročno evidentiranje bančnih transakcij"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:116
msgid ""
"You can also record your bank transactions manually. To do so, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, click the :guilabel:`Bank` journal's "
"name, and then on :guilabel:`New`. The :guilabel:`Partner` field is optional "
"to ease the reconciliation process, but the :guilabel:`Label` "
"and :guilabel:`Date` fields are mandatory."
msgstr ""
"Bančne transakcije lahko evidentirate tudi ročno. To storite tako, da greste "
"na :guilabel:`Nadzorno ploščo računovodstva`, kliknete ime dnevnika "
":guilabel:`Banka` in nato na :guilabel:`Novo`. Polje :guilabel:`Partner` je "
"neobvezno za lažji proces usklajevanja, medtem ko sta polji "
":guilabel:`Oznaka` in :guilabel:`Datum` obvezni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:124
msgid "Statements"
msgstr "Izpiski"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:126
msgid ""
"A **bank statement** is a document provided by a bank or financial "
"institution that lists the transactions that have occurred in a particular "
"bank account over a specified period of time."
msgstr ""
"**Bančni izpisek** je dokument, ki ga zagotovi banka ali finančna ustanova "
"in vsebuje seznam transakcij, ki so se zgodile na določenem bančnem računu v "
"določenem časovnem obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:129
msgid ""
"In Odoo Accounting, it is optional to group transactions by their related "
"statement, but depending on your business flow, you may want to record them "
"for record-keeping and organizational purposes."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo Računovodstvu je združevanje transakcij po povezanem izpisku "
"neobvezno, vendar boste morda želeli, odvisno od vašega poslovnega poteka, "
"evidentirati izpiske za namene vodenja evidenc in organizacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:132
msgid ""
"To access a list of existing statements, go to the :guilabel:`Accounting "
"Dashboard`, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(dropdown menu)` icon "
"next to the bank or cash journal you want to check, then "
"click :guilabel:`Statements`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do seznama obstoječih izpiskov pojdite na :guilabel:`Nadzorno "
"ploščo računovodstva`, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`"
"(spustni meni)` ob bančnem ali gotovinskem dnevniku, ki ga želite preveriti, "
"nato pa kliknite :guilabel:`Izpiski`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:137
msgid ""
"To ensure the ending balances of your bank statements in Odoo align with the "
"ending balances of the statements that are provided by your bank, create an "
"opening transaction to record the bank account balance as of the date you "
"begin synchronizing or importing transactions. This is necessary to ensure "
"the accuracy of your accounting."
msgstr ""
"Za zagotovitev, da se končna stanja vaših bančnih izpiskov v Odoo ujemajo s "
"končnimi stanji izpiskov, ki jih zagotavlja vaša banka, ustvarite začetno "
"transakcijo za evidentiranje stanja bančnega računa na dan, ko začnete "
"sinhronizirati ali uvažati transakcije. To je potrebno za zagotovitev "
"natančnosti vašega računovodstva."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:143
msgid ""
"To access a statement's transactions, click :guilabel:`Transactions` "
"directly from the :guilabel:`Bank Statements` list view or open a statement "
"and click the :guilabel:`Statement lines` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do transakcij izpiska kliknite :guilabel:`Transakcije` neposredno "
"iz seznamskega pogleda :guilabel:`Bančni izpiski` ali odprite izpisek in "
"kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Vrstice izpiska`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:150
msgid "Statement creation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje izpiska"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:152
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Bank Matching` view displays transactions from most recent to "
"oldest and groups them by statement, with any recent transactions that do "
"not belong to a statement at the top. To add transactions to a statement, "
"hover on the most recent transaction that should be included in the "
"statement, and click the :guilabel:`Statement` button that appears on the "
"upper separator line. Doing so creates a statement from that transaction "
"down to the oldest transaction that is not yet part of a statement."
msgstr ""
"Pogled :guilabel:`Ujemanje s banko` prikazuje transakcije od najnovejših do "
"najstarejših in jih združuje po izpisках, pri čemer so vse nedavne "
"transakcije, ki ne pripadajo izpisku, na vrhu. Za dodajanje transakcij v "
"izpisek premaknite kazalec na najnovejšo transakcijo, ki bi morala biti "
"vključena v izpisek, in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Izpisek`, ki se prikaže na "
"zgornji ločilni črti. S tem ustvarite izpisek od te transakcije navzdol do "
"najstarejše transakcije, ki še ni del izpiska."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:None
msgid "A \"Statement\" button is visible when hovering on a transaction."
msgstr "Gumb \"Izpisek\" je viden, ko premaknete kazalec na transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:162
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Create Statement` window, fill out the "
"statement's :guilabel:`Reference`, verify its :guilabel:`Starting Balance` "
"and :guilabel:`Ending Balance`, add an attachment such as a PDF of the "
"statement if desired, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari izpisek` izpolnite :guilabel:`Sklic` izpiska, "
"preverite njegovo :guilabel:`Začetno stanje` in :guilabel:`Končno stanje`, "
"po želji dodajte prilogo, kot je PDF izpiska, in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:167
msgid ""
"Transactions can also be added to statements from the list view. Select all "
"the transactions corresponding to the bank statement, and, in "
"the :guilabel:`Statement` column, select an existing statement or create a "
"new one by typing its reference, clicking on :guilabel:`Create and edit...`, "
"filling out the statement's details, and saving."
msgstr ""
"Transakcije lahko dodate tudi v izpiske iz seznamskega pogleda. Izberite vse "
"transakcije, ki ustrezajo bančnemu izpisku, in v stolpcu :guilabel:`Izpisek` "
"izberite obstoječi izpisek ali ustvarite novega tako, da vnesete njegov "
"sklic, kliknete na :guilabel:`Ustvari in uredi...`, izpolnite podrobnosti "
"izpiska in shranite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:175
msgid "Statement viewing, editing, and printing"
msgstr "Ogled, urejanje in tiskanje izpiska"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:177
msgid ""
"To view an existing statement, click the statement amount in "
"the :guilabel:`Bank Matching` view or click the statement name and then "
"the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(Internal link)` icon in "
"the :guilabel:`Bank Matching` list view. From here, you can edit "
"the :guilabel:`Reference`, :guilabel:`Starting Balance`, :guilabel:`Ending "
"Balance`, and :guilabel:`Attachments`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled obstoječega izpiska kliknite znesek izpiska v pogledu "
":guilabel:`Ujemanje s banko` ali kliknite ime izpiska in nato ikono "
":icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(Notranja povezava)` v seznamskem pogledu "
":guilabel:`Ujemanje s banko`. Od tukaj lahko urejate :guilabel:`Sklic`, "
":guilabel:`Začetno stanje`, :guilabel:`Končno stanje` in :guilabel:`Priloge`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:183
msgid ""
"Manually updating the :guilabel:`Starting Balance` automatically updates "
"the :guilabel:`Ending Balance` based on the new value of "
"the :guilabel:`Starting Balance` and the value of the statement's "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Ročno posodabljanje :guilabel:`Začetnega stanja` samodejno posodobi "
":guilabel:`Končno stanje` na podlagi nove vrednosti :guilabel:`Začetnega "
"stanja` in vrednosti transakcij izpiska."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:186
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Starting Balance` doesn't equal the previous "
"statement's :guilabel:`Ending Balance`, or if the :guilabel:`Ending Balance` "
"doesn't equal the running balance (:guilabel:`Starting Balance` plus the "
"statement's transactions), a warning appears explaining the issue. To "
"maintain flexibility, it is still possible to save without first resolving "
"the issue."
msgstr ""
"Če :guilabel:`Začetno stanje` ni enako :guilabel:`Končnemu stanju` "
"prejšnjega izpiska ali če :guilabel:`Končno stanje` ni enako tekočemu stanju "
"(:guilabel:`Začetno stanje` plus transakcije izpiska), se prikaže opozorilo, "
"ki pojasnjuje težavo. Za ohranitev prilagodljivosti je še vedno mogoče "
"shraniti, ne da bi najprej rešili težavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:192
msgid ""
"To generate and print a PDF of the bank statement, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon and click :icon:`fa-"
"print` :guilabel:`Statement`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje in tiskanje PDF bančnega izpiska kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(zobnik)` in kliknite :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Izpisk`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/transactions.rst:196
msgid ""
"When a bank statement is generated to be printed, it is automatically added "
"to the :guilabel:`Attachments` if no file was attached when creating the "
"statement."
msgstr ""
"Ko je bančni izpisk ustvarjen za tiskanje, je samodejno dodan k "
":guilabel:`Prilogam`, če pri ustvarjanju izpiska ni bila priložena nobena "
"datoteka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:7
msgid ""
"A customer invoice is a document issued by a company for products and/or "
"services sold to a customer. It records receivables as they are sent to "
"customers. Customer invoices can include amounts due for the goods and/or "
"services provided, applicable sales taxes, shipping and handling fees, and "
"other charges. Odoo supports multiple invoicing and payment workflows."
msgstr ""
"Račun stranki je dokument, ki ga izdaja podjetje za izdelke in/ali storitve, "
"prodane stranki. Beleži terjatve, ko so poslane strankam. Računi strankam "
"lahko vključujejo zneske, dolgove za dobavljeno blago in/ali storitve, "
"veljavne davke od prodaje, stroške pošiljanja in obdelave ter druge stroške. "
"Odoo podpira več potov dela pri izdajanju računov in plačilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:13
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/overview.rst:102
