msgstr "V zavihku :guilabel:`Vrstice računa`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: Click :guilabel:`Add a line`, then search for and "
"select the product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izdelek`: Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, nato poiščite in "
"izberite izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:53
msgid ":guilabel:`Quantity`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Količina`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:54
msgid ":guilabel:`Price`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Cena`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:55
msgid ":doc:`Taxes <taxes>` (if applicable)"
msgstr ":doc:`Davki <taxes>` (če je primerno)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:57
msgid ""
"To access the product catalog and view all items in an organized display, "
"click :doc:`Catalog </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/product_catalog>`. When the products "
"and quantities are selected, click :guilabel:`Back to Invoice` to return to "
"the invoice; the selected catalog items will appear in the invoice lines."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do kataloga izdelkov in ogled vseh postavk v organiziranem prikazu "
"kliknite :doc:`Katalog </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/product_catalog>`. Ko so izdelki in "
"količine izbrani, kliknite :guilabel:`Nazaj na račun`, da se vrnete na "
"račun; izbrane postavke kataloga se bodo prikazale v vrsticah računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:63
msgid ""
"To display the total amount of the invoice in words, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and activate "
"the :guilabel:`Total amount of invoice in letters` option."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz skupnega zneska računa v besedah pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in "
"aktivirajte možnost :guilabel:`Skupni znesek računa v besedah`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:67
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab displays the accounting entries created. "
"Additional invoice information such as the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Reference`, :guilabel:`Payment Reference`, :doc:`Fiscal Positions <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`, :doc:`Incoterms <customer_invoices/incoterms>`, and more "
"can be added or modified in the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Postavke dnevnika` prikazuje ustvarjene računovodske "
"vnose. Dodatne informacije o računu, kot so :guilabel:`Sklic stranke`, "
":guilabel:`Sklic plačila`, :doc:`Davčne pozicije <taxes/fiscal_positions>`, "
":doc:`Incoterms <customer_invoices/incoterms>` in več, je mogoče dodati ali "
"spremeniti v zavihku :guilabel:`Druge informacije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:73
msgid ""
"Odoo initially creates invoices in :guilabel:`Draft` status. Draft invoices "
"have no accounting impact until they are :ref:`confirmed <accounting/invoice/"
"confirmation>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo prvotno ustvari račune v statusu :guilabel:`Osnutek`. Osnutki računov "
"nimajo računovodskega vpliva, dokler niso :ref:`potrjeni <accounting/invoice/"
"confirmation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/overview.rst:47
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:82
msgid "Invoice confirmation"
msgstr "Potrditev računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:84
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` when the invoice is completed. The invoice's "
"status changes to :guilabel:`Posted`, and a journal entry is generated based "
"on the invoice configuration. On confirmation, Odoo assigns each invoice a "
"unique number from a defined :doc:`sequence <customer_invoices/sequence>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun dokončan, kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`. Status računa se spremeni "
"v :guilabel:`Knjiženo` in na podlagi konfiguracije računa se ustvari "
"dnevniški vnos. Ob potrditvi Odoo vsakemu računu dodeli edinstveno številko "
"iz določenega :doc:`zaporedja <customer_invoices/sequence>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, an invoice can no longer be updated. Click :guilabel:`Reset "
"to draft` if changes are needed."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun potrjen, ga ni več mogoče posodobiti. Če so potrebne spremembe, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Ponastavi na osnutek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:92
msgid ""
"If required, invoices and other journal entries can be locked once posted "
"using the :ref:`Secure posted entries with hash <data-inalterability/"
"restricted>` feature."
msgstr ""
"Če je potrebno, je mogoče račune in druge dnevniške vnose po knjiženju "
"zakleniti z uporabo funkcije :ref:`Zavaruj knjižene vnose z razpršilom <data-"
"inalterability/restricted>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:98
msgid "Invoice sending"
msgstr "Pošiljanje računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:100
msgid ""
"To set a preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method for a customer, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers` and select the "
"customer. In the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab of the contact form, select the "
"preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method in the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoices` section."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev prednostne metode :guilabel:`Pošiljanje računa` za stranko "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Stranke` in "
"izberite stranko. V zavihku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` obrazca za stik "
"izberite prednostno metodo :guilabel:`Pošiljanje računa` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Računi strank`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:106
msgid ""
"Sending letters in Odoo requires :doc:`In-App Purchase (IAP) <../../"
"essentials/in_app_purchase>` credit or tokens."
msgstr ""
"Pošiljanje pisem v Odooju zahteva dobroimetje ali žetone :doc:`nakupa v "
"aplikaciji (IAP) <../../essentials/in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:109
msgid ""
"To send the invoice to the customer, navigate back to the invoice record and "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za pošiljanje računa stranki se vrnite na zapis računa in sledite tem "
"korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:147
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:163
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:180
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/poland.rst:130
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:112
msgid ""
"If the :ref:`default invoice layout <studio/pdf-reports/default-layout>` has "
"not been customized yet, a :guilabel:`Configure your document layout` pop-up "
"window appears. Configure the layout and click :guilabel:`Continue`."
msgstr ""
"Če :ref:`privzeta postavitev računa <studio/pdf-reports/default-layout>` še "
"ni bila prilagojena, se prikaže pojavno okno :guilabel:`Konfigurirajte "
"postavitev dokumenta`. Konfigurirajte postavitev in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Nadaljuj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:117
msgid "The document layout can be changed at any time in the general settings."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev dokumenta lahko kadar koli spremenite v splošnih nastavitvah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:118
msgid ""
"To add a QR code for banking app payments to the invoice, enable "
"the :guilabel:`QR Code` option in the :guilabel:`Configure Your Document "
"Layout` window. To modify this option, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Payments` section, and enable/disable the :guilabel:`QR Codes` option."
msgstr ""
"Če želite na račun dodati QR-kodo za plačila prek bančne aplikacije, "
"omogočite možnost :guilabel:`QR Code` v oknu :guilabel:`Configure Your "
"Document Layout`. Za spremembo te možnosti pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, se pomaknite "
"navzdol do razdelka :guilabel:`Customer Payments` in omogočite/onemogočite "
"možnost :guilabel:`QR Codes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:123
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Send` window:"
msgstr "V oknu :guilabel:`Pošlji`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:125
msgid ""
"If a preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method was set in the contact "
"form, it is selected by default. Select another one if needed."
msgstr ""
"Če je bila v obrazcu stika nastavljena prednostna metoda :guilabel:`Invoice "
"sending`, je privzeto izbrana. Po potrebi izberite drugo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:127
msgid ""
"If no preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method was set in the contact "
"form, select the method to use for sending the invoice to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Če v obrazcu stika ni bila nastavljena prednostna metoda :guilabel:`Invoice "
"sending`, izberite metodo, ki jo želite uporabiti za pošiljanje računa "
"stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:130
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` if the :guilabel:`by Email` option is selected, or "
"click :guilabel:`Download`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`, če je izbrana možnost :guilabel:`po e-pošti`, "
"ali kliknite :guilabel:`Prenesi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:136
msgid "Sending multiple invoices"
msgstr "Pošiljanje več računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:138
msgid ""
"To send multiple invoices, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --"
"> Invoices`, select them in the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view and "
"click :guilabel:`Send`. The :guilabel:`Send` window displays the number of "
"selected invoice to send by email."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poslati več računov, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Stranke --> Računi`, izberite jih v seznamskem pogledu :guilabel:`Računi` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`. Okno :guilabel:`Pošlji` prikaže število "
"izbranih računov za pošiljanje po e-pošti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:142
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Send`, a banner is added to the selected invoices "
"to indicate they are part of an ongoing send batch. This helps prevent the "
"process from being triggered manually again, as it may take some time to "
"complete for exceptionally large batches."
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na :guilabel:`Pošlji` se izbranim računom doda pasica, ki označuje, "
"da so del tekočega sklopa pošiljanja. To pomaga preprečiti ročno ponovitev "
"postopka, saj lahko pri izjemno velikih sklopih traja nekaj časa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:146
msgid ""
"To check all invoices that have not yet been sent, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, click into the search bar and filter "
"on :guilabel:`Not Sent`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preveriti vse račune, ki še niso bili poslani, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`. V seznamskem pogledu "
":guilabel:`Invoices` kliknite v iskalno vrstico in filtrirajte po "
":guilabel:`Not Sent`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:153
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:190
msgid "Payment and reconciliation"
msgstr "Plačilo in uskladitev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:155
msgid ""
"In Odoo, an invoice is considered :guilabel:`Paid` when the associated "
"accounting entry has been reconciled with a corresponding bank transaction."
msgstr ""
"V Odooju se račun šteje za :guilabel:`Paid`, ko je povezan računovodski vnos "
"uskladjen z ustrezno bančno transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:159
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:209
msgid ":doc:`payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:160
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:19
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:210
msgid ":doc:`bank/reconciliation`"
msgstr ":doc:`bank/reconciliation`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:165
msgid "Payment follow-up"
msgstr "Spremljanje plačil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:167
msgid ""
"Odoo's :doc:`follow-up actions <payments/follow_up>` help companies follow "
"up on customer invoices. Different actions can be set up to remind customers "
"to pay their outstanding invoices, depending on how much the customer is "
"overdue. These actions are bundled into follow-up levels that trigger when "
"an invoice is overdue by a certain number of days. If there are multiple "
"overdue invoices for the same customer, the actions are performed on the "
"most overdue invoice."
msgstr ""
"Odoo :doc:`follow-up actions <payments/follow_up>` podjetjem pomagajo pri "
"spremljanju računov strank. Nastavite lahko različna dejanja za opominjanje "
"strank, naj plačajo neporavnane račune, odvisno od tega, kako zamuja "
"stranka. Ta dejanja so združena v ravni spremljanja, ki se sprožijo, ko je "
"račun zamuden določeno število dni. Če ima ista stranka več zamudnih "
"računov, se dejanja izvedejo na najbolj zamudnem računu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:181
msgid "Partner reports"
msgstr "Poročila o partnerjih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:186
msgid "Partner Ledger"
msgstr "Saldakonti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:188
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Partner Ledger` report shows the balance of customers and "
"suppliers. To access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Partner Ledger`."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`Partner Ledger` prikazuje saldo strank in dobaviteljev. "
"Za dostop pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Partner "
"Ledger`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:194
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:103
msgid "Aged Receivable"
msgstr "Zastarane terjatve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:196
msgid ""
"To review outstanding customer invoices and their related due dates, use "
"the :ref:`Aged Receivable <accounting/reporting/aged-receivable>` report. To "
"access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged "
"Receivable`."
msgstr ""
"Za pregled neporavnanih računov strank in povezanih datumov zapadlosti "
"uporabite poročilo :ref:`Aged Receivable <accounting/reporting/aged-"
"receivable>`. Za dostop pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Aged Receivable`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:203
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:111
msgid "Aged Payable"
msgstr "Zastarela obveznost"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:205
msgid ""
"To review outstanding vendor bills and their related due dates, use "
"the :ref:`Aged Payable <accounting/reporting/aged-payable>` report. To "
"access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged Payable`."
msgstr ""
"Za pregled neporavnanih računov dobaviteljev in povezanih datumov zapadlosti "
"uporabite poročilo :ref:`Aged Payable <accounting/reporting/aged-payable>`. "
"Za dostop pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged "
"Payable`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:212
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:49
msgid "Profit and Loss"
msgstr "Dobiček in izguba"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:214
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>` statement "
"shows details of income and expenses."
msgstr ""
"Izkaz :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>` "
"prikazuje podrobnosti prihodkov in odhodkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:222
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Balance Sheet <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>` summarizes the "
"company's assets, liabilities, and equity at a specific time."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Balance Sheet <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>` povzema sredstva, "
"obveznosti in kapital podjetja v določenem času."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:3
msgid "Cash discounts and tax reduction"
msgstr "Gotovinski popusti in znižanje davka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Cash discounts** are reductions in the amount a customer must pay for "
"goods or services offered as an incentive for paying their invoice promptly. "
"These discounts are typically a percentage of the total invoice amount and "
"are applied if the customer pays within a specified time. Cash discounts can "
"help a company maintain a steady cash flow."
msgstr ""
"**Gotovinski popusti** so znižanja zneska, ki ga mora stranka plačati za "
"blago ali storitve, ponujeni kot spodbuda za pravočasno plačilo računa. Ti "
"popusti so običajno odstotek skupnega zneska računa in se uporabijo, če "
"stranka plača v določenem roku. Gotovinski popusti lahko pomagajo podjetju "
"vzdrževati stabilen denarni tok."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:11
msgid ""
"You issue a €100 invoice on the 1st of January. The full payment is due "
"within 30 days, and you also offer a 2% discount if your customer pays you "
"within seven days."
msgstr ""
"Izdajate račun v višini 100 €, ki je izdan 1. januarja. Celotno plačilo "
"zapade v 30 dneh, poleg tega ponujate 2-odstotni popust, če vas stranke "
"plačajo v sedmih dneh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:14
msgid ""
"The customer can pay €98 up to the 8th of January. After that date, they "
"would have to pay €100 by the 31st of January."
msgstr ""
"Stranka lahko plača 98 € do 8. januarja. Po tem datumu bi morala plačati 100 "
"€ najpozneje do 31. januarja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:17
msgid ""
"A :ref:`tax reduction <cash-discounts/tax-reductions>` can also be applied "
"depending on the country or region."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Znižanje davka <cash-discounts/tax-reductions>` se lahko uporabi tudi "
"glede na državo ali regijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:21
msgid ":doc:`payment_terms`"
msgstr ":doc:`payment_terms`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:22
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:55
msgid ":doc:`../payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`../payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:29
msgid ""
"To grant cash discounts to customers, you must first verify the :ref:`gain "
"and loss accounts <cash-discounts/gain-loss-accounts>`. Then, "
"configure :ref:`payment terms <cash-discounts/payment-terms>` and add a cash "
"discount by checking the :guilabel:`Early Discount` checkbox and filling in "
"the discount percentage, discount days, and :ref:`tax reduction <cash-"
"discounts/tax-reductions>` fields."
msgstr ""
"Če želite strankam odobriti popuste pri plačilu v gotovini, morate najprej "
"preveriti :ref:`račune dobička in izgube <cash-discounts/gain-loss-accounts>"
"`. Nato konfigurirajte :ref:`plačilne pogoje <cash-discounts/payment-terms>` "
"in dodajte popust pri plačilu v gotovini tako, da potrdite potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`Zgodnji popust` ter izpolnite polja za odstotek popusta, dneve "
"popusta in :ref:`znižanje davka <cash-discounts/tax-reductions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:38
msgid "Cash discount gain/loss accounts"
msgstr "Računi dobička/izgube pri popustu za plačilo v gotovini"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:40
msgid ""
"With a cash discount, the amount you earn depends on whether the customer "
"benefits from the cash discount or not. This inevitably leads to gains and "
"losses, which are recorded on default accounts."
msgstr ""
"Pri popustu za plačilo v gotovini je znesek, ki ga zaslužite, odvisen od "
"tega, ali stranka izkoristi popust ali ne. To neizogibno vodi do dobičkov in "
"izgub, ki se evidentirajo na privzetih računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:43
msgid ""
"To modify these accounts, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`, and, in the :guilabel:`Default Accounts` section, select the "
"accounts you want to use for the :guilabel:`Cash Discount Gain account` "
"and :guilabel:`Cash Discount Loss account`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti te račune, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in v razdelku :guilabel:`Privzeti računi` "
"izberite račune, ki jih želite uporabiti za :guilabel:`Račun dobička pri "
"popustu za plačilo` in :guilabel:`Račun izgube pri popustu za plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:50
msgid "Payment terms"
msgstr "Plačilni pogoji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:52
msgid ""
"Cash discounts are defined on :doc:`payment terms <payment_terms>`. "
"Configure them to your liking by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Payment Terms`, and make sure to fill out the discount "
"percentage, discount days, and :ref:`tax reduction <cash-discounts/tax-"
"reductions>` fields."
msgstr ""
"Popusti za plačilo v gotovini so določeni v :doc:`plačilnih pogojih "
"<payment_terms>`. Konfigurirajte jih po svoje tako, da odprete "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Plačilni pogoji` in "
"izpolnite polja za odstotek popusta, dneve popusta in :ref:`znižanje davka "
"<cash-discounts/tax-reductions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Configuration of payment terms named \"2/7 Net 30\". The field \"Description "
"on Invoices\"\n"
"reads: \"Payment terms: 30 Days, 2% Early Payment Discount under 7 days\"."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija plačilnih pogojev z imenom \"2/7 neto 30\". Polje \"Opis na "
"računih\"\n"
"bere: \"Plačilni pogoji: 30 dni, 2% popusta pri zgodnjem plačilu v 7 dneh\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:64
msgid "Tax reductions"
msgstr "Davčne olajšave"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:66
msgid ""
"Depending on the country or region, the base amount used to compute the tax "
"can vary, which can lead to a **tax reduction**. Since tax reductions are "
"set on individual payment terms, each term can use a specific tax reduction."
msgstr ""
"Glede na državo ali regijo se lahko osnovna vsota, ki se uporablja za "
"izračun davka, razlikuje, kar lahko povzroči **znižanje davka**. Ker so "
"znižanja davka nastavljena na posameznih plačilnih pogojih, lahko vsak pogoj "
"uporablja določeno znižanje davka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:70
msgid ""
"To configure how the tax reduction is applied, go to a payment term with "
"the :guilabel:`Early Discount` checkbox enabled, and select one of the three "
"following options:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati način uporabe znižanja davka, pojdite na plačilni "
"pogoj z omogočenim poljem :guilabel:`Zgodnji popust` in izberite eno od treh "
"naslednjih možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:75
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:94
msgid "Always (upon invoice)"
msgstr "Vedno (ob izdaji računa)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:74
msgid ""
"The tax is always reduced. The base amount used to compute the tax is the "
"discounted amount, whether the customer benefits from the discount or not."
msgstr ""
"Davek je vedno znižan. Osnovna vsota, ki se uporablja za izračun davka, je "
"znižana vsota ne glede na to, ali stranka izkoristi popust ali ne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:109
msgid "On early payment"
msgstr "Pri predčasnem plačilu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:78
msgid ""
"The tax is reduced only if the customer pays early. The base amount used to "
"compute the tax is the same as the sale: if the customer benefits from the "
"reduction, then the tax is reduced. This means that, depending on the "
"customer, the tax amount can vary after the invoice is issued."
msgstr ""
"Davek je znižan le, če stranka plača zgodaj. Osnovna vsota, ki se uporablja "
"za izračun davka, je enaka kot pri prodaji: če stranka izkoristi znižanje, "
"se davek zniža. To pomeni, da se lahko znesek davka razlikuje glede na "
"stranko po izdaji računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:124
msgid "Never"
msgstr "Nikoli"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:83
msgid ""
"The tax is never reduced. The base amount used to compute the tax is the "
"full amount, whether the customer benefits from the discount or not."
msgstr ""
"Davek ni nikoli znižan. Osnovna vsota, ki se uporablja za izračun davka, je "
"celotna vsota ne glede na to, ali stranka izkoristi popust ali ne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts.rst:88
msgid ""
"You issue a €100 invoice (tax-excluded) on the 1st of January, with a 21% "
"tax rate. The full payment is due within 30 days, and you also offer a 2% "
"discount if your customer pays you within seven days."
msgstr ""
"Izdajate račun v višini 100 € (brez davka) 1. januarja z 21-odstotno davčno "
"stopnjo. Celotno plačilo zapade v 30 dneh, poleg tega ponujate 2-odstotni "
"popust, če vas stranke plačajo v sedmih dneh."

