#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:3
msgid "Delivery and invoice addresses"
msgstr "Naslovi za dostavo in izdajo računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:5
msgid ""
"Companies often have multiple locations, and it is common that a customer "
"invoice should be sent to one address and the delivery should be sent to "
"another. Odoo's **Customer Addresses** feature is designed to handle this "
"scenario by making it easy to specify which address to use for each case."
msgstr ""
"Podjetja imajo pogosto več lokacij in običajno je, da mora biti račun za "
"stranko poslan na en naslov, dostava pa na drug naslov. Odoo-jeva funkcija "
"**Naslovi strank** je zasnovana za ta scenarij, saj omogoča enostavno "
"določanje, kateri naslov uporabiti v posameznem primeru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`overview`"
msgstr ":doc:`overview`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:15
msgid ""
"To specify a sales order's invoice and delivery addresses, first go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` section, enable :guilabel:`Customer "
"Addresses` and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite določiti naslova za izdajo računa in dostavo prodajnega naloga, "
"najprej odprite :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`. V razdelku :guilabel:`Računi za stranke` omogočite "
":guilabel:`Naslovi strank` in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:19
msgid ""
"On quotations and sales orders, there are now fields for :guilabel:`Invoice "
"Address` and :guilabel:`Delivery Address`. If the customer has an invoice or "
"delivery address listed on their :ref:`contact record <sales/send_quotations/"
"contact-form-config>`, the corresponding field uses that address, by "
"default, but any contact's address can be used instead."
msgstr ""
"V ponudbah in prodajnih nalogih sta zdaj polji :guilabel:`Naslov za izdajo "
"računa` in :guilabel:`Naslov za dostavo`. Če ima stranka naslov za izdajo "
"računa ali dostavo naveden v svojem :ref:`kontaktnem zapisu <sales/"
"send_quotations/contact-form-config>`, ustrezno polje privzeto uporablja ta "
"naslov, vendar se lahko namesto tega uporabi naslov katerega koli kontakta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:25
msgid ""
"For more information, refer to the documentation on :ref:`Contact Form "
"Configuration <sales/send_quotations/contact-form-config>`."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij si oglejte dokumentacijo o :ref:`Konfiguraciji obrazca za "
"kontakt <sales/send_quotations/contact-form-config>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:30
msgid "Invoice and deliver to different addresses"
msgstr "Izdaja računa in dostava na različne naslove"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:32
msgid ""
"Delivery orders and their delivery slip reports use the address set as "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Address` on the sales order. By default, invoice "
"reports show both the shipping address and the invoice address to assure the "
"customer that the delivery is going to the correct location."
msgstr ""
"Dobavnice in njihova poročila uporabljajo naslov, ki je nastavljen kot "
":guilabel:`Naslov za dostavo` na prodajnem nalogu. Privzeto poročila o "
"računih prikazujejo tako naslov za dostavo kot naslov za izdajo računa, da "
"se stranko prepriča, da gre dostava na pravo lokacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:36
msgid ""
"Emails also go to different addresses. The quotation and sales order are "
"sent to the main contact's email, as usual, but the invoice is sent to the "
"email of the address set as the :guilabel:`Invoice Address` on the sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
"E-pošta gre tudi na različne naslove. Ponudba in prodajni nalog se pošljeta "
"na e-poštni naslov glavnega kontakta, kot običajno, račun pa se pošlje na e-"
"poštni naslov, ki je nastavljen kot :guilabel:`Naslov za izdajo računa` na "
"prodajnem nalogu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:41
msgid ""
"Reports, such as the delivery slip and invoice report, can "
"be :doc:`customized using Studio </applications/studio/pdf_reports>`."
msgstr ""
"Poročila, kot sta dobavnica in poročilo o računu, je mogoče "
":doc:`prilagoditi s Studiem </applications/studio/pdf_reports>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/customer_addresses.rst:43
msgid ""
"If :doc:`Send by Post <snailmail>` is checked when you "
"click :guilabel:`Send`, the invoice will be mailed to the invoice address."
msgstr ""
"Če je :doc:`Pošlji po pošti <snailmail>` označeno, ko kliknete "
":guilabel:`Pošlji`, bo račun poslan na račun za dostavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:3
msgid "Deferred revenues"
msgstr "Odloženi prihodki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Deferred revenues**, or **unearned revenues**, are invoices addressed to "
"customers for goods yet to be delivered or services yet to be rendered."
msgstr ""
"**Odloženi prihodki** ali **nerealizirani prihodki** so računi, naslovljeni "
"na stranke za blago, ki še ni bilo dostavljeno, ali storitve, ki še niso "
"bile opravljene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:8
msgid ""
"The company cannot report them on the current **profit and loss statement**, "
"or *income statement*, since the goods and services will be effectively "
"delivered/rendered in the future."
msgstr ""
"Podjetje jih ne more prikazati v trenutnem **izkazu poslovnega izida** ali "
"*izkazu prihodkov in odhodkov*, saj bodo blago in storitve dejansko "
"dostavljeni/opravljeni v prihodnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:11
msgid ""
"These future revenues must be deferred on the company's balance sheet among "
"the current liabilities until they can be **recognized**, at once or over a "
"defined period, on the profit and loss statement."
msgstr ""
"Ti prihodnji prihodki morajo biti odloženi v bilanci stanja podjetja med "
"kratkoročne obveznosti, dokler jih ni mogoče **realizirati**, enkrat ali v "
"določenem obdobju, v izkazu poslovnega izida."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:15
msgid ""
"For example, let's say a business sells a software license of $1200 for 1 "
"year. They immediately invoice it to the customer but can't consider it "
"earned yet, as the future months of licensing have not yet been delivered. "
"Therefore, they post this new revenue in a deferred revenue account and "
"recognize it on a monthly basis. Each month, for the next 12 months, $100 "
"will be recognized as revenue."
msgstr ""
"Recimo na primer, da podjetje proda licenco za programsko opremo za 1200 $ "
"za 1 leto. Takoj izda račun stranki, vendar ga še ne more šteti za "
"realiziranega, saj prihodnji meseci licenciranja še niso bili dostavljeni. "
"Zato ta novi prihodek knjižijo na račun odloženih prihodkov in ga "
"realizirajo mesečno. Vsak mesec bo v naslednjih 12 mesecih 100 $ "
"realiziranih kot prihodek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:21
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting handles deferred revenues by spreading them in multiple "
"entries that are posted periodically."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Računovodstvo obravnava odložene prihodke tako, da jih razporedi v več "
"knjižb, ki se knjižijo periodično."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:25
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:25
msgid ""
"The server checks once a day if an entry must be posted. It might then take "
"up to 24 hours before you see a change from :guilabel:`Draft` "
"to :guilabel:`Posted`."
msgstr ""
"Strežnik enkrat dnevno preveri, ali je treba knjižbo objaviti. Lahko traja "
"do 24 ur, preden opazite spremembo iz :guilabel:`Osnutek` v "
":guilabel:`Objavljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:31
msgid ""
"Make sure the default settings are correctly configured for your business. "
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"The following options are available:"
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so privzete nastavitve pravilno konfigurirane za vaše "
"podjetje. To storite tako, da odprete :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. Na voljo so naslednje možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:34
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:34
msgid "Journal"
msgstr "Dnevnik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:35
msgid "The deferral entries are posted in this journal."
msgstr "Knjižbe odloženih prihodkov se knjižijo v tem dnevniku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:36
msgid "Deferred Revenue"
msgstr "Časovna razmejitev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:37
msgid ""
"Revenues are deferred on this Current Liability account until they are "
"recognized."
msgstr ""
"Prihodki so odloženi na tem računu kratkoročnih obveznosti, dokler niso "
"pripoznani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:41
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:41
msgid "Generate Entries"
msgstr "Generiraj vnose"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:39
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo :ref:`automatically generates <customer_invoices/deferred/"
"generate_on_validation>` the deferral entries when you post a customer "
"invoice. However, you can also choose to :ref:`generate them manually "
"<customer_invoices/deferred/generate_manually>` by selecting "
"the :guilabel:`Manually & Grouped` option instead."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto Odoo :ref:`samodejno ustvari <customer_invoices/deferred/"
"generate_on_validation>` vnose za odlog, ko knjižite račun kupca. Lahko pa "
"se odločite, da jih :ref:`ustvarite ročno <customer_invoices/deferred/"
"generate_manually>`, tako da namesto tega izberete možnost :guilabel:`Ročno "
"in združeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:64
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:64
msgid "Based on"
msgstr "Na osnovi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:44
msgid "There are three ways to calculate the deferred revenue recognition:"
msgstr "Obstajajo trije načini izračuna odloženega pripoznavanja prihodkov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:46
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Days`: The total amount is divided equally by the total number of "
"days in the period, inclusive of the start and end dates."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dnevi`: Skupni znesek je enakomerno razdeljen na skupno število "
"dni v obdobju, vključno z začetnim in končnim datumom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:48
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Months`: Each full month represents an equal proportion of the "
"total amount, regardless of the actual number of days in that month "
"(standardized basis)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Meseci`: Vsak poln mesec predstavlja enak delež skupnega zneska, "
"ne glede na dejansko število dni v tem mesecu (standardizirana osnova)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:50
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Full Months`: Any month started is treated as a complete month. "
"However, the final month is only considered full if the period extends to "
"the very last day of that month."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Polni meseci`: Vsak začeti mesec se obravnava kot popoln mesec. "
"Vendar se zadnji mesec šteje za poln le, če obdobje traja do zadnjega dne "
"tega meseca."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:53
msgid "Suppose an invoice of $1200 must be deferred over 12 months."
msgstr ""
"Predpostavimo, da je treba račun v višini 1200 $ odložiti preko 12 mesecev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:55
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:55
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Days` option accounts for different amounts depending on the "
"number of days in each month (e.g., ~$102 for January and ~$92 for February)."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :guilabel:`Dnevi` upošteva različne zneske glede na število dni v "
"vsakem mesecu (npr. ~102 $ za januar in ~92 $ za februar)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:57
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:57
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Months` option accounts for $100 each month prorated to the "
"number of days in that month (e.g., $50 for the first month if "
"the :guilabel:`Start Date` is set to the 15th of the month)."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :guilabel:`Meseci` upošteva 100 $ vsak mesec, sorazmerno s številom "
"dni v tem mesecu (npr. 50 $ za prvi mesec, če je :guilabel:`Datum začetka` "
"nastavljen na 15. dan v mesecu)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:60
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Full Months` option considers each month started to be full "
"(e.g., $100 for the first month even if the :guilabel:`Start Date` is set to "
"the 15th of the month); this means that with the :guilabel:`Full Months` "
"option, a full $100 is recognized in the first partial month, eliminating "
"the need for a 13th month to recognize any remainder as would be the case "
"when using the :guilabel:`Months` option."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :guilabel:`Polni meseci` obravnava vsak začeti mesec kot poln (npr. "
"100 $ za prvi mesec, tudi če je :guilabel:`Datum začetka` nastavljen na 15. "
"dan v mesecu); to pomeni, da se pri možnosti :guilabel:`Polni meseci` v "
"prvem delnem mesecu pripozna celotnih 100 $, kar odpravlja potrebo po 13. "
"mesecu za pripoznanje morebitnega preostanka, kot bi bilo v primeru uporabe "
"možnosti :guilabel:`Meseci`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:69
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:69
msgid "Generate deferral entries on validation"
msgstr "Ustvari vnose za odlog ob potrditvi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:72
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`Deferred Date` field is visible in "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab. In most cases, the start of the deferred "
"period should be in the same month as the :guilabel:`Invoice Date`. Deferred "
"revenue entries are posted from the invoice date and are displayed in the "
"report accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je polje :guilabel:`Datum odloga` vidno na zavihku "
":guilabel:`Vrstice računa`. V večini primerov bi moral začetek odloženega "
"obdobja biti v istem mesecu kot :guilabel:`Datum računa`. Vnosi odloženih "
"prihodkov se knjižijo od datuma računa in se ustrezno prikažejo v poročilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:77
msgid ""
"For each line of the invoice that should be deferred, specify the start and "
"end dates of the deferral period."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako vrstico računa, ki naj bo odložena, določite začetni in končni "
"datum obdobja odloga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:80
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Generate Entries` field in the **Settings** is set "
"to :guilabel:`On invoice/bill validation`, Odoo automatically generates the "
"deferral entries when the invoice is validated. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Deferred Entries` smart button to see them."
msgstr ""
"Če je polje :guilabel:`Ustvari vnose` v **Nastavitvah** nastavljeno na "
":guilabel:`Ob potrditvi računa/dobavnice`, Odoo samodejno ustvari vnose za "
"odlog, ko je račun potrjen. Kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Vnosi za "
"odlog`, da si jih ogledate."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:84
msgid ""
"One entry, dated on the same day as the invoice's accounting date, moves the "
"invoice amounts from the income account to the deferred account. The other "
"entries are deferral entries which, month after month, move the invoice "
"amounts from the deferred account to the income account to recognize the "
"revenue."
msgstr ""
"En vnos, datiran na isti dan kot računovodski datum računa, premakne zneske "
"računa z računa prihodkov na račun odloga. Drugi vnosi so vnosi za odlog, ki "
"mesec za mesecem premikajo zneske računa z računa odloga na račun prihodkov, "
"da pripoznajo prihodek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:90
msgid ""
"You can defer a January invoice of $1200 over 12 months by specifying a "
"start date of 01/01/2023 and an end date of 12/31/2023. At the end of "
"August, $800 is recognized as an income, whereas $400 remains on the "
"deferred account."
msgstr ""
"Račun iz januarja v višini 1200 $ lahko odložite preko 12 mesecev tako, da "
"določite datum začetka 1. 1. 2023 in datum konca 31. 12. 2023. Konec avgusta "
"je 800 $ pripoznanih kot prihodek, medtem ko 400 $ ostane na računu odloga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:97
msgid ""
"The deferred revenue report computes an overview of the necessary deferral "
"entries for each account. To access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Deferred Revenue`."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo o odloženih prihodkih izračuna pregled potrebnih vnosov za odlog za "
"vsak račun. Za dostop do njega pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročanje --> Odloženi prihodki`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:100
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:100
msgid ""
"To view the journal items of each account, click on the account name and "
"then :guilabel:`Journal Items`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled postavk dnevnika za vsak račun kliknite ime računa in nato "
":guilabel:`Postavke dnevnika`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:None
msgid "Deferred revenue report"
msgstr "Poročilo o odloženih prihodkih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:107
msgid ""
"Only invoices whose accounting date is before the end of the period of the "
"report are taken into account."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajo se samo računi, katerih računovodski datum je pred koncem obdobja "
"poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:113
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:113
msgid "Generate grouped deferral entries manually"
msgstr "Ustvari združene vnose za odlog ročno"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:115
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:115
msgid ""
"If you have a lot of deferred revenues and wish to reduce the number of "
"journal entries created, you can generate deferral entries manually. To do "
"so, set the :guilabel:`Generate Entries` field in the **Settings** "
"to :guilabel:`Manually & Grouped`. Odoo then aggregates the deferred amounts "
"in a single entry."
msgstr ""
"Če imate veliko odloženih prihodkov in želite zmanjšati število ustvarjenih "
"knjižb, lahko vnose za odlog ustvarite ročno. To storite tako, da polje "
":guilabel:`Ustvari vnose` v **Nastavitvah** nastavite na :guilabel:`Ročno in "
"združeno`. Odoo nato združi odložene zneske v en sam vnos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:120
msgid ""
"At the end of each month, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Deferred Revenue` and click the :guilabel:`Generate Entries` button. This "
"generates two deferral entries:"
msgstr ""
"Ob koncu vsakega meseca pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročanje --> Odloženi prihodki` in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Ustvari vnose`. "
"To ustvari dva vnosa za odlog:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:123
msgid ""
"One dated at the end of the month which aggregates, for each account, all "
"the deferred amounts of that month. This means that a part of the deferred "
"revenue is recognized at the end of that period."
msgstr ""
"Eden, datiran na konec meseca, ki združi vse odložene zneske tega meseca za "
"vsak račun. To pomeni, da je del odloženega prihodka pripoznan ob koncu tega "
"obdobja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:126
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/deferred_expenses.rst:126
msgid ""
"The reversal of this created entry, dated on the following day (i.e., the "
"first day of the next month) to cancel the previous entry."
msgstr ""
"Storno tega ustvarjenega vnosa, datiran na naslednji dan (tj. prvi dan "
"naslednjega meseca), da prekliče prejšnji vnos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/deferred_revenues.rst:130
msgid "There are three invoices deferred based on :guilabel:`Months`:"
msgstr "Obstajajo trije računi, odloženi na osnovi :guilabel:`Meseci`:"

