#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:301
msgid "Peppol deregistration from Odoo"
msgstr "Odjava iz Peppol prek Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:303
msgid ""
"Only one Peppol receiver registration can be active for each Peppol endpoint "
"identifier at a time. To stop using Odoo as the Peppol access point, e.g., "
"to switch to another provider or reconfigure the registration for a new "
"database, you must first deregister from Peppol. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`PEPPOL Electronic Invoicing` section, and click :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Advanced Configuration`. Then "
"click :guilabel:`Remove from Peppol` and confirm."
msgstr ""
"Za vsak identifikator končne točke Peppol je lahko hkrati aktivna samo ena "
"registracija prejemnika Peppol. Če želite prenehati uporabljati Odoo kot "
"dostopno točko Peppol, npr. za preklop na drugega ponudnika ali ponovno "
"konfiguriranje registracije za novo podatkovno bazo, se morate najprej "
"odjaviti iz Peppol. To storite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se "
"pomaknete do razdelka :guilabel:`PEPPOL elektronsko izdajanje računov` in "
"kliknete :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Napredna konfiguracija`. Nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Odstrani iz Peppol` in potrdite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:310
msgid ""
"Once removed, the Peppol registration is deleted from the database, and "
"documents can no longer be sent or received via Peppol in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Ko je odstranjena, se registracija Peppol izbriše iz podatkovne baze in "
"dokumentov ni več mogoče pošiljati ali prejemati prek Peppol v Odoo."

