"standardom in združljive z zahtevami, ki jih določa `Administración Federal "
"de Ingresos Públicos (AFIP) <https://www.afip.gob.ar/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/argentina.rst:12
