"prilagojene vašim specifičnim poslovnim potrebam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:5
msgid "Odoo electronic invoicing in Belgium"
msgstr "Elektronsko izdajanje računov Odoo v Belgiji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing is your trusted partner for safe, efficient, and legally "
"compliant e-invoicing solutions tailored to Belgium's regulatory standards, "
"and compatible with the European `Peppol <https://peppol.org/about/>`_ "
"framework."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Invoicing je vaš zaupanja vreden partner za varne, učinkovite in "
"zakonsko skladne rešitve e-izdajanja računov, prilagojene regulativnim "
"standardom Belgije in združljive z evropskim okvirom `Peppol <https://"
"peppol.org/about/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:12
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Belgium"
msgstr "Pravni okvir za e-izdajanje računov v Belgiji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:14
msgid ""
"In Belgium, businesses must adhere to e-invoicing laws that ensure secure, "
"authentic, and storable transactions. The primary regulation governing e-"
"invoicing requirements in Belgium is the `Belgian VAT Code <https://"
"finances.belgium.be/fr/sur_le_spf/r%C3%A9glementation/"
"r%C3%A9glementation-2023/tva>`_ and its related `e-invoicing standards for "
"public procurement <https://www.ejustice.just.fgov.be/cgi_loi/article.pl?"
"language=fr&sum_date=&pd_search=2023-09-21&numac_search=2023045155&page=1&lg_txt=F&caller=list&2023045155=0&trier=promulgation&fr=f&nm_ecran=2023045155&choix1=et&choix2=et>`_, "
"which align with `EU Directive 2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-"
"content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_. These laws mandate that all "
"businesses engaged in :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` transactions must "
"use e-invoicing via Mercurius, Belgium's official electronic invoicing "
"platform for public procurement transactions. Additionally, Belgium is part "
"of the Peppol network, which provides a standardized framework for cross-"
"border e-invoicing across Europe. Increasingly, e-invoicing is also "
"encouraged for B2B transactions to enhance tax compliance and transparency."
msgstr ""
"V Belgiji se morajo podjetja držati zakonov o e-izdajanju računov, ki "
"zagotavljajo varne, avtentične in shranjive transakcije. Glavna uredba, ki "
"določa zahteve za e-izdajanje računov v Belgiji, je `Belgian VAT Code "
"<https://finances.belgium.be/fr/sur_le_spf/r%C3%A9glementation/"
"r%C3%A9glementation-2023/tva>`_ in z njim povezani `standardi e-izdajanja "
"računov za javna naročila <https://www.ejustice.just.fgov.be/cgi_loi/"
"article.pl?language=fr&sum_date=&pd_search=2023-09-"
"21&numac_search=2023045155&page=1&lg_txt=F&caller=list&2023045155=0&trier=promulgation&fr=f&nm_ecran=2023045155&choix1=et&choix2=et>"
"`_, ki so usklajeni z `Direktivo EU 2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/"
"legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_. Ti zakoni določajo, da "
"morajo vsa podjetja, ki so vključena v transakcije :abbr:`B2G (poslovanje z "
"vlado)`, uporabljati e-izdajanje računov prek platforme Mercurius, uradne "
"belgijske platforme za elektronsko izdajanje računov za transakcije javnih "
"naročil. Poleg tega je Belgija del omrežja Peppol, ki zagotavlja "
"standardiziran okvir za čezmejno e-izdajanje računov v Evropi. E-izdajanje "
"računov je vse bolj spodbujano tudi za transakcije B2B za izboljšanje davčne "
"skladnosti in preglednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:26
msgid "Compliance with Belgian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Skladnost z belgijskimi predpisi o e-izdajanju računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:31
msgid ""
"**Peppol-compliant formats**: Odoo supports the standardized XML (:abbr:`UBL "
"(Universal Business Language)`) format for Peppol, ensuring compliance with "
"both Belgian and European e-invoicing standards. This ensures your invoices "
"meet the legal requirements for public procurement in Belgium and other EU "
"countries. Odoo enables businesses to send e-invoices directly to government "
"entities in compliance with Belgian regulations through Belgium’s Mercurius "
"platform for public procurement."
msgstr ""
"**Formati, skladni s Peppol**: Odoo podpira standardizirani format XML "
"(:abbr:`UBL (Universal Business Language)`) za Peppol, kar zagotavlja "
"skladnost z belgijskimi in evropskimi standardi e-izdajanja računov. To "
"zagotavlja, da vaši računi izpolnjujejo zakonske zahteve za javna naročila v "
"Belgiji in drugih državah EU. Odoo podjetjem omogoča pošiljanje e-računov "
"neposredno vladnim organom v skladu z belgijskimi predpisi prek belgijske "
"platforme Mercurius za javna naročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrieval**: In accordance with Belgian requirements to "
"store invoices for a minimum of seven years, Odoo securely archives all "
"invoices in a tamper-proof system, ensuring that they can be easily "
"retrieved during audits."
msgstr ""
"**Varno shranjevanje in iskanje**: V skladu z belgijskimi zahtevami za "
"shranjevanje računov najmanj sedem let Odoo varno arhivira vse račune v "
"sistemu, zaščitenem pred nedovoljenim spreminjanjem, kar zagotavlja, da jih "
"je mogoče med revizijami enostavno najti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium.rst:40
msgid ""
"**Automatic VAT calculation and reporting**: Odoo Invoicing helps businesses "
"comply with Belgian VAT requirements by automatically calculating and "
"including VAT in invoices and ensuring that each invoice follows the legal "
"format for B2B and :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Samodejni izračun in poročanje DDV**: Odoo Invoicing pomaga podjetjem pri "
"skladnosti z belgijskimi zahtevami za DDV s samodejnim izračunom in "
"vključevanjem DDV v račune ter zagotavlja, da vsak račun ustreza zakonskemu "
"formatu za transakcije B2B in :abbr:`B2G (poslovanje z vlado)`."

