msgstr "Pravni okvir za e-izdajanje računov v Braziliji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/brazil.rst:15
msgid ""
"In Brazil, e-invoicing is highly regulated and mandatory for most businesses "
"to ensure tax compliance and transparency. The key regulations governing e-"
"invoicing, which is supported through integration with Avalara, include:"
msgstr ""
