#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/chile.rst:14
msgid ""
"Chile is a pioneer in mandatory electronic invoicing, with comprehensive "
"regulations to ensure tax compliance and enhance transparency. Key elements "
"include:"
