"pravnim strokovnjakom, ki pozna ekvadorske predpise za e-izdajanje računov, "
"da zagotovite skladnost, prilagojeno vašim specifičnim poslovnim potrebam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:5
msgid "Odoo electronic invoicing in Estonia"
msgstr "Odoo elektronsko izdajanje računov v Estoniji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing is your trusted partner for safe, efficient, and legally "
"compliant e-invoicing solutions tailored to Estonia's regulatory standards."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Invoicing je vaš zanesljiv partner za varne, učinkovite in zakonsko "
"skladne rešitve za e-izdajanje računov, prilagojene regulativnim standardom "
"Estonije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Estonia"
msgstr "Pravni okvir za e-izdajanje računov v Estoniji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Estonia, businesses must comply with e-invoicing regulations to ensure "
"secure, authentic, and storable transactions. The main legal framework "
"governing e-invoicing in Estonia is the `Accounting Act <https://"
"www.riigiteataja.ee/en/eli/ee/514052021001/consolide/current>`_ and its "
"provisions related to e-invoicing, which align with `EU Directive 2014/55/EU "
"<https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ "
"on e-invoicing in public procurement. Since 2019, :abbr:`B2G (business-to-"
"government)` transactions must use electronic invoices via Estonia's Rik's e-"
"Invoicing System, the government's platform for public sector e-invoicing. "
"Estonia is also part of the Peppol network, which ensures standardized cross-"
"border e-invoicing across Europe. Additionally, the use of e-invoicing is "
"encouraged for B2B transactions, promoting better transparency, efficiency, "
"and compliance with VAT requirements."
msgstr ""
"V Estoniji morajo podjetja upoštevati predpise za e-izdajanje računov, da "
"zagotovijo varne, pristne in shranjive transakcije. Glavni pravni okvir, ki "
"ureja e-izdajanje računov v Estoniji, je `Accounting Act <https://"
"www.riigiteataja.ee/en/eli/ee/514052021001/consolide/current>`_ in njegove "
"določbe v zvezi z e-izdajanjem računov, ki so usklajene z `EU Directive 2014/"
"55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/"
"?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ o e-izdajanju računov pri javnem naročanju. Od "
"leta 2019 morajo transakcije :abbr:`B2G (poslovanje z vlado)` uporabljati "
"elektronske račune prek estonskega sistema Rik's e-Invoicing System, vladne "
"platforme za e-izdajanje računov v javnem sektorju. Estonija je tudi del "
"omrežja Peppol, ki zagotavlja standardizirano čezmejno e-izdajanje računov "
"po Evropi. Poleg tega je uporaba e-izdajanja računov spodbujana za "
"transakcije B2B, kar spodbuja boljšo preglednost, učinkovitost in skladnost "
"z zahtevami za DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:24
msgid "Compliance with Estonian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Skladnost z estonskimi predpisi za e-izdajanje računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Supported formats**: Odoo supports standard e-invoice formats, such as XML "
"in :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business Language)` format, which is fully "
"compatible with Estonia's Rik’s e-Invoicing System for public procurement "
"transactions. Additionally, Odoo enables seamless transmission of e-invoices "
"through platforms connected to the Peppol network, ensuring compliance with "
"Estonian and EU e-invoicing standards."
msgstr ""
"**Podprti formati**: Odoo podpira standardne formate e-računov, kot je XML v "
"formatu :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business Language)`, ki je popolnoma združljiv "
"z estonskim sistemom e-računov Rik za transakcije javnih naročil. Poleg tega "
"Odoo omogoča nemoteno pošiljanje e-računov prek platform, povezanih z "
"omrežjem Peppol, kar zagotavlja skladnost z estonskimi in standardi EU za e-"
"račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:34
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrival**: In accordance with Estonian regulations to "
"store invoices for a minimum of seven years, Odoo securely archives all "
"invoices in a tamper-proof system, making them easily retrievable during "
"audits."
msgstr ""
"**Varno shranjevanje in pridobivanje**: V skladu z estonskimi predpisi o "
"shranjevanju računov najmanj sedem let Odoo varno arhivira vse račune v "
"sistemu, zaščitenem pred nedovoljenimi spremembami, zaradi česar so med "
"revizijami enostavno dostopni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Automatic VAT calculation and reporting**: Odoo Invoicing automates VAT "
"calculations and ensures invoices are formatted to meet Denmark’s legal "
"requirements for :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` and B2B transactions, "
"helping businesses compliant with local tax laws."
msgstr ""
"**Samodejni izračun in poročanje DDV**: Odoo Invoicing avtomatizira izračune "
"DDV in zagotavlja, da so računi oblikovani v skladu z danskimi pravnimi "
"zahtevami za transakcije :abbr:`B2G (podjetje javnemu sektorju)` in B2B, s "
"čimer pomaga podjetjem pri skladnosti z lokalnimi davčnimi zakoni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:43
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of Estonian e-invoicing laws and how Odoo "
"Invoicing supports compliance with the Accounting Act, Peppol standards, and "
"other relevant regulations. It does not constitute legal advice. We "
"recommend consulting with a tax advisor or legal professional familiar with "
"Estonian e-invoicing regulations to ensure compliance tailored to your "
"specific business needs."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran ponuja pregled estonskih zakonov o e-računih in kako Odoo Invoicing "
"podpira skladnost z zakonom o računovodstvu, standardi Peppol in drugimi "
"ustreznimi predpisi. Ne predstavlja pravnega svetovanja. Priporočamo "
"posvetovanje z davčnim svetovalcem ali pravnim strokovnjakom, ki pozna "
"estonske predpise o e-računih, da zagotovite skladnost, prilagojeno vašim "
"specifičnim poslovnim potrebam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/finland.rst:5
msgid "Odoo electronic invoicing in Finland"
msgstr "Elektronski računi Odoo na Finskem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/finland.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo Invoicing is your trusted partner for safe, efficient, and legally "
"compliant e-invoicing solutions tailored to Finland's regulatory standards."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Invoicing je vaš zaupanja vreden partner za varne, učinkovite in "
"zakonsko skladne rešitve e-računov, prilagojene finskim regulativnim "
"standardom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/finland.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Finland"
msgstr "Pravni okvir za e-račune na Finskem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/finland.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Finland, businesses must comply with e-invoicing regulations to ensure "
"secure, authentic, and storable transactions. The primary legal framework "
"governing e-invoicing is the `Act on Electronic Invoicing (241/2019) "
"<https://www.finlex.fi/fi/laki/alkup/2019/20190241#Pidp446241968>`_, which "
"aligns with `EU Directive 2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-"
"content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ on electronic invoicing in public "
"procurement. Under Finnish law, all :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` "
"transactions require the use of electronic invoices via Apix Messaging or "
"other Peppol-connected platforms, Finland’s standard for public sector e-"
"invoicing. Finland is also part of the Peppol network, ensuring "
"interoperability and standardization for cross-border e-invoicing within the "
"EU. Additionally, e-invoicing is widely adopted for B2B transactions, "
"promoting efficient processes and improved tax compliance."
msgstr ""
"Na Finskem morajo podjetja upoštevati predpise o e-računih, da zagotovijo "
"varne, pristne in shranljive transakcije. Primarni pravni okvir, ki ureja e-"
"račune, je `zakon o elektronskih računih (241/2019) <https://www.finlex.fi/"
"fi/laki/alkup/2019/20190241#Pidp446241968>`_, ki je usklajen z `direktivo EU "
"2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/"
"?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ o elektronskih računih pri javnih naročilih. Po "
"finskem pravu vse transakcije :abbr:`B2G (podjetje javnemu sektorju)` "
"zahtevajo uporabo elektronskih računov prek Apix Messaging ali drugih "
"platform, povezanih s Peppol, finskega standarda za e-račune javnega "
"sektorja. Finska je tudi del omrežja Peppol, kar zagotavlja "
"interoperabilnost in standardizacijo za čezmejne e-račune v EU. Poleg tega "
"so e-računi široko sprejeti za transakcije B2B, kar spodbuja učinkovite "
"procese in izboljšano skladnost z davki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/finland.rst:25
msgid "Compliance with Finnish e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Skladnost s finskimi predpisi o e-računih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/finland.rst:27
msgid ""
"Odoo invoicing module makes it easy for businesses to adhere to Finland's e-"
