#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/italy.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Italy"
msgstr "Pravni okvir za e-računovodstvo v Italiji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/italy.rst:13
msgid ""
"Italy has one of the most advanced e-invoicing frameworks in Europe, "
"governed by the `Italian budget law <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/"
"2022/12/29/22G00211/sg>`_ and regulations issued by the Agenzia delle "
"Entrate. Since 2019, e-invoicing is mandatory for B2B, B2C, and :abbr:`B2G "
"(business-to-government)` transactions. All e-invoices must be submitted "
"through the :abbr:`Sdi (Sistema di Interscambio)`, the Italian government's "
"centralized exchange system. The format for e-invoices is FatturaPA, a "
"structured XML format specifically designed for compliance with Italian "
"regulations. As part of its compliance with `EU Directive 2014/55/EU "
"<https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, "
"Italy also supports Peppol standards for cross-border e-invoicing."
msgstr ""
"Italija ima enega najbolj naprednih okvirov za e-računovodstvo v Evropi, ki "
"ga ureja `italijanski proračunski zakon <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/"
"eli/id/2022/12/29/22G00211/sg>`_ in predpisi Agenzia delle Entrate. Od leta "
"2019 je e-računovodstvo obvezno za transakcije B2B, B2C in :abbr:`B2G "
"(poslovnih z državo)`. Vsi e-računi morajo biti poslani prek :abbr:`Sdi "
"(Sistema di Interscambio)`, centraliziranega sistema izmenjave italijanske "
"vlade. Format za e-račune je FatturaPA, strukturiran format XML, posebej "
"zasnovan za skladnost z italijanskimi predpisi. Kot del skladnosti z "
"`Direktivo EU 2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/"
"?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ Italija podpira tudi standarde Peppol za čezmejno "
"e-računovodstvo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/italy.rst:23
msgid "Compliance with Italian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Skladnost z italijanskimi predpisi o e-računovodstvu"

