#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/romania.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Romania"
msgstr "Pravni okvir za e-fakturiranje v Romuniji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/romania.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Romania, e-invoicing is regulated under the `Fiscal Code <http://"
"www.dreptonline.ro/carti/start_carte.php?id_carte=324>`_ and aligned with "
"`EU Directive 2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?"
"uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, which mandates e-invoicing for :abbr:`B2G "
"(business-to-government)` transactions. Romania has implemented the RO e-"
"Factura system, the national platform for issuing and receiving electronic "
"invoices in a standardized format. The use of RO e-Factura is mandatory "
"for :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` transactions and for specific high-"
"risk B2B sectors, with further expansion anticipated. Romania is also "
"integrated with the Peppol network, facilitating cross-border e-invoicing "
"and compliance within the European Union."
msgstr ""
"V Romuniji e-fakturiranje ureja `Davčni zakonik <http://www.dreptonline.ro/"
"carti/start_carte.php?id_carte=324>`_ in je usklajeno z `Direktivo EU 2014/"
"55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/"
"?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, ki nalaga e-fakturiranje za transakcije "
":abbr:`B2G (podjetje-vlada)`. Romunija je uvedla sistem RO e-Factura, "
"nacionalno platformo za izdajo in prejemanje elektronskih računov v "
"standardizirani obliki. Uporaba RO e-Factura je obvezna za transakcije "
":abbr:`B2G (podjetje-vlada)` in za določene visoko tvegane sektorje B2B, "
"pričakuje pa se nadaljnja širitev. Romunija je integrirana tudi z omrežjem "
"Peppol, kar olajšuje čezmejno e-fakturiranje in skladnost v Evropski uniji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/romania.rst:23
msgid "Compliance with Romanian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr "Skladnost s predpisi o e-fakturiranju v Romuniji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/romania.rst:25
msgid ""
"Odoo invoicing module is fully equipped to help businesses comply with "
"Romania’s specific e-invoicing requirements. Here’s how Odoo supports "
"compliance:"
msgstr ""
"Modul Odoo Invoicing je v celoti opremljen za pomoč podjetjem pri "
"izpolnjevanju posebnih zahtev Romunije glede e-fakturiranja. Tako Odoo "
"podpira skladnost:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/romania.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Supported formats**: Odoo supports XML in :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business "
"Language)` and the structured formats required by RO e-Factura, ensuring "
"compliance with Romania's e-invoicing standards for B2G and high-risk B2B "
"transactions. Additionally, Odoo supports formats compatible with the Peppol "
"network, enabling seamless cross-border invoicing. Odoo integrates with the "
"RO e-Factura system, allowing businesses to generate, validate, and submit e-"
"invoices directly to Romanian public authorities or private entities as "
"required by law. Odoo helps businesses comply with eTransport requirements "
"by generating and managing the data necessary for reporting the movement of "
"high-fiscal risk goods. This includes shipment details such as the nature of "
"the goods, vehicle information, and delivery destinations, ensuring timely "
"submission to the :abbr:`ANAF (Romanian National Agency for Fiscal "
"Administration)`."
msgstr ""
"**Podprte oblike**: Odoo podpira XML v obliki :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business "
"Language – univerzalni poslovni jezik)` in strukturirane oblike, ki jih "
"zahteva RO e-Factura, kar zagotavlja skladnost s standardi e-fakturiranja v "
"Romuniji za transakcije B2G in visoko tvegane transakcije B2B. Poleg tega "
"Odoo podpira oblike, združljive z omrežjem Peppol, kar omogoča nemoteno "
"čezmejno fakturiranje. Odoo se integrira s sistemom RO e-Factura, kar "
"podjetjem omogoča neposredno generiranje, preverjanje in pošiljanje e-"
"računov romunskim javnim organom ali zasebnim subjektom, kot to zahteva "
"zakon. Odoo pomaga podjetjem izpolnjevati zahteve eTransport z generiranjem "
"in upravljanjem podatkov, potrebnih za poročanje o gibanju blaga z visokim "
"fiskalnim tveganjem. To vključuje podrobnosti o pošiljki, kot so vrsta "
"blaga, podatki o vozilu in cilji dostave, kar zagotavlja pravočasno "
"predložitev :abbr:`ANAF (Romunska nacionalna agencija za davčno upravo)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/romania.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrieval**: In compliance with Romanian regulations, "
"which require invoices to be stored for a minimum of ten years, Odoo "
"securely archives all invoices in a tamper-proof system, ensuring "
"accessibility during audits or inspections."
msgstr ""
"**Varno shranjevanje in iskanje**: V skladu z romunskimi predpisi, ki "
"zahtevajo hrambo računov najmanj deset let, Odoo varno arhivira vse račune v "
"sistemu, odpornem na posege, kar zagotavlja dostopnost med revizijami ali "
"inšpekcijskimi pregledi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/romania.rst:41
msgid ""
"**Automatic VAT calculation and reporting**: Odoo Invoicing automates VAT "
"calculations and formats invoices to comply with Romanian VAT requirements, "
"ensuring accuracy and adherence to legal standards for both :abbr:`B2G "
"(business-to-government)` and B2B transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Samodejno izračunavanje in poročanje DDV**: Odoo Invoicing avtomatizira "
"izračune DDV in oblikuje račune v skladu z romunskimi zahtevami glede DDV, "
"kar zagotavlja natančnost in skladnost s pravnimi standardi tako za "
"transakcije :abbr:`B2G (podjetje-vlada)` kot B2B."

