#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/spain.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Spain"
msgstr "Pravni okvir za e-fakturiranje v Španiji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/spain.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Spain, e-invoicing is governed by the `Ley de Facturación Electrónica "
"<https://www.facturae.gob.es/face/Paginas/FACE.aspx>`_ and aligned with `EU "
"Directive 2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?"
"uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, mandating e-invoicing for :abbr:`B2G (business-to-"
"government)` transactions. All invoices to public sector entities must be "
"submitted through the FACe platform, Spain’s official electronic invoicing "
"hub, using the required Facturae format. Additionally, the :abbr:`SII "
"(Immediate Supply of Information)` system mandates near real-time reporting "
"of VAT-related invoice data for certain companies, reinforcing transparency "
"and compliance. While e-invoicing is not yet mandatory for B2B transactions, "
"its adoption is expected to expand in the near future."
msgstr ""
"V Španiji e-fakturiranje ureja `Zakon o elektronskem fakturiranju <https://"
"www.facturae.gob.es/face/Paginas/FACE.aspx>`_ in je usklajeno z `Direktivo "
"EU 2014/55/EU <https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/"
"?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_, ki nalaga e-fakturiranje za transakcije "
":abbr:`B2G (podjetje-vlada)`. Vsi računi javnemu sektorju morajo biti "
"predloženi prek platforme FACe, španskega uradnega vozlišča za elektronsko "
"fakturiranje, z uporabo zahtevane oblike Facturae. Poleg tega sistem "
":abbr:`SII (Immediate Supply of Information – takojšnja dobava informacij)` "
"nalaga skoraj takojšnje poročanje podatkov o računih, povezanih z DDV, za "
"določena podjetja, kar krepi preglednost in skladnost. Čeprav e-fakturiranje "
"še ni obvezno za transakcije B2B, se pričakuje, da se bo njegova uporaba v "
"bližnji prihodnosti razširila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/spain.rst:23
msgid "Compliance with Spanish e-invoicing regulations"
