#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/avg_price_valuation.rst:352
msgid ""
"In this example, a company starts with zero units of a product, table, in "
"stock. Then, 8 tables are received from the vendor. When the bill is "
"received from vendor for 8 tables:"
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru ima podjetje na začetku nič enot izdelka, mize, na zalogi. "
"Nato je od dobavitelja prejeto 8 miz. Ko je prejet račun od dobavitelja za 8 "
"miz:"

