#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **chart of accounts (COA)** is the list of all the accounts used to "
"record financial transactions in the general ledger of an organization. The "
"chart of accounts can be found under :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Chart of Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"**Kontni načrt** je seznam vseh računov, ki se uporabljajo za beleženje "
"finančnih transakcij v glavni knjigi organizacije. Kontni načrt najdete v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> Kontni načrt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:9
msgid ""
"When browsing your chart of accounts, you can sort the accounts "
"by :guilabel:`Code`, :guilabel:`Account Name`, or :guilabel:`Type`, but "
"other options are available in the drop-down menu"
msgstr ""
"Ko brskate po kontnem načrtu, lahko račune razvrstite po :guilabel:`Šifri`, "
":guilabel:`Imenu računa` ali :guilabel:`Vrsti`, vendar so v spustnem meniju "
"na voljo tudi druge možnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:None
msgid "Drop-down toggle button"
msgstr "Gumb za preklop spustnega menija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:None
msgid "Group the accounts by type in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr "Združite račune po vrsti v Odoo računovodstvu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:21
msgid "Configuration of an account"
msgstr "Konfiguracija računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:23
msgid ""
"The country you select during the creation of your database (or additional "
"company in your database) determines which :doc:`fiscal localization package "
"<../../fiscal_localizations>` is installed by default. This package adds a "
"standard chart of accounts already configured according to the country's "
"regulations, including expense accounts that may be :ref:`linked to default "
"asset models <chart-of-account/assets>`. You can use the chart of accounts "
"directly or modify it according to your company's needs."
msgstr ""
"Država, ki jo izberete med ustvarjanjem vaše baze podatkov (ali dodatnega "
"podjetja v vaši bazi podatkov), določa, kateri :doc:`paket fiskalne "
"lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>` je privzeto nameščen. Ta paket "
"doda standardni kontni načrt, ki je že konfiguriran v skladu s predpisi "
"države, vključno z računom odhodkov, ki je lahko :ref:`povezan s privzetimi "
"modeli sredstev <chart-of-account/assets>`. Kontni načrt lahko uporabite "
"neposredno ali ga spremenite glede na potrebe vašega podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:30
msgid ""
"To create a new account, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Chart of Accounts`, click :guilabel:`Create`, and fill in (at the "
"minimum) the required fields (:guilabel:`Code, Account Name, Type`)."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li vytvořit nový účet, přejděte do :menuselection:`Účetnictví --> "
"Konfigurace --> Účtová osnova`, klikněte na :guilabel:`Vytvořit` a vyplňte "
"(minimálně) povinná pole (:guilabel:`Kód, Název účtu, Typ`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:35
msgid ""
"It is not possible to modify the **fiscal localization** of a company once a "
"journal entry has been posted."
msgstr ""
"Po zaúčtování položky deníku není možné upravit **fiskální lokalizaci** "
"společnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:39
msgid "Code and account name"
msgstr "Šifra in ime računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:41
msgid ""
"Each account is identified by its :guilabel:`Code` and :guilabel:`Account "
"Name`, which also indicate the account's purpose."
msgstr ""
"Vsak račun je identificiran s svojo :guilabel:`Šifro` in :guilabel:`Imenom "
"računa`, ki prav tako označujeta namen računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:47
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Tip"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:49
msgid ""
"Correctly configuring the account's :guilabel:`Type` is critical as it "
"serves multiple purposes:"
msgstr ""
"Pravilna konfiguracija :guilabel:`Tipa` računa je ključnega pomena, saj "
"služi več namenom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:51
msgid "Provide information on the account's purpose and behavior"
msgstr "Zagotoviti informacije o namenu in obnašanju računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:52
msgid "Generate country-specific legal and financial reports"
msgstr "Vygenerujte právní a finanční výkazy specifické pro danou zemi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:53
msgid "Set the rules to close a fiscal year"
msgstr "Nastavte pravidla pro uzavření fiskálního roku"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:54
msgid "Generate opening entries"
msgstr "Vygenerujte otevírací položky"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts.rst:56
msgid ""
"To configure an account type, open the :guilabel:`Type` field's drop-down "
"selector and select the corresponding type from the following list:"
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li konfigurovat typ účtu, otevřete rozevírací nabídku pole "
":guilabel:`Typ` a vyberte odpovídající typ z následujícího seznamu:"

