#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:3
msgid "Consolidation"
msgstr "Konsolidacija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:5
msgid ""
"Consolidation allows combining financial data from **multiple separate "
"companies**, each with its own books, into a unified view, providing a "
"\"fair image\" of the entire group's financial health."
msgstr ""
"Konsolidacija omogoča združevanje finančnih podatkov iz **več ločenih "
"podjetij**, od katerih ima vsako svoje knjige, v enoten pogled, ki "
"zagotavlja \"resnično podobo\" finančnega zdravja celotne skupine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:8
msgid ""
"It helps create a clear, comprehensive view of the group's financial "
"performance by combining data from multiple companies."
msgstr ""
"Pomaga ustvariti jasen, celovit pregled finančne uspešnosti skupine s "
"kombiniranjem podatkov iz več podjetij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:12
msgid ""
"Consolidating companies involves **legally separate entities**, "
"whereas :ref:`branches <general/branches>` are **subdivisions** of a single "
"legal entity which often share the head office's resources (journals, taxes, "
"accounts, fiscal positions) and are not consolidated in the same way."
msgstr ""
"Konsolidacija podjetij vključuje **pravno ločene subjekte**, medtem ko so "
":ref:`podružnice <general/branches>` **pododdelki** enega pravnega subjekta, "
"ki pogosto delijo vire glavne pisarne (dnevnike, davke, račune, davčne "
"pozicije) in se ne konsolidirajo na enak način."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:20
msgid "Consolidation tools"
msgstr "Orodja za konsolidacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Several tools** combined together will contribute to the construction of "
"the financial consolidation:"
msgstr "**Več orodij** skupaj prispeva k izdelavi finančne konsolidacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Account Mapping:** Similar accounts from different companies can be mapped "
"together. This allows Odoo to combine them correctly in consolidated "
"reports. To map accounts, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Chart of Accounts`.  Click :guilabel:`View` on the account line. In "
"the :guilabel:`Mapping` tab, enter a code in the corresponding "
"company :guilabel:`Code` column to map the account."
msgstr ""
"**Preslikava računov:** Podobni računi iz različnih podjetij se lahko "
"preslikajo skupaj. To omogoča Odoo, da jih pravilno kombinira v "
"konsolidiranih poročilih. Za preslikavo računov pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Kontni načrt`. Kliknite "
":guilabel:`Poglej` v vrstici računa. V zavihku :guilabel:`Preslikava` "
"vnesite kodo v ustrezen stolpec podjetja :guilabel:`Koda`, da preslikate "
"račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:None
msgid "Mapping different codes to different companies."
msgstr "Preslikava različnih kod različnim podjetjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:36
msgid ""
":ref:`Import mapping <consolidation_import_account_mapping>` or merge "
"existing accounts using the :ref:`merging tool <consolidation_merge_tool>` "
"can simplify the process."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Uvoz preslikave <consolidation_import_account_mapping>` ali "
"združevanje obstoječih računov z uporabo :ref:`orodja za združevanje "
"<consolidation_merge_tool>` lahko poenostavi postopek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:39
msgid ""
"When multiple accounts from one company are mapped to a single account in "
"another, it is then possible to group the multiple accounts into a single "
"line in the other company's reporting by :ref:`grouping by <customize-"
"reports/lines-group-by>` the *account code* (`account_code`) rather than the "
"*account ID* (`account_id`)."
msgstr ""
"Ko je več računov iz enega podjetja preslikanih na en sam račun v drugem, je "
"mogoče združiti več računov v eno vrstico v poročanju drugega podjetja z "
":ref:`združevanjem po <customize-reports/lines-group-by>` *kodi računa* "
"(`account_code`) namesto po *ID računa* (`account_id`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:45
msgid ""
"Some reports, such as the :ref:`profit and loss <accounting/reporting/profit-"
"and-loss>`, split the lines into different sections by account type. When "
"these reports are grouped by account code, the section splits are "
"maintained, but within each section, line grouping by account code is "
"respected."
msgstr ""
"Nekatera poročila, kot je :ref:`izkaz poslovnega izida <accounting/reporting/"
"profit-and-loss>`, razdelijo vrstice v različne razdelke po vrsti računa. Ko "
"so ta poročila združena po kodi računa, se razdelitev razdelkov ohrani, "
"vendar se znotraj vsakega razdelka upošteva združevanje vrstic po kodi "
"računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:51
msgid ""
"Belgian Company is a parent company with a subsidiary, American Company. "
"American Company has five income accounts:"
msgstr ""
"Belgian Company je matično podjetje s hčerinsko družbo, American Company. "
"American Company ima pet prihodkovnih računov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:54
msgid "400000 Product Sales - Domestic"
msgstr "400000 Prodaja izdelkov - domače"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:55
msgid "400100 Product Sales - International"
msgstr "400100 Prodaja izdelkov - mednarodne"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:56
msgid "410000 Service Revenue - Consulting"
msgstr "410000 Prihodki od storitev - Svetovanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:57
msgid "420000 Subscription Revenue"
msgstr "420000 Prihodki od naročnin"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:58
msgid "430000 Freight & Handling Revenue"
msgstr "430000 Prihodki od prevoza in manipulacije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:60
msgid ""
"All five of the US income accounts correspond to one single income account "
"(700000 Income) in the Belgian Company."
msgstr ""
"Vseh pet prihodkovnih računov ZDA ustreza enemu samemu prihodkovnemu računu "
"(700000 Prihodki) v Belgian Company."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:63
msgid ""
"For the Belgian Company's profit and loss report to show one line for all of "
"the American Company's combined income accounts related to the Belgian "
"Company's single income account, all five income accounts from the American "
"Company must be mapped to The Belgian Company's 700000 Income account, and "
"the report's lines must be :ref:`grouped by <customize-reports/lines-group-"
"by>` the account code."
msgstr ""
"Da bi izkaz poslovnega izida Belgian Company prikazal eno vrstico za vse "
"kombinirane prihodkovne račune American Company, povezane z enim "
"prihodkovnim računom Belgian Company, je treba vseh pet prihodkovnih računov "
"iz American Company preslikati na račun 700000 Prihodki Belgian Company, "
"vrstice poročila pa morajo biti :ref:`združene po <customize-reports/lines-"
"group-by>` kodi računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:71
msgid ""
"**Multi-Ledgers:** Ledgers are fundamental to the process of consolidation. "
"They are either:"
msgstr ""
"**Več-glavne knjige:** Glavne knjige so temeljne za proces konsolidacije. So "
"bodisi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:73
msgid ""
"*Regular Ledgers:* Each company in the consolidation scope has its own "
"standard accounting ledger where all the regular day-to-day transactions are "
"recorded. It excludes the company's consolidation adjustment journals."
msgstr ""
"*Redne glavne knjige:* Vsako podjetje v obsegu konsolidacije ima svojo "
"standardno računovodsko glavno knjigo, kjer so zabeležene vse redne "
"vsakodnevne transakcije. Izključuje dnevnike konsolidacijskih prilagoditev "
"podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:77
msgid ""
"*Multi-Ledger for Consolidation:* The company doing the actual consolidation "
"also has a special multi-ledger. This one includes all the other companies' "
"consolidation adjustments journals (the ones excluded from their own "
"ledgers). This allows for viewing the total impact of all the adjustments."
msgstr ""
"*Več-glavna knjiga za konsolidacijo:* Podjetje, ki dejansko izvaja "
"konsolidacijo, ima tudi posebno več-glavno knjigo. Ta vključuje dnevnike "
"konsolidacijskih prilagoditev vseh drugih podjetij (tiste, ki so izključeni "
"iz njihovih lastnih glavnih knjig). To omogoča pregled celotnega vpliva vseh "
"prilagoditev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:82
msgid ""
"To create a new ledger, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Multi-Ledgers` and hit the :guilabel:`New` button. Enter a name, pick the "
"company the ledger is linked to and most importantly, determine which "
"journals are to be excluded from the ledger."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove knjige pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Več knjig` in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo`. Vnesite ime, "
"izberite podjetje, s katerim je knjiga povezana, in kar je najpomembneje, "
"določite, kateri dnevniki naj bodo iz knjige izključeni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:91
msgid ""
"**Multi-Company Selector:** The consolidated view can be accessed using the "
"multi-company"
msgstr ""
"**Izbirnik za več podjetij:** Do konsolidiranega pogleda lahko dostopate z "
"uporabo izbirnika za več podjetij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:89
msgid ""
"selector. Selecting the consolidating company as the current company and "
"making the other companies visible in the selector, all the journal items "
"are displayed from the consolidating company's perspective."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete konsolidirano podjetje kot trenutno podjetje in omogočite "
"vidnost drugih podjetij v izborniku, se vsi dnevniški vnosi prikažejo s "
"perspektive konsolidiranega podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:None
msgid "Selecting the main company and activating others."
msgstr "Izbira glavnega podjetja in aktiviranje drugih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:111
msgid ""
"**Horizontal Groups:** Odoo's reporting tools allow for combining multi-"
"ledgers and using"
msgstr ""
"**Horizontalne skupine:** Odoo-jeva orodja za poročanje omogočajo "
"združevanje več knjig in uporabo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:99
msgid ""
"horizontal groups to view the consolidated Balance Sheet or P&L. They also "
"show how much each company contributes to the overall consolidated figures."
msgstr ""
"horizontalnih skupin za ogled konsolidirane bilance stanja ali izkaza "
"poslovnega izida. Prikažejo tudi, koliko vsako podjetje prispeva k skupnim "
"konsolidiranim številkam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:102
msgid "Follow these steps to create an :guilabel:`Horizontal Group`:"
msgstr "Sledite tem korakom za ustvarjanje :guilabel:`Horizontalne skupine`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:105
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Horizontal Groups` "
"and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Horizontalne "
"skupine` in kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:107
msgid ""
"Add a :guilabel:`Group Name` and select the :guilabel:`Reports` where the "
"horizontal group can be used."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte :guilabel:`Naziv skupine` in izberite :guilabel:`Poročila`, kjer je "
"mogoče uporabiti horizontalno skupino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:109
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Field` column, click :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr "V stolpcu :guilabel:`Polje` kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:110
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Create rules` window, add a :guilabel:`Field` and create a "
"new :guilabel:`Domain` rule if needed. Then, click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari pravila` dodajte :guilabel:`Polje` in po potrebi "
"ustvarite novo pravilo :guilabel:`Domena`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani "
"in zapri`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:None
msgid "Using horizontal groups to see each company's contribution."
msgstr "Uporaba horizontalnih skupin za prikaz prispevka vsakega podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:117
msgid ""
"When opened, financial reports usually default to a statutory view, using "
"the company's regular ledger (including its consolidation adjustment). To "
"see the full consolidation picture, **make sure to select the multi-ledger** "
"that includes all the consolidation adjustments."
msgstr ""
"Ko so odprta, se finančna poročila običajno privzeto prikažejo v zakonskem "
"pogledu z uporabo redne knjige podjetja (vključno s konsolidacijskimi "
"prilagoditvami). Za ogled celotne konsolidacijske slike **poskrbite, da "
"izberete knjigo z več knjigami**, ki vključuje vse konsolidacijske "
"prilagoditve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:123
msgid ""
"**Cumulative Translation Adjustments:** When consolidating companies with "
"different currencies, Odoo handles the translation."
msgstr ""
"**Kumulativne prevajalske prilagoditve:** Pri konsolidaciji podjetij z "
"različnimi valutami Odoo upravlja prevod."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:126
msgid "Equity accounts: Use the historical exchange rate."
msgstr "Računi lastniškega kapitala: Uporabite zgodovinski menjalniški tečaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:128
msgid ""
"Profit and loss (P&L) accounts (including :ref:`appropriation accounts "
"<accounting/year-end/appropriation>`): Use the weighted average exchange "
"rate."
msgstr ""
"Računi dobička in izgube (vključno z :ref:`računi razporeditve <accounting/"
"year-end/appropriation>`): Uporabite tehtano povprečje menjalniških tečajev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:131
msgid ""
"Balance sheet accounts (excluding equity): Use the closing exchange rate."
msgstr ""
"Računi bilance stanja (brez lastniškega kapitala): Uporabite zaključni "
"menjalniški tečaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:134
msgid "The rates used are those of the company currently selected."
msgstr "Uporabljene so tečajnice podjetja, ki je trenutno izbrano."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:139
msgid "Account merging"
msgstr "Združevanje računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:141
msgid ""
"Accounts can be merged to reduce the number of accounts and standardize them "
"across companies. This is optional; consolidation works without it."
msgstr ""
"Račune je mogoče združiti za zmanjšanje števila računov in njihovo "
"standardizacijo med podjetji. To je neobvezno; konsolidacija deluje tudi "
"brez tega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:144
msgid ""
"To use the merge tool, select all the companies with an account that needs "
"to be merged in the company selector in the top right corner of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo orodja za združevanje izberite vsa podjetja z računom, ki ga je "
"treba združiti, v izborniku podjetij v zgornjem desnem kotu zaslona."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:None
msgid "Selecting all companies that have accounts to be merged."
msgstr "Izbira vseh podjetij, ki imajo račune za združitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:150
msgid ""
"Then, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Chart of "
"Accounts` and select the accounts to merge. Click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` menu and select :guilabel:`Merge accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Nato pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Kontni "
"načrt` in izberite račune za združitev. Kliknite meni :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Dejanja` in izberite :guilabel:`Združi račune`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:154
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Merge accounts` window, enable the :guilabel:`Group by "
"name?` option if needed and click :guilabel:`Merge`."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Združi konte` po potrebi omogočite možnost "
":guilabel:`Združi po imenu?` in kliknite :guilabel:`Združi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:157
msgid ""
"The selected accounts are then merged into a single shared account, "
"accessible by all the chosen companies, just as if the account had been "
"directly created to be shared."
msgstr ""
"Izbrani konti se nato združijo v en sam deljeni konto, dostopen vsem "
"izbranim podjetjem, tako kot če bi bil konto ustvarjen neposredno kot "
"deljeni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:163
msgid "Account unmerging"
msgstr "Razdelitev kontov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:165
msgid "Accounts can also be unmerged if needed."
msgstr "Konte je mogoče po potrebi tudi razdeliti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:169
msgid ""
"Note that unmerging accounts **will not unmerge the chatters** of the "
"accounts. Once merged, the changes' histories are permanently merged."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da razdelitev kontov **ne bo razdelila pogovorov** kontov. Ko "
"so združeni, so zgodovine sprememb trajno združene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:172
msgid ""
"To unmerge accounts, select a company with a shared account in the company "
"selector at the top right corner of the screen. Then, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Chart of Accounts` and "
"select the account to unmerge. Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` "
"menu and select :guilabel:`Unmerge accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Za razdelitev kontov izberite podjetje z deljenim kontom v izbirniku "
"podjetij v zgornjem desnem kotu zaslona. Nato pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Kontni načrt` in "
"izberite konto za razdelitev. Kliknite meni :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Dejanja` in izberite :guilabel:`Razdeli konte`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:177
msgid ""
"An :guilabel:`Odoo Warning` confirmation pop-up window will appear, listing "
"how the accounts will be split."
msgstr ""
"Pojavilo se bo potrditveno pojavno okno :guilabel:`Odoo opozorilo`, ki bo "
"prikazalo, kako bodo konti razdeljeni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:None
msgid ""
"Confirmation wizard for the Unmerge Tool of the shared accounts feature."
msgstr "Čarovnik za potrditev orodja za razdelitev funkcije deljenih kontov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:183
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Unmerge`. A new account linked to each company will be "
"created for the previously shared account."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Razdeli`. Za prej deljeni konto bo ustvarjen nov konto, "
"povezan z vsakim podjetjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:189
msgid "Import a mapping"
msgstr "Uvoz preslikave"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:191
msgid ""
"To **import an account mapping**, select all the related companies in the "
"company selector at the top right corner of the screen and go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Chart of Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Za **uvoz preslikave kontov** izberite vsa povezana podjetja v izbirniku "
"podjetij v zgornjem desnem kotu zaslona in pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Kontni načrt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:195
msgid ""
"First, to choose the fields to export, select the accounts, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button and select :guilabel:`Export`. "
"Then, in the :guilabel:`Export data` window, add the :guilabel:`Code mapping/"
"Code`, :guilabel:`Code Mapping/Company` and :guilabel:`External ID` fields "
"using the :icon:`fa-plus` icon and click :guilabel:`Export`. No other field "
"is required."
msgstr ""
"Najprej za izbiro polj za izvoz izberite konte, kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Dejanja` in izberite :guilabel:`Izvozi`. Nato v oknu "
":guilabel:`Izvozi podatke` dodajte polja :guilabel:`Preslikava kode/Koda`, "
":guilabel:`Preslikava kode/Podjetje` in :guilabel:`Zunanji ID` z uporabo "
"ikone :icon:`fa-plus` in kliknite :guilabel:`Izvozi`. Nobeno drugo polje ni "
"potrebno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:201
msgid ""
"Second, rework it in a spreadsheet adding the desired code for each company "
"on desired accounts."
msgstr ""
"Nato ga predelate v preglednici in dodate želeno kodo za vsako podjetje pri "
"želenih kontih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:203
msgid ""
"Third, to reimport the file (xlsx or csv format) in Odoo, "
"click :guilabel:`Import` and, in the :guilabel:`Import Chart of Accounts` "
"section, click :guilabel:`Import CoA`. In the :guilabel:`Accounting Import "
"Guide`, drop or click :guilabel:`Upload Data File` to import the file. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Import`."
msgstr ""
"Za ponovno uvoz datoteke (v formatu xlsx ali csv) v Odoo kliknite "
":guilabel:`Uvozi` in v razdelku :guilabel:`Uvozi kontni načrt` kliknite "
":guilabel:`Uvozi kontni načrt`. V :guilabel:`Vodnik za uvoz računovodstva` "
"povlecite ali kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži podatkovno datoteko` za uvoz "
"datoteke. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Uvozi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/consolidation.rst:208
msgid ""
"Finally, the codes now take into account the mapping company per company."
msgstr "Nazadnje kode zdaj upoštevajo preslikavo podjetje za podjetje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:104
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:260
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:283
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:343
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:541
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:349
msgid "Journals"
msgstr "Dnevniki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:5
msgid ""
"Journal entries are recorded in different **journals** to maintain an "
"organized record of a company's financial transactions. Odoo uses six "
"different types of journals to organize accounting records:"
msgstr ""
"Postavke dnevnika se beležijo v različnih **dnevnikih** za vzdrževanje "
"organiziranega zapisa finančnih transakcij podjetja. Odoo uporablja šest "
"različnih vrst dnevnikov za organizacijo računovodskih zapisov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:9
msgid ":ref:`Bank <accounting/journals/bank>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Banka <accounting/journals/bank>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:10
msgid ":ref:`Cash <accounting/journals/cash>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Gotovina <accounting/journals/cash>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:11
msgid ":ref:`Credit Card <accounting/journals/credit>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Kreditna kartica <accounting/journals/credit>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:12
msgid ":ref:`Sales <accounting/journals/sales>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Prodaja <accounting/journals/sales>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:13
msgid ":ref:`Purchase <accounting/journals/purchase>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Nabava <accounting/journals/purchase>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`Miscellaneous <accounting/journals/misc>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Razno <accounting/journals/misc>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:17
msgid ""
"It is possible to have multiple journals of the same type, such as two "
"separate bank journals, each for a unique bank account, or two separate "
"sales journals to track :abbr:`B2B (business to business)` versus :abbr:`B2C "
"(business to customer)` income."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je imeti več dnevnikov iste vrste, kot sta na primer dva ločena "
"bančna dnevnika, vsak za unikaten bančni račun, ali dva ločena prodajna "
"dnevnika za sledenje prihodkom :abbr:`B2B (poslovanje s podjetji)` v "
"primerjavi s prihodki :abbr:`B2C (poslovanje s strankami)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:21
msgid ""
"Each card on the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` represents a journal. To "
"edit the configuration of a journal, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` on the journal card, then "
"click :guilabel:`Configuration`. Alternatively, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` to select and "
"edit an existing journal or to create a new one."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka kartica na :guilabel:`Nadzorni plošči za računovodstvo` predstavlja "
"dnevnik. Za urejanje konfiguracije dnevnika kliknite :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
":guilabel:`(navpična tri-pika)` na kartici dnevnika, nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Konfiguracija`. Druga možnost je, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki`, kjer lahko "
"izberete in uredite obstoječi dnevnik ali ustvarite novega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:26
msgid ""
"While different journal types have slightly different fields to configure, "
"some fields are consistent across all the journal types:"
msgstr ""
"Čeprav imajo različne vrste dnevnikov nekoliko različna polja za "
"konfiguracijo, so nekatera polja dosledna v vseh vrstah dnevnikov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Short Code`: Each journal must have a unique code (from 1 to 5 "
"characters long). The short code is used as the prefix for all journal "
"entries belonging to this journal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kratka koda`: Vsak dnevnik mora imeti edinstveno kodo (od 1 do 5 "
"znakov). Kratka koda se uporablja kot predpona za vse dnevniške vnose, ki "
"pripadajo temu dnevniku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: If desired, set the currency of this journal. For bank "
"and cash journals, this is the currency of the journal's :doc:`transactions "
"<../bank/transactions>`. This field is only visible when :doc:`multiple "
"currencies <multi_currency>` are enabled."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Valuta`: Po želji nastavite valuto tega dnevnika. Za bančne in "
"gotovinske dnevnike je to valuta dnevnikovih :doc:`transakcij <../bank/"
"transactions>`. To polje je vidno le, ko so omogočene :doc:`več valut "
"<multi_currency>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:35
msgid "The :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab contains more technical options:"
msgstr "Zavihek :guilabel:`Napredne nastavitve` vsebuje bolj tehnične možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allowed accounts`: Limit which accounts are available when "
"recording journal entries in this journal. Leave this field blank to allow "
"all accounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dovoljeni računi`: Omejite, kateri računi so na voljo pri "
"beleženju dnevniških vnosov v tem dnevniku. Pustite to polje prazno, če "
"želite dovoliti vse račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Email Alias`: Set an email address to create journal entries by "
"digitizing PDFs sent to this address. This is most commonly used to "
"create :ref:`customer invoices and vendor bills <accounting/bill-"
"digitization/email-alias>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`E-poštni vzdevek`: Nastavite e-poštni naslov za ustvarjanje "
"dnevniških vnosov z digitalizacijo PDF-jev, poslanih na ta naslov. To se "
"najpogosteje uporablja za ustvarjanje :ref:`računov strank in računov "
"dobaviteljev <accounting/bill-digitization/email-alias>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Secure Posted Entries with Hash`: Restrict the :doc:`alterability "
"<../reporting/data_inalterability>` of this journal's entries to comply with "
"tax authorities in certain countries."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zavaruj objavljene vnose z zgoščeno vrednostjo`: Omejite "
":doc:`spremenljivost <../reporting/data_inalterability>` vnosov tega "
"dnevnika v skladu z davčnimi organi v nekaterih državah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:47
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Secure Posted Entries with Hash` option cannot be removed "
"from a journal once the journal has a posted journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti :guilabel:`Zavaruj objavljene vnose z zgoščeno vrednostjo` ni "
"mogoče odstraniti iz dnevnika, ko ima dnevnik že objavljen dnevniški vnos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:51
msgid ""
"Bank and cash journals do not have the :guilabel:`Secure Posted Entries with "
"Hash` or :guilabel:`Email Alias` fields."
msgstr ""
"Bančni in gotovinski dnevniki nimajo polj :guilabel:`Zavaruj objavljene "
"vnose z zgoščeno vrednostjo` ali :guilabel:`E-poštni vzdevek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:53
msgid ""
"If an :ref:`alias domain <email-inbound-custom-domain>` has not yet been "
"configured, a link to :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Alias "
"Domain` is displayed instead of the :guilabel:`Email Alias` field."
msgstr ""
"Če :ref:`domena vzdevka <email-inbound-custom-domain>` še ni bila "
"konfigurirana, se namesto polja :guilabel:`E-poštni vzdevek` prikaže "
"povezava do :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj domeno vzdevka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:60
msgid "Bank, cash, and credit card journals"
msgstr "Bančni, gotovinski in kreditnokartiški dnevniki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:62
msgid "Bank, cash, and credit card journals share the following features:"
msgstr ""
"Bančni, gotovinski in kreditnokartiški dnevniki si delijo naslednje funkcije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Suspense Account`: :doc:`../bank/transactions` on this journal "
"are posted on this account until they are reconciled, at which point this "
"account is replaced with the account the transaction was reconciled against. "
"At any moment, the suspense account's balance in the general ledger shows "
"the balance of transactions that have not yet been reconciled."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Začasni račun`: :doc:`../bank/transactions` v tem dnevniku so "
"knjižene na ta račun, dokler niso usklajene, ko se ta račun nadomesti z "
"računom, s katerim je bila transakcija usklajena. Stanje začasnega računa v "
"glavni knjigi kadarkoli prikazuje stanje transakcij, ki še niso bile "
"usklajene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:70
msgid ""
"When a bank transaction is reconciled, the journal entry is modified to "
"replace the bank suspense account with the account of the journal item it is "
"reconciled with. This account is usually either:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je bančna transakcija usklajena, se dnevniški vnos spremeni tako, da se "
"bančni začasni račun nadomesti z računom postavke dnevnika, s katero je "
"usklajena. Ta račun je običajno:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:74
msgid ""
"the :ref:`outstanding receipts or payments account <accounting/journals/"
"outstanding-accounts>` if reconciling with a registered payment; or"
msgstr ""
":ref:`račun za neporavnane prejemke ali plačila <accounting/journals/"
"outstanding-accounts>`, če usklajujete z registriranim plačilom; ali"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:76
msgid ""
"the account receivable or payable if reconciling with an invoice or bill "
"directly."
msgstr ""
"račun terjatev ali obveznosti, če usklajujete neposredno s frakturo ali "
"računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dedicated Payment Sequence`: Tick this field to use separate "
"sequences for payments and transactions posted on this journal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Namensko zaporedje plačil`: Označite to polje, če želite "
"uporabljati ločena zaporedja za plačila in transakcije, knjižene v tem "
"dnevniku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:82
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Dedicated Payment Sequence` field is ticked, payments that "
"use an :ref:`outstanding account <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` "
"will have references that add :guilabel:`P` before the journal's short code. "
"Otherwise, the references will begin with :guilabel:`PAY`."
msgstr ""
"Če je polje :guilabel:`Namensko zaporedje plačil` označeno, bodo imela "
"plačila, ki uporabljajo :ref:`vmesni račun <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>`, reference, ki pred kratko kodo dnevnika dodajo :guilabel:`P`. V "
"nasprotnem primeru se bodo reference začele z :guilabel:`PAY`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:87
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` and :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tabs "
"contain the :ref:`payment methods <accounting/payments/payment-methods>` of "
"this journal. Different payment methods are available depending on the "
"journal type. If desired, set :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/"
"journals/outstanding-accounts>` on the payment methods."
msgstr ""
"Zavihka :guilabel:`Dohodna plačila` in :guilabel:`Odhodna plačila` vsebujeta "
":ref:`načine plačila <accounting/payments/payment-methods>` tega dnevnika. "
"Na voljo so različni načini plačila, odvisno od vrste dnevnika. Če želite, "
"nastavite :ref:`vmesne račune <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` "
"pri načinih plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:94
msgid ":doc:`multi_currency`"
msgstr ":doc:`multi_currency`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:95
msgid ":doc:`../bank/transactions`"
msgstr ":doc:`../bank/transactions`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:96
msgid "`Bank configuration <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tVhhXw-VnGE>`_"
msgstr "`Konfiguracija banke <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tVhhXw-VnGE>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:101
msgid "Outstanding accounts"
msgstr "Neporavnani računi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:103
msgid ""
"By default, payments in Odoo do not create journal entries, but they can be "
"configured to create journal entries by using **outstanding accounts** "
"on :ref:`bank <accounting/journals/bank>` and :ref:`cash <accounting/"
"journals/cash>` journals."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto plačila v Odoo ne ustvarjajo dnevniških knjižb, vendar jih je "
"mogoče konfigurirati tako, da ustvarjajo dnevniške knjižbe z uporabo "
"**vmesnih računov** v dnevnikih :ref:`bank <accounting/journals/bank>` in "
":ref:`gotovine <accounting/journals/cash>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:107
msgid ""
"An **outstanding receipts account** is where incoming payments are posted "
"until they are linked with incoming bank transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Neporavnani račun prejemkov** je račun, kamor se knjižijo vhodna plačila, "
"dokler niso povezana z vhodnimi bančnimi transakcijami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:109
msgid ""
"An **outstanding payments account** is where outgoing payments are posted "
"until they are linked with outgoing bank transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Neporavnani račun plačil** je račun, kamor se knjižijo izhodna plačila, "
"dokler niso povezana z izhodnimi bančnimi transakcijami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:112
msgid ""
"These accounts are usually of :ref:`type <chart-of-account/"
"type>` :guilabel:`Current Assets` and :guilabel:`Current Liabilities`."
msgstr ""
"Ti računi so običajno :ref:`vrste <chart-of-account/type>` "
":guilabel:`Kratkoročna sredstva` in :guilabel:`Kratkoročne obveznosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:115
msgid ""
"Payments that are registered in Odoo are posted to the outstanding receipts "
"and outstanding payments accounts until they are reconciled. At any moment, "
"the outstanding receipts account's balance in the general ledger shows the "
"balance of registered incoming payments that have not yet been reconciled, "
"and the outstanding payments account's balance in the general ledger shows "
"the balance of registered outgoing payments that have not yet been "
"reconciled."
msgstr ""
"Plačila, ki so registrirana v Odoo, se knjižijo na račune za neporavnane "
"prejemke in neporavnana plačila, dokler niso usklajena. Saldo računa za "
"neporavnane prejemke v glavni knjigi kadar koli prikazuje saldo "
"registriranih dohodnih plačil, ki še niso bila usklajena, saldo računa za "
"neporavnana plačila v glavni knjigi pa prikazuje saldo registriranih "
"odhodnih plačil, ki še niso bila usklajena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:124
msgid ""
"To configure outstanding accounts, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals` and select or create a bank or cash journal. In "
"the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` and :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tabs, "
"set :guilabel:`Outstanding Receipts accounts` and :guilabel:`Outstanding "
"Payments accounts` for each payment method that you want to create journal "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo vmesnih računov pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki` in izberite "
"ali ustvarite bančni ali gotovinski dnevnik. V zavihkih :guilabel:`Dohodna "
"plačila` in :guilabel:`Odhodna plačila` nastavite :guilabel:`Račune za "
"neporavnane prejemke` in :guilabel:`Račune za neporavnana plačila` za vsak "
"način plačila, pri katerem želite ustvarjati dnevniške knjižbe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:131
msgid ""
"If the main bank account of the journal is added as an outstanding receipts "
"account or outstanding payments account, when a payment is registered, the "
"invoice or bill's status is directly set to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Če je glavni bančni račun dnevnika dodan kot neporavnani račun prejemkov ali "
"neporavnani račun plačil, se ob registraciji plačila status računa ali "
"dobaviteljevega računa neposredno nastavi na :guilabel:`Plačano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:134
msgid ""
"If the outstanding receipts or outstanding payments account for a payment "
"method is left blank, registering a payment with that payment method will "
"not create any journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Če je neporavnani račun prejemkov ali neporavnani račun plačil za način "
"plačila prazen, registracija plačila s tem načinom plačila ne bo ustvarila "
"nobenega knjiženja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:142
msgid ""
"Bank journals are used to record journal entries related to :doc:`bank "
"transactions <../bank/transactions>` and incoming and "
"outgoing :doc:`payments <../payments>`. The following fields are specific to "
"bank journals:"
msgstr ""
"Bančni dnevniki se uporabljajo za beleženje dnevniških knjižb, povezanih z "
":doc:`bančnimi transakcijami <../bank/transactions>` ter dohodnimi in "
"odhodnimi :doc:`plačili <../payments>`. Naslednja polja so specifična za "
"bančne dnevnike:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:146
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Account`: This :guilabel:`Bank and Cash` type account is the "
"default account for this bank journal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bančni račun`: Ta račun tipa :guilabel:`Banka in gotovina` je "
"privzeti račun za ta bančni dnevnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:148
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Account Number`: The bank account's number is used when "
"registering payments and is required for generating outgoing payment files, "
"such as :doc:`SEPA <../payments/pay_sepa>` or :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`. "
"To edit the bank account details, click on the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(Internal link)` button next to the :guilabel:`Account "
"Number` and update the account information accordingly."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Številka računa`: Številka bančnega računa se uporablja pri "
"registraciji plačil in je potrebna za ustvarjanje datotek izhodnih plačil, "
"kot so :doc:`SEPA <../payments/pay_sepa>` ali :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`. "
"Za urejanje podatkov bančnega računa kliknite gumb :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`(Notranja povezava)` poleg :guilabel:`Številka računa` in "
"ustrezno posodobite podatke o računu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank`: The bank name is used when registering payments and is "
"required for generating outgoing payment files. To edit the bank account "
"details, click on the :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(Internal link)` "
"button next to the :guilabel:`Bank` name and update the account information "
"accordingly."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Banka`: Ime banke se uporablja pri registraciji plačil in je "
"potrebno za ustvarjanje datotek izhodnih plačil. Za urejanje podatkov "
"bančnega računa kliknite gumb :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(Notranja "
"povezava)` poleg imena :guilabel:`Banka` in ustrezno posodobite podatke o "
"računu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:157
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Feeds`: Define the method of creating "
"bank :doc:`transactions <../bank/transactions>`, whether :guilabel:`Manual` "
"or via :doc:`Online Synchronization <../bank/bank_synchronization>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bančni viri`: Določite način ustvarjanja bančnih :doc:`transakcij "
"<../bank/transactions>`, bodisi :guilabel:`Ročno` bodisi prek :doc:`Spletne "
"sinhronizacije <../bank/bank_synchronization>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:160
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Split Transactions`: Split collective payments for CODA files."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Razdeli transakcije`: Razdelite skupinska plačila za datoteke "
"CODA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:162
msgid ""
"Multiple payment methods are available for bank journals, as are "
"configurations for generating outgoing payment files, such as :doc:`SEPA <../"
"payments/pay_sepa>` or :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."
msgstr ""
"Za bančne dnevnike je na voljo več načinov plačila, prav tako so na voljo "
"konfiguracije za ustvarjanje datotek izhodnih plačil, kot so :doc:`SEPA <../"
"payments/pay_sepa>` ali :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:168
msgid "Cash"
msgstr "Gotovina"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:170
msgid ""
"Cash journals are used to record journal entries related to "
"cash :doc:`transactions <../bank/transactions>`. The following fields are "
"specific to cash journals:"
msgstr ""
"Gotovinski dnevniki se uporabljajo za beleženje dnevniških knjižb, povezanih "
"z gotovinskimi :doc:`transakcijami <../bank/transactions>`. Naslednja polja "
"so specifična za gotovinske dnevnike:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:173
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cash Account`: This :guilabel:`Bank and Cash` type account is the "
"default account for this cash journal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gotovinski račun`: Ta račun tipa :guilabel:`Banka in gotovina` je "
"privzeti račun za ta gotovinski dnevnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:175
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Profit Account`: This :guilabel:`Income` or :guilabel:`Other "
"Income` type account is used to register a profit when the ending balance of "
"a cash register is greater than expected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Račun dobička`: Ta račun tipa :guilabel:`Prihodki` ali "
":guilabel:`Drugi prihodki` se uporablja za beleženje dobička, ko je končno "
"stanje blagajne večje od pričakovanega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:177
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Loss Account`: This :guilabel:`Expenses` type account is used to "
"register a loss when the ending balance of a cash register is less than "
"expected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Račun izgube`: Ta račun tipa :guilabel:`Odhodki` se uporablja za "
"beleženje izgube, ko je končno stanje blagajne manjše od pričakovanega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:180
msgid "Only manual payment methods are available for cash journals."
msgstr "Za blagajniške dnevnike so na voljo samo ročni načini plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:185
msgid "Credit card"
msgstr "Kreditna kartica"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:187
msgid ""
"Credit card journals are used to record journal entries related to credit "
"cards. The following fields are specific to credit card journals:"
msgstr ""
"Dnevniki kreditnih kartic se uporabljajo za beleženje dnevniških vnosov, "
"povezanih s kreditnimi karticami. Naslednja polja so specifična za dnevnike "
"kreditnih kartic:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:190
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal Account`: This :guilabel:`Credit Card` type account is "
"the default account for this credit card journal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dnevniški račun`: Ta račun tipa :guilabel:`Kreditna kartica` je "
"privzeti račun za ta dnevnik kreditnih kartic."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:192
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Feeds`: Define the method of creating credit card "
"transactions, whether manual or via :doc:`Online Synchronization <../bank/"
"bank_synchronization>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bančni viri`: Določite način ustvarjanja transakcij kreditnih "
"kartic, bodisi ročno ali prek :doc:`spletne sinhronizacije <../bank/"
"bank_synchronization>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:195
msgid "Only manual payment methods are available for credit card journals."
msgstr "Za dnevnike kreditnih kartic so na voljo samo ročni načini plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:200
msgid "Sales, purchase, and miscellaneous journals"
msgstr "Prodajni, nabavni in razni dnevniki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:207
msgid ""
"Sales journals, also known as income journals, are used to record journal "
"entries related to :doc:`customer invoices <../customer_invoices>`. The "
"following fields are specific to customer invoice journals:"
msgstr ""
"Prodajni dnevniki, znani tudi kot prihodkovni dnevniki, se uporabljajo za "
"beleženje dnevniških vnosov, povezanih z :doc:`računi strankam <../"
"customer_invoices>`. Naslednja polja so specifična za dnevnike računov "
"strankam:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:211
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Income Account`: Invoices in this journal use "
"this :guilabel:`Income` or :guilabel:`Other Income` type account unless "
"overwritten by another income account set on the product category, product, "
"or invoice line itself."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeti prihodkovni račun`: Računi v tem dnevniku uporabljajo ta "
"račun tipa :guilabel:`Prihodki` ali :guilabel:`Drugi prihodki`, razen če ga "
"prepiše drug prihodkovni račun, nastavljen na kategoriji izdelka, izdelku "
"ali vrstici računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:214
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dedicated Credit Note Sequence`: Check this box to use a separate "
"sequence for the reference of credit notes that increments separately from "
"the main invoice sequence and adds an `R` to the reference before the "
"journal's short code."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Namensko zaporedje dobropisov`: Označite to polje, če želite za "
"sklicevanje dobropisov uporabiti ločeno zaporedje, ki se povečuje ločeno od "
"glavnega zaporedja računov in doda `R` v sklicevanje pred kratko kodo "
"dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:217
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:246
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dedicated Debit Note Sequence`: Check this box to use a separate "
"sequence for the reference of credit notes that increments separately from "
"the main invoice sequence and adds a `D` before the journal's short code."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Namensko zaporedje terjatvenih not`: Označite to polje, če želite "
"za sklicevanje terjatvenih not uporabiti ločeno zaporedje, ki se povečuje "
"ločeno od glavnega zaporedja računov in doda `D` pred kratko kodo dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:221
msgid ""
"Sales journals have additional fields in the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` "
"tab that allow you to set the default communication format that will appear "
"on customer invoices so that the customer can refer to that particular "
"invoice when making a payment:"
msgstr ""
"Prodajni dnevniki imajo dodatna polja v zavihku :guilabel:`Napredne "
"nastavitve`, ki vam omogočajo nastavitev privzete oblike komunikacije, ki se "
"bo prikazala na računih strankam, tako da lahko stranka pri plačilu sklicuje "
"na določen račun:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:225
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Communication Type`: Choose if the format of the payment "
"reference communicated to the customer should be based on the invoice number "
"or the customer's number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta komunikacije`: Izberite, ali naj bo oblika plačilnega "
"sklicevanja, sporočenega stranki, osnovana na številki računa ali številki "
"stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:227
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Communication Standard`: Choose the format of the payment "
"reference itself that is communicated to the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Standard komunikacije`: Izberite obliko samega plačilnega "
"sklicevanja, ki je sporočeno stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:233
msgid "Purchase"
msgstr "Nabava"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:235
msgid ""
"Purchase journals are used to record journal entries related to :doc:`vendor "
"bills <../vendor_bills>`. The following fields are specific to purchase "
"journals:"
msgstr ""
"Nabavni dnevniki se uporabljajo za beleženje dnevniških vnosov, povezanih z "
":doc:`računi dobaviteljev <../vendor_bills>`. Naslednja polja so specifična "
"za nabavne dnevnike:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:238
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Expense Account`: Vendor bills in this journal use "
"this :guilabel:`Expense` type account unless overwritten by another expense "
"account set on the product category, product, or expense."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeti stroškovni račun`: Računi dobaviteljev v tem dnevniku "
"uporabljajo ta račun tipa :guilabel:`Odhodki`, razen če ga prepiše drug "
"stroškovni račun, nastavljen na kategoriji izdelka, izdelku ali strošku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:241
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Private Part Account`: Select the account to be used to register "
"the private part of mixed expenses."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Račun zasebnega dela`: Izberite račun, ki se bo uporabljal za "
"beleženje zasebnega dela mešanih stroškov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:243
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dedicated Credit Note Sequence`: Check this box to use a separate "
"sequence for the reference of credit notes that increments separately from "
"the main vendor bill sequence and adds an `R` to the reference before the "
"journal's short code."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Namensko zaporedje dobropisov`: Označite to polje, če želite za "
"sklicevanje dobropisov uporabiti ločeno zaporedje, ki se povečuje ločeno od "
"glavnega zaporedja računov dobaviteljev in doda `R` v sklicevanje pred "
"kratko kodo dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:253
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Razno"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:255
msgid ""
"Miscellaneous journals are used to record journal entries that are not "
"related to any of the other journal types such as tax closing journal "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Razni dnevniki se uporabljajo za beleženje dnevniških vnosov, ki niso "
"povezani z nobeno drugo vrsto dnevnika, kot so npr. dnevniški vnosi za "
"zaprtje davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:259
msgid ""
"`Tax return eLearning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/tax-return-10564>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Davčna napoved eLearning <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/tax-return-"
"10564>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:260
msgid ":doc:`../reporting/tax_returns`"
msgstr ":doc:`../reporting/tax_returns`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/journals.rst:261
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:15
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:119
