msgstr ":doc:`../taxes`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:3
msgid "Multi-currency system"
msgstr "Večvalutni sistem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to issue invoices, receive bills, and record transactions in "
"currencies other than the main currency configured for your company. You can "
"also set up bank accounts in other currencies and run reports on your "
"foreign currency activities."
msgstr ""
"Odoo vam omogoča izdajanje računov, prejemanje računov in beleženje "
"transakcij v drugih valutah kot je glavna valuta, konfigurirana za vaše "
"podjetje. Prav tako lahko nastavite bančne račune v drugih valutah in "
"izvajate poročila o dejavnostih v tujih valutah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`../bank/foreign_currency`"
msgstr ":doc:`../bank/foreign_currency`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:20
msgid "Main currency"
msgstr "Glavna valuta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:22
msgid ""
"The **main currency** is defined by default according to the company's "
"country. You can change it by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings --> Currencies` and changing the currency in "
"the :guilabel:`Main Currency` setting."
msgstr ""
"**Glavna valuta** je privzeto določena glede na državo podjetja. Spremenite "
"jo lahko tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve --> Valute` in spremenite valuto v nastavitvi "
":guilabel:`Glavna valuta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:29
msgid "Enable foreign currencies"
msgstr "Omogoči tuje valute"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:31
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Currencies`, and "
"enable the currencies you wish to use by toggling the :guilabel:`Active` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Valute` in "
"omogočite valute, ki jih želite uporabljati, s preklopom gumba "
":guilabel:`Aktivno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Enable the currencies you wish to use."
msgstr "Omogočite valute, ki jih želite uporabljati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:41
msgid "Currency rates"
msgstr "Valutni tečaji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:46
msgid "Manual update"
msgstr "Ročna posodobitev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:48
msgid ""
"To manually create and set a currency rate, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Configuration --> Currencies`, click on the currency you wish to change "
"the rate of, and under the :guilabel:`Rates` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` to create a new rate."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ročno ustvariti in nastaviti valutni tečaj, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Valute`, kliknite na "
"valuto, katere tečaj želite spremeniti, in pod zavihkom :guilabel:`Tečaji` "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da ustvarite nov tečaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Create or modify the currency rate."
msgstr "Ustvarite ali spremenite valutni tečaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:59
msgid "Automatic update"
msgstr "Samodejna posodobitev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:61
msgid ""
"When you activate a second currency for the first time, :guilabel:`Automatic "
"Currency Rates` appears under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings` in the :guilabel:`Currencies` section. Click the :icon:`os-"
"refresh-data` :guilabel:`(Update now)` icon to update the rates."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič aktivirate drugo valuto, se v razdelku :guilabel:`Valute` pod "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` pojavi "
":guilabel:`Samodejni tečaji`. Kliknite ikono :icon:`os-refresh-data` "
":guilabel:`(Posodobi zdaj)`, da posodobite tečaje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:65
msgid ""
"Rates can be updated at regular intervals automatically. To do so, change "
"the :guilabel:`Interval` from :guilabel:`Manually` "
"to :guilabel:`Daily`, :guilabel:`Weekly`, or :guilabel:`Monthly`. You can "
"also select the web service from which you want to retrieve the latest "
"currency rates by clicking the :guilabel:`Service` field."
msgstr ""
"Tečaji se lahko posodabljajo samodejno v rednih intervalih. To storite tako, "
"da spremenite :guilabel:`Interval` iz :guilabel:`Ročno` na "
":guilabel:`Dnevno`, :guilabel:`Tedensko` ali :guilabel:`Mesečno`. Prav tako "
"lahko izberete spletno storitev, iz katere želite pridobiti najnovejše "
"tečaje, tako da kliknete polje :guilabel:`Storitev`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:73
msgid "Exchange difference entries"
msgstr "Vnosi tečajnih razlik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:75
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically records exchange differences entries on dedicated "
"accounts, in a dedicated journal."
msgstr ""
"Odoo samodejno zabeleži vnose tečajnih razlik na namenskih kontih v "
"namenskem dnevniku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:78
msgid ""
"To define which journal and accounts to use to post exchange difference "
"entries, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, "
"scroll to the :guilabel:`Default Accounts` section, and edit "
"the :guilabel:`Journal`, the :guilabel:`Gain` and :guilabel:`Loss accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Določite, kateri dnevnik in konta uporabiti za knjiženje vnosov tečajnih "
"razlik, tako da greste v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`, se pomaknete do razdelka :guilabel:`Privzeti konti` in uredite "
":guilabel:`Dnevnik`, :guilabel:`Dobiček` in :guilabel:`Konti izgub`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:84
msgid ""
"If you receive a payment for a customer invoice one month after it was "
"issued, the exchange rate has likely changed since. Therefore, this "
"fluctuation implies some profit or loss due to the exchange difference, "
"which Odoo automatically records in the default **Exchange Difference** "
"journal."
msgstr ""
"Če prejmete plačilo za račun stranke en mesec po izdaji, se je valutni tečaj "
"verjetno spremenil. Ta nihanja zato pomenijo dobiček ali izgubo zaradi "
"tečajne razlike, kar Odoo samodejno zabeleži v privzetem dnevniku **Tečajne "
"razlike**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:94
msgid ""
"Each account can have a set currency. By doing so, all moves relevant to the "
"account are forced to have that account's currency."
msgstr ""
"Vsak konto ima lahko nastavljeno valuto. S tem so vsi prenosi, povezani s "
"kontom, prisilno v valuti tega konta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:97
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Charts of "
"Accounts` and select a currency in the field :guilabel:`Currency`. If left "
"empty, all active currencies are handled instead of just one."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da greste v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Kontni načrti` in izberete valuto v polju "
":guilabel:`Valuta`. Če je prazno, se namesto samo ene obravnavajo vse "
"aktivne valute."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:106
msgid ""
"If a currency is set on a **journal**, that journal only handles "
"transactions in that currency."
msgstr ""
"Če je valuta nastavljena na **dnevniku**, ta dnevnik obravnava samo "
"transakcije v tej valuti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:108
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, "
"open the journal you want to edit, and select a currency in the "
"field :guilabel:`Currency`."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki`, odprete dnevnik, ki ga želite urediti, in "
"izberete valuto v polju :guilabel:`Valuta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Select the currency for the journal to handle."
msgstr "Izberite valuto, ki jo bo dnevnik obravnaval."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:118
msgid "Multi-currency accounting"
msgstr "Večvalutno računovodstvo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:123
msgid "Invoices, bills, and other documents"
msgstr "Računi, predračuni in drugi dokumenti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:125
msgid ""
"For all documents, you can select the currency and journal to use for the "
"transaction on the document itself."
msgstr ""
"Za vse dokumente lahko izberete valuto in dnevnik, ki ju želite uporabiti za "
"transakcijo, neposredno na dokumentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Select the currency and journal to use."
msgstr "Izberite valuto in dnevnik za uporabo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:135
msgid "Payment registration"
msgstr "Evidentiranje plačil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:137
msgid ""
"To register a payment in a currency other than your company's main currency, "
"click on the :guilabel:`Register Payment` payment button of your document "
"and, in the pop-up window, select a **currency** in the :guilabel:`Amount` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Če želite registrirati plačilo v drugi valuti kot je glavna valuta vašega "
"podjetja, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Registriraj plačilo` na vašem dokumentu "
"in v pojavnem oknu izberite **valuto** v polju :guilabel:`Znesek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Select the currency and journal to use before registering the payment."
msgstr ""
"Pred registracijo plačila izberite valuto in dnevnik, ki ju želite uporabiti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:148
msgid "Bank transactions"
msgstr "Bančne transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:150
msgid ""
"When creating or importing bank transactions, the amount is in the company's "
"main currency. To input a **foreign currency**, select a currency in "
"the :guilabel:`Foreign Currency`. Once selected, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` in your main currency for it to automatically get "
"converted in the foreign currency in the :guilabel:`Amount in Currency "
"field`."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju ali uvažanju bančnih transakcij je znesek v glavni valuti "
"podjetja. Za vnos **tuje valute** izberite valuto v polju :guilabel:`Tuja "
"valuta`. Ko je izbrana, vnesite :guilabel:`Znesek` v vaši glavni valuti, da "
"se samodejno pretvori v tujo valuto v polju :guilabel:`Znesek v valuti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "The extra fields related to foreign currencies."
msgstr "Dodatna polja povezana s tujimi valutami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:159
msgid ""
"When reconciling, Odoo displays both the foreign currency amount and the "
"equivalent amount in your company's main currency."
msgstr ""
"Pri usklajevanju Odoo prikaže tako znesek v tuji valuti kot enakovreden "
"znesek v glavni valuti vašega podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:165
msgid "Exchange rate journal entries"
msgstr "Knjigovodski zapisi menjalnega tečaja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:167
msgid ""
"To see **exchange difference journal entries**, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> Journal Items`. In the search "
"bar, click the :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(down caret)` icon and, in "
"the :guilabel:`Group By` column, select :guilabel:`Miscellaneous`."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati **vnose v dnevnik tečajnih razlik**, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Pregled --> Dnevniški vnosi`. V iskalni "
"vrstici kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`(puščica navzdol)` "
"in v stolpcu :guilabel:`Združi po` izberite :guilabel:`Razno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:None
msgid "Exchange rate journal entry."
msgstr "Knjigovodski zapis menjalnega tečaja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:3
msgid "Tax units"
msgstr "Davčne enote"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:6
msgid "This is only applicable to multi-company environments."
msgstr "To velja samo za okolja z več podjetji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:8
msgid ""
"A **tax unit** is a group of VAT-taxable enterprises that are legally "
"independent of each other but are closely linked financially, "
"organizationally, and economically and therefore considered the same VAT-"
"taxable enterprise. **Tax units** are not mandatory, but if created, "
"constituent companies of the unit must belong to the same **country**, use "
"the same **currency**, and one company must be designated as the "
"**representative** company of the **tax unit**. **Tax units** receive a "
"specific **tax ID** intended only for **tax returns**. **Constituent** "
"companies keep their **tax ID** used for **commercial purposes**."
msgstr ""
"**Davčna enota** je skupina podjetij, zavezanih za DDV, ki so pravno "
"neodvisna, vendar so tesno povezana finančno, organizacijsko in gospodarsko, "
"zato se štejejo za isto podjetje, zavezano za DDV. **Davčne enote** niso "
"obvezne, vendar morajo v primeru ustanovitve članice enote pripadati isti "
"**državi**, uporabljati isto **valuto**, pri čemer mora biti eno podjetje "
"določeno kot **predstavniško** podjetje **davčne enote**. **Davčne enote** "
"prejmejo poseben **davčni ID**, namenjen samo za **davčne napovedi**. "
"**Članice** obdržijo svoj **davčni ID**, ki se uporablja za **komercialne "
"namene**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:17
msgid ""
"Enterprise **A** owes €300.000,00 of VAT taxes and enterprise **B** can "
"recover €280.000,00 of VAT taxes. They form up as a **tax unit** so that the "
"two amounts balance out and must conjointly only pay €20.000,00 of VAT taxes."
msgstr ""
"Podjetje **A** dolguje DDV v višini 300.000,00 €, podjetje **B** pa lahko "
"povrne DDV v višini 280.000,00 €. Združita se v **davčno enoto**, tako da se "
"zneska uravnovesita in skupaj plačata samo 20.000,00 € DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:24
msgid ""
"To create a **tax unit**, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Tax Units`, and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter a **name** for the unit, "
"select a :guilabel:`Country`, the :guilabel:`Companies` to incorporate in "
"the unit, the :guilabel:`Main Company`, and the :guilabel:`Tax ID` of the "
"**constituent** company of that tax unit."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje **davčne enote** pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Nastavitve --> Davčne enote` in kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Vnesite **ime** "
"enote, izberite :guilabel:`Državo`, :guilabel:`Podjetja`, ki jih želite "
"vključiti v enoto, :guilabel:`Glavno podjetje` in :guilabel:`Davčni ID` "
"**članice** te davčne enote."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:30
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax.rst:343
msgid "Fiscal position"
msgstr "Fiskalni položaj"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:32
msgid ""
"As transactions between constituents of the same **tax unit** are not "
"subject to VAT, it is possible to create a :doc:`tax mapping (fiscal "
"position) <../taxes/fiscal_positions>` to avoid the application of VAT on "
"inter-constituent transactions."
msgstr ""
"Ker transakcije med članicami iste **davčne enote** ne podlegajo DDV, je "
"mogoče ustvariti :doc:`davčno preslikavo (davčni položaj) <../taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`, da se izognete uporabi DDV pri transakcijah med "
"članicami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:36
msgid ""
"Be sure a constituent company has been selected before, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Fiscal Positions`, "
"and :guilabel:`Create` a new **fiscal position**. Click the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Mapping` tab, select the :guilabel:`Tax on Product` usually applied for "
"**non-constituent** transactions, and in :guilabel:`Tax to Apply`, select "
"the 0% tax to apply for **constituent** transactions."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je bila prej izbrana članica, nato pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> Davčni položaji` in "
":guilabel:`Ustvarite` nov **davčni položaj**. Kliknite zavihek "
":guilabel:`Preslikava davkov`, izberite :guilabel:`Davek na izdelek`, ki se "
"običajno uporablja za transakcije z **nečlanicami**, in v :guilabel:`Davek "
"za uporabo` izberite 0% davek za transakcije med **članicami**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:42
msgid ""
"Do the same for the :guilabel:`Account Mapping` tab if required, and repeat "
"this process for **each** constituent company on your database."
msgstr ""
"Enako naredite za zavihek :guilabel:`Preslikava kontov`, če je potrebno, in "
"ponovite postopek za **vsako** članico v vaši bazi podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:46
msgid ""
"Depending on your :doc:`localization package </applications/finance/"
"fiscal_localizations>`, taxes may vary from the screenshot displayed."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od vašega :doc:`lokalizacijskega paketa </applications/finance/"
"fiscal_localizations>` se lahko davki razlikujejo od prikazanega posnetka "
"zaslona."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:0
msgid "Tax mapping of fiscal position for tax unit"
msgstr "Davčna preslikava davčnega položaja za davčno enoto"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:52
msgid ""
"Then, assign the fiscal position by opening the **Contacts** app. Search for "
"a **constituent** company, and open the contact's **card**. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, and in the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` "
"field, input the **fiscal position** created for the **tax unit**. Repeat "
"the process for each **constituent** company card form, on each company "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Nato dodelite davčni položaj tako, da odprete aplikacijo **Stiki**. Poiščite "
"**članico** in odprite **kartico** stika. Kliknite zavihek "
":guilabel:`Prodaja in nakup` ter v polje :guilabel:`Davčni položaj` vnesite "
"**davčni položaj**, ustvarjen za **davčno enoto**. Ponovite postopek za vsak "
"obrazec kartice **članice** v vsaki bazi podatkov podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:58
msgid ":doc:`../taxes/fiscal_positions`."
msgstr ":doc:`../taxes/fiscal_positions`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:61
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:38
msgid "Tax report"
msgstr "Davčno poročanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:63
msgid ""
"The **representative** company can access the aggregated tax report of the "
"**tax unit** by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax "
"Report`, and selecting the **tax unit** in :guilabel:`Tax Unit`. This report "
"contains the aggregated transactions of all **constituents** and the .XML "
"export contains the name and VAT number of the **main** company."
msgstr ""
"Podjetje **zastopnik** lahko dostopa do zbirnega davčnega poročila **davčne "
"enote** tako, da gre v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> "
"Davčno poročilo` in izbere **davčno enoto** v :guilabel:`Davčna enota`. To "
"poročilo vsebuje združene transakcije vseh **sestavnih delov**, izvoz .XML "
"pa vsebuje ime in davčno številko **glavnega** podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/tax_units.rst:None
msgid "tax unit tax report"
msgstr "davčno poročilo davčne enote"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:7
msgid ""
"In Odoo, payments can either be automatically linked to an invoice or bill "
"or be stand-alone records for use at a later date:"
msgstr ""
"V Odooju so lahko plačila samodejno povezana s prejetim ali izdanim računom "
"ali pa so samostojni zapisi za uporabo pozneje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:10
msgid ""
"If a payment is **linked to an invoice or bill**, it reduces/settles the "
"amount due on the invoice. Multiple payments on the same invoice are "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Če je plačilo **povezano s prejetim ali izdanim računom**, zmanjša/poravna "
"znesek, ki zapade na računu. Več plačil na istem računu je mogoče."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:13
msgid ""
"If a payment is **not linked to an invoice or bill**, the customer has an "
"outstanding credit with the company, or the company has an outstanding debit "
"with a vendor. Those outstanding amounts reduce/settle unpaid invoices/bills."
msgstr ""
"Če plačilo **ni povezano s prejetim ali izdanim računom**, ima stranka pri "
"podjetju neporavnani kredit ali pa ima podjetje pri dobavitelju neporavnani "
"debet. Ti neporavnani zneski zmanjšajo/poravnajo neplačane račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:18
msgid ":doc:`Internal transfers <bank/internal_transfers>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Interna nakazila <bank/internal_transfers>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Bank Configuration <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/bank-"
"configuration-6832>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo vodniki: Konfiguracija banke <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/bank-"
"configuration-6832>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:283
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/nuvei.rst:51
msgid "Payment methods"
msgstr "Načini plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:28
msgid ""
"Several payment methods are available in Odoo to allow different "
"configurations for different types of payments. Examples of payment methods "
"include manual payments (such as cash), :doc:`checks <payments/pay_checks>`, "
"and batch payment files (such as :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-"
"transfers>` and :doc:`SEPA <payments/pay_sepa>`). Payment methods can be "
"configured in the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` and :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"Payments` tabs of a bank or cash journal."
msgstr ""
"V Odooju je na voljo več načinov plačila, ki omogočajo različne "
"konfiguracije za različne vrste plačil. Primeri načinov plačila vključujejo "
"ročna plačila (kot je gotovina), :doc:`čeke <payments/pay_checks>` in "
"paketne datoteke plačil (kot so :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-"
"transfers>` in :doc:`SEPA <payments/pay_sepa>`). Načine plačila je mogoče "
"konfigurirati na zavihkih :guilabel:`Vhodna plačila` in :guilabel:`Izhodna "
"plačila` bančnega ali gotovinskega dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:36
msgid ":doc:`../../sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods` for Point of Sale"
msgstr ":doc:`../../sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods` za Prodajno točko"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:41
msgid "Preferred payment method"
msgstr "Želeni način plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:43
msgid ""
"A contact's preferred payment method can be set so that when a payment is "
"created for that contact, the payment method is automatically selected by "
"default. Invoices and bills can be filtered by :guilabel:`Payment Method` to "
"simplify :ref:`group <accounting/payments/group-payments>` payments."
msgstr ""
"Želeni način plačila stika je mogoče nastaviti tako, da je ob ustvarjanju "
"plačila za ta stik način plačila samodejno izbran kot privzet. Prejete in "
"izdane račune je mogoče filtrirati po :guilabel:`Načinu plačila`, da se "
"poenostavi :ref:`skupinska <accounting/payments/group-payments>` plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:47
msgid ""
"To set a preferred :guilabel:`Payment Method` for a customer or a vendor, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers` "
"or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors` and select the "
"customer or vendor. In the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab of the contact "
"form, select the preferred :guilabel:`Payment Method` in "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` section for invoice payments or for vendor bill "
"payments in the :guilabel:`Purchase` section."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti želeni :guilabel:`Način plačila` za stranko ali "
"dobavitelja, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> "
"Stranke` ali :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Dobavitelji` "
"in izberite stranko ali dobavitelja. Na zavihku :guilabel:`Prodaja in nakup` "
"obrazca stika izberite želeni :guilabel:`Način plačila` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Prodaja` za plačila računov ali za plačila dobaviteljevih računov "
"v razdelku :guilabel:`Nakup`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:54
msgid ""
"Access a full list of all contacts from the :guilabel:`Customers` "
"or :guilabel:`Vendors` list view by removing the :guilabel:`Customers` "
"or :guilabel:`Vendors` filter. Alternatively, access the full contact list "
"through the Contacts app."
msgstr ""
"Dostopajte do celotnega seznama vseh stikov iz pogleda seznama "
":guilabel:`Stranke` ali :guilabel:`Dobavitelji` tako, da odstranite filter "
":guilabel:`Stranke` ali :guilabel:`Dobavitelji`. Druga možnost je dostop do "
"celotnega seznama stikov prek aplikacije Stiki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:61
msgid "Checks"
msgstr "Čeki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:63
msgid ""
":doc:`Vendor bills can be paid by check <payments/pay_checks>` using a "
"dedicated outgoing payment method, which allows check numbers to be tracked "
"and checks to be printed directly from Odoo."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dobaviteljeve račune je mogoče plačati s čekom <payments/pay_checks>` "
"z uporabo namenskega načina izhodnega plačila, ki omogoča sledenje številkam "
"čekov in tiskanje čekov neposredno iz Odooja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:66
msgid ""
"For incoming customer check payments, you can use the "
"default :guilabel:`Manual Payment` payment method, or you can create a "
"payment method specifically for checks to help identify such payments "
"quickly. To create a *Check* payment method, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za vhodna plačila strank s čekom lahko uporabite privzeti način plačila "
":guilabel:`Ročno plačilo` ali pa lahko ustvarite način plačila posebej za "
"čeke, kar omogoča hitro prepoznavanje takšnih plačil. Za ustvarjanje načina "
"plačila *Ček* sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:70
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and select "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` journal."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki` in "
"izberite dnevnik :guilabel:`Banka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:72
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku :guilabel:`Vhodna plačila` kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:73
msgid ""
"As :guilabel:`Payment Method`, select :guilabel:`Manual`, then enter `Check` "
"as the :guilabel:`Name`."
msgstr ""
"Kot :guilabel:`Način plačila` izberite :guilabel:`Ročno`, nato vnesite `Ček` "
"kot :guilabel:`Ime`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:76
msgid ""
"When registering a customer payment :ref:`on an invoice <accounting/payments/"
"from-invoice-bill>` or :ref:`not related to an invoice <accounting/payments/"
"not-tied>`, use the new :guilabel:`Check` payment method."
msgstr ""
"Pri registraciji plačila stranke :ref:`na računu <accounting/payments/from-"
"invoice-bill>` ali :ref:`ki ni povezano z računom <accounting/payments/not-"
"tied>`, uporabite novi način plačila :guilabel:`Ček`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:81
msgid ""
"Registering a customer payment by check in Odoo does not move funds. Checks "
"must be deposited in order to make the payment. Once deposited to your bank, "
"the check should appear as a :doc:`bank transaction <bank/transactions>`, at "
"which point it can be :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with the "
"registered payment."
msgstr ""
"Registracija plačila stranke s čekom v Odooju ne premakne sredstev. Čeke je "
"treba položiti, da bi izvedli plačilo. Ko je položen na vašo banko, bi se "
"moral ček pojaviti kot :doc:`bančna transakcija <bank/transactions>`, pri "
"čemer ga je nato mogoče :doc:`uskladiti <bank/reconciliation>` z "
"registriranim plačilom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:87
msgid ""
"For best practice, enter the check number as the :guilabel:`Memo` when "
"registering a customer payment by check."
msgstr ""
"Za najboljšo prakso vnesite številko čeka kot :guilabel:`Opombo`, ko "
"registrirate plačilo stranke s čekom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:89
msgid ""
":doc:`Batch payments <payments/batch>` can simplify reconciling deposits "
"containing multiple checks."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Paketna plačila <payments/batch>` lahko poenostavijo uskladitev "
"pologov, ki vsebujejo več čekov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:97
msgid "Registering payment from an invoice or bill"
msgstr "Registriranje plačila iz računa ali predračuna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:99
msgid "To register a payment for an invoice or a bill, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za registracijo plačila za račun ali predračun sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:101
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Pay` on a customer invoice or vendor bill. In "
"the :guilabel:`Pay` window, select the :guilabel:`Journal` and "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Date`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Plačaj` na računu stranke ali predračunu dobavitelja. V "
"oknu :guilabel:`Plačaj` izberite :guilabel:`Dnevnik` in :guilabel:`Datum "
"plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:103
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:297
msgid ""
"If previously set, the contact's preferred :guilabel:`Payment Method` is "
"automatically selected by default but can be updated if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Če je bila predhodno nastavljena, je privzeta metoda plačila stika "
":guilabel:`Način plačila` samodejno izbrana, vendar jo je mogoče po potrebi "
"posodobiti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:105
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:299
msgid ""
"If using :doc:`payment terms <customer_invoices/payment_terms>`, "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` is automatically set based on the installment amounts "
"defined by the payment term. To pay the full amount instead, "
"click :guilabel:`full amount`."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi :doc:`plačilnih pogojev <customer_invoices/payment_terms>` je "
":guilabel:`Znesek` samodejno nastavljen na podlagi zneskov obrokov, "
"določenih s plačilnimi pogoji. Za plačilo celotnega zneska namesto tega "
"kliknite :guilabel:`celoten znesek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:108
msgid "If necessary, edit the :guilabel:`Memo`."
msgstr "Po potrebi uredite :guilabel:`Opombo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:109
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Create Payment`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:111
msgid ""
"After the payment is registered, the customer invoice or vendor bill is "
"marked as :guilabel:`In payment`."
msgstr ""
"Po registraciji plačila je račun stranke ali predračun dobavitelja označen "
"kot :guilabel:`V plačilu`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:116
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:174
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:206
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:231
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:255
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:308
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:359
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:387
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:164
msgid "Without outstanding accounts"
msgstr "Brez odprtih računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:118
msgid ""
"If no :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` "
"are configured, no journal entry is created. To display more information "
"about the payment, click the :guilabel:`Payments` smart button."
msgstr ""
"Če :ref:`izravnalni računi <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` niso "
"konfigurirani, se dnevniški zapis ne ustvari. Za prikaz dodatnih informacij "
"o plačilu kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:122
msgid ""
"When the invoice or vendor bill is :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` "
"with a bank transaction, its status is updated to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun ali predračun dobavitelja :doc:`usklajen <bank/reconciliation>` "
"z bančno transakcijo, se njegov status posodobi na :guilabel:`Plačano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:126
msgid ""
"If a bank transaction is reconciled in a different currency, a journal entry "
"is automatically created to post the currency exchange gains/loss amount."
msgstr ""
"Če je bančna transakcija usklajena v drugi valuti, se samodejno ustvari "
"knjižba za knjiženje zneska dobička/izgube pri menjavi valut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:128
msgid ""
"When a bank transaction is reconciled with an invoice with cash-basis, a "
"journal entry is automatically created to post the cash-basis tax amount."
msgstr ""
"Ko je bančna transakcija usklajena z računom z obdavčitvijo na podlagi "
"denarnega toka, se samodejno ustvari knjižba za knjiženje zneska davka na "
"podlagi denarnega toka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:131
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:182
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:211
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:236
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:264
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:313
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:365
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:394
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:181
msgid "Using outstanding accounts"
msgstr "Uporaba odprtih računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:133
msgid ""
"By default, payments in Odoo do not create journal entries, but they can "
"easily be configured to create journal entries using :ref:`outstanding "
"accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>`."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto plačila v Odoo ne ustvarijo dnevniških zapisov, vendar jih je "
"mogoče enostavno konfigurirati za ustvarjanje dnevniških zapisov z uporabo "
":ref:`izravnalnih računov <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:137
msgid ""
"Registering a payment on a customer invoice or vendor bill generates a new "
"journal entry and reduces the :guilabel:`Amount Due` based on the payment "
"amount. The counterpart is reflected in an :ref:`outstanding <accounting/"
"journals/outstanding-accounts>` **receipts** or **payments** account. At "
"this point, the customer invoice or vendor bill is marked as :guilabel:`In "
"payment`. Then, when the payment is :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` "
"with a bank transaction, the invoice or vendor bill status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Evidentiranje plačila na račun stranki ali dobavitelju ustvari nov dnevniški "
"zapis in zmanjša :guilabel:`Znesek za plačilo` glede na znesek plačila. "
"Protikonto se odraža na :ref:`izravnalnem <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>` računu **prejemkov** ali **plačil**. V tej točki je račun stranki "
"ali dobavitelju označen kot :guilabel:`V plačilu`. Nato, ko je plačilo "
":doc:`usklajeno <bank/reconciliation>` z bančno transakcijo, se status "
"računa ali dobavitelja spremeni v :guilabel:`Plačano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:144
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-info-circle` information icon next to the payment line "
"displays more information about the payment. To access additional "
"information, such as the related journal, click :guilabel:`View`."
msgstr ""
"Ikona z informacijami :icon:`fa-info-circle` poleg vrstice plačila prikazuje "
"več informacij o plačilu. Za dostop do dodatnih informacij, kot je povezan "
"dnevnik, kliknite :guilabel:`Ogled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:0
msgid "See detailed information of a payment."
msgstr "Oglejte si podrobne informacije o plačilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:152
msgid ""
"Unreconciling a payment unlinks it from the invoice or bill but does not "
"delete the payment."
msgstr ""
"Preklic uskladitve plačila ga odveže od računa ali predračuna, vendar ne "
"izbriše plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:154
msgid ""
"If a payment is (un)reconciled in a different currency, a journal entry is "
"automatically created to post the currency exchange gains/losses (reversal) "
"amount."
msgstr ""
"Če je plačilo usklajeno ali prekinjeno v drugi valuti, se samodejno ustvari "
"knjižba za knjiženje zneska dobička/izgube (stornacije) pri menjavi valut."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:156
msgid ""
"If a payment is (un)reconciled on an invoice with cash-basis taxes, a "
"journal entry is automatically created to post the cash-basis tax (reversal) "
"amount."
msgstr ""
"Če je plačilo usklajeno ali prekinjeno na računu z obdavčitvijo na podlagi "
"denarnega toka, se samodejno ustvari knjižba za knjiženje zneska davka "
"(stornacije) na podlagi denarnega toka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:160
msgid ""
"If the main bank account is set as the outstanding account on the bank "
"journal's payment method, registering the full payment on an invoice or bill "
"moves the invoice/bill directly to the :guilabel:`Paid` status without "
"requiring bank reconciliation."
msgstr ""
"Če je glavni bančni račun nastavljen kot račun za neporavnane postavke na "
"način plačila bančnega dnevnika, registracija celotnega plačila na računu "
"ali predračunu premakne račun/predračun neposredno v status "
":guilabel:`Plačano` brez potrebe po usklajevanju z banko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:167
msgid "Registering payments not tied to an invoice or bill"
msgstr "Registracija plačil, ki niso povezana z računom ali predračunom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:169
msgid ""
"When a new payment is registered via :menuselection:`Customers / Vendors --> "
"Payments`, it is not directly linked to an invoice or bill."
msgstr ""
"Ko je novo plačilo registrirano prek :menuselection:`Stranke / "
"Dobavitelji --> Plačila`, ni neposredno povezano z računom ali predračunom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:176
msgid ""
"Payments that are not linked to an invoice or bill should not be registered "
"without using :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>`, as there is no way to associate the payment with the invoice or "
"bill since no journal entry is created for the payment. The amount paid or "
"received is not reflected in the accounting and the :guilabel:`Amount Due` "
"is not updated based on the payment amount."
msgstr ""
"Plačil, ki niso povezana z računom ali dobaviteljem, ne bi smeli "
"evidentirati brez uporabe :ref:`izravnalnih računov <accounting/journals/"
"outstanding-accounts>`, saj ni načina, da bi plačilo povezali z računom, ker "
"za plačilo ni ustvarjen noben dnevniški zapis. Plačani ali prejeti znesek se "
"ne odraža v računovodstvu in :guilabel:`Znesek za plačilo` ni posodobljen "
"glede na znesek plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:184
msgid ""
"Instead, the payment's journal entry matches the :guilabel:`outstanding "
"account` with the account receivable or the account payable until the "
"payment is manually matched with its related invoice or bill. "
"Then, :doc:`reconciling <bank/reconciliation>` the payment with the bank "
"transaction completes the payment workflow."
msgstr ""
"Namesto tega knjižba plačila uskladi :guilabel:`račun za neporavnane "
"postavke` z terjatvami do kupcev ali obveznostmi do dobaviteljev, dokler "
"plačilo ni ročno usklajeno z ustreznim računom ali predračunom. Nato "
":doc:`usklajevanje <bank/reconciliation>` plačila z bančno transakcijo "
"zaključi postopek plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:192
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:334
msgid "Payments matching"
msgstr "Ujemanje plačil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:195
msgid ""
"During the :doc:`bank reconciliation <bank/reconciliation>` process, a "
"remaining balance is identified if the total debits and credits do not match "
"when records are compared with bank transactions. This balance must either "
"be reconciled later or written off immediately."
msgstr ""
"Med postopkom :doc:`usklajevanja z banko <bank/reconciliation>` je "
"ugotovljeno preostalo stanje, če se skupni debeti in krediti ne ujemajo pri "
"primerjavi zapisov z bančnimi transakcijami. To stanje je treba bodisi "
"uskladiti kasneje bodisi takoj odpisati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:202
msgid "For a single invoice or bill"
msgstr "Za posamezen račun ali predračun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:208
msgid ""
"By default, payments in Odoo do not create journal entries. As a result, "
"there is no payment to match."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto plačila v Odoo ne ustvarijo knjižb. Posledično ni plačila za "
"usklajevanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:213
msgid ""
"A blue banner appears when validating a new invoice/bill and an "
"**outstanding payment** exists for this specific customer or vendor. To "
"match it with the invoice or bill, click :guilabel:`Add` "
"under :guilabel:`Outstanding Credits` or :guilabel:`Outstanding Debits`."
msgstr ""
"Ko potrdite nov račun/predračun in za to določeno stranko ali dobavitelja "
"obstaja **neporavnano plačilo**, se prikaže moder pasic. Za uskladitev s "
"računom ali predračunom kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj` pod "
":guilabel:`Neporavnani krediti` ali :guilabel:`Neporavnani debeti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:0
msgid "Shows the Add option to reconcile an invoice or a bill with a payment."
msgstr "Prikaže možnost Dodaj za uskladitev računa ali predračuna s plačilom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:220
msgid ""
"The invoice or bill is then marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until the "
"payment is :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with its "
"corresponding :doc:`bank transaction(s) <bank/transactions>`."
msgstr ""
"Račun ali predračun je nato označen kot :guilabel:`V plačilu`, dokler "
"plačilo ni :doc:`usklajeno <bank/reconciliation>` z ustrezno :doc:`bančno "
"transakcijo (transakcijami) <bank/transactions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:227
msgid "For multiple invoices or bills"
msgstr "Za več računov ali predračunov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:233
msgid ""
"By default, payments in Odoo do not create journal entries. As a result, "
"there is no payment to match, but this feature can still be used to match "
"miscellaneous journal items."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto plačila v Odoo ne ustvarijo knjižb. Posledično ni plačila za "
"usklajevanje, vendar lahko to funkcijo še vedno uporabite za usklajevanje "
"raznih postavk dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:238
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Payments matching` or :guilabel:`Auto-reconcile` tool allows "
"reconciling journal items with each other (i.e., payments with customer "
"invoices or vendor bills) either individually or in batches. Access "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`ellipsis`) button from the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` "
"or :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` journals, and select :guilabel:`Payments "
"Matching`. Alternatively, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --"
"> Reconcile`."
msgstr ""
"Orodje :guilabel:`Ujemanje plačil` ali :guilabel:`Samodejno usklajevanje` "
"omogoča usklajevanje postavk dnevnika med seboj (tj. plačil z računi strank "
"ali predračuni dobaviteljev) posamično ali paketno. Odprite "
":guilabel:`Nadzorno ploščo`, kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`tripičje`) v dnevnikih :guilabel:`Računi strank` ali "
":guilabel:`Predračuni dobaviteljev` in izberite :guilabel:`Ujemanje plačil`. "
"Druga možnost je :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> "
"Uskladi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:245
msgid ""
"To manually :guilabel:`Reconcile` journal items, select the individual items "
"from the list view and click :guilabel:`Reconcile`."
msgstr ""
"Za ročno :guilabel:`usklajevanje` postavk dnevnika izberite posamezne "
"postavke s seznama in kliknite :guilabel:`Uskladi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:251
msgid "Auto-Reconcile Feature"
msgstr "Funkcija samodejnega usklajevanja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:257
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:266
msgid "To use the :guilabel:`Auto-Reconcile` feature, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo funkcije :guilabel:`Samodejno usklajevanje` sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:268
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Items to reconcile` list view, "
"click :guilabel:`Auto-Reconcile` next to the receivable or payable account "
"(or a specific contact's group of journal items in that account)."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu :guilabel:`Postavke dnevnika za usklajevanje` kliknite "
":guilabel:`Samodejno usklajevanje` poleg računa terjatev ali obveznosti (ali "
"skupine postavk dnevnika določenega kontakta na tem računu)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:262
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Reconcile automatically` window, "
"click :guilabel:`Reconcile`."
msgstr "V oknu :guilabel:`Samodejno usklajevanje` kliknite :guilabel:`Uskladi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:271
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Reconcile Automatically` window, set "
"the :guilabel:`Reconcile` field depending on how you want to match journal "
"items:"
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Samodejno usklajevanje` nastavite polje "
":guilabel:`Uskladi` glede na to, kako želite uskladiti postavke dnevnika:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:274
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Perfect Match`: Each debit journal item will be matched with the "
"corresponding credit journal item of the same value."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Popolno ujemanje`: Vsaka debetna postavka dnevnika bo usklajena z "
"ustrezno kreditno postavko dnevnika enake vrednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:276
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Clear Accounts`: All reconciled journal items will have the same "
"matching number, as they are selected from the same account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Počisti račune`: Vse usklajene postavke dnevnika bodo imele enako "
"številko ujemanja, saj so izbrane iz istega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:281
msgid ""
"Invoices and bills are automatically matched to their corresponding payments "
"and marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until they are :doc:`reconciled <bank/"
"reconciliation>` with their corresponding :doc:`bank transactions <bank/"
"transactions>`."
msgstr ""
"Računi in predračuni se samodejno uskladijo z ustreznimi plačili in označijo "
"kot :guilabel:`V plačilu`, dokler niso :doc:`usklajeni <bank/reconciliation>"
"` z ustreznimi :doc:`bančnimi transakcijami <bank/transactions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:288
msgid ""
"Registering payments on multiple invoices/credit notes or bills/refunds "
"(group payments)"
msgstr ""
"Registriranje plačil za več računov/dobropisov ali predračunov/vračil "
"(skupinska plačila)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:290
msgid ""
"To register payments on multiple invoices/credit notes or bills/refunds, "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za registriranje plačil za več računov/dobropisov ali predračunov/vračil "
"sledite naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:292
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices/Credit Notes` "
"or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Bills/Refunds`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Kupci --> Računi/Dobropisi` ali "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Predračuni/Vračila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:294
msgid ""
"In the list view, click into the search bar, group by :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method`, select the relevant invoices/credit notes or bills/refunds and "
"click :guilabel:`Pay`."
msgstr ""
"V seznamskem pogledu kliknite v iskalno vrstico, grupirajte po "
":guilabel:`Način plačila`, izberite ustrezne račune/dobropise ali predračune/"
"vračila in kliknite :guilabel:`Plačaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:296
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Pay` window, select the :guilabel:`Journal` and "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Date`."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Plačaj` izberite :guilabel:`Dnevnik` in :guilabel:`Datum "
"plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:302
msgid ""
"To combine all payments from the same contact into a single payment, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Group Payments` option, or leave it unchecked to create "
"separate payments."
msgstr ""
"Če želite združiti vsa plačila istega kontakta v eno samo plačilo, omogočite "
"možnost :guilabel:`Skupinska plačila` ali pa jo pustite neopravljeno, da "
"ustvarite ločena plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:304
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Create payment`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:310
msgid ""
"The invoices or bills are then marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until they "
"are :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with the bank transactions."
msgstr ""
"Računi ali predračuni so nato označeni kot :guilabel:`V plačilu`, dokler "
"niso :doc:`usklajeni <bank/reconciliation>` z bančnimi transakcijami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:315
msgid ""
"The invoices or bills are then marked as :guilabel:`In payment` until the "
"bank transactions are :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` with the "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Računi ali predračuni so nato označeni kot :guilabel:`V plačilu`, dokler "
"bančne transakcije niso :doc:`usklajene <bank/reconciliation>` s plačili."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:321
msgid ""
"Registering a single payment for multiple customers or vendors (batch "
"payments)"
msgstr ""
"Registriranje enega plačila za več kupcev ali dobaviteljev (paketna plačila)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:323
msgid ""
"Batch payments allow grouping payments from multiple customers to "
"ease :doc:`reconciliation <bank/reconciliation>`. They are also useful when "
"depositing :ref:`checks <accounting/payments/checks>` or cash payments to "
"the bank or for generating bank payment files such as :doc:`SEPA <payments/"
"pay_sepa>` or :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."
msgstr ""
"Paketna plačila omogočajo združevanje plačil več kupcev za lažje "
":doc:`usklajevanje <bank/reconciliation>`. Uporabna so tudi pri vplačevanju "
":ref:`čekov <accounting/payments/checks>` ali gotovinskih plačil v banko ali "
"za ustvarjanje datotek za bančna plačila, kot so :doc:`SEPA <payments/"
"pay_sepa>` ali :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:329
msgid ":doc:`payments/batch`"
msgstr ":doc:`payments/batch`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:336
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Payments matching` tool opens all unreconciled journal items "
"and allows them to be processed individually, matching all payments and "
"journal items. Go to the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard`, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Reconcile` or click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`ellipsis`) button from "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` or :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` journals, and "
"select :guilabel:`Payments Matching`."
msgstr ""
"Orodje :guilabel:`Ujemanje plačil` odpre vse neusklajene postavke dnevnika "
"in omogoča njihovo posamično obdelavo ter ujemanje vseh plačil in postavk "
"dnevnika. Pojdite na :guilabel:`Nadzorna plošča računovodstva`, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Uskladi` ali kliknite "
"gumb :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`tri pike`) v dnevnikih "
":guilabel:`Računi kupcev` ali :guilabel:`Predračuni dobaviteljev` in "
"izberite :guilabel:`Ujemanje plačil`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:None
msgid "Payments matching menu in the drop-down menu."
msgstr "Meni za ujemanje plačil v spustnem meniju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:346
msgid ""
"During the :doc:`reconciliation <bank/reconciliation>`, if the sum of the "
"debits and credits does not match, there is a remaining balance. This either "
"needs to be reconciled at a later date or written off directly."
msgstr ""
"Med :doc:`usklajevanjem <bank/reconciliation>`, če se vsota debitov in "
"kreditov ne ujema, obstaja preostalo stanje. To je treba bodisi uskladiti "
"pozneje bodisi neposredno odpisati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:353
msgid "Registering a partial payment"
msgstr "Registriranje delnega plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:355
msgid ""
"To register a partial payment, click on :guilabel:`Pay` from the related "
"invoice or bill."
msgstr ""
"Za registriranje delnega plačila kliknite :guilabel:`Plačaj` na ustreznem "
"računu ali predračunu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:361
msgid ""
"In the case of a partial payment (when the :guilabel:`Amount` paid is less "
"than the total remaining amount on the invoice or the bill), fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` in the :guilabel:`Pay` window."
msgstr ""
"V primeru delnega plačila (ko je plačan :guilabel:`Znesek` manjši od "
"skupnega preostalega zneska na računu ali predračunu) izpolnite "
":guilabel:`Znesek` v oknu :guilabel:`Plačaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:367
msgid ""
"In the case of a partial payment (when the :guilabel:`Amount` paid is less "
"than the total remaining amount on the invoice or the bill), "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Difference` field displays the outstanding balance. "
"There are two options:"
msgstr ""
"V primeru delnega plačila (ko je plačan :guilabel:`Znesek` manjši od "
"skupnega preostalega zneska na računu ali predračunu) polje "
":guilabel:`Razlika pri plačilu` prikaže neporavnano stanje. Na voljo sta dve "
"možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:371
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Keep open`: Keep the invoice or the bill open and mark it with "
"a :guilabel:`Partial` banner;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pusti odprto`: Račun ali predračun ostane odprt in je označen z "
"oznako :guilabel:`Delno`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:373
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mark as fully paid`: Select an account in the :guilabel:`Post "
"Difference In` field and change the :guilabel:`Label` if needed. A journal "
"entry will be created to balance the accounts payable or receivable with the "
"selected account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Označi kot v celoti plačano`: V polju :guilabel:`Knjižite razliko "
"na` izberite konto in po potrebi spremenite :guilabel:`Oznako`. Ustvarjen bo "
"dnevniški vnos za izenačitev obveznosti do dobaviteljev ali terjatev s "
"izbrano kontom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:0
msgid "register a partial payment"
msgstr "evidentiranje delnega plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:383
msgid "Reconciling payments with bank transactions"
msgstr "Uskladitev plačil z bančnimi transakcijami"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:389
msgid ""
"Once a payment has been registered, the status of the invoice or bill "
"is :guilabel:`In payment`. The next step is :doc:`reconciling <bank/"
"reconciliation>` the related :doc:`bank transaction <bank/transactions>` "
"line with the invoice or bill to finalize the payment workflow and mark the "
"invoice or bill as :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je plačilo evidentirano, je status računa ali predračuna :guilabel:`V "
"plačilu`. Naslednji korak je :doc:`uskladitev <bank/reconciliation>` "
"povezane vrstice :doc:`bančne transakcije <bank/transactions>` z računom ali "
"predračunom, da se zaključi potek plačila in račun ali predračun označi kot "
":guilabel:`Plačano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments.rst:396
msgid ""
"Once a payment has been registered, the status of the invoice or bill "
"is :guilabel:`In payment`. The next step is :doc:`reconciling <bank/"
"reconciliation>` the payment with the related :doc:`bank transaction <bank/"
"transactions>` line to finalize the payment workflow and mark the invoice or "
"bill as :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je plačilo evidentirano, je status računa ali predračuna :guilabel:`V "
"plačilu`. Naslednji korak je :doc:`uskladitev <bank/reconciliation>` plačila "
"s povezano vrstico :doc:`bančne transakcije <bank/transactions>`, da se "
"zaključi potek plačila in račun ali predračun označi kot :guilabel:`Plačano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:410
msgid "Batch payments"
msgstr "Paketna plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:5
msgid ""
"Batch payments allow grouping payments from multiple customers or vendors "
"into a single batch and generating a detailed deposit slip or payment file "
"with a batch reference. This reference can be used "
"during :doc:`reconciliation <../bank/reconciliation>` to match bank "
"transactions with the corresponding payments. This feature is particularly "
"useful for submitting :doc:`SEPA Direct Debit payments <batch_sdd>`, "
"depositing cash payments or :ref:`checks <accounting/payments/checks>`, or "
"generating outgoing payment files, such as :doc:`SEPA <pay_sepa>` "
"or :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."
msgstr ""
"Paketna plačila omogočajo združevanje plačil več strank ali dobaviteljev v "
"en sam paket in ustvarjanje podrobnega položnice ali plačilne datoteke s "
"sklicno številko paketa. Ta sklic se lahko uporabi med :doc:`uskladitvijo "
"<../bank/reconciliation>` za ujemanje bančnih transakcij z ustreznimi "
"plačili. Ta funkcija je še posebej uporabna za oddajo :doc:`SEPA Direct "
"Debit plačil <batch_sdd>`, polaganje gotovinskih plačil ali :ref:`čekov "
"<accounting/payments/checks>` ali ustvarjanje datotek za odhodna plačila, "
"kot so :doc:`SEPA <pay_sepa>` ali :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/nacha>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:15
msgid ""
"To enable batch payments, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` section, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Batch Payments`."
msgstr ""
"Za omogočitev paketnih plačil pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, pomaknite se navzdol do razdelka "
":guilabel:`Plačila strank` in omogočite :guilabel:`Paketna plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:21
msgid "Batch creation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje paketa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:23
msgid "To create a batch payment, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za ustvarjanje paketnega plačila sledite naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:25
msgid ""
"Make sure all payments to be included in the batch have "
"been :ref:`registered <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so vsa plačila, ki bodo vključena v paket, "
":ref:`evidentirana <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:27
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Payments`."
msgstr "Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:28
msgid "Select the payments to include in the batch."
msgstr "Izberite plačila, ki jih želite vključiti v paket."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:31
msgid ""
"All payments in the batch must use the same payment method. If needed, "
"payments can be grouped using the :guilabel:`Payment Method Line`."
msgstr ""
"Vsa plačila v paketu morajo uporabljati isto plačilno metodo. Po potrebi "
"lahko plačila združite z uporabo :guilabel:`Vrstica plačilne metode`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:34
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create batch` or click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` "
"and select :guilabel:`Create batch payment`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari paket` ali kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Dejanja` in izberite :guilabel:`Ustvari paketno plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:36
msgid ""
"In the batch payment form, review the selected payments. If any individual "
"payments were missed, click :guilabel:`Add a line` and select the missing "
"payments to be included in the batch."
msgstr ""
"V obrazcu za paketno plačilo preglejte izbrana plačila. Če ste kakšno "
"posamezno plačilo izpustili, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` in izberite "
"manjkajoča plačila, ki jih želite vključiti v paket."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:38
msgid ""
"Once all relevant payments are included, click :guilabel:`Validate` to "
"finalize the batch."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vključena vsa ustrezna plačila, kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da "
"dokončate paket."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:41
msgid "Once validated, no additional payments can be added to a batch."
msgstr ""
"Ko je potrjeno, paketni plačilni operaciji ni mogoče dodati dodatnih plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:44
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Print` to download a list of the included payments."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Natisni`, da prenesete seznam vključenih plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:45
msgid ""
"To view existing batch payments, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Batch Payments`."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati obstoječa paketna plačila, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Kupci --> Paketna plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:51
msgid ""
"Once the bank transactions :doc:`have been created <../bank/transactions>` "
"in your database, you can :ref:`reconcile <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` them with the batch payment."
msgstr ""
"Ko bodo bančne transakcije :doc:`ustvarjene <../bank/transactions>` v vaši "
"bazi podatkov, jih lahko :ref:`uskladite <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` s paketnim plačilom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch.rst:56
msgid ":doc:`batch_sdd`"
msgstr ":doc:`batch_sdd`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:3
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) customer payments"
msgstr "Plačila strank prek SEPA direktne obremenitve (SDD)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:7
msgid ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) is a payment-integration initiative of the "
"European Union that facilitates standardized and simplified electronic "
"payments in euros across participating countries. With **SEPA Direct Debit** "
"(SDD), customers sign a mandate that authorizes you to collect future "
"payments from their bank accounts. This is particularly useful for recurring "
"payments based on a :doc:`subscription </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."
msgstr ""
"SEPA (Enotno območje plačil v evrih) je plačilna pobuda Evropske unije, ki "
"omogoča standardizirana in poenostavljena elektronska plačila v evrih v "
"sodelujočih državah. S **SEPA direktno obremenitvijo** (SDD) stranke "
"podpišejo mandat, ki vam dovoljuje, da prihodnja plačila poberate z njihovih "
"bančnih računov. To je še posebej uporabno za ponavljajoča se plačila na "
"podlagi :doc:`naročnine </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:13
msgid ""
"You can record customer |sdd| mandates in Odoo and generate XML files "
"listing payments to be collected with the mandates. :ref:`Uploading these "
"files to your bank <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` instructs them to collect "
"these payments from your customers."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo lahko zabeležite mandate strank |sdd| in ustvarite datoteke XML s "
"seznamom plačil, ki jih je treba pobrati z mandati. :ref:`Nalaganje teh "
"datotek v vašo banko <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` banki naroči, naj ta "
"plačila pobere od vaših strank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:18
msgid ""
"|sdd| is supported by all SEPA countries, which includes the 27 member "
"states of the European Union as well as additional countries."
msgstr ""
"|sdd| podpirajo vse države SEPA, kar vključuje 27 držav članic Evropske "
"unije in dodatne države."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:20
msgid ""
"`List of all SEPA countries <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-"
"library/other/epc-list-sepa-scheme-countries>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Seznam vseh držav SEPA <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-"
"library/other/epc-list-sepa-scheme-countries>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:29
msgid "Creditor identifier"
msgstr "Identifikator upnika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:31
msgid ""
"To enable |sdd| for customer payments, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` "
"section, enable :guilabel:`SEPA Direct Debit (SDD)`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. Then, scroll to the :guilabel:`Customer Payments` "
"section again, set the company's :guilabel:`Creditor Identifier`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti |sdd| za plačila strank, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se "
"pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`Plačila strank`, omogočite :guilabel:`SEPA "
"direktna obremenitev (SDD)` in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`. Nato se znova "
"pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`Plačila strank`, nastavite "
":guilabel:`Identifikator upnika` podjetja in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:37
msgid ""
"The creditor identifier is provided by your bank or the authority "
"responsible for delivering them in your country. For testing purposes, you "
"can use the test creditor identifier `DE98ZZZ09999999999`."
msgstr ""
"Identifikator upnika zagotovi vaša banka ali organ, pristojen za njihovo "
"izdajo v vaši državi. Za namene testiranja lahko uporabite testni "
"identifikator upnika `DE98ZZZ09999999999`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:42
msgid "PAIN file version"
msgstr "Različica datoteke PAIN"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:44
msgid ""
"By default, the :ref:`SEPA-compliant XML files <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>` "
"generated by Odoo use the |sdd| **PAIN.008.001.02** format. If your bank "
"requires the updated 2023 version, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals` and select the :guilabel:`Bank` journal. Then, "
"in the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` tab, set the :guilabel:`SEPA Pain "
"version` field to :guilabel:`Updated 2023 (Pain 008.001.08)`."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto :ref:`datoteke XML, skladne s SEPA <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>`, ki "
"jih ustvari Odoo, uporabljajo format |sdd| **PAIN.008.001.02**. Če vaša "
"banka zahteva posodobljeno različico iz leta 2023, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki` in izberite "
"dnevnik :guilabel:`Banka`. Nato na zavihku :guilabel:`Dohodna plačila` "
"nastavite polje :guilabel:`Različica SEPA Pain` na :guilabel:`Posodobljena "
"2023 (Pain 008.001.08)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:51
msgid ""
"`SEPA Direct Debit Core Customer-to-PSP Implementation Guidelines <https://"
"www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/implementation-guidelines/"
"sepa-direct-debit-core-customer-psp-implementation-0>`_."
msgstr ""
"`SEPA Direct Debit Core Customer-to-PSP Implementation Guidelines <https://"
"www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/implementation-guidelines/"
"sepa-direct-debit-core-customer-psp-implementation-0>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:57
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit Mandates"
msgstr "Mandati SEPA direktne obremenitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:59
msgid ""
"An |sdd| mandate is a legal document authorizing a company to debit funds "
"from a customer's bank account. It includes key information, such as the "
"customer's name and IBAN, the mandate's start and end date, and the "
"mandate's unique identifier. The mandate form must be filled in and signed "
"by the customer."
msgstr ""
"Mandat |sdd| je pravni dokument, ki podjetju dovoljuje obremenitev sredstev "
"z bančnega računa stranke. Vključuje ključne informacije, kot so ime stranke "
"in IBAN, začetni in končni datum mandata ter edinstveni identifikator "
"mandata. Obrazec mandata mora izpolniti in podpisati stranka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:65
msgid "Creating mandates"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje mandatov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:67
msgid "To create an |sdd| mandate:"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje mandata |sdd|:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:69
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Direct Debit Mandates`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Kupci --> Mandati za direktno "
"bremenitev`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:70
msgid "Click :guilabel:`New` and fill out the fields."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` in izpolnite polja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:71
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send & Print`, optionally edit the email, then "
"click :guilabel:`Send & Print` to email the mandate form to the customer for "
"signature."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji in natisni`, po želji uredite e-poštno sporočilo, "
"nato kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji in natisni`, da kupcu po e-pošti pošljete "
"obrazec za mandat v podpis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:73
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Validate` to activate the mandate."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da aktivirate mandat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:76
msgid ""
"A valid IBAN must be defined in the :guilabel:`Account Number` field of "
"the :doc:`bank journal <../bank>` used to receive |sdd| payments for the "
"mandate."
msgstr ""
"Veljaven IBAN mora biti določen v polju :guilabel:`Številka računa` v "
":doc:`bančnem dnevniku <../bank>`, ki se uporablja za prejemanje |sdd| "
"plačil za mandat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:80
msgid ""
"To print the mandate form after the mandate has been validated, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then select :guilabel:`Mandate "
"form`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite natisniti obrazec za mandat po potrditvi mandata, kliknite ikono "
":icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`zobnik`), nato izberite :guilabel:`Obrazec za "
"mandat`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:82
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SDD Scheme` depends on the type of customer: "
"Select :guilabel:`CORE` for B2C customers and :guilabel:`B2B` for B2B "
"customers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`SDD shema` je odvisna od vrste kupca: Izberite :guilabel:`CORE` "
"za B2C kupce in :guilabel:`B2B` za B2B kupce."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:84
msgid ""
"|sdd| mandates are created automatically for :ref:`online payments made with "
"SDD <payment_providers/bank_payments/sdd>`."
msgstr ""
"Mandati |sdd| se ustvarijo samodejno za :ref:`spletna plačila, opravljena s "
"SDD <payment_providers/bank_payments/sdd>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:87
msgid ""
"Once an |sdd| mandate is active, subsequent |sdd| payments can be generated "
"via Odoo and :ref:`uploaded to your online banking interface <accounting/"
"batch_sdd/XML>`. Customers with an active |sdd| mandate can also use this "
"payment method for :ref:`online purchases <payment_providers/bank_payments/"
"sdd>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je mandat |sdd| aktiven, je mogoče naslednja plačila |sdd| ustvariti prek "
"Odoo in :ref:`jih naložiti v vmesnik spletnega bančništva <accounting/"
"batch_sdd/XML>`. Stranke z aktivnim mandatom |sdd| lahko ta način plačila "
"uporabijo tudi za :ref:`spletne nakupe <payment_providers/bank_payments/sdd>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:95
msgid "Closing or revoking a mandate"
msgstr "Zapiranje ali preklic mandata"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:97
msgid ""
"|sdd| mandates are closed automatically after their :guilabel:`End Date`. If "
"this field is left empty, the mandate remains active until it is closed or "
"revoked. To close or revoke a mandate, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Direct Debit Mandates`, select the relevant mandate, and "
"click :guilabel:`Close` or :guilabel:`Revoke`."
msgstr ""
"|sdd| mandati se samodejno zaprejo po njihovem :guilabel:`Končnem datumu`. "
"Če to polje ostane prazno, mandat ostane aktiven, dokler se ne zapre ali "
"prekliče. Za zaprtje ali preklic mandata pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Kupci --> Mandati za direktno bremenitev`, "
"izberite ustrezen mandat in kliknite :guilabel:`Zapri` ali "
":guilabel:`Prekliči`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:102
msgid ""
"**Closing** a mandate updates the mandate's end date to the current day. "
"Invoices issued after the present day will not be processed with an |sdd| "
"payment. **Revoking** a mandate disables the mandate immediately. No |sdd| "
"payment can be registered anymore, regardless of the invoice's date. "
"However, payments that have already been registered are still included in "
"the next :ref:`SDD XML file <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>`."
msgstr ""
"**Zapiranje** mandata posodobi datum konca mandata na trenutni dan. Računi, "
"izdani po današnjem dnevu, ne bodo obdelani s plačilom |sdd|. **Preklic** "
"mandata takoj onemogoči mandat. Nobeno plačilo |sdd| ni več mogoče "
"zabeležiti, ne glede na datum računa. Vendar so plačila, ki so že bila "
"zabeležena, še vedno vključena v naslednjo :ref:`datoteko SDD XML "
"<accounting/batch_sdd/XML>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:109
msgid ""
"Mandates are automatically closed 36 months after the date of the last "
"collection."
msgstr "Mandati se samodejno zaprejo 36 mesecev po datumu zadnjega pobiranja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:110
msgid "Closed or revoked mandates cannot be reactivated."
msgstr "Zaprtih ali preklicanih mandatov ni mogoče ponovno aktivirati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:115
msgid "Processing |sdd| payments"
msgstr "Obdelava |sdd| plačil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:117
msgid ""
"All registered |sdd| payments can be processed at once by uploading an XML "
"file containing a batch of all posted |sdd| payments to your online banking "
"interface. To do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Vsa registrirana |sdd| plačila je mogoče obdelati hkrati z nalaganjem "
"datoteke XML, ki vsebuje paket vseh knjiženih |sdd| plačil, v vmesnik "
"spletnega bančništva. To storite tako:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:120
msgid ""
":ref:`Create a batch payment <accounting/batch/creation>` and include the |"
"sdd| payments to collect."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Ustvarite paketno plačilo <accounting/batch/creation>` in vključite "
"|sdd| plačila za pobiranje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:124
msgid ""
"You can filter payments by SDD scheme using the :guilabel:`SDD CORE` "
"and :guilabel:`SDD B2B` filters."
msgstr ""
"Plačila lahko filtrirate po SDD shemi z uporabo filtrov :guilabel:`SDD CORE` "
"in :guilabel:`SDD B2B`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Validate` the batch payment. The XML file is generated "
"automatically and available for download in the chatter."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Potrdite` paketno plačilo. Datoteka XML se samodejno ustvari in "
"je na voljo za prenos v pogovoru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:129
msgid ""
"Download the XML file and upload it to your online banking interface to "
"process the payments."
msgstr ""
"Prenesite datoteko XML in jo naložite v vmesnik spletnega bančništva za "
"obdelavo plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:130
msgid ""
"Once the |sdd| batch payment has been received, :doc:`reconcile the "
"transaction <../bank/reconciliation>` with the batch payment to mark the "
"related invoices as :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je |sdd| paketno plačilo prejeto, :doc:`uskladite transakcijo <../bank/"
"reconciliation>` s paketnim plačilom, da označite povezane račune kot "
":guilabel:`Plačano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:135
msgid ""
"To view the payments and invoices linked to a specific |sdd| mandate, click "
"the :guilabel:`Collections` and :guilabel:`Invoices Paid` smart button on "
"the :ref:`Direct Debit Mandate <accounting/batch_sdd/sdd_mandates>` form."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti plačila in račune, povezane s specifičnim |sdd| mandatom, "
"kliknite pametno tipko :guilabel:`Pobiranja` in :guilabel:`Plačani računi` "
"na obrazcu :ref:`Mandat za direktno bremenitev <accounting/batch_sdd/"
"sdd_mandates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:138
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Re-generate Export file` in the batch payment form to "
"regenerate the XML file."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ponovno ustvari izvozno datoteko` v obrazcu paketnega "
"plačila, da ponovno ustvarite datoteko XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:141
msgid ":doc:`batch`"
msgstr ":doc:`batch`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:142
msgid ""
":ref:`SEPA Direct Debit for online payments <payment_providers/bank_payments/"
"sdd>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`SEPA direktna bremenitev za spletna plačila <payment_providers/"
"bank_payments/sdd>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:143
msgid ""
"`SEPA guidelines <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/"
"implementation-guidelines/sepa-credit-transfer-inter-psp-implementation-"
