"zapise. Če je |sdd| plačilo zavrnjeno, morate stornirati dnevniški zapis, "
"povezan z zavrnjenim plačilom, in uskladiti storno dnevniškega zapisa s "
"transakcijo za |sdd| zavrnitev. Za to sledite naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:190
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(information)` icon in the "
"footer of the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab, then click :guilabel:`View` to "
"access the payment associated with the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(informacije)` v nogi "
"zavihka :guilabel:`Postavke računa`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Prikaži`, da "
"dostopate do plačila, povezanega z računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:193
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Journal entry` smart button to access the related "
"journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite pametno tipko :guilabel:`Vnos v dnevnik`, da dostopate do "
"povezanega vnosa v dnevnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:194
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Reverse entry`, optionally edit the fields in the popup, "
"then click :guilabel:`Reverse`. A reversal entry is created with "
"a :guilabel:`Reference` mentioning the initial journal entry. As a result, "
"the invoice is marked as :guilabel:`Not paid`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Storniraj vnos`, po želji uredite polja v pojavnem oknu, "
"nato kliknite :guilabel:`Storniraj`. Ustvari se stornirani vnos z "
":guilabel:`Referenco`, ki omenja prvotni vnos v dnevnik. Posledično je račun "
"označen kot :guilabel:`Neplačan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/batch_sdd.rst:197
msgid ""
":ref:`Access the bank journal's reconciliation view <accounting/"
"reconciliation/access>` and :ref:`reconcile <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` the transaction created for the |sdd| rejection with the "
"reversal of the entry related to the payment."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dostopajte do pogleda uskladitve bančnega dnevnika <accounting/"
"reconciliation/access>` in :ref:`uskladite <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` transakcijo, ustvarjeno za zavrnitev |sdd|, s stornirano "
"postavko, povezano s plačilom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:3
msgid "Follow-up on invoices"
msgstr "Spremljanje računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:5
msgid ""
"Follow-up messages can be sent to customers when payments are overdue. Odoo "
"helps identify late payments and allows scheduling and sending the "
"appropriate reminders using **follow-up actions** according to the number of "
"overdue days. Follow-ups can be sent through different methods, including "
"email, WhatsApp message, SMS, or post."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila za spremljanje lahko pošljete strankam, ko so plačila zamudna. "
"Odoo pomaga prepoznati zamudna plačila in omogoča načrtovanje ter pošiljanje "
"ustreznih opominov z uporabo **dejanj za spremljanje** glede na število "
"zamudnih dni. Spremljanja lahko pošljete prek različnih načinov, vključno z "
"e-pošto, sporočilom WhatsApp, SMS-om ali pošto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:11
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Payment Follow-up <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=50qy2ygS7eM>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Payment Follow-up <https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=50qy2ygS7eM>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:12
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/payment_terms`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/payment_terms`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:19
msgid ""
"To configure :guilabel:`Follow-up actions`, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Configuration --> Follow-up Levels`. In the :guilabel:`Follow-up Levels` "
"list view, several follow-up levels and actions are configured by default."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo :guilabel:`Dejanj za spremljanje` pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Ravni spremljanja`. V "
"seznamskem pogledu :guilabel:`Ravni spremljanja` je privzeto konfiguriranih "
"več ravni in dejanj spremljanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:23
msgid ""
"To modify a follow-up level, click on the record. From the form view, edit "
"the :guilabel:`Description` or adjust the number of days before a reminder "
"is sent. In the :guilabel:`Notification` tab, select :guilabel:`Actions` "
"such as :guilabel:`Send Email`, :doc:`Send WhatsApp message </applications/"
"productivity/whatsapp>`, :ref:`Send SMS Message <pricing/pricing_and_faq>`, "
"and :ref:`Send a Letter <customer_invoices/snailmail>`."
msgstr ""
"Za spremembo ravni spremljanja kliknite zapis. V obrazčnem pogledu uredite "
":guilabel:`Opis` ali prilagodite število dni pred pošiljanjem opomina. V "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Obvestilo` izberite :guilabel:`Dejanja`, kot so "
":guilabel:`Pošlji e-pošto`, :doc:`Pošlji sporočilo WhatsApp </applications/"
"productivity/whatsapp>`, :ref:`Pošlji SMS sporočilo <pricing/pricing_and_faq>"
"` in :ref:`Pošlji pismo <customer_invoices/snailmail>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:30
msgid ""
"Sending letters and WhatsApp or SMS messages in Odoo requires :doc:`In-App "
"Purchase (IAP) </applications/essentials/in_app_purchase>` credit or tokens."
msgstr ""
"Pošiljanje pisem ter sporočil WhatsApp ali SMS v Odoo zahteva :doc:`kredit "
"ali žetone za nakupe v aplikaciji (IAP) </applications/essentials/"
"in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:33
msgid ""
"To use a pre-filled template when sending an email or letter, select "
"a :guilabel:`Content Template`. To modify it, click the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(internal link arrow)` icon next to the :guilabel:`Content "
"Template` field. If enabled, WhatsApp and SMS messages use a "
"specific :guilabel:`WhatsApp Template` or :guilabel:`Sms Template` field "
"that can be modified by clicking the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(internal link arrow)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo vnaprej izpolnjene predloge pri pošiljanju e-pošte ali pisma "
"izberite :guilabel:`predlogo vsebine`. Za spreminjanje kliknite ikono "
":icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(puščica za notranjo povezavo)` poleg "
"polja :guilabel:`Predloga vsebine`. Če je omogočeno, sporočila WhatsApp in "
"SMS uporabljajo določeno polje :guilabel:`Predloga WhatsApp` ali "
":guilabel:`Predloga SMS`, ki ga lahko spremenite s klikom na ikono :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`(puščica za notranjo povezavo)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:39
msgid ""
"Other options can be enabled in the :guilabel:`Options` section within the "
"specific follow-up level:"
msgstr ""
"Druge možnosti lahko omogočite v razdelku :guilabel:`Možnosti` znotraj "
"določene ravni opomina:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:41
msgid "Automate the reminder with the :guilabel:`Automatic` option."
msgstr "Opomnik avtomatizirajte z možnostjo :guilabel:`Samodejno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:42
msgid ":guilabel:`Attach Invoices` that are overdue in the reminder."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Priloži račune`, ki so v opominiku že zapadli."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add followers` on the related customer to receive notifications "
"about any email reply made on the reminder's email."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodaj sledilce` k povezanemu stranki, da prejmejo obvestila o "
"vseh e-poštnih odgovorih na e-pošto opomina."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:46
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Activity` tab, enable the option to automatically "
"schedule :doc:`activities </applications/essentials/activities>` when the "
"follow-up level is triggered. Select the :guilabel:`Responsible` user and "
"the :guilabel:`Activity Type`, and enter a :guilabel:`Summary`."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Dejavnost` omogočite možnost za samodejno načrtovanje "
":doc:`dejavnosti </applications/essentials/activities>`, ko se sproži raven "
"opomina. Izberite odgovornega uporabnika :guilabel:`Odgovorni` in "
":guilabel:`Vrsto dejavnosti` ter vnesite :guilabel:`Povzetek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:50
msgid ""
"To add a new :guilabel:`Follow-up Level`, click :guilabel:`New` and fill in "
"the fields."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje nove :guilabel:`ravni opomina` kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` in "
"izpolnite polja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:53
msgid ""
"Set a negative number of days to send a reminder before the invoice due date."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite negativno število dni za pošiljanje opomina pred rokom plačila "
"računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:58
msgid "Invoice follow-ups"
msgstr "Opomini za plačilo računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:61
msgid ""
"Reconcile all bank transactions before starting the follow-up process to "
"avoid sending reminders for invoices that have already been paid."
msgstr ""
"Pred začetkom postopka opominjanja uskladite vse bančne transakcije, da se "
"izognete pošiljanju opominov za račune, ki so že plačani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:64
msgid ""
"To view all overdue invoices, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers "
"--> Invoices`. In the :guilabel:`Invoices` list view, click into the search "
"bar and filter on :guilabel:`Overdue`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled vseh zapadlih računov pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Stranke --> Računi`. V seznamskem pogledu :guilabel:`Računi` kliknite v "
"iskalno vrstico in filtrirajte po :guilabel:`Zapadlo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:70
msgid "Follow-ups for one customer"
msgstr "Opomini za eno stranko"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:72
msgid ""
"For a detailed overview of a customer's invoice follow-up status, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`. Open the "
"customer's form and click the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. In "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice follow-ups` section, click on the different levels to "
"view the :guilabel:`Follow-up Status` of each level. If actions are needed, "
"click :guilabel:`Overdue Invoices` to have a detailed list of the overdue "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
"Za podroben pregled stanja opominov računov stranke pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Stranke`. Odprite obrazec "
"stranke in kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Računovodstvo`. V razdelku "
":guilabel:`Opomini za račune` kliknite na različne ravni za ogled "
":guilabel:`statusa opomina` za vsako raven. Če so potrebna dejanja, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Zapadli računi` za podroben seznam zapadlih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:78
msgid "Additional options can be set:"
msgstr "Nastavite lahko dodatne možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminders`: These are either :guilabel:`Automatic` "
"or :guilabel:`Manual`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opomini`: Ti so lahko :guilabel:`Samodejni` ali :guilabel:`Ročni`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:81
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Next reminder`: The date by which the next follow-up actions "
"should be taken is automatically set when follow-ups are processed, but can "
"be manually adjusted if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Naslednji opomin`: Datum, do katerega je treba izvesti naslednja "
"dejanja opominjanja, se samodejno nastavi ob obdelavi opominov, vendar ga je "
"mogoče po potrebi ročno prilagoditi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:83
msgid ":guilabel:`Responsible`: The user who handles the follow-up actions."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Odgovorni`: Uporabnik, ki izvaja dejanja opominjanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:85
msgid ""
"To manually send a payment reminder to a customer, click :guilabel:`Send` "
"and select the actions in the :guilabel:`Send and Print` window:"
msgstr ""
"Za ročno pošiljanje opomina za plačilo stranki kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji` "
"in izberite dejanja v oknu :guilabel:`Pošlji in natisni`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:88
msgid ":guilabel:`Print`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Natisni`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:90
msgid ":guilabel:`WhatsApp`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`WhatsApp`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:91
msgid ":guilabel:`Sms`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`SMS`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:92
msgid ":guilabel:`By post`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Po pošti`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:94
msgid ""
"Enable the :guilabel:`Attach Invoices` option, and change "
"the :guilabel:`Content Template`, :guilabel:`WhatsApp Template`, "
"or :guilabel:`Phone` if needed. Then, click :guilabel:`Send` "
"or :guilabel:`Send & Print` to send the :ref:`follow-up report <accounting/"
"follow_up/follow-up-report>`."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite možnost :guilabel:`Attach Invoices` in po potrebi spremenite "
":guilabel:`Content Template`, :guilabel:`WhatsApp Template` ali "
":guilabel:`Phone`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Send` ali :guilabel:`Send & "
"Print`, da pošljete :ref:`follow-up report <accounting/follow_up/follow-up-"
"report>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:100
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:19
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/invoice_digitization.rst:217
msgid ":doc:`/applications/essentials/in_app_purchase`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/essentials/in_app_purchase`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:103
msgid ""
"The contact information on the invoice or the contact form is used to send "
"the reminder."
msgstr ""
"Za pošiljanje opomina se uporabijo kontaktni podatki na računu ali "
"kontaktnem obrazcu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:104
msgid "The chatter keeps a full record of all follow-up actions."
msgstr "Pogovor hrani celotno evidenco vseh dejanj spremljanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:109
msgid "Follow-ups for all customers due for action"
msgstr "Spremljanja za vse stranke, ki zahtevajo ukrepanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:111
msgid ""
"After setting up the additional :ref:`follow-up <accounting/follow_up/follow-"
"ups-for-one-customer>` options, review which customers have overdue invoices "
"or require follow-up. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Customers`. In the :guilabel:`Customers` kanban view, click "
"the search bar and filter by :guilabel:`Overdue Invoices` "
"or :guilabel:`Requires Follow-up`."
msgstr ""
"Po nastavitvi dodatnih možnosti :ref:`follow-up <accounting/follow_up/follow-"
"ups-for-one-customer>` preglejte, katere stranke imajo zapadle račune ali "
"zahtevajo spremljanje. To storite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`. V pogledu kanban "
":guilabel:`Customers` kliknite iskalno vrstico in filtrirajte po "
":guilabel:`Overdue Invoices` ali :guilabel:`Requires Follow-up`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:117
msgid ""
"To take follow-up actions for all relevant customers, switch to the list "
"view and select the customers requiring follow-up. Then, click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` and select :guilabel:`Process Follow-ups` to send "
"them the :ref:`follow-up report <accounting/follow_up/follow-up-report>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti dejanja spremljanja za vse ustrezne stranke, preklopite na "
"seznamski pogled in izberite stranke, ki zahtevajo spremljanje. Nato "
"kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` in izberite :guilabel:`Process "
"Follow-ups`, da jim pošljete :ref:`follow-up report <accounting/follow_up/"
"follow-up-report>`."

