#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:132
msgid ""
"To get a comprehensive overview of a customer's account status, click "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Statement` smart button on the customer's form. This "
"statement corresponds to the :ref:`Partner Ledger <accounting/invoices/"
"partner-ledger>` report's portion specific to that customer."
msgstr ""
"Za celovit pregled stanja računa stranke kliknite pametno tipko "
":guilabel:`Customer Statement` na obrazcu stranke. Ta izpis ustreza delu "
"poročila :ref:`Partner Ledger <accounting/invoices/partner-ledger>`, ki je "
"specifičen za to stranko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:136
msgid ""
"To send it to the customer, click :guilabel:`Send`, change "
"the :guilabel:`Email Template` if needed, and click :guilabel:`Print & Send`."
msgstr ""
"Če ga želite poslati stranki, kliknite :guilabel:`Send`, po potrebi "
"spremenite :guilabel:`Email Template` in kliknite :guilabel:`Print & Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:139
msgid ""
"To view the customer statements for multiple customers at once, select the "
"customers from the :guilabel:`Customers` list view, click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)`, and select :guilabel:`Open Customer Statements`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite hkrati pregledati izpiske strank za več strank, izberite stranke "
"iz seznamskega pogleda :guilabel:`Customers`, kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`(Actions)` in izberite :guilabel:`Open Customer Statements`."

