msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`PDF` ali :guilabel:`XLSX`, da ustvarite datoteko PDF "
"oziroma XLSX."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:148
msgid "Follow-up report"
msgstr "Poročilo o opominih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:150
msgid ""
"To get a complete overview of a customer's due invoices, separating those "
"that are due from those that are overdue, click the :ref:`Customer Statement "
"<accounting/follow_up/customer-statement>` smart button on the customer's "
"form. Then, click :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report: Customer Statement` and "
"select :guilabel:`Follow-Up Report`."
msgstr ""
"Za popoln pregled zapadlih računov stranke, ki ločuje tiste, ki so zapadli, "
"od tistih, ki so že potekli, kliknite pametno tipko :ref:`Customer Statement "
"<accounting/follow_up/customer-statement>` na obrazcu stranke. Nato kliknite "
":icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report: Customer Statement` in izberite "
":guilabel:`Follow-Up Report`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/follow_up.rst:155
msgid ""
"To view the follow-up report for all customers at once, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Partner Ledger`. Then, "
"click :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report:` and select :guilabel:`Follow-Up "
"Report`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite hkrati pregledati poročilo o spremljanju za vse stranke, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Partner Ledger`. Nato "
"kliknite :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report:` in izberite :guilabel:`Follow-"
"Up Report`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:3
msgid "Forecast future bills to pay"
msgstr "Napovedovanje prihodnjih računov za plačilo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo, you can manage payments by setting automatic **Payments Terms** and "
"**follow-ups**."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo lahko upravljate plačila z nastavitvijo samodejnih **Plačilnih "
"pogojev** in **spremljanj**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:8
msgid "Configuration: payment terms"
msgstr "Konfiguracija: plačilni pogoji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:10
msgid ""
"In order to track vendor conditions, we use **Payment Terms** in Odoo. They "
"allow keeping track of due dates on invoices. Examples of **Payment Terms** "
"are:"
msgstr ""
"Za sledenje pogojev dobaviteljev v Odoo uporabljamo **Plačilne pogoje**. "
"Omogočajo sledenje rokom plačila na računih. Primeri **Plačilnih pogojev** "
"so:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:13
msgid "50% within 30 days"
msgstr "50% v 30 dneh"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:14
msgid "50% within 45 days"
msgstr "50% v 45 dneh"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:16
msgid ""
"To create them, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Invoicing: Payment Terms` and click on :guilabel:`Create` to add new terms "
"or click existing ones to modify them."
msgstr ""
"Za njihovo ustvarjanje pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Fakturiranje: Plačilni pogoji` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Ustvari`, da dodate nove pogoje, ali kliknite obstoječe, da jih "
"spremenite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Payment Terms <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/payment-"
"terms-terms-and-conditions-6852>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo vadnice: Plačilni pogoji <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/payment-"
"terms-terms-and-conditions-6852>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:23
msgid ""
"Once **Payment Terms** are defined, you can assign them to your vendor by "
"default. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Vendors --> Vendors`, select a "
"vendor, click the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, and select a specific "
"**Payment Term**. This way, every time you purchase from this vendor, Odoo "
"automatically proposes the chosen Payment Term."
msgstr ""
"Ko so **Plačilni pogoji** določeni, jih lahko privzeto dodelite svojemu "
"dobavitelju. To storite tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Dobavitelji --> "
"Dobavitelji`, izberete dobavitelja, kliknete zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja in "
"nabava` ter izberete določen **Plačilni pogoj**. Tako bo Odoo ob vsakem "
"nakupu pri tem dobavitelju samodejno predlagal izbrani plačilni pogoj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you do not set a specific Payment Term on a vendor, you can still set one "
"on the vendor bill."
msgstr ""
"Če za dobavitelja ne nastavite posebnega plačilnega pogoja, ga lahko še "
"vedno nastavite na računu dobavitelja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:32
msgid "Forecast bills to pay with the aged payable report"
msgstr "Napoved računov za plačilo z uporabo poročila o zapadlih obveznostih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:34
msgid ""
"To track amounts to be paid to the vendors, use the **Aged Payable** report. "
"To access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Partner "
"Reports: Aged Payable`. This report gives you a summary per vendor of the "
"amounts to pay, compared to their due date (the due date being computed on "
"each bill using the terms). This report tells you how much you will have to "
"pay within the following months."
msgstr ""
"Za sledenje zneskov, ki jih je treba plačati dobaviteljem, uporabite "
"poročilo **Aged Payable**. Za dostop do njega pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Poročila o partnerjih: Aged "
"Payable`. To poročilo vam poda povzetek po dobaviteljih o zneskih za plačilo "
"glede na njihov rok plačila (rok plačila se izračuna na vsakem računu z "
"uporabo pogojev). To poročilo vam pove, koliko boste morali plačati v "
"naslednjih mesecih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:41
msgid "Select bills to pay"
msgstr "Izberite račune za plačilo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:43
msgid ""
"You can get a list of all your vendor bills by going "
"to :menuselection:`Vendors --> Bills`. To view only the bills that you need "
"to pay, click :menuselection:`Filters --> Bills to Pay`. To view only "
"overdue payments, select the :guilabel:`Overdue` filter instead."
msgstr ""
"Seznam vseh računov dobaviteljev lahko dobite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Dobavitelji --> Računi`. Za ogled samo računov, ki jih "
"morate plačati, kliknite :menuselection:`Filtri --> Računi za plačilo`. Za "
"ogled samo zapadlih plačil izberite filter :guilabel:`Zapadlo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/forecast.rst:47
msgid ""
"You can also group bills by their due date by clicking :menuselection:`Group "
"By --> Due Date` and selecting a time period."
msgstr ""
"Račune lahko razvrstite tudi po njihovem datumu zapadlosti s klikom na "
":menuselection:`Združi po --> Rok plačila` in izborom časovnega obdobja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:5
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:796
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:5
msgid "Online payments"
msgstr "Spletna plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:7
msgid ""
"To make it more convenient for your customers to pay the invoices you issue, "
"you can activate the **Invoice Online Payment** feature, which adds a *Pay "
"Now* button on their **Customer Portal**. This allows your customers to see "
"their invoices online and pay directly with their favorite payment method, "
"making the payment process much easier."
msgstr ""
"Da vašim strankam olajšate plačevanje računov, ki jih izdajate, lahko "
"aktivirate funkcijo **Spletno plačilo računov**, ki doda gumb *Plačaj zdaj* "
"na njihov **Portal za stranke**. To strankam omogoča ogled računov na spletu "
"in neposredno plačilo z njihovim najljubšim načinom plačila, kar močno "
"olajša postopek plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:None
msgid "Payment provider choice after having clicked on \"Pay Now\""
msgstr "Izbira ponudnika plačilnih storitev po kliku na \"Plačaj zdaj\""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:19
msgid ""
"Make sure your :doc:`payment providers are correctly configured <../../"
"payment_providers>`."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so vaši :doc:`ponudniki plačilnih storitev pravilno "
"konfigurirani <../../payment_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:22
msgid ""
"By default, :ref:`Wire Transfer <payment_providers/bank_payments/"
"wire_transfer>` is the only payment provider activated, but you still have "
"to fill out the payment details."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je aktiviran le ponudnik plačil :ref:`Bančno nakazilo "
"<payment_providers/bank_payments/wire_transfer>`, vendar morate še vedno "
"izpolniti podatke o plačilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:25
msgid ""
"To activate the Invoice Online Payment, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings --> Customer Payments`, enable **Invoice Online "
"Payment**, and click on *Save*."
msgstr ""
"Za aktivacijo spletnega plačila računov pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve --> Plačila "
"strank`, omogočite **Spletno plačilo računov** in kliknite na *Shrani*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:29
msgid "Customer Portal"
msgstr "Portal za stranke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:31
msgid ""
"After issuing the invoice, click on :guilabel:`Send` and send the invoice by "
"email to the customer. They will receive an email with a link that redirects "
"them to the invoice on their **Customer Portal**."
msgstr ""
"Po izdaji računa kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji` in pošljite račun stranki po e-"
"pošti. Prejela bo e-pošto s povezavo, ki jo preusmeri na račun v njenem "
"**portalu za stranke**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:None
msgid "Email with a link to view the invoice online on the Customer Portal."
msgstr "E-pošta s povezavo za ogled računa na spletu na portalu za stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:38
msgid "They can choose which Payment Provider to use by clicking on *Pay Now*."
msgstr ""
"Izberejo lahko, katerega ponudnika plačilnih storitev bodo uporabili, s "
"klikom na *Plačaj zdaj*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:None
msgid "\"Pay now\" button on an invoice in the Customer Portal."
msgstr "Gumb \"Plačaj zdaj\" na računu v portalu za stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online.rst:45
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:3
msgid "Pay by checks"
msgstr "Plačilo s čeki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:5
msgid ""
"Once you decide to pay a supplier bill, you can select to pay by check. You "
"can then print all the payments registered by check. Finally, the bank "
"reconciliation process will match the checks you sent to suppliers with "
"actual bank statements."
msgstr ""
"Ko se odločite plačati račun dobavitelja, lahko izberete plačilo s čekom. "
"Nato lahko natisnete vsa plačila, registrirana s čekom. Nazadnje bo postopek "
"uskladitve bančnega izpiska usklajevanje čekov, ki ste jih poslali "
"dobaviteljem, z dejanskimi bančnimi izpiski."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:15
msgid "Activate checks payment methods"
msgstr "Aktivirajte načine plačila s čeki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:17
msgid ""
"To activate the checks payment method, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and scroll down to the :guilabel:`Vendor "
"Payments` section. There, you can activate the payment method as well as set "
"up the :guilabel:`Check Layout`."
msgstr ""
"Za aktiviranje načina plačila s čeki pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in se "
"pomaknite navzdol do oddelka :guilabel:`Plačila dobaviteljem`. Tam lahko "
"aktivirate način plačila in nastavite :guilabel:`Postavitev čeka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:22
msgid ""
"Once the :guilabel:`Checks` setting is activated, the **Checks** payment "
"method is automatically set up in the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tabs of "
"**bank** journals."
msgstr ""
"Ko je nastavitev :guilabel:`Čeki` aktivirana, se način plačila **Čeki** "
"samodejno nastavi v zavihkih :guilabel:`Odhodna plačila` **bančnih** "
"dnevnikov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:24
msgid ""
"Some countries require specific modules to print checks; such modules may be "
"installed by default. For instance, the :guilabel:`U.S. Checks Layout` "
"module is required to print U.S. checks."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere države zahtevajo posebne module za tiskanje čekov; takšni moduli so "
"lahko nameščeni privzeto. Na primer, modul :guilabel:`Postavitev čekov ZDA` "
"je potreben za tiskanje čekov ZDA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:29
msgid "Compatible check stationery for printing checks"
msgstr "Združljiva čekovna papirologija za tiskanje čekov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:32
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:3
msgid "United States"
msgstr "Združene države"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:34
msgid "For the United States, Odoo supports by default the check formats of:"
msgstr "Za Združene države Odoo privzeto podpira čekovne formate:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:36
msgid "**Quickbooks & Quicken**: check on top, stubs in the middle and bottom;"
msgstr "**Quickbooks & Quicken**: ček na vrhu, odtrganci na sredini in spodaj;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:37
msgid "**Peachtree**: check in the middle, stubs on top and bottom;"
msgstr "**Peachtree**: ček na sredini, odtrganci na vrhu in spodaj;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:38
msgid "**ADP**: check in the bottom, and stubs on the top."
msgstr "**ADP**: ček na dnu in odtrganci na vrhu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:43
msgid "Pay a supplier bill with a check"
msgstr "Plačajte račun dobavitelja s čekom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:45
msgid "Paying a supplier with a check is done in three steps:"
msgstr "Plačilo dobavitelju s čekom se izvede v treh korakih:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:47
msgid "registering a payment"
msgstr "registracija plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:48
msgid "printing checks in batch for all registered payments"
msgstr "paketno tiskanje čekov za vsa registrirana plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:49
msgid "reconciling bank statements"
msgstr "uskladitev bančnih izpiskov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:52
msgid "Register a payment by check"
msgstr "Registrirajte plačilo s čekom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:54
msgid ""
"To register a payment, open any supplier bill from the "
"menu :menuselection:`Purchases --> Vendor Bills`. Once the supplier bill is "
"validated, you can register a payment. Set the :guilabel:`Payment Method` "
"to :guilabel:`Checks` and validate the payment."
msgstr ""
"Za registracijo plačila odprite katerikoli račun dobavitelja iz menija "
":menuselection:`Nabava --> Računi dobaviteljev`. Ko je račun dobavitelja "
"potrjen, lahko registrirate plačilo. Nastavite :guilabel:`Način plačila` na "
":guilabel:`Čeki` in potrdite plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:60
msgid "Print checks"
msgstr "Natisnite čeke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:62
msgid ""
"On your :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` in the :guilabel:`Bank` Journal, "
"you can see the number of checks registered. By clicking "
"on :guilabel:`Checks to print` you have got the possibility to print the "
"reconciled checks."
msgstr ""
"Na vaši :guilabel:`Nadzorni plošči računovodstva` v dnevniku "
":guilabel:`Banka` lahko vidite število registriranih čekov. S klikom na "
":guilabel:`Čeki za tiskanje` imate možnost tiskanja usklajenih čekov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_checks.rst:66
msgid ""
"To print all checks in batch, select all payments from the list view and "
"click on :guilabel:`Print`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite natisniti vse čeke skupaj, izberite vsa plačila s seznamskega "
"pogleda in kliknite na :guilabel:`Natisni`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:3
msgid "Pay with SEPA"
msgstr "Plačilo s SEPA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:5
msgid ""
"SEPA, the Single Euro Payments Area, is a payment-integration initiative of "
"the European Union to simplify bank transfers denominated in euros. SEPA "
"allows you to send payment orders to your bank to automate bank wire "
"transfers."
msgstr ""
"SEPA, enotno euroobmočje za plačila, je plačilna pobuda Evropske unije za "
"poenostavitev bančnih nakazil v evrih. SEPA vam omogoča pošiljanje plačilnih "
"nalogov vaši banki za avtomatizacijo bančnih nakazil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:9
msgid "SEPA is supported by the banks of the 27 EU member states, as well as:"
msgstr "SEPA podpirajo banke v 27 državah članicah EU, pa tudi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:11
msgid "EFTA countries:"
msgstr "države EFTE:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:13
msgid "Iceland;"
msgstr "Islandija;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:14
msgid "Liechtenstein;"
msgstr "Lihtenštajn;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:15
msgid "Norway;"
msgstr "Norveška;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:16
msgid "Switzerland."
msgstr "Švica."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:18
msgid "Non-EEA SEPA countries:"
msgstr "Države SEPA zunaj EGP:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:20
msgid "Andorra;"
msgstr "Andora;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:21
msgid "Monaco;"
msgstr "Monako;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:22
msgid "San Marino;"
msgstr "San Marino;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:23
msgid "United Kingdom;"
msgstr "Združeno kraljestvo;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:24
msgid "Vatican City State."
msgstr "Vatikan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:26
msgid "Non-EEA territories:"
msgstr "Ozemlja zunaj EGP:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:28
msgid "Saint-Pierre-et-Miquelon;"
msgstr "Saint-Pierre in Miquelon;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:29
msgid "Guernsey;"
msgstr "Guernsey;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:30
msgid "Jersey;"
msgstr "Jersey;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:31
msgid "Isle of Man."
msgstr "Otok Man."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:33
msgid ""
"When paying a bill in Odoo, you can select SEPA mandates as a payment "
"option. At the end of the day, you can generate the SEPA file containing all "
"bank wire transfers and upload it to your online banking interface to "
"process the payments."
msgstr ""
"Pri plačevanju računa v Odoo lahko kot možnost plačila izberete SEPA "
"mandate. Ob koncu dne lahko ustvarite datoteko SEPA, ki vsebuje vsa bančna "
"nakazila, in jo naložite v vmesnik spletnega bančništva za obdelavo plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:37
msgid ""
"By default, the file follows the SEPA Credit Transfer **'pain.001.001.03'** "
"specifications. This is a well-defined standard among banks. However, for "
"Swiss and German companies, other formats are used "
"**'pain.001.001.03.ch.02'** for Switzerland and **'pain.001.003.03'** for "
"Germany."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto datoteka sledi specifikacijam SEPA Credit Transfer "
"**'pain.001.001.03'**. To je dobro opredeljen standard med bankami. Vendar "
"pa se za švicarska in nemška podjetja uporabljajo drugi formati: "
"**'pain.001.001.03.ch.02'** za Švico in **'pain.001.003.03'** za Nemčijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:41
msgid ""
"Once the payments are processed by your bank, you can directly import the "
"account statement in Odoo. The bank reconciliation process will seamlessly "
"match the SEPA orders you sent to your bank with actual bank statements."
msgstr ""
"Ko vaša banka obdela plačila, lahko bančni izpisek neposredno uvozite v "
"Odoo. Postopek bančnega usklajevanja bo brez težav uskladil SEPA naloge, ki "
"ste jih poslali banki, z dejanskimi bančnimi izpiski."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:51
msgid "Activate SEPA Credit Transfer (SCT)"
msgstr "Aktivacija SEPA Credit Transfer (SCT)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:53
msgid ""
"To pay suppliers with SEPA, you must activate the **SEPA Credit Transfer** "
"setting. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Settings --> Vendor Payments: SEPA Credit Transfer (SCT)`. By activating the "
"setting and filling out your company data, you will be able to use the SCT "
"option when paying your vendor."
msgstr ""
"Za plačilo dobaviteljem s SEPA morate aktivirati nastavitev **SEPA Credit "
"Transfer**. To storite tako, da odprete :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve --> Plačila dobaviteljem: SEPA Credit Transfer "
"(SCT)`. Z aktivacijo nastavitve in izpolnitvijo podatkov o vašem podjetju "
"boste lahko pri plačilu dobavitelju uporabili možnost SCT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:59
msgid ""
"According to the localization package installed, the **SEPA Direct Debit** "
"and **SEPA Credit Transfer** modules may be installed by default. If not, "
"they need to be :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Glede na nameščen paket za lokalizacijo sta modula **SEPA Direct Debit** in "
"**SEPA Credit Transfer** morda privzeto nameščena. Če nista, ju je treba "
":ref:`namestiti <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:65
msgid "Activate SEPA payment methods on banks"
msgstr "Aktivacija plačilnih metod SEPA pri bankah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:67
msgid ""
"From the accounting dashboard, click on the drop-down menu (:guilabel:`⋮`) "
"on your bank journal and select :guilabel:`Configuration`. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab, and, if not already present, "
"add :guilabel:`SEPA Credit Transfer` under :guilabel:`Payment Method`."
msgstr ""
"Na nadzorni plošči računovodstva kliknite spustni meni (:guilabel:`⋮`) pri "
"vašem bančnem dnevniku in izberite :guilabel:`Konfiguracija`. Kliknite "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Odhodna plačila` in, če še ni dodana, dodajte "
":guilabel:`SEPA Credit Transfer` pod :guilabel:`Način plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:71
msgid ""
"Make sure to specify the IBAN account number (domestic account numbers do "
"not work with SEPA) and the BIC (bank identifier code) in "
"the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da navedete številko računa IBAN (domače številke računov ne "
"delujejo s SEPA) in BIC (identifikacijska koda banke) na zavihku "
":guilabel:`Knjižbe`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:77
msgid "Registering payments"
msgstr "Registracija plačil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:79
msgid ""
"You can register any vendor payments made with SEPA. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Payments`. When creating your "
"payment, select :guilabel:`SEPA Credit Transfer` as the :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method`."
msgstr ""
"Plačila dobaviteljem, opravljena s SEPA, lahko registrirate. To storite "
"tako, da odprete :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Plačila`. "
"Pri ustvarjanju plačila izberite :guilabel:`SEPA Credit Transfer` kot "
":guilabel:`Način plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:83
msgid ""
"The first time you pay a vendor with SEPA, you have to fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank Account` field with the bank name, IBAN, and "
"BIC (Bank Identifier Code). Odoo automatically verifies if the IBAN format "
"is respected."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič plačate dobavitelju s SEPA, morate izpolniti polje "
":guilabel:`Bančni račun prejemnika` z imenom banke, IBAN in BIC "
"(identifikacijska koda banke). Odoo samodejno preveri, ali je format IBAN "
"pravilen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:87
msgid ""
"For future payments to this vendor, Odoo will automatically suggest you the "
"bank account, but it remains possible to select a new one."
msgstr ""
"Pri prihodnjih plačilih temu dobavitelju vam bo Odoo samodejno predlagal "
"bančni račun, vendar je še vedno mogoče izbrati novega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/pay_sepa.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once your payment is registered, do not forget to confirm it. You can also "
"pay vendor bills from the bill directly using the :guilabel:`Register "
"Payment` button at the top of a vendor bill. The form is the same, but the "
"payment is directly linked to the bill and will be automatically reconciled "
"with it."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vaše plačilo registrirano, ne pozabite ga potrditi. Račune "
"dobaviteljev lahko plačate tudi neposredno iz računa z gumbom "
":guilabel:`Registriraj plačilo` na vrhu računa dobavitelja. Obrazec je enak, "
"vendar je plačilo neposredno povezano z računom in se bo samodejno uskladilo "
"z njim."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:3
msgid "Trusted accounts (send money)"
msgstr "Zaupanja vredni računi (pošiljanje denarja)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:5
msgid ""
"To protect users from sending money to scammers, vendor bank account numbers "
"must be marked as trusted before you can use them to make an outgoing "
"payment."
msgstr ""
"Za zaščito uporabnikov pred pošiljanjem denarja prevarantom je treba "
"številke bančnih računov dobaviteljev označiti kot zaupanja vredne, preden "
"jih lahko uporabite za odhodna plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:8
msgid ""
"To do so, open the vendor bank account and click on the :guilabel:`Send "
"Money` toggle switch button."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da odprete bančni račun dobavitelja in kliknete stikalo "
":guilabel:`Pošlji denar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:None
msgid ""
"Example of a vendor bank account with the \"Send Money\" toggle button "
"switched to \"trusted.\""
msgstr ""
"Primer bančnega računa dobavitelja s stikalom \"Pošlji denar\" preklopljenim "
"na \"zaupanja vreden\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:15
msgid "All accounts are initially marked as untrusted."
msgstr "Vsi računi so sprva označeni kot nezaupanja vredni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:18
msgid "Phishing attacks"
msgstr "Phishingové útoky"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:20
msgid ""
"A **phishing attack** is an online scam designed to trick individuals or "
"companies into giving away sensitive information or money by sending out "
"fraudulent communication. Fraudsters pretend to be legitimate companies and "
"may use partial information to give credibility to their requests."
msgstr ""
"**Phishingový útok** je online podvod navržený tak, aby přiměl jednotlivce "
"nebo společnosti k vyzrazení citlivých informací nebo peněz prostřednictvím "
"podvodné komunikace. Podvodníci se vydávají za legitimní společnosti a mohou "
"použít částečné informace, aby dodali svým požadavkům věrohodnost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:24
msgid ""
"There are several types of phishing attacks, including **invoice fraud**. In "
"this case, the fraudster pretends to be a genuine supplier following up on "
"unpaid bills or sending a new invoice, but with different payment "
"information than usual and with fake contact details."
msgstr ""
"Existuje několik typů phishingových útoků, včetně **podvodu s fakturami**. V "
"tomto případě se podvodník vydává za skutečného dodavatele, který se "
"dotazuje na nezaplacené faktury nebo zasílá novou fakturu, ale s jinými "
"platebními údaji než obvykle a s falešnými kontaktními údaji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:28
msgid ""
"To protect yourself from these types of phishing attacks, remain vigilant "
"when you receive unexpected invoices or payment requests."
msgstr ""
"Abyste se ochránili před těmito typy phishingových útoků, zůstaňte "
"obezřetní, když obdržíte neočekávané faktury nebo žádosti o platbu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:32
msgid ""
"In case of doubt, **we recommend contacting the vendor by phone**. Make sure "
"to call an official phone number by searching yourself, as the URLs, email "
"addresses, and phone numbers written in the communication you received may "
"be fake."
msgstr ""
"V případě pochybností **doporučujeme kontaktovat dodavatele telefonicky**. "
"Ujistěte se, že voláte na oficiální telefonní číslo tak, že si ho sami "
"vyhledáte, protože URL adresy, e-mailové adresy a telefonní čísla uvedené v "
"komunikaci, kterou jste obdrželi, mohou být falešné."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:37
msgid "Elements to check"
msgstr "Prvky ke kontrole"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:39
msgid ""
"There are several elements you can check by yourself when you receive an "
"outgoing payment request to a new account:"
msgstr ""
"Existuje několik prvků, které můžete sami zkontrolovat, když obdržíte žádost "
"o odchozí platbu na nový účet:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:46
msgid "Communication style"
msgstr "Styl komunikace"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:43
msgid ""
"Fraudulent emails and invoices often use a different communication style, "
"such as **different wording**, and may include **spelling and grammatical "
"mistakes**. Examine and **compare** them with previous ones that you know to "
"be authentic (e.g., payment instructions, language, company logo, etc.).*"
msgstr ""
"Podvodné e-maily a faktury často používají odlišný styl komunikace, jako "
"například **odlišné formulace**, a mohou obsahovat **pravopisné a gramatické "
"chyby**. Prozkoumejte je a **porovnejte** je s předchozími, o nichž víte, že "
"jsou autentické (např. platební instrukce, jazyk, logo společnosti atd.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:50
msgid "Urgency"
msgstr "Naléhavost"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:49
msgid ""
"Invoice frauds often use **urgent or threatening language** and change the "
"**payment deadline**. Check if you really received a late payment reminder "
"previously."
msgstr ""
"Podvody s fakturami často používají **naléhavý nebo hrozivý jazyk** a mění "
"**termín platby**. Zkontrolujte, zda jste skutečně dříve obdrželi připomínku "
"k po splatnosti platby."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:53
msgid "Type of account"
msgstr "Typ účtu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:53
msgid ""
"A company is unlikely to replace a bank account with a **money transfer "
"service**."
msgstr ""
"Je nepravděpodobné, že by společnost nahradila bankovní účet **službou pro "
"převod peněz**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:60
msgid "Email and links domain names"
msgstr "Názvy domén e-mailů a odkazů"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:56
msgid ""
"Double-check the **email address domain** (`example@domain.com`). However, "
"be wary that fraudsters can make their email addresses look genuine or even "
"hack email addresses from your vendor's employees or even someone within "
"your own organization."
msgstr ""
"Důkladně zkontrolujte **doménu e-mailové adresy** (`priklad@domena.cz`). "
"Mějte však na paměti, že podvodníci mohou své e-mailové adresy upravit tak, "
"aby vypadaly skutečně, nebo dokonce napadnout e-mailové adresy zaměstnanců "
"vašeho dodavatele nebo dokonce někoho z vaší vlastní organizace."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/trusted_accounts.rst:60
msgid ""
"Hover over the links in your email and check that the URLs they redirect to "
"are genuine. Your internet browser usually displays the link's target at the "
"bottom left of the window."
msgstr ""
"Najeďte myší na odkazy v e-mailu a zkontrolujte, že URL adresy, na které "
"přesměrovávají, jsou skutečné. Váš internetový prohlížeč obvykle zobrazuje "
"cíl odkazu v levém dolním rohu okna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo includes **generic** and **dynamic** reports available for all "
"countries, regardless of the :doc:`localization package <../../finance/"
"fiscal_localizations>` installed:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo zahrnuje **obecné** a **dynamické** sestavy dostupné pro všechny země "
"bez ohledu na nainstalovaný :doc:`balíček lokalizace <../../finance/"
"fiscal_localizations>`:"

