msgid ":ref:`accounting/reporting/executive-summary`"
msgstr ":ref:`accounting/reporting/executive-summary`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:13
msgid ":ref:`accounting/reporting/general-ledger`"
msgstr ":ref:`accounting/reporting/general-ledger`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`accounting/reporting/aged-receivable`"
msgstr ":ref:`accounting/reporting/aged-receivable`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:15
msgid ":ref:`accounting/reporting/aged-payable`"
msgstr ":ref:`accounting/reporting/aged-payable`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:16
msgid ":ref:`accounting/reporting/cash-flow-statement`"
msgstr ":ref:`accounting/reporting/cash-flow-statement`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:17
msgid ":ref:`accounting/reporting/tax-report`"
msgstr ":ref:`accounting/reporting/tax-report`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:18
msgid ":ref:`accounting/reporting/audit-trail`"
msgstr ":ref:`accounting/reporting/audit-trail`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:20
msgid ""
"To expand the lines of a report and view its details, click the :icon:`fa-"
"caret-right` (:guilabel:`right arrow`) on the left. Then click the :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` (:guilabel:`down arrow`) to the right of the account, journal "
"entry, payment, invoice, etc. to :guilabel:`Annotate` and view the details."
msgstr ""
"Če želite razširiti vrstice poročila in si ogledati podrobnosti, kliknite "
":icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`puščica desno`) na levi strani. Nato "
"kliknite :icon:`fa-caret-down` (:guilabel:`puščica dol`) desno od konta, "
"knjižbe, plačila, računa itd., da lahko :guilabel:`Dodajate opombe` in si "
"ogledate podrobnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:None
msgid "Annotate reports."
msgstr "Dodajanje opomb k poročilom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:28
msgid ""
"To export reports in PDF or XLSX format, click :guilabel:`PDF` at the top or "
"click the :icon:`fa-caret-down` (:guilabel:`down arrow`) icon next to "
"the :guilabel:`PDF` button and select :guilabel:`XLSX`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvoziti poročila v obliki PDF ali XLSX, kliknite :guilabel:`PDF` "
"na vrhu ali kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-caret-down` (:guilabel:`puščica dol`) "
"poleg gumba :guilabel:`PDF` in izberite :guilabel:`XLSX`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:32
msgid ""
"To compare values across periods, click the :guilabel:`Comparison` menu and "
"select the periods you want to compare."
msgstr ""
"Če želite primerjati vrednosti med obdobji, kliknite meni "
":guilabel:`Primerjava` in izberite obdobja, ki jih želite primerjati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:None
msgid "Comparison menu to compare time periods."
msgstr "Meni primerjave za primerjavo časovnih obdobij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:43
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Balance Sheet` shows a snapshot of your organization's "
"assets, liabilities, and equity at a particular date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bilanca stanja` prikazuje posnetek sredstev, obveznosti in "
"kapitala vaše organizacije na določen datum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:51
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Profit and Loss` report (or **Income Statement**) shows your "
"company's net income by deducting expenses from revenue for the reporting "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`Izkaz poslovnega izida` (ali **izkaz prihodkov in "
"odhodkov**) prikazuje čisti dobiček vašega podjetja z odštevanjem stroškov "
"od prihodkov za poročevalsko obdobje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:57
msgid "Executive Summary"
msgstr "Povzetek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:59
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Executive Summary` provides an overview of all the important "
"figures for overseeing your company's performance."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izvršni povzetek` zagotavlja pregled vseh pomembnih številk za "
"nadzor uspešnosti vašega podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:62
msgid "It includes the following items:"
msgstr "Vključuje naslednje elemente:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:72
msgid ":guilabel:`Performance`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uspešnost`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:66
msgid ":guilabel:`Gross profit margin`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Bruto dobičkovni pribitek`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:66
msgid ""
"The contribution of all sales your business makes **minus** any direct costs "
"needed to make those sales (labor, materials, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Prispevek vseh prodaj, ki jih opravi vaše podjetje, **minus** neposredni "
"stroški, potrebni za te prodaje (delo, materiali itd.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:70
msgid ":guilabel:`Net profit margin`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Neto dobičkovni pribitek`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:69
msgid ""
"The contribution of all sales made by your business **minus** any direct "
"costs needed to make those sales *and* fixed overheads your company has "
"(electricity, rent, taxes to be paid as a result of those sales, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Prispevek vseh prodaj, ki jih opravi vaše podjetje, **minus** neposredni "
"stroški, potrebni za te prodaje *in* fiksni splošni stroški vašega podjetja "
"(elektrika, najemnina, davki, ki jih je treba plačati zaradi teh prodaj itd.)"
"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:72
msgid ":guilabel:`Return on investment (per annum)`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Donosnost naložbe (na leto)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:73
msgid ""
"The ratio of the net profit to the amount of assets the company used to make "
"those profits."
msgstr ""
"Razmerje med neto dobičkom in višino sredstev, ki jih je podjetje uporabilo "
"za dosego tega dobička."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:88
msgid ":guilabel:`Position`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pozicija`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:76
msgid ":guilabel:`Average debtors days`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Povprečno število dni dolga`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:76
msgid ""
"The average number of days it takes your customers to (fully) pay you across "
"all your customer invoices."
msgstr ""
"Povprečno število dni, ki ga vaše stranke potrebujejo, da vas (v celoti) "
"plačajo, za vse vaše račune strankam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:78
msgid ":guilabel:`Average creditors days`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Povprečno število dni upnika`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:79
msgid ""
"The average number of days it takes you to (fully) pay your suppliers across "
"all your bills."
msgstr ""
"Povprečno število dni, ki jih potrebujete, da (v celoti) plačate svoje "
"dobavitelje, za vse vaše račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Short-term cash forecast`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kratkoročna napoved denarnega toka`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:81
msgid ""
"How much cash is expected in or out of your business in the next month, "
"i.e., the balance of your **Sales account** for the month **minus** the "
"balance of your **Purchases account** for the month."
msgstr ""
"Koliko denarja se pričakuje v vaše podjetje ali iz njega v naslednjem "
"mesecu, tj. stanje vašega **računa prodaje** za mesec **minus** stanje "
"vašega **računa nakupov** za mesec."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:88
msgid ":guilabel:`Current assets to liabilities`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kratkoročna sredstva glede na obveznosti`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:85
msgid ""
"Also referred to as the **current ratio**, this is the ratio of current "
"assets (:dfn:`assets that could be turned into cash within a year`) to the "
"current liabilities (:dfn:`liabilities that will be due in the next year`). "
"It is typically used to measure a company's ability to service its debt."
msgstr ""
"Znano tudi kot **kazalnik tekočega razmerja**, to je razmerje kratkoročnih "
"sredstev (:dfn:`sredstva, ki bi jih bilo mogoče spremeniti v gotovino v enem "
"letu`) do kratkoročnih obveznosti (:dfn:`obveznosti, ki bodo zapadle v "
"naslednjem letu`). Običajno se uporablja za merjenje zmožnosti podjetja za "
"servisiranje svojega dolga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:93
msgid "General Ledger"
msgstr "Kartica glavne knjige"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:95
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`General Ledger` report shows all transactions from all "
"accounts for a selected date range. The initial summary report shows the "
"totals for each account. To expand an account and view its details, click "
"the :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`right arrow`) on the left. This "
"report is useful for reviewing each transaction that occurred during a "
"specific period."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`Glavna knjiga` prikazuje vse transakcije z vseh računov "
"za izbrano časovno obdobje. Začetno povzeto poročilo prikazuje skupne zneske "
"za vsak račun. Če želite razširiti račun in si ogledati podrobnosti, "
"kliknite :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`puščica desno`) na levi strani. "
"To poročilo je uporabno za pregled vsake transakcije, ki se je zgodila v "
"določenem obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:105
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Aged Receivable` report shows the sales invoices awaiting "
"payment during a selected month and several months prior."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`Starostna struktura terjatev` prikazuje račune za "
"prodajo, ki čakajo na plačilo v izbranem mesecu in več mesecih nazaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:113
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Aged Payable` report displays information on individual "
"bills, credit notes, and overpayments you owe and how long these have gone "
"unpaid."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`Starostna struktura obveznosti` prikazuje informacije o "
"posameznih računih, dobropisih in preplačilih, ki jih dolgujete, in kako "
"dolgo so ti že neplačani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:119
msgid "Cash Flow Statement"
msgstr "Izkaz denarnih tokov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:121
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Cash Flow Statement` shows how changes in balance sheet "
"accounts and income affect cash and cash equivalents and breaks the analysis "
"down to operating, investing, and financing activities."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izkaz denarnega toka` prikazuje, kako spremembe na kontih bilance "
"stanja in prihodki vplivajo na denar in denarne ustreznike ter razdeli "
"analizo na operativne, naložbene in finančne dejavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:128
msgid "Tax Report"
msgstr "Davčno poročanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:130
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Report` shows the :guilabel:`NET` and :guilabel:`TAX` "
"amounts for all the taxes grouped by type "
"(:guilabel:`Sales`/:guilabel:`Purchases`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Davčno poročilo` prikazuje :guilabel:`NETO` in :guilabel:`DAVČNE` "
"zneske za vse davke, združene po vrsti (:guilabel:`Prodaja`/"
":guilabel:`Nakupi`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:150
msgid "Audit Trail"
msgstr "Revizijska sled"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:152
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Audit Trail` report tracks changes made to fields that have "
"an impact on accounting and includes the date and time of the changes, the "
"user who made the changes, the type of change, the previous value, and the "
"updated value."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`Revizijska sled` sledi spremembam polj, ki vplivajo na "
"računovodstvo, in vključuje datum in čas sprememb, uporabnika, ki je naredil "
"spremembe, vrsto spremembe, prejšnjo vrednost in posodobljeno vrednost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:156
msgid ""
"In addition to being recorded in the :doc:`chatter </applications/"
"productivity/discuss/chatter>`, changes to records are also tracked in the "
"audit trail, providing users a dedicated and detailed audit trail report. "
"The audit trail report is available for audit checks, satisfying the "
"requirements of the financial authorities and auditors of various countries."
msgstr ""
"Poleg beleženja v :doc:`klepetu </applications/productivity/discuss/chatter>"
"` so spremembe zapisov tudi sledene v revizijski sledi, kar uporabnikom "
"zagotavlja namensko in podrobno poročilo revizijske sledi. Poročilo "
"revizijske sledi je na voljo za revizijske preglede in izpolnjuje zahteve "
"finančnih organov in revizorjev različnih držav."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:161
msgid ""
"To access the audit trail, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review "
"--> Audit Trail`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do revizijske sledi pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Pregled --> Revizijska sled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:163
msgid ""
"An optional restrictive mode prevents tracked records from being deleted for "
"more controlled immutability. Instead of being deleted, these records can "
"only be cancelled or archived. To enable this restrictive mode, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Settings --> Configuration`, scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`Reporting` section, and tick the checkbox "
"beside :guilabel:`Restrictive Audit Trail`."
msgstr ""
"Neobvezen omejevalni način preprečuje brisanje sledenih zapisov za bolj "
"nadzorovano nespremenljivost. Namesto brisanja lahko te zapise le prekličete "
"ali arhivirate. Za omogočitev tega omejujočega načina pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> Konfiguracija`, se "
"pomaknite navzdol do razdelka :guilabel:`Poročanje` in označite potrditveno "
"polje poleg :guilabel:`Omejevalna revizijska sled`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:3
msgid "Analytic accounting"
msgstr "Analitično računovodstvo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:5
msgid ""
"Analytic accounting helps track costs and revenues and analyze a project's "
"or service's profitability. When creating journal entries, costs can "
"be :ref:`distributed <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` "
"across one or more analytic accounts."
msgstr ""
"Analitično računovodstvo pomaga slediti stroškom in prihodkom ter "
"analizirati donosnost projekta ali storitve. Pri ustvarjanju knjižb je "
"mogoče stroške :ref:`porazdeliti <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-"
"distribution>` po enem ali več analitičnih računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:9
msgid ""
"To activate this feature, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings` and enable :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting` in "
"the :guilabel:`Analytics` section."
msgstr ""
"Za aktiviranje te funkcije pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in omogočite :guilabel:`Analitično "
"računovodstvo` v razdelku :guilabel:`Analitika`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:13
msgid ":doc:`Analytic budget <budget>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Analitični proračun <budget>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:18
msgid "Analytic accounts"
msgstr "Analitični računi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:20
msgid "Analytic accounts give an overview of costs and revenue."
msgstr "Analitični konti dajejo pregled stroškov in prihodkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:22
msgid ""
"To access analytic accounts, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Analytic Accounts`. To create a new analytic account, "
"click :guilabel:`New` and fill in the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do analitičnih kontov pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Analitični konti`. Za ustvarjanje novega analitičnega "
"konta kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` in izpolnite naslednje podatke:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:26
msgid ":guilabel:`Analytic Account`: Assign the name of the analytic account."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Analitični konto`: Dodelite ime analitičnega konta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:27
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer`: Select the customer linked to the project, if "
"applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stranka`: Izberite stranko, povezano s projektom, če je primerno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:28
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reference`: Include a reference to make the account easier to "
"find if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sklic`: Vključite sklic, da bo konto lažje najti, če bo potrebno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Plan`: Link the :guilabel:`Analytic Account` to an :ref:`analytic "
"plan <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Načrt`: Povežite :guilabel:`Analitični konto` z :ref:`analitičnim "
"načrtom <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: In a :doc:`multi-company </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` environment, select the company using the analytic "
"account. To make the analytic account accessible to all companies, leave the "
"field empty."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podjetje`: V :doc:`večpodjetniških </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` okoljih izberite podjetje, ki uporablja analitični "
"konto. Če želite, da je analitični konto dostopen vsem podjetjem, pustite "
"polje prazno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: Update the currency of the analytic account if needed."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Valuta`: Po potrebi posodobite valuto analitičnega konta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:36
msgid "Then, the :doc:`budget <budget>` information can be filled in."
msgstr "Nato je mogoče izpolniti podatke o :doc:`proračunu <budget>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:41
msgid "Analytic plans"
msgstr "Analitični načrti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:43
msgid ""
"Analytic plans group :ref:`analytic accounts <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic_accounts>`, allowing the company to analyze its accounting, such as "
"tracking costs and revenues by project or department."
msgstr ""
"Analitični načrti združujejo :ref:`analitične konte <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`, kar podjetju omogoča analizo "
"računovodstva, kot je sledenje stroškom in prihodkom po projektih ali "
"oddelkih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:47
msgid ""
"To access analytic plans, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Analytic Plans`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new plan, add a name, "
"and fill in the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do analitičnih načrtov pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Analitični načrti`. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite nov načrt, dodajte ime in izpolnite "
"naslednje podatke:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Parent`: Link the plan to another analytic plan if a hierarchy "
"between plans must be built."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nadrejeni`: Povežite načrt z drugim analitičnim načrtom, če je "
"treba zgraditi hierarhijo med načrti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Applicability`: Define how the plan is applied when "
"creating a new journal entry:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeta uporabnost`: Določite, kako se načrt uporablja pri "
"ustvarjanju novega vnosa v dnevnik:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:55
msgid ":guilabel:`Optional`: Adding the analytic plan is not mandatory."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Neobvezno`: Dodajanje analitičnega načrta ni obvezno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mandatory`: The entry cannot be confirmed if no analytic account "
"is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obvezno`: Vnosa ni mogoče potrditi, če ni izbran noben analitični "
"konto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:57
msgid ":guilabel:`Unavailable`: The plan is not available."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ni na voljo`: Načrt ni na voljo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Color`: Set a color for the tag related to this specific plan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Barva`: Nastavite barvo za oznako, povezano s tem specifičnim "
"načrtom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:61
msgid ""
"To fine-tune a plan's applicability, create a new line in "
"the :guilabel:`Applicability` tab and set the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Za natančnejše prilagajanje uporabnosti načrta ustvarite novo vrstico v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Uporabnost` in nastavite naslednja polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Domain`: Choose the accounting documents to which the plan "
"applies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Domena`: Izberite računovodske dokumente, za katere velja načrt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Financial Accounts Prefixes`: Enter the prefix(es) of the "
"account(s) to which the plan applies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Predpone računovodskih kontov`: Vnesite predpono(-e) konta(-ov), "
"za katerega(-e) velja načrt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Category`: Choose the product category to which the plan "
"applies."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategorija izdelka`: Izberite kategorijo izdelka, za katerega "
"velja načrt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Applicability`: Define how the plan is applied when creating a "
"new journal entry. The applicability set here always overrides the default "
"applicability."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabnost`: Določite, kako se načrt uporabi pri ustvarjanju "
"novega knjiženja. Tukaj nastavljena uporabnost vedno preglasi privzeto "
"uporabnost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:70
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: In a :doc:`multi-company </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` environment, select the company using the plan. To "
"make the analytic plan accessible to all companies, leave the field empty."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podjetje`: V :doc:`več-podjetniških </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` okoljih izberite podjetje, ki uporablja načrt. Če "
"želite, da je analitični načrt dostopen vsem podjetjem, pustite polje prazno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:74
msgid "Two smart buttons are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo sta dva pametna gumba:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Subplans`: To have a more complex analytic structure. Click the "
"smart button, then click :guilabel:`New` to add a subplan. This creates a "
"parent-child relationship between the two plans, and the :guilabel:`Parent` "
"field of the subplan is automatically populated with the original plan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podnačrti`: Za bolj zapleteno analitično strukturo. Kliknite "
"pametni gumb, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Nov`, da dodate podnačrt. To ustvari "
"razmerje nadrejeni-podrejeni med načrtoma, polje :guilabel:`Nadrejeni` "
"podnačrta pa se samodejno izpolni z izvirnim načrtom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Accounts`: To access the :ref:`analytic accounts "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` linked to the plan."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Analitični konti`: Za dostop do :ref:`analitičnih kontov "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`, povezanih z načrtom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:84
msgid "Each analytic plan must have at least one analytic account."
msgstr "Vsak analitični načrt mora imeti vsaj en analitični konto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:89
msgid "Analytic distribution"
msgstr "Analitična razdelitev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:91
msgid ""
"The distribution of costs in one or more analytic accounts can be set in "
"each :ref:`invoice/bill <accounting/analytic_accounting/distribution-"
"invoices-bills>` or :ref:`en masse <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"distribution-mass>`."
msgstr ""
"Razdelitev stroškov na enega ali več analitičnih kontov je mogoče nastaviti "
"v vsakem :ref:`računu/terjatvah <accounting/analytic_accounting/distribution-"
"invoices-bills>` ali :ref:`množično <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"distribution-mass>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:96
msgid ""
"The analytic distribution is prefilled based on the applicability and "
"the :ref:`analytic distribution models <accounting/"
"analytic_distribution_models>`."
msgstr ""
"Analitična razdelitev je vnaprej izpolnjena glede na uporabnost in "
":ref:`modele analitične razdelitve <accounting/analytic_distribution_models>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:102
msgid "Analytic distribution on invoices or bills"
msgstr "Analitična razdelitev na računih ali terjatvah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:104
msgid ""
"To add analytic distribution, click the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` "
"column when creating an :ref:`invoice <accounting/invoice/creation>` "
"or :ref:`bill <accounting/vendor_bills/creation>`."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje analitične razdelitve kliknite stolpec :guilabel:`Analitična "
"razdelitev` pri ustvarjanju :ref:`računa <accounting/invoice/creation>` ali "
":ref:`terjatvice <accounting/vendor_bills/creation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:108
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field is mandatory only if "
"the :ref:`analytic plan <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` has "
"been set as :guilabel:`Mandatory` in either the :guilabel:`Default "
"Applicability` field on an analytic plan or the :guilabel:`Applicability` "
"field on an analytic plan line."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Analitična razdelitev` je obvezno samo, če je bil "
":ref:`analitični načrt <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` "
"nastavljen kot :guilabel:`Obvezno` bodisi v polju :guilabel:`Privzeta "
"uporabnost` na analitičnem načrtu ali v polju :guilabel:`Uporabnost` na "
"vrstici analitičnega načrta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:113
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Analytic` window, select the desired :guilabel:`Analytic "
"Accounts` in the different :guilabel:`Analytic Plans` displayed in columns. "
"Then, split the costs between the accounts by modifying the percentage."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Analitika` izberite želene :guilabel:`Analitične konte` v "
"različnih :guilabel:`Analitičnih načrtih`, prikazanih v stolpcih. Nato "
"razdelite stroške med konte z urejanjem odstotka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:None
msgid "create a distribution template"
msgstr "ustvarite predlogo razdelitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:123
msgid "Analytic distribution en masse"
msgstr "Analitična razdelitev množično"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:125
msgid ""
"To mass-edit analytic accounts in several entries simultaneously, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Journal items`, and select "
"the ones that need to be updated. Click the :guilabel:`Analytic "
"Distribution` column and add the required distribution in "
"the :guilabel:`Analytic` column, then click the :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(cross)` and :guilabel:`Update`. The analytic distribution "
"is then added to the selected journal items."
msgstr ""
"Za množično urejanje analitičnih kontov v več knjiženjah hkrati pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Postavke knjiženja` in "
"izberite tiste, ki jih je treba posodobiti. Kliknite stolpec "
":guilabel:`Analitična razdelitev` in dodajte zahtevano razdelitev v stolpec "
":guilabel:`Analitika`, nato kliknite :icon:`oi-close` :guilabel:`(križ)` in "
":guilabel:`Posodobi`. Analitična razdelitev je nato dodana izbranim "
"postavkam knjiženja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:134
msgid "Analytic distribution models"
msgstr "Modeli analitične razdelitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:136
msgid ""
"Analytic distribution models automatically apply a specific distribution "
"based on defined criteria."
msgstr ""
"Modeli analitične razdelitve samodejno uporabijo določeno razdelitev na "
"podlagi določenih meril."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:138
msgid ""
"To create a new analytic distribution model, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Analytic Distribution "
"Models`, click :guilabel:`New`, and set the conditions the model has to meet "
"to apply automatically:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega modela analitične razdelitve pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Modeli analitične "
"razdelitve`, kliknite :guilabel:`Nov` in nastavite pogoje, ki jih mora model "
"izpolnjevati za samodejno uporabo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:143
msgid ""
"All specified conditions of an analytic distribution model must be met for "
"the model to be applied. To apply an analytic distribution model based on "
"individual conditions, create separate analytic distribution models for each "
"condition."
msgstr ""
"Vsi navedeni pogoji modela analitične razdelitve morajo biti izpolnjeni, da "
"se model uporabi. Za uporabo modela analitične razdelitve na podlagi "
"posameznih pogojev ustvarite ločene modele analitične razdelitve za vsak "
"pogoj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:146
msgid ""
"Analytic distribution models can be combined and sequenced, allowing "
"distribution across multiple models if linked to different :ref:`analytic "
"plans <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>`. To adjust the order, "
"drag and drop the models using the :icon:`oi-"
"draggable` :guilabel:`(draggable)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Modele analitične razdelitve je mogoče kombinirati in zaporediti, kar "
"omogoča razdelitev po več modelih, če so povezani z različnimi "
":ref:`analitičnimi načrti <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>`. "
"Za prilagoditev vrstnega reda povlecite in spustite modele s pomočjo ikone "
":icon:`oi-draggable` :guilabel:`(vlečno)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:151
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accounts Prefixes`: Apply the distribution model only to journal "
"items involving accounts that begin with specific prefixes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Predpone kontov`: Model razdelitve uporabite samo za postavke "
"dnevnika, ki vključujejo konte, ki se začnejo s posebnimi predponami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partner`: Apply the distribution model only to journal items "
"involving a specific partner."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Partner`: Model razdelitve uporabite samo za postavke dnevnika, "
"ki vključujejo določenega partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:155
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: Apply the distribution model only to journal items "
"involving a specific product."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izdelek`: Model razdelitve uporabite samo za postavke dnevnika, "
"ki vključujejo določen izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:157
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: In a :doc:`multi-company </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` environment, apply the distribution model only to "
"journal items involving a specific company. To apply it across all "
"companies, leave the field empty."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podjetje`: V okolju z :doc:`več podjetji </applications/general/"
"companies/multi_company>` uporabite model razdelitve samo za postavke "
"dnevnika, ki vključujejo določeno podjetje. Za uporabo v vseh podjetjih "
"pustite polje prazno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:160
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`: :ref:`Analytic distribution <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` that will be applied when the "
"above conditions are met."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Analitična razdelitev`: :ref:`Analitična razdelitev <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>`, ki bo uporabljena, ko so "
"izpolnjeni zgornji pogoji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:165
msgid ""
"Any time a journal item is posted to the :guilabel:`Utilities (601000)` "
"account, it should be automatically distributed in "
"the :guilabel:`Departments` analytic plan as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli je postavka dnevnika knjižena na konto :guilabel:`Komunalne "
"storitve (601000)`, mora biti samodejno razdeljena v analitičnem načrtu "
":guilabel:`Oddelki` na naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:168
msgid "60% to the :guilabel:`Manufacturing` analytic account"
msgstr "60 % na analitični konto :guilabel:`Proizvodnja`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:169
msgid "30% to the :guilabel:`Marketing` analytic account"
msgstr "30 % na analitični konto :guilabel:`Trženje`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:170
msgid "10% to the :guilabel:`Admin` analytic account"
msgstr "10 % na analitični konto :guilabel:`Administracija`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:172
msgid ""
"To automate this distribution, the :guilabel:`Accounts Prefix` can be set to "
"`601`, as :guilabel:`Utilities (601000)` is the only account in the chart of "
"accounts that begins with `601`."
msgstr ""
"Za avtomatizacijo te razdelitve lahko nastavite :guilabel:`Predpono konta` "
"na `601`, saj je :guilabel:`Komunalne storitve (601000)` edini konto v "
"kontnem načrtu, ki se začne s `601`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:176
msgid ""
"If additional accounts such as :guilabel:`Electricity (601100)` "
"or :guilabel:`Gas (601200)` are available in the chart of accounts, the "
"distribution will also apply to both since they share the same prefix."
msgstr ""
"Če so v kontnem načrtu na voljo dodatni konti, kot sta :guilabel:`Elektrika "
"(601100)` ali :guilabel:`Plin (601200)`, se bo razdelitev uporabila tudi za "
"oba, ker imata isto predpono."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:180
msgid ""
"To define more criteria, use the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(adjust settings)` icon to reveal more columns or "
"click :guilabel:`View` on an individual analytic distribution model."
msgstr ""
"Za določitev več meril uporabite ikono :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`"
"(prilagodi nastavitve)`, da razkrijete več stolpcev, ali kliknite "
":guilabel:`Pogled` na posameznem modelu analitične razdelitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:183
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partner Category`: Apply this distribution model only to journal "
"items involving a partner in a specific category."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategorija partnerja`: Ta model razdelitve uporabite samo za "
"postavke dnevnika, ki vključujejo partnerja v določeni kategoriji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:185
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Category`: Apply this distribution model to journal items "
"involving a product in a specific category."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategorija izdelka`: Ta model razdelitve uporabite za postavke "
"dnevnika, ki vključujejo izdelek v določeni kategoriji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:189
msgid ""
"Alternatively, it is possible to create an analytic distribution model from "
"the :guilabel:`Analytic` window by clicking :guilabel:`New Model`:"
msgstr ""
"Alternativno je mogoče ustvariti model analitične razdelitve iz okna "
":guilabel:`Analitika` s klikom na :guilabel:`Nov model`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:192
msgid ""
"either when creating an invoice/bill and filling in the :ref:`analytic "
"distribution <accounting/analytic_accounting/distribution-invoices-bills>`;"
msgstr ""
"bodisi pri ustvarjanju računa/predračuna in izpolnjevanju :ref:`analitične "
"razdelitve <accounting/analytic_accounting/distribution-invoices-bills>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/analytic_accounting.rst:194
msgid ""
"or when :ref:`mass-editing analytic accounts <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"distribution-mass>` in several entries simultaneously."
msgstr ""
"ali pri :ref:`množičnem urejanju analitičnih kontov <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/distribution-mass>` v več vnosih hkrati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:3
msgid "Annual/Audit report"
msgstr "Letno poročilo/revizijsko poročilo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:5
msgid ""
"Annual reports document annual financial performance, operational "
"challenges, and organizational achievements for stakeholder review."
msgstr ""
"Letna poročila dokumentirajo letno finančno uspešnost, operativne izzive in "
"organizacijske dosežke za pregled deležnikov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:8
msgid ""
"Odoo :ref:`generates annual reports <accounting/annual-report/creation>` "
"from pre-configured templates. Users can :ref:`edit and customize "
"<accounting/annual-report/edit>` content, :ref:`add more content or upload "
"PDF files <accounting/annual-report/additional-content>`, and :ref:`export "
"the report as a PDF <accounting/annual-report/export>` for distribution."
msgstr ""
"Odoo :ref:`ustvari letna poročila <accounting/annual-report/creation>` iz "
"vnaprej pripravljenih predlog. Uporabniki lahko :ref:`urejajo in prilagajajo "
"<accounting/annual-report/edit>` vsebino, :ref:`dodajajo več vsebine ali "
"nalagajo datoteke PDF <accounting/annual-report/additional-content>` in "
":ref:`izvozijo poročilo kot PDF <accounting/annual-report/export>` za "
"distribucijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:14
msgid ""
"The annual report is edited using the :doc:`Knowledge app <../../../"
"productivity/knowledge>` interface from within the Accounting app."
msgstr ""
"Letno poročilo se ureja z vmesnikom :doc:`aplikacije Knowledge <../../../"
"productivity/knowledge>` iz aplikacije Accounting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:20
msgid "Create an annual report"
msgstr "Ustvarite letno poročilo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:22
msgid "To create an annual report, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za ustvarjanje letnega poročila sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:24
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> Annual Report` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> Annual Report` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:25
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Create an Annual Report` window, enter a :guilabel:`Title` "
"and, if necessary, update the start and end :guilabel:`Dates` of the period "
"covered by the report."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari letno poročilo` vnesite :guilabel:`Naslov` in po "
"potrebi posodobite začetni in končni :guilabel:`Datumi` obdobja, ki ga "
"zajema poročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:27
msgid ""
"Update the :guilabel:`Responsibles` field to let other users access and edit "
"the report, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Posodobite polje :guilabel:`Odgovorni`, da drugim uporabnikom po potrebi "
"omogočite dostop do poročila in njegovo urejanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:31
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Draft` annual report card is then created in "
"the :guilabel:`Annual Reports` Kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Kartica osnutka letnega poročila :guilabel:`Osnutek` je nato ustvarjena v "
"pogledu Kanban :guilabel:`Letna poročila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:35
msgid ""
"Clicking the card opens the annual report in the :ref:`editable view "
"<accounting/annual-report/edit>`."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na kartico se letno poročilo odpre v :ref:`pogledu za urejanje "
"<accounting/annual-report/edit>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:37
msgid ""
"The annual report is stored in the :doc:`Knowledge app <../../../"
"productivity/knowledge>`, under the :guilabel:`Private` category in the "
"sidebar tree, making the editable report visible only to its creator. If "
"additional users are added to the :guilabel:`Responsibles` field, the annual "
"report is then moved to the :guilabel:`Shared` category, allowing those "
"users to access it as well."
msgstr ""
"Letno poročilo je shranjeno v :doc:`aplikaciji Znanje <../../../productivity/"
"knowledge>`, pod kategorijo :guilabel:`Zasebno` v drevesu stranske vrstice, "
"kar omogoča, da je poročilo vidno samo njegovemu ustvarjalcu. Če so v polje "
":guilabel:`Odgovorni` dodani dodatni uporabniki, se letno poročilo premakne "
"v kategorijo :guilabel:`V skupni rabi`, kar omogoča dostop tudi tem "
"uporabnikom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:46
msgid "Edit an annual report"
msgstr "Urejanje letnega poročila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:49
msgid ""
"To modify the annual report's :guilabel:`Title`, :guilabel:`Dates`, "
"or :guilabel:`Responsibles`, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> "
"Annual Report`, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical "
"ellipsis)` icon of the annual report card, and select :guilabel:`Configure`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti :guilabel:`Naslov`, :guilabel:`Datume` ali "
":guilabel:`Odgovorne` letnega poročila, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Pregled --> Letno poročilo`, kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tri-pika)` na kartici "
"letnega poročila in izberite :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:53
msgid ""
"To edit the content of the annual report, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Review --> Annual Report`, then click on the annual report card to open it."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti vsebino letnega poročila, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Pregled --> Letno poročilo`, nato kliknite "
"na kartico letnega poročila, da ga odprete."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:56
msgid ""
"In the sidebar tree, hover over the new annual report and click "
"the :icon:`fa-caret-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` icon to the left of the "
"title to display the different sections. The detailed view appears in the "
"main editing area. Click any item in the sidebar or main view to open it for "
"editing:"
msgstr ""
"V drevesu stranske vrstice se pomaknite nad novo letno poročilo in kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-caret-right` :guilabel:`(puščica desno)` levo od naslova, da "
"prikažete različne razdelke. Podroben pogled se prikaže v glavnem področju "
"urejanja. Kliknite poljuben element v stranski vrstici ali glavnem pogledu, "
"da ga odprete za urejanje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:61
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Attestation`: Use the :icon:`fa-toggle-on` :guilabel:`(toggle-"
"on)` or :icon:`fa-toggle-off` :guilabel:`(toggle-off)` icons to show or hide "
"attestations, which contain dynamic text. Dates and company values are "
"automatically updated when the final PDF report is generated, which includes "
"only attestations with the toggle enabled."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Potrdilo`: Uporabite ikoni :icon:`fa-toggle-on` :guilabel:`(vklop-"
"preklop)` ali :icon:`fa-toggle-off` :guilabel:`(izklop-preklop)`, da "
"prikažete ali skrijete potrdila, ki vsebujejo dinamično besedilo. Datumi in "
"vrednosti podjetja se samodejno posodobijo, ko je ustvarjeno končno poročilo "
"PDF, ki vključuje samo potrdila z omogočenim preklopom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:67
msgid ""
"Attestations can be signed electronically by clicking :guilabel:`SIGNATURE`. "
"For users who have previously signed documents in Odoo, "
"click :guilabel:`Sign`. For first-time signers, :ref:`define a signature "
"<sign/sign-document/initials-signature>`, then click :guilabel:`Adopt & "
"Sign`."
msgstr ""
"Potrdila je mogoče elektronsko podpisati s klikom na :guilabel:`PODPIS`. Za "
"uporabnike, ki so že prej podpisali dokumente v Odoo, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Podpiši`. Za tiste, ki podpisujejo prvič, :ref:`določite podpis "
"<sign/sign-document/initials-signature>`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Sprejmi "
"in podpiši`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Balance Sheet`: Click :guilabel:`Customize` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Balance Sheet` and customize it using filters and options. "
"Any configurations performed are reflected in the :ref:`exported PDF report "
"<accounting/annual-report/export>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bilanca stanja`: Kliknite :guilabel:`Prilagodi`, da odprete "
":guilabel:`Bilanco stanja` in jo prilagodite s filtri in možnostmi. Vse "
"izvedene konfiguracije se odražajo v :ref:`izvoženem poročilu PDF "
"<accounting/annual-report/export>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:75
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Profit and Loss`: Click :guilabel:`Customize` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Profit and Loss` statement and customize it using filters and "
"options. Any configurations performed are reflected in the :ref:`exported "
"PDF report <accounting/annual-report/export>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izkaz poslovnega izida`: Kliknite :guilabel:`Prilagodi`, da "
"odprete :guilabel:`Izkaz poslovnega izida` in ga prilagodite s filtri in "
"možnostmi. Vse izvedene konfiguracije se odražajo v :ref:`izvoženem poročilu "
"PDF <accounting/annual-report/export>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Annexes`: Displays :ref:`additional items <accounting/annual-"
"report/additional-content>` included in the report."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Priloge`: Prikazuje :ref:`dodatne elemente <accounting/annual-"
"report/additional-content>`, vključene v poročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Supporting Documents`: Allows :ref:`uploaded PDF files "
"<accounting/annual-report/additional-content>` to be included in the report."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Spremna dokumentacija`: Omogoča, da so :ref:`naložene datoteke "
"PDF <accounting/annual-report/additional-content>` vključene v poročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:83
msgid ""
"To remove items from the annual report, drag and drop them into :icon:`fa-"
"trash` :guilabel:`Open the Trash` in the sidebar, or hover over the item in "
"the main view and click the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti elemente iz letnega poročila, jih povlecite in spustite "
"v :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Odpri koš` v stranski vrstici ali se pomaknite "
"nad element v glavnem pogledu in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`"
"(koš)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:88
msgid "Drag and drop items in the sidebar or main view to reorder them."
msgstr ""
"Povlecite in spustite elemente v stranski vrstici ali glavnem pogledu, da "
"jih prerazporedite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:89
msgid ""
"To create a new article, hover over a section in the sidebar and click "
"the :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon that appears next to it. The "
"article is then nested under the relevant section."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov članek, se pomaknite nad razdelek v stranski vrstici "
"in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)`, ki se prikaže ob njem. "
"Članek je nato umeščen pod ustrezen razdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:92
msgid ""
"To show or hide sub-articles, click :icon:`fa-sitemap` :guilabel:`Show sub-"
"articles` or :icon:`fa-sitemap` :guilabel:`Hide sub-articles` in the main "
"view."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati ali skriti podčlanke, kliknite :icon:`fa-sitemap` "
":guilabel:`Prikaži podčlanke` ali :icon:`fa-sitemap` :guilabel:`Skrij "
"podčlanke` v glavnem pogledu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:98
msgid "Additional content"
msgstr "Dodatna vsebina"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:100
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Annexes` section contains additional items, such as "
"customizable accounting reports, and articles with sections or tables to "
"complete. Review and delete any items that should not be included in the "
"final report."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek :guilabel:`Priloge` vsebuje dodatne elemente, kot so prilagodljiva "
"računovodska poročila in članki z razdelki ali tabelami za izpolnitev. "
"Preglejte in izbrišite vse elemente, ki ne bi smeli biti vključeni v končno "
"poročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:104
msgid ""
"To add additional annexes, click :guilabel:`Annexes` in the sidebar, then, "
"in the main view, choose one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati dodatne priloge, kliknite :guilabel:`Priloge` v stranski "
"vrstici, nato pa v glavnem pogledu izberite eno od naslednjih možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Load a Template`: Click to select extra items not included by "
"default. Complete the sections, disable the :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"on` :guilabel:`(toggle-on)` icons to hide unnecessary parts, and "
"click :guilabel:`Load Template`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Naloži predlogo`: Kliknite za izbiro dodatnih elementov, ki "
"privzeto niso vključeni. Izpolnite razdelke, onemogočite ikone :icon:`fa-"
"toggle-on` :guilabel:`(toggle-on)`, da skrijete nepotrebne dele, in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Naloži predlogo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add an Article`: Click to create a blank article to complete "
"manually."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodaj članek`: Kliknite za ustvarjanje praznega članka, ki ga "
"izpolnite ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:112
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Supporting Documents` section, click :guilabel:`Upload "
"files` to include additional PDF files in the annual report."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Spremljevalni dokumenti` kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži "
"datoteke`, da v letno poročilo vključite dodatne datoteke PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:118
msgid "Export an annual report"
msgstr "Izvoz letnega poročila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:120
msgid "To export the annual report as a PDF, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za izvoz letnega poročila v obliki PDF sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:122
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> Annual Report`, then click "
"on the annual report card to open it in the editable view."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Pregled --> Letno poročilo`, "
"nato kliknite na kartico letnega poročila, da jo odprete v uredljivem "
"pogledu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:124
msgid "Click on the upper-most level of the annual report in the sidebar tree."
msgstr "Kliknite na najvišjo raven letnega poročila v drevesu stranske vrstice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:125
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon in the "
"top-right corner and select :icon:`fa-file-pdf-o` :guilabel:`Download Annual "
"Report`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpično tri pike)` v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu in izberite :icon:`fa-file-pdf-o` :guilabel:`Prenesi "
"letno poročilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:127
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Download Annual Report` window, disable the :icon:`fa-"
"toggle-on` :guilabel:`(toggle-on)` icons to exclude sub-articles and PDF "
"files, if needed."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Prenesi letno poročilo` onemogočite ikone :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"on` :guilabel:`(toggle-on)`, da po potrebi izključite podčlanke in datoteke "
"PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:129
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Download PDF`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Prenesi PDF`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:131
msgid ""
"Alternatively, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> Annual "
"Report` and click :guilabel:`Print` on the annual report card. This option "
"includes sub-articles and uploaded PDF files by default."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da greste na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Pregled --> "
"Letno poročilo` in kliknete :guilabel:`Natisni` na kartici letnega poročila. "
"Ta možnost privzeto vključuje podčlanke in naložene datoteke PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:136
msgid ""
"The logo configured in the :ref:`company form <general/companies/company>` "
"is displayed on the cover page of the annual report."
msgstr ""
"Logotip, nastavljen v :ref:`obrazcu podjetja <general/companies/company>`, "
"je prikazan na naslovni strani letnega poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/annual-report.rst:139
msgid ""
"To mark an annual report as :guilabel:`Done` or to delete it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Review --> Annual Report`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the report "
"card, then select :guilabel:`Set to Done` or :guilabel:`Delete`, as "
"appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Če želite letno poročilo označiti kot :guilabel:`Dokončano` ali ga "
"izbrisati, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Pregled --> Letno "
"poročilo`, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpično tri "
"pike)` na kartici poročila, nato pa izberite :guilabel:`Nastavi na "
"dokončano` ali :guilabel:`Izbriši`, kot je primerno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:3
msgid "Budgets"
msgstr "Proračuni"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:5
msgid ""
":ref:`Analytic budgets <accounting/budgets/analytic-budgets>` track specific "
"activities and projects using analytic accounts, helping businesses make "
"informed decisions about specific departments, projects, or other groups of "
"transactions. In contrast, :ref:`financial budgets <accounting/budgets/"
"financial>` are tied to the general ledger accounts that appear on the "
"profit and loss and focus on the company's overall economic position."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Analitični proračuni <accounting/budgets/analytic-budgets>` sledijo "
"določenim dejavnostim in projektom z uporabo analitičnih kontov ter "
"podjetjem pomagajo sprejemati premišljene odločitve o določenih oddelkih, "
"projektih ali drugih skupinah transakcij. Nasprotno pa so :ref:`finančni "
"proračuni <accounting/budgets/financial>` vezani na konte glavne knjige, ki "
"se pojavljajo v izkazu poslovnega izida, in se osredotočajo na splošni "
"ekonomski položaj podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:14
msgid "Analytic budgets"
msgstr "Analitični proračuni"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:16
msgid ""
"Analytic budgets allow for allocating and tracking income and expenses in "
"detail, breaking down costs and revenues by specific projects, departments, "
"or groups of transactions. Analytic budgets can be applied across various "
"departments or projects to measure profitability and performance. Odoo "
"manages analytic budgets using :doc:`analytic accounting "
"<analytic_accounting>`."
msgstr ""
"Analitični proračuni omogočajo podrobno dodeljevanje in sledenje prihodkov "
"ter odhodkov, s čimer se stroški in prihodki razčlenijo po določenih "
"projektih, oddelkih ali skupinah transakcij. Analitične proračune je mogoče "
"uporabiti v različnih oddelkih ali projektih za merjenje donosnosti in "
"učinkovitosti. Odoo upravlja analitične proračune z uporabo "
":doc:`analitičnega računovodstva <analytic_accounting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:21
msgid ""
"To activate the option for creating analytic budgets, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Budget Management` in the :guilabel:`Analytics` section."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati možnost za ustvarjanje analitičnih proračunov, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Analitika` omogočite :guilabel:`Upravljanje proračunov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:26
msgid ""
"Odoo structures budgets using :ref:`plans <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic_plans>` and :ref:`accounts <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic_accounts>`, which must be configured *before* creating a budget."
msgstr ""
"Odoo strukturira proračune z uporabo :ref:`planov <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` in :ref:`kontov <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`, ki jih je treba nastaviti *pred* "
"ustvarjanjem proračuna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:33
msgid "Set an analytic budget"
msgstr "Nastavitev analitičnega proračuna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:35
msgid ""
"To create a new budget, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> "
"Analytic Budgets` and click :guilabel:`New`. Make sure the following fields "
"are appropriately completed: :guilabel:`Budget Name`, :guilabel:`Period`, "
"and :guilabel:`Budget Type`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov proračun, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Analitični proračuni` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Preverite, da so ustrezno izpolnjena naslednja "
"polja: :guilabel:`Ime proračuna`, :guilabel:`Obdobje` in :guilabel:`Vrsta "
"proračuna`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:39
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Budget Lines` tab to "
"structure the budget with the :ref:`analytic plans <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` and :ref:`accounts <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` previously created. While "
"the :ref:`analytic plans <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` "
"correspond to the column names, select the :ref:`analytic accounts "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>` to define the budget "
"lines and set the amounts for each in the :guilabel:`Budgeted` column. Once "
"all the budget lines are settled, click :guilabel:`Open`. If changes need to "
"be made once the budget's status is :guilabel:`Open`, there are two options:"
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Vrstice proračuna` kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, "
"da strukturirate proračun s prej ustvarjenimi :ref:`analitičnimi plani "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` in :ref:`konti <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`. Medtem ko :ref:`analitični plani "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_plans>` ustrezajo imenom stolpcev, "
"izberite :ref:`analitične konte <accounting/analytic_accounting/"
"analytic_accounts>`, da določite vrstice proračuna in nastavite zneske za "
"vsakega v stolpcu :guilabel:`Proračun`. Ko so vse vrstice proračuna "
"določene, kliknite :guilabel:`Odpri`. Če je treba po tem, ko je status "
"proračuna :guilabel:`Odprto`, vnesti spremembe, sta na voljo dve možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reset to Draft`: To overwrite the data, then reopen the budget."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ponastavi na osnutek`: za prepisovanje podatkov in nato ponovno "
"odprite proračun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Revise`: A new budget will be created. Once it "
"is :guilabel:`Open`, a :guilabel:`Rev` reference is added to "
"the :guilabel:`Budget Name`. The original budget is then :guilabel:`Revised`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Revidiraj`: Ustvarjen bo nov proračun. Ko je :guilabel:`Odprto`, "
"se k :guilabel:`Ime proračuna` doda sklic :guilabel:`Rev`. Izvirni proračun "
"je nato :guilabel:`Revidiran`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:56
msgid "Check an analytic budget"
msgstr "Preverjanje analitičnega proračuna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:58
msgid ""
"Once the budget is :guilabel:`Open`, two additional columns are "
"available: :guilabel:`Committed` and :guilabel:`Achieved`. These columns' "
"amounts are automatically calculated based on the related :ref:`analytic "
"distribution <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` of "
"journal items. When the :ref:`analytic distribution <accounting/"
"analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` of a journal item within the "
"budget's period is updated, the budget's columns for the analytic account(s) "
"selected in the distribution are automatically updated. "
"The :guilabel:`Achieved` amount reflects the current result according to the "
"items of confirmed journal entries for the associated :ref:`analytic account "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`. In contrast, "
"the :guilabel:`Committed` amount displays the full value of "
"the :guilabel:`Achieved` amount, plus any confirmed purchase orders that "
"have not yet been billed."
msgstr ""
"Ko je proračun :guilabel:`Odprto`, sta na voljo dva dodatna stolpca: "
":guilabel:`Obvezano` in :guilabel:`Doseženo`. Zneski v teh stolpcih se "
"samodejno izračunajo na podlagi povezane :ref:`analitične porazdelitve "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-distribution>` postavk dnevnika. Ko "
"se :ref:`analitična porazdelitev <accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic-"
"distribution>` postavke dnevnika v obdobju proračuna posodobi, se stolpci "
"proračuna za analitični(-e) konto(-e), izbrane v porazdelitvi, samodejno "
"posodobijo. Znesek :guilabel:`Doseženo` odraža trenutni rezultat glede na "
"postavke potrjenih vnosov v dnevnik za povezani :ref:`Analitični konto "
"<accounting/analytic_accounting/analytic_accounts>`. Nasprotno pa znesek "
":guilabel:`Obvezano` prikazuje celotno vrednost zneska :guilabel:`Doseženo` "
"ter morebitna potrjena naročila za nakup, ki še niso bila fakturirana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:70
msgid ""
"When a line in a request for quotation or purchase order includes an "
"analytic distribution, a :guilabel:`Budget` smart button appears, providing "
"a link to the :ref:`budget report <accounting/budgets/analytic-budget-"
"reporting>` for more details."
msgstr ""
"Ko vrstica v zahtevku za ponudbo ali naročilu za nakup vključuje analitično "
"porazdelitev, se prikaže pametni gumb :guilabel:`Proračun`, ki omogoča "
"povezavo do :ref:`poročila o proračunu <accounting/budgets/analytic-budget-"
"reporting>` za več podrobnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:73
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Open` budgets, if a request for quotation or a purchase order "
"is created using the associated analytic distribution and exceeds the "
"allocated budget amount, the corresponding purchase order line is "
"highlighted in red."
msgstr ""
"Za :guilabel:`Odprte` proračune, če je zahtevek za ponudbo ali naročilo za "
"nakup ustvarjeno z uporabo povezane analitične porazdelitve in presega "
"dodeljeni znesek proračuna, je ustrezna vrstica naročila za nakup označena "
"rdeče."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:77
msgid ""
"To reveal the :guilabel:`Theoretical` amount or percentage, use "
"the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`adjust settings`) icon in "
"the :guilabel:`Budget Lines`' header. The :guilabel:`Theoretical` amount "
"represents the amount of money that could theoretically have been spent or "
"should have been received based on the current date relative to the start/"
"end dates. Click :guilabel:`Details` to open a filtered view of "
"the :ref:`budget report <accounting/budgets/analytic-budget-reporting>` "
"related to that specific budget line."
msgstr ""
"Če želite razkriti znesek ali odstotek :guilabel:`Teoretično`, uporabite "
"ikono :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` (:guilabel:`prilagodi nastavitve`) v glavi "
":guilabel:`Vrstice proračuna`. Znesek :guilabel:`Teoretično` predstavlja "
"znesek denarja, ki bi ga bilo teoretično mogoče potrošiti ali bi ga bilo "
"treba prejeti na podlagi trenutnega datuma glede na začetni/končni datum. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Podrobnosti`, da odprete filtriran pogled :ref:`poročila "
"o proračunu <accounting/budgets/analytic-budget-reporting>`, povezanega s to "
"določeno vrstico proračuna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:None
msgid "open budget with committed, achieved, and theoretical amounts"
msgstr "odprt proračun z obvezanimi, doseženimi in teoretičnimi zneski"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:88
msgid ""
"Deleting a budget is only allowed in the :guilabel:`Draft` "
"and :guilabel:`Cancelled` stages."
msgstr ""
"Brisanje proračuna je dovoljeno samo v fazah :guilabel:`Osnutek` in "
":guilabel:`Preklicano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:90
msgid ""
"To view the budget lines of one or multiple budgets directly from "
"the :guilabel:`Budgets` list view, select the budget(s) and "
"click :guilabel:`Budget Lines`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vrstice proračuna enega ali več proračunov prikazati neposredno iz "
"seznama :guilabel:`Proračuni`, izberite proračun(-e) in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Vrstice proračuna`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:96
msgid "Generate periodic budgets"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje periodičnih proračunov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:98
msgid ""
"To create periodic budgets (monthly, quarterly, and yearly) for the "
"selected :guilabel:`Analytic Plans`, click :guilabel:`Generate`. A new "
"budget is created for each :guilabel:`Period` between the start and end "
"dates:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti periodične proračune (mesečne, četrtletne in letne) za "
"izbrane :guilabel:`Analitične plane`, kliknite :guilabel:`Generiraj`. Nov "
"proračun se ustvari za vsako :guilabel:`Obdobje` med začetnim in končnim "
"datumom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:102
msgid ""
"If a single analytic plan is selected, each budget includes a line for each "
"account in that analytic plan."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbran en sam analitični načrt, vsak proračun vključuje vrstico za "
"vsak konto v tem analitičnem načrtu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:104
msgid ""
"If multiple analytic plans are selected, each budget includes a line for "
"each account/analytic plan combination."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbranih več analitičnih načrtov, vsak proračun vključuje vrstico za "
"vsako kombinacijo konta/analitičnega načrta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:107
msgid "To generate periodic budgets, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za generiranje periodičnih proračunov sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:109
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Budgets` list view, click :guilabel:`Generate`."
msgstr ""
"V seznamskem pogledu :guilabel:`Proračuni` kliknite :guilabel:`Generiraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:110
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Generate Budget` window, set the dates and select "
"the :guilabel:`Period` and the :guilabel:`Analytic Plans`."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Generiraj proračun` nastavite datume in izberite "
":guilabel:`Obdobje` ter :guilabel:`Analitične načrte`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:0
msgid "all the options to generate periodical budgets"
msgstr "vse možnosti za generiranje periodičnih proračunov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:116
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Split` to create the periodic budgets."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Razdeli`, da ustvarite periodične proračune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:117
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Budgets` in the top-left corner to return to "
"the :guilabel:`Budgets` list view."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Proračuni` v zgornjem levem kotu, da se vrnete na "
"seznamski pogled :guilabel:`Proračuni`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:118
msgid ""
"One by one, click on the different periodic budgets with "
"the :guilabel:`Draft` status to open them and set the amounts in "
"the :guilabel:`Budgeted` column for each analytic account linked to the "
"chosen analytic plans."
msgstr ""
"Enega za drugim kliknite na različne periodične proračune s statusom "
":guilabel:`Osnutek`, da jih odprete, in nastavite zneske v stolpcu "
":guilabel:`Proračunsko` za vsak analitični konto, povezan z izbranimi "
"analitičnimi načrti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:121
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Open` for each periodic budget."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Odpri` za vsak periodični proračun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:128
msgid ""
"To perform various reporting actions, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Budget Report`, then:"
msgstr ""
"Za izvajanje različnih poročevalskih dejanj pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Poročilo o proračunu`, nato:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:131
msgid "Track, analyze, and compare budget data."
msgstr "Sledite, analizirajte in primerjajte podatke o proračunu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:132
msgid ""
"Filter and group data using the :icon:`fa-plus-square` (:guilabel:`plus-"
"square`) or :icon:`fa-minus-square` :guilabel:`(minus-square)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Filtrirajte in združujte podatke s pomočjo ikone :icon:`fa-plus-square` "
"(:guilabel:`plus-square`) ali :icon:`fa-minus-square` :guilabel:`(minus-"
"square)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:134
msgid ""
"Drill down into the report to see more details on the actual amounts and "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Poglobite se v poročilo, da si ogledate več podrobnosti o dejanskih zneskih "
"in transakcijah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:135
msgid "Export the data for further analysis or reporting needs."
msgstr "Izvozite podatke za nadaljnjo analizo ali potrebe po poročanju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:140
msgid "Financial budgets"
msgstr "Finančni proračuni"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:142
msgid ""
"Financial budgets are structured around specific income and expense accounts "
"and transactions for official financial reporting and compliance purposes."
msgstr ""
"Finančni proračuni so strukturirani okoli določenih kontov prihodkov in "
"odhodkov ter transakcij za namene uradnega finančnega poročanja in "
"skladnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:146
msgid ""
"Financial budgets are available on the :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/"
"reporting/profit-and-loss>` report."
msgstr ""
"Finančni proračuni so na voljo v poročilu :ref:`Izkaz poslovnega izida "
"<accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:152
msgid "Set a financial budget"
msgstr "Nastavitev finančnega proračuna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:154
msgid "To create a new financial budget, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za ustvarjanje novega finančnega proračuna sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:156
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Profit and Loss` to open "
"the :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>` report."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Profit and Loss`, da "
"odprete poročilo :ref:`Profit and Loss <accounting/reporting/profit-and-loss>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:158
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)` button to use the date "
"selector and choose a period."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)`, da uporabite "
"izbirnik datuma in izberete obdobje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:160
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`Budget` button and name the "
"budget. A new column labeled with the budget name will appear next to "
"the :guilabel:`Balance` column."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`Budget` in poimenujte "
"proračun. Poleg stolpca :guilabel:`Balance` se bo prikazal nov stolpec z "
"imenom proračuna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:162
msgid "Assign amounts to each account requiring analysis."
msgstr "Dodelite zneske vsakemu računu, ki zahteva analizo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:163
msgid ""
"A new :guilabel:`%` column will appear to the right of the new budget "
"column, indicating the current status."
msgstr ""
"Na desni strani novega stolpca proračuna se bo prikazal nov stolpec "
":guilabel:`%`, ki označuje trenutno stanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:166
msgid ""
"Different financial budgets can be created using these steps for comparison "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
"Za primerjavo je mogoče ustvariti različne finančne proračune z uporabo teh "
"korakov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/budget.rst:169
msgid ""
"The date selector enables the division of periods and navigation between "
"periods, automatically updating the amounts accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Izbirnik datuma omogoča delitev obdobij in navigacijo med obdobji, pri čemer "
"se zneski samodejno ustrezno posodobijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:3
msgid "Custom reports"
msgstr "Poročilo po meri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo comes with a powerful and easy-to-use reporting framework. The engine "
"allows you to create new reports, such as tax reports, balance sheets, and "
"income statements with specific groupings and layouts."
msgstr ""
"Odoo je opremljen z zmogljivim in enostavnim ogrodjem za poročanje. "
"Mehanizem omogoča ustvarjanje novih poročil, kot so davčna poročila, bilance "
"stanja in izkazi poslovnega izida s specifičnimi združevanji in "
"razporeditvami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:10
msgid ""
"Activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` to access the accounting "
"report configuration."
msgstr ""
"Aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>`, da dostopate do "
"konfiguracije računovodskih poročil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:13
msgid ""
"To create a new report, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Accounting Reports`. From here, create either a :ref:`root report "
"<customize-reports/root>` or a :ref:`variant <customize-reports/variants>`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje novega poročila pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Računovodska poročila`. Od tu ustvarite bodisi "
":ref:`korensko poročilo <customize-reports/root>` bodisi :ref:`različico "
"<customize-reports/variants>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:18
msgid ""
"Consider saving modified reports as report variants to keep their root "
"reports intact."
msgstr ""
"Razmislite o shranjevanju spremenjenih poročil kot različic poročil, da "
"ohranite njihova korenska poročila nedotaknjena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:19
msgid ""
"To access an existing report's management interface from the report itself, "
"click on the :icon:`fa-cogs` :guilabel:`(gears)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do vmesnika za upravljanje obstoječega poročila iz samega poročila "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cogs` :guilabel:`(zobniki)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:25
msgid "Root reports"
msgstr "Korenska poročila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:27
msgid ""
"Root reports can be regarded as generic, neutral accounting reports. They "
"serve as models on which local accounting versions are built. If a report "
"has no root report, it is considered to be a root report itself."
msgstr ""
"Korenska poročila je mogoče obravnavati kot generična, nevtralna "
"računovodska poročila. Služijo kot modeli, na katerih so zgrajene lokalne "
"računovodske različice. Če poročilo nima korenskega poročila, se šteje, da "
"je samo korensko poročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:32
msgid ""
"A tax report for Belgium and the US would both use the same generic version "
"as a base and adapt it for their domestic regulations."
msgstr ""
"Davčno poročilo za Belgijo in ZDA bi obe uporabljali isto generično "
"različico kot osnovo in jo prilagodili svojim domačim predpisom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:35
msgid ""
"Creating a menu item is required to access a new root report. To do so, open "
"the report's configuration, click :guilabel:`Action`, :guilabel:`Create Menu "
"Item`, and refresh the page. The report is now available "
"under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do novega korenskega poročila je potrebno ustvariti element "
"menija. To storite tako, da odprete konfiguracijo poročila, kliknete "
":guilabel:`Dejanje`, :guilabel:`Ustvari element menija` in osvežite stran. "
"Poročilo je zdaj na voljo pod :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:40
msgid ""
"Cases that require creating a new root report are rare, such as when a "
"country's tax authorities require a new and specific type of report."
msgstr ""
"Primeri, ki zahtevajo ustvarjanje novega korenskega poročila, so redki, na "
"primer ko davčni organi države zahtevajo novo in specifično vrsto poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:46
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:142
msgid "Variants"
msgstr "Različice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:48
msgid ""
"Variants are country-specific versions of root reports and, therefore, "
"always refer to a root report. To create a variant, select a generic (root) "
"report in the :guilabel:`Root Report` field when creating a new report."
msgstr ""
"Različice so državno specifične različice korenskih poročil in se zato vedno "
"sklicujejo na korensko poročilo. Za ustvarjanje različice izberite generično "
"(korensko) poročilo v polju :guilabel:`Korensko poročilo` pri ustvarjanju "
"novega poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:52
msgid ""
"When a root report is opened from the Accounting app's :guilabel:`Reporting` "
"menu, all of its variants are displayed in the report variant selector in "
"the top right corner of the view."
msgstr ""
"Ko je korensko poročilo odprto iz menija :guilabel:`Poročanje` aplikacije "
"Računovodstvo, so vse njegove različice prikazane v izbirniku različic "
"poročila v zgornjem desnem kotu pogleda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`VAT Report (BE)` is a variant of the root :guilabel:`Generic Tax "
"report`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`VAT Report (BE)` je različica korenske :guilabel:`Generic Tax "
"report`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "Report variant selection."
msgstr "Izbira različice poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:64
msgid "Lines"
msgstr "Vrstice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:66
msgid ""
"After creating a report (either root or variant), the next step is to fill "
"it with lines. To create a new line, click on :guilabel:`Add a line`. To "
"modify an existing line, click on the line itself and edit the popup. All "
"lines require a :guilabel:`Name` and can have an optional :guilabel:`Code` "
"which allows using the line's value in formulas."
msgstr ""
"Po ustvarjanju poročila (bodisi korenskega bodisi različice) je naslednji "
"korak zapolnitev z vrsticami. Za ustvarjanje nove vrstice kliknite na "
":guilabel:`Add a line`. Za urejanje obstoječe vrstice kliknite na samo "
"vrstico in uredite pojavno okno. Vse vrstice zahtevajo :guilabel:`Name` in "
"lahko imajo neobvezno :guilabel:`Code`, ki omogoča uporabo vrednosti vrstice "
"v formulah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:None
msgid "Engine lines options."
msgstr "Možnosti vrstic motorja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:75
msgid "Expressions"
msgstr "Izrazi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:77
msgid ""
"Each line can contain one or multiple **expressions**. Expressions can be "
"seen as **sub-variables** needed by a report line. To create an expression, "
"click on :guilabel:`Add a line` *within* a line's popup."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka vrstica lahko vsebuje enega ali več **izrazov**. Izraze je mogoče "
"razumeti kot **pod-spremenljivke**, ki jih potrebuje vrstica poročila. Za "
"ustvarjanje izraza kliknite na :guilabel:`Add a line` *znotraj* pojavnega "
"okna vrstice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:81
msgid ""
"When creating an expression, you must enter a :guilabel:`Label` used to "
"refer to that expression. The label must be unique among the expressions of "
"each report line. Both the :guilabel:`Computation Engine` and "
"the :guilabel:`Formula` fields must also be completed. The **computation "
"engine** defines how the **formula(s)** and **subformula(s)** are "
"interpreted. It is possible to mix expressions using different computation "
"engines under the same line if needed."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju izraza morate vnesti :guilabel:`Label`, ki se uporablja za "
"sklicevanje na ta izraz. Oznaka mora biti edinstvena med izrazi vsake "
"vrstice poročila. Izpolniti je treba tudi polja :guilabel:`Computation "
"Engine` in :guilabel:`Formula`. **Računski motor** določa, kako se **formula"
"(e)** in **podformula(e)** interpretirajo. Po potrebi je mogoče pod isto "
"vrstico združiti izraze, ki uporabljajo različne računske motorje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:88
msgid "Depending on the engine, :guilabel:`subformulas` may also be required."
msgstr "Odvisno od motorja so lahko potrebne tudi :guilabel:`subformulas`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:91
msgid "Odoo Domain computation engine"
msgstr "Računski motor Odoo Domain"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:93
msgid ""
"When using the :guilabel:`Odoo Domain` computation engine, a formula is "
"interpreted as an :ref:`Odoo domain <reference/orm/domains>` targeting "
"`account.move.line` objects."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi računskega motorja :guilabel:`Odoo Domain` se formula "
"interpretira kot :ref:`Odoo domain <reference/orm/domains>`, ki cilja na "
"objekte `account.move.line`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:96
msgid ""
"The subformula allows you to define how the move lines matching the domain "
"are used to compute the value of the expression:"
msgstr ""
"Podformula vam omogoča opredelitev načina, kako se vrstice premikov, ki se "
"ujemajo z domeno, uporabljajo za izračun vrednosti izraza:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:100
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:266
msgid "`sum`"
msgstr "`sum`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:100
msgid "The result is the sum of all the balances of the matched move lines."
msgstr "Rezultat je vsota vseh sald ujemajočih se vrstic premikov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:104
msgid "`sum_if_pos`"
msgstr "`sum_if_pos`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:103
msgid ""
"The result is the sum of all the balances of the matched move lines if this "
"amount is positive. Otherwise, it is `0`."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat je vsota vseh sald ujemajočih se vrstic premikov, če je ta znesek "
"pozitiven. V nasprotnem primeru je `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:108
msgid "`sum_if_neg`"
msgstr "`sum_if_neg`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:107
msgid ""
"The result is the sum of all the balances of the matched move lines if this "
"amount is negative. Otherwise, it is `0`."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat je vsota vseh sald ujemajočih se vrstic premikov, če je ta znesek "
"negativen. V nasprotnem primeru je `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:113
msgid "`count_rows`"
msgstr "`count_rows`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:111
msgid ""
"The result is the number of sub-lines of this expression. If the parent line "
"has a :ref:`group-by <customize-reports/lines-group-by>` value, this will "
"correspond to the number of distinct grouping keys in the matched move "
"lines. Otherwise, it will be the number of matched move lines."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat je število podvrstic tega izraza. Če ima nadrejena vrstica vrednost "
":ref:`group-by <customize-reports/lines-group-by>`, bo to ustrezalo številu "
"različnih ključev združevanja v ujemajočih se vrsticah premikov. V "
"nasprotnem primeru bo to število ujemajočih se vrstic premikov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:116
msgid ""
"To **reverse** the sign of the result, put a `-` sign at the beginning of "
"the subformula."
msgstr ""
"Za **obrnitev** predznaka rezultata postavite znak `-` na začetek podformule."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:None
msgid "Expression line within a line report"
msgstr "Vrstica izraza znotraj vrstice poročila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:122
msgid "Tax Tags computation engine"
msgstr "Računski mehanizem davčnih oznak"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:124
msgid ""
"When using the :guilabel:`Tax Tags` computation engine, the contents of "
"the :guilabel:`Formula` field are matched to tax tags. If such tags do not "
"exist when creating the expression, they will be created."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi računskega mehanizma :guilabel:`Davčne oznake` se vsebina polja "
":guilabel:`Formula` ujema z davčnimi oznakami. Če takšne oznake ob "
"ustvarjanju izraza ne obstajajo, bodo ustvarjene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:128
msgid ""
"When evaluating the expression, the expression computation can roughly be "
"expressed as: **(amount of the move lines with** `+` **tag)** `-` **(amount "
"of the move lines with** `-` **tag)**."
msgstr ""
"Pri vrednotenju izraza lahko izračun izraza približno izrazimo kot: **"
"(znesek vrstic premika z oznako** `+`)** `-` **(znesek vrstic premika z "
"oznako** `-`)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:132
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Formula` is set to `tag_name`, the engine matches tax tags "
"`+tag_name` and `-tag_name`, creating them if necessary. To exemplify "
"further: two tags are matched by the formula. If the formula is `A`, it will "
"require (and create, if needed) tags `+A` and `-A`."
msgstr ""
"Če je :guilabel:`Formula` nastavljena na `ime_oznake`, mehanizem ujema "
"davčni oznaki `+ime_oznake` in `-ime_oznake` ter ju po potrebi ustvari. "
"Dodatno pojasnilo: formula ujema dve oznaki. Če je formula `A`, bo zahtevala "
"(in po potrebi ustvarila) oznaki `+A` in `-A`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:137
msgid "Aggregate Other Formulas computation engine"
msgstr "Računski mehanizem za združevanje drugih formul"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:139
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Aggregate Other Formulas` computation engine performs "
"arithmetic operations on the amounts obtained from other expressions. "
"Formulas here are composed of references to expressions separated by one of "
"the four basic arithmetic operators (addition `+`, subtraction `-`, division "
"`/`, and multiplication `*`). To refer to an expression, type in its parent "
"line's **code** followed by a period `.` and the expression's **label** (ex. "
"**code.label**)."
msgstr ""
"Računski mehanizem :guilabel:`Združi druge formule` izvaja aritmetične "
"operacije na zneskih, pridobljenih iz drugih izrazov. Formule so tu "
"sestavljene iz sklicevanj na izraze, ločene z enim od štirih osnovnih "
"aritmetičnih operatorjev (seštevanje `+`, odštevanje `-`, deljenje `/` in "
"množenje `*`). Za sklicevanje na izraz vnesite **kodo** nadrejene vrstice, "
"ki ji sledi pika `.`, in **oznako** izraza (npr. **koda.oznaka**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:145
msgid "**Subformulas** can be one of the following:"
msgstr "**Podformule** so lahko ene izmed naslednjih:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:149
msgid "`if_above(CUR(amount))`"
msgstr "`if_above(VAL(znesek))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:148
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if it is "
"greater than the provided bound. Otherwise, the result will be `0`."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost aritmetičnega izraza bo vrnjena le, če je večja od podane meje. V "
"nasprotnem primeru bo rezultat `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:153
msgid "`if_below(CUR(amount))`"
msgstr "`if_below(VAL(znesek))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:152
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if it is lower "
"than the provided bound. Otherwise, the result will be `0`."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost aritmetičnega izraza bo vrnjena le, če je nižja od podane meje. V "
"nasprotnem primeru bo rezultat `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:157
msgid "`if_between(CUR1(amount1), CUR2(amount2))`"
msgstr "`if_between(VAL1(znesek1), VAL2(znesek2))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:156
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if it is "
"strictly between the provided bounds. Otherwise, it will be brought back to "
"the closest bound."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost aritmetičnega izraza bo vrnjena le, če je strogo med podanima "
"mejama. V nasprotnem primeru bo premaknjena na najbližjo mejo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:162
msgid "`if_other_expr_above(LINE_CODE.EXPRESSION_LABEL, CUR(amount))`"
msgstr "`if_other_expr_above(KODA_VRSTICE.OZNAKA_IZRAZA, VAL(znesek))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:160
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if the value of "
"the expression denoted by the provided line code and expression label is "
"greater than the provided bound. Otherwise, the result will be `0`."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost aritmetičnega izraza bo vrnjena le, če je vrednost izraza, "
"označenega s podano kodo vrstice in oznako izraza, večja od podane meje. V "
"nasprotnem primeru bo rezultat `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:167
msgid "`if_other_expr_below(LINE_CODE.EXPRESSION_LABEL, CUR(amount))`"
msgstr "`if_other_expr_below(KODA_VRSTICE.OZNAKA_IZRAZA, VAL(znesek))`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:165
msgid ""
"The value of the arithmetic expression will be returned only if the value of "
"the expression denoted by the provided line code and expression label is "
"lower than the provided bound. Otherwise, the result will be `0`."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost aritmetičnega izraza bo vrnjena le, če je vrednost izraza, "
"označenega s podano kodo vrstice in oznako izraza, nižja od podane meje. V "
"nasprotnem primeru bo rezultat `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:169
msgid ""
"`CUR` is the currency code in capital letters, and `amount` is the amount of "
"the bound expressed in that currency."
msgstr ""
"`VAL` je koda valute z velikimi črkami, `znesek` pa je znesek meje, izražen "
"v tej valuti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:173
msgid "`cross_report(xml_id | report_id)`"
msgstr "`cross_report(xml_id | id_poročila)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:173
msgid ""
"Used to match an expression from another report targeted by the xml_id or "
"the report ID itself."
msgstr ""
"Uporablja se za ujemanje izraza iz drugega poročila, določenega z xml_id ali "
"samim ID-jem poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:176
msgid "Prefix of Account Codes computation engine"
msgstr "Motor za izračun predpon kod računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:178
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Prefix of Account Codes` computation engine is used to match "
"amounts made on accounts using the prefixes of these accounts' codes as "
"variables in an arithmetic expression."
msgstr ""
"Motor za izračun :guilabel:`Predpon kod računov` se uporablja za ujemanje "
"zneskov na računih z uporabo predpon kod teh računov kot spremenljivk v "
"aritmetičnem izrazu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21`"
msgstr "`21`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "Arithmetic expressions can also be a single prefix, such as here."
msgstr "Aritmetični izrazi so lahko tudi samo ena predpona, kot tukaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21 + 10 - 5`"
msgstr "`21 + 10 - 5`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula adds the balances of the move lines made on accounts whose "
"codes start with `21` and `10`, and subtracts the balance of the ones on "
"accounts with the prefix `5`."
msgstr ""
"Ta formula sešteje salda postavk knjiženja na računih, katerih kode se "
"začnejo z `21` in `10`, ter odšteje saldo tistih na računih s predpono `5`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:190
msgid "It is also possible to ignore a selection of sub-prefixes."
msgstr "Mogoče je tudi prezreti izbor pod-predpon."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21 + 10\\\\(101, 102) - 5\\\\(57)`"
msgstr "`21 + 10\\\\(101, 102) - 5\\\\(57)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula works the same way as the previous example but ignores the "
"prefixes `101`, `102`, and `57`."
msgstr ""
"Ta formula deluje enako kot prejšnji primer, vendar prezre predpone `101`, "
"`102` in `57`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:197
msgid ""
"You can apply 'sub-filtering' on **credits and debits** using the `C` and "
"`D` suffixes. In this case, an account will only be considered if its prefix "
"matches, *and* if the total balance of the move lines made on this account "
"is **credit/debit**."
msgstr ""
"Na **dobropise in bremena** lahko uporabite 'pod-filtriranje' z uporabo "
"pripon `C` in `D`. V tem primeru bo račun upoštevan le, če se njegova "
"predpona ujema *in* če je skupni saldo postavk knjiženja na tem računu "
"**dobropis/breme**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:202
msgid ""
"Account `210001` has a balance of -42 and account `210002` has a balance of "
"25. The formula `21D` only matches the account `210002`, and hence returns "
"25. `210001` is not matched, as its balance is *credit*."
msgstr ""
"Račun `210001` ima saldo -42 in račun `210002` ima saldo 25. Formula `21D` "
"se ujema le z računom `210002` in zato vrne 25. `210001` se ne ujema, ker je "
"njegov saldo *dobropis*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:206
msgid "Prefix exclusions can be mixed with the `C` and `D` suffixes."
msgstr "Izključitve predpon je mogoče mešati s priponama `C` in `D`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21D + 10\\\\(101, 102)C - 5\\\\(57)`"
msgstr "`21D + 10\\\\(101, 102)C - 5\\\\(57)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula adds the balances of the move lines made on accounts whose code "
"starts with `21` *if* it is debit (`D`) and `10` *if* it is credit (`C`), "
"but ignores prefixes `101`, `102`, and subtracts the balance of the ones on "
"accounts with the prefix `5`, ignoring the prefix `57`."
msgstr ""
"Ta formula sešteje salda postavk knjiženja na računih, katerih koda se začne "
"z `21`, *če* je breme (`D`), in `10`, *če* je dobropis (`C`), vendar prezre "
"predpone `101`, `102`, ter odšteje saldo tistih na računih s predpono `5`, "
"pri čemer prezre predpono `57`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:214
msgid ""
"To match the letter `C` or `D` in a prefix and not use it as a suffix, use "
"an empty exclusion `()`."
msgstr ""
"Za ujemanje črke `C` ali `D` v predponi brez uporabe kot pripona uporabite "
"prazno izključitev `()`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`21D\\\\()`"
msgstr "`21D\\\\()`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts whose code starts with `21D`, regardless of "
"their balance sign."
msgstr ""
"Ta formula se ujema z računi, katerih koda se začne z `21D`, ne glede na "
"predznak njihovega salda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:220
msgid ""
"In addition to using code prefixes to include accounts, you can also match "
"them with **account tags**. This is especially useful, for example, if your "
"country lacks a standardized chart of accounts, where the same prefix might "
"be used for different purposes across companies."
msgstr ""
"Poleg uporabe predpon kod za vključitev računov jih lahko ujemete tudi z "
"**oznakami računov**. To je še posebej uporabno, na primer, če vaša država "
"nima standardiziranega kontnega načrta, kjer se lahko ista predpona "
"uporablja za različne namene v različnih podjetjih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(25)`"
msgstr "`tag(25)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts whose associated tags contain the one with ID "
"*25*."
msgstr ""
"Ta formula se ujema z računi, katerih povezane oznake vsebujejo tisto z ID-"
"jem *25*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:228
msgid ""
"If the tag you reference is defined in a data file, an XMLID can be used "
"instead of the ID."
msgstr ""
"Če je značka, na katero se sklicujete, definirana v podatkovni datoteki, "
"lahko namesto ID uporabite XMLID."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(my_module.my_tag)`"
msgstr "`tag(my_module.my_tag)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts whose associated tags include the tag denoted "
"by *my_module.my_tag*."
msgstr ""
"Ta formula se ujema s konti, katerih povezane značke vključujejo značko, "
"označeno z *my_module.my_tag*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:235
msgid ""
"You can also use arithmetic expressions with tags, possibly combining them "
"with prefix selections."
msgstr ""
"Lahko uporabite tudi aritmetične izraze z značkami, po možnosti jih "
"kombinirate z izbirami predpon."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(my_module.my_tag) + tag(42) + 10`"
msgstr "`tag(my_module.my_tag) + tag(42) + 10`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"The balances of accounts tagged as *my_module.my_tag* will be summed with "
"those of accounts linked to the tag with ID *42* and accounts with the code "
"prefix `10`"
msgstr ""
"Stanja kontov, označenih kot *my_module.my_tag*, bodo sešteta s tistimi "
"kontov, povezanih z značko z ID *42*, in konti s predpono kode `10`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:242
msgid "`C` and `D` suffixes can be used in the same way with tags."
msgstr "Priponi `C` in `D` se lahko uporabljata na enak način z značkami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(my_module.my_tag)C`"
msgstr "`tag(my_module.my_tag)C`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts with the tag *my_module.my_tag* and a credit "
"balance."
msgstr ""
"Ta formula se ujema s konti z značko *my_module.my_tag* in kreditnim stanjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:248
msgid "Prefix exclusion also works with tags."
msgstr "Izključitev predpone deluje tudi z značkami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`tag(my_module.my_tag)\\\\(10)`"
msgstr "`tag(my_module.my_tag)\\\\(10)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid ""
"This formula matches accounts with the tag *my_module.my_tag* and a code not "
"starting with `10`."
msgstr ""
"Ta formula se ujema s konti z značko *my_module.my_tag* in kodo, ki se ne "
"začne z `10`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:256
msgid "External Value computation engine"
msgstr "Pogon za izračun zunanje vrednosti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:258
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`External Value` computation engine is used to refer to "
"**manual** and **carryover values**. Those values are not stored using "
"`account.move.line`, but with `account.report.external.value`. Each of these "
"objects directly points to the expression it impacts, so very little needs "
"to be done about their selection here."
msgstr ""
"Pogon za izračun :guilabel:`Zunanja vrednost` se uporablja za sklicevanje na "
"**ročne** in **prenosne vrednosti**. Te vrednosti niso shranjene z "
"`account.move.line`, ampak z `account.report.external.value`. Vsak od teh "
"objektov neposredno kaže na izraz, na katerega vpliva, zato je tukaj treba "
"narediti zelo malo glede njihove izbire."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:263
msgid "**Formulas** can be one of the following:"
msgstr "**Formule** so lahko ena od naslednjih:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:266
msgid "If the result must be the sum of all the external values in the period."
msgstr "Če mora biti rezultat vsota vseh zunanjih vrednosti v obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:269
msgid "`most_recent`"
msgstr "`most_recent`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:269
msgid ""
"If the result must be the value of the latest external value in the period."
msgstr "Če mora biti rezultat vrednost najnovejše zunanje vrednosti v obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:271
msgid "In addition, **subformulas** can be used in two ways:"
msgstr "Poleg tega je **podformule** mogoče uporabiti na dva načina:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:274
msgid "`rounding=X`"
msgstr "`rounding=X`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:274
msgid ""
"Replacing `X` with a number instructs to round the amount to X decimals."
msgstr ""
"Zamenjava `X` s številko določa zaokrožitev zneska na X decimalnih mest."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:278
msgid "`editable`"
msgstr "`editable`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:277
msgid ""
"Indicates this expression can be edited manually, triggering the display of "
"an icon in the report, allowing the user to perform this action."
msgstr ""
"Označuje, da je ta izraz mogoče ročno urejati, kar sproži prikaz ikone v "
"poročilu, s katero lahko uporabnik izvede to dejanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:281
msgid ""
"Manual values are created at the `date_to` currently selected in the report."
msgstr ""
"Ročne vrednosti so ustvarjene na datum `date_to`, ki je trenutno izbran v "
"poročilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:283
msgid "Both subformulas can be mixed by separating them with a `;`."
msgstr "Obe podformuli je mogoče združiti tako, da ju ločite s `;`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "`editable;rounding=2`"
msgstr "`editable;rounding=2`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:0
msgid "This subformula shows the correct way to mix both behaviors."
msgstr "Ta podformula prikazuje pravilen način združevanja obeh vedenj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:290
msgid "Custom Python Function computation engine"
msgstr "Računski mehanizem po meri funkcije Python"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:292
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Custom Python Function` computation engine is a means for "
"developers to introduce custom computation of expressions on a case-by-case "
"basis. The :guilabel:`Formula` is the name of a **python function** to call, "
"and the :guilabel:`Subformula` is a **key** to fetch in the **dictionary** "
"returned by this function. Use this computation engine only if making a "
"custom module."
msgstr ""
"Računski mehanizem :guilabel:`Po meri funkcija Python` je sredstvo za "
"razvijalce, s katerim lahko uvedejo prilagojeno računanje izrazov za "
"posamezne primere. :guilabel:`Formula` je ime **funkcije python**, ki jo je "
"treba poklicati, :guilabel:`Podformula` pa je **ključ** za pridobitev v "
"**slovarju**, ki ga ta funkcija vrne. Ta računski mehanizem uporabite samo, "
"če izdelujete modul po meri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:299
msgid "Columns"
msgstr "Columns"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:301
msgid ""
"Reports can have an **indefinite number** of columns to display. Each column "
"gets its values from the **expressions** declared on the **lines**. The "
"field :guilabel:`expression_label` of the column gives the label of the "
"expressions whose value is displayed. If a line has no **expression** in "
"that field, then nothing is displayed for it in this column. If multiple "
"columns are required, you must use different **expression** labels."
msgstr ""
"Poročila imajo lahko **nedoločeno število** stolpcev za prikaz. Vsak stolpec "
"pridobi svoje vrednosti iz **izrazov**, deklariranih v **vrsticah**. Polje "
":guilabel:`expression_label` stolpca podaja oznako izrazov, katerih vrednost "
"je prikazana. Če vrstica v tem polju nima **izraza**, potem v tem stolpcu "
"zanjo ni prikazano nič. Če potrebujete več stolpcev, morate uporabiti "
"različne oznake **izrazov**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:None
msgid "Columns of report."
msgstr "Stolpci poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:310
msgid ""
"When using the **period comparison** feature found under "
"the :guilabel:`Options` tab of an accounting report, all columns are "
"repeated in and for each period."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi funkcije **primerjava obdobja**, ki jo najdete na zavihku "
":guilabel:`Možnosti` računovodskega poročila, so vsi stolpci ponovljeni v "
"vsakem obdobju in za vsako obdobje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:316
msgid "Line grouping"
msgstr "Združevanje vrstic"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:318
msgid ""
"Non-standard grouping is possible by adding or using existing fields on the "
