"Nestandardno združevanje je mogoče z dodajanjem ali uporabo obstoječih polj "
"v modelu *Postavka dnevnika*, pod pogojem, da so polja povezana in "
"neshranjena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:322
msgid ""
"Grouping lines requires the report to have explicit report lines that can be "
