msgstr ""
"Za združevanje po prodajni ekipi poslovnega partnerja nastavite definicijo "
"povezanega polja na `move_id.team_id`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:347
msgid "Group lines"
msgstr "Združevanje vrstic"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:349
msgid ""
"To group lines, go to the :ref:`Lines <accounting/customize/lines>` tab of "
"the desired report, click on the line you want to group, and edit "
"the :guilabel:`Group by` field. Enter the technical name (:guilabel:`Field "
"Name`) of the field to use as the grouping key."
msgstr ""
"Za združevanje vrstic pojdite na zavihek :ref:`Vrstice <accounting/customize/"
"lines>` želenega poročila, kliknite na vrstico, ki jo želite združiti, in "
"uredite polje :guilabel:`Združi po`. Vnesite tehnično ime (:guilabel:`Ime "
"polja`) polja, ki se bo uporabilo kot ključ za združevanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/customize.rst:354
msgid ""
