"report. If your contacts are related (e.g., related partners, divisions "
"within the same company, etc.), consider using :doc:`parent-type and "
"children-type contacts <../../../essentials/contacts>`."
msgstr ""
"Različni kontakti, ki si delijo isti davčni identifikator, lahko privedejo "
"do nepravilnega davčnega poročila. Če so vaši kontakti povezani (npr. "
"povezani partnerji, oddelki znotraj istega podjetja itd.), razmislite o "
"uporabi :doc:`kontaktov tipa nadrejeni in podrejeni <../../../essentials/"
"contacts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:33
msgid "Tax return periodicity"
msgstr "Periodičnost davčne napovedi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:35
msgid ""
"The configuration of the tax return periodicity allows Odoo to compute tax "
"returns correctly and automatically send reminders to make sure that "
"deadlines are met."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija periodičnosti davčne napovedi omogoča Odoo pravilno "
"izračunavanje davčnih napovedi in samodejno pošiljanje opomnikov, da se "
"zagotovi spoštovanje rokov."

