msgid "Close a tax period"
msgstr "Zapiranje davčnega obdobja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:91
msgid "Tax return lock date"
msgstr "Datum zaklepa davčne napovedi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:93
msgid ""
"Setting a tax lock date prevents changes that could impact VAT-related "
"journal entries. Locking the period before processing the :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry` helps ensure the accuracy of the final report and reduces the "
"risk of tax errors."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev datuma zaklepa davkov preprečuje spremembe, ki bi lahko vplivale "
"na postavke dnevnika, povezane z DDV. Zaklepanje obdobja pred obdelavo "
":guilabel:`Zaključne knjižbe` pomaga zagotoviti pravilnost končnega poročila "
"in zmanjšuje tveganje davčnih napak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:97
msgid ""
"To view or edit the current :guilabel:`Lock Tax Return` date, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Lock Dates`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled ali urejanje trenutnega datuma :guilabel:`Zaklep davčne napovedi` "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Datumi "
"zaklepov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:101
msgid ""
"Any new transaction whose accounting date is before the :guilabel:`Lock Tax "
"Return` date has its tax values moved to the next open tax period, "
"preventing any changes to a report after its period is closed."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka nova transakcija, katere računovodski datum je pred datumom "
":guilabel:`Zaklep davčne napovedi`, ima svoje davčne vrednosti premaknjene v "
"naslednje odprto davčno obdobje, kar preprečuje kakršne koli spremembe "
"poročila po zaprtju njegovega obdobja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:110
msgid ""
"On the Accounting Dashboard, the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal displays "
"automatic reminders to avoid missing important tasks and deadlines."
msgstr ""
"Na nadzorni plošči računovodstva dnevnik :guilabel:`Davčne napovedi` "
"prikazuje samodejne opomnike, da se izognete zamudi pomembnih opravil in "
"rokov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:113
msgid ""
"After completing all :ref:`configurations <accounting/tax-returns/"
"configuration>` and posting all tax-related transactions for the reporting "
"period, click :guilabel:`Tax Returns` on the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal "
"from the Accounting dashboard. Alternatively, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Tax Returns`."
msgstr ""
"Po dokončanju vseh :ref:`konfiguracij <accounting/tax-returns/configuration>"
"` in knjiženju vseh transakcij, povezanih z davki, za obdobje poročanja "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Davčne napovedi` v dnevniku :guilabel:`Davčne napovedi` "
"na nadzorni plošči računovodstva. Alternativno pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Davčne napovedi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:118
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Return` view displays a chronological list of all "
"pending :ref:`tax returns (VAT report) <accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` "
"and :ref:`advance payments <accounting/tax-returns/advance-payments>` (based "
"on the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`). Each item "
"on the list includes:"
msgstr ""
"Pogled :guilabel:`Davčna napoved` prikazuje kronološki seznam vseh čakajočih "
":ref:`davčnih napovedi (poročilo DDV) <accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` "
"in :ref:`akontacij <accounting/tax-returns/advance-payments>` (glede na "
":doc:`fiskalno lokalizacijo <../../fiscal_localizations>`). Vsak element na "
"seznamu vključuje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:123
msgid "A period (month or quarter)."
msgstr "Obdobje (mesec ali četrtletje)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:124
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:273
msgid "A deadline date."
msgstr "Rok."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:125
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:274
msgid ""
"The related company and :ref:`branch(es) <general/branches>`, if applicable."
msgstr ""
"Povezano podjetje in :ref:`podružnico/-e <general/branches>`, če je primerno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:126
msgid ""
"Action steps, such as :ref:`Review <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-"
"review>`, :ref:`Submit <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-submit>`, "
"and :ref:`Pay <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-pay>`, which turn green "
"when completed."
msgstr ""
"Korake dejanj, kot so :ref:`Pregled <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-"
"review>`, :ref:`Oddaj <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-submit>` in "
":ref:`Plačaj <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-pay>`, ki postanejo zeleni, "
"ko so dokončani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:129
msgid ""
"Action buttons: These are displayed as primary (purple) and secondary (grey) "
"buttons to indicate their priority."
msgstr ""
"Gumbe za dejanja: Ti so prikazani kot primarni (vijolični) in sekundarni "
"(sivi) gumbi za označevanje njihove prioritete."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:131
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:278
msgid ""
"A :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` menu for additional "
"options."
msgstr ""
"Meni :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tri-pika)` za dodatne "
"možnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:None
msgid "Tax return tool overview"
msgstr "Pregled orodja za davčne napovedi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:137
msgid ""
"Before the tax return is reviewed, the number of :guilabel:`Pending` "
"or :guilabel:`Passed` tax validation checks is displayed in red or green, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"Pred pregledom davčne napovedi se število preverjanj veljavnosti davka "
":guilabel:`Čakajoče` ali :guilabel:`Opravljeno` prikaže rdeče oziroma zeleno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:139
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:283
msgid "If the :guilabel:`Deadline` date has passed, it appears in red."
msgstr "Če je datum :guilabel:`Rok` potekel, se prikaže rdeče."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:142
msgid ""
"To export all tax returns from the selected period, click the :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then click :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`Export All` "
"to download the tax returns XLSX."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvoziti vse davčne napovedi iz izbranega obdobja, kliknite ikono "
":icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`zobnik`), nato kliknite :icon:`fa-upload` "
":guilabel:`Izvozi vse`, da prenesete XLSX davčnih napovedi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:148
msgid "VAT report"
msgstr "Poročilo o DDV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:150
msgid ""
"Each pending tax return (VAT report) follows these steps: :ref:`review "
"<accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-review>`, :ref:`submit <accounting/tax-"
"returns/vat-return-submit>`, and :ref:`pay <accounting/tax-returns/vat-"
"return-pay>`."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka davčna napoved v čakanju (poročilo o DDV) sledi tem korakom: "
":ref:`pregled <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-review>`, :ref:`oddaja "
"<accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-submit>` in :ref:`plačilo <accounting/tax-"
"returns/vat-return-pay>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:154
msgid ""
"To access a tax return, click the local VAT report button "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`VAT Return (BE)` or :guilabel:`Tax Report (US)`, depending "
"on the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`) or "
"the :guilabel:`Generic Tax report` button on the tax return line in "
"the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do davčne napovedi kliknite gumb lokalnega poročila o DDV (npr. "
":guilabel:`Napoved DDV (BE)` ali :guilabel:`Davčno poročilo (US)`, odvisno "
"od :doc:`davčne lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>`) ali gumb "
":guilabel:`Splošno davčno poročilo` v vrstici davčne napovedi v pogledu "
":guilabel:`Davčna napoved`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:161
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon and :guilabel:`Copy to "
"Documents` to save the report to the :doc:`Documents <../../../productivity/"
"documents>` app. Select the format to :guilabel:`Export to`, "
"the :guilabel:`Documents Name`, the :guilabel:`Folder` to store it in, and "
"add any :guilabel:`Tags`. Then click :guilabel:`Export`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`zobnik`) in :guilabel:`Kopiraj v "
"Dokumente`, da shranite poročilo v aplikacijo :doc:`Dokumenti <../../../"
"productivity/documents>`. Izberite obliko za :guilabel:`Izvozi v`, "
":guilabel:`Ime dokumenta`, :guilabel:`Mapo` za shranjevanje in dodajte "
":guilabel:`Oznake`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Izvozi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:166
msgid ""
"To create a new return, click :guilabel:`New`, select the "
"relevant :guilabel:`Return Type`, and fill in the "
"required :guilabel:`Dates`. Then, click :guilabel:`Generate Return`. The "
"following returns can be generated:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo napoved, kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, izberite "
"ustrezno :guilabel:`Vrsto napovedi` in izpolnite zahtevane "
":guilabel:`Datume`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari napoved`. Ustvarite "
"lahko naslednje napovedi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:170
msgid ":guilabel:`Annual Closing: Corporate Tax`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Letno zaprtje: davek od dohodkov pravnih oseb`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:171
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT` (return)/:guilabel:`Tax`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`DDV` (napoved)/:guilabel:`Davek`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:172
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT Listing` (Belgium-specific)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Seznam DDV` (specifično za Belgijo)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:173
msgid ":guilabel:`EC Sales List` (EU-specific)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Seznam prodaj ES` (specifično za EU)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:174
msgid ":guilabel:`Advance Payment` (Belgium-specific)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Akontacijsko plačilo` (specifično za Belgijo)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:175
msgid ":guilabel:`Intrastat` (EU-specific)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Intrastat` (specifično za EU)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:180
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:288
msgid "Review"
msgstr "Pregled"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:182
msgid ""
"To start the review of a tax return, click on the relevant tax return line:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite začeti s pregledom davčne napovedi, kliknite na ustrezno vrstico "
"davčne napovedi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:184
msgid ""
"If all automatic tax validation checks have passed, "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the :guilabel:`Review` step. "
"The :ref:`Lock Tax Return <accounting/tax-returns/lock-date>` date is "
"automatically updated, and the closing journal entry is posted in "
"the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal. The tax return can then "
"be :ref:`submitted <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-submit>`."
msgstr ""
"Če so vsa avtomatska preverjanja veljavnosti davka uspešno opravljena, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da dokončate korak :guilabel:`Pregled`. Datum "
":ref:`Zakleni davčno napoved <accounting/tax-returns/lock-date>` se "
"samodejno posodobi in zaključni knjižni vnos se knjiga v dnevnik "
":guilabel:`Davčne napovedi`. Davčno napoved lahko nato :ref:`oddate "
"<accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-submit>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:188
msgid ""
"If any automatic tax validation checks are pending, the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Checks` view displays the following, depending on the :doc:`fiscal "
"localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`:"
msgstr ""
"Če so kakšna avtomatska preverjanja veljavnosti davka v čakanju, pogled "
":guilabel:`Davčna preverjanja` prikaže naslednje, odvisno od :doc:`davčne "
"lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:191
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Matching`: This check is used to identify any missing bills; "
"it is optional for VAT reports."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ujemanje bank`: To preverjanje se uporablja za prepoznavanje "
"morebitnih manjkajočih računov; je neobvezno za poročila o DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:193
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bill attachments`: Bills must have attached documents as proof in "
"case of an audit."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Priloge računov`: Računi morajo imeti priložene dokumente kot "
"dokazilo v primeru revizije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:194
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company data`: Missing information (e.g., VAT number or country) "
"can lead to errors in tax reports or exemptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Podatki podjetja`: Manjkajoče informacije (npr. davčna številka "
"ali država) lahko privedejo do napak v davčnih poročilih ali oprostitvah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:196
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Draft entries`: Any draft invoices and bills within the "
"corresponding period must be reviewed and posted, or assigned a different "
"accounting date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Osnutki vnosov`: Vsi osnutki računov in prejetih računov v "
"ustreznem obdobju morajo biti pregledani in knjiženi ali jim mora biti "
"dodeljen drug datum knjiženja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:198
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No negative amount in VAT report`: Some countries only allow "
"positive values in tax returns, as a negative amount could indicate "
"misconfigurations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Brez negativnih zneskov v poročilu o DDV`: Nekatere države v "
"davčnih napovedi dovoljujejo samo pozitivne vrednosti, saj lahko negativen "
"znesek kaže na napačne nastavitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:200
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Taxes and countries matching`: Taxes applied on invoices and "
"bills must match the customer’s country."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ujemanje davkov in držav`: Davki, uporabljeni na računih in "
"prejetih računih, se morajo ujemati z državo kupca."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:203
msgid ""
"Each check card is either highlighted in green (Reviewed or Supervised), red "
"(Anomaly) or grey (To review). If a check fails, there are two options:"
msgstr ""
"Kartica vsakega preverjanja je označena z zeleno (Pregledano ali Nadzorovano)"
", rdečo (Nepravilnost) ali sivo (Za pregled). Če preverjanje ne uspe, "
"obstajata dve možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:206
msgid "Click on the failed check's card to fix the issue."
msgstr "Kliknite na kartico neuspelega preverjanja, da odpravite težavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:207
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:326
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Anomaly` and select :guilabel:`Reviewed` "
"or :guilabel:`Supervised` to pass the check without fixing the issue."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Nepravilnost` in izberite :guilabel:`Pregledano` ali "
":guilabel:`Nadzorovano`, da opravite preverjanje brez odprave težave."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:210
msgid ""
"Once all checks have passed, click :guilabel:`Validate`. Then, depending on "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`, "
"click :guilabel:`Lock` in the :guilabel:`Lock` window."
msgstr ""
"Ko vsa preverjanja uspejo, kliknite :guilabel:`Preveri veljavnost`. Nato, "
"odvisno od :doc:`fiskalne lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>`, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Zakleni` v oknu :guilabel:`Zakleni`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:213
msgid ""
"On validating the tax return, the :ref:`Lock Tax Return <accounting/tax-"
"returns/lock-date>` date is automatically updated, and the closing journal "
"entry is posted in the :guilabel:`Tax Returns` journal."
msgstr ""
"Ob potrditvi veljavnosti davčne napovedi se datum :ref:`Zaklepanja davčne "
"napovedi <accounting/tax-returns/lock-date>` samodejno posodobi, knjižni "
"zapis zaprtja pa se knjiži v dnevnik :guilabel:`Davčne napovedi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:218
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:334
msgid ""
"To add customized checks, activate :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, "
"and go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Check`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`New` and complete the necessary fields."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje prilagojenih preverjanj aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način "
"<developer-mode>` in pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Nastavitev --> Preverjanje`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` in izpolnite "
"zahtevana polja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:221
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:337
msgid "All check status changes are logged in the chatter."
msgstr "Vse spremembe statusa preverjanja so zabeležene v klepetu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:224
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Lock Tax Return` date is not locked before reviewing the "
"tax return, the fiscal period is automatically locked on the same date as "
"the accounting date of the closing journal entry. While this feature helps "
"prevent certain fiscal errors, it is recommended to set the :ref:`Lock Tax "
"Return date <accounting/tax-returns/lock-date>` manually beforehand."
msgstr ""
"Če datum :guilabel:`Zaklepanja davčne napovedi` ni zaklenjen pred pregledom "
"davčne napovedi, se fiskalno obdobje samodejno zaklene na isti datum kot je "
"datum knjiženja knjižnega zapisa zaprtja. Čeprav ta funkcija pomaga "
"preprečiti določene fiskalne napake, je priporočljivo ročno vnaprej "
"nastaviti :ref:`datum Zaklepanja davčne napovedi <accounting/tax-returns/"
"lock-date>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:230
msgid ""
"After the tax report for a period has been posted, that period is locked to "
"prevent new VAT-related journal entries from being created. Corrections to "
"customer invoices or vendor bills must be recorded in the following period."
msgstr ""
"Po knjiženju davčnega poročila za obdobje se to obdobje zaklene, da se "
"prepreči ustvarjanje novih knjižnih zapisov, povezanih z DDV. Popravki "
"računov za stranke ali prejetih računov morajo biti zabeleženi v naslednjem "
"obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:237
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:342
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Pošlji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:239
msgid ""
"Once a tax return has completed the :ref:`Review <accounting/tax-returns/vat-"
"return-review>` step, proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je davčna napoved zaključila korak :ref:`Pregled <accounting/tax-returns/"
"vat-return-review>`, nadaljujte takole:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:242
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view, click the local VAT report button "
"(e.g., :guilabel:`VAT Return (BE)` or :guilabel:`Tax Report (US)`, depending "
"on the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`) or "
"the :guilabel:`Generic Tax report` button on the relevant tax return line to "
"preview the tax return report."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu :guilabel:`Davčna napoved` kliknite gumb lokalnega poročila o DDV "
"(npr. :guilabel:`Napoved DDV (BE)` ali :guilabel:`Davčno poročilo (US)`, "
"odvisno od :doc:`fiskalne lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>`) ali "
"gumb :guilabel:`Splošno davčno poročilo` na ustrezni vrstici davčne napovedi "
"za predogled poročila o davčni napovedi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:246
msgid ""
"Once the tax return report has been verified, go back to the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Return` view and click :guilabel:`Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je poročilo o davčni napovedi preverjeno, se vrnite v pogled "
":guilabel:`Davčna napoved` in kliknite :guilabel:`Oddaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:248
msgid ""
"If a :guilabel:`Submission Instructions` pop-up window appears, follow the "
"local :guilabel:`Instructions`, and click :guilabel:`Mark as Submitted` "
"or :ref:`Mark Paid <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-pay>`."
msgstr ""
"Če se prikaže pojavno okno :guilabel:`Navodila za oddajo`, sledite lokalnim "
":guilabel:`Navodilom` in kliknite :guilabel:`Označi kot oddano` ali "
":ref:`Označi kot plačano <accounting/tax-returns/vat-return-pay>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:252
msgid ""
"The submitted tax return contains all the values tax authorities need, and "
"the amount to be paid or refunded."
msgstr ""
"Oddana davčna napoved vsebuje vse vrednosti, ki jih potrebujejo davčni "
"organi, ter znesek, ki ga je treba plačati ali povrniti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:256
msgid ""
"To display all posted closing journal entries, click the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Returns` journal in the Accounting dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz vseh knjiženih knjižnih zapisov zaprtja kliknite dnevnik "
":guilabel:`Davčne napovedi` na Nadzorna plošča računovodstva."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:258
