"Predplačila davka so specifična za lokalne :doc:`davčne lokalizacije <../../"
"fiscal_localizations>` in zahteve davčnih sistemov določenih držav."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:297
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view, click :guilabel:`Pay` on the relevant "
"advance tax payment line that needs to be processed."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu :guilabel:`Davčna napoved` kliknite :guilabel:`Plačaj` na ustrezni "
