#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:300
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Advance Payment` window, follow the local recommendations, "
"fill in the required local fields, and use the provided payment details to "
"finalize the transaction. Two options are available:"
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Predplačilo` sledite lokalnim priporočilom, izpolnite "
"zahtevana lokalna polja in uporabite priložene podatke o plačilu za "
"dokončanje transakcije. Na voljo sta dve možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:304
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Mark Paid` once the payment is processed: The corresponding "
"advance tax payment line disappears from the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Označi kot plačano`, ko je plačilo obdelano: ustrezna "
"vrstica predplačila davka izgine iz pogleda :guilabel:`Davčna napoved`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:306
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Send` to email all payment information. Once sent, the "
"advance tax payment completes the :guilabel:`Pay` step, and its "
"corresponding line disappears from the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view."
