"Kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`, da pošljete vse podatke o plačilu po e-pošti. "
"Ko je poslano, predplačilo davka dokonča korak :guilabel:`Plačaj` in "
"ustrezna vrstica izgine iz pogleda :guilabel:`Davčna napoved`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:309
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Discard`: The corresponding advance tax payment line "
"remains visible in the :guilabel:`Tax Return` view."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Zavrzi`: ustrezna vrstica predplačila davka ostane vidna "
"v pogledu :guilabel:`Davčna napoved`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:313
msgid ""
"To mark a tax payment that has already been completed, click the :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon and select :guilabel:`Mark "
"as Completed`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite označiti davčno plačilo, ki je bilo že dokončano, kliknite ikono "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tri pika)` in izberite "
":guilabel:`Označi kot dokončano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:3
msgid "Year-end closing"
msgstr "Zaključek poslovnega leta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:5
msgid ""
"Year-end closing is essential for maintaining financial accuracy, complying "
"with regulations, making informed decisions, and ensuring transparency in "
"reporting."
msgstr ""
"Zaključek leta je bistveni za vzdrževanje finančne natančnosti, skladnost s "
"predpisi, sprejemanje informiranih odločitev in zagotavljanje preglednosti "
"pri poročanju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`Tax return <tax_returns>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Davčna napoved <tax_returns>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:14
msgid "Fiscal years"
msgstr "Fiskalna leta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:16
msgid ""
"By default, the fiscal year is set to last 12 months and ends on December "
"31st. However, its duration and end date can vary due to cultural, "
"administrative, and economic considerations."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je poslovno leto nastavljeno na 12 mesecev in se konča 31. "
"decembra. Vendar se lahko njegovo trajanje in končni datum razlikujeta "
"zaradi kulturnih, upravnih in ekonomskih dejavnikov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:19
msgid ""
"To modify these values, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Fiscal Periods` section, change "
"the :guilabel:`Last Day` field if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Za spremembo teh vrednosti pojdite v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. V razdelku :guilabel:`Poslovna obdobja` po "
"potrebi spremenite polje :guilabel:`Zadnji dan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:22
msgid ""
"If the period lasts *more* than or *less* than 12 months, "
"enable :guilabel:`Fiscal Years` and :guilabel:`Save`. Go back to "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Periods` section and click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Fiscal Years`. Then, click :guilabel:`New`, give it "
"a :guilabel:`Name` and both a :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End "
"Date`."
msgstr ""
"Če obdobje traja *več* kot ali *manj* kot 12 mesecev, omogočite "
":guilabel:`Poslovna leta` in :guilabel:`Shranite`. Vrnite se v razdelek "
":guilabel:`Poslovna obdobja` in kliknite :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Poslovna leta`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, določite "
":guilabel:`Naziv` ter :guilabel:`Začetni datum` in :guilabel:`Končni datum`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:28
msgid ""
"Once the set fiscal period is over, Odoo automatically reverts to the "
"default periodicity, considering the value specified in the :guilabel:`Last "
"Day` field."
msgstr ""
"Ko se nastavljeno poslovno obdobje konča, Odoo samodejno povrne na privzeto "
"periodičnost ob upoštevanju vrednosti, določene v polju :guilabel:`Zadnji "
"dan`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:34
msgid "Year-end checklist"
msgstr "Kontrolni seznam za konec leta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:39
msgid "Before closure"
msgstr "Pred zaprtjem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:41
msgid ""
"Before closing a fiscal year, ensure that everything is accurate and up-to-"
"date:"
msgstr ""
"Pred zaprtjem poslovnega leta se prepričajte, da je vse natančno in "
"posodobljeno:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:43
msgid ""
"Make sure all bank accounts are fully :doc:`reconciled <../bank/"
"reconciliation>` up to year-end and confirm that the ending book balances "
"match the bank statement balances."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so vsi bančni računi v celoti :doc:`usklajeni <../bank/"
"reconciliation>` do konca leta in potrdite, da se končna stanja v knjigah "
"ujemajo s stanji na bančnih izpiskih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:45
msgid ""
"Confirm that all :doc:`customer invoices <../customer_invoices>` "
"and :doc:`vendor bills <../vendor_bills>` have been created and all draft "
"entries have been either confirmed or cancelled, as needed."
msgstr ""
"Potrdite, da so bili vsi :doc:`računi strankam <../customer_invoices>` in "
":doc:`dobaviteljski računi <../vendor_bills>` ustvarjeni ter da so bili vsi "
"osnutki vnosov po potrebi potrjeni ali preklicani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:48
msgid ""
"Ensure the accuracy of all :doc:`expenses <../../expenses>` and validate "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovite natančnost vseh :doc:`stroškov <../../expenses>` in jih potrdite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:49
msgid ""
"Check that all :doc:`received payments <../payments>` have been encoded and "
"confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, da so vsa :doc:`prejeta plačila <../payments>` vnesena in "
"potrjena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:50
msgid "Close all :ref:`suspense accounts <accounting/journals/bank-cash-cc>`."
msgstr "Zaprite vse :ref:`začasne račune <accounting/journals/bank-cash-cc>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:51
msgid ""
"Ensure :doc:`loans <../bank/loans>` are properly registered for automatic "
"amortization calculations."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovite, da so :doc:`posojila <../bank/loans>` pravilno registrirana za "
"samodejne izračune amortizacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:53
msgid ""
"Review overdue payables and receivables aged over 60 days, and assess "
"whether a provision for uncertain liabilities or an allowance for doubtful "
"accounts is required."
msgstr ""
"Preglejte zapadle obveznosti in terjatve, starejše od 60 dni, in ocenite, "
"ali je potrebna rezervacija za negotove obveznosti ali popravek vrednosti za "
"dvomljive terjatve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:55
msgid ""
"Book all :doc:`depreciation <../vendor_bills/assets>` and :doc:`deferred "
"revenue <../customer_invoices/deferred_revenues>` entries."
msgstr ""
"Knjižite vse vnose :doc:`amortizacije <../vendor_bills/assets>` in "
":doc:`odloženih prihodkov <../customer_invoices/deferred_revenues>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:61
msgid "Closing a fiscal year"
msgstr "Zaprtje poslovnega leta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:63
msgid "Then, to close the fiscal year:"
msgstr "Nato za zaprtje poslovnega leta:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:65
msgid ""
"Run a :ref:`tax report <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`, and verify that "
"all tax information is correct."
msgstr ""
"Zaženite :ref:`davčno poročilo <accounting/reporting/tax-report>` in "
"preverite, da so vse davčne informacije pravilne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:67
msgid ""
"Reconcile all accounts on the :ref:`balance sheet <accounting/reporting/"
"balance-sheet>`:"
msgstr ""
"Uskladite vse račune v :ref:`bilanci stanja <accounting/reporting/balance-"
"sheet>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:69
msgid ""
"Update the bank balances in Odoo to reflect the actual balances as per the "
"bank statements."
msgstr ""
"Posodobite bančna stanja v Odoo, da odražajo dejanska stanja glede na bančne "
"izpiske."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:70
msgid ""
"Reconcile all transactions in the cash and bank accounts by running "
"the :ref:`aged receivables <accounting/reporting/aged-receivable>` "
"and :ref:`aged payables <accounting/reporting/aged-payable>` reports."
msgstr ""
"Uskladite vse transakcije na denarnih in bančnih računih tako, da zaženete "
"poročili :ref:`starostna struktura terjatev <accounting/reporting/aged-"
"receivable>` in :ref:`starostna struktura obveznosti <accounting/reporting/"
"aged-payable>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:73
msgid ""
"Audit all accounts, fully understanding all transactions and their nature, "
"including :doc:`loans <../bank/loans>` and :doc:`fixed assets <../"
"vendor_bills/assets>`."
msgstr ""
"Revidirajte vse račune in popolnoma razumejte vse transakcije in njihovo "
"naravo, vključno z :doc:`posojili <../bank/loans>` in :doc:`osnovnimi "
"sredstvi <../vendor_bills/assets>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:75
msgid ""
"Optionally, :ref:`match payments <accounting/payments/payments-matching>` to "
"validate any open vendor bills and customer invoices with their payments. "
"While this step is optional, it could assist the year-end closing process if "
"all outstanding payments and invoices are reconciled, potentially finding "
"errors or mistakes in the system."
msgstr ""
"Po želji :ref:`uskladite plačila <accounting/payments/payments-matching>`, "
"da potrdite odprte račune dobaviteljev in kupcev z njihovimi plačili. Čeprav "
"je ta korak neobvezen, lahko pomaga pri procesu zaprtja leta, če so vsa "
"neporavnana plačila in računi uskladeni, kar lahko razkrije napake ali "
"pomanjkljivosti v sistemu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:80
msgid ""
"Next, the accountant likely verifies balance sheet items and book entries "
"for:"
msgstr ""
"Nato računovodja običajno preveri postavke bilance stanja in knjižne vnose "
"za:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:82
msgid "year-end manual adjustments,"
msgstr "ročne prilagoditve ob koncu leta,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:83
msgid "work in progress,"
msgstr "nedokončano delo,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:84
msgid "depreciation journal entries,"
msgstr "knjižne vnose amortizacije,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:85
msgid "loans,"
msgstr "posojila,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:86
msgid "tax adjustments,"
msgstr "davčne prilagoditve,"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:87
msgid "etc."
msgstr "itd."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:89
msgid ""
"During the year-end audit, the accountant may print paper copies of all "
"balance sheet items (e.g., loans, bank accounts, prepayments, sales tax "
"statements) to compare them against the balances recorded in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Med revizijo ob koncu leta lahko računovodja natisne papirnate kopije vseh "
"postavk bilance stanja (npr. posojila, bančni računi, vnaprejšnja plačila, "
"izpisi prometnega davka), da jih primerja z bilancami, vnešenimi v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:94
msgid ""
"As part of this process, setting a :ref:`Lock Everything <accounting/year-"
"end/lock-everything-date>` date to the last day (inclusive) of the preceding "
"fiscal year is good practice. This ensures that journal entries with an "
"accounting date on or before the lock date cannot be created or modified "
"during the audit. Users with *administrator* access rights can still create "
"and edit entries if an :ref:`exception is configured <accounting/year-end/"
"lock-date-exception>`."
msgstr ""
"Kot del tega postopka je dobra praksa nastaviti datum :ref:`Zakleni vse "
"<accounting/year-end/lock-everything-date>` na zadnji dan (vključno) "
"prejšnjega poslovnega leta. To zagotavlja, da knjižb z računovodskim datumom "
"na datum zaklepa ali pred njim med revizijo ni mogoče ustvariti ali "
"spremeniti. Uporabniki s skrbniškimi pravicami dostopa lahko še vedno "
"ustvarjajo in urejajo vnose, če je :ref:`konfigurirana izjema <accounting/"
"year-end/lock-date-exception>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:104
msgid "Lock everything date"
msgstr "Datum zaklepa vsega"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:106
msgid ""
"Setting a lock date prevents modifications to any posted journal entries "
"with an accounting date on or before the lock date. It also prevents posting "
"new entries with an accounting date on or before the lock date. In such "
"cases, the system automatically sets the accounting date to the day after "
"the lock date."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev datuma zaklepa prepreči spremembe vseh knjiženih knjižb z "
"računovodskim datumom na ali pred datumom zaklepa. Prav tako prepreči "
"knjiženje novih vnosov z računovodskim datumom na ali pred datumom zaklepa. "
"V takih primerih sistem samodejno nastavi računovodski datum na dan po "
"datumu zaklepa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:111
msgid ""
"To set a :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date, go to :menuselection:`Accounting "
"--> Accounting --> Lock Dates`. In the :guilabel:`Lock Journal Entries` "
"window, set the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti datum :guilabel:`Zaklep vsega`, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Datumi zaklepa`. V oknu "
":guilabel:`Zaklep knjižb` nastavite datum :guilabel:`Zaklep vsega` in "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:115
msgid ""
"After setting the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date, an :ref:`exception "
"<accounting/year-end/lock-date-exception>` can be made if a modification is "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
"Po nastavitvi datuma :guilabel:`Zakleni vse` je mogoče narediti :ref:`izjemo "
"<accounting/year-end/lock-date-exception>`, če je potrebna sprememba."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:121
msgid "Lock date exception"
msgstr "Izjema datuma zaklepa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:123
msgid ""
"Users with :ref:`Administrator <accounting/accountant-access-rights>` access "
"rights to the Accounting app can create exceptions. To do so:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki z :ref:`administratorskimi <accounting/accountant-access-rights>` "
"pravicami dostopa do aplikacije Računovodstvo lahko ustvarijo izjeme. Za to:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:126
msgid ""
"After setting and saving a lock date, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Accounting --> Lock Dates`. In the :guilabel:`Lock Journal Entries` window, "
"remove the :guilabel:`Lock Everything` date."
msgstr ""
"Po nastavitvi in shranjevanju datuma zaklepa pojdite v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Datumi zaklepa`. V oknu "
":guilabel:`Zakleni postavke dnevnika` odstranite datum :guilabel:`Zakleni "
"vse`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:129
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Exception` banner, choose if this exception should be "
"set :guilabel:`for me` (the current user) or :guilabel:`for everyone`, and "
"how long it should last."
msgstr ""
"V pasici :guilabel:`Izjema` izberite, ali naj bo ta izjema nastavljena "
":guilabel:`zame` (trenutni uporabnik) ali :guilabel:`za vse`, ter kako dolgo "
"naj traja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:131
msgid "A :guilabel:`Reason` for this exception can be added."
msgstr "Dodate lahko :guilabel:`Razlog` za to izjemo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:132
msgid ""
"All of this information is logged in the chatter of the :doc:`company record "
"</applications/general/companies>`."
msgstr ""
"Vse te informacije so zabeležene v pogovorih :doc:`zapisa podjetja </"
"applications/general/companies>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:136
msgid ""
"To remove a lock date after it has been saved, configure the exception to "
"apply :guilabel:`for everyone` and set the duration to :guilabel:`forever`. "
"This does not apply to the :guilabel:`Hard Lock` date, which is irreversible "
"to ensure inalterability and to meet accounting requirements in certain "
"countries."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti datum zaklepa po tem, ko je bil shranjen, "
"konfigurirajte izjemo tako, da velja :guilabel:`za vse` in nastavite "
"trajanje na :guilabel:`za vedno`. To ne velja za datum :guilabel:`Trdega "
"zaklepa`, ki je nepreklicen za zagotovitev nespremenljivosti in za "
"izpolnjevanje računovodskih zahtev v določenih državah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:144
msgid "Current year earnings"
msgstr "Poslovni izid tekočega leta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:147
msgid ""
"In versions before Odoo 19, current year earnings were handled differently. "
"For consistency in your reporting history, upgrading users should revisit "
"past fiscal years and explicitly book the results that were previously "
"handled implicitly by the system. These :ref:`manual journal entries "
"<accounting/year-end/manual-je>` should be made in chronological order. For "
"more information on why this change was made and how versions before Odoo 19 "
"compare to versions after it, see this `blog post <https://www.odoo.com/blog/"
"business-hacks-1/how-to-manage-current-years-earnings-in-odoo-19-compared-to-"
"previous-versions-2107>`_."
msgstr ""
"V različicah pred Odoo 19 je bil poslovni izid tekočega leta obravnavan "
"drugače. Za doslednost v vaši zgodovini poročanja bi morali uporabniki po "
"nadgradnji ponovno obiskati pretekla poslovna leta in izrecno knjižiti "
"rezultate, ki jih je sistem prej obravnaval implicitno. Te :ref:`ročne "
"knjižbe <accounting/year-end/manual-je>` je treba vnesti v kronološkem "
"vrstnem redu. Za več informacij o tem, zakaj je bila ta sprememba narejena "
"in kako se različice pred Odoo 19 primerjajo z različicami po njej, glejte "
"ta `zapis na blogu<https://www.odoo.com/blog/business-hacks-1/how-to-manage-"
"current-years-earnings-in-odoo-19-compared-to-previous-versions-2107>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:154
msgid ""
"At the end of a fiscal year, a company will almost always have a net profit "
"or a net loss that is calculated by summing the income and expenses accounts "
"of the profit and loss statement. Odoo displays the result for year **N** as "
"a **dynamic line** called *Result Brought Forward* in the trial balance and "
"general ledger of the year **N+1**. To clear this dynamic line, create "
"a :ref:`manual journal entry <accounting/year-end/manual-je>` in year **N** "
"for the end-of-year result using a :ref:`Current Year Earnings type account "
"<accounting/year-end/appropriation>`."
msgstr ""
"Ob koncu poslovnega leta ima podjetje skoraj vedno neto dobiček ali neto "
"izgubo, ki se izračuna s seštevkom računov prihodkov in odhodkov iz izkaza "
"poslovnega izida. Odoo prikaže rezultat za leto **N** kot **dinamično "
"vrstico** z imenom *Prenos rezultata* v preizkusni bilanci in glavni knjigi "
"za leto **N+1**. Za počiščenje te dinamične vrstice ustvarite :ref:`ročno "
"knjiženje <accounting/year-end/manual-je>` v letu **N** za rezultat ob koncu "
"leta z uporabo :ref:`računa vrste Tekoči letni dobički <accounting/year-end/"
"appropriation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:164
msgid "Balancing the trial balance"
msgstr "Uravnoteženje obratne bilance"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:166
msgid ""
"A trial balance is, by default, always balanced (meaning the sum of debits "
"equals the sum of credits) because it records the sum of all journal entries "
"which are themselves balanced. However, **balance sheet accounts** (assets, "
"liabilities, and equity) carry over their balances from previous fiscal "
"years, whereas **profit and loss accounts** (income, expense, "
"and :ref:`appropriation accounts <accounting/year-end/appropriation>`) reset "
"to zero at the start of a new fiscal year. This difference in account "
"behavior would leave the trial balance unbalanced if it were not for the "
"dynamic line - *Result Brought Forward* - that balances this difference "
"temporarily until an explicit, :ref:`manual journal entry <accounting/year-"
"end/manual-je>` is made to appropriate the profit or the loss. Posting an "
"explicit entry to a :ref:`current year earnings account <accounting/year-end/"
"appropriation>` at year-end \"neutralizes\" the dynamic line and ensures the "
"trial balance is balanced by actual journal items. This manual journal entry "
"does not need to be made immediately following the end of the fiscal year "
"because the trial balance is always balanced, but whenever the company's "
"profit/loss is ready to be appropriated, this manual journal entry replaces "
"the dynamic line."
msgstr ""
"Preizkusna bilanca je privzeto vedno uravnotežena (kar pomeni, da je vsota "
"bremena enaka vsoti dobropisa), ker beleži vsoto vseh knjižb, ki so same "
"uravnotežene. Vendar pa **računi bilance stanja** (sredstva, obveznosti in "
"kapital) prenašajo svoja salda iz prejšnjih poslovnih let, medtem ko se "
"**računi dobička in izgube** (prihodki, odhodki in :ref:`računi razporeditve "
"<accounting/year-end/appropriation>`) ponastavijo na nič ob začetku novega "
"poslovnega leta. Ta razlika v obnašanju računov bi pustila preizkusno "
"bilanco neuravnoteženo, če ne bi bilo dinamične vrstice - *Prenos "
"rezultata* - ki začasno uravnoteži to razliko, dokler ni narejeno izrecno, "
":ref:`ročno knjiženje <accounting/year-end/manual-je>` za razporeditev "
"dobička ali izgube. Knjiženje izrecnega vnosa na :ref:`račun tekočih letnih "
"dobičkov <accounting/year-end/appropriation>` ob koncu leta \"nevtralizira\" "
"dinamično vrstico in zagotavlja, da je preizkusna bilanca uravnotežena z "
"dejanskimi knjižbami. Tega ročnega knjiženja ni treba izvesti takoj po koncu "
"poslovnega leta, ker je preizkusna bilanca vedno uravnotežena, vendar kadar "
"koli je dobiček/izguba podjetja pripravljena za razporeditev, to ročno "
"knjiženje nadomesti dinamično vrstico."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:184
msgid "Appropriation (current year earnings) accounts"
msgstr "Računi za razporeditev (poslovni izid tekočega leta)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:186
msgid ""
"Appropriation accounts (also called by their account type, current year "
"earnings) are used to allocate a company's profit or loss, whether that "
"allocation is to reserves, dividends, or any other destination. There are "
"several key pieces of information to know about these accounts and how they "
"function:"
msgstr ""
"Računi za razporeditev (imenovani tudi po njihovi vrsti računa, poslovni "
"izid tekočega leta) se uporabljajo za razporeditev dobička ali izgube "
"podjetja, ne glede na to, ali gre za razporeditev v rezerve, dividende ali "
"drugo namembnost. O teh računih in njihovem delovanju je treba poznati več "
"ključnih informacij:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:191
msgid ""
"**Annual reset**: Like the income and expenses accounts that are also found "
"on the profit and loss statement, allocation accounts have their opening "
"balances reset at the beginning of a fiscal year."
msgstr ""
"**Letno ponastavljanje**: Tako kot računi prihodkov in odhodkov, ki se prav "
"tako nahajajo v izkazu poslovnega izida, imajo tudi računi razporeditve na "
"začetku poslovnega leta ponastavljene začetne salde."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:194
msgid ""
"**P&L presentation**: These accounts appear at the bottom of the **profit "
"and loss** statement."
msgstr ""
"**Predstavitev v P&L**: Ti računi se pojavijo na dnu izkaza **poslovnega "
"izida**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:195
msgid ""
"**No profit effect**: Unlike income and expenses accounts, these accounts "
"**do not affect** the calculation of the net profit."
msgstr ""
"**Brez vpliva na dobiček**: Za razliko od računov prihodkov in odhodkov ti "
"računi **ne vplivajo** na izračun čistega dobička."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:197
msgid ""
"**Balance sheet counterparts**: Only the *counterparts* of the journal items "
"that debit or credit appropriations accounts (e.g., the dividends payable or "
"the reserve accounts) appear on the balance sheet. This maintains a strict "
"separation between the process of distributing profit and the resulting "
"liabilities or equity."
msgstr ""
"**Protipostavke v bilanci stanja**: V bilanci stanja se prikažejo samo "
"*protipostavke* postavk dnevnika, ki bremenijo ali dobropisujejo račune "
"razporeditve (npr. dividende za izplačilo ali računi rezerv). To ohranja "
"strogo ločitev med postopkom razdelitve dobička in posledičnimi obveznostmi "
"ali kapitalom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:205
msgid "Manual journal entry"
msgstr "Ročni vnos v dnevnik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:207
msgid ""
"To roll up income and expenses and replace the dynamic *Result Brought "
"Forward* line with an explicit journal item that balances the trial balance, "
"create a manual journal entry by following these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za seštevanje prihodkov in odhodkov ter zamenjavo dinamične vrstice *Prenos "
"rezultata* z izrecnim knjižbom, ki uravnoteži preizkusno bilanco, ustvarite "
"ročno knjiženje z naslednjimi koraki:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:211
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Journal Entries`."
msgstr ""
"Odprite :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Vnosi v dnevnik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:212
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:146
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:175
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr "Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:213
msgid ""
"Add a :guilabel:`Reference` such as `Annual Closing [YEAR]`, replacing "
"`[YEAR]` with the current year."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte :guilabel:`Sklic`, kot je `Letno zaprtje [LETO]`, pri čemer `[LETO]` "
"zamenjajte s tekočim letom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:215
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Accounting Date` to the end of the fiscal year in which "
"the profit or loss was incurred."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite :guilabel:`Računovodski datum` na konec poslovnega leta, v katerem "
"je nastal dobiček ali izguba."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:217
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab, add the necessary appropriation lines. "
"In the case of recording a profit, debit one or more appropriation (current "
"year earnings) accounts. In the case of recording a loss, credit one or more "
"appropriation (current year earnings) accounts. Either way, to fully "
"distribute the year's profit or loss, the amount should sum to the amount "
"that is on the dynamic :guilabel:`Result Brought Forward` line of the trial "
"balance **for the year after the profit or loss was incurred**."
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku :guilabel:`Postavke knjižb` dodajte potrebne vrstice "
"razporeditve. V primeru beleženja dobička bremenite enega ali več računov "
"razporeditve (tekoči letni dobički). V primeru beleženja izgube dobropišite "
"enega ali več računov razporeditve (tekoči letni dobički). V vsakem primeru, "
"da v celoti razporedite letni dobiček ali izgubo, mora znesek sešteti "
"znesek, ki je na dinamični vrstici :guilabel:`Prenos rezultata` v preizkusni "
"bilanci **za leto po tem, ko je bil dobiček ali izguba ustvarjena**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:223
msgid ""
"Add one or more additional lines that credit (in the case of a profit) or "
"debit (in the case of a loss) one or more destination accounts to balance "
"the journal entry. Depending on the localization and the situation, the "
"destination account(s) will vary, but they could be other appropriation "
"(current year earnings) accounts, equity accounts, current liabilities "
"accounts, or a combination thereof. The sum of these lines must balance the "
"line(s) from the previous step."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte eno ali več dodatnih vrstic, ki dobropisujejo (v primeru dobička) "
"ali bremenijo (v primeru izgube) enega ali več ciljnih računov, da "
"uravnotežite vnos v dnevnik. Glede na lokalizacijo in situacijo se bo(do) "
"ciljni račun(i) razlikoval(i), lahko pa so to drugi računi razporeditve "
"(tekoče leto dobička), kapitalski računi, računi kratkoročnih obveznosti ali "
"njihova kombinacija. Vsota teh vrstic mora uravnotežiti vrstico(e) iz "
"prejšnjega koraka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:228
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Post`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Objavi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:231
msgid ""
"Depending on the localization and the situation, the accounts involved will "
"vary. The following example illustrates one potential journal entry using "
"accounts from the Belgian :abbr:`GAAP (generally accepted accounting "
"principles)` / :abbr:`CSA-WVV (code des sociétés et des associations - "
"wetboek van vennootschappen en verenigingen)`. This example debits three "
"different allocation (current year earnings) accounts and credits three "
"different destination accounts (two equity accounts and one current "
"liabilities account)."
msgstr ""
"Glede na lokalizacijo in situacijo se bodo vključeni računi razlikovali. "
"Naslednji primer prikazuje en možen vnos v dnevnik z računi iz belgijskih "
":abbr:`GAAP (splošno sprejetih računovodskih načel)` / :abbr:`CSA-WVV (code "
"des sociétés et des associations - wetboek van vennootschappen en "
"verenigingen)`. Ta primer bremeni tri različne račune razporeditve (tekoče "
"leto dobička) in dobropisuje tri različne ciljne račune (dva kapitalska "
"računa in en račun kratkoročnih obveznosti)."

