"zaprtji. Čakajoče :guilabel:`Letno zaprtje` sledi dvema korakoma: "
":ref:`pregled <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/review>` in :ref:`oddaja "
"<accounting/year-end/annual-closing/submit>`. Postavka :guilabel:`Letno "
"zaprtje` vključuje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:272
