#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:275
msgid ""
"Action steps, such as :ref:`Review <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/"
"review>` and :ref:`Submit <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/submit>`, "
