":doc:`fiskalne lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:293
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Aged payables per partner`: Review payables without a partner."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Starane obveznosti po partnerju`: Preglejte obveznosti brez "
"partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:294
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Aged receivables per partner`: Review receivables without a "
"partner."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Starane terjatve po partnerju`: Preglejte terjatve brez partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:295
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Reconciliation`: Reconcile all bank account transactions up "
"to year-end."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bančno uskladitev`: Uskladite vse transakcije bančnega računa do "
"konca leta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:296
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Deferred Entries`: Ensure start and end dates are correctly set "
"on bills and invoices."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Odloženi vnosi`: Zagotovite, da so začetni in končni datumi "
"pravilno nastavljeni na računih in fakturah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:298
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Earnings Allocation`: After adjustments, transfer the result "
"brought forward to an equity account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Razporeditev dobička`: Po prilagoditvah prenesite prenos "
"rezultata na račun lastniškega kapitala."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:300
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fixed Assets`: Ensure assets are properly registered for "
"automatic depreciation calculation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Osnovna sredstva`: Zagotovite, da so sredstva pravilno "
"registrirana za samodejni izračun amortizacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:302
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Loans`: Ensure loans are properly registered for automatic "
"amortization calculations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Posojila`: Prepričajte se, da so posojila pravilno registrirana "
"za samodejne izračune amortizacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:303
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manual Adjustments`: Complete any necessary manual adjustments "
"and internal checks."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ročne prilagoditve`: Dokončajte vse potrebne ročne prilagoditve "
"in notranje preglede."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:304
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No draft entries`: Review and post draft invoices, bills, and "
"entries in the period, or change their accounting date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Brez osnutkov vnosov`: Preglejte in knjižite osnutke računov, "
"prejetih računov in vnosov v obdobju ali spremenite njihov računovodski "
"datum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:306
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Overdue payables`: Review overdue payables aged over 60 days and "
"assess the need for an allowance for uncertain liabilities."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zapadle obveznosti`: Preglejte zapadle obveznosti, stare več kot "
"60 dni, in ocenite potrebo po rezervaciji za negotove obveznosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:308
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Overdue receivables`: Review overdue receivables aged over 60 "
"days and assess the need for an allowance for doubtful accounts or expected "
"credit loss provision, as per IFRS 9 guidelines."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zapadle terjatve`: Preglejte zapadle terjatve, stare več kot 60 "
"dni, in ocenite potrebo po rezervaciji za dvomljive terjatve ali rezervaciji "
"za pričakovano kreditno izgubo v skladu s smernicami MSRP 9."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:311
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Total Receivables`: Verify that the total aged receivables equals "
"the customer account balance."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skupne terjatve`: Preverite, ali se skupne starostno razporejene "
"terjatve ujemajo s stanjem računa kupca."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:313
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Total payables`: Verify that the total aged payables equals the "
"vendor account balance."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skupne obveznosti`: Preverite, ali se skupne starostno "
"razporejene obveznosti ujemajo s stanjem računa dobavitelja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:316
msgid ""
"Some of the checks are performed automatically, while others serve as "
"reminders to review essential tasks. Each check card is either labeled as:"
msgstr ""
"Nekateri pregledi se izvedejo samodejno, drugi pa služijo kot opomniki za "
"pregled bistvenih nalog. Vsaka kartica pregleda je označena kot:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:319
msgid ":guilabel:`Reviewed` (highlighted in green): The check has passed."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pregledano` (označeno zeleno): Pregled je uspel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:320
msgid ""
":guilabel:`To review` (highlighted in grey): Action is required before the "
"check can be manually marked as :guilabel:`Reviewed` "
"or :guilabel:`Supervised`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Za pregled` (označeno sivo): Potrebno je ukrepanje, preden lahko "
"pregled ročno označite kot :guilabel:`Pregledano` ali "
":guilabel:`Nadzorovano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:322
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Anomaly` (highlighted in red): The automatic check detects an "
"issue. There are two options:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Anomalija` (označeno rdeče): Samodejni pregled zazna težavo. Na "
"voljo sta dve možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:325
msgid "Click the failed check's card to fix the issue."
msgstr "Kliknite na kartico neuspelega pregleda, da odpravite težavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:329
msgid ""
"Once all closing validation checks have passed, either labeled "
"as :guilabel:`Reviewed` or :guilabel:`Supervised`, "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to complete the :guilabel:`Review` step. The "
"annual closing can then be :ref:`submitted <accounting/year-end/annual-"
"closing/submit>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi pregledi za preverjanje zaključka uspešno opravljeni in označeni "
"kot :guilabel:`Pregledano` ali :guilabel:`Nadzorovano`, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Potrdi`, da dokončate korak :guilabel:`Pregled`. Letni zaključek "
"lahko nato :ref:`oddate <accounting/year-end/annual-closing/submit>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:344
msgid ""
"Once a tax return has completed the :ref:`Review <accounting/tax-returns/vat-"
"return-review>` step, click :guilabel:`Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je davčna napoved dokončala korak :ref:`Pregled <accounting/tax-returns/"
"vat-return-review>`, kliknite :guilabel:`Oddaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:347
msgid ""
"If a :guilabel:`Submission Instructions` pop-up window appears, depending on "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../fiscal_localizations>`, follow the "
"local :guilabel:`Instructions`, and click :guilabel:`Mark as Submitted`."
msgstr ""
"Če se prikaže pojavno okno :guilabel:`Navodila za oddajo`, odvisno od "
":doc:`fiskalne lokalizacije <../../fiscal_localizations>`, sledite lokalnim "
":guilabel:`Navodilom` in kliknite :guilabel:`Označi kot oddano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/year_end.rst:352
msgid ""
"To review checks before submitting the annual closing, click the :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the annual closing line "
"and select :guilabel:`Reset`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pregledati preglede pred oddajo letnega zaključka, kliknite ikono "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tri-pičje)` v vrstici letnega "
"zaključka in izberite :guilabel:`Ponastavi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:7
msgid ""
"Tax regulations generally require companies to compute tax amounts on sales, "
"keep a record of accumulated tax debit and credit, and periodically file "
"this information in tax returns."
msgstr ""
"Davčni predpisi na splošno zahtevajo, da podjetja izračunavajo zneske davkov "
"pri prodaji, vodijo evidenco zbranega davčnega dolga in dobropisa ter "
"periodično poročajo te informacije v davčnih napovedbah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:11
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:13
msgid "In general, managing taxes in Odoo involves the following steps:"
msgstr "Na splošno upravljanje davkov v Odoo vključuje naslednje korake:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:15
msgid ""
"Taxes are added on individual lines of documents created via the Sales, "
"Purchase, Accounting, and Point of Sale apps."
msgstr ""
"Davki se dodajo na posamezne vrstice dokumentov, ustvarjenih prek aplikacij "
"Prodaja, Nabava, Računovodstvo in Prodajna točka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:17
msgid "Odoo automatically computes tax amounts on the documents."
msgstr "Odoo samodejno izračuna zneske davkov na dokumentih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:18
msgid ""
"On accounting documents, Odoo generates journal items to keep track of tax "
"debit and tax credit."
msgstr ""
"Pri računovodskih dokumentih Odoo ustvari postavke dnevnika za sledenje "
"davčnega dolga in davčnega dobropisa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:19
msgid ""
"The total base, tax debit, and tax credit for a period can be viewed in the "
"tax return report and used to file a tax return."
msgstr ""
"Skupno osnovo, davčni dolg in davčni dobropis za obdobje si lahko ogledate v "
"poročilu o davčni napovedi in uporabite za oddajo davčne napovedi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:23
msgid "Taxes on sales and purchases"
msgstr "Davki pri prodaji in nakupih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:25
msgid ""
"Most sales and purchase documents have a :guilabel:`Taxes` field where taxes "
"can be applied to individual lines. This includes :doc:`invoices "
"<customer_invoices>` and :doc:`vendor bills <vendor_bills>` in the "
"Accounting app, :doc:`sales quotations <../../sales/sales/sales_quotations>` "
"in the Sales app, and :doc:`purchase orders <../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"purchase/manage_deals/rfq>` in the Purchase app."
msgstr ""
"Večina dokumentov za prodajo in nabavo ima polje :guilabel:`Davki`, kjer je "
"mogoče davke uporabiti na posameznih vrsticah. To vključuje :doc:`račune "
"<customer_invoices>` in :doc:`račune dobaviteljev <vendor_bills>` v "
"aplikaciji Računovodstvo, :doc:`prodajne ponudbe <../../sales/sales/"
"sales_quotations>` v aplikaciji Prodaja in :doc:`nabavne naročilnice <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/purchase/manage_deals/rfq>` v aplikaciji Nabava."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Adding a 21% tax on an invoice line."
msgstr "Dodajanje 21% davka na vrstico računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:35
msgid ""
"When adding a product to a sale or purchase line, the taxes :ref:`assigned "
"to the product <taxes/product>` are automatically applied to the line."
msgstr ""
"Pri dodajanju izdelka v vrstico prodaje ali nabave se davki, :ref:`dodeljeni "
"izdelku <taxes/product>`, samodejno uporabijo na vrstici."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:38
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`Point of Sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>` app, the "
"taxes :ref:`assigned to the products <taxes/product>` are applied directly "
"to the order and cannot be changed except by a :doc:`fiscal position <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji :doc:`Prodajna točka <../../sales/point_of_sale>` se davki, "
":ref:`dodeljeni izdelkom <taxes/product>`, uporabijo neposredno na naročilo "
"in jih ni mogoče spremeniti, razen z :doc:`davčnim položajem <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:43
msgid "Automatic computation of tax amounts"
msgstr "Samodejni izračun zneskov davkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:45
msgid ""
"Applying a tax to a sale or purchase line allows Odoo to automatically "
"compute the tax amount based on the sale or purchase line's subtotal and the "
"tax's configuration. The details of the computation are explained in "
"the :doc:`Tax computation documentation <taxes/tax_computation>`."
msgstr ""
"Použití daně na prodejní nebo nákupní řádek umožňuje Odoo automaticky "
"vypočítat částku daně na základě mezisoučtu prodejního nebo nákupního řádku "
"a konfigurace daně. Podrobnosti výpočtu jsou vysvětleny v :doc:`dokumentaci "
"k výpočtu daně <taxes/tax_computation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "Odoo automatically computes a tax amount for the 21% tax."
msgstr "Odoo samodejno izračuna znesek davka za 21% davek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:53
msgid "Automatic generation of tax journal items"
msgstr "Samodejno ustvarjanje postavk dnevnika za davke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:55
msgid ""
"Upon applying a tax on an :doc:`invoice <customer_invoices>` or :doc:`vendor "
"bill <vendor_bills>`, a tax payable journal item is automatically generated "
"with the tax amount. This keeps track of the tax debit or credit associated "
"with the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi davka na :doc:`računu <customer_invoices>` ali :doc:`računu "
"dobavitelja <vendor_bills>` se samodejno ustvari postavka dnevnika za davek, "
"ki ga je treba plačati, z zneskom davka. To omogoča sledenje davčnemu dolgu "
"ali dobropisu, povezanemu s transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:59
msgid ""
"Furthermore, the tax amount is added to the amount due on the receivable or "
"payable journal item."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega se znesek davka doda k dolgovanemu znesku na postavki dnevnika za "
"terjatve ali obveznosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:61
msgid ""
"Finally, :ref:`Tax Grids <accounting/tax-returns/tax-grids>` are added both "
"to the automatically created tax payable journal item and to the invoice "
"line on which the tax is applied. These tags are used to retrieve the "
"journal items corresponding to the tax's base and tax amount in "
"the :doc:`Tax Return <reporting/tax_returns>` report."
msgstr ""
"Nakonec se :ref:`daňové mřížky <accounting/tax-returns/tax-grids>` přidají "
"jak k automaticky vytvořené položce deníku daně splatné, tak k řádku "
"faktury, na kterém je daň uplatněna. Tyto štítky se používají k načtení "
"položek deníku odpovídajících základu daně a částce daně v přehledu "
":doc:`daňového přiznání <reporting/tax_returns>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically generates a tax payable journal item for the 21% tax."
msgstr "Odoo automaticky vytvoří položku deníku daně splatné pro 21% daň."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:70
msgid ""
"If :doc:`Cash Basis <taxes/cash_basis>` is enabled, upon reconciling the "
"invoice or vendor bill with the payment, an additional journal entry is "
"created to represent the creation of the tax debit or credit at that point "
"in time."
msgstr ""
"Pokud je povolena možnost :doc:`peněžní báze <taxes/cash_basis>`, po "
"vyrovnání faktury nebo faktury dodavatele s platbou se vytvoří další zápis v "
"deníku, který reprezentuje vznik daňového závazku nebo pohledávky v daném "
"okamžiku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:75
msgid "Filing tax returns"
msgstr "Podávání daňových přiznání"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:77
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Tax Return <reporting/tax_returns>` report aggregates the base and "
"tax amounts from invoices and vendor bills over a given period and presents "
"it in a format tailored to the :doc:`fiscal localization <../"
"fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Přehled :doc:`daňového přiznání <reporting/tax_returns>` agreguje základy a "
"částky daně z faktur a faktur dodavatelů za dané období a prezentuje je ve "
"formátu přizpůsobeném :doc:`fiskální lokalizaci <../fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:81
msgid ""
"The amounts presented in the tax return report can be used to complete tax "
"declarations that need to be periodically submitted to the government. In "
"most cases, there is a one-to-one correspondence between the lines of the "
"tax return and the official tax declaration, allowing amounts to simply be "
"copied from one to the other."
msgstr ""
"Částky uvedené v přehledu daňového přiznání lze použít k vyplnění daňových "
"přiznání, která je nutné pravidelně podávat vládě. Ve většině případů "
"existuje vzájemný vztah jeden k jednomu mezi řádky daňového přiznání a "
"oficiálního daňového přiznání, což umožňuje jednoduše zkopírovat částky z "
"jednoho do druhého."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The base section of the tax return report for Belgium."
msgstr "Sekce základu v přehledu daňového přiznání pro Belgii."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:None
msgid "The tax section of the tax return report for Belgium."
msgstr "Sekce daně v přehledu daňového přiznání pro Belgii."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:95
msgid "Basic tax configuration"
msgstr "Základní konfigurace daní"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:97
msgid "Follow these basic steps to set up taxes:"
msgstr "Pro nastavení daní postupujte podle těchto základních kroků:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:99
msgid ""
"Enable any relevant :ref:`company-wide options <taxes/configuration/"
"company>`."
msgstr ""
"Povolte všechny relevantní :ref:`možnosti platné pro celou společnost <taxes/"
"configuration/company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:100
msgid ""
"Activate any needed :ref:`pre-configured taxes <taxes/list_activation>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivujte všechny potřebné :ref:`předkonfigurované daně <taxes/"
"list_activation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:101
msgid "Assign taxes on your :ref:`products <taxes/product>`."
msgstr "Přiřaďte daně k vašim :ref:`výrobkům <taxes/product>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:106
msgid "Company-wide options"
msgstr "Možnosti pro celou společnost"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:108
msgid ""
"To access these configuration options, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and scroll down to :guilabel:`Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Pro přístup k těmto možnostem konfigurace přejděte do "
":menuselection:`Účetnictví --> Konfigurace --> Nastavení` a posuňte se dolů "
"do sekce :guilabel:`Daně`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:116
msgid ""
"The default :guilabel:`Sales Tax` and :guilabel:`Purchase Tax` are "
"automatically set on products when creating new products."
msgstr ""
"Výchozí :guilabel:`prodejní daň` a :guilabel:`nákupní daň` se automaticky "
"nastaví u produktů při vytváření nových produktů."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:119
msgid ""
"If :ref:`Accounting Firms <accounting/fiduciaries>` mode is enabled, the "
"default sales tax is automatically set on new invoice lines, and the default "
"purchase tax is automatically set on new vendor bill lines."
msgstr ""
"Pokud je povolen režim :ref:`účetních firem <accounting/fiduciaries>`, "
"výchozí prodejní daň se automaticky nastaví na nových řádcích faktury a "
"výchozí nákupní daň se automaticky nastaví na nových řádcích faktury "
"dodavatele."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prices` can be changed to :guilabel:`Tax Included` to treat all "
"taxes as :ref:`tax included <taxes/included-in-price>` by default. This "
"would be appropriate if all of a company's pricing is done tax-included. If "
"only some of a company's pricing is tax-included, individual taxes can be "
"set as :guilabel:`Tax Included`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ceny` lze změnit na :guilabel:`včetně daně`, aby se všechny daně "
"ve výchozím nastavení považovaly za :ref:`ceny včetně daně <taxes/included-"
"in-price>`. To by bylo vhodné, pokud se veškeré ceny společnosti tvoří "
"včetně daně. Pokud jsou jen některé ceny společnosti uvedeny včetně daně, "
"lze jednotlivé daně nastavit jako :guilabel:`včetně daně`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:129
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:3
msgid "EU intra-community distance selling"
msgstr "Medskupnostna prodaja na daljavo znotraj EU"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:131
msgid ""
"Activate this option if you are based in the EU and sell to consumers in "
"other EU countries to apply local VAT rates."
msgstr ""
"Aktivujte tuto možnost, pokud máte sídlo v EU a prodáváte spotřebitelům v "
"jiných zemích EU, abyste použili místní sazby DPH."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:135
msgid ":doc:`EU intra-community distance selling<taxes/eu_distance_selling>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Prodej na dálku uvnitř Společenství EU<taxes/eu_distance_selling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:138
msgid "Cash basis"
msgstr "Peněžní báze"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:140
msgid ""
"Activate this option if taxes must be accounted for on a cash rather than "
"accruals basis. Some countries mandate cash basis accounting; in that case, "
"this option will be activated by default by the :doc:`fiscal localization "
"package <../fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"Aktivujte tuto možnost, pokud musí být daně účtovány na peněžní bázi spíše "
"než na akruální bázi. Některé země vyžadují účetnictví na peněžní bázi; v "
"takovém případě bude tato možnost ve výchozím nastavení aktivována "
":doc:`balíčkem fiskální lokalizace <../fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:145
msgid ":doc:`Cash basis <taxes/cash_basis>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Peněžní báze <taxes/cash_basis>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:150
msgid "Activate pre-configured taxes"
msgstr "Aktiviraj vnaprej konfigurirane davke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:152
msgid ""
"The list of taxes can be accessed by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Seznam davkov je dostopen prek :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Davki`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:155
msgid ""
"Generally, inactive taxes are created for most sales tax rates by "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../fiscal_localizations>` package, but only "
"the main tax rate is active by default. To activate an inactive tax, click "
"the toggle in the :guilabel:`Active` column."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno so neaktivni davki ustvarjeni za večino stopenj prometnega davka "
"s paketom :doc:`fiskalne lokalizacije <../fiscal_localizations>`, vendar je "
"privzeto aktivna samo glavna davčna stopnja. Za aktiviranje neaktivnega "
"davka kliknite stikalo v stolpcu :guilabel:`Aktiven`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:162
msgid "Assign taxes on products"
msgstr "Dodelitev davkov izdelkom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:164
msgid ""
"To configure the taxes used for each product, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Products`, select the "
"product to configure, and fill the :guilabel:`Sales Taxes` "
"and :guilabel:`Purchase Taxes` fields. These taxes are automatically applied "
"when adding the product to an invoice, vendor bill, sales order, purchase "
"order, or point of sale order."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo davkov, ki se uporabljajo za posamezen izdelek, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Izdelki`, izberite izdelek za "
"konfiguracijo in izpolnite polji :guilabel:`Prodajni davki` in "
":guilabel:`Nabavni davki`. Ti davki se samodejno uporabijo pri dodajanju "
"izdelka na fakturo, dobaviteljski račun, prodajni nalog, nabavni nalog ali "
"naročilo na prodajni točki."

