msgstr ":doc:`avatax_use`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:3
msgid "AvaTax use"
msgstr "Uporaba AvaTax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:5
msgid ""
"AvaTax is a tax calculation software that can be integrated with Odoo in the "
"United States and Canada. Once the :doc:`integration setup <../avatax>` is "
"complete, the calculated tax is simple and automatic."
msgstr ""
"AvaTax je programska oprema za izračun davkov, ki jo je mogoče integrirati z "
"Odoo v Združenih državah Amerike in Kanadi. Ko je :doc:`nastavitev "
"integracije <../avatax>` končana, je izračun davka preprost in samodejen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:12
msgid "Tax calculation"
msgstr "Izračun davka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:14
msgid ""
"Automatically calculate taxes on Odoo quotations and invoices with AvaTax by "
"confirming the documents during the sales flow. Alternatively, calculate the "
"taxes manually by clicking the :guilabel:`Compute Taxes` button, while these "
"documents are in draft stage."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno izračunajte davke na ponudbah in računih Odoo z AvaTax s "
"potrditvijo dokumentov med prodajnim postopkom. Druga možnost je, da davke "
"izračunate ročno s klikom na gumb :guilabel:`Izračunaj davke`, medtem ko so "
"ti dokumenti v osnutku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:19
msgid ""
"Clicking the :guilabel:`Compute Taxes` button recalculates taxes, if any "
"product lines are edited on the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Klik na gumb :guilabel:`Izračunaj davke` ponovno izračuna davke, če so na "
"računu urejene katere koli vrstice izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:None
msgid "Sales quotation with the confirm and compute taxes button highlighted."
msgstr "Prodajna ponudba s označenima gumboma za potrditev in izračun davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:26
msgid ""
"The tax calculation is triggered during the following :ref:`automatic "
"trigger <avatax/automatic-triggers>` and :ref:`manual trigger <avatax/manual-"
"triggers>` circumstances."
msgstr ""
"Izračun davka se sproži ob naslednjih okoliščinah :ref:`samodejnega "
"sprožilca <avatax/automatic-triggers>` in :ref:`ročnega sprožilca <avatax/"
"manual-triggers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:32
msgid "Automatic triggers"
msgstr "Samodejni sprožilci"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:34
msgid ""
"When the sales rep sends the quote by email with :guilabel:`Send by email` "
"button (pop-up)."
msgstr ""
"Ko prodajni predstavnik pošlje ponudbo po e-pošti z gumbom :guilabel:`Pošlji "
"po e-pošti` (pojavno okno)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:35
msgid "When the customer views the online quote on the portal."
msgstr "Ko stranka ogleda spletno ponudbo na portalu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:36
msgid "When a quote is confirmed and becomes a sales order."
msgstr "Ko je ponudba potrjena in postane prodajni nalog."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:37
msgid "When the customer views the invoice on the portal."
msgstr "Ko stranka ogleda račun na portalu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:38
msgid "When a draft invoice is validated."
msgstr "Ko je osnutek računa potrjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:39
msgid "When the customer views the subscription in the portal."
msgstr "Ko stranka ogleda naročnino na portalu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:40
msgid "When a subscription generates an invoice."
msgstr "Ko naročnina ustvari račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:41
msgid "When the customer gets to the last screen of the eCommerce checkout."
msgstr "Ko stranka pride do zadnjega zaslona blagajne e-trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:46
msgid "Manual triggers"
msgstr "Ročni sprožilci"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:48
msgid ":guilabel:`Compute Taxes` button at the bottom of the quote."
msgstr "gumb :guilabel:`Izračunaj davke` na dnu ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:49
msgid ":guilabel:`Compute Taxes` button at the top of the invoice."
msgstr "gumb :guilabel:`Izračunaj davke` na vrhu računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:51
msgid "Use each of these buttons to manually re-calculate the sales tax."
msgstr "Uporabite vsak od teh gumbov za ročni ponovni izračun davka od prometa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:54
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Avalara Partner Code` field that is available on customer "
"records, quotations, and invoices to cross-reference data in Odoo and "
"AvaTax. This field is located under the :menuselection:`Other info` tab of "
"the sales order or quotation in the :guilabel:`Sales` section."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite polje :guilabel:`Avalara Partner Code`, ki je na voljo na zapisih "
"strank, ponudbah in računih, za navzkrižno referenco podatkov v Odoo in "
"AvaTax. To polje se nahaja na zavihku :menuselection:`Druge informacije` "
"prodajnega naloga ali ponudbe v razdelku :guilabel:`Prodaja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:58
msgid ""
"On the customer record, navigate to *Contacts app* and select a contact. "
"Then open the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab and the :guilabel:`Avalara "
"Partner Code` under the :guilabel:`Sales` section."
msgstr ""
"Na zapisu stranke pojdite v *aplikacijo Stiki* in izberite stik. Nato "
"odprite zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja in nakup` in polje :guilabel:`Avalara "
"Partner Code` v razdelku :guilabel:`Prodaja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:63
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Automatic Tax Mapping (AvaTax)` fiscal position is also "
"applied on those Odoo documents, like subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Fiskalni položaj :guilabel:`Automatic Tax Mapping (AvaTax)` se prav tako "
"uporabi na teh dokumentih Odoo, kot so naročnine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:67
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:167
msgid ":doc:`../fiscal_positions`"
msgstr ":doc:`../fiscal_positions`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:70
msgid "AvaTax synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija AvaTax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:72
msgid ""
"Synchronization occurs with AvaTax, when the *invoice* is created in Odoo. "
"This means the sales tax is recorded with Avalara (AvaTax software "
"developer)."
msgstr ""
"Sinhronizacija z AvaTax se izvede, ko je *račun* ustvarjen v Odoo. To "
"pomeni, da je davek od prometa zabeležen pri Avalara (razvijalec programske "
"opreme AvaTax)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:75
msgid ""
"To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Quotations`. "
"Select a quotation from the list."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da pojdete na :menuselection:`aplikacija Prodaja --> "
"Naročila --> Ponudbe`. S seznama izberite ponudbo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:78
msgid ""
"After confirming a quotation and validating the delivery, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`. Indicate whether it is "
"a :guilabel:`Regular invoice`, :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, "
"or :guilabel:`Down payment (fixed amount)`."
msgstr ""
"Po potrditvi ponudbe in validaciji dostave kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"račun`. Navedite, ali gre za :guilabel:`Redni račun`, :guilabel:`Akontacijo "
"(odstotek)` ali :guilabel:`Akontacijo (fiksni znesek)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:82
msgid ""
"Then click :guilabel:`Create and view invoice`. The recorded taxes can be "
"seen in the :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab of the invoice. There will be "
"different taxes depending on the location of the :guilabel:`Delivery "
"Address`."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari in prikaži račun`. Zabeležene davke lahko "
"vidite na zavihku :guilabel:`Postavke dnevnika` računa. Glede na lokacijo "
":guilabel:`Naslova za dostavo` bodo različni davki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:None
msgid "Journal items highlighted on a invoice in Odoo."
msgstr "Postavke dnevnika, označene na računu v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:90
msgid ""
"Finally, press the :guilabel:`Confirm` button to complete the invoice and "
"synchronize with the AvaTax portal."
msgstr ""
"Končno pritisnite gumb :guilabel:`Potrdi` za dokončanje računa in "
"sinhronizacijo s portalom AvaTax."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:94
msgid ""
"An invoice cannot be :guilabel:`Reset to draft` because this causes de-"
"synchronization with the AvaTax Portal. Instead, click :guilabel:`Add credit "
"note` and state: `Sync with AvaTax Portal`. See this "
"documentation: :doc:`../../../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`."
msgstr ""
"Računa ni mogoče :guilabel:`Ponastaviti v osnutek`, ker to povzroči "
"desinhronizacijo s portalom AvaTax. Namesto tega kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"dobropis` in navedite: `Sync with AvaTax Portal`. Glejte to dokumentacijo: "
":doc:`../../../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:99
msgid "Fixed price discounts"
msgstr "Popusti s fiksno ceno"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:101
msgid ""
"Add a fixed price discount to a valuable customer, by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add a line` on the customer's invoice. Add the product "
"discount, and set the :guilabel:`Price` to either a positive or negative "
"value. To recalculate the taxes, click :guilabel:`Compute Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte popust s fiksno ceno pomembni stranki tako, da kliknete "
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` na računu stranke. Dodajte popust izdelka in "
"nastavite :guilabel:`Ceno` na pozitivno ali negativno vrednost. Za ponovni "
"izračun davkov kliknite :guilabel:`Izračunaj davke`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:106
msgid ""
"Tax calculation can even be done on negative subtotals and credit notes."
msgstr ""
"Izračun davka je mogoč tudi pri negativnih vmesnih seštevkih in dobropisih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:109
msgid "Logging"
msgstr "Beleženje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:111
msgid ""
"It is possible to log Avalara/*AvaTax* actions in Odoo for further analysis, "
"or verification of functionality. Logging is accessible through the *AvaTax* "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je beležiti dejanja Avalara/*AvaTax* v Odoo za nadaljnjo analizo ali "
"preverjanje funkcionalnosti. Beleženje je dostopno prek nastavitev *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:114
msgid ""
"To start logging *AvaTax* actions, first, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite začeti beležiti dejanja *AvaTax*, najprej pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:117
msgid ""
"Then, in the :guilabel:`Taxes` section, under the :guilabel:`AvaTax` "
"settings, click :guilabel:`Start logging for 30 minutes`."
msgstr ""
"Nato v razdelku :guilabel:`Davki` pod nastavitvami :guilabel:`AvaTax` "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Začni beležiti za 30 minut`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:120
msgid ""
"Upon starting the log process, Odoo will log all Avalara/*AvaTax* actions "
"performed in the database."
msgstr ""
"Ob začetku postopka beleženja bo Odoo beležil vsa dejanja Avalara/*AvaTax*, "
"izvedena v zbirki podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:122
msgid ""
"To view the logs, click on :guilabel:`Show logs` to the right of "
"the :guilabel:`Start logging for 30 minutes`. This reveals a detailed list "
"of Avalara/*AvaTax* actions. This list is sortable by the following columns:"
msgstr ""
"Za ogled dnevnikov kliknite na :guilabel:`Prikaži dnevnike` desno od "
":guilabel:`Začni beležiti za 30 minut`. S tem se prikaže podroben seznam "
"dejanj Avalara/*AvaTax*. Ta seznam je mogoče razvrstiti po naslednjih "
"stolpcih:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:126
msgid ":guilabel:`Created on`: timestamp of the *AvaTax* calculation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ustvarjeno`: časovni žig izračuna *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:127
msgid ":guilabel:`Created by`: numeric value of the user in the database."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ustvaril`: številčna vrednost uporabnika v zbirki podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:128
msgid ":guilabel:`Database name`: name of the database."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime zbirke podatkov`: ime zbirke podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: two values can be chosen for this "
"field, :guilabel:`Server` or :guilabel:`Client`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta`: za to polje je mogoče izbrati dve vrednosti, "
":guilabel:`Strežnik` ali :guilabel:`Odjemalec`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Name`: Avalara service name. In this case, it will be *AvaTax*."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime`: ime storitve Avalara. V tem primeru bo to *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:132
msgid ":guilabel:`Level`: by default, this will be `INFO`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Raven`: privzeto bo to `INFO`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:133
msgid ":guilabel:`Path`: indicates the path taken to make the calculation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pot`: označuje pot, uporabljeno za izračun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:134
msgid ":guilabel:`Line`: indicates the line the calculation is made on."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrstica`: označuje vrstico, v kateri se izvede izračun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:135
msgid ":guilabel:`Function`: indicates the calculation taken on the line."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Funkcija`: označuje izračun, izveden v vrstici."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:None
msgid "Avalara logging page with top row of list highlighted."
msgstr "Stran beleženja Avalara z označeno zgornjo vrstico seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:141
msgid ""
"Click into the log line to reveal another field, called :guilabel:`Message`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite v vrstico dnevnika, da se prikaže dodatno polje z imenom "
":guilabel:`Sporočilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:143
msgid ""
"This field populates a raw transcription of the transaction, which involves "
"the creation (or adjustment) of a sales invoice using the Avalara *AvaTax* "
"API."
msgstr ""
"To polje vsebuje neobdelan prepis transakcije, ki vključuje ustvarjanje (ali "
"prilagoditev) prodajnega računa z uporabo API-ja Avalara *AvaTax*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:146
msgid ""
"The transaction includes details, such as addresses for shipping from and "
"to, line items describing the products or services, tax codes, tax amounts, "
"and other relevant information."
msgstr ""
"Transakcija vključuje podrobnosti, kot so naslovi za pošiljanje od in do, "
"postavke, ki opisujejo izdelke ali storitve, davčne kode, davčne zneske in "
"druge ustrezne informacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:149
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Message` contains the calculated taxes for different "
"jurisdictions and confirms the creation (or adjustment) of the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Sporočilo` vsebuje izračunane davke za različne "
"jurisdikcije in potrjuje ustvarjanje (ali prilagoditev) transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:153
msgid ""
"Custom fields can be made using Odoo *Studio*. Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` menu to the far-right of the header row. Then "
"click :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Add custom field`. This action opens Odoo "
"*Studio*."
msgstr ""
"Polja po meri je mogoče ustvariti z uporabo Odoo *Studio*. Kliknite meni "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(tri pike)` na skrajni desni strani vrstice "
"z glavo. Nato kliknite :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Dodaj polje po meri`. To "
"dejanje odpre Odoo *Studio*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:158
msgid ""
"Odoo *Studio* requires a *custom* pricing plan. Consult the database's "
"customer success manager for more information on switching plans. Or to see "
"if Odoo *Studio* is included in the database's current pricing plan. See "
"this documentation: :doc:`../../../../studio`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo *Studio* zahteva cenovni načrt *po meri*. Za več informacij o preklopu "
"načrtov se posvetujte z vodjem za uspeh strank zbirke podatkov. Ali "
"preverite, ali je Odoo *Studio* vključen v trenutni cenovni načrt zbirke "
"podatkov. Oglejte si to dokumentacijo: :doc:`../../../../studio`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/avatax/avatax_use.rst:164
msgid ":doc:`avalara_portal`"
msgstr ":doc:`avalara_portal`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:3
msgid "Cash basis taxes"
msgstr "Davki na gotovinski osnovi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:5
msgid ""
"Cash basis taxes are due when the payment is made, as opposed to standard "
"taxes that are due when the invoice is confirmed. Reporting your income and "
"expenses to the government based on the cash basis method is mandatory in "
"some countries and under some conditions."
msgstr ""
"Davki na gotovinski osnovi so zapadli ob plačilu, za razliko od standardnih "
"davkov, ki so zapadli ob potrditvi računa. Poročanje o prihodkih in odhodkih "
"državi na podlagi gotovinskega načina je v nekaterih državah in pod "
"določenimi pogoji obvezno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:10
msgid ""
"You sell a product in the 1st quarter of your fiscal year, and the payment "
"is received in the 2nd quarter. Based on the cash basis method, the tax you "
"must pay is for the 2nd quarter."
msgstr ""
"Izdelek prodate v 1. četrtletju poslovnega leta, plačilo pa prejmete v 2. "
"četrtletju. Na podlagi gotovinskega načina morate davek plačati za 2. "
"četrtletje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:16
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and under "
"the :guilabel:`Taxes` section, enable :guilabel:`Cash Basis`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` "
"in v razdelku :guilabel:`Davki` omogočite :guilabel:`Gotovinska osnova`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:19
msgid ""
"Then, define the :guilabel:`Tax Cash Basis Journal`. Click on the external "
"link button next to the journal to update its default properties such as "
"the :guilabel:`Journal Name`, :guilabel:`Type` or :guilabel:`Short Code`."
msgstr ""
"Nato določite :guilabel:`Dnevnik davkov na gotovinski osnovi`. Kliknite gumb "
"za zunanjo povezavo poleg dnevnika, da posodobite njegove privzete "
"lastnosti, kot so :guilabel:`Ime dnevnika`, :guilabel:`Vrsta` ali "
":guilabel:`Kratka koda`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:None
msgid "Select your Tax Cash Basis Journal and click on the external link"
msgstr ""
"Izberite svoj dnevnik davkov na gotovinski osnovi in kliknite zunanjo "
"povezavo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:28
msgid ""
"By default, the journal entries of the :guilabel:`Cash Basis Taxes` journal "
"are named using the :guilabel:`CABA` short code."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so vnosi v dnevnik :guilabel:`Davki na gotovinski osnovi` "
"poimenovani s kratko kodo :guilabel:`CABA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:31
msgid ""
"Once this is done, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Accounting: Taxes` to configure your taxes. You can "
"either :guilabel:`Create` a new tax or update an existing one by clicking on "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to opravljeno, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Računovodstvo: Davki`, da konfigurirate svoje davke. Lahko "
":guilabel:`Ustvarite` nov davek ali posodobite obstoječega s klikom nanj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:35
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Account` column reflects the proper transitional accounts to "
"post taxes until the payment is registered."
msgstr ""
"Stolpec :guilabel:`Konto` odraža ustrezne prehodne konte za knjiženje "
"davkov, dokler ni plačilo registrirano."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:None
msgid ""
"Fill in the account column with a transitional accounts where taxes go until "
"the payment\n"
"is registered"
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite stolpec konto s prehodnimi konti, kamor gredo davki, dokler "
"plačilo ni\n"
"registrirano"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:43
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, decide of the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Exigilibity`. Select :guilabel:`Based on Payment`, so the tax is due when "
"the payment of the invoice is received. You can then also define "
"the :guilabel:`Cash Basis Transition Account` where the tax amount is "
"recorded as long as the original invoice has not been reconciled."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Napredne možnosti` se odločite o :guilabel:`Davčni "
"obveznosti`. Izberite :guilabel:`Na podlagi plačila`, tako da je davek "
"zapadel ob prejemu plačila računa. Nato lahko določite tudi "
":guilabel:`Prehodni konto gotovinske osnove`, kamor se znesek davka "
"zabeleži, dokler prvotni račun ni usklajen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:None
msgid ""
"Fill in the Cash Basis Transition Account where taxes amounts go until "
"payment\n"
"reconciliation."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite prehodni konto gotovinske osnove, kamor gredo zneski davkov do "
"uskladitve\n"
"plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:54
msgid "Impact of cash basis taxes on accounting"
msgstr "Vpliv davkov na gotovinski osnovi na računovodstvo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:56
msgid ""
"To illustrate the impact of cash basis taxes on accounting transactions, "
"let's take an example with the sales of a product that costs 1,000$, with a "
"cash basis tax of 15%."
msgstr ""
"Za ponazoritev vpliva davkov na gotovinski osnovi na računovodske "
"transakcije vzemimo primer s prodajo izdelka, ki stane 1.000 $, z davkom na "
"gotovinski osnovi 15 %."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:63
msgid ""
"The following entries are created in your accounting, and the tax report is "
"currently empty."
msgstr ""
"V vašem računovodstvu so ustvarjeni naslednji vnosi, davčno poročilo pa je "
"trenutno prazno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:66
msgid "**Customer journal (INV)**"
msgstr "**Dnevnik kupcev (INV)**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:70
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:86
msgid "Receivable $1,150"
msgstr "Terjatve 1.150 $"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:72
msgid "Income $1,000"
msgstr "Prihodki 1.000 $"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:74
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:103
msgid "Temporary tax account $150"
msgstr "Začasni davčni konto 150 $"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:77
msgid "When the payment is then received, it is registered as below :"
msgstr "Ko je plačilo nato prejeto, je registrirano kot spodaj:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:80
msgid "**Bank journal (BANK)**"
msgstr "**Bančni dnevnik (BANK)**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:84
msgid "Bank $1,150"
msgstr "Banka 1.150 $"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once the payment is registered, you can use the :guilabel:`Cash Basis "
"Entries` smart button on the invoice to access them directly."
msgstr ""
"Ko je plačilo registrirano, lahko uporabite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Vnosi na "
"gotovinski osnovi` na računu za neposreden dostop do njih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:93
msgid ""
"Finally, upon reconciliation of the invoice with the payment, the below "
"entry is automatically created:"
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje se ob uskladitvi računa s plačilom samodejno ustvari spodnji vnos:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:97
msgid "**Tax Cash Basis Journal (Caba)**"
msgstr "**Dnevnik gotovinske osnove DDV (Caba)**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:101
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:105
msgid "Income account $1,000"
msgstr "Prihodkovni račun 1.000 $"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:107
msgid "Tax Received $150"
msgstr "Prejeti DDV 150 $"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:110
msgid ""
"The journal items :guilabel:`Income account` vs. :guilabel:`Income account` "
"are neutral, but they are needed to ensure correct tax reports in Odoo with "
"accurate base tax amounts."
msgstr ""
"Postavke dnevnika :guilabel:`Prihodkovni račun` proti :guilabel:`Prihodkovni "
"račun` so nevtralne, vendar so potrebne za zagotovitev pravilnih davčnih "
"poročil v Odooju z natančnimi osnovnimi davčnimi zneski."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis.rst:113
msgid ""
"Using a default :guilabel:`Base Tax Received Account` is recommended so your "
"balance is at zero and your income account is not polluted by unnecessary "
"accounting movements. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> "
"Settings --> Taxes`, and select a :guilabel:`Base Tax Received Account` "
"under :guilabel:`Cash Basis`."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je uporabiti privzeti :guilabel:`Račun prejetega osnovnega "
"davka`, da bo vaše stanje na ničli in vaš prihodkovni račun ne bo onesnažen "
"z nepotrebnimi računovodskimi gibanji. Za to pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve --> Davki` in izberite "
":guilabel:`Račun prejetega osnovnega davka` pod :guilabel:`Gotovinska "
"osnova`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:5
msgid ""
"EU intra-community distance selling involves the cross-border trade of goods "
"and services from vendors registered for VAT purposes to individuals (B2C) "
"located in a European Union member state. The transaction is conducted "
"remotely, typically through online platforms, mail orders, telephone, or "
"other means of communication."
msgstr ""
"Medskupnostna prodaja na daljavo znotraj EU vključuje čezmejno trgovino z "
"blagom in storitvami od prodajalcev, registriranih za namene DDV, "
"posameznikom (B2C), ki se nahajajo v državi članici Evropske unije. "
"Transakcija se izvaja na daljavo, običajno prek spletnih platform, poštnih "
"naročil, telefona ali drugih komunikacijskih sredstev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:10
msgid ""
"EU intra-community distance selling is subject to specific VAT rules and "
"regulations. The vendor must charge VAT per the VAT rate applicable in the "
"buyer's country."
msgstr ""
"Medskupnostna prodaja na daljavo znotraj EU je predmet specifičnih pravil in "
"predpisov o DDV. Prodajalec mora zaračunati DDV glede na stopnjo DDV, ki "
"velja v državi kupca."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:14
msgid ""
"This remains applicable even if the vendor is located outside of the "
"European Union."
msgstr "To velja tudi, če se prodajalec nahaja zunaj Evropske unije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:19
msgid ""
"The **EU Intra-community Distance Selling** feature helps you comply with "
"this regulation by creating and configuring new **fiscal positions** and "
"**taxes** based on your company's country. To enable it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings --> Taxes`, "
"tick :guilabel:`EU Intra-community Distance Selling`, and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija **Medskupnostna prodaja na daljavo znotraj EU** vam pomaga pri "
"skladnosti s tem predpisom z ustvarjanjem in konfiguracijo novih **davčnih "
"položajev** in **davkov** na podlagi države vašega podjetja. Za omogočanje "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve --> Davki`, označite :guilabel:`Medskupnostna prodaja na daljavo "
"znotraj EU` in :guilabel:`Shranite`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:None
msgid "EU intra-community Distance Selling feature in Odoo Accounting settings"
msgstr ""
"Funkcija medskupnostne prodaje na daljavo znotraj EU v nastavitvah Odoo "
"Računovodstva"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:28
msgid ""
"Whenever you add or modify taxes, you can automatically update your fiscal "
"positions. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting/Invoicing --> Settings "
"--> Taxes --> EU Intra-community Distance Selling` and click on "
"the :guilabel:`Refresh tax mapping`."
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli dodate ali spremenite davke, lahko samodejno posodobite svoje "
"davčne položaje. Za to pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo/"
"Fakturiranje --> Nastavitve --> Davki --> Medskupnostna prodaja na daljavo "
"znotraj EU` in kliknite na :guilabel:`Osveži preslikavo davkov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:33
msgid ""
"We highly recommend checking that the proposed mapping is suitable for the "
"products and services you sell before using it."
msgstr ""
"Toplo priporočamo, da preverite, ali je predlagana preslikava primerna za "
"izdelke in storitve, ki jih prodajate, preden jo uporabite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:42
msgid "One-Stop Shop (OSS)"
msgstr "Enotna točka (OSS)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:44
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`OSS (One-Stop Shop)` system introduced by the European Union "
"simplifies VAT collection for **cross-border** sales of goods and services. "
"It primarily applies to business-to-consumer **(B2C)** cases. With the OSS, "
"businesses can register for VAT in their home country and use a single "
"online portal to handle VAT obligations for their sales within the EU. There "
"are **two primary schemes**: the **Union OSS** scheme for cross-border "
"services and the **Import OSS** scheme for goods valued at or below €150."
msgstr ""
"Sistem :abbr:`OSS (One-Stop Shop)`, ki ga je uvedla Evropska unija, "
"poenostavlja pobiranje DDV za **čezmejno** prodajo blaga in storitev. "
"Predvsem velja za primere **poslovanje s potrošniki (B2C)**. Z OSS se lahko "
"podjetja registrirajo za DDV v svoji domači državi in uporabljajo en sam "
"spletni portal za obravnavo obveznosti DDV za svojo prodajo znotraj EU. "
"Obstajata **dve primarni shemi**: shema **Union OSS** za čezmejne storitve "
"in shema **Import OSS** za blago, vredno 150 € ali manj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:54
msgid ""
"To generate **OSS sales** or **OSS imports** reports and submit them onto "
"the OSS portal, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax "
"Report`, click :guilabel:`Report: Generic Tax report`, and select "
"either :guilabel:`OSS Sales` or :guilabel:`OSS Imports`. Once selected, "
"click on :guilabel:`PDF`, :guilabel:`XLSX`, or :guilabel:`XML` in the top-"
"left corner. This generates the currently-opened report in the selected "
"format. Once generated, log into the platform of your competent federal "
"authority to submit it onto the OSS portal."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje poročil **OSS prodaja** ali **OSS uvoz** ter njihovo "
"predložitev na portal OSS pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročanje --> Davčno poročilo`, kliknite :guilabel:`Poročilo: Splošno davčno "
"poročilo` in izberite :guilabel:`OSS prodaja` ali :guilabel:`OSS uvoz`. Po "
"izbiri kliknite :guilabel:`PDF`, :guilabel:`XLSX` ali :guilabel:`XML` v "
"zgornjem levem kotu. S tem ustvarite trenutno odprto poročilo v izbranem "
"formatu. Po ustvarjanju se prijavite na platformo pristojnega zveznega "
"organa in ga predložite na portal OSS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:None
msgid "OSS reports view"
msgstr "Prikaz poročil OSS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/eu_distance_selling.rst:65
msgid ""
"`European Commission: OSS | Taxation and Customs Union <https://ec.europa.eu/"
"taxation_customs/business/vat/oss_en>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Evropska komisija: OSS | Obdavčitev in carinska unija <https://ec.europa.eu/"
"taxation_customs/business/vat/oss_en>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:3
msgid "Fiscal positions (tax and account mapping)"
msgstr "Davčni položaji (preslikava davkov in računov)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:5
msgid ""
"Default taxes and accounts are set on products and customers to create new "
"transactions on the fly. However, depending on the customers' and vendors' "
"location and business type, using different taxes and accounts for a "
"transaction might be necessary."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti davki in računi so nastavljeni na izdelkih in strankah za hitro "
"ustvarjanje novih transakcij. Vendar je glede na lokacijo in vrsto "
"poslovanja strank in dobaviteljev morda potrebno uporabiti različne davke in "
"račune za transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Fiscal positions** allow the creation of rules to adapt the taxes and the "
"income and expense accounts used for a transaction automatically."
msgstr ""
"**Fiskalni položaji** omogočajo ustvarjanje pravil za samodejno prilagoditev "
"davkov ter prihodkovnih in odhodkovnih računov, uporabljenih za transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:12
msgid ""
"They can be applied :ref:`automatically <fiscal_positions/"
"automatic>`, :ref:`manually <fiscal_positions/manual>`, or :ref:`assigned to "
"a partner <accounting/fiscal_positions/partner>`."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljajo se lahko :ref:`samodejno <fiscal_positions/automatic>`, "
":ref:`ročno <fiscal_positions/manual>` ali :ref:`dodeljeno partnerju "
"<accounting/fiscal_positions/partner>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:16
msgid ""
"Several default fiscal positions are available as part of your :ref:`fiscal "
"localization package <fiscal_localizations/packages>`."
msgstr ""
"Več privzetih davčnih položajev je na voljo kot del vašega :ref:`paketa "
"davčne lokalizacije <fiscal_localizations/packages>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:24
msgid ""
"To edit or create a fiscal position, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Fiscal Positions`, and open the record to modify or "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Za urejanje ali ustvarjanje fiskalnega položaja pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Fiskalni položaji`, "
"odprite zapis za urejanje ali kliknite :guilabel:`Nov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:28
msgid ""
"If any notes are legally required when using this fiscal position, add them "
"in the :guilabel:`Legal Notes...` field below the :ref:`tax mapping "
"<fiscal_positions/tax-mapping>` section to display them on quotations, sales "
"orders, invoices, and bills."
msgstr ""
"Če so pri uporabi tega fiskalnega položaja zakonsko zahtevane kakršne koli "
"opombe, jih dodajte v polje :guilabel:`Pravne opombe...` pod razdelkom "
":ref:`preslikava davkov <fiscal_positions/tax-mapping>`, da se prikažejo na "
"ponudbah, prodajnih nalogih, računih in dobaviteljih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:37
msgid ""
"Fiscal positions are required to map taxes. :ref:`Tax mapping <taxes/tax-"
"mapping>` is configured on taxes themselves."
msgstr ""
"Fiskalne pozicije so potrebne za preslikavo davkov. :ref:`Preslikava davkov "
"<taxes/tax-mapping>` je konfigurirana na samih davkih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:43
msgid "Account mapping"
msgstr "Preslikava kontov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:45
msgid ""
"Account mapping is based on the income and expense accounts defined on the "
"product or product category. To map to another account, select the account "
"to be replaced in the left column (:guilabel:`Account on Product`) and "
"select the account to use instead in the right column (:guilabel:`Account to "
"Use Instead`)."
msgstr ""
"Preslikava kontov temelji na kontih prihodkov in odhodkov, določenih na "
"izdelku ali kategoriji izdelka. Za preslikavo na drug kont izberite kont, ki "
"ga želite zamenjati, v levem stolpcu (:guilabel:`Kont na izdelku`) in "
"izberite kont, ki ga želite namesto tega uporabiti, v desnem stolpcu "
"(:guilabel:`Kont za uporabo namesto tega`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:None
msgid "Example of a fiscal position's account mapping"
msgstr "Primer preslikave računov davčnega položaja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:54
msgid "Application"
msgstr "Aplikacija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:59
msgid "Automatic application"
msgstr "Samodejna uporaba"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:61
msgid ""
"To automatically apply a fiscal position following a set of conditions, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Fiscal Positions`, open "
"the fiscal position to modify, and tick :guilabel:`Detect Automatically`."
msgstr ""
"Za samodejno uporabo davčnega položaja glede na nabor pogojev pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Davčni položaji`, "
"odprite davčni položaj za spremembo in označite :guilabel:`Zaznavaj "
"samodejno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:65
msgid "From there, several conditions can be activated:"
msgstr "Od tam je mogoče aktivirati več pogojev:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`VAT Required`: the customer's VAT number must be present on their "
"contact form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obvezna DDV številka`: DDV številka stranke mora biti prisotna na "
"njenem kontaktnem obrazcu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Country Group` and :guilabel:`Country`: the fiscal position is "
"only applied to the selected country or country group."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skupina držav` in :guilabel:`Država`: davčni položaj se uporabi "
"samo za izbrano državo ali skupino držav."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:None
msgid "Example of a fiscal position automatic application settings"
msgstr "Primer nastavitev samodejne uporabe davčnega položaja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:75
msgid ""
"If the :doc:`Verify VAT Numbers <vat_verification>` feature is enabled, any "
"fiscal positions with :guilabel:`VAT required` enabled will require Intra-"
"Community valid VAT numbers to apply automatically."
msgstr ""
"Če je funkcija :doc:`Preverjanje DDV številk <vat_verification>` omogočena, "
"bodo vsi davčni položaji z omogočeno možnostjo :guilabel:`Obvezna DDV "
"številka` za samodejno uporabo zahtevali veljavne znotrajskupnostne DDV "
"številke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:78
msgid ""
"Taxes on **eCommerce orders** are automatically updated once the customer "
"has logged in or filled out their billing details."
msgstr ""
"Davki pri **naročilih eCommerce** se samodejno posodobijo, ko se stranka "
"prijavi ali izpolni svoje podatke za obračun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:82
msgid ""
"The fiscal positions' **sequence** defines which fiscal position is applied "
"if all conditions set on multiple fiscal positions are met simultaneously."
msgstr ""
"**Zaporedje** davčnih položajev določa, kateri davčni položaj se uporabi, če "
"so hkrati izpolnjeni vsi pogoji, nastavljeni za več davčnih položajev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:85
msgid ""
"For example, suppose the first fiscal position in a sequence targets "
"*country A* while the second fiscal position targets a *country group* that "
"comprises *country A*. In that case, only the first fiscal position will be "
"applied to customers from *country A*."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če prvi davčni položaj v zaporedju cilja na *državo A*, drugi "
"davčni položaj pa cilja na *skupino držav*, ki vključuje *državo A*, se bo "
"za stranke iz *države A* uporabil samo prvi davčni položaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:92
msgid "Manual application"
msgstr "Ročna uporaba"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:94
msgid ""
"To manually select a fiscal position, open a sales order, purchase order, "
"invoice, or bill, go to the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and select the "
"desired :guilabel:`Fiscal Position` before adding product lines."
msgstr ""
"Za ročno izbiro fiskalne pozicije odprite prodajni nalog, nabavni nalog, "
"fakturo ali račun, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Druge informacije` in "
"izberite želeno :guilabel:`Fiskalno pozicijo`, preden dodate vrstice "
"izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:None
msgid "Selection of a fiscal position on a sales order, invoice, or bill"
msgstr ""
"Izbira davčnega položaja na prodajnem nalogu, računu ali dobaviteljevem "
"računu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:104
msgid "Assign to a partner"
msgstr "Dodelitev partnerju"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:106
msgid ""
"To define which fiscal position must be used by default for a specific "
"partner, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`, "
"select the partner, open the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, and select "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Position`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite določiti, kateri davčni položaj je treba privzeto uporabiti za "
"določenega partnerja, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Stranke --> Stranke`, izberite partnerja, odprite zavihek :guilabel:`Prodaja "
"in nabava` ter izberite :guilabel:`Davčni položaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:None
msgid "Selection of a fiscal position on a customer"
msgstr "Izbira davčnega položaja pri stranki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:114
msgid ""
"To view all partners at once instead of only customers, remove "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` filter or use the **Contacts** application."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti vse partnerje hkrati namesto samo strank, odstranite filter "
":guilabel:`Računi strankam` ali uporabite aplikacijo **Stiki**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions.rst:120
msgid ":doc:`B2B_B2C`"
msgstr ":doc:`B2B_B2C`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:137
msgid "Withholding taxes"
msgstr "Akontacijski davki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:5
msgid ""
"A **withholding tax**, also known as retention tax, mandates the payer of a "
"customer invoice to deduct a tax from the payment and remit it to the "
"government. Typically, a tax is included in the subtotal to calculate the "
"total amount paid, while withholding taxes are directly subtracted from the "
"payment."
msgstr ""
"**Akontacijski davek**, znan tudi kot retencijski davek, nalašča plačniku "
"računa stranke, da od plačila odbije davek in ga nakaže državi. Običajno je "
"davek vključen v vmesni seštevek za izračun skupnega plačanega zneska, "
"medtem ko se akontacijski davki odbijejo neposredno od plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Odoo, a withholding tax is defined by creating a negative tax. To create "
"one, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes` and, in "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` field, enter a negative amount."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo je akontacijski davek določen z ustvarjanjem negativnega davka. Za "
"ustvarjanje pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Davki` in v polje :guilabel:`Znesek` vnesite negativni znesek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:None
msgid "negative tax amount in field"
msgstr "negativni davek v polju"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:20
msgid ""
"Then, go to the :menuselection:`Advanced Options` tab and create a "
"retention :guilabel:`Tax Group`."
msgstr ""
"Nato pojdite na zavihek :menuselection:`Napredne možnosti` in ustvarite "
"retencijsko :guilabel:`Davčno skupino`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:None
msgid "tax group for retention tax."
msgstr "davčna skupina za retencijski davek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:26
msgid ""
"If the retention is a percentage of a regular tax, create a :guilabel:`Tax` "
"with a :guilabel:`Tax Computation` as a :guilabel:`Group of Taxes`. Then, "
"set both the regular tax and the retention one in the :guilabel:`Definition` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Če je retencija odstotek običajnega davka, ustvarite :guilabel:`Davek` z "
":guilabel:`Izračunom davka` kot :guilabel:`Skupino davkov`. Nato nastavite "
"tako običajni davek kot retencijskega na zavihku :guilabel:`Definicija`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:31
msgid "Retention taxes on invoices"
msgstr "Retencijski davki na računih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:33
msgid ""
"Once the retention tax has been created, it can be used on customer forms, "
"sales orders, and customer invoices. Several taxes can be applied on a "
"single customer invoice line."
msgstr ""
"Ko je retencijski davek ustvarjen, ga je mogoče uporabiti na obrazcih "
"strank, prodajnih nalogčilih in računih za stranke. Na eni vrstici računa "
"stranke je mogoče uporabiti več davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/retention.rst:None
msgid "invoice lines with taxes"
msgstr "vrstice računa z davki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:8
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:413
msgid "Tax computation"
msgstr "Izračun davka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:10
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tax Computation` field determines the relation between the "
"tax amount and the base the tax is based on. The following options are "
"available:"
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Izračun davka` določa razmerje med zneskom davka in osnovo, "
"na kateri temelji davek. Na voljo so naslednje možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:13
msgid ""
":ref:`Group of Taxes <taxes/computation/group-of-taxes>`: a combination of "
"several other taxes"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Skupina davkov <taxes/computation/group-of-taxes>`: kombinacija več "
"drugih davkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`Fixed <taxes/computation/fixed>`: a fixed amount"
msgstr ":ref:`Fiksno <taxes/computation/fixed>`: fiksni znesek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:15
msgid ""
":ref:`Percentage of Price <taxes/computation/percentage-of-price>`: a "
"percentage of the tax-excluded sales price"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odstotek cene <taxes/computation/percentage-of-price>`: odstotek "
"prodajne cene brez davka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:17
msgid ""
":ref:`Percentage of Price Tax Included <taxes/computation/percentage-of-"
"price-tax-included>`: a percentage of the tax-included total"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odstotek cene z vključenim davkom <taxes/computation/percentage-of-"
"price-tax-included>`: odstotek skupnega zneska z vključenim davkom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:19
msgid ""
":ref:`Custom Formula <taxes/computation/python-code>`: a custom, user-"
"defined formula"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Formula po meri <taxes/computation/python-code>`: formula, ki jo "
"določi uporabnik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:24
msgid "Group of taxes"
msgstr "Skupina davkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:26
msgid ""
"The tax is a combination of multiple sub-taxes. You can add as many taxes as "
"you want, in the order you want them to be applied."
msgstr ""
"Davek je kombinacija več poddavkov. Dodate lahko toliko davkov, kot želite, "
"v vrstnem redu, v katerem jih želite uporabiti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:30
msgid ""
"Make sure the tax sequence is correct, as the display order determines the "
"application order and may affect tax computation, particularly if a "
"tax :ref:`affects the base of subsequent taxes <taxes/base-subsequent>`."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je zaporedje davkov pravilno, saj vrstni red prikaza "
"določa vrstni red uporabe in lahko vpliva na izračun davka, še posebej če "
"davek :ref:`vpliva na osnovo naslednjih davkov <taxes/base-subsequent>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:37
msgid "Fixed"
msgstr "Fiksno"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:39
msgid ""
