msgid ""
"Note that the real tax rate in terms of the tax-excluded price "
"is :math:`\\frac{111.11}{1000} = 11.111\\%`."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je dejanska davčna stopnja glede na ceno brez davka "
":math:`\\frac{111.11}{1000} = 11.111\\%`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:137
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Included in Price` is set to :guilabel:`Tax Included`, the "
"computation is :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{sales price} \\times "
"\\text{tax rate}`."
msgstr ""
"Če je :guilabel:`Included in Price` nastavljen na :guilabel:`Tax Included`, "
"je izračun :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{sales price} \\times \\text"
"{tax rate}`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:141
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price Tax Included` tax that is :guilabel:`Tax "
"Included`. We then have:"
msgstr ""
"Izdelek ima prodajno ceno $1000 in uporabimo 10% davek :guilabel:`Percentage "
"of Price Tax Included`, ki je :guilabel:`Tax Included`. Potem imamo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:149
msgid "900"
msgstr "900"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:152
msgid ""
"Note that the real tax rate in terms of the tax-excluded price "
"is :math:`\\frac{100}{900} = 11.111\\%`."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je dejanska davčna stopnja glede na ceno brez davka "
":math:`\\frac{100}{900} = 11.111\\%`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:158
msgid "Custom formula"
msgstr "Formula po meri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:161
msgid ""
"If a tax can be expressed as a multiple of the quantity of the product to "
"which it applies, it can be defined as a :ref:`Fixed <taxes/computation/"
"fixed>` tax. Doing so is strongly recommended over defining "
"a :guilabel:`Custom Formula` tax."
msgstr ""
"Če je davek mogoče izraziti kot večkratnik količine izdelka, na katerega se "
"nanaša, ga je mogoče definirati kot davek :ref:`Fixed <taxes/computation/"
"fixed>`. To je močno priporočljivo namesto definiranja davka "
":guilabel:`Custom Formula`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:166
msgid ""
"To use :guilabel:`Custom Formula` taxes, :ref:`install <general/install>` "
"the :guilabel:`Define Taxes as Python Code` (`account_python_tax`) module."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo davkov :guilabel:`Custom Formula` :ref:`namestite <general/"
"install>` modul :guilabel:`Define Taxes as Python Code` "
"(`account_python_tax`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:169
msgid ""
"For a :guilabel:`Custom Formula` tax, the tax amount is computed according "
"to a Python expression defined in the :guilabel:`Formula` field. The Python "
"expression may contain the following tokens:"
msgstr ""
"Za davek :guilabel:`Custom Formula` se davčni znesek izračuna v skladu z "
"izrazom Python, opredeljenim v polju :guilabel:`Formula`. Izraz Python lahko "
"vsebuje naslednje oznake:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:172
msgid "any of the following variables:"
msgstr "katero koli od naslednjih spremenljivk:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:174
msgid "`price_unit`: the unit price of the product"
msgstr "`price_unit`: enotna cena izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:175
msgid ""
"`base`: the taxable basis on which the tax is applied - may differ from the "
"`price_unit` if other taxes are applied first"
msgstr ""
"`base`: davčna osnova, na katero se davek nanaša - se lahko razlikuje od "
"`price_unit`, če so najprej uporabljeni drugi davki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:177
msgid "`quantity`: the quantity of the product"
msgstr "`quantity`: količina izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:178
msgid "`product`: the product record - product fields can also be accessed"
msgstr "`product`: zapis izdelka - dostop je mogoč tudi do polj izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:180
msgid "integers and floating-point numbers"
msgstr "cela števila in števila s plavajočo vejico"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:182
msgid ""
"the following permitted tokens: `(`, `)`, `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`, `,`, `<`, `>`, "
"`<=`, `>=`, `and`, `or`, `None`, `min`, and `max`"
msgstr ""
"naslednji dovoljeni žetoni: `(`, `)`, `+`, `-`, `*`, `/`, `,`, `<`, `>`, "
"`<=`, `>=`, `and`, `or`, `None`, `min` in `max`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:186
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a :guilabel:`Custom "
"Formula` tax with a :guilabel:`Formula` of `min(base, 500) * 0.10 + max(base "
"- 500, 0) * 0.20`"
msgstr ""
"Izdelek ima prodajno ceno 1000 $, nanj pa uporabimo davek :guilabel:`Formule "
"po meri` z :guilabel:`Formulo` `min(base, 500) * 0.10 + max(base - 500, 0) * "
"0.20`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:189
msgid "We then have:"
msgstr "Imamo torej:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:195
msgid "150"
msgstr "150"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:195
msgid "1,150.00"
msgstr "1.150,00"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:201
msgid "Included in price"
msgstr "Vključeno v ceno"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:204
msgid ""
"To set a company-wide default for this setting, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, find "
"the :guilabel:`Taxes` section, and set the :guilabel:`Prices` setting "
"to :guilabel:`Tax Excluded` or :guilabel:`Tax Included`. This setting cannot "
"be changed once invoices have been created."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti privzeto nastavitev za celotno podjetje, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, poiščite "
"razdelek :guilabel:`Davki` in nastavite :guilabel:`Cene` na :guilabel:`Brez "
"davka` ali :guilabel:`Z davkom`. Te nastavitve po izdaji računov ni mogoče "
"spremeniti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:209
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default` indicates that the tax follows the company-wide default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeto` pomeni, da davek sledi privzeti nastavitvi celotnega "
"podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:211
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Excluded` indicates that the tax amount is not included in "
"the sales price. The tax computation will therefore compute a tax amount on "
"top of the sales price."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Brez davka` pomeni, da znesek davka ni vključen v prodajno ceno. "
"Izračun davka bo zato izračunal znesek davka poleg prodajne cene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:214
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax Included` indicates that the tax amount is included in the "
"sales price. The tax computation will therefore split the sales price into a "
"tax-excluded base and the tax amount. This makes it suitable for B2C sales "
"in most countries, where prices are quoted tax-inclusive."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Z davkom` pomeni, da je znesek davka vključen v prodajno ceno. "
"Izračun davka bo zato razdelil prodajno ceno na osnovo brez davka in znesek "
"davka. To je primerno za B2C prodajo v večini držav, kjer so cene navedene z "
"vključenim davkom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:219
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax with :guilabel:`Included in Price` "
"set to :guilabel:`Tax Included`. We then have:"
msgstr ""
"Izdelek ima prodajno ceno 1000 $, nanj pa uporabimo 10-odstotni davek "
":guilabel:`Odstotek od cene`, pri čemer je :guilabel:`Vključeno v ceno` "
"nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Z davkom`. Imamo torej:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:230
msgid ""
"For a guide on configuring tax-excluded and tax-included prices for B2B and "
"B2C customers, see :doc:`B2B_B2C`."
msgstr ""
"Za navodila o konfiguraciji cen brez davka in z davkom za stranke B2B in B2C "
"glejte :doc:`B2B_B2C`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:236
msgid "Affect base of subsequent taxes"
msgstr "Vpliva na osnovo za naslednje davke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:238
msgid ""
"This setting controls how multiple taxes on a product line affect each other."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev nadzoruje, kako več davkov na vrstici izdelka vpliva drug na "
"drugega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:240
msgid ""
"If this setting is enabled, this tax's tax amount is included in the base of "
"any subsequent tax applied on the same product line that has its :ref:`taxes/"
"base-affected` setting enabled. As such, the subsequent tax's base is the "
"sum of the tax-excluded base and this tax's tax amount."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta nastavitev omogočena, je znesek davka tega davka vključen v osnovo "
"katerega koli naslednjega davka, ki se uporabi na isti vrstici izdelka in "
"ima omogočeno nastavitev :ref:`taxes/base-affected`. Tako je osnova "
"naslednjega davka vsota osnove brez davka in zneska davka tega davka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:246
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Affect base of subsequent taxes` is enabled "
"and :guilabel:`Included in Price` is set to :guilabel:`Tax Excluded`, "
"subsequent taxes with the :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` "
"setting enabled will be based on a modified sales price equal to the "
"original sales price plus the tax amount."
msgstr ""
"Če je :guilabel:`Vpliva na osnovo naslednjih davkov` omogočeno in je "
":guilabel:`Vključeno v ceno` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Brez davka`, bodo "
"naslednji davki z omogočeno nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Osnova, na katero "
"vplivajo predhodni davki`, temeljili na spremenjeni prodajni ceni, ki je "
"enaka prvotni prodajni ceni plus znesek davka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:252
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax where the :guilabel:`Included in "
"Price` setting is set to :guilabel:`Tax Excluded` and the :guilabel:`Affect "
"base of subsequent taxes` setting is enabled. Any subsequent tax with "
"its :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` will be based on a modified "
"sales price of $1100."
msgstr ""
"Izdelek ima prodajno ceno 1000 $, nanj pa uporabimo 10-odstotni davek "
":guilabel:`Odstotek od cene`, pri čemer je nastavitev :guilabel:`Vključeno v "
"ceno` nastavljena na :guilabel:`Brez davka` in je nastavitev "
":guilabel:`Vpliva na osnovo naslednjih davkov` omogočena. Vsak naslednji "
"davek z :guilabel:`Osnova, na katero vplivajo predhodni davki`, bo temeljil "
"na spremenjeni prodajni ceni 1100 $."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:259
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Affect base of subsequent taxes` is enabled "
"and :guilabel:`Included in Price` is set to :guilabel:`Tax Included`, "
"subsequent taxes with the :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` "
"setting enabled will be based on the original sales price."
msgstr ""
"Če je :guilabel:`Vpliva na osnovo naslednjih davkov` omogočeno in je "
":guilabel:`Vključeno v ceno` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Z davkom`, bodo "
"naslednji davki z omogočeno nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Osnova, na katero "
"vplivajo predhodni davki`, temeljili na prvotni prodajni ceni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:264
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax where the :guilabel:`Included in "
"Price` setting is set to :guilabel:`Tax Included` and the :guilabel:`Affect "
"base of subsequent taxes` setting is enabled. Any subsequent tax with "
"its :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` will be based on the "
"original sales price of $1000."
msgstr ""
"Izdelek ima prodajno ceno 1000 $, nanj pa uporabimo 10-odstotni davek "
":guilabel:`Odstotek od cene`, pri čemer je nastavitev :guilabel:`Vključeno v "
"ceno` nastavljena na :guilabel:`Z davkom` in je nastavitev :guilabel:`Vpliva "
"na osnovo naslednjih davkov` omogočena. Vsak naslednji davek z "
":guilabel:`Osnova, na katero vplivajo predhodni davki`, bo temeljil na "
"prvotni prodajni ceni 1000 $."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:270
msgid ""
"If this setting is disabled, the tax amount will not be included in the base "
"of any subsequent tax applied on the same product line."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta nastavitev onemogočena, znesek davka ne bo vključen v osnovo "
"kakršnega koli naslednjega davka, ki se uporabi za isto vrstico izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:275
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Affect base of subsequent taxes` is disabled "
"and :guilabel:`Included in Price` is set to :guilabel:`Tax Excluded`, "
"subsequent taxes with the :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` "
"setting enabled will be based on the original sales price."
msgstr ""
"Če je :guilabel:`Vpliv na osnovo naslednjih davkov` onemogočeno in je "
":guilabel:`Vključeno v ceno` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Davek izključen`, "
"bodo naslednji davki z omogočeno nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Osnova pod vplivom "
"predhodnih davkov` temeljili na izvirni prodajni ceni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:280
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax where the :guilabel:`Included in "
"Price` setting is set to :guilabel:`Tax Excluded` and the :guilabel:`Affect "
"base of subsequent taxes` setting is enabled. Any subsequent tax with "
"its :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` will be based on the "
"original sales price of $1000."
msgstr ""
"Izdelek ima prodajno ceno 1000 USD in uporabimo 10-odstotni davek "
":guilabel:`Odstotek cene`, pri katerem je nastavitev :guilabel:`Vključeno v "
"ceno` nastavljena na :guilabel:`Davek izključen` in je nastavitev "
":guilabel:`Vpliv na osnovo naslednjih davkov` omogočena. Vsak naslednji "
"davek z nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Osnova pod vplivom predhodnih davkov` bo "
"temeljil na izvirni prodajni ceni 1000 USD."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:287
msgid ""
"If :guilabel:`Affect base of subsequent taxes` is disabled "
"and :guilabel:`Included in Price` is set to :guilabel:`Tax Included`, "
"subsequent taxes with the :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` "
"setting enabled will be based on a modified sales price equal to the "
"original sales price minus the tax amount."
msgstr ""
"Če je :guilabel:`Vpliv na osnovo naslednjih davkov` onemogočeno in je "
":guilabel:`Vključeno v ceno` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Davek vključen`, bodo "
"naslednji davki z omogočeno nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Osnova pod vplivom "
"predhodnih davkov` temeljili na spremenjeni prodajni ceni, ki je enaka "
"izvirni prodajni ceni minus znesek davka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:293
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax where the :guilabel:`Included in "
"Price` setting is set to :guilabel:`Tax Included` and the :guilabel:`Affect "
"base of subsequent taxes` setting is enabled. Any subsequent tax with "
"its :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` will be based on a modified "
"sales price of $909.09."
msgstr ""
"Izdelek ima prodajno ceno 1000 USD in uporabimo 10-odstotni davek "
":guilabel:`Odstotek cene`, pri katerem je nastavitev :guilabel:`Vključeno v "
"ceno` nastavljena na :guilabel:`Davek vključen` in je nastavitev "
":guilabel:`Vpliv na osnovo naslednjih davkov` omogočena. Vsak naslednji "
"davek z nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Osnova pod vplivom predhodnih davkov` bo "
"temeljil na spremenjeni prodajni ceni 909,09 USD."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:299
msgid ""
"This setting is considered any time multiple taxes are applied to the same "
"product line, whether via a :ref:`group of taxes <taxes/computation>` or "
"multiple taxes added directly to a product line."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev se upošteva vsakič, ko se za isto vrstico izdelka uporabi več "
"davkov, bodisi prek :ref:`skupine davkov <taxes/computation>` bodisi več "
"davkov, dodanih neposredno k vrstici izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:303
msgid ""
"The order in which taxes are applied depends only on the order in which they "
"appear in the :guilabel:`Taxes` list, not on the order in which they are "
"added to a product line."
msgstr ""
"Vrstni red uporabe davkov je odvisen samo od vrstnega reda, v katerem se "
"pojavljajo na seznamu :guilabel:`Davki`, ne pa od vrstnega reda, v katerem "
"so dodani k vrstici izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:306
msgid ""
"To modify the order, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Taxes`, and drag and drop taxes using the handles to the left of the tax "
"names."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti vrstni red, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Davki` in povlecite ter "
"spustite davke z uporabo ročic na levi strani imen davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:None
msgid ""
"The order of appearance of taxes in the Taxes list determines which tax is "
"applied first"
msgstr ""
"Vrstni red pojavljanja davkov na seznamu davkov določa, kateri davek se "
"uporabi prvi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:312
msgid ""
"Regardless of the order in the :guilabel:`Taxes` list, :guilabel:`Tax "
"Excluded` taxes do not affect the base of subsequent :guilabel:`Tax "
"Included` taxes (see the note in :ref:`taxes/base-affected`)."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na vrstni red na seznamu :guilabel:`Davki`, davki :guilabel:`Davek "
"izključen` ne vplivajo na osnovo naslednjih davkov :guilabel:`Davek "
"vključen` (glejte opombo v :ref:`taxes/base-affected`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:317
msgid "In the following example:"
msgstr "V naslednjem primeru:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:319
msgid ""
"the Ecotax is a :guilabel:`Fixed` tax of €0.90 per unit, with "
"the :guilabel:`Affect base of subsequent taxes` setting enabled."
msgstr ""
"je ekotaksa davek :guilabel:`Fiksno` v višini 0,90 EUR na enoto z omogočeno "
"nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Vpliv na osnovo naslednjih davkov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:321
msgid ""
"The 21% VAT tax is a 21% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax with "
"the :guilabel:`Base affected by preceding taxes` setting enabled."
msgstr ""
"Davek DDV 21 % je davek :guilabel:`Odstotek cene` 21 % z omogočeno "
"nastavitvijo :guilabel:`Osnova pod vplivom predhodnih davkov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:323
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Taxes` list, the 21% VAT tax comes after the Ecotax, as "
"shown in the configuration above."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu :guilabel:`Davki` davek DDV 21 % pride za ekotakso, kot je "
"prikazano v zgornji konfiguraciji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:326
msgid ""
"When applying both taxes to a product line, the Ecotax amount is added to "
"the basis of the 21% VAT tax."
msgstr ""
"Če oba davka uporabimo za vrstico izdelka, se znesek ekotakse doda k osnovi "
"davka DDV 21 %."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:0
msgid "The Ecotax is added to the basis of the 21% VAT tax"
msgstr "Ekotaksa se doda k osnovi davka DDV 21 %"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:335
msgid "Base affected by preceding taxes"
msgstr "Osnova pod vplivom predhodnih davkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:337
msgid ""
"This setting, which is only visible in :doc:`developer mode <../../../"
"general/developer_mode>`, determines whether any previous tax "
"that :ref:`affects the base of subsequent taxes <taxes/base-subsequent>` "
"will modify the sales price that this tax is based on."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev, ki je vidna samo v :doc:`razvijalskem načinu <../../../"
"general/developer_mode>`, določa, ali bo kateri koli prejšnji davek, ki "
":ref:`vpliva na osnovo naslednjih davkov <taxes/base-subsequent>`, spremenil "
"prodajno ceno, na kateri temelji ta davek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:342
msgid ""
"Taxes with :ref:`Included in Price <taxes/included-in-price>` set "
"to :guilabel:`Tax Included` do not have this setting. Such taxes are never "
"affected by previous :guilabel:`Tax Excluded` taxes, except if they have "
"the :guilabel:`Fixed` :ref:`tax computation <taxes/computation>` type."
msgstr ""
"Davki z nastavitvijo :ref:`Vključeno v ceno <taxes/included-in-price>`, "
"nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Davek vključen`, nimajo te nastavitve. Na takšne "
"davke nikoli ne vplivajo prejšnji davki :guilabel:`Davek izključen`, razen "
"če imajo vrsto :guilabel:`Fiksno` :ref:`obračunavanje davka <taxes/"
"computation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:3
msgid "VAT numbers verification (VIES)"
msgstr "Preverjanje davčnih številk DDV (VIES)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:5
msgid ""
"`VAT Information Exchange System <https://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/vies/"
"#/vat-validation>`_, or **VIES**, is a tool provided by the European "
"Commission that allows you to check the validity of VAT numbers for "
"companies registered in the European Union."
msgstr ""
"`Sistem za izmenjavo informacij o DDV <https://ec.europa.eu/taxation_customs/"
"vies/#/vat-validation>`_, ali **VIES**, je orodje, ki ga zagotavlja Evropska "
"komisija in vam omogoča preverjanje veljavnosti davčnih številk DDV za "
"podjetja, registrirana v Evropski uniji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:9
msgid ""
"Odoo's VAT Validation feature uses the VIES to verify your contacts' VAT "
"numbers directly from Odoo's interface."
msgstr ""
"Odoo funkcija za preverjanje DDV uporablja VIES za preverjanje davčnih "
"številk DDV vaših stikov neposredno iz vmesnika Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:13
msgid ""
"Regardless of whether or not the Verify VAT Numbers feature is enabled, Odoo "
"checks the format of a contact's VAT against the `expected format of VAT "
"numbers <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VAT_identification_number>`_ from "
"that country."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali je funkcija Preveri davčne številke DDV omogočena ali "
"ne, Odoo preveri obliko DDV stika glede na `pričakovano obliko davčnih "
"številk DDV <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VAT_identification_number>`_ iz "
"te države."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:18
msgid "VIES VAT number verification"
msgstr "Preverjanje davčne številke DDV VIES"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:20
msgid ""
"To activate this feature, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Taxes` section, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Verify VAT Numbers` feature, and click on :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za aktiviranje te funkcije pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. V razdelku :guilabel:`Davki` omogočite "
"funkcijo :guilabel:`Preveri davčne številke DDV` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:24
msgid ""
"Once the :guilabel:`Verify VAT Numbers` feature is enabled, if the "
"contact's :guilabel:`Tax ID` field is populated *and* its country is "
"different from your company's country, Odoo displays an :guilabel:`Intra-"
"Community Valid` checkbox. Odoo tests the VAT number through the VIES and "
"automatically checks or unchecks the :guilabel:`Intra-Community Valid` "
"checkbox depending on the validity of the VAT number."
msgstr ""
"Ko je funkcija :guilabel:`Preveri davčne številke DDV` omogočena, če je "
"polje :guilabel:`Davčna številka` stika izpolnjeno *in* je njegova država "
"drugačna od države vašega podjetja, Odoo prikaže potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`Znotrajskupnostno veljavno`. Odoo preveri davčno številko DDV "
"prek VIES in samodejno označi ali odoznači potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`Znotrajskupnostno veljavno` glede na veljavnost davčne številke "
"DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:None
msgid "Intra-community valid checkbox on the contact record"
msgstr "Potrditveno polje znotrajskupnostno veljavno v zapisu stika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:34
msgid ""
"It is possible to manually override the :guilabel:`Intra-Community Valid` "
"field on a contact in case the automatic VIES check is incorrect (for "
"example, if the company was recently created and its VAT is not yet in the "
"VIES). This change is logged in the chatter for transparency."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Intra-Community Valid` je na kontaktu mogoče ročno "
"preglasiti v primeru, da je samodejni VIES preizkus napačen (na primer, če "
"je bilo podjetje pred kratkim ustanovljeno in njegova DDV številka še ni v "
"VIES). Ta sprememba je zabeležena v pogovorih za preglednost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/vat_verification.rst:39
msgid ""
"Odoo can :ref:`automatically apply fiscal positions <fiscal_positions/"
"automatic>`. If the Verify VAT Numbers feature is enabled, any fiscal "
"positions with VAT required enabled will require Intra-Community valid VAT "
"numbers to apply automatically."
msgstr ""
"Odoo lahko :ref:`samodejno uporabi davčne položaje <fiscal_positions/"
"automatic>`. Če je omogočena funkcija Preveri DDV številke, bodo vsi davčni "
"položaji z omogočeno zahtevo po DDV zahtevali veljavne DDV številke "
"Skupnosti za samodejno uporabo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:7
msgid ""
"Vendor bills can be registered either **manually** or **automatically** in "
"Odoo. The :ref:`Aged Payable report <accounting/vendor_bills/age-payable-"
"report>` provides an overview of all outstanding bills to help ensure timely "
"payment of the correct amounts."
msgstr ""
"Dobaviteljeve račune je mogoče v Odoo registrirati **ročno** ali "
"**samodejno**. :ref:`Poročilo o staranju obveznosti <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"age-payable-report>` zagotavlja pregled vseh neporavnanih računov in pomaga "
"zagotoviti pravočasno plačilo pravilnih zneskov."

