"the information on the vendor's contact record as well as previous purchase "
"orders and bills."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dobavitelj`: Odoo samodejno izpolni nekatere informacije na "
"podlagi podatkov v kontaktnem zapisu dobavitelja ter prejšnjih nabavnih "
"nalogov in računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:78
