#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Auto-Complete`: Select a past bill/purchase order to complete the "
"document automatically. The :guilabel:`Vendor` field should be completed "
"before completing this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Samodejno izpolni`: Izberite pretekli račun/nabavni nalog za "
"samodejno izpolnitev dokumenta. Polje :guilabel:`Dobavitelj` mora biti "
"izpolnjeno pred izpolnitvijo tega polja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Bill Date`: Select the document's issuance date."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum računa`: Izberite datum izdaje dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accounting Date`: Update the document's accounting registration "
"date if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Računovodski datum`: Po potrebi posodobite datum računovodske "
"registracije dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Reference`: The :guilabel:`Memo` field automatically "
"includes the payment reference once the payment is registered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Plačilni sklic`: Polje :guilabel:`Opomba` samodejno vključi "
"plačilni sklic, ko je plačilo registrirano."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recipient Bank`: Indicates the account number to which the "
"payment will be made. This field is required when paying via batch payment "
"files (such as :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-transfers>` "
"and :doc:`SEPA <payments/pay_sepa>`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prejemnikova banka`: Označuje številko računa, na katerega bo "
"izvedeno plačilo. To polje je obvezno pri plačevanju prek paketnih plačilnih "
"datotek (kot sta :ref:`NACHA <l10n_us/ach-electronic-transfers>` in "
":doc:`SEPA <payments/pay_sepa>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Due Date` or :guilabel:`Payment Terms` must be specified for the "
"bill payment."
msgstr ""
"Za plačilo računa mora biti naveden :guilabel:`Datum zapadlosti` ali "
":guilabel:`Plačilni pogoji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select which journal should record the bill and in "
"which :doc:`currency <get_started/multi_currency>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dnevnik`: Izberite, kateri dnevnik naj zabeleži račun in v kateri "
":doc:`valuti <get_started/multi_currency>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:95
msgid ""
"To access the product catalog, click :doc:`Catalog </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/"
"product_catalog>`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do kataloga izdelkov kliknite :doc:`Katalog </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/inventory_management/"
"product_catalog>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:97
msgid ""
"Select the products and quantities, then click :guilabel:`Back to Bill` to "
"return to the vendor bill; the selected catalog items will appear in the "
"vendor bill lines."
msgstr ""
"Izberite izdelke in količine, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Nazaj na račun`, da "
"se vrnete na dobaviteljev račun; izbrani elementi kataloga se bodo pojavili "
"v vrsticah dobaviteljevega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:99
msgid ""
"Update the :guilabel:`Quantity`, :guilabel:`Price`, and :doc:`Taxes <taxes>` "
"fields if needed."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi posodobite polja :guilabel:`Količina`, :guilabel:`Cena` in "
":doc:`Davki <taxes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:102
msgid ""
"If the bill line does not correspond to an existing product in the database, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` and enter a description for the bill line "
"without linking it to a product."
msgstr ""
"Če vrstica računa ne ustreza obstoječemu izdelku v zbirki podatkov, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` in vnesite opis vrstice računa brez povezovanja z "
"izdelkom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:106
msgid ""
"Multiple bills for the same purchase order may be issued if the vendor is on "
"back-order and sends invoices as products are shipped or if the vendor sends "
"partial bills or requests a deposit. In this case, multiple bills may have "
"the same :guilabel:`Bill Reference`."
msgstr ""
"Za isti nabavni nalog je lahko izdanih več računov, če ima dobavitelj "
"zaostalo naročilo in pošilja račune ob pošiljanju izdelkov ali če dobavitelj "
"pošilja delne račune ali zahteva polog. V tem primeru ima lahko več računov "
"enak :guilabel:`Sklic računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:113
msgid "Bill confirmation"
msgstr "Potrditev računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:115
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` when the document is completed. The status changes "
"to :guilabel:`Posted`, and a journal entry is generated based on the vendor "
"bill information. On confirmation, Odoo assigns each vendor bill a unique "
"number from a defined :doc:`sequence <vendor_bills/sequence>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je dokument izpolnjen, kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`. Status se spremeni v "
":guilabel:`Knjiženo` in na podlagi informacij dobaviteljevega računa se "
"ustvari knjižba. Ob potrditvi Odoo vsakemu dobaviteljevemu računu dodeli "
"edinstveno številko iz določenega :doc:`zaporedja <vendor_bills/sequence>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:120
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, a vendor bill can no longer be updated. "
"Click :guilabel:`Reset to draft` if changes are required."
msgstr ""
"Po potrditvi računa dobavitelja ni več mogoče posodobiti. Kliknite "
":guilabel:`Ponastavi na osnutek`, če so potrebne spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:126
msgid "Self-billing"
msgstr "Lastni računi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:128
msgid ""
"Self-billing is a workflow where a customer generates a vendor bill on the "
"supplier's behalf and sends a copy to the supplier for their records. It "
"removes the need for the supplier to send the customer a vendor bill and is "
"common in industries where the customer has more reliable transaction data. "
"It also reduces payment time as the customer does not have to wait for the "
"supplier to issue a vendor bill."
msgstr ""
"Lastni računi so delovni proces, pri katerem stranka ustvari dobaviteljev "
"račun v imenu dobavitelja in dobavitelju pošlje kopijo za njegove evidence. "
"To odpravlja potrebo, da bi dobavitelj stranki poslal dobaviteljev račun, in "
"je pogost v panogah, kjer ima stranka bolj zanesljive podatke o "
"transakcijah. Skrajša tudi čas plačila, saj stranka ne rabi čakati, da "
"dobavitelj izda dobaviteljev račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:134
msgid ""
"Odoo supports the generation of self-billing vendor bills and self-billing "
"credit notes, both of which can be sent by email and via Peppol."
msgstr ""
"Odoo podpira ustvarjanje dobaviteljevih računov in dobropisov za lastne "
"račune, ki jih je mogoče poslati po e-pošti in prek Peppola."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:142
msgid ""
"To configure self-billing in Odoo, first create a separate purchase journal "
"specifically for self-billing:"
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo lastnih računov v Odoo najprej ustvarite ločen dnevnik "
"nabave posebej za lastne račune:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:147
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Journal Name` and set the :guilabel:`Type` "
"to :guilabel:`Purchase`."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite :guilabel:`Ime dnevnika` in nastavite :guilabel:`Tip` na "
":guilabel:`Nabava`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:148
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab, enable :guilabel:`Self Billing`."
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku :guilabel:`Napredne nastavitve` omogočite "
":guilabel:`Samofakturiranje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:151
msgid ":doc:`get_started/journals`"
msgstr ":doc:`get_started/journals`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:156
msgid "Create a self-bill"
msgstr "Ustvarite samofakturo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:158
msgid ""
"Self-bills can be created both :ref:`manually <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"creation-manual>` and :ref:`automatically <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"automatic>`. When creating self-bills, be sure to either create them "
"directly from the :ref:`self-billing purchase journal <accounting/"
"vendor_bills/self-billing-config>` on the :guilabel:`Accounting Dashboard` "
"or manually set the :guilabel:`Journal` of the self-bill to the self-billing "
"purchase journal."
msgstr ""
"Samofakture lahko ustvarite :ref:`ročno <accounting/vendor_bills/creation-"
"manual>` ali :ref:`samodejno <accounting/vendor_bills/automatic>`. Pri "
"ustvarjanju samofaktur jih ustvarite neposredno iz :ref:`dnevnika nabavnih "
"samofaktur <accounting/vendor_bills/self-billing-config>` na "
":guilabel:`Nadzorni plošči` ali ročno nastavite :guilabel:`Dnevnik` "
"samofakture na dnevnik nabavnih samofaktur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:165
msgid ""
"The sequence of self-bills contains the :ref:`database ID "
"<export_import_data/different-ids>` (also known as the internal ID) of the "
"partner, making the sequence unique per partner."
msgstr ""
"Zaporedje samofaktur vsebuje :ref:`ID baze podatkov <export_import_data/"
"different-ids>` (znan tudi kot interni ID) partnerja, zaradi česar je "
"zaporedje edinstveno za vsakega partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:171
msgid "Send a self-bill"
msgstr "Pošljite samofakturo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:173
msgid ""
"To send a self-bill after :ref:`creating <accounting/vendor_bills/self-"
"billing-create>` and confirming it, click :guilabel:`Send`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Send` popup window, select the sending methods "
"(i.e., :guilabel:`by Email`, :guilabel:`by Post`, and/or :guilabel:`by "
"Peppol`), and click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poslati samofakturo po :ref:`ustvarjanju <accounting/vendor_bills/"
"self-billing-create>` in potrditvi, kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`. V pojavnem "
"oknu :guilabel:`Pošlji` izberite načine pošiljanja (tj. :guilabel:`po e-"
"pošti`, :guilabel:`po pošti` in/ali :guilabel:`prek Peppol`) in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Pošlji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:179
msgid ""
"If sending self-bills via :ref:`Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`, "
"first :ref:`configure your Peppol registration <accounting/e-invoicing/"
"peppol-registration>`, then verify that the vendor is registered with "
"Peppol. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Vendors`, "
"then go through the :ref:`contact verification process <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/contact-verification>`."
msgstr ""
"Če pošiljate samofakture prek :ref:`Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`, "
"najprej :ref:`konfigurirajte svojo registracijo Peppol <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol-registration>`, nato preverite, ali je dobavitelj "
"registriran pri Peppol. To storite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Dobavitelji` in izvedete "
":ref:`postopek preverjanja kontaktov <accounting/e-invoicing/contact-"
"verification>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:184
msgid ""
"Not every Peppol access point supports self-billing. Check with your "
"suppliers to ensure theirs does."
msgstr ""
"Vse dostopne točke Peppol ne podpirajo samofakturiranja. Preverite pri "
"svojih dobaviteljih, ali njihova to podpira."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:192
msgid ""
"To register a payment, click on :guilabel:`Pay`. In the :guilabel:`Pay` "
"window, select the :guilabel:`Journal`, the :guilabel:`Payment Method`, "
"the :guilabel:`Amount`, and the :guilabel:`Currency`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite registrirati plačilo, kliknite :guilabel:`Plačaj`. V oknu "
":guilabel:`Plačaj` izberite :guilabel:`Dnevnik`, :guilabel:`Način plačila`, "
":guilabel:`Znesek` in :guilabel:`Valuto`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:196
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Amount` paid is less than the total remaining amount on "
"the vendor bill, the payment is :ref:`partial <accounting/payments/partial-"
"payment>`, and the :guilabel:`Payment Difference` field displays the "
"outstanding balance."
msgstr ""
"Ko je plačani :guilabel:`Znesek` manjši od skupnega preostalega zneska na "
"računu dobavitelja, je plačilo :ref:`delno <accounting/payments/partial-"
"payment>`, polje :guilabel:`Razlika v plačilu` pa prikazuje neporavnano "
"stanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:200
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Memo` field is filled automatically if the :guilabel:`Payment "
"Reference` has been set correctly on the vendor bill. If the field is empty, "
"select the vendor invoice number as a reference."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Opomba` se samodejno izpolni, če je bila "
":guilabel:`Plačilna referenca` pravilno nastavljena na računu dobavitelja. "
"Če je polje prazno, kot referenco izberite številko računa dobavitelja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:204
msgid ""
"Then click :guilabel:`Create payment`. An :guilabel:`In "
"Payment`/:guilabel:`Partial` banner appears on the bill until it "
"is :doc:`reconciled <bank/reconciliation>` and its status updates "
"to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari plačilo`. Na računu se prikaže pasica "
":guilabel:`V plačilu`/:guilabel:`Delno`, dokler ni :doc:`usklajeno <bank/"
"reconciliation>` in se status posodobi na :guilabel:`Plačano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:215
msgid "Aged payable report"
msgstr "Poročilo o staranju obveznosti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:217
msgid ""
"For an overview of the open vendor bills and their due dates, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Aged payable`."
msgstr ""
"Za pregled odprtih računov dobaviteljev in njihovih rokov plačila pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Staranje obveznosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills.rst:220
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-caret-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` icon next to a "
"vendor to view the details of all their outstanding bills, including the due "
"dates and amounts."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-caret-right` :guilabel:`(puščica desno)` ob "
"dobavitelju, da si ogledate podrobnosti vseh njegovih neporavnanih računov, "
"vključno z roki plačila in zneski."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:3
msgid "Non-current assets and fixed assets"
msgstr "Nekratkoročna sredstva in osnovna sredstva"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Non-current Assets**, also known as **long-term assets**, are investments "
"that are expected to be realized after one year. They are capitalized rather "
"than being expensed and appear on the company's balance sheet. Depending on "
"their nature, they may undergo **depreciation**."
msgstr ""
"**Nekratkoročna sredstva**, znana tudi kot **dolgoročna sredstva**, so "
"naložbe, ki se pričakuje, da bodo realizirane po enem letu. Kapitalizirajo "
"se namesto da bi bile knjižene kot odhodek in se pojavijo v bilanci stanja "
"podjetja. Glede na njihovo naravo lahko podležejo **amortizaciji**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Fixed Assets** are a type of Non-current Assets and include the properties "
"bought for their productive aspects, such as buildings, vehicles, equipment, "
"land, and software."
msgstr ""
"**Osnovna sredstva** so vrsta nekratkoročnih sredstev in vključujejo "
"nepremičnine, kupljene zaradi njihovega produktivnega vidika, kot so "
"zgradbe, vozila, oprema, zemljišča in programska oprema."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:12
msgid ""
"For example, let's say we buy a car for $ 27,000. We plan to amortize it "
"over five years, and we will sell it for $ 7,000 afterward. Using the "
"linear, or straight-line, depreciation method, $ 4,000 are expensed each "
"year as **depreciation expenses**. After five years, the **Accumulated "
"Depreciation** amount reported on the balance sheet equals $ 20,000, leaving "
"us with $ 7,000 of **Not Depreciable Value**, or Salvage value."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, recimo, da kupimo avto za 27.000 $. Načrtujemo ga amortizirati v "
"petih letih in ga nato prodati za 7.000 $. Z uporabo linearne metode "
"amortizacije se vsako leto knjiži 4.000 $ kot **odhodki amortizacije**. Po "
"petih letih **Nabrana amortizacija**, poročana v bilanci stanja, znaša "
"20.000 $, kar nam pusti 7.000 $ **Neamortizirane vrednosti** ali preostale "
"vrednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:18
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting handles depreciation by creating all depreciation entries "
"automatically in *draft mode*. They are then posted periodically."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Accounting obravnava amortizacijo tako, da samodejno ustvari vse vnose "
"amortizacije v *osnutku*. Nato se periodično knjižijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:21
msgid "Odoo supports the following **Depreciation Methods**:"
msgstr "Odoo podpira naslednje **Metode amortizacije**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:23
msgid "Straight Line"
msgstr "Enakomerna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:24
msgid "Declining"
msgstr "Upadanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:25
msgid "Declining Then Straight Line"
msgstr "Padajoča nato linearna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:28
msgid ""
"The server checks once a day if an entry must be posted. It might then take "
"up to 24 hours before you see a change from *draft* to *posted*."
msgstr ""
"Strežnik enkrat na dan preveri, ali je treba vnos knjižiti. Zato lahko traja "
"do 24 ur, preden vidite spremembo iz *osnutka* v *knjiženo*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:34
msgid ""
"Such transactions must be posted on an **Assets Account** rather than on the "
"default expense account."
msgstr ""
"Take transakcije morajo biti knjižene na **Račun sredstev** in ne na "
"privzeti račun odhodkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/vendor_bills/assets.rst:38
