msgid ""
"`Days` × `Home-work distance` × `2` × (`Number of office days` / `7`) × "
"`Vehicle model CO₂ emissions`"
msgstr ""
"`Dnevi` × `Razdalja dom-delo` × `2` × (`Število dni v pisarni` / `7`) × "
"`Emisije CO₂ modela vozila`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:63
msgid "To ensure accurate calculations:"
msgstr "Za zagotovitev natančnih izračunov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:65
msgid ""
"Define the average number of days per week the employees commute to the "
"office by going to :menuselection:`ESG --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"filling in the :guilabel:`Weekly Office Attendance`."
msgstr ""
"Določite povprečno število dni na teden, ko zaposleni prihajajo v pisarno, "
"tako da greste na :menuselection:`ESG --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in "
"izpolnite :guilabel:`Tedensko prisotnost v pisarni`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:68
msgid ""
"Set the emissions of each vehicle model by going to :menuselection:`Fleet --"
"> Configuration --> Models`, selecting a model, and entering "
"its :guilabel:`CO₂ Emissions`."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite emisije za vsak model vozila tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Vozni park --> Konfiguracija --> Modeli`, izberete model in "
"vnesete njegove :guilabel:`Emisije CO₂`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:70
msgid ""
"Set each employee's home-to-work distance by opening "
"the :guilabel:`Employees` app, selecting an employee, and filling in the "
"employee's :guilabel:`Home-Work Distance`."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite razdaljo od doma do dela za vsakega zaposlenega tako, da odprete "
"aplikacijo :guilabel:`Kader`, izberete zaposlenega in izpolnite "
":guilabel:`Razdalja dom-delo` zaposlenega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:74
msgid ""
"The employee vehicle's :guilabel:`Start Date` and, if "
"applicable, :guilabel:`End Date`, are used to calculate the emissions. "
"Ensure they are set by opening the :guilabel:`Employees` app, selecting an "
"employee, and clicking the :guilabel:`Cars` smart button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum začetka` in, če je primerno, :guilabel:`Datum konca` vozila "
"zaposlenega se uporabita za izračun emisij. Preverite, ali sta nastavljena, "
"tako da odprete aplikacijo :guilabel:`Kader`, izberete zaposlenega in "
"kliknete pametni gumb :guilabel:`Avtomobili`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:78
msgid ""
"To access the employee commuting emissions pivot table, go "
"to :menuselection:`ESG --> Collect --> Employee Commuting`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do vrtilne tabele emisij pri prevozu zaposlenih greste na "
":menuselection:`ESG --> Zbiranje --> Prevoz zaposlenih`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:None
msgid "The employee commuting emissions pivot table"
msgstr "Vrtilna tabela emisij pri prevozu zaposlenih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:84
msgid ""
"To add the data to the emitted emissions, click :guilabel:`Add Emissions`, "
"define the :guilabel:`Emissions Period` that should be covered, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje podatkov v oddane emisije kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj emisije`, "
"določite :guilabel:`Obdobje emisij`, ki naj bo zajeto, in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:90
msgid "Manual input"
msgstr "Ročni vnos"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:92
msgid ""
"You can manually enter emissions for activities that not tracked "
"automatically (e.g., employee lunches, waste, etc.). To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`ESG --> Collect --> Emitted Emissions` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`, then:"
msgstr ""
"Emisije za dejavnosti, ki se ne sledijo samodejno (npr. kosila zaposlenih, "
"odpadki itd.), lahko vnesete ročno. Za to greste na :menuselection:`ESG --> "
"Zbiranje --> Oddane emisije` in kliknete :guilabel:`Novo`, nato:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:96
msgid "Name the activity."
msgstr "Poimenujte dejavnost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:97
msgid "Select a :guilabel:`Date`."
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Datum`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:98
msgid "Select an :guilabel:`Emission factor`."
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Emisijski faktor`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:99
msgid "Enter a :guilabel:`Quantity`."
msgstr "Vnesite :guilabel:`Količino`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:101
msgid ""
"Once saved, the entry appears under :menuselection:`ESG --> Collect --> "
"Emitted Emissions` and is included in the carbon footprint report."
msgstr ""
"Ko je shranjeno, se vnos prikaže pod :menuselection:`ESG --> Zbiranje --> "
"Oddane emisije` in je vključen v poročilo o ogljičnem odtisu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:105
msgid "Emission factors"
msgstr "Emisijski faktorji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:107
msgid ""
"An emission factor is a coefficient that indicates the rate at which a "
"specific activity emits greenhouse gases into the atmosphere."
msgstr ""
"Emisijski faktor je koeficient, ki označuje stopnjo, s katero določena "
"dejavnost oddaja toplogredne pline v ozračje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:111
msgid "Source database"
msgstr "Izvorna podatkovna zbirka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:113
msgid ""
"Import the data from a certified emission factors database by going "
"to :menuselection:`ESG --> Configuration --> Source Databases`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Download` on the `ADEME <https://www.ademe.fr/en/our-"
"missions/data>`_ database to import its emission factors and sources."
msgstr ""
"Uvozite podatke iz certificirane podatkovne zbirke emisijskih faktorjev "
"tako, da greste na :menuselection:`ESG --> Konfiguracija --> Izvorne "
"podatkovne zbirke`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Prenesi` pri podatkovni zbirki "
"`ADEME <https://www.ademe.fr/en/our-missions/data>`_, da uvozite njene "
"emisijske faktorje in vire."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:118
msgid "Main components of an emission factor"
msgstr "Glavne komponente emisijskega faktorja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:121
msgid "Source"
msgstr "Vir"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:123
msgid ""
"Each emission factor is assigned to a scope, following the GHG Protocol:"
msgstr ""
"Vsak emisijski faktor je dodeljen področju uporabe v skladu s protokolom GHG:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:125
msgid ""
"Scope 1 – Direct emissions (e.g., fuel burned on-site or in company vehicles)"
msgstr ""
"Obseg 1 – Neposredni izpusti (npr. gorivo, sežgano na lokaciji ali v vozilih "
"podjetja)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:126
msgid ""
"Scope 2 – Indirect emissions from purchased energy (e.g., electricity or "
"heat)"
msgstr ""
"Obseg 2 – Posredni izpusti iz kupljene energije (npr. električna energija "
"ali toplota)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:127
msgid ""
"Scope 3 – All other indirect emissions across the value chain (e.g., "
"purchased goods, travel, waste)"
msgstr ""
"Obseg 3 – Vsi drugi posredni izpusti v celotni vrednostni verigi (npr. "
"kupljeno blago, potovanja, odpadki)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:130
msgid ""
"Scopes can be structured hierarchically (parent-child) for more detailed "
"categorization, such as \"Scope 3: Others Indirect > Purchased Goods > "
"Electronics\"."
msgstr ""
"Obsegi so lahko strukturirani hierarhično (nadrejeni-podrejeni) za "
"podrobnejšo kategorizacijo, kot je \"Obseg 3: Drugi posredni > Kupljeno "
"blago > Elektronika\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:134
msgid "Uncertainty"
msgstr "Negotovost"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:136
msgid ""
"Uncertainty represents the potential margin of error in an emission factor. "
"It reflects how precise or reliable the factor is when estimating emissions "
"for a given activity, based on the quality of data, assumptions used, and "
"calculation methodology."
msgstr ""
"Negotovost predstavlja potencialno napako v faktorju izpustov. Odraža, kako "
"natančen ali zanesljiv je faktor pri ocenjevanju izpustov za določeno "
"dejavnost, na podlagi kakovosti podatkov, uporabljenih predpostavk in "
"metodologije izračuna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:140
msgid ""
"It helps you assess the confidence level of the emissions data used in the "
"reporting."
msgstr ""
"Pomaga vam oceniti raven zaupanja v podatke o izpustih, uporabljene v "
"poročanju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:143
msgid "Compute method"
msgstr "Metoda izračuna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:145
msgid ""
"The compute method determines whether emissions are calculated using "
"physical quantities (e.g., kg, liters, units) or monetary values (e.g., € "
"spent). In physical mode, the system uses the quantity from the transaction "
"(e.g., 10 units × :abbr:`EF (emission factor)` per unit). In monetary mode, "
"it uses the transaction amount (e.g., €500 × :abbr:`EF (emission factor)` "
"per €)."
msgstr ""
"Metoda izračuna določa, ali se izpusti izračunajo na podlagi fizičnih "
"količin (npr. kg, litri, enote) ali denarnih vrednosti (npr. porabljeni €). "
"V fizičnem načinu sistem uporablja količino iz transakcije (npr. 10 enot × "
":abbr:`EF (faktor izpustov)` na enoto). V denarnem načinu uporablja znesek "
"transakcije (npr. 500 € × :abbr:`EF (faktor izpustov)` na €)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:151
msgid "Gas emissions lines"
msgstr "Vrstice izpustov plinov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:153
msgid ""
"Each emission factor can include multiple gas emission lines, representing "
"the different greenhouse gases involved in the activity. The ESG app "
"includes the six main gases from the Kyoto Protocol — CO₂, CH₄, N₂O, HFCs, "
"PFCs, SF₆ — each with a predefined Global Warming Potential (GWP) used to "
"convert them into a common unit: CO₂-equivalent (kgCO₂e)."
msgstr ""
"Vsak faktor izpustov lahko vključuje več vrstic izpustov plinov, ki "
"predstavljajo različne toplogredne pline, vključene v dejavnost. Aplikacija "
"ESG vključuje šest glavnih plinov iz Kjotskega protokola — CO₂, CH₄, N₂O, "
"HFC, PFC, SF₆ — vsak s preddoločenim globalnim potencialom segrevanja (GWP), "
"ki se uporablja za njihovo pretvorbo v skupno enoto: ekvivalent CO₂ (kgCO₂e)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:159
msgid ""
"Add more specific gases by going to :menuselection:`ESG --> Configuration --"
"> Gases`."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte bolj specifične pline tako, da greste na :menuselection:`ESG --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Plini`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:161
msgid ""
"Each gas line can be linked to an activity type such as production, "
"transport, or use, allowing for detailed breakdowns in your emissions "
"reporting."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka vrstica plina je lahko povezana z vrsto dejavnosti, kot je "
"proizvodnja, prevoz ali uporaba, kar omogoča podrobne razčlenitve v "
"poročanju o izpustih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:164
msgid ""
"The final emission factor value is the sum of all these gases’ emissions "
"converted into CO₂-equivalents."
msgstr ""
"Končna vrednost faktorja izpustov je vsota izpustov vseh teh plinov, "
"pretvorjenih v ekvivalente CO₂."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:168
msgid "Assignation rules"
msgstr "Pravila dodeljevanja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:170
msgid ""
"Assignation rules allow emission factors to be automatically applied to "
"relevant activity data based on specific criteria: the product, partner, and/"
"or account involved in the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Pravila dodeljevanja omogočajo, da se faktorji izpustov samodejno uporabijo "
"za ustrezne podatke o dejavnosti na podlagi določenih meril: izdelka, "
"partnerja in/ali konta, vključenega v transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:174
msgid ""
"You have assigned an emission factor to the *Zenith Pro Computer* product "
"and later receive a vendor bill for 150 units; the system automatically "
"applies the assigned emission factor, multiplying the emission factor's "
"emissions (kgCO₂e) by 150."
msgstr ""
"Faktor izpustov ste dodelili izdelku *Zenith Pro Computer* in pozneje "
"prejmete dobaviteljev račun za 150 enot; sistem samodejno uporabi dodeljeni "
"faktor izpustov in pomnoži izpuste faktorja izpustov (kgCO₂e) s 150."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:178
msgid ""
"To define assignation rules on emissions factors, go to :menuselection:`ESG "
"--> Configuration --> Emission Factors` and select an emission factor. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Assignations` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, and select a "
"record for one or more of the following "
"attributes: :guilabel:`Product`, :guilabel:`Partner`, "
"and :guilabel:`Account`."
msgstr ""
"Za določitev pravil dodeljevanja za faktorje izpustov pojdite na "
":menuselection:`ESG --> Konfiguracija --> Faktorji izpustov` in izberite "
"faktor izpustov. Pod zavihkom :guilabel:`Dodelitve` kliknite "
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` in izberite zapis za enega ali več naslednjih "
"atributov: :guilabel:`Izdelek`, :guilabel:`Partner` in :guilabel:`Konto`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:183
msgid "All attributes have to match for the rule to be applied."
msgstr "Vsi atributi se morajo ujemati, da se pravilo uporabi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:186
msgid ""
"Ensure the unit of measure set next to the product's :guilabel:`Cost` "
"matches the emission factor's :guilabel:`Unit of Measure`."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovite, da se merska enota, nastavljena poleg :guilabel:`Stroška` "
"izdelka, ujema z :guilabel:`Mersko enoto` faktorja izpustov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:None
msgid "A product's unit of measure"
msgstr "Merska enota izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:192
msgid ""
"If the field is not displayed, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and enable the :guilabel:`Units of Measure & "
"Packagings` option."
msgstr ""
"Če polje ni prikazano, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in omogočite možnost :guilabel:`Merske enote "
"in pakiranja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:196
msgid ""
"Accounting journal entries with a missing emission factor can be found by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Emissions to define` under the :guilabel:`Collect "
"Emissions` card on the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Računovodske knjižbe z manjkajočim emisijskim faktorjem lahko najdete s "
"klikom na :guilabel:`Emisije za določitev` pod kartico :guilabel:`Zbiranje "
"emisij` na nadzorni plošči."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:200
msgid "Rules priority"
msgstr "Prednost pravil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:202
msgid ""
"When multiple assignation rules match, Odoo prioritizes the most specific "
"rule based on the following criteria:"
msgstr ""
"Ko se ujema več pravil dodelitve, Odoo daje prednost najbolj specifičnemu "
"pravilu na podlagi naslednjih meril:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:205
msgid ""
"Attribute specificity: Odoo first evaluates rules by the most precise "
"attribute, following this priority hierarchy (from most to least specific):"
msgstr ""
"Specifičnost atributa: Odoo najprej ovrednoti pravila po najpreciznejšem "
"atributu, pri čemer sledi tej hierarhiji prednosti (od najbolj do najmanj "
"specifičnega):"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:208
#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:226
#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:238
#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:257
#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:269
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:98
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:387
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:113
msgid "Product"
msgstr "Izdelek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/esg.rst:212
msgid ""
"Attribute count: if multiple rules share the same level of attribute "
"specificity, Odoo then considers the number of attributes in the rule. The "
"rule with more attributes defined will take priority."
msgstr ""
"Število atributov: če več pravil deli enako raven specifičnosti atributa, "
"Odoo nato upošteva število atributov v pravilu. Pravilo z več opredeljenimi "
"atributi bo imelo prednost."

