#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:574
msgid "Troubleshooting and auditing"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav in revizija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:576
msgid ""
"For auditing and troubleshooting purposes, it is possible to obtain detailed "
"information of an invoice number that has been previously sent to the AFIP. "
"To retrieve this information, activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, then go to the :menuselection:`Accounting` menu and click on the "
"button :guilabel:`Consult Invoice` button in AFIP."
msgstr ""
"Za namene revizije in odpravljanja težav je mogoče pridobiti podrobne "
"informacije o številki računa, ki je bila predhodno poslana v AFIP. Za "
"pridobitev teh informacij aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-"
"mode>`, nato pojdite v meni :menuselection:`Računovodstvo` in kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Poizvedba po računu` v AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Consult invoice in AFIP."
msgstr "Poizvedba po računu v AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Details of invoice consulted in AFIP."
msgstr "Podrobnosti računa, poizvedenega v AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:589
msgid ""
"It is also possible to retrieve the last number used in AFIP for a specific "
"document type and POS Number as a reference for any possible issues on the "
"sequence synchronization between Odoo and AFIP."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je tudi pridobiti zadnjo uporabljeno številko v AFIP za določeno "
"vrsto dokumenta in številko POS kot referenco za morebitne težave pri "
"sinhronizaciji zaporedja med Odoo in AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Consult the last invoice number."
msgstr "Poizvedba po zadnji številki računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:600
msgid ""
"Based on the purchase journal selected for the vendor bill, "
"the :guilabel:`Document Type` is now a required field. This value is auto-"
"populated based on the AFIP Responsibility type of Issuer and Customer, but "
"the value can be changed if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Na podlagi dnevnika nakupov, izbranega za dobaviteljev račun, je "
":guilabel:`Vrsta dokumenta` zdaj obvezno polje. Ta vrednost se samodejno "
"izpolni na podlagi vrste odgovornosti AFIP izdajatelja in stranke, vendar je "
"mogoče vrednost po potrebi spremeniti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Changing journal and document type."
msgstr "Spreminjanje dnevnika in vrste dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:608
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Document Number` field needs to be registered manually and "
"the format will be validated automatically. However, in case the format is "
"invalid, a user error will be displayed indicating the correct format that "
"is expected."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Številka dokumenta` je treba vnesti ročno in format se bo "
"preveril samodejno. Če pa je format neveljaven, se prikaže uporabniška "
"napaka, ki navaja pravilen pričakovani format."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Vendor bill document number."
msgstr "Številka dobaviteljevega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:616
msgid ""
"The vendor bill number is structured in the same way as the customer "
"invoices, excepted that the document sequence is entered by the user using "
"the following format: *Document Prefix - Letter - Document Number*."
msgstr ""
"Številka dobaviteljevega računa je strukturirana enako kot računi za "
"stranke, le da uporabnik vnese zaporedje dokumenta v naslednji obliki: "
"*Predpona dokumenta - Črka - Številka dokumenta*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:621
msgid "Validate vendor bill number in AFIP"
msgstr "Preverjanje veljavnosti številke dobaviteljevega računa v AFIP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:623
msgid ""
"As most companies have internal controls to verify that the vendor bill is "
"related to an AFIP valid document, an automatic validation can be set "
"in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Settings --> Argentinean Localization --> "
"Validate document in the AFIP`, considering the following levels:"
msgstr ""
"Ker ima večina podjetij notranje kontrole za preverjanje, ali je "
"dobaviteljev račun povezan z veljavnim dokumentom AFIP, je mogoče nastaviti "
"samodejno preverjanje v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> "
"Argentinska lokalizacija --> Preveri dokument v AFIP`, ob upoštevanju "
"naslednjih ravni:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:627
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Not available:` the verification is not done (this is the default "
"value);"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ni na voljo:` preverjanje se ne izvede (to je privzeta vrednost);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:628
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Available:` the verification is done. In case the number is not "
"valid, it only displays a warning but still allows the vendor bill to be "
"posted;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Na voljo:` preverjanje se izvede. V primeru, da številka ni "
"veljavna, prikaže samo opozorilo, vendar še vedno dovoli knjiženje "
"dobaviteljevega računa;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:630
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Required:` the verification is done, and it does not allow the "
"user to post the vendor bill if the document number is not valid."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zahtevano:` preverjanje se izvede in uporabniku ne dovoli "
"knjiženja dobaviteljevega računa, če številka dokumenta ni veljavna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Verify Vendor Bills validity in AFIP."
msgstr "Preverjanje veljavnosti dobaviteljevih računov v AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:638
msgid "Validate vendor bills in Odoo"
msgstr "Preverjanje veljavnosti dobaviteljevih računov v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:640
msgid ""
"With the vendor validation settings enabled, a new button shows up on the "
"vendor bills inside of Odoo, labeled :guilabel:`Verify on AFIP`, which is "
"located next to the :guilabel:`AFIP Authorization code` field."
msgstr ""
"Ko so omogočene nastavitve preverjanja dobavitelja, se na računih "
"dobavitelja v Odooju prikazuje nov gumb z oznako :guilabel:`Preveri v AFIP`, "
"ki se nahaja poleg polja :guilabel:`Avtorizacijska koda AFIP`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Verify on AFIP."
msgstr "Preveri v AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:648
msgid ""
"In case the vendor bill cannot be validated in AFIP, a value "
"of :guilabel:`Rejected` will be displayed on the dashboard and the details "
"of the invalidation will be added to the chatter."
msgstr ""
"V primeru, da računa dobavitelja ni mogoče preveriti v AFIP, se na nadzorni "
"plošči prikaže vrednost :guilabel:`Zavrnjeno`, podrobnosti o zavrnitvi pa "
"bodo dodane v klepet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "AFIP authorization Rejected."
msgstr "Avtorizacija AFIP zavrnjena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:659
msgid "Untaxed concepts"
msgstr "Neobdavčeni koncepti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:661
msgid ""
"There are some transactions that include items that are not a part of the "
"VAT base amount, such as fuel and gasoline invoices."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo nekatere transakcije, ki vključujejo postavke, ki niso del osnove "
"za DDV, kot so računi za gorivo in bencin."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:664
msgid ""
"The vendor bill will be registered using one item for each product that is "
"part of the VAT base amount, and an additional item to register the amount "
"of the exempt concept."
msgstr ""
"Račun dobavitelja bo registriran z eno postavko za vsak izdelek, ki je del "
"osnove za DDV, in dodatno postavko za registracijo zneska oprostitvenega "
"koncepta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "VAT exempt."
msgstr "Oprostitev DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:672
msgid "Perception taxes"
msgstr "Davki zaznave"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:674
msgid ""
"The vendor bill will be registered using one item for each product that is "
"part of the VAT base amount, and the perception tax can be added in any of "
"the product lines. As a result, there will be one tax group for the VAT and "
"another for the perception. The perception default value is "
"always :guilabel:`0.10`."
msgstr ""
"Račun dobavitelja bo registriran z eno postavko za vsak izdelek, ki je del "
"osnove za DDV, davek zaznave pa je mogoče dodati v kateri koli vrstici "
"izdelka. Posledica je, da bo obstajala ena davčna skupina za DDV in druga za "
"zaznavo. Privzeta vrednost zaznave je vedno :guilabel:`0,10`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:679
msgid ""
"To edit the VAT perception and set the correct amount, you should use "
"the :guilabel:`Pencil` icon that is the next to the :guilabel:`Perception` "
"amount. After the VAT perception amount has been set, the invoice can then "
"be validated."
msgstr ""
"Za urejanje zaznave DDV in nastavitev pravilnega zneska uporabite ikono "
":guilabel:`Svečnik`, ki se nahaja poleg zneska :guilabel:`Zaznava`. Ko je "
"znesek zaznave DDV nastavljen, lahko račun potrdite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Enter the perception amount."
msgstr "Vnesite znesek zaznave."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:690
msgid "Withholding management"
msgstr "Upravljanje zadrževanja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:692
msgid ""
"The Argentinean fiscal localization module is already loaded with the "
"necessary withholdings records, which can be seen by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Taxes` and removing "
"the default :guilabel:`Sale or Purchase` filter. To verify these records, "
"the **Argentina Payment Withholdings** (`l10n_ar_withholding`) module must "
"be :ref:`installed <general/install>`:"
msgstr ""
"Argentinski modul fiskalne lokalizacije že vsebuje potrebne zapise o "
"zadrževanjih, ki si jih lahko ogledate tako, da se pomaknete na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Davki` in "
"odstranite privzeti filter :guilabel:`Prodaja ali nakup`. Za preverjanje teh "
"zapisov mora biti modul **Argentina Payment Withholdings** "
"(`l10n_ar_withholding`) :ref:`nameščen <general/install>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:698
msgid ""
"Journal entries are *not* created when payments are posted "
"unless :ref:`outstanding accounts <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>` are set up. Thus, for this feature to work properly, it is "
"important to verify that *all* payment methods within the bank journals have "
"an outstanding payment and receipt account set."
msgstr ""
"Knjižbe *niso* ustvarjene, ko so plačila knjižena, razen če so nastavljen "
":ref:`vmesni konti <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>`. Zato je za "
"pravilno delovanje te funkcije pomembno preveriti, da imajo *vsi* načini "
"plačila znotraj bančnih dnevnikov nastavljen vmesni kont za plačila in "
"prejemke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "An outstanding payment account must be set."
msgstr "Račun za neporavnana plačila mora biti nastavljen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:706
msgid ""
"This configuration is crucial for the proper accounting of withholding "
"transactions with clients and vendors."
msgstr ""
"Ta konfiguracija je ključnega pomena za pravilno računovodstvo transakcij "
"zadrževanja s strankami in dobavitelji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:710
msgid ""
"In Argentina, withholdings represent the cancellation of a specific portion "
"of the total debt owed to a supplier or a reduction in the total payment to "
"be collected from a customer. Therefore, one or multiple withholdings can be "
"recorded for each payment applied to an invoice."
msgstr ""
"V Argentini zadrževanja predstavljajo odpis določenega dela skupnega dolga "
"do dobavitelja ali zmanjšanje skupnega plačila, ki ga je treba pobrežkovati "
"od stranke. Zato je mogoče za vsako plačilo, uporabljeno za račun, "
"zabeležiti eno ali več zadrževanj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:717
msgid ""
"While Odoo already creates most of the required withholdings inside "
"the :guilabel:`Taxes` menu, in several cases, it is necessary to apply or "
"modify certain configurations to correctly calculate the withholding amount "
"on vendor payments. The following withholding types are available:"
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko Odoo večino zahtevanih zadrževanj že ustvari v meniju "
":guilabel:`Davki`, je v več primerih potrebno uporabiti ali spremeniti "
"določene konfiguracije za pravilno izračunavanje zneska zadrževanja pri "
"plačilih dobaviteljem. Na voljo so naslednje vrste zadrževanja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:721
msgid ":ref:`Earnings <l10n_ar/earnings-withholdings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Zaslužki <l10n_ar/earnings-withholdings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:722
msgid ":ref:`Earnings Scale <l10n_ar/earnings-scale-withholdings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Lestvica zasluźkov <l10n_ar/earnings-scale-withholdings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:723
msgid ":ref:`IIBB Total Amount <l10n_ar/iib-total-amount-withholdings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`IIBB skupni znesek <l10n_ar/iib-total-amount-withholdings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:724
msgid ":ref:`IIBB Non-Taxable <l10n_ar/iib-nontax-withholdings>`"
msgstr ":ref:`IIBB neobdavčljivo <l10n_ar/iib-nontax-withholdings>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:729
msgid "Earnings"
msgstr "Zaslužek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:731
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Earnings` withholdings, Odoo already has a record for each "
"regime group, which is stated under the name of the tax and the AFIP code."
msgstr ""
"Za :guilabel:`Dohodek` davčne odtegljaje Odoo že ima zapis za vsako skupino "
"režima, ki je navedena pod imenom davka in kodo AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:734
msgid ""
"Each of these records are ready to be used. As a good practice, the "
"configuration should be double checked to make sure the configuration is "
"updated and well-applied. The fields to validate are:"
msgstr ""
"Vsi ti zapisi so pripravljeni za uporabo. Kot dobra praksa je treba "
"konfiguraciju dvakrat preveriti, da se prepričamo, da je posodobljena in "
"pravilno uporabljena. Polja za preverjanje so:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:737
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount`: This is the percentage of the total payment amount which "
"is withheld."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Znesek`: To je odstotek celotnega zneska plačila, ki se odtegne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:738
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Non-Taxable Amount`: Up to this amount, the withholding does not "
"apply."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Neobdavčljiv znesek`: Do tega zneska se davčni odtegljaj ne "
"uporablja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:739
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Minimum Withholding`: If the calculated withholding amount is "
"smaller than this value, the total withholding amount is set to `0.0`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Najmanjši odtegljaj`: Če je izračunani znesek odtegljaja manjši "
"od te vrednosti, se skupni znesek odtegljaja nastavi na `0.0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:741
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Withholding Sequence`: This field helps to automate the capture "
"of a withholding number under the payment line. If this field is not set, a "
"number is manually captured while adding a withholding to a payment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zaporedje odtegljaja`: To polje pomaga pri avtomatizaciji zajema "
"številke odtegljaja v vrstici plačila. Če to polje ni nastavljeno, se "
"številka ročno zajame pri dodajanju odtegljaja k plačilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Earnings withholding type."
msgstr "Vrsta odtegljaja dohodka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:751
msgid "Earnings Scale"
msgstr "Lestvica dohodka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:753
msgid ""
"In this particular case, a percentage does not need to be set. Instead, this "
"withholding is calculated based on the value of the :guilabel:`Scale` field."
msgstr ""
"V tem posebnem primeru odstotka ni treba nastaviti. Namesto tega se ta "
"odtegljaj izračuna na podlagi vrednosti polja :guilabel:`Lestvica`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:756
msgid ""
"To view, modify, or create new scales, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Earnings Scale`. By "
"default, the Argentinian localization is preconfigured with two main scales. "
"However, scales should be created and updated as necessary to suit a "
"business's needs."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled, spreminjanje ali ustvarjanje novih lestvic pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Lestvica dohodka`. "
"Privzeto ima argentinska lokalizacija vnaprej konfigurirani dve glavni "
"lestvici. Vendar je treba lestvice ustvariti in posodobiti po potrebi glede "
"na potrebe podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:761
msgid ""
"Earnings scales are cumulative, which means that Odoo keeps track of the "
"different records created for a bill and automatically calculates the proper "
"withholding amount."
msgstr ""
"Lestvice dohodka so kumulativne, kar pomeni, da Odoo spremlja različne "
"zapise, ustvarjene za račun, in samodejno izračuna ustrezen znesek "
"odtegljaja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:767
msgid "IIBB Total Amount"
msgstr "IIBB skupni znesek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:769
msgid ""
"In this case, the necessary records related to the applicable province need "
"to be created. The withholding amount is calculated based on the "
"percentage :guilabel:`Amount` set on the tax configuration. Since Odoo does "
"not automatically synchronize the percentages applicable to each province, "
"this information needs to be manually updated."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru je treba ustvariti potrebne zapise, povezane z ustrezno "
"provinco. Znesek odtegljaja se izračuna na podlagi odstotka "
":guilabel:`Znesek`, nastavljenega v konfiguraciji davka. Ker Odoo samodejno "
"ne sinhronizira odstotkov, ki veljajo za posamezno provinco, je treba te "
"informacije ročno posodobiti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:774
msgid ""
"The recommendation, in this case, is to always duplicate and apply the "
"different configurations for each record to safeguard any technical "
"configurations that allow the proper calculation and accounting of the "
"withholding."
msgstr ""
"Priporočilo je v tem primeru vedno podvojiti in uporabiti različne "
"konfiguracije za vsak zapis, da se zaščitijo kakršne koli tehnične "
"konfiguracije, ki omogočajo pravilno izračun in računovodenje odtegljaja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:781
msgid "IIBB Untaxed"
msgstr "IIBB neobdavčeno"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:783
msgid ""
"The configuration of non-taxable gross income withholdings is very similar "
"to that of a :ref:`total amount withholding <l10n_ar/iib-total-amount-"
"withholdings>`, so the percentage :guilabel:`Amount` in each of the records "
"needs to be maintained. However, Odoo comes preconfigured with several "
"records that apply to different provinces. The difference, in this case, is "
"that it is not necessary to establish a non-taxable amount or minimum "
"withholding for this record type."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija neobdavčljivih odtegljajev bruto dohodka je zelo podobna "
"konfiguraciji :ref:`odtegljaja skupnega zneska <l10n_ar/iib-total-amount-"
"withholdings>`, zato je treba vzdrževati odstotek :guilabel:`Znesek` v "
"vsakem od zapisov. Vendar pa Odoo že vsebuje vnaprej konfigurirane številne "
"zapise, ki veljajo za različne province. Razlika je v tem primeru ta, da za "
"to vrsto zapisa ni treba določiti neobdavčljivega zneska ali najmanjšega "
"odtegljaja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:790
msgid "Partner withholding assignation"
msgstr "Dodelitev odtegljaja partnerju"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:792
msgid ""
"Once the proper configuration is set on each possible withholding for "
"partners, the applicable withholdings need to be assigned to each contact. "
"To do this, open the :guilabel:`Contacts` app and select the desired "
"partner. In the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, find the :guilabel:`Purchase "
"Withholdings` table."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ustrezna konfiguracija nastavljena za vsak možen odtegljaj za "
"partnerje, je treba veljavne odtegljaje dodeliti vsakemu kontaktu. Za to "
"odprite aplikacijo :guilabel:`Stiki` in izberite željenega partnerja. Na "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` poiščite tabelo :guilabel:`Nabavni "
"odtegljaji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:797
msgid ""
"By using the additional fields :guilabel:`From Date` and :guilabel:`To "
"Date`, the applicability of multiple withholdings can be automated across "
"different date ranges. The :guilabel:`ref` field allows you to apply an "
"internal control number to each withholding line, which is just for internal "
"reference, so it does not affect any transactions and is not visible on "
"them. These fields are accessible from the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(adjust settings)` menu."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo dodatnih polj :guilabel:`Datum od` in :guilabel:`Datum do` je "
"mogoče uporabo več obdavčitev avtomatizirati v različnih časovnih obdobjih. "
"Polje :guilabel:`ref` vam omogoča, da vsaki vrstici obdavčitve dodelite "
"interno kontrolno številko, ki služi le za interno referenco, zato ne vpliva "
"na nobene transakcije in ni vidna na njih. Ta polja so dostopna iz menija "
":icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(prilagodi nastavitve)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:803
msgid ":guilabel:`From Date`: the start of the withholding date range."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum od`: začetek časovnega obdobja obdavčitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:804
msgid ":guilabel:`To Date`: the end of the withholding date range."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum do`: konec časovnega obdobja obdavčitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:805
msgid ""
":guilabel:`ref`: apply an internal control number to each withholding line "
"that is only visible for internal reference and does not affect any "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ref`: dodelite interno kontrolno številko vsaki vrstici "
"obdavčitve, ki je vidna le za interno referenco in ne vpliva na nobene "
"transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:809
msgid "Automatic withholding calculation and application per payment"
msgstr "Samodejen izračun in uporaba obdavčitve na plačilo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:811
msgid ""
"By applying new payments to vendor bills, Odoo automatically applies and "
"calculates the proper withholding into the payment. Based on the record's "
"configuration, it may be necessary to use a reference number for each "
"withholding line."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo novih plačil na dobaviteljske račune Odoo samodejno uporabi in "
"izračuna ustrezno obdavčitev v plačilu. Glede na konfiguracijo zapisa je "
"morda potrebno uporabiti referenčno številko za vsako vrstico obdavčitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:815
msgid ""
"More withholdings can be added, or computed withholdings can be edited if "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi je mogoče dodati več obdavčitev ali urediti izračunane obdavčitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment with applied withholdings."
msgstr "Plačilo z uporabljenimi obdavčitvami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:821
msgid ""
"The total amount of the debt to be canceled is the total amount of the "
"payment. However, Odoo still captures the net amount (i.e. the amount to be "
"reconciled with the bank), which will be represented as the payment amount "
"after the withholding application."
msgstr ""
"Skupni znesek dolga, ki ga je treba poravnati, je skupni znesek plačila. "
"Vendar Odoo še vedno zajame neto znesek (tj. znesek, ki ga je treba "
"uskladiti z banko), ki bo po uporabi obdavčitve predstavljen kot znesek "
"plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:0
msgid "Payment registered form."
msgstr "Obrazec registriranega plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:829
msgid "Check management"
msgstr "Upravljanje s čeki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:831
msgid ""
"To install the *Third Party and Deferred/Electronic Checks Management* "
"module, go to :menuselection:`Apps` and search for the module by its "
"technical name `l10n_latam_check` and click the :guilabel:`Activate` button."
msgstr ""
"Za namestitev modula *Upravljanje s čeki tretjih oseb in odloženih/"
"elektronskih čekov* pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacije` in poiščite modul "
"po njegovem tehničnem imenu `l10n_latam_check` ter kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Aktiviraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "l10n_latam_check module."
msgstr "Modul l10n_latam_check."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:839
msgid ""
"This module enables the required configuration for journals and payments to:"
msgstr "Ta modul omogoča potrebno konfiguracijo za dnevnike in plačila za:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:841
msgid "Create, manage, and control your different types of checks"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje, upravljanje in nadzor različnih vrst čekov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:842
msgid "Optimize the management of *own checks* and *third party checks*"
msgstr "Optimizacija upravljanja *lastnih čekov* in *čekov tretjih oseb*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:843
msgid ""
"Have an easy and effective way to manage expiration dates from your own and "
"third party checks"
msgstr ""
"Enostaven in učinkovit način upravljanja datumov zapadlosti lastnih in čekov "
"tretjih oseb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:845
msgid ""
"Once all the configurations are made for the Argentinian electronic invoice "
"flow, it is also needed to complete certain configurations for the own "
"checks and the third party checks flows."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse konfiguracije za argentinski tok elektronskega računa opravljene, "
"je treba dokončati tudi določene konfiguracije za tok lastnih čekov in čekov "
"tretjih oseb."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:849
msgid "Own checks"
msgstr "Lastni čeki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:851
msgid ""
"Configure the bank journal used to create your own checks by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, selecting the "
"bank journal, and opening the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte bančni dnevnik, ki se uporablja za ustvarjanje lastnih čekov, "
"tako da pojdete na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Dnevniki`, izberete bančni dnevnik in odprete zavihek :guilabel:`Odhodna "
"plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:855
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Checks` should be available as a :guilabel:`Payment Method`. If "
"not, click :guilabel:`Add a line` and type `Checks` under :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method` to add them"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Čeki` bi morali biti na voljo kot :guilabel:`Način plačila`. Če "
"niso, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` in pod :guilabel:`Način plačila` "
"vnesite `Checks`, da jih dodate"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:857
msgid "Enable the :guilabel:`Use electronic and deferred checks` setting."
msgstr "Omogočite nastavitev :guilabel:`Uporabi elektronske in odložene čeke`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:860
msgid ""
"This last configuration **disables** the printing ability but enables to:"
msgstr "Ta zadnja konfiguracija **onemogoči** možnost tiskanja, vendar omogoča:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:862
msgid "Enter check numbers manually"
msgstr "Ročno vnesite številke čekov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:863
msgid "Adds a field to allocate the payment date of the check"
msgstr "Doda polje za dodelitev datuma plačila čeka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Bank journal configurations."
msgstr "Konfiguracije bančnega dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:870
msgid "Management of own checks"
msgstr "Upravljanje lastnih čekov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:872
msgid ""
"Own checks can be created directly from the vendor bill. For this process, "
"click on the :guilabel:`Register Payment` button."
msgstr ""
"Lastne čeke lahko ustvarite neposredno iz dobaviteljevega računa. Za ta "
"postopek kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Registriraj plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:875
msgid ""
"On the payment registration modal, select the bank journal from which the "
"payment is to be made and set the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Amount`."
msgstr ""
"V modalnem oknu za registracijo plačila izberite bančni dnevnik, iz katerega "
"se bo opravilo plačilo, in nastavite :guilabel:`Datum vnovčitve čeka` ter "
":guilabel:`Znesek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment pop-up window with own check options enabled."
msgstr "Pojavno okno za plačilo z omogočenimi možnostmi lastnega čeka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:883
msgid ""
"To manage current checks, the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date` field must be "
"left blank or filled in with the current date. To manage deferred checks, "
"the :guilabel:`Check Cash-In Date` must be set in the future."
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje tekočih čekov mora polje :guilabel:`Datum vnovčitve čeka` "
"ostati prazno ali izpolnjeno s trenutnim datumom. Za upravljanje odloženih "
"čekov mora biti :guilabel:`Datum vnovčitve čeka` nastavljen v prihodnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:887
msgid ""
"To manage your existing own checks, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Vendors --> Own Checks`. This window shows critical information such as "
"the dates when checks need to be paid, the total quantity of checks, and the "
"total amount paid in checks."
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje obstoječih lastnih čekov pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Lastni čeki`. To okno "
"prikazuje kritične informacije, kot so datumi, ko je treba čeke plačati, "
"skupno število čekov in skupni znesek, plačan s čeki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Own checks menu location."
msgstr "Lokacija menija lastnih čekov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:895
msgid ""
"It is important to note that the list is pre-filtered by checks that are "
"still *not reconciled* with a bank statement - that were not yet debited "
"from the bank - which can be verified with the :guilabel:`Is Matched with a "
"Bank Statement` field. If you want to see all of your own checks, delete "
"the :guilabel:`No Bank Matching` filter by clicking on the :guilabel:`X` "
"symbol."
msgstr ""
"Pomembno je opozoriti, da je seznam vnaprej filtriran po čekih, ki še *niso "
"usklajeni* z bančnim izpiskom - ki še niso bili obremenjeni iz banke - kar "
"lahko preverite s poljem :guilabel:`Je usklajen z bančnim izpiskom`. Če "
"želite videti vse svoje lastne čeke, izbrišite filter :guilabel:`Brez "
"bančnega ujemanja` s klikom na simbol :guilabel:`X`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Own checks menu organization and filtering."
msgstr "Organizacija in filtriranje menija lastnih čekov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:905
msgid "Cancel an own check"
msgstr "Prekliči lastni ček"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:907
msgid ""
"To cancel an own check created in Odoo, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Own Checks` and select the "
"check to be cancelled, then click on the :guilabel:`Void Check` button. This "
"will break the reconciliation with the vendor bills and the bank statements "
"and leave the check in a **cancelled** state."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preklicati lastni ček, ustvarjen v Odoo, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Lastni čeki` in izberite "
"ček, ki ga želite preklicati, nato kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Razveljavi ček`. "
"To bo prekinilo uskladitev z dobaviteljevimi računi in bančnimi izpiski ter "
"pustilo ček v stanju **preklican**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Empty Check button to cancel Own Checks"
msgstr "Gumb za razveljavitev za preklic lastnih čekov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:917
msgid "Third party checks"
msgstr "Čeki tretjih oseb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:919
msgid ""
"In order to register payments using third party checks, two specific "
"journals need to be configured. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and create two "
"new journals:"
msgstr ""
"Za registracijo plačil s čeki tretjih oseb je treba konfigurirati dva "
"specifična dnevnika. To storite tako, da pojdete na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki` in ustvarite "
"dva nova dnevnika:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:923
msgid "`Third Party Checks`"
msgstr "Čeki tretjih oseb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:924
msgid "`Rejected Third Party Checks`"
msgstr "`Zavrnjeni čeki tretjih oseb`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:927
msgid ""
"You can manually create more journals if you have multiple points of sale "
"and need journals for those."
msgstr ""
"Če imate več prodajnih mest in potrebujete dnevnike zanje, lahko ročno "
"ustvarite dodatne dnevnike."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:930
msgid ""
"To create the *Third Party Checks* journal, click the :guilabel:`New` button "
"and configure the following:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje dnevnika *Čeki tretjih oseb* kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo` "
"in konfigurirajte naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:933
msgid "Type `Third Party Checks` as the :guilabel:`Journal Name`"
msgstr "Vnesite `Third Party Checks` kot :guilabel:`Ime dnevnika`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:934
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:968
msgid "Select :guilabel:`Cash` as :guilabel:`Type`"
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Gotovina` kot :guilabel:`Tip`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:935
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab, set :guilabel:`Cash Account`: to "
"`1.1.1.02.010 Cheques de Terceros`, input a :guilabel:`Short Code` of your "
"choice, and select a :guilabel:`Currency`"
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Vnosi v dnevnik` nastavite :guilabel:`Račun gotovine`: "
"na `1.1.1.02.010 Cheques de Terceros`, vnesite :guilabel:`Kratko kodo` po "
"vaši izbiri in izberite :guilabel:`Valuto`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Automatically created cash account."
msgstr "Samodejno ustvarjen račun gotovine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:942
msgid "The available payment methods are listed in the *payments* tabs:"
msgstr "Razpoložljive plačilne metode so navedene v zavihkih *plačila*:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:944
msgid ""
"For new incoming third party checks, go to :menuselection:`Incoming Payments "
"tab --> Add a line` and select :guilabel:`New Third Party Checks`. This "
"method is used to create *new* third party checks."
msgstr ""
"Za nove prejete čeke tretjih oseb pojdite na :menuselection:`zavihek Prejeta "
"plačila --> Dodaj vrstico` in izberite :guilabel:`Novi čeki tretjih oseb`. "
"Ta metoda se uporablja za ustvarjanje *novih* čekov tretjih oseb."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:947
msgid ""
"For incoming and outgoing existing third party checks, go "
"to :menuselection:`Incoming Payments tab --> Add a line` and "
"select :guilabel:`Existing Third Party Checks`. Repeat the same step for "
"the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab. This method is used to receive and/or "
"pay vendor bills using already *existing* checks, as well as for internal "
"transfers."
msgstr ""
"Za prejete in izdane obstoječe čeke tretjih oseb pojdite na "
":menuselection:`zavihek Prejeta plačila --> Dodaj vrstico` in izberite "
":guilabel:`Obstoječi čeki tretjih oseb`. Ponovite isti korak za zavihek "
":guilabel:`Izdana plačila`. Ta metoda se uporablja za prejemanje in/ali "
"plačevanje računov dobaviteljev z že *obstoječimi* čeki, kot tudi za "
"notranje prenose."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:953
msgid ""
"You can delete pre-existing payment methods appearing by default when "
"configuring the third party checks journals."
msgstr ""
"Vnaprej obstoječe načine plačila, ki se privzeto prikažejo pri konfiguraciji "
"dnevnikov čekov tretjih oseb, lahko izbrišete."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment methods automatically created."
msgstr "Samodejno ustvarjeni načini plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:960
msgid ""
"The *Rejected Third Party Checks* journal also needs to be created and/or "
"configured. This journal is used to manage rejected third party checks and "
"can be utilized to send checks rejected at the moment of collection or when "
"coming from vendors when rejected."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako je treba ustvariti in/ali konfigurirati dnevnik *Zavrnjeni čeki "
"tretjih oseb*. Ta dnevnik se uporablja za upravljanje zavrnjenih čekov "
"tretjih oseb in ga je mogoče uporabiti za pošiljanje čekov, zavrnjenih v "
"trenutku pobotnice, ali ko prihajajo od dobaviteljev in so zavrnjeni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:964
msgid ""
"To create the *Rejected Third Party Checks* journal, click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button and configure the following:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje dnevnika *Zavrnjeni čeki tretjih oseb* kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Novo` in konfigurirajte naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:967
msgid "Type `Rejected Third Party Checks` as the :guilabel:`Journal Name`"
msgstr "Vnesite `Zavrnjeni čeki tretjih oseb` kot :guilabel:`Ime dnevnika`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:969
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab, set :guilabel:`Cash Account`: to "
"`1.1.1.01.002 Rejected Third Party Checks`, input a :guilabel:`Short Code` "
"of your choice, and select a :guilabel:`Currency`"
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Knjižbe` nastavite :guilabel:`Denarni račun`: na "
"`1.1.1.01.002 Zavrnjeni čeki tretjih oseb`, vnesite :guilabel:`Kratko kodo` "
"po vaši izbiri in izberite :guilabel:`Valuto`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:973
msgid "Use the same payment methods as the *Third Party Checks* journal."
msgstr "Uporabite enake načine plačila kot pri dnevniku *Čeki tretjih oseb*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:976
msgid "New third party checks"
msgstr "Novi čeki tretjih oseb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:978
msgid ""
"To register a *new* third party check for a customer invoice, click "
"the :guilabel:`Register Payment` button. In the pop-up window, you must "
"select :guilabel:`Third Party Checks` as journal for the payment "
"registration."
msgstr ""
"Za registracijo *novega* čeka tretje osebe za račun stranke kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Registriraj plačilo`. V pojavnem oknu morate izbrati "
":guilabel:`Čeki tretjih oseb` kot dnevnik za registracijo plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:982
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`New Third Party Checks` as :guilabel:`Payment Method`, and "
"fill in the :guilabel:`Check Number`, :guilabel:`Payment Date`, "
"and :guilabel:`Check Bank`. Optionally, you can manually add "
"the :guilabel:`Check Issuer Vat`, but this is automatically filled by the "
"customer's VAT number related to the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`New Third Party Checks` kot :guilabel:`Payment Method` "
"in izpolnite :guilabel:`Check Number`, :guilabel:`Payment Date` in "
":guilabel:`Check Bank`. Po želji lahko ročno dodate :guilabel:`Check Issuer "
"Vat`, vendar se to polje samodejno izpolni z davčno številko stranke, "
"povezano z računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment pop-up window with New Third Party Check options enabled."
msgstr "Pojavno okno za plačilo z omogočenimi možnostmi New Third Party Check."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:992
msgid "Existing third party checks"
msgstr "Obstoječi čeki tretjih oseb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:994
msgid ""
"To pay a vendor bill with an *existing* check, click the :guilabel:`Register "
"Payment` button. In the pop-up window, you must select :guilabel:`Third "
"Party Checks` as journal for the payment registration."
msgstr ""
"Če želite plačati dobaviteljev račun z *obstoječim* čekom, kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Register Payment`. V pojavnem oknu morate izbrati "
":guilabel:`Third Party Checks` kot dnevnik za registracijo plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:998
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Existing Third Party Checks` as :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method`, and select a check from the :guilabel:`Check` field. The field "
"shows all **available existing checks** to be used as payment for vendor "
"bills."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Existing Third Party Checks` kot :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method` in izberite ček v polju :guilabel:`Check`. Polje prikazuje vse "
"**razpoložljive obstoječe čeke**, ki jih je mogoče uporabiti kot plačilo za "
"dobaviteljeve račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Payment pop-up window with Existing Third Party Check options enabled."
msgstr ""
"Pojavno okno za plačilo z omogočenimi možnostmi Existing Third Party Check."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1006
msgid ""
"When an **existing third party check** is used, you can review the "
"operations related to it. For example, you can see if a third party check "
"made to pay a customer invoice was later used as an existing third party "
"check to pay a vendor bill."
msgstr ""
"Ko je uporabljen **obstoječ ček tretje osebe**, si lahko ogledate operacije, "
"povezane z njim. Na primer, vidite lahko, ali je bil ček tretje osebe, "
"narejen za plačilo računa stranki, pozneje uporabljen kot obstoječ ček "
"tretje osebe za plačilo dobaviteljevega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1010
msgid ""
"To do so, either go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Third "
"Party Checks` or :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Own Checks` "
"depending on the case, and click on a check. In the :guilabel:`Check Current "
"Journal` field, click on :guilabel:`=> Check Operations` to bring up the "
"check's history and movements."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da greste bodisi na :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Third Party Checks` ali :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Vendors --> Own Checks`, odvisno od primera, in kliknite na ček. V polju "
":guilabel:`Check Current Journal` kliknite na :guilabel:`=> Check "
"Operations`, da prikažete zgodovino in premike čeka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Check Operations menu."
msgstr "Meni Check Operations."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1019
msgid ""
"The menu also displays critical information related to these operations, "
"such as:"
msgstr ""
"Meni prav tako prikazuje kritične informacije, povezane s temi operacijami, "
"kot so:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1021
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Payment Type`, allowing to classify whether it is a payment "
"*sent* to a vendor or a payment *received* from a customer"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Payment Type`, ki omogoča razvrstitev, ali gre za plačilo "
"*poslano* dobavitelju ali plačilo *prejeto* od stranke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1023
msgid "The :guilabel:`Journal` in which the check is currently registered"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Journal`, v katerem je ček trenutno registriran"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1024
msgid ""
"The **partner** associated with the operation (either customer or vendor)."
msgstr "**Partner**, povezan z operacijo (bodisi stranka bodisi dobavitelj)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1029
msgid "Ecommerce electronic invoicing"
msgstr "Elektronsko izdajanje računov za e-trgovino"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1032
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the *Argentinian eCommerce* "
"(`l10n_ar_website_sale`) module to enable the following features and "
"configurations:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Namestite <general/install>` modul *Argentinian eCommerce* "
"(`l10n_ar_website_sale`), da omogočite naslednje funkcije in konfiguracije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1035
msgid "Clients being able to create online accounts for eCommerce purposes."
msgstr "Možnost, da stranke ustvarijo spletne račune za namene e-trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1036
msgid "Support for required fiscal fields in the eCommerce application."
msgstr "Podpora za obvezna fiskalna polja v aplikaciji za e-trgovino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1037
msgid "Receive payments for sale orders online."
msgstr "Prejem plačil za prodajne naloge prek spleta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1038
msgid "Generate electronic documents from the eCommerce application."
msgstr "Ustvarjanje elektronskih dokumentov iz aplikacije za e-trgovino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1043
msgid ""
"Once all of the configurations are made for the Argentinian :ref:`electronic "
"invoice <argentina/configure-your-company>` flow, it is also necessary to "
"complete certain configurations to integrate the eCommerce flow."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse konfiguracije opravljene za argentinski :ref:`elektronski račun "
"<argentina/configure-your-company>`, je treba dokončati tudi določene "
"konfiguracije za integracijo poteka dela e-trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1048
msgid "Client account registration"
msgstr "Registracija računa stranke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1050
msgid ""
"To configure your website for client accounts, follow the instructions in "
"the :doc:`checkout <../../websites/ecommerce/checkout>` documentation."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo spletnega mesta za račune strank sledite navodilom v "
"dokumentaciji :doc:`checkout <../../websites/ecommerce/checkout>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1054
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:810
msgid "Automatic invoice"
msgstr "Samodejen račun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1056
msgid ""
"Configure your website to generate electronic documents in the sales process "
"by navigating to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"activating the :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice` feature in "
"the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section to automatically generate the required "
"electronic documents when the online payment is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte spletno mesto za ustvarjanje elektronskih dokumentov v "
"prodajnem procesu tako, da se pomaknete na :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` in aktivirate funkcijo :guilabel:`Automatic "
"Invoice` v razdelku :guilabel:`Invoicing`, da se zahtevani elektronski "
"dokumenti samodejno ustvarijo, ko je spletno plačilo potrjeno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Feature activated to invoice automatically."
msgstr "Aktivirana funkcija za samodejno izdajanje računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1065
msgid ""
"Since an online payment needs to be confirmed for the :guilabel:`Automatic "
"Invoice` feature to generate the document, a :doc:`payment provider <../"
"payment_providers>` **must** be configured for the related website."
msgstr ""
"Ker mora biti spletno plačilo potrjeno, da funkcija :guilabel:`Automatic "
"Invoice` ustvari dokument, **mora** biti za povezano spletno mesto "
"konfiguriran :doc:`payment provider <../payment_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1070
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/brazil.rst:294
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:246
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:121
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:172
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/indonesia.rst:60
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:258
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:348
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1338
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1773
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:846
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1019
msgid "Products"
msgstr "Izdelki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1072
msgid ""
"To allow your products to be invoiced when an online payment is confirmed, "
"navigate to the desired product from :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --"
"> Products`. In the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, set "
"the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` to :guilabel:`Ordered quantities` and "
"define the desired :guilabel:`Customer Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Da dovolite, da se vaši izdelki zaračunajo, ko je spletno plačilo potrjeno, "
"se pomaknite na želeni izdelek iz :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> "
"Products`. V zavihku :guilabel:`General Information` nastavite "
":guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` na :guilabel:`Ordered quantities` in določite "
"želene :guilabel:`Customer Taxes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1078
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:970
msgid "Invoicing flow for eCommerce"
msgstr "Potek izdajanja računov za eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1080
msgid ""
"Once the configurations mentioned above are all set, clients can complete "
"the following required steps in the *Argentinian eCommerce* flow to input "
"fiscal fields in the checkout process."
msgstr ""
"Ko so zgoraj omenjene konfiguracije vse nastavljene, lahko stranke izpolnijo "
"naslednje zahtevane korake v poteku *Argentinian eCommerce* za vnos davčnih "
"polj v postopku blagajne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1083
msgid ""
"Fiscal fields are available for input in the checkout process once "
"the :guilabel:`Country` field is set as `Argentina`. Inputting the fiscal "
"data enables the purchase to conclude in the corresponding electronic "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Davčna polja so na voljo za vnos v postopku blagajne, ko je polje "
":guilabel:`Country` nastavljeno na `Argentina`. Vnos davčnih podatkov "
"omogoči zaključek nakupa v ustreznem elektronskem dokumentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "Fiscal required fields for electronic invoicing."
msgstr "Zahtevana davčna polja za elektronsko izdajanje računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1091
msgid ""
"When the client makes a successful purchase and payment, the necessary "
"invoice is generated with the corresponding layout and fiscal stamps stated "
"in the :ref:`Invoice printed report <argentina/invoice-printed-report>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko stranka uspešno opravi nakup in plačilo, se ustvari potreben račun z "
"ustrezno postavitvijo in davčnimi žigi, navedenimi v :ref:`Invoice printed "
"report <argentina/invoice-printed-report>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1096
msgid ":doc:`Client account creation <../../websites/ecommerce/checkout>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Client account creation <../../websites/ecommerce/checkout>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1099
msgid "Liquidity product direct sales"
msgstr "Neposredna prodaja likvidnostnih izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1101
msgid ""
"Liquidity product direct sales are used for sales involving third parties. "
"For such sales, the seller and the proprietary company of the goods can each "
"register their corresponding sales and purchases."
msgstr ""
"Neposredna prodaja likvidnostnih izdelkov se uporablja za prodajo, ki "
"vključuje tretje osebe. Za takšno prodajo lahko prodajalec in lastniško "
"podjetje blaga vsak registrira svoje ustrezne prodaje in nakupe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1106
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the *Argentinian Electronic Invoicing* "
"module (`l10n_ar_edi`) to use this feature."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` modul *Argentinian Electronic Invoicing* "
"(`l10n_ar_edi`) za uporabo te funkcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1113
msgid "Purchase journal"
msgstr "Dnevnik nakupov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1115
msgid ""
"A purchase journal is needed to generate an electronic vendor bill with a "
"document type *Liquidity Product*. This journal needs to be synchronized "
"with the AFIP as it will be used to generate the liquidity product "
"electronic document."
msgstr ""
"Dnevnik nakupov je potreben za ustvarjanje elektronskega dobaviteljevega "
"računa z vrsto dokumenta *Liquidity Product*. Ta dnevnik mora biti "
"sinhroniziran z AFIP, saj bo uporabljen za ustvarjanje elektronskega "
"dokumenta likvidnostnega izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1119
msgid ""
"To modify the existing purchase journal or create a new one, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`. Then, select "
"the existing purchase journal or click the :guilabel:`New` button, and fill "
"in the following required information:"
msgstr ""
"Za spremembo obstoječega dnevnika nakupov ali ustvarjanje novega se "
"pomaknite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`. "
"Nato izberite obstoječi dnevnik nakupov ali kliknite gumb :guilabel:`New` in "
"izpolnite naslednje zahtevane informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1123
msgid ":guilabel:`Type`: select :guilabel:`Purchase`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Type`: izberite :guilabel:`Purchase`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Documents`: check this field to to be able select the "
"electronic document type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabi dokumente`: označite to polje, da boste lahko izbrali "
"vrsto elektronskega dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1125
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is AFIP POS`: check this field to be able to generate electronic "
"documents."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Je AFIP POS`: označite to polje, da boste lahko ustvarili "
"elektronske dokumente."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`AFIP POS System`: select :guilabel:`Electronic Invoice - Web "
"Service` from the drop-down menu in order to send the electronic document to "
"AFIP via web service."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`AFIP POS sistem`: izberite :guilabel:`Elektronski račun - spletna "
"storitev` iz spustnega menija, da boste poslali elektronski dokument na AFIP "
"prek spletne storitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`AFIP POS Number`: is the number configured in the AFIP to "
"identify the operations related to this AFIP POS."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`AFIP POS številka`: je številka, konfigurirana v AFIP za "
"identifikacijo operacij, povezanih s tem AFIP POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`AFIP POS Address`: is the field related to the commercial address "
"registered for the POS, which is usually the same address as the company. "
"For example, if a company has multiple stores (fiscal locations) then the "
"AFIP will require the company to have one AFIP POS per location. This "
"location will be printed in the invoice report."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`AFIP POS naslov`: je polje, povezano s poslovnim naslovom, "
"registriranim za POS, ki je običajno enak naslov kot naslov podjetja. Na "
"primer, če ima podjetje več trgovin (davčnih lokacij), bo AFIP zahteval, da "
"ima podjetje en AFIP POS na lokacijo. Ta lokacija bo natisnjena na poročilu "
"o računu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "l10n_ar Purchase Journal Configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija dnevnika nabav l10n_ar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1140
msgid "Sales journal"
msgstr "Dnevnik prodaje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1142
msgid ""
"A sales journal is needed to register the invoice when a product is sold to "
"a third party that will then sell the same product. This journal will not be "
"synced with AFIP as the invoice will not be electronic."
msgstr ""
"Dnevnik prodaje je potreben za registracijo računa, ko je izdelek prodan "
"tretji osebi, ki bo nato prodala isti izdelek. Ta dnevnik ne bo "
"sinhroniziran z AFIP, saj račun ne bo elektronski."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1146
msgid ""
"To modify the existing sales journal or create a new one, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`. Then, "
"selecting the sales journal or click the :guilabel:`New` button, and fill in "
"the following required information:"
msgstr ""
"Za spremembo obstoječega dnevnika prodaje ali ustvarjanje novega pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki`. Nato izberite "
"dnevnik prodaje ali kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo` in izpolnite naslednje "
"zahtevane informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1150
msgid ":guilabel:`Type`: select :guilabel:`Sales`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrsta`: izberite :guilabel:`Prodaja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1151
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Documents`: check this field on the journal to select the "
"electronic document type (in this case the electronic invoice)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabi dokumente`: označite to polje v dnevniku, da boste lahko "
"izbrali vrsto elektronskega dokumenta (v tem primeru elektronski račun)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "l10n_ar Sales Journal Configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija dnevnika prodaje l10n_ar."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1159
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1360
msgid "Invoicing flow"
msgstr "Potek izdajanja računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1161
msgid ""
"Once the configurations are all set, the *Liquidity Product Vendor Bill* "
"will be generated by the company that is selling the product on behalf of "
"another party. For example, a distributor of a specific product."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse konfiguracije nastavljene, bo *račun dobavitelja izdelka "
"likvidnosti* ustvarilo podjetje, ki prodaja izdelek v imenu druge stranke. "
"Na primer, distributer določenega izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1168
msgid ""
"As part of the localization installation, financial reporting for Argentina "
"is available in the :guilabel:`Accounting` dashboard. To access these "
"reports, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Argentinean Statements`."
msgstr ""
"Kot del namestitve lokalizacije je finančno poročanje za Argentino na voljo "
"na nadzorni plošči :guilabel:`Računovodstvo`. Za dostop do teh poročil "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Argentinski "
"izkazi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1172
msgid ""
"To access the VAT book report, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Tax Report`, click the :icon:`fa-book` (:guilabel:`book`), and "
"select :guilabel:`Argentinean VAT book (AR)`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do poročila knjige DDV pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Davčno poročilo`, kliknite "
":icon:`fa-book` (:guilabel:`knjiga`) in izberite :guilabel:`Argentinska "
"knjiga DDV (AR)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1176
msgid ""
"The VAT book report can be exported as a `.zip` file by selecting it in the "
"dropdown menu in the top-left corner."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo knjige DDV lahko izvozite kot datoteko `.zip`, tako da jo izberete "
"v spustnem meniju v zgornjem levem kotu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1180
msgid "VAT summary"
msgstr "Povzetek DDV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1182
msgid ""
"This pivot table is designed to check the monthly VAT totals. This report is "
"for internal use and is not sent to the AFIP."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrtilna tabela je zasnovana za preverjanje mesečnih vsot DDV. To poročilo "
"je za notranjo uporabo in se ne pošilja na AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1186
msgid "IIBB - Sales by jurisdiction"
msgstr "IIBB - Prodaja po jurisdikcijah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1188
msgid ""
"This pivot table allows you to validate the gross income in each "
"jurisdiction. It serves as an affidavit for the corresponding taxes due but "
"is not submitted to the AFIP."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrtilna tabela omogoča preverjanje bruto dohodka v vsaki jurisdikciji. "
"Služi kot izjava za ustrezne davke, vendar se ne predloži AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "IIBB Sales by jurisdiction."
msgstr "IIBB - Prodaja po jurisdikcijah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1195
msgid "IIBB - Purchases by jurisdiction"
msgstr "IIBB - Nakupi po jurisdikcijah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:1197
msgid ""
"This pivot table allows you to validate the gross purchases in each "
"jurisdiction. It serves as an affidavit for the corresponding taxes due but "
"is not submitted to the AFIP."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrtilna tabela omogoča preverjanje bruto nakupov v vsaki jurisdikciji. "
"Služi kot izjava za ustrezne davke, vendar se ne predloži AFIP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/argentina.rst:None
msgid "IIBB Purchases by jurisdiction."
msgstr "IIBB Nakupi po jurisdikcijah."

