"For example, adding the `1000` tag to an account maps it (virtually) to the "
"SAF-T COA account with the code `1000`. Any number can be used as long as "
"there is an account in the SAF-T COA with that code."
msgstr ""
"Potrebne informacije za preslikavo se zagotovijo z dodajanjem oznak kontom. "
"Če na primer kontu dodate oznako `1000`, ga preslika (virtualno) na SAF-T "
"kontni načrt s kodo `1000`. Uporabite lahko katero koli številko, če obstaja "
"konto v SAF-T kontnem načrtu s to kodo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:135
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Austria - Accounting` module adds a tag for each SAF-T COA "
"account. Furthermore, it automatically maps many accounts from the default "
"Austrian COA."
msgstr ""
"Modul :guilabel:`Avstrija - Računovodstvo` doda oznako za vsak SAF-T kontni "
"načrt. Poleg tega samodejno preslika številne konte iz privzetega "
"avstrijskega kontnega načrta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:138
msgid ""
"You can try exporting the SAF-T report to check if there are unmapped "
"accounts (or mapped to multiple SAF-T accounts). A warning will be displayed "
"if there is any issue with your configuration or the mapping. "
"Clicking :guilabel:`View Problematic Accounts` lets you view them."
msgstr ""
"Lahko poskusite izvoziti poročilo SAF-T, da preverite, ali obstajajo "
"nepreslikani konti (ali preslikani na več SAF-T kontov). Prikazalo se bo "
"opozorilo, če obstaja kakršna koli težava z vašo konfiguracijo ali "
"preslikavo. S klikom na :guilabel:`Prikaži problematične konte` si jih lahko "
"ogledate."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:143
msgid ""
":doc:`Chart of accounts documentation <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dokumentacija kontnega načrta <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:148
msgid "Exporting the SAF-T report"
msgstr "Izvoz poročila SAF-T"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:150
msgid ""
"To export the SAF-T report, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reports --> "
"General Ledger`. Click the right side of the :guilabel:`PDF` button and "
"select :guilabel:`SAF-T`."
msgstr ""
"Za izvoz poročila SAF-T pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročila --> Glavna knjiga`. Kliknite na desno stran gumba :guilabel:`PDF` "
"in izberite :guilabel:`SAF-T`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:None
msgid "The SAF-T button to export the file in XML format"
msgstr "Gumb SAF-T za izvoz datoteke v formatu XML"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:159
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/germany.rst:235
msgid "Point of Sale"
msgstr "Prodajna točka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:164
msgid "RKSV (Registrierkassensicherheitsverordnung)"
msgstr "RKSV (Registrierkassensicherheitsverordnung)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:166
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`RKSV (Registrierkassensicherheitsverordnung)` is an Austrian "
"regulation designed to secure cash registers and prevent tax fraud. It "
"requires businesses to use tamper-proof electronic cash register systems, "
"including :doc:`point of sale </applications/sales/point_of_sale>` systems."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`RKSV (Registrierkassensicherheitsverordnung)` je avstrijska uredba, "
"zasnovana za zaščito blagajn in preprečevanje davčnih goljufij. Od podjetij "
"zahteva uporabo varnih elektronskih blagajniških sistemov, vključno s "
"sistemi :doc:`prodajne točke </applications/sales/point_of_sale>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:171
msgid ""
"These systems must be equipped with a **Signature Creation Unit (SCU)**, "
"which is responsible for signing each transaction. This ensures that the "
"transaction data cannot be altered. Additionally, the regulation mandates "
"periodic transaction data exports for audit purposes. Odoo provides a "
"compliant solution through `fiskaly <https://fiskaly.com>`_, a *cloud-based "
"solution*."
msgstr ""
"Ti sistemi morajo biti opremljeni z **enoto za ustvarjanje podpisov (SCU)**, "
"ki je odgovorna za podpisovanje vsake transakcije. To zagotavlja, da "
"podatkov o transakciji ni mogoče spremeniti. Poleg tega uredba zahteva "
"periodične izvoz podatkov o transakcijah za revizijske namene. Odoo "
"zagotavlja skladno rešitev prek `fiskaly <https://fiskaly.com>`_, *rešitve v "
"oblaku*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:181
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the **Austria - Security Regulation for "
"Point of Sale** (`l10n_at_pos`) module."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Namestite <general/install>` modul **Avstrija - Varnostna uredba za "
"prodajno točko** (`l10n_at_pos`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:185
msgid ""
"If this module is not listed, :ref:`update the app list <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Če ta modul ni naveden, :ref:`posodobite seznam aplikacij <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:187
msgid ""
"Once installed, open the Settings app, navigate to the :guilabel:`Companies` "
"section, and click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Update Info` to make "
"sure the :ref:`information <localizations/austria/saf-t-company>` is up-to-"
"date and correctly filled in."
msgstr ""
"Po namestitvi odprite aplikacijo Nastavitve, pojdite na razdelek "
":guilabel:`Podjetja` in kliknite :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Posodobi "
"podatke`, da zagotovite ažurnost in pravilnost :ref:`podatkov <localizations/"
"austria/saf-t-company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:191
msgid ""
"Then, open the :guilabel:`Fiskaly` tab and click :guilabel:`Generate "
"Credentials` to create a new organization in the Fiskaly system and generate "
"the necessary credentials to run the service. Next, "
"click :guilabel:`Authenticate Keys` to validate those credentials."
msgstr ""
"Nato odprite zavihek :guilabel:`Fiskaly` in kliknite :guilabel:`Generiraj "
"poverilnice`, da ustvarite novo organizacijo v sistemu Fiskaly in generirate "
"potrebne poverilnice za zagon storitve. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Preveri "
"ključe`, da potrdite te poverilnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:198
msgid "Link a Fiskaly organization to FinanzOnline"
msgstr "Povežite organizacijo Fiskaly s FinanzOnline"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:200
msgid ""
"To link the Fiskaly organization with the Austrian Ministry of Finance, "
"FinanzOnline credentials must be provided. To do so, fill in the following "
"information in your company's :guilabel:`Fiskaly` tab:"
msgstr ""
"Za povezavo organizacije Fiskaly z avstrijskim ministrstvom za finance je "
"treba navesti poverilnice FinanzOnline. To storite tako, da v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Fiskaly` vašega podjetja izpolnite naslednje informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:204
msgid ":guilabel:`Participant Identifier`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Identifikator udeleženca`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:205
msgid ":guilabel:`User Identifier`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Identifikator uporabnika`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:206
msgid ":guilabel:`User Pin`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`PIN uporabnika`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:209
msgid ""
"FinanzOnline credentials can be accessed through an existing account or by "
"`creating a new one <https://finanzonline.bmf.gv.at/>`_ if it has not yet "
"been set up."
msgstr ""
"Do poverilnic FinanzOnline lahko dostopate prek obstoječega računa ali `z "
"ustvarjanjem novega<https://finanzonline.bmf.gv.at/>`_, če še ni bil "
"nastavljen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:213
msgid ""
"Random credentials can be used in **test mode**, but valid credentials are "
"required in **production mode**."
msgstr ""
"V **preskusnem načinu** lahko uporabite naključne poverilnice, vendar so v "
"**produkcijskem načinu** potrebne veljavne poverilnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:216
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Authenticate FON` to link your Fiskaly organization to the "
"Austrian Ministry of Finance and start regular :doc:`point of sale </"
"applications/sales/point_of_sale>` operations."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Overi FON`, da povežete svojo organizacijo Fiskaly z "
"avstrijskim ministrstvom za finance in začnete z rednim delovanjem "
":doc:`prodajne točke </applications/sales/point_of_sale>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:222
msgid "Digitally signatured receipts"
msgstr "Digitalno podpisani računi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:224
msgid ""
"To ensure the integrity and authenticity of the receipts, the system "
"automatically signs them using the :abbr:`SCU (Signature Creation Unit)` in "
"a background process. The receipt then displays an encrypted signature as a "
"QR code containing the receipt number and information about the SCU used to "
"sign it."
msgstr ""
"Za zagotovitev celovitosti in pristnosti računov jih sistem samodejno "
"podpiše z uporabo :abbr:`SCU (enota za ustvarjanje podpisa)` v postopku v "
"ozadju. Račun nato prikaže šifriran podpis v obliki QR kode, ki vsebuje "
"številko računa in informacije o SCU, uporabljenem za podpis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:230
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`SCU (Signature Creation Unit)` is unavailable, receipts may "
"not include a QR code; in such cases:"
msgstr ""
"Če :abbr:`SCU (enota za ustvarjanje podpisa)` ni na voljo, računi morda ne "
"bodo vključevali QR kode; v takih primerih:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:233
msgid ""
"Make sure the receipt includes a :guilabel:`Sicherheitseinrichtung "
"ausgefallen` message, indicating that the system is linked to Fiskaly "
"services, but the SCU is temporarily unavailable."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da račun vsebuje sporočilo :guilabel:`Sicherheitseinrichtung "
"ausgefallen`, kar pomeni, da je sistem povezan s storitvami Fiskaly, vendar "
"SCU začasno ni na voljo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:236
msgid ""
"If this message is missing from the receipt, it indicates no connection to "
"Fiskaly services."
msgstr ""
"Če tega sporočila ni na računu, to pomeni, da ni povezave s storitvami "
"Fiskaly."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:238
msgid ""
"Orders that remain unsigned due to SCU unavailability can be signed "
"manually. To do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Naročila, ki ostanejo nepodpisana zaradi nedosegljivosti SCU, je mogoče "
"podpisati ročno. To storite tako:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:241
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`."
msgstr "Pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Naročila --> Naročila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:242
msgid ""
"To identify unsigned orders, click the :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(adjust settings)` icon in the :guilabel:`Orders` list "
"view to reveal the :guilabel:`Receipt Signed?` column."
msgstr ""
"Za prepoznavanje nepodpisanih naročil kliknite ikono :icon:`oi-settings-"
"adjust` :guilabel:`(prilagodi nastavitve)` v pogledu seznama "
":guilabel:`Naročila`, da se prikaže stolpec :guilabel:`Račun podpisan?`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:245
msgid ""
"Select the unsigned orders, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, and "
"select :guilabel:`Sign Order`."
msgstr ""
"Izberite nepodpisana naročila, kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` "
"in izberite :guilabel:`Podpiši naročilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:251
msgid "DEP7 export"
msgstr "Izvoz DEP7"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:253
msgid ""
"The exported :abbr:`DEP7 (Digitale Schnittstelle der Finanzverwaltung für "
"Kassensysteme)` file allows authorities to verify transactions and ensure "
"compliance with anti-fraud measures. Businesses must periodically generate "
"it for audit purposes and submit it to the Austrian tax authorities upon "
"request."
msgstr ""
"Izvožena datoteka :abbr:`DEP7 (digitalni vmesnik davčne uprave za "
"blagajniške sisteme)` organom omogoča preverjanje transakcij in "
"zagotavljanje skladnosti s protiprevarniškim ukrepi. Podjetja jo morajo "
"redno ustvarjati za namene revizije in jo na zahtevo predložiti avstrijskim "
"davčnim organom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:258
msgid ""
"To generate it, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Reporting --> DEP7 "
"Reports`, and, in the :guilabel:`DEP7 Reports`, fill in the following "
"mandatory fields:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Poročanje --> "
"Poročila DEP7` in v :guilabel:`Poročila DEP7` izpolnite naslednja obvezna "
"polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:261
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Start Datetime`: Exports data with dates on or after the start "
"date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Začetni datum in čas`: Izvozi podatke z datumi na ali po začetnem "
"datumu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:262
msgid ""
":guilabel:`End Datetime`: Exports data with dates on or before the end date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Končni datum in čas`: Izvozi podatke z datumi na ali pred končnim "
"datumom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:263
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Point of Sale`: Specify from which point of sale(s) data must be "
"exported."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prodajna točka`: Določite, iz katere prodajne točke (točk) je "
"treba izvoziti podatke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:265
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Print` to download the :abbr:`JSON (JavaScript Object "
"Notation)` file with DEP7 data."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Natisni`, da prenesete datoteko :abbr:`JSON "
"(JavaScript Object Notation)` s podatki DEP7."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:None
msgid "DEP7 Reports"
msgstr "Poročila DEP7"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:274
msgid "Monthly / Yearly closing receipts"
msgstr "Mesečni / letni zapiralni računi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:276
msgid ""
"To print monthly/yearly closing receipts, :ref:`open the related POS "
"register <pos/use/open-register>` from the **POS dashboard**. Click "
"the :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(list view)` icon in the top-right "
"corner and select :guilabel:`Montly/Yearly Receipts`."
msgstr ""
"Za tiskanje mesečnih/letnih zapiralno priloženih računov :ref:`odprite "
"povezano POS blagajno <pos/use/open-register>` iz **POS nadzorne plošče**. "
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`seznamski pogled` v zgornjem "
"desnem kotu in izberite :guilabel:`Mesečni/letni računi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/austria.rst:280
msgid ""
"The last month is selected by default in the :guilabel:`Print closing "
"receipts` window. To change it,  select :guilabel:`Monthly` "
"or :guilabel:`Yearly`, then click the :icon:`fa-calendar-"
"o` :guilabel:`(calendar)` icon to select the desired month/year."
msgstr ""
"Zadnji mesec je privzeto izbran v oknu :guilabel:`Natisni zapiralne račune`. "
"Za spremembo izberite :guilabel:`Mesečno` ali :guilabel:`Letno`, nato "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-calendar-o` :guilabel:`(koledar)`, da izberete "
"želeni mesec/leto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:10
msgid ""
"Install the :guilabel:`🇧🇪 Belgium` :ref:`fiscal localization package "
"<fiscal_localizations/packages>` to get all the default accounting features "
"of the Belgian localization, following the :abbr:`IFRS(International "
"Financial Reporting Standards)` rules."
msgstr ""
"Namestite paket :guilabel:`🇧🇪 Belgija` :ref:`fiskalnih lokalizacij "
"<fiscal_localizations/packages>`, da dobite vse privzete računovodske "
"funkcije belgijske lokalizacije v skladu s pravili :abbr:`MSFI (Mednarodni "
"standardi računovodskega poročanja)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:15
msgid ""
":doc:`Documentation on e-invoicing’s legality and compliance in Belgium <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dokumentacija o zakonitosti in skladnosti e-računov v Belgiji <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/belgium>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:23
msgid ""
"You can reach the :guilabel:`Chart of accounts` by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Accounting: Chart of "
"Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Do :guilabel:`Kontnega načrta` lahko dostopate prek "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Računovodstvo: Kontni "
"načrt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:26
msgid ""
"The Belgian chart of accounts includes pre-configured accounts as described "
"in the :abbr:`PCMN(Plan Comptable Minimum Normalisé)`. To add a new account, "
"click :guilabel:`New`. A new line appears. Fill it in, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`, and then :guilabel:`Setup` to configure it further."
msgstr ""
"Belgijski kontni načrt vključuje vnaprej konfigurirane račune, kot so "
"opisani v :abbr:`PCMN (Plan Comptable Minimum Normalisé)`. Za dodajanje "
"novega računa kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Pojavi se nova vrstica. Izpolnite "
"jo, kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani` in nato :guilabel:`Nastavitev` za dodatno "
"konfiguracijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:126
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:378
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:83
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:174
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:222
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:38
msgid ""
"Default Belgian taxes are created automatically when the :guilabel:`Belgium "
"- Accounting` and the :guilabel:`Belgium - Accounting Reports` modules are "
"installed. Each tax impacts the Belgian :guilabel:`Tax Report`, available by "
"going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Statements Reports: "
"Tax Report`."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti belgijski davki so ustvarjeni samodejno, ko sta nameščena modula "
":guilabel:`Belgija - Računovodstvo` in :guilabel:`Belgija - Računovodska "
"poročila`. Vsak davek vpliva na belgijsko :guilabel:`Davčno poročilo`, "
"dostopno prek :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Izpisi "
"poročil: Davčno poročilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:43
msgid ""
"In Belgium, the standard VAT rate is **21%**, but there are lower rates for "
"some categories of goods and services. An intermediate rate of **12%** is "
"applied on social housing and food served in restaurants, while a reduced "
"rate of **6%** applies to most basic goods, such as food, water supply, "
"books, and medicine. A **0%** rate applies to some exceptional goods and "
"services, such as some daily and weekly publications, as well as recycled "
"goods."
msgstr ""
"V Belgiji je standardna stopnja DDV **21 %**, vendar obstajajo nižje stopnje "
"za nekatere kategorije blaga in storitev. Vmesna stopnja **12 %** se "
"uporablja za socialna stanovanja in hrano, postreženo v restavracijah, "
"medtem ko se znižana stopnja **6 %** uporablja za večino osnovnega blaga, "
"kot so hrana, oskrba z vodo, knjige in zdravila. Stopnja **0 %** se "
"uporablja za nekatero izjemno blago in storitve, kot so nekatere dnevne in "
"tedenske publikacije ter reciklirano blago."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:52
msgid "Non-deductible taxes"
msgstr "Neodbitni davki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:54
msgid ""
"In Belgium, some taxes are not fully deductible, such as taxes on the "
"maintenance of cars. This means a part of these taxes is considered as an "
"expense."
msgstr ""
"V Belgiji nekateri davki niso v celoti odbitni, na primer davki na "
"vzdrževanje avtomobilov. To pomeni, da se del teh davkov šteje za odhodek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:57
msgid ""
"In Odoo, you can configure non-deductible taxes by creating tax rules for "
"these taxes and linking them to the corresponding accounts. This way, the "
"system automatically calculates the taxes and allocates them to the "
"appropriate accounts."
msgstr ""
"V Odoou lahko konfigurirate neodbitne davke tako, da ustvarite davčna "
"pravila za te davke in jih povežete s pripadajočimi konti. Na ta način "
"sistem samodejno izračuna davke in jih dodeli ustreznim kontom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:61
msgid ""
"To configure a new non-deductible tax, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Accounting: Taxes`, and click :guilabel:`New`:"
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo novega neodbitnega davka pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Računovodstvo: Davki` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a line` and select :guilabel:`Base` in the :guilabel:`Based "
"On` column;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` in izberite :guilabel:`Osnova` v stolpcu "
":guilabel:`Na osnovi`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a line`, then select :guilabel:`on tax` in "
"the :guilabel:`Based on` column and enter the **non-deductible** percentage "
"in the :guilabel:`%` column;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, nato izberite :guilabel:`na davek` v stolpcu "
":guilabel:`Na osnovi` in vnesite **neodbitni** odstotek v stolpec "
":guilabel:`%`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:67
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`of tax` line, select the :guilabel:`Tax Grid(s)` related "
"to your tax;"
msgstr ""
"V vrstici :guilabel:`na davek` izberite :guilabel:`Davčno mrežo(e)`, "
"povezane z vašim davkom;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add a line` with the **deductible** percentage in "
"the :guilabel:`%` column;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` z **odbitnim** odstotkom v stolpcu :guilabel:`%`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:69
msgid "Set :guilabel:`of tax` in :guilabel:`Based On`;"
msgstr "Nastavite :guilabel:`davka` v :guilabel:`Osnova`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:70
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`411000 VAT recoverable` as account, and select the related "
"tax grid."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`411000 povračilo DDV` kot konto in izberite povezano "
"davčno mrežo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:72
msgid ""
"Once you have created a non-deductible tax, you can apply it to your "
"transactions by selecting the appropriate tax during the encoding of bills "
"and credit notes. The system automatically calculates the tax amount and "
"allocates it to the corresponding accounts based on the tax rules configured."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite neodbitni davek, ga lahko uporabite za svoje transakcije tako, "
"da med vnašanjem računov in dobropisov izberete ustrezen davek. Sistem "
"samodejno izračuna znesek davka in ga dodeli ustreznim kontom na podlagi "
"konfiguriranih davčnih pravil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:77
msgid ""
"With the Belgian localization, the **21% car** tax is created by default "
"(50% non-deductible)."
msgstr ""
"Pri belgijski lokalizaciji je privzeto ustvarjen davek **21% avto** (50% "
"neodbitno)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:0
msgid "Example of not-fully deductible tax"
msgstr "Primer ne povsem odbitnega davka"

