msgstr "Seznam prodaje ES;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:98
msgid "Intrastat."
msgstr "Intrastat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:100
msgid ""
"You can access Belgian-specific versions of reports by clicking on the "
"**book** icon when on a report and selecting its Belgian version: **(BE)**."
msgstr ""
"Do belgijskih različic poročil lahko dostopate tako, da kliknete ikono "
"**knjiga**, ko ste v poročilu, in izberete njegovo belgijsko različico: **"
"(BE)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
