msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/reporting`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:112
msgid "Disallowed expenses report"
msgstr "Poročilo o nedovoljenih odhodkih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:114
msgid ""
"**Disallowed expenses** are expenses that can be deducted from your "
"accounting result but not from your fiscal result."
msgstr ""
"**Nedovoljeni odhodki** so odhodki, ki jih lahko odštejete od svojega "
"računovodskega rezultata, vendar ne od fiskalnega rezultata."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:117
msgid ""
"The **disallowed expenses report** is available by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Management: Disallowed "
"Expenses`. It allows financial results in real-time, and periodic changes. "
"This report is generated based on the **disallowed expenses categories** "
"that you can reach by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Management: Disallowed Expenses Categories`. Some categories already "
"exist by default but do not have any rates. Click on :guilabel:`Set Rates` "
"to update a specific category."
msgstr ""
"**Poročilo o nedovoljenih odhodkih** je na voljo v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Upravljanje: Nedovoljeni "
"odhodki`. Omogoča finančne rezultate v realnem času in periodične spremembe. "
"To poročilo je ustvarjeno na podlagi **kategorij nedovoljenih odhodkov**, do "
"katerih lahko dostopate v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Upravljanje: Kategorije nedovoljenih odhodkov`. Nekatere "
"kategorije že privzeto obstajajo, vendar nimajo nobenih stopenj. Kliknite "
":guilabel:`Nastavi stopnje`, da posodobite določeno kategorijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:125
msgid ""
"You can add multiple rates for various dates. In that case, the rate used to "
"calculate the expense depends on the date at which it is calculated, and the "
"rate set for that date."
msgstr ""
"Za različne datume lahko dodate več stopenj. V tem primeru se stopnja, "
"uporabljena za izračun stroška, določi glede na datum izračuna in stopnjo, "
"določeno za ta datum."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:127
msgid ""
"If you have the **Fleet** app installed, tick the :guilabel:`Car Category` "
"box when applicable. This makes the vehicle mandatory while booking a vendor "
"bill."
msgstr ""
"Če imate nameščeno aplikacijo **Vozni park**, po potrebi označite polje "
":guilabel:`Kategorija vozila`. To naredi vozilo obvezno pri knjiženju "
"dobaviteljevega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:130
msgid ""
"To link a disallowed expenses category with a specific account, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Accounting: Chart of "
"Accounts`. Find the account you want, and click on :guilabel:`Setup`. Add "
"the :guilabel:`Disallowed Expense category` in the :guilabel:`Disallowed "
"Expenses` field. From now, when an expense is created with this account, the "
"disallowed expense is calculated based on the rate mentioned in "
"the :guilabel:`Disallowed Expense category`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite povezati kategorijo nedovoljenih stroškov z določenim kontom, "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Računovodstvo: Kontni načrt`. Poiščite želeni konto in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Nastavitev`. Dodajte :guilabel:`Kategorijo nedovoljenih stroškov` "
"v polje :guilabel:`Nedovoljeni stroški`. Od zdaj naprej, ko se ustvari "
"strošek s tem kontom, se nedovoljeni strošek izračuna na podlagi stopnje, "
"navedene v :guilabel:`Kategoriji nedovoljenih stroškov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:136
msgid "Let's take an example reflecting **restaurant** and **car expenses**."
msgstr ""
"Vzemimo primer, ki odraža **stroške restavracij** in **stroške avtomobilov**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:141
msgid "Restaurant expenses"
msgstr "Stroški restavracij"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:143
msgid ""
"In Belgium, 69% of **restaurant** expenses are deductible. Create a new "
"**disallowed expenses category** and set both :guilabel:`Related Account(s)` "
"and :guilabel:`Current Rate`."
msgstr ""
"V Belgiji je 69 % **stroškov restavracij** odbitnih. Ustvarite novo "
"**kategorijo nedovoljenih stroškov** in nastavite :guilabel:`Povezani konti` "
"in :guilabel:`Trenutna stopnja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:149
msgid "Car expenses: vehicle split"
msgstr "Stroški avtomobilov: razdelitev po vozilih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:151
msgid ""
"In Belgium, the deductible percentage varies from car to car and, therefore, "
"should be indicated for each vehicle. To do so, open :menuselection:`Fleet` "
"and select a vehicle. In the :guilabel:`Tax info` tab, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Deductibility Rates` section and click on :guilabel:`Add a "
"line`. Add a :guilabel:`Start Date` and a :guilabel:`%`. The amounts go in "
"the same account for all car expenses."
msgstr ""
"V Belgiji se odbitni odstotek razlikuje od avtomobila do avtomobila in ga je "
"zato treba navesti za vsako vozilo. To storite tako, da odprete "
":menuselection:`Vozni park` in izberete vozilo. Na zavihku :guilabel:`Davčne "
"informacije` pojdite na razdelek :guilabel:`Stopnje odbitnosti` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`. Dodajte :guilabel:`Začetni datum` in "
":guilabel:`%`. Zneski gredo na isti konto za vse stroške avtomobilov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:157
msgid ""
"When you create a bill for car expenses, you can link each expense to a "
"specific car by filling the :guilabel:`Vehicle` column, so the right "
"percentage is applied."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite račun za stroške avtomobilov, lahko vsak strošek povežete z "
"določenim avtomobilom tako, da izpolnite stolpec :guilabel:`Vozilo`, tako da "
"se uporabi pravilen odstotek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Disallowed expenses categories"
msgstr "Kategorije nedovoljenih stroškov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:163
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`vehicle split` option available in the disallowed expenses "
"report allows you to see the rate and disallowed amount for each car."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :guilabel:`razdelitve po vozilih`, dostopna v poročilu o "
"nedovoljenih stroških, vam omogoča vpogled v stopnjo in nedovoljeni znesek "
"za vsak avtomobil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:172
msgid "Fee form 281.50 and form 325"
msgstr "Obrazec pristojbin 281.50 in obrazec 325"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:177
msgid "Fee form 281.50"
msgstr "Obrazec pristojbin 281.50"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:179
msgid ""
"Annually, a **281.50 fee form** must be reported to the fiscal authorities. "
"To do so, the tag `281.50` must be added on the **contact form** of the "
"entities concerned by the **281.50** fee. To add the tag, "
"open :menuselection:`Contacts`, select the person or company you want to "
"create a **281.50 fee form** for, and add the `281.50` tag in "
"the :guilabel:`Tags` field."
msgstr ""
"Letno je treba davčnim organom prijaviti **obrazec pristojbin 281.50**. Zato "
"je treba oznako `281.50` dodati na **obrazec stika** subjektov, ki jih "
"zadeva pristojbina **281.50**. Če želite dodati oznako, odprite "
":menuselection:`Stiki`, izberite osebo ali podjetje, za katerega želite "
"ustvariti **obrazec pristojbin 281.50**, in dodajte oznako `281.50` v polje "
":guilabel:`Oznake`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "add the tag 281.50 on a contact form"
msgstr "dodajte oznako 281.50 na obrazec stika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:188
msgid ""
"Make sure the **street, zip code, country**, and **VAT number** are also "
"informed on the **Contact form**."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, ali so na **obrazcu stika** navedeni tudi **ulica, poštna "
"številka, država** in **davčna številka**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:191
msgid ""
"Then, depending on the nature of the expense, add the corresponding `281.50` "
"tag on the impact accounts. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Accounting: Chart of Accounts`, and click "
"on :guilabel:`Setup` to add the corresponding `281.50` tag on the impacted "
"accounts, i.e., :guilabel:`281.50 - Commissions`, depending on the nature of "
"the expense."
msgstr ""
"Nato, odvisno od narave stroška, dodajte ustrezno oznako `281.50` na "
"prizadete konte. To storite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Računovodstvo: Kontni "
"načrt` in kliknete :guilabel:`Nastavitev`, da dodate ustrezno oznako "
"`281.50` na prizadete konte, npr. :guilabel:`281.50 - Provizije`, odvisno od "
"narave stroška."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:199
msgid "Form 325"
msgstr "Obrazec 325"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:201
msgid ""
"You can create a **325 form** by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Belgium: Create 325 form`. A new page pops up: select the "
"right options and click :guilabel:`Generate 325 form`. To open an already "
"generated **325 form**, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Belgium: Open 325 forms`."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec **325** lahko ustvarite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Belgija: Ustvari obrazec "
"325`. Prikaže se nova stran: izberite pravilne možnosti in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Generiraj obrazec 325`. Če želite odpreti že ustvarjen obrazec "
"**325**, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Belgija: "
"Odpri obrazce 325`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Add the tag 281-50 on a contact form"
msgstr "Dodajte oznako 281-50 na obrazec stika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:212
msgid "CODA and SODA statements"
msgstr "Izpiski CODA in SODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:217
msgid "CODA"
msgstr "CODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:219
msgid ""
"**CODA** is an electronic XML format used to import Belgian bank statements. "
"You can download CODA files from your bank and import them directly into "
"Odoo by clicking :guilabel:`Import file` from your :guilabel:`Bank` journal "
"on your dashboard."
msgstr ""
"**CODA** je elektronski format XML, ki se uporablja za uvoz belgijskih "
"bančnih izpiskov. Datoteke CODA lahko prenesete iz svoje banke in jih "
"uvozite neposredno v Odoo tako, da kliknete :guilabel:`Uvozi datoteko` iz "
"dnevnika :guilabel:`Banka` na vaši nadzorni plošči."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Import CODA files"
msgstr "Uvoz datotek CODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:227
msgid ":ref:`Import bank files <accounting/transactions/import>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Uvoz bančnih datotek <accounting/transactions/import>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:232
msgid "SODA"
msgstr "SODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:234
msgid ""
"**SODA** is an electronic XML format used to import accounting entries "
"related to salaries. SODA files can be imported into the journal you use to "
"record salaries by going to your Accounting **dashboard** and "
"clicking :guilabel:`Upload` in the related journal card form."
msgstr ""
"**SODA** je elektronski format XML, ki se uporablja za uvoz knjigovodskih "
"vnosov, povezanih s plačami. Datoteke SODA lahko uvozite v dnevnik, ki ga "
"uporabljate za beleženje plač, tako da odprete svojo **nadzorno plošč** "
"Računovodstva in kliknete :guilabel:`Naloži` na kartici povezanega dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:238
msgid ""
"Once your **SODA** files are imported, the entries are created automatically "
"in your salary journal."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vaše datoteke **SODA** uvožene, se vnosi avtomatsko ustvarijo v vašem "
"dnevniku plač."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Import SODA files"
msgstr "Uvoz datotek SODA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:246
msgid "CodaBox"
msgstr "CodaBox"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:248
msgid ""
"**CodaBox** is a service that allows Belgian companies and accounting firms "
"to access bank information and statements. Odoo provides a way to import "
"such statements automatically."
msgstr ""
"**CodaBox** je storitev, ki belgijskim podjetjem in računovodskim firmam "
"omogoča dostop do bančnih informacij in izpiskov. Odoo omogoča samodejni "
"uvoz takšnih izpiskov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:254
msgid ""
"To configure and use Codabox, first :ref:`install <general/install>` "
"the :guilabel:`CodaBox` module."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo in uporabo Codabox najprej :ref:`namestite <general/install>"
"` modul :guilabel:`CodaBox`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:259
msgid "Configure the Connection"
msgstr "Konfiguracija povezave"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:263
msgid "For companies"
msgstr "Za podjetja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:266
msgid ""
"Make sure the :doc:`company settings </applications/general/companies>` are "
"correctly configured, i.e., the country is set to :guilabel:`Belgium` and "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` or :guilabel:`Company ID` field is filled."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so :doc:`nastavitve podjetja </applications/general/"
"companies>` pravilno konfigurirane, kar pomeni, da je država nastavljena na "
":guilabel:`Belgija` in je polje :guilabel:`Davčna številka` ali "
":guilabel:`ID podjetja` izpolnjeno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:270
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:299
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, then go to "
"the :guilabel:`CodaBox & SODA` section."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, "
"nato pojdite na razdelek :guilabel:`CodaBox & SODA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:272
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Manage Connection` to open the connection wizard, which "
"shows the :guilabel:`Company VAT/ID` number that will be used for the "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na :guilabel:`Upravljaj povezavo`, da odprete čarovnika za "
"povezavo, ki prikaže :guilabel:`DDV/ID podjetja`, ki bo uporabljen za "
"povezavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:274
msgid ""
"If this is your **first connection**, click on :guilabel:`Create "
"connection`. The wizard confirms that the connection has been created on "
"**Odoo's side**. Follow the steps to validate the connection on **CodaBox's "
"side** too."
msgstr ""
"Če je to vaša **prva povezava**, kliknite na :guilabel:`Ustvari povezavo`. "
"Čarovnik potrdi, da je bila povezava ustvarjena na **Odoo strani**. Sledite "
"korakom za potrditev povezave tudi na **CodaBox strani**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:278
msgid ""
"If this is **not your first connection**, the :guilabel:`Password` provided "
"by Odoo during the first connection will be requested to create a new "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Če to **ni vaša prva povezava**, bo za ustvarjanje nove povezave zahtevano "
":guilabel:`Geslo`, ki ga je Odoo zagotovil med prvo povezavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:282
msgid ""
"This :guilabel:`Password` is unique to Odoo and must be stored securely on "
"your side."
msgstr ""
"To :guilabel:`Geslo` je edinstveno za Odoo in ga morate varno shraniti na "
"svoji strani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:285
msgid "For accounting firms"
msgstr "Za računovodske družbe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:287
msgid ""
"Accounting firms must manage their clients on separate databases and "
"configure them individually to avoid mixing up their data. The connection "
"must be made by an accounting firm with valid CodaBox Connect credentials. "
"In the following instructions, we will refer to your client's company as "
"*Company* and to your accounting firm as *Accounting Firm*."
msgstr ""
"Računovodske družbe morajo upravljati svoje stranke v ločenih podatkovnih "
"bazah in jih posamezno konfigurirati, da se njihovi podatki ne pomešajo. "
"Povezavo mora vzpostaviti računovodska družba z veljavnimi poverilnicami "
"CodaBox Connect. V naslednjih navodilih bomo podjetje vaše stranke imenovali "
"*Podjetje*, vašo računovodsko družbo pa *Računovodska družba*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:294
msgid ""
"Make sure the :doc:`company settings </applications/general/companies>` are "
"correctly configured, i.e., the country is set to :guilabel:`Belgium`, "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` or :guilabel:`Company ID` and :guilabel:`Accounting "
"Firm` fields are filled, as well as the :guilabel:`Tax ID` of "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm`."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so :doc:`nastavitve podjetja </applications/general/"
"companies>` pravilno konfigurirane, tj. da je država nastavljena na "
":guilabel:`Belgija`, da so izpolnjena polja :guilabel:`Davčna številka` ali "
":guilabel:`ID podjetja` in :guilabel:`Računovodska družba`, pa tudi "
":guilabel:`Davčna številka` :guilabel:`Računovodske družbe`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:301
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Manage Connection` to open the connection wizard, which "
"shows the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` number and the :guilabel:`Company "
"VAT/ID` number that will be used for the connection."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na :guilabel:`Upravljaj povezavo`, da odprete čarovnika za "
"povezavo, ki prikazuje številko :guilabel:`DDV računovodske družbe` in "
"številko :guilabel:`DDV/ID podjetja`, ki bo uporabljena za povezavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:304
msgid ""
"If this is your **first connection**, click on :guilabel:`Create "
"connection`. The wizard confirms that the connection has been created on "
"**Odoo's side**. Follow the steps to validate the connection on **CodaBox's "
"side**, too."
msgstr ""
"Če je to vaša **prva povezava**, kliknite na :guilabel:`Ustvari povezavo`. "
"Čarovnik potrdi, da je bila povezava ustvarjena na **Odoo strani**. Sledite "
"korakom za potrditev povezave tudi na **CodaBox strani**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:308
msgid ""
"If this is **not your first connection**, the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm "
"Password` provided by Odoo during the first connection will be requested to "
"create a new connection."
msgstr ""
"Če to **ni vaša prva povezava**, bo za ustvarjanje nove povezave zahtevano "
":guilabel:`Geslo računovodske družbe`, ki ga je Odoo zagotovil med prvo "
"povezavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:312
msgid ""
"This :guilabel:`Accounting Firm Password` is unique to Odoo and must be "
"stored securely on your side."
msgstr ""
"To :guilabel:`Geslo računovodske družbe` je edinstveno za Odoo in ga morate "
"varno shraniti na svoji strani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:315
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Status` should have now switched to :guilabel:`Connected`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Stanje` bi se moralo zdaj spremeniti v :guilabel:`Povezano`."

