msgstr "Konfiguracija dnevnika SODA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:348
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:492
msgid "Synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:350
msgid ""
"Once the connection is established, Odoo can be synchronized with CodaBox."
msgstr "Ko je povezava vzpostavljena, lahko Odoo sinhronizirate s CodaBox."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:356
msgid ""
"CODA files are automatically imported from CodaBox every 12 hours. You do "
"not have to do anything. However, if you wish, it can also be done manually, "
"by clicking on :guilabel:`Fetch from CodaBox` in the Accounting Dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke CODA se samodejno uvozijo iz CodaBox vsakih 12 ur. Vam ni treba "
"storiti ničesar. Če pa želite, lahko to storite tudi ročno s klikom na "
":guilabel:`Pridobi iz CodaBox` na nadzorni plošči računovodstva."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:362
msgid ""
"SODA files are automatically imported from CodaBox once a day as a draft. "
"You do not have to do anything. However, if you wish, it can also be done "
"manually by clicking on :guilabel:`Fetch from CodaBox` in the Accounting "
"Dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke SODA se samodejno uvozijo iz CodaBox enkrat na dan kot osnutek. Vam "
"ni treba storiti ničesar. Če pa želite, lahko to storite tudi ročno s klikom "
"na :guilabel:`Pridobi iz CodaBox` na nadzorni plošči računovodstva."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:366
msgid ""
"By default, if an account in the SODA file is not mapped to an account in "
"Odoo, the Suspense Account (499000) is used, and a note is added to the "
"created journal entry."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto se uporabi začasni konto (499000), če konto v datoteki SODA ni "
"preslikano na konto v Odoo, ustvarjenemu knjigovodskemu vnosu pa se doda "
"opomba."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:370
msgid ""
"You can access the mapping between the SODA and Odoo accounts by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and clicking "
"on the :guilabel:`Open SODA Mapping` button in the :guilabel:`CodaBox` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Do preslikave med kontom SODA in Odoo dostopate tako, da greste v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in kliknete "
"gumb :guilabel:`Odpri preslikavo SODA` v razdelku :guilabel:`CodaBox`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:376
msgid "Potential issues"
msgstr "Morebitne težave"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:378
msgid "**CodaBox is not configured. Please check your configuration.**"
msgstr "**CodaBox ni konfiguriran. Preverite svojo konfiguracijo.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:380
msgid ""
"Either the :guilabel:`Company VAT` or the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` is "
"not set."
msgstr ""
"Bodisi :guilabel:`DDV podjetja` bodisi :guilabel:`DDV računovodskega "
"podjetja` ni nastavljen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:382
msgid ""
"**No connection exists with these accounting firms and company VAT "
"numbers.** **Please check your configuration.**"
msgstr ""
"**S tem računovodskim podjetjem in številko DDV podjetja ne obstaja nobena "
"povezava.** **Preverite svojo konfiguracijo.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:385
msgid ""
"This can happen when checking the connection status, and "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` and :guilabel:`Company VAT` combination "
"still needs to be registered. This may happen if you have changed "
"the :guilabel:`Company VAT` after the connection was established. For "
"security reasons, you have to :ref:`recreate a connection <belgium/codabox-"
"configuration-connection>` for this :guilabel:`Company VAT`."
msgstr ""
"Do tega lahko pride pri preverjanju stanja povezave, če kombinacija "
":guilabel:`DDV računovodskega podjetja` in :guilabel:`DDV podjetja` še ni "
"registrirana. To se lahko zgodi, če ste spremenili :guilabel:`DDV podjetja` "
"po vzpostavitvi povezave. Iz varnostnih razlogov morate za to :guilabel:`DDV "
"podjetja` :ref:`ponovno ustvariti povezavo <belgium/codabox-configuration-"
"connection>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:391
msgid ""
"**It seems that your CodaBox connection is not valid anymore. Please connect "
"again.**"
msgstr ""
"**Videti je, da vaša povezava CodaBox ni več veljavna. Ponovno se povežite.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:393
msgid ""
"This can happen if you revoke Odoo's access to your CodaBox account or still "
"need to complete the configuration process. In this case, you must revoke "
"the connection and create a new one."
msgstr ""
"Do tega lahko pride, če prekličete dostop Odoo do vašega računa CodaBox ali "
"še niste dokončali postopka konfiguracije. V tem primeru morate preklicati "
"povezavo in ustvariti novo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:396
msgid ""
"**The provided password is not valid for this accounting firm.** **You must "
"reuse the password you received from Odoo during your first connection.**"
msgstr ""
"**Navedeno geslo ni veljavno za to računovodsko podjetje.** **Uporabiti "
"morate geslo, ki ste ga prejeli od Odoo med prvo povezavo.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:399
msgid ""
"The password you provided is different from the one you received from Odoo "
"during your first connection. You must use the password you received from "
"Odoo during your first connection to create a new connection for this "
"accounting firm. If you have lost your password, you must first revoke the "
"Odoo connection on CodaBox's side (i.e., on your myCodaBox portal). Then, "
"you can revoke the connection on Odoo's side and :ref:`create a new one "
"<belgium/codabox-configuration-connection>`."
msgstr ""
"Geslo, ki ste ga navedli, se razlikuje od gesla, ki ste ga prejeli od Odoo "
"med prvo povezavo. Za ustvarjanje nove povezave za to računovodsko podjetje "
"morate uporabiti geslo, ki ste ga prejeli od Odoo med prvo povezavo. Če ste "
"geslo izgubili, morate najprej preklicati povezavo Odoo na strani CodaBox "
"(tj. na vašem portalu myCodaBox). Nato lahko prekličete povezavo na strani "
"Odoo in :ref:`ustvarite novo <belgium/codabox-configuration-connection>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:406
msgid ""
"**It seems that the company or accounting firm VAT number you provided is "
"not valid.** **Please check your configuration.**"
msgstr ""
"**Videti je, da navedena številka DDV podjetja ali računovodskega podjetja "
"ni veljavna.** **Preverite svojo konfiguracijo.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:409
msgid ""
"Either the :guilabel:`Company VAT` or the :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` is "
"not in a valid Belgian format."
msgstr ""
"Bodisi :guilabel:`DDV podjetja` bodisi :guilabel:`DDV računovodskega "
"podjetja` ni v veljavni belgijski obliki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:412
msgid ""
"**It seems that the accounting firm VAT number you provided does not exist "
"in CodaBox.** **Please check your configuration.**"
msgstr ""
"**Videti je, da številka DDV računovodskega podjetja, ki ste jo navedli, ne "
"obstaja v CodaBox.** **Preverite svojo konfiguracijo.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:415
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Accounting Firm VAT` number you provided is not registered in "
"CodaBox. You may not have a valid CodaBox license linked to this VAT number."
msgstr ""
"Številka :guilabel:`DDV računovodskega podjetja`, ki ste jo navedli, ni "
"registrirana v CodaBox. Morda nimate veljavne licence CodaBox, povezane s to "
"številko DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:418
msgid ""
"**It seems you have already created a connection to CodaBox with this "
"accounting firm.** **To create a new connection, you must first revoke the "
"old one on myCodaBox portal.**"
msgstr ""
"**Videti je, da ste že ustvarili povezavo s CodaBox s tem računovodskim "
"podjetjem.** **Če želite ustvariti novo povezavo, morate najprej preklicati "
"staro na portalu myCodaBox.**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:421
msgid ""
"You must go to your myCodaBox portal and revoke Odoo's access to your "
"CodaBox account. Then, you can :ref:`create a new connection <belgium/"
"codabox-configuration-connection>` on Odoo's side."
msgstr ""
"Do portala myCodaBox se morate prijaviti in preklicati dostop Odooja do "
"računa CodaBox. Nato lahko :ref:`ustvarite novo povezavo <belgium/codabox-"
"configuration-connection>` na strani Odooja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:426
msgid ""
"To revoke the connection between Odoo and CodaBox, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down "
"to the :guilabel:`CodaBox` section, click on :guilabel:`Manage Connection`, "
"then click on :guilabel:`Revoke`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preklicati povezavo med Odoojem in CodaBoxom, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, pomaknite "
"se navzdol do razdelka :guilabel:`CodaBox`, kliknite :guilabel:`Upravljaj "
"povezavo` in nato kliknite :guilabel:`Prekliči`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:434
msgid "Codaclean"
msgstr "Codaclean"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:436
msgid ""
"**Codaclean** is a service that allows Belgian companies and accounting "
"firms to access bank information and statements. Odoo provides a way to "
"import such statements and their transactions automatically."
msgstr ""
"**Codaclean** je storitev, ki belgijskim podjetjem in računovodskim firmam "
"omogoča dostop do bančnih informacij in izpiskov. Odoo omogoča samodejni "
"uvoz takih izpiskov in njihovih transakcij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:446
msgid ""
"Make sure to :ref:`install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Codaclean` "
"(`l10n_be_codaclean`) module."
msgstr ""
"Poskrbite, da :ref:`namestite <general/install>` modul :guilabel:`Codaclean` "
"(`l10n_be_codaclean`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:455
msgid "To connect Odoo with Codaclean, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za povezavo Odooja s Codaclean sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:457
msgid ""
"Open the Settings app, navigate to the :ref:`Companies <general/companies/"
"company>` section, and click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage "
"Companies` to make sure the company's :guilabel:`Country` is set "
"to :guilabel:`Belgium`."
msgstr ""
"Odprite aplikacijo Nastavitve, pomaknite se do razdelka :ref:`Podjetja "
"<general/companies/company>` in kliknite :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Upravljaj podjetja`, da se prepričate, da je :guilabel:`Država` "
"podjetja nastavljena na :guilabel:`Belgija`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:460
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Codaclean` section."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` "
"in se pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`Codaclean`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:462
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Manage Connection` to open the connection wizard, enter the "
"Codaclean :guilabel:`Username` and :guilabel:`Password` and "
"click :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Upravljaj povezavo`, da odprete čarovnika za povezavo, "
"vnesite :guilabel:`Uporabniško ime` in :guilabel:`Geslo` za Codaclean ter "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Poveži`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:465
msgid "The :guilabel:`Status` is updated to :guilabel:`Connected`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Stanje` je posodobljeno na :guilabel:`Povezano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:468
msgid ""
"Once the connection is established, the :guilabel:`Manage Connection` wizard "
"provides two options:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je povezava vzpostavljena, čarovnik :guilabel:`Upravljaj povezavo` ponuja "
"dve možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:470
msgid ""
"Update Codaclean credentials: Enter the new :guilabel:`Username` "
"and :guilabel:`Password`, then click :guilabel:`Change Credentials`."
msgstr ""
"Posodobitev poverilnic Codaclean: Vnesite novo :guilabel:`Uporabniško ime` "
"in :guilabel:`Geslo`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Spremeni poverilnice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:472
msgid ""
"Remove Codaclean connection: Click :guilabel:`Disconnect`; "
"no :guilabel:`Username` or :guilabel:`Password` is required."
msgstr ""
"Odstranitev povezave Codaclean: Kliknite :guilabel:`Prekini povezavo`; "
":guilabel:`Uporabniško ime` ali :guilabel:`Geslo` nista potrebna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:478
msgid "Journal creation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje dnevnika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:480
msgid ""
"A specific bank journal must be created for Codaclean synchronization. To do "
"so, :doc:`create a new bank journal <../accounting/bank>`, make sure to "
"enter the correct IBAN in the :guilabel:`Bank Account Number` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`Codaclean Syncronization` in the :guilabel:`Bank Feeds` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Za sinhronizacijo s Codaclean je treba ustvariti poseben bančni dnevnik. Za "
"to :doc:`ustvarite nov bančni dnevnik <../accounting/bank>`, poskrbite, da "
"vnesete pravilen IBAN v polje :guilabel:`Številka bančnega računa`, ter v "
"polju :guilabel:`Bančni viri` izberite :guilabel:`Sinhronizacija Codaclean`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:486
msgid ""
"For bank transactions in different currencies, it is recommended to create a "
"separate journal for each currency, using the same bank account."
msgstr ""
"Za bančne transakcije v različnih valutah je priporočljivo ustvariti ločen "
"dnevnik za vsako valuto z uporabo istega bančnega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:494
msgid ""
"Once the connection is established, Odoo is synchronized with Codaclean, and "
"new CODA files received via Codaclean are checked every twelve hours."
msgstr ""
"Ko je povezava vzpostavljena, je Odoo sinhroniziran s Codaclean in nove "
"datoteke CODA, prejete prek Codaclean, so preverjene vsakih dvanajst ur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:498
msgid ""
"To manually check for new CODA files, go to the Accounting Dashboard and "
"click :guilabel:`Fetch from Codaclean` on the relevant :ref:`journal "
"<belgium/codaclean-configuration-journal>` ."
msgstr ""
"Za ročno preverjanje novih datotek CODA pojdite na Nadzorno ploščo "
"računovodstva in kliknite :guilabel:`Pridobi iz Codaclean` na ustreznem "
":ref:`dnevniku <belgium/codaclean-configuration-journal>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:504
msgid "Electronic invoicing with Peppol"
msgstr "Elektronsko izdajanje računov s Peppol"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:506
msgid ""
"As of 1 January 2026, all Belgian companies must be registered on the Peppol "
"network to send and receive electronic invoices."
msgstr ""
"Od 1. januarja 2026 morajo biti vsa belgijska podjetja registrirana v "
"omrežju Peppol za pošiljanje in prejemanje elektronskih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:509
msgid ""
"To activate Peppol, refer to the :ref:`Peppol documentation <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol>`, ensuring during :ref:`registration <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol-registration>` that:"
msgstr ""
"Za aktivacijo Peppol glejte :ref:`dokumentacijo Peppol <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/peppol>`, pri čemer zagotovite med :ref:`registracijo <accounting/"
"e-invoicing/peppol-registration>`, da:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:512
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Peppol EAS` field is set to :guilabel:`0208 - Numero "
"d'entreprise / ondernemingsnummer / Unternehmensnummer`."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Peppol EAS` je nastavljeno na :guilabel:`0208 - Numero "
"d'entreprise / ondernemingsnummer / Unternehmensnummer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:514
msgid ""
"the :guilabel:`Peppol Endpoint` field is set to the company registry number."
msgstr ""
"polje :guilabel:`Peppol Endpoint` je nastavljeno na matično številko "
"podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:516
msgid ""
"In addition, when veryfing that a customer is :ref:`registered as a Peppol "
"participant <accounting/e-invoicing/contact-verification>`, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Format` field is set to :guilabel:`BIS Billing 3.0`."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega pri preverjanju, da je stranka :ref:`registrirana kot udeleženec "
"Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/contact-verification>`, zagotovite, da je "
"polje :guilabel:`Format` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`BIS Billing 3.0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:521
msgid ":ref:`Peppol documentation <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Dokumentacija Peppol <accounting/e-invoicing/peppol>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:526
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:257
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:441
msgid "Cash discount"
msgstr "Popust za plačilo v gotovinskem roku"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:528
msgid ""
"In Belgium, if an early payment discount is offered on an invoice, the tax "
"is calculated based on the discounted total amount, whether the customer "
"benefits from the discount or not."
msgstr ""
"V Belgiji, če je na računu ponujen popust za predplačilo, se davek izračuna "
"na podlagi zmanjšanega skupnega zneska, ne glede na to, ali stranka "
"izkoristi popust ali ne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:531
msgid ""
"To apply the right tax amount and report it correctly in your VAT return, "
"set the tax reduction as :guilabel:`Always (upon invoice)`."
msgstr ""
"Za uveljavitev pravilnega zneska davka in pravilno poročanje v vaši DDV "
"napovedi nastavite zmanjšanje davka kot :guilabel:`Vedno (ob izdaji računa)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:535
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:263
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:447
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/cash_discounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:540
msgid "Fiscal certification: POS restaurant"
msgstr "Fiskalna certifikacija: restavracija POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:542
msgid ""
"In Belgium, the owner of a cooking business such as a restaurant or food "
"truck is required by law to use a government-certified **Cash Register "
"System** for their receipts. This applies if their yearly earnings "
"(excluding VAT, drinks, and take-away food) exceed 25,000 euros."
msgstr ""
"V Belgiji mora lastnik kuharskega posla, kot je restavracija ali prevozna "
"jedilnica, po zakonu za svoje račune uporabljati vladno certificiran "
"**sistem blagajne**. To velja, če njihov letni dohodek (brez DDV, pijač in "
"hrane za s seboj) presega 25.000 evrov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:546
msgid ""
"This government-certified system entails the use of a :ref:`certified POS "
"system <belgium/certified-pos>`, along with a device called a :ref:`Fiscal "
"Data Module <belgium/fdm>` (or **black box**) and a :ref:`VAT Signing Card "
"<belgium/vat>`."
msgstr ""
"Ta vladno certificiran sistem vključuje uporabo :ref:`certificiranega "
"sistema POS <belgium/certified-pos>` skupaj z napravo, imenovano "
":ref:`fiskalni podatkovni modul <belgium/fdm>` (ali **črna škatla**) in "
":ref:`kartico za podpisovanje DDV <belgium/vat>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:551
msgid ""
"Do not forget to register as *foodservice industry manager* on the `Federal "
"Public Service Finance registration form <https://"
"www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/enregistrement>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite se registrirati kot *upravitelj gostinske dejavnosti* na "
"`registracijskem obrazcu Zvezne javne službe za finance <https://"
"www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/enregistrement>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:557
msgid "Certified POS system"
msgstr "Certificiran sistem POS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:559
msgid ""
"The Odoo POS system is certified for databases hosted on **Odoo Online**, "
"**Odoo.sh**, and **On-Premise**."
msgstr ""
"Sistem Odoo POS je certificiran za zbirke podatkov, gostovane na **Odoo "
"Online**, **Odoo.sh** in **On-Premise**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:563
msgid ":doc:`/administration/standard_extended_support`"
msgstr ":doc:`/administration/standard_extended_support`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:565
msgid ""
"A `certified POS system <https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/"
"systemes-certifies>`_ must adhere to rigorous government regulations, which "
"means it operates differently from a non-certified POS."
msgstr ""
"`Certificiran sistem POS <https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/"
"systemes-certifies>`_ se mora držati strogih vladnih predpisov, kar pomeni, "
"da deluje drugače kot necertificiran POS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:569
msgid "On a certified POS, you cannot:"
msgstr "Na certificiranem POS ne morete:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:571
msgid ""
"Set up and use the **global discounts** feature (the `pos_discount` module "
"is blacklisted and cannot be activated)."
msgstr ""
"Nastaviti in uporabljati funkcije **splošnih popustov** (modul "
"`pos_discount` je na črnem seznamu in ga ni mogoče aktivirati)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:573
msgid ""
"Set up and use the **loyalty programs** feature (the `pos_loyalty` module is "
"blacklisted and cannot be activated)."
msgstr ""
"Nastaviti in uporabljati funkcije **programov zvestobe** (modul "
"`pos_loyalty` je na črnem seznamu in ga ni mogoče aktivirati)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:575
msgid ""
"Reprint receipts (the `pos_reprint` module is blacklisted and cannot be "
"activated)."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno natisniti računov (modul `pos_reprint` je na črnem seznamu in ga ni "
"mogoče aktivirati)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:576
msgid "Modify prices in order lines."
msgstr "Spreminjati cen v vrsticah naročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:577
msgid "Modify or delete order lines in POS orders."
msgstr "Spreminjati ali brisati vrstic naročila v POS naročilih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:578
msgid "Sell products without a valid VAT number."
msgstr "Prodajati izdelkov brez veljavne DDV številke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:579
msgid "Use a POS that is not connected to an IoT box."
msgstr "Uporabljati POS, ki ni povezan z IoT poljem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:581
msgid ""
"The :ref:`cash rounding <pos/pricing/rounding>` feature must be activated "
"and set to a :guilabel:`Rounding Precision` of `0,05` and "
"a :guilabel:`Rounding Method` set as :guilabel:`Nearest`."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija :ref:`zaokroževanja gotovine <pos/pricing/rounding>` mora biti "
"aktivirana in nastavljena na :guilabel:`Natančnost zaokroževanja` `0,05` ter "
":guilabel:`Metoda zaokroževanja` nastavljena na :guilabel:`Najbližje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:584
msgid ""
"Taxes must be set as included in the price. To set it up, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Settings`, and from "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` section, open the :guilabel:`Default Sales Tax` "
"form by clicking the arrow next to the default sales tax field. There, "
"click :guilabel:`Advanced Options` and enable :guilabel:`Included in Price`."
msgstr ""
"Davki morajo biti nastavljeni kot vključeni v ceno. Za nastavitev pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` odprite obrazec :guilabel:`Privzeti davek "
"od prodaje` s klikom na puščico poleg polja privzetega davka od prodaje. Tam "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Napredne možnosti` in omogočite :guilabel:`Vključeno v "
"ceno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:588
msgid ""
"At the opening of the POS register, users must click :guilabel:`Work in` to "
"clock in. Doing so allows the registration of POS orders. If users are not "
"clocked in, they cannot make POS orders. Likewise, they must "
"click :guilabel:`Work Out` to clock out at the end of the session."
msgstr ""
"Ob odprtju POS blagajne morajo uporabniki klikniti :guilabel:`Prijavitev v "
"delo`, da se prijavijo. To omogoča registracijo POS naročil. Če uporabniki "
"niso prijavljeni, ne morejo izdajati POS naročil. Prav tako morajo klikniti "
":guilabel:`Odjava iz dela`, da se odjavijo ob koncu seje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:593
msgid ""
"If you configure a POS to work with a :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)`, you "
"cannot use it again without it."
msgstr ""
"Če konfigurirate prodajno točko za delo z :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)`, "
"je brez njega ne morete več uporabljati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:599
msgid "Fiscal Data Module (FDM)"
msgstr "Modul fiskalnih podatkov (FDM)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:601
msgid ""
"An FDM, or **black box**, is a government-certified device that works "
"together with the Point of Sale application and saves your POS orders "
"information. Concretely, a **hash** (:dfn:`unique code`) is generated for "
"each POS order and added to its receipt. This allows the government to "
"verify that all revenue is declared."
msgstr ""
"FDM ali **črna škatla** je vladna certificirana naprava, ki deluje skupaj z "
"aplikacijo Prodajna točka in shranjuje informacije o naročilih vaše prodajne "
"točke. Konkretno se za vsako naročilo prodajne točke ustvari **zgoščena "
"vrednost** (:dfn:`edinstvena koda`), ki se doda na račun. To vladi omogoča "
"preverjanje, ali so prijavljeni vsi prihodki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:607
msgid ""
"Only the FDM from **Boîtenoire.be** with the `FDM certificate number BMC04 "
"<https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/systemes-"
"certifies#FDM%20certifiés>`_ is supported by Odoo. `Contact the manufacturer "
"(GCV BMC) <https://www.boîtenoire.be/contact>`_ to order one."
msgstr ""
"Odoo podpira samo FDM podjetja **Boîtenoire.be** s `certifikatom FDM "
"številka BMC04 <https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/systemes-"
"certifies#FDM%20certifiés>`_. Za naročilo se `obrnite na proizvajalca (GCV "
"BMC) <https://www.boîtenoire.be/contact>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:615
msgid ""
"Before setting up your database to work with an FDM, ensure you have the "
"following hardware:"
msgstr ""
"Preden nastavite svojo podatkovno bazo za delo z FDM, poskrbite za naslednjo "
"strojno opremo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:617
msgid "a **Boîtenoire.be** (certificate number BMC04) FDM;"
msgstr "FDM **Boîtenoire.be** (certifikat številka BMC04);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:618
msgid "an RS-232 serial null modem cable per FDM;"
msgstr "serijski kabel RS-232 null modem za vsak FDM;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:619
msgid "an RS-232 serial-to-USB adapter per FDM;"
msgstr "adapter RS-232 serijski-na-USB za vsak FDM;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:620
msgid "an :ref:`IoT Box <belgium/iotbox>` (one IoT box per FDM); and"
msgstr ":ref:`IoT Box <belgium/iotbox>` (en IoT box za vsak FDM); in"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:621
msgid "a receipt printer."
msgstr "tiskalnik računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:626
msgid "Black box module"
msgstr "Modul črne škatle"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:628
msgid ""
"As a pre-requisite, :ref:`activate <general/install>` the `Belgian "
"Registered Cash Register` module (technical name: `pos_blackbox_be`)."
msgstr ""
"Kot predpogoj :ref:`aktivirajte <general/install>` modul `Belgian Registered "
"Cash Register` (tehnično ime: `pos_blackbox_be`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "black box modules for belgian fiscal certification"
msgstr "moduli črne škatle za belgijsko fiskalno certifikacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:634
msgid ""
"Once the module is activated, add your VAT number to your company "
"information. To set it up, go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Companies --> "
"Update Info`, and fill in the :guilabel:`VAT` field. Then, enter a national "
"registration number for every staff member who operates the POS system. To "
"do so, go to the :guilabel:`Employees` app and open an employee form. There, "
"go to :menuselection:`HR settings tab --> Attendance/Point of Sale`, and "
"fill in the :guilabel:`INSZ or BIS number` field."
msgstr ""
"Ko je modul aktiviran, dodajte svojo davčno številko k podatkom o podjetju. "
"Za nastavitev pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Podjetja --> "
"Posodobi podatke` in izpolnite polje :guilabel:`DDV`. Nato vnesite "
"nacionalno registrsko številko za vsakega kadrovika, ki upravlja sistem "
"prodajne točke. To storite tako, da odprete aplikacijo :guilabel:`Kader` in "
"odprete obrazec kadrovika. Tam pojdite na :menuselection:`zavihek Nastavitve "
"kadrov --> Prisotnost/Prodajna točka` in izpolnite polje :guilabel:`INSZ ali "
"BIS številka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "ISNZ or BIS number field on employee form"
msgstr "polje ISNZ ali BIS številka na obrazcu kadrovika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:644
msgid ""
"To input your information, click on your avatar, go to :menuselection:`My "
"Profile --> Preference tab`, and enter your INSZ or BIS number in the "
"designated field."
msgstr ""
"Za vnos svojih podatkov kliknite na svoj avatar, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Moj profil --> zavihek Nastavitve` in vnesite svojo INSZ ali "
"BIS številko v predvideno polje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:648
msgid ""
"You must configure the :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)` directly in the "
"production database. Utilizing it in a testing environment may result in "
"incorrect data being stored within the FDM."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)` morate konfigurirati neposredno v "
"produkcijski podatkovni bazi. Uporaba v testnem okolju lahko povzroči "
"shranjevanje nepravilnih podatkov v FDM."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:654
msgid "IoT Box"
msgstr "IoT Box"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:656
msgid ""
"In order to use an :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)`, you need a registered "
"IoT Box. To register your IoT box, you must contact us through our `support "
"contact form <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ and provide the following "
"information:"
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo :abbr:`FDM (Fiscal Data Module)` potrebujete registriran IoT Box. "
"Za registracijo IoT boxa nas morate kontaktirati prek našega `obrazca za "
"podporo <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ in zagotoviti naslednje informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:660
msgid "your VAT number;"
msgstr "vašo davčno številko;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:661
msgid "your company's name, address, and legal structure;"
msgstr "ime, naslov in pravno obliko vašega podjetja;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:662
msgid "the identifier of your IoT Box."
msgstr "identifikator vaše IoT naprave."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:664
msgid ""
"Once your IoT box is certified, :doc:`connect <../../general/iot/connect>` "
"it to your database. To verify that the IoT Box recognizes the FDM, go to "
"the IoT homepage and scroll down the :guilabel:`IOT Device` section, which "
"should display the FDM."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vaša IoT naprava certificirana, jo :doc:`povežite <../../general/iot/"
"connect>` s svojo podatkovno bazo. Če želite preveriti, ali IoT naprava "
"prepozna FDM, pojdite na domačo stran IoT in se pomaknite navzdol do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`IOT Device`, ki bi moral prikazati FDM."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Hardware status page on a registered IoT Box"
msgstr "Stran stanja strojne opreme na registrirani IoT napravi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:671
msgid ""
"Then, add the IoT to your POS. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale "
"--> Configuration --> Point of Sale`, select your POS, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`Connected Device` section, and enable :guilabel:`IoT Box`. "
"Lastly, add the FMD in the :guilabel:`Fiscal Data Module` field."
msgstr ""
"Nato dodajte IoT v svojo prodajno točko. To storite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Konfiguracija --> Prodajna točka`, "
"izberete svojo prodajno točko, se pomaknete navzdol do razdelka "
":guilabel:`Connected Device` in omogočite :guilabel:`IoT Box`. Nazadnje "
"dodajte FMD v polje :guilabel:`Fiscal Data Module`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:676
msgid ""
"To be able to use an FDM, you must at least connect one :guilabel:`Receipt "
"Printer`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabljati FDM, morate povezati vsaj en :guilabel:`Receipt "
"Printer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:681
msgid "VAT signing card"
msgstr "Kartica za podpisovanje DDV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/belgium.rst:683
msgid ""
"When you open the POS register and make your initial transaction, you are "
"prompted to enter the PIN provided with your :abbr:`VSC (VAT signing card)`. "
"The card is delivered by the :abbr:`FPS (Service Public Federal Finances)` "
"upon `registration <https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/"
"enregistrement>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ko odprete POS blagajno in opravite svojo prvo transakcijo, boste pozvani k "
"vnosu PIN-a, ki ste ga prejeli z :abbr:`VSC (kartica za podpisovanje DDV)`. "
"Kartico izda :abbr:`FPS (Service Public Federal Finances)` ob `registraciji "
"<https://www.systemedecaisseenregistreuse.be/fr/enregistrement>`_."

