#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:182
msgid ""
"In Canada, tax rates and what is considered taxable vary by province and "
"territory. Default *Sales* and *Purchases* taxes are created automatically "
"when the Odoo **Accounting** application is installed. To manage existing or "
"configure additional taxes, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"V Kanadi se davčne stopnje in kar je obdavčljivo razlikujejo po provincah in "
"ozemljih. Privzete davščine za *prodajo* in *nakupe* se ustvarijo samodejno "
"ob namestitvi aplikacije **Računovodstvo** v Odoo. Za upravljanje obstoječih "
"ali konfiguracijo dodatnih davščin pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Davščine`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:190
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:237
msgid "AvaTax"
msgstr "AvaTax"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:192
msgid ""
"**Avalara AvaTax** is a cloud-based tax calculation and compliance software "
"that integrates with Odoo for several localizations, including Canada. "
"Integrating AvaTax with Odoo provides real-time and region-specific tax "
"calculations when items are sold, purchased, and invoiced in the database."
msgstr ""
"**Avalara AvaTax** je v oblaku gostovana programska oprema za izračun "
"davščin in skladnost, ki se integrira z Odoo za več lokalizacij, vključno s "
"Kanado. Integracija AvaTax z Odoo zagotavlja izračune davščin v realnem času "
"in glede na regijo, ko se izdelki prodajajo, kupujejo in fakturirajo v bazi "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:197
msgid ""
"AvaTax is available for integration with databases/companies that have "
"locations in Canada and/or the United States. Reference the :ref:`accounting/"
"avatax/fiscal_country` documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"AvaTax je na voljo za integracijo z bazami podatkov/podjetji, ki imajo "
"lokacije v Kanadi in/ali Združenih državah Amerike. Za več informacij si "
"oglejte dokumentacijo :ref:`accounting/avatax/fiscal_country`."

