#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:216
msgid ""
"A number of :doc:`report selections <../accounting/reporting>` are readily "
"available for the Canadian localization, under "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Reporting` drop-down menu:"
msgstr ""
"Številne :doc:`možnosti poročil <../accounting/reporting>` so na voljo za "
"kanadsko lokalizacijo v spustnem meniju :menuselection:`aplikacija "
"Računovodstvo --> Poročanje`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:219
msgid ""
":ref:`Balance Sheet <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>`: a \"snapshot\" of "
"a company's financial position at a specific point in time, which contains "
"an overview of a company's assets, liabilities, and equity."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Bilanca stanja <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>`: \"posnetek\" "
"finančnega položaja podjetja na določeni časovni točki, ki vsebuje pregled "
"sredstev, obveznosti in kapitala podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:223
msgid ""
"Be sure to select the :menuselection:`Balance sheet (CA)` option from "
"the :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report` filter."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da izberete možnost :menuselection:`Balance sheet (CA)` iz "
"filtra :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Poročilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:0
msgid "Balance sheet report selection for CA localization in Odoo."
msgstr "Izbira poročila bilance stanja za kanadsko lokalizacijo v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:229
msgid ""
":ref:`Profit & Loss <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>`: otherwise known "
"as a *P&L statement* or *income statement*, provides a summary of a "
"company's revenues, expenses, and profits/losses over a given period of time."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Izkaz poslovnega izida <accounting/reporting/balance-sheet>`: znan "
"tudi kot *izkaz P&L* ali *izkaz prihodkov in odhodkov*, podaja povzetek "
"prihodkov, odhodkov in dobičkov/izgub podjetja v določenem časovnem obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:233
msgid ""
"Be sure to select the :menuselection:`Profit and loss (CA)` option from "
"the :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report` filter."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da v filtru :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Poročilo` izberete "
"možnost :menuselection:`Profit and loss (CA)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:0
msgid "Profit and loss report selection for CA localization in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Izbira poročila izkaza poslovnega izida za kanadsko lokalizacijo v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cash Flow Statement`: shows how much cash and cash equivalents a "
"company has received and spent in a given period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izkaz denarnih tokov`: prikazuje, koliko gotovine in gotovinskih "
"ekvivalentov je podjetje prejelo in porabilo v določenem obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:241
msgid ""
":ref:`Executive Summary <accounting/reporting/executive-summary>`: an "
"overview report that covers the key performance indicators of a company's "
"financial position, such as revenue, profit, and debt."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Izvršni povzetek <accounting/reporting/executive-summary>`: pregledno "
"poročilo, ki zajema ključne kazalnike uspešnosti finančnega položaja "
"podjetja, kot so prihodki, dobiček in dolg."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/canada.rst:244
msgid ""
":ref:`Tax Report <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`: an official form filed "
"for a tax authority that reports income, expenses, and other pertinent tax "
"information. Tax reports allow taxpayers to calculate their tax liability, "
"schedule tax payments, or request refunds for the overpayment of taxes. In "
"Odoo, the tax report can be made monthly, every two months, quarterly, every "
"4 months, semi-annually, and annually."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Davčno poročilo <accounting/reporting/tax-report>`: uradni obrazec, "
"predložen davčnemu organu, ki poroča o dohodkih, odhodkih in drugih "
"ustreznih davčnih informacijah. Davčna poročila omogočajo davkoplačevalcem, "
"da izračunajo svojo davčno obveznost, načrtujejo davčne plačane ali "
"zahtevajo vračila za preveč plačane davke. V Odoo se davčno poročilo lahko "
