"The :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` :guilabel:`Email Box "
"Electronic Invoicing` can be defined to receive your customers' claim and "
"acceptance emails. Enabling this option from :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings --> Chilean Localization` is necessary if you "
"want to use *Email Box Electronic Invoicing* as the :abbr:`DTE (Documentos "
"Tributarios Electrónicos)` incoming email server."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` :guilabel:`poštni predal "
"za elektronsko izstavljanje računov` je mogoče določiti za prejemanje "
"pritožb in sprejemnih e-poštnih sporočil vaših strank. Omogočanje te "
"možnosti v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve --> Čilenska lokalizacija` je potrebno, če želite uporabiti "
"*poštni predal za elektronsko izstavljanje računov* kot strežnik za "
"prejemanje :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` po e-pošti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:157
msgid ""
"In order to receive your SII documents, it's necessary to set up your own "
"email server. More information on how to do this can be found in this "
"documentation: :doc:`../../general/email_communication`"
msgstr ""
"Za prejemanje dokumentov SII je potrebno nastaviti svoj e-poštni strežnik. "
"Več informacij o tem najdete v tej dokumentaciji: :doc:`../../general/"
"email_communication`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:161
msgid ""
"Begin by clicking :guilabel:`Configure DTE Incoming Email`, then "
"click :guilabel:`New` to add a server and fill in the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Začnite s klikom na :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj prejemanje DTE po e-pošti`, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da dodate strežnik, in izpolnite naslednja polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:164
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: give the server a name."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime`: poimenujte strežnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:165
msgid ":guilabel:`Server Type`: select the server type used."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrsta strežnika`: izberite uporabljeno vrsto strežnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:167
msgid ":guilabel:`IMAP Server`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Strežnik IMAP`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:168
msgid ":guilabel:`POP Server`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Strežnik POP`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:169
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Local Server`: uses a local script to fetch emails and create new "
"records. The script can be found in the :guilabel:`Configuration` section "
"with this option selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lokalni strežnik`: uporablja lokalno skripto za pridobivanje e-"
"poštnih sporočil in ustvarjanje novih zapisov. Skripto najdete v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Konfiguracija`, ko je ta možnost izbrana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:171
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Gmail OAuth Authentication`: requires your Gmail API credentials "
"to be configured in the general settings. A direct link to the configuration "
"can be found in the :guilabel:`Login Information` section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Avtentikacija Gmail OAuth`: zahteva, da so vaše poverilnice Gmail "
"API konfigurirane v splošnih nastavitvah. Neposredno povezavo do "
"konfiguracije najdete v razdelku :guilabel:`Podatki za prijavo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:175
msgid ""
":guilabel:`DTE Server`: enable this option. By checking this option, this "
"email account will be used to receive the electronic invoices from the "
"suppliers, and communications from the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)` regarding the electronic invoices issued. In this case, this "
"email should match both emails declared on the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` site in the section: *ACTUALIZACION DE DATOS DEL "
"CONTRIBUYENTE*, *Mail Contacto SII* and *Mail Contacto Empresas*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Strežnik DTE`: omogočite to možnost. S tem bo ta e-poštni račun "
"uporabljen za prejemanje elektronskih računov dobaviteljev in komunikacij od "
":abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` glede izdanih elektronskih "
"računov. V tem primeru se mora ta e-pošta ujemati z obema e-poštama, "
"deklariranima na spletnem mestu :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` "
"v razdelku: *ACTUALIZACION DE DATOS DEL CONTRIBUYENTE*, *Mail Contacto SII* "
"in *Mail Contacto Empresas*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:182
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Server & Login` tab (for IMAP and POP servers):"
msgstr "V zavihku :guilabel:`Strežnik in prijava` (za strežnike IMAP in POP):"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:184
msgid ":guilabel:`Server Name`: enter the hostname or IP of the server."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime strežnika`: vnesite ime gostitelja ali IP strežnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:185
msgid ":guilabel:`Port`: enter the server port."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrata`: vnesite vrata strežnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:186
msgid ""
":guilabel:`SSL/TLS`: enable this option if connections are encrypted using "
"the SSL/TLS protocol."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`SSL/TLS`: omogočite to možnost, če so povezave šifrirane s "
"protokolom SSL/TLS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:187
msgid ":guilabel:`Username`: enter the server login username."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabniško ime`: vnesite uporabniško ime za prijavo v strežnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:188
msgid ":guilabel:`Password`: enter the server login password."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Geslo`: vnesite geslo za prijavo v strežnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Incoming email server configuration for Chilean DTE."
msgstr "Konfiguracija strežnika za dohodno e-pošto za čilski DTE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:194
msgid ""
"Before going live, it is recommended to archive or remove all emails related "
"to vendor bills that are not required to be processed in Odoo from your "
"inbox."
msgstr ""
"Pred začetkom uporabe v živo je priporočljivo arhivirati ali odstraniti vso "
"e-pošto, povezano z računi dobaviteljev, ki jih ni treba obdelati v Odoo iz "
"vašega nabiralnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:273
msgid "Certificate"
msgstr "Potrdilo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:202
msgid ""
"A digital certificate in `.pfx` format is required to generate the "
"electronic invoice signature. To add one, click :guilabel:`Configure "
"Signature Certificates` under the :guilabel:`Signature Certificates` "
"section. Then, click :guilabel:`New` to configure the certificate:"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje podpisa elektronskega računa je potrebno digitalno potrdilo v "
"formatu `.pfx`. Za dodajanje kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj potrdila za "
"podpisovanje` v razdelku :guilabel:`Potrdila za podpisovanje`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Novo` za konfiguracijo potrdila:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Certificate Key`: click :guilabel:`Upload your file` and select "
"the `.pfx` file."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ključ potrdila`: kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži svojo datoteko` in "
"izberite datoteko `.pfx`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:207
msgid ":guilabel:`Certificate Passkey`: enter the file's passphrase."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ključ Passkey potrdila`: vnesite geslo datoteke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:208
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Subject Serial Number`: depending on the certificate format, the "
"field might not be automatically populated. In that case, enter the "
"certificate's legal representative :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Serijska številka subjekta`: glede na format potrdila se polje "
"morda ne bo samodejno izpolnilo. V tem primeru vnesite :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único "
"Tributario)` zakonitega zastopnika potrdila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:211
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Certificate Owner`: select one if you need to restrict the "
"certificate for a specific user. Leave the field empty to share it with all "
"billing users."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lastnik potrdila`: izberite enega, če morate omejiti potrdilo za "
"določenega uporabnika. Pustite polje prazno, da ga delite z vsemi uporabniki "
"za izdajanje računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Digital certificate configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija digitalnega potrdila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:218
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Certificate Owner` field is set to a specific user, and "
"there are no certificates shared with users, then the automatic sending of "
"electronic documents and receipt acknowledgments is **disabled**."
msgstr ""
"Če je polje :guilabel:`Lastnik potrdila` nastavljeno na določenega "
"uporabnika in ni potrdil, deljenih z uporabniki, je samodejno pošiljanje "
"elektronskih dokumentov in potrdil o prejemu **onemogočeno**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:223
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:335
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:811
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:283
msgid "Multicurrency"
msgstr "Več valut"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:225
msgid ""
"The official currency rate is provided by `Chilean mindicador.cl <https://"
"mindicador.cl>`_. Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings --> Currencies: Automatic Currency Rates` to set "
"an :guilabel:`Interval` for when the rate is automatically updated, or to "
"select another :guilabel:`Service`."
msgstr ""
"Uradni tečaj valut zagotavlja `Chilean mindicador.cl <https://mindicador.cl>"
"`_. Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve --> Valute: Samodejni tečaji valut`, da nastavite "
":guilabel:`Interval` za samodejno posodabljanje tečaja ali da izberete drugo "
":guilabel:`Storitev`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:233
msgid "Partner information"
msgstr "Informacije o partnerju"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:235
msgid ""
"Configuring partner contacts is also required to send :abbr:`SII (Servicio "
"de Impuestos Internos)` electronic invoices. Open "
"the :menuselection:`Contacts` app to do so and fill in the following fields "
"on a new or existing contact form."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija kontaktov partnerjev je prav tako potrebna za pošiljanje "
"elektronskih računov :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`. Odprite "
"aplikacijo :menuselection:`Stiki` in izpolnite naslednja polja na novem ali "
"obstoječem obrazcu stika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:241
msgid ":guilabel:`Identification Number`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Identifikacijska številka`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:242
msgid ":guilabel:`Taxpayer Type`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrsta davčnega zavezanca`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:243
msgid ":guilabel:`Activity Description`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Opis dejavnosti`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:245
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing` tab:"
msgstr "V zavihku :guilabel:`Elektronsko izdajanje računov`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`DTE Email`: enter the sender's email address for the partner."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`E-pošta DTE`: vnesite e-poštni naslov pošiljatelja za partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:248
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Guide Price`: select which price the delivery guide "
"displays, if any."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cena dobavnice`: izberite, katero ceno prikazuje dobavnica, če "
"sploh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:251
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`DTE Email` is the email used for sending electronic documents "
"and must be set in the contact that will be part of an electronic document."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`E-pošta DTE` je e-pošta, ki se uporablja za pošiljanje "
"elektronskih dokumentov, in mora biti nastavljena pri stiku, ki bo del "
"elektronskega dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Chilean electronic invoice data for partners."
msgstr "Podatki o čilskem elektronskem računu za partnerje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:260
msgid ""
"Accounting documents are categorized by :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)`-defined document types."
msgstr ""
"Računovodski dokumenti so razvrščeni po vrstah dokumentov, ki jih "
"opredeljuje :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:263
msgid ""
"Document types are created automatically upon installation of the "
"localization module, and can be managed by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Document Types`."
msgstr ""
"Vrste dokumentov so ustvarjene samodejno ob namestitvi lokalizacijskega "
"modula in jih je mogoče upravljati prek :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Vrste dokumentov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Chilean fiscal document types list."
msgstr "Seznam čilskih vrst davčnih dokumentov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:270
msgid ""
"Several document types are inactive by default but can be activated by "
"toggling the :guilabel:`Active` option."
msgstr ""
"Več vrst dokumentov je privzeto neaktivnih, vendar jih lahko aktivirate s "
"preklopom možnosti :guilabel:`Aktivno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:276
msgid "The document type on each transaction is determined by:"
msgstr "Vrsta dokumenta pri vsaki transakciji je določena z:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:278
msgid ""
"The journal related to the invoice, identifying if the journal uses "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"Dnevnikom, povezanim z računom, ki identificira, ali dnevnik uporablja "
"dokumente."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:279
msgid ""
"The condition applied based on the type of issuer and recipient (e.g., the "
"buyer or vendor's fiscal regime)."
msgstr ""
"Pogojem, ki se uporabi glede na vrsto izdajatelja in prejemnika (npr. davčni "
"režim kupca ali dobavitelja)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:285
msgid "*Sales journals* in Odoo usually represent a business unit or location."
msgstr ""
"*Prodajni dnevniki* v Odooju običajno predstavljajo poslovno enoto ali "
"lokacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:288
msgid "Ventas Santiago."
msgstr "Ventas Santiago."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:289
msgid "Ventas Valparaiso."
msgstr "Ventas Valparaiso."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:291
msgid ""
"For retail stores it is common to have one journal per :abbr:`POS (Point of "
"Sale)`."
msgstr ""
"Za maloprodajne trgovine je običajno imeti en dnevnik na :abbr:`POS "
"(Prodajna točka)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:294
msgid "Cashier 1."
msgstr "Blagajnik 1."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:295
msgid "Cashier 2."
msgstr "Blagajnik 2."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:297
msgid ""
"The *purchase* transactions can be managed with a single journal, but "
"sometimes companies use more than one journal in order to handle some "
"accounting transactions that are not related to vendor bills. This "
"configuration can easily be set by using the following model."
msgstr ""
"Transakcije *nakupov* je mogoče upravljati z enim samim dnevnikom, vendar "
"podjetja včasih uporabljajo več kot en dnevnik, da obdelajo nekatere "
"računovodske transakcije, ki niso povezane z računi dobaviteljev. To "
"konfiguracijo je mogoče enostavno nastaviti z uporabo naslednjega modela."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:302
msgid "Tax payments to the government."
msgstr "Plačila davkov državi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:303
msgid "Employees payments."
msgstr "Plačila zaposlenim."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:306
msgid "Create a sales journal"
msgstr "Ustvari dnevnik prodaje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:308
msgid ""
"To create a sales journal, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals`. Then, click the :guilabel:`New` button, and "
"fill in the following required information:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti dnevnik prodaje, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki`. Nato kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Novo` in izpolnite naslednje zahtevane informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:311
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: select :guilabel:`Sale` from the drop-down menu for "
"customer invoice journals."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta`: v spustnem meniju izberite :guilabel:`Prodaja` za "
"dnevnike računov kupcev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:312
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Point of sale type`: if the sales journal will be used for "
"electronic documents, the option :guilabel:`Online` must be selected. "
"Otherwise, if the journal is used for invoices imported from a previous "
"system or if you are using the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` "
"portal *Facturación MiPyme*, you can use the option :guilabel:`Manual`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta prodajnega mesta`: če bo dnevnik prodaje uporabljen za "
"elektronske dokumente, mora biti izbrana možnost :guilabel:`Spletno`. V "
"nasprotnem primeru, če se dnevnik uporablja za račune, uvožene iz prejšnjega "
"sistema, ali če uporabljate portal :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)` *Facturación MiPyme*, lahko uporabite možnost :guilabel:`Ročno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:316
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Documents`: check this field if the journal will use document "
"types. This field is only applicable to purchase and sales journals that can "
"be related to the different sets of document types available in Chile. By "
"default, all the sales journals created will use documents."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabi dokumente`: označite to polje, če bo dnevnik uporabljal "
"vrste dokumentov. To polje se uporablja samo za dnevnike nakupov in prodaje, "
"ki so lahko povezani z različnimi nizi vrst dokumentov, ki so na voljo v "
"Čilu. Privzeto bodo vsi ustvarjeni dnevniki prodaje uporabljali dokumente."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:320
msgid ""
"Next, from the :guilabel:`Jounal Entries` tab, define the :guilabel:`Default "
"Income Account` and :guilabel:`Dedicated Credit Note Squence` in "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting Information` section. Configuring these fields is "
"required for one of the debit notes :ref:`use cases <chile/use-cases>`."
msgstr ""
"Nato na zavihku :guilabel:`Vnosi v dnevnik` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Računovodske informacije` določite :guilabel:`Privzeti "
"prihodkovni račun` in :guilabel:`Namensko zaporedje dobropisov`. "
"Konfiguracija teh polj je potrebna za enega od :ref:`primerov uporabe <chile/"
"use-cases>` dobropisov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:327
msgid "CAF"
msgstr "CAF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:329
msgid ""
"A *folio authorization code* (CAF) is required for each document type that "
"will be issued electronically. The :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` is "
"a file the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` provides to the "
"issuer with the folios/sequences authorized for the electronic invoice "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"*Koda za odobritev folija* (CAF) je potrebna za vsako vrsto dokumenta, ki bo "
"izdan elektronsko. :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` je datoteka, ki jo "
":abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` zagotovi izdajatelju z "
"odobrenimi foliji/zaporedji za elektronske dokumente računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:334
msgid ""
"Your company can request multiple folios and obtain several :abbr:`CAFs "
"(Folio Authorization Codes)` linked to different folio ranges. "
"These :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)` are shared within all "
"journals, so you only need one active :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` "
"per document type, and it will be applied to all journals."
msgstr ""
"Vaše podjetje lahko zahteva več folijev in pridobi več :abbr:`CAF-ov (Folio "
"Authorization Codes)`, povezanih z različnimi razponi folijev. Ti :abbr:`CAF-"
"i (Folio Authorization Code)` so skupni vsem dnevnikom, zato potrebujete "
"samo en aktiven :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` na vrsto dokumenta in "
"bo apliciran na vse dnevnike."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:339
msgid ""
"Please refer to the `SII documentation <https://palena.sii.cl/dte/"
"mn_timbraje.html>`_ to check the details on how to acquire the :abbr:`CAF "
"(Folio Authorization Code)` files."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo, glejte `dokumentacijo SII <https://palena.sii.cl/dte/"
"mn_timbraje.html>`_, da preverite podrobnosti o tem, kako pridobiti datoteke "
":abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:343
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)` required by the :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` are different from production to test "
"(certification mode). Make sure you have the correct :abbr:`CAF (Folio "
"Authorization Code)` set depending on your environment."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`CAF-i (Folio Authorization Code)`, ki jih zahteva :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, se razlikujejo glede na proizvodnjo in "
"testiranje (način certifikacije). Prepričajte se, da imate pravilno "
"nastavljen :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)`, odvisno od vašega okolja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:348
msgid "Upload CAF files"
msgstr "Naloži datoteke CAF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:350
msgid ""
"Once the :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` files have been acquired "
"from the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` portal, they need to "
"be uploaded in the database by navigating to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration: Chilean SII --> CAFs`. Then, click the :guilabel:`New` begin "
"the configuration. On the :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` form, "
"upload your :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` file by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Upload your file` button and then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so datoteke :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` pridobljene s portala "
":abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, jih je treba naložiti v bazo "
"podatkov tako, da pojdete na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija: Čilski SII --> CAF-i`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da "
"začnete konfiguracijo. V obrazcu :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` "
"naložite svojo datoteko :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` s klikom na "
"gumb :guilabel:`Naloži svojo datoteko` in nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:357
msgid ""
"Once uploaded, the status changes to :guilabel:`In Use`. At this moment, "
"when a transaction is used for this document type, the invoice number takes "
"the first folio in the sequence."
msgstr ""
"Po naložitvi se stanje spremeni v :guilabel:`V uporabi`. V tem trenutku, ko "
"se transakcija uporabi za to vrsto dokumenta, številka računa vzame prvi "
"folij v zaporedju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:361
msgid ""
"The document types have to be active before uploading the :abbr:`CAF (Folio "
"Authorization Code)` files. In case some folios have been used in the "
"previous system, the next valid folio has to be set when the first "
"transaction is created."
msgstr ""
"Vrste dokumentov morajo biti aktivne pred nalaganjem datotek :abbr:`CAF "
"(Folio Authorization Code)`. V primeru, da so bili nekateri foliji "
"uporabljeni v prejšnjem sistemu, mora biti naslednji veljavni folij "
"nastavljen ob ustvarjanju prve transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:368
msgid ""
"The chart of accounts is installed by default as part of the data set "
"included in the localization module. The accounts are mapped automatically "
"in:"
msgstr ""
"Kontni načrt je privzeto nameščen kot del nabora podatkov, vključenega v "
"lokalizacijski modul. Računi so samodejno preslikani v:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:372
msgid "Default Account Payable"
msgstr "Privzeti račun obveznosti do dobaviteljev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:373
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:130
msgid "Default Account Receivable"
msgstr "Privzeti račun terjatev do kupcev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:374
msgid "Transfer Accounts"
msgstr "Prenosni računi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:375
msgid "Conversion Rate"
msgstr "Stopnja konverzije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:383
msgid ""
"As part of the localization module, taxes are created automatically with "
"their related financial account and configuration. These taxes can be "
"managed from :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Kot del lokalizacijskega modula se davki ustvarijo samodejno s povezanim "
"finančnim računom in konfiguracijo. Te davke lahko upravljate iz "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Davki`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:387
msgid "Chile has several tax types, the most common ones are:"
msgstr "Čile ima več vrst davkov, najpogostejši so:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:389
msgid "**VAT**: the regular VAT can have several rates."
msgstr "**DDV**: redni DDV lahko ima več stopenj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:390
msgid "**ILA**: the tax for alcoholic drinks."
msgstr "**ILA**: davek na alkoholne pijače."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:393
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/egypt.rst:125
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/romania.rst:110
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/taxes`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/taxes`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:399
msgid "Electronic invoice workflow"
msgstr "Potek elektronskega računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:401
msgid ""
"In the Chilean localization, the electronic invoice workflow includes "
"customer invoice issuance and vendor bill reception. The following diagram "
"explains how information is shared to the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)`, customers, and vendors."
msgstr ""
"V čilski lokalizaciji potek elektronskega računa vključuje izdajo računov "
"strankam in prejemanje računov dobaviteljev. Naslednja shema pojasnjuje, "
"kako se informacije delijo s :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, "
"strankami in dobavitelji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Diagram with Electronic invoice transactions."
msgstr "Shema s transakcijami elektronskega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:409
msgid "Customer invoice emission"
msgstr "Izdaja računa stranki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:411
msgid ""
"After the partners and journals are created and configured, the invoices are "
"created in the standard way. For Chile, one of the differences is the "
"document type that is automatically selected based on the taxpayer. The "
"document type can be changed manually if needed on the invoice by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so partnerji in dnevniki ustvarjeni in konfigurirani, se računi ustvarijo "
"na standardni način. Za Čile je ena od razlik vrsta dokumenta, ki je "
"samodejno izbrana glede na davčnega zavezanca. Vrsto dokumenta lahko po "
"potrebi ročno spremenite na računu tako, da se pomaknete na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Računi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Customer invoice document type selection."
msgstr "Izbira vrste dokumenta računa stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:420
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Documents type 33` electronic invoice must have at least one item "
"with tax, otherwise the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` rejects "
"the document validation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta dokumenta 33` elektronski račun mora imeti vsaj eno "
"postavko z davkom, sicer :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` zavrne "
"preverjanje veljavnosti dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:426
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:902
msgid "Validation and DTE status"
msgstr "Preverjanje veljavnosti in status DTE"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:428
msgid ""
"Once all invoice information is filled, either manually or automatically "
"when generated from a sales order, validate the invoice. After the invoice "
"is posted:"
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse informacije na računu izpolnjene, ročno ali samodejno, ko se "
"ustvari iz prodajnega naloga, potrdite račun. Po knjiženju računa:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:431
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` file is created "
"automatically and recorded in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` je ustvarjena "
"samodejno in zabeležena v klepetu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:433
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` :abbr:`SII (Servicio "
"de Impuestos Internos)` status is set as :guilabel:`Pending` to be sent."
msgstr ""
"Status :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` je nastavljen kot :guilabel:`V teku` za "
"pošiljanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "DTE XML File displayed in chatter."
msgstr "Datoteka DTE XML prikazana v pogovoru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:439
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` status is updated "
"automatically by Odoo with a scheduled action that runs every day at night, "
"if the response from the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` is "
"needed immediately, you can do it manually as well by following "
"the :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` status workflow:"
msgstr ""
"Status :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` se samodejno "
"posodobi v Odoo z načrtovano akcijo, ki se izvaja vsako noč. Če je potreben "
"takojšen odgovor s strani :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, "
"lahko posodobitev izvedete tudi ročno tako, da sledite poteku statusa "
":abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Transition of DTE status flow."
msgstr "Prehod med statusi DTE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:447
msgid ""
"The first step is to send the :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios "
"Electrónicos)` to the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`. This can "
"be sent manually by clicking the :guilabel:`Enviar Ahora` button. This "
"generates a :guilabel:`SII Tack number` for the invoice, which is used to "
"check the details sent by the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` "
"via email. Then, the :guilabel:`DTE status` is updated to :guilabel:`Ask for "
"Status`."
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak je pošiljanje :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` "
"na :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`. To lahko pošljete ročno s "
"klikom na gumb :guilabel:`Enviar Ahora`. To ustvari :guilabel:`SII Tack "
"number` za račun, ki se uporablja za preverjanje podrobnosti, poslanih s "
"strani :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` po e-pošti. Nato se "
":guilabel:`DTE status` posodobi na :guilabel:`Ask for Status`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:452
msgid ""
"Once the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` response is received, "
"Odoo updates the :guilabel:`DTE status`. To do it manually, click on the "
"button :guilabel:`Verify on SII`. The result can either "
"be :guilabel:`Accepted`, :guilabel:`Accepted With Objection` "
"or :guilabel:`Rejected`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je odgovor :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` prejet, Odoo "
"posodobi :guilabel:`DTE status`. Za ročno izvedbo kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Verify on SII`. Rezultat je lahko :guilabel:`Accepted`, "
":guilabel:`Accepted With Objection` ali :guilabel:`Rejected`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "Identification transaction for invoice and Status update."
msgstr "Identifikacijska transakcija za račun in posodobitev statusa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:461
msgid ""
"There are intermediate statuses in the :abbr:`SII (Serviciqo de Impuestos "
"Internos)` before acceptance or rejection. It's recommended to **NOT** "
"continuously click :guilabel:`Verify in SII` for smooth processing."
msgstr ""
"V :abbr:`SII (Serviciqo de Impuestos Internos)` obstajajo vmesni statusi "
"pred sprejemom ali zavrnitvijo. Priporočljivo je, da **NE** neprestano "
"klikate :guilabel:`Verify in SII` za nemoteno obdelavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "Electronic invoice data statuses."
msgstr "Statusi podatkov elektronskega računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:468
msgid ""
"The final response from the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` can "
"take on one of these values:"
msgstr ""
"Končni odgovor s strani :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` je "
"lahko ena od naslednjih vrednosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:471
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accepted`: indicates the invoice information is correct, our "
"document is now fiscally valid and it's automatically sent to the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Accepted`: označuje, da so podatki o računu pravilni, naš "
"dokument je zdaj davčno veljaven in se samodejno pošlje stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:473
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Accepted with objections`: indicates the invoice information is "
"correct, but a minor issue was identified, nevertheless the document is now "
"fiscally valid and it's automatically sent to the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Accepted with objections`: označuje, da so podatki o računu "
"pravilni, vendar je bila ugotovljena manjša težava, kljub temu je dokument "
"zdaj davčno veljaven in se samodejno pošlje stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:476
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rejected`: indicates the invoice information is incorrect and "
"must be corrected. Details are sent to emails you registered in "
"the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`. If it is properly "
"configured in Odoo, the details are also retrieved in the chatter once the "
"email server is processed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rejected`: označuje, da so podatki o računu nepravilni in jih je "
"treba popraviti. Podrobnosti se pošljejo na e-poštne naslove, ki ste jih "
"registrirali v :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`. Če je pravilno "
"konfigurirano v Odoo, se podrobnosti prav tako pridobijo v pogovoru, ko je e-"
"poštni strežnik obdelan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:481
msgid "If the invoice is rejected please follow these steps:"
msgstr "Če je račun zavrnjen, sledite naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:483
msgid "Change the document to :guilabel:`Draft`."
msgstr "Spremenite dokument v :guilabel:`Draft`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:484
msgid ""
"Make the required corrections based on the message received from "
"the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Opravite zahtevane popravke na podlagi sporočila, prejetega s strani "
":abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` v pogovoru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:486
msgid "Post the invoice again."
msgstr "Ponovno objavite račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "Message when an invoice is rejected."
msgstr "Sporočilo, ko je račun zavrnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:492
msgid "Crossed references"
msgstr "Navzkrižne reference"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:494
msgid ""
"When the invoice is created, as a result of another fiscal document, the "
"information related to the originator document must be registered in "
"the :guilabel:`Cross-Reference` tab. This tab is commonly used for credit or "
"debit notes, however, in some cases it can be used for customer invoices, as "
"well. In the case of the credit and debit notes, they are set automatically "
"by Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun ustvarjen kot posledica drugega davčnega dokumenta, je treba "
"informacije, povezane z izvornim dokumentom, registrirati na zavihku "
":guilabel:`Cross-Reference`. Ta zavihek se običajno uporablja za dobropise "
"ali bremepise, vendar se lahko v nekaterih primerih uporablja tudi za račune "
"strankam. V primeru dobropisov in bremepisov jih Odoo nastavi samodejno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Crossed referenced document(s)."
msgstr "Navzkrižno sklicevani dokumenti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:505
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:174
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:327
msgid "Invoice PDF report"
msgstr "Poročilo o računu v PDF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:507
msgid ""
"Once the invoice is accepted and validated by the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` and the PDF is printed, it includes the fiscal elements "
"that indicate that the document is fiscally valid."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun sprejet in potrjen s strani :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)` in je PDF natisnjen, vključuje fiskalne elemente, ki označujejo, "
"da je dokument fiskalno veljaven."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Fiscal elements and barcode printed in accepted invoices."
msgstr "Fiskalni elementi in črtna koda, natisnjeni na sprejetih računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:515
msgid ""
"If you are hosted in Odoo SH or On-Premise, you should manually install the "
"`pdf417gen <https://pypi.org/project/pdf417gen/>`_ library. Use the "
"following command to install it: :command:`pip install pdf417gen`."
msgstr ""
"Če imate gostovanje v Odoo SH ali On-Premise, morate ročno namestiti "
"knjižnico `pdf417gen <https://pypi.org/project/pdf417gen/>`_. Za namestitev "
"uporabite naslednji ukaz: :command:`pip install pdf417gen`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:520
msgid "Commercial validation"
msgstr "Komercialna potrditev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:522
msgid "Once the invoice has been sent to the customer:"
msgstr "Ko je račun poslan stranki:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:524
msgid ":guilabel:`DTE Partner Status` changes to :guilabel:`Sent`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Stanje partnerja DTE` se spremeni v :guilabel:`Poslano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:525
msgid "The customer must send a reception confirmation email."
msgstr "Stranka mora poslati e-poštno sporočilo s potrditvijo prejema."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:526
msgid ""
"Subsequently, if commercial terms and invoice data are correct, an "
"acceptance confirmation is sent; otherwise, a claim is sent."
msgstr ""
"Nato se, če so komercialni pogoji in podatki na računu pravilni, pošlje "
"potrditev sprejema; v nasprotnem primeru se pošlje ugovor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:528
msgid "The field :guilabel:`DTE Acceptance Status` is updated automatically."
msgstr "Polje :guilabel:`Stanje sprejema DTE` se posodobi samodejno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Message with the commercial acceptance from the customer."
msgstr "Sporočilo s komercialnim sprejemom stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:534
msgid "Processed for claimed invoices"
msgstr "Obdelano za račune z ugovorom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:536
msgid ""
"Once the invoice has been accepted by the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)`, **it can not be cancelled in Odoo**. In case you get a claim for "
"your customer, the correct way to proceed is with a credit note to either "
"cancel the invoice or correct it. Please refer to the :ref:`chile/credit-"
"notes` section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun sprejet s strani :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, "
"**ga ni mogoče preklicati v Odoo**. V primeru, da prejmete ugovor s strani "
"stranke, je pravilen postopek z dobropisom za preklic računa ali njegovo "
"popravilo. Za več podrobnosti glejte razdelek :ref:`chile/credit-notes`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Invoice Commercial status updated to claimed."
msgstr "Komercialno stanje računa posodobljeno na ugovor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:545
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:500
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:881
msgid "Common errors"
msgstr "Pogoste napake"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:547
msgid ""
"There are multiple reasons behind a rejection from the :abbr:`SII (Servicio "
"de Impuestos Internos)`, but these are some of the common errors you might "
"have and how to solve them:"
msgstr ""
"Obstaja več razlogov za zavrnitev s strani :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)`, vendar tukaj je nekaj pogostih napak, ki jih lahko imate, in "
"kako jih rešiti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "**Error:** `RECHAZO- DTE Sin Comuna Origen`"
msgstr "**Napaka:** `RECHAZO- DTE Sin Comuna Origen`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Hint:** make sure the company address is properly filled including the "
"state and city."
msgstr ""
"**Namig:** prepričajte se, da je naslov podjetja pravilno izpolnjen, "
"vključno z državo in mestom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "**Error:** `en Monto - IVA debe declararse`"
msgstr "**Napaka:** `en Monto - IVA debe declararse`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Hint:** the invoice lines should include one VAT tax, make sure you add "
"one on each invoice line."
msgstr ""
"**Namig:** vrstice računa morajo vključevati en davek DDV, prepričajte se, "
"da ga dodate v vsako vrstico računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "**Error:** `Rut No Autorizado a Firmar`"
msgstr "**Napaka:** `Rut No Autorizado a Firmar`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Hint:** the :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)` entered is not allowed to "
"invoice electronically, make sure the company :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único "
"Tributario)` is correct and is valid in the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` to invoice electronically."
msgstr ""
"**Namig:** vneseni :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)` ni pooblaščen za "
"elektronsko izstavljanje računov, preverite, ali je :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único "
"Tributario)` podjetja pravilen in veljaven v :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` za elektronsko izstavljanje računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Error:** `Fecha/Número Resolucion Invalido RECHAZO- CAF Vencido : "
"(Firma_DTE[AAAA-MM-DD] - CAF[AAAA-MM-DD]) &gt; 6 meses`"
msgstr ""
"**Napaka:** `Fecha/Número Resolucion Invalido RECHAZO- CAF Vencido : "
"(Firma_DTE[AAAA-MM-DD] - CAF[AAAA-MM-DD]) > 6 meses`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Hint:** try to add a new CAF related to this document as the one you're "
"using is expired."
msgstr ""
"**Namig:** poskusite dodati nov CAF, povezan s tem dokumentom, saj je tisti, "
"ki ga uporabljate, potekel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Error:** `Element '{http://www.sii.cl/SiiDte%7DRutReceptor': This element "
"is not expected. Expected is ( {http://www.sii.cl/SiiDte%7DRutEnvia ).`"
msgstr ""
"**Napaka:** `Element '{http://www.sii.cl/SiiDte%7DRutReceptor': This element "
"is not expected. Expected is ( {http://www.sii.cl/SiiDte%7DRutEnvia ).`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Hint:** Make sure the field :guilabel:`Document Type` and :guilabel:`VAT` "
"are set in the customer and in the main company."
msgstr ""
"**Namig:** prepričajte se, da sta polji :guilabel:`Vrsta dokumenta` in "
":guilabel:`DDV` nastavljeni pri stranki in v glavnem podjetju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "**Error:** `Usuario sin permiso de envio.`"
msgstr "**Napaka:** `Usuario sin permiso de envio.`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Hint:** this error indicates that most likely, your company has not passed "
"the `Certification process <https://www.sii.cl/factura_electronica/"
"factura_mercado/proceso_certificacion.htm>`_ in the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` - Sistema de Facturación de Mercado. If this is the "
"case, please contact your Account Manager or Customer Support as this "
"certification is not part of the Odoo services, but we can give you some "
"alternatives. If you already passed the certification process, this error "
"appears when a user different from the owner of the certificate is trying to "
"send :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` files to "
"the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`."
msgstr ""
"**Namig:** ta napaka kaže, da vaše podjetje najverjetneje ni opravilo "
"`postopka certificiranja <https://www.sii.cl/factura_electronica/"
"factura_mercado/proceso_certificacion.htm>`_ v :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` - Sistema de Facturación de Mercado. Če je temu tako, "
"se obrnite na vašega upravitelja računa ali podporo strankam, saj ta "
"certifikacija ni del storitev Odoo, lahko pa vam ponudimo nekatere "
"alternative. Če ste postopek certificiranja že opravili, se ta napaka "
"pojavi, ko uporabnik, ki ni lastnik certifikata, poskuša poslati datoteke "
":abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` v :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "**Error:** `CARATULA`"
msgstr "**Napaka:** `CARATULA`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid ""
"**Hint:** there are just five reasons why this error could show up and all "
"of them are related to the *Caratula* section of the XML:"
msgstr ""
"**Namig:** obstaja le pet razlogov, zakaj bi se ta napaka lahko pojavila, in "
"vsi so povezani z odsekom *Caratula* datoteke XML:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:579
msgid ""
"The company's :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)` number is incorrect or "
"missing."
msgstr ""
"Številka :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)` podjetja je napačna ali manjka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:580
msgid ""
"The certificate owner :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)` number is incorrect "
"or missing."
msgstr ""
"Številka :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)` lastnika certifikata je napačna "
"ali manjka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:581
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SII's (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único "
"Tributario)` number (this should be correct by default) is incorrect or "
"missing."
msgstr ""
"Številka :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único "
"Tributario)` (privzeto bi morala biti pravilna) je napačna ali manjka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:583
msgid "The resolution date is incorrect or missing."
msgstr "Datum sklepa je napačen ali manjka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:584
msgid "The resolution number is incorrect or missing."
msgstr "Številka sklepa je napačna ali manjka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:591
msgid ""
"When a cancellation or correction is needed over a validated invoice, a "
"credit note must be generated. It is important to consider that a :abbr:`CAF "
"(Folio Authorization Code)` file is required for the credit note, which is "
"identified as :guilabel:`Document Type` :guilabel:`61` in the :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`. Please refer to the :ref:`CAF section "
"<chile/caf-documentation>` for more information on the process to load "
"the :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` on each document type."
msgstr ""
"Ko je potrebna razveljavitev ali popravek potrjenega računa, je treba "
"ustvariti dobropis. Pomembno je upoštevati, da je za dobropis potrebna "
"datoteka :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)`, ki je identificirana kot "
":guilabel:`Vrsta dokumenta` :guilabel:`61` v :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)`. Za več informacij o postopku nalaganja :abbr:`CAF "
"(Folio Authorization Code)` za vsako vrsto dokumenta glejte :ref:`CAF "
"razdelek <chile/caf-documentation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Creation of CAF for Credit notes."
msgstr "Ustvarjanje CAF za dobropise."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:602
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:654
msgid "Use cases"
msgstr "Primeri uporabe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:605
msgid "Cancel referenced document"
msgstr "Prekliči sklicevani dokument"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:607
msgid ""
"In case you need to cancel or invalidate an invoice, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices` and select the "
"desired invoice. Then, use the button :guilabel:`Add Credit Note` and "
"select :guilabel:`Full Refund`, in this case the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` reference code is automatically set to :guilabel:`Anula "
"Documento de referencia`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preklicati ali razveljaviti račun, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Računi` in izberite želeni "
"račun. Nato uporabite gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj dobropis` in izberite "
":guilabel:`Polno povračilo`. V tem primeru je referenčna koda :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` samodejno nastavljena na :guilabel:`Anula "
"Documento de referencia`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Credit note cancelling the referenced document."
msgstr "Dobropis, ki razveljavlja referenčni dokument."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:616
msgid "Correct referenced document"
msgstr "Popravi referenčni dokument"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:618
msgid ""
"If a correction in the invoice information is required, for example the "
"street name on the original invoice is wrong, then use the "
"button :guilabel:`Add Credit Note`, select :guilabel:`Partial Refund` and "
"select the option :guilabel:`Only Text Correction`. In this case "
"the :guilabel:`SII Reference Code` field is automatically set "
"to :guilabel:`Corrects Referenced Document Text`."
msgstr ""
"Če je potrebna popravek informacij na računu, na primer ulica na prvotnem "
"računu je napačna, uporabite gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj dobropis`, izberite "
":guilabel:`Delni povračilo` in izberite možnost :guilabel:`Samo popravek "
"besedila`. V tem primeru je polje :guilabel:`Referenčna koda SII` samodejno "
"nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Popravi besedilo referenčnega dokumenta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Credit note correcting referenced document text."
msgstr "Dobropis, ki popravlja besedilo referenčnega dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:626
msgid ""
"Odoo creates a credit note with the corrected text in an invoice "
"and :guilabel:`Price` `0.00`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ustvari dobropis s popravljenim besedilom na računu in :guilabel:`Ceno` "
"`0.00`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Credit note with the corrected value on the invoice lines."
msgstr "Dobropis s popravljeno vrednostjo na postavkah računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:632
msgid ""
"Make sure to define the :guilabel:`Default Credit Account` in the sales "
"journal specifically for this use case."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da določite :guilabel:`Privzeti konto dobropisa` v prodajnem "
"dnevniku posebej za ta primer uporabe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:636
msgid "Corrects referenced document amount"
msgstr "Popravi znesek referenčnega dokumenta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:638
msgid ""
"When a correction on the amounts is required, use the button :guilabel:`Add "
"Credit note` and select :guilabel:`Partial Refund`. In this case "
"the :guilabel:`SII Reference Code` is automatically set "
"to :guilabel:`Corrige el monto del Documento de Referencia`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je potreben popravek zneskov, uporabite gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj dobropis` "
"in izberite :guilabel:`Delni povračilo`. V tem primeru je "
":guilabel:`Referenčna koda SII` samodejno nastavljena na :guilabel:`Corrige "
"el monto del Documento de Referencia`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid ""
"Credit note for partial refund to correct amounts, using the SII reference "
"code 3."
msgstr ""
"Dobropis za delni povračilo za popravek zneskov z uporabo referenčne kode "
"SII 3."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:648
msgid ""
"In Chilean localization, debit notes, in addition to credit notes, can be "
"created using the :guilabel:`Add Debit Note` button, with two main use cases."
msgstr ""
"V čilenski lokalizaciji je mogoče poleg dobropisa ustvariti tudi bremepise z "
"uporabo gumba :guilabel:`Dodaj bremepis`, z dvema glavnima primeroma uporabe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:657
msgid "Add debt on invoices"
msgstr "Dodaj dolg na račune"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:659
msgid ""
"The primary use case for debit notes is to increase the value of an existing "
"invoice. To do so, select option :guilabel:`3. Corrige el monto del "
"Documento de Referencia` for the :guilabel:`Reference Code SII` field."
msgstr ""
"Primarni primer uporabe bremepisov je povečanje vrednosti obstoječega "
"računa. Za to izberite možnost :guilabel:`3. Corrige el monto del Documento "
"de Referencia` za polje :guilabel:`Referenčna koda SII`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Debit note correcting referenced document amount."
msgstr "Bremepis, ki popravlja znesek referenčnega dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:666
msgid ""
"In this case Odoo automatically includes the :guilabel:`Source Invoice` in "
"the :guilabel:`Cross Reference` tab."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru Odoo samodejno vključi :guilabel:`Izvorni račun` v zavihek "
":guilabel:`Navzkrižna referenca`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Automatic reference to invoice in a debit note."
msgstr "Samodejna referenca na račun v bremepisu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:673
msgid "You can only add debit notes to an invoice already accepted by the SII."
msgstr "Bremepise lahko dodate računu šele, ko ga je SII že sprejel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:676
msgid "Cancel credit notes"
msgstr "Razveljavitev dobropisa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:678
msgid ""
"In Chile, debits notes are used to cancel a valid credit note. To do this, "
"click the :guilabel:`Add Debit Note` button and select the :guilabel:`1: "
"Anula Documentos de referencia` option for the :guilabel:`Reference Code "
"SII` field."
msgstr ""
"V Čilu se bremepisi uporabljajo za razveljavitev veljavnega dobropisa. Za to "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj bremepis` in izberite možnost :guilabel:`1: "
"Anula Documentos de referencia` za polje :guilabel:`Referenčna koda SII`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Debit note to cancel the referenced document (credit note)."
msgstr "Bremepis za razveljavitev referenčnega dokumenta (dobropisa)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:688
msgid ""
"As part of the Chilean localization, you can configure your incoming email "
"server to match the one you have registered in the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` in order to:"
msgstr ""
"V okviru čilske lokalizacije lahko konfigurirate strežnik za prejemanje e-"
"pošte tako, da se ujema s tistim, ki ste ga registrirali v :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, da:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:691
msgid ""
"Automatically receive the vendor bills :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios "
"Electrónicos)` and create the vendor bill based on this information."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno prejmete račune dobaviteljev :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios "
"Electrónicos)` in ustvarite račun dobavitelja na podlagi teh informacij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:693
msgid "Automatically send the reception acknowledgement to your vendor."
msgstr "Samodejno pošljete potrdilo o prejemu vašemu dobavitelju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:694
msgid "Accept or claim the document and send this status to your vendor."
msgstr ""
"Sprejmete ali uveljavljate dokument in pošljete to stanje vašemu dobavitelju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:697
msgid "Reception"
msgstr "Prejem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:699
msgid ""
"As soon as the vendor email with the attached :abbr:`DTE (Documentos "
"Tributarios Electrónicos)` is received:"
msgstr ""
"Takoj ko je prejeta e-pošta dobavitelja s priloženim :abbr:`DTE (Documentos "
"Tributarios Electrónicos)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:702
msgid "The vendor bill maps all the information included in the XML."
msgstr "Račun dobavitelja preslika vse informacije, vključene v XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:703
msgid "An email is sent to the vendor with the reception acknowledgement."
msgstr "Dobavitelju je poslan e-poštni naslov s potrdilom o prejemu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:704
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`DTE Status` is set as :guilabel:`Acuse de Recibido Enviado`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status DTE` je nastavljen kot :guilabel:`Acuse de Recibido "
"Enviado`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:707
msgid "Acceptation"
msgstr "Sprejem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:709
msgid ""
"If all the commercial information is correct on your vendor bill, then you "
"can accept the document using the :guilabel:`Aceptar Documento` button. Once "
"this is done, the :guilabel:`DTE Acceptation Status` changes "
"to :guilabel:`Accepted` and an email of acceptance is sent to the vendor."
msgstr ""
"Če so vse poslovne informacije na vašem računu dobavitelja pravilne, lahko "
"dokument sprejmete z gumbom :guilabel:`Aceptar Documento`. Ko je to "
"narejeno, se :guilabel:`Status sprejetja DTE` spremeni v "
":guilabel:`Sprejeto` in dobavitelju je poslan e-poštni naslov s sprejetjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Button for accepting vendor bills."
msgstr "Gumb za sprejem računov dobaviteljev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:717
msgid "Claim"
msgstr "Zahtevek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:719
msgid ""
"In case there is a commercial issue or the information is not correct on "
"your vendor bill, you can claim the document before validating it, using "
"the :guilabel:`Claim` button. Once this is done, the :guilabel:`DTE "
"Acceptation Status` changes to :guilabel:`Claim` and a rejection email is "
"sent to the vendor."
msgstr ""
"V primeru poslovne težave ali če informacije na vašem računu dobavitelja "
"niso pravilne, lahko pred overjanjem uveljavite dokument z gumbom "
":guilabel:`Uveljavitev`. Ko je to narejeno, se :guilabel:`Status sprejetja "
"DTE` spremeni v :guilabel:`Uveljavitev` in dobavitelju je poslana e-pošta o "
"zavrnitvi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid ""
"Claim button in vendor bills to inform the vendor all the document is "
"commercially\n"
"rejected."
msgstr ""
"Gumb za uveljavitev v računih dobaviteljev, da obvestite dobavitelja, da je "
"dokument poslovno zavrnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:728
msgid ""
"If you claim a vendor bill, the status changes from :guilabel:`Draft` "
"to :guilabel:`Cancel` automatically. Considering this as best practice, all "
"the claimed documents should be cancelled as they won't be valid for your "
"accounting records."
msgstr ""
"Če uveljavite račun dobavitelja, se status samodejno spremeni iz "
":guilabel:`Osnutek` v :guilabel:`Preklicano`. Ker je to najboljša praksa, je "
"treba vse uveljavljene dokumente preklicati, saj ne bodo veljavni za vaše "
"računovodske evidence."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:733
msgid "Electronic purchase invoice"
msgstr "Elektronski nabavni račun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:735
msgid ""
"The *electronic purchase invoice* is a feature included in the `l10n_cl_edi` "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija *elektronski nabavni račun* je vključena v modul `l10n_cl_edi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:737
msgid ""
"Once all configurations have been made for :ref:`electronic invoices <chile/"
"electronic-invoice>` (e.g., uploading a valid company certificate, setting "
"up master data, etc.), the electronic purchase invoices need their "
"own :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)`. Please refer to the :ref:`CAF "
"documentation <chile/caf-documentation>` to check the details on how to "
"acquire the :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)` for electronic purchase "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse konfiguracije izvedene za :ref:`elektronske račune <chile/"
"electronic-invoice>` (npr. nalaganje veljavnega certifikata podjetja, "
"nastavitev glavnih podatkov itd.), potrebujejo elektronski nabavni računi "
"lastne :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)`. Glejte :ref:`dokumentacijo "
"CAF <chile/caf-documentation>`, da preverite podrobnosti o tem, kako "
"pridobiti :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` za elektronske nabavne "
"račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:743
msgid ""
"Electronic purchase invoices are useful when vendors are not obligated to "
"expedite an electronic vendor bill for your purchase. Still, your "
"obligations require a document to be sent to the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` as proof of purchase."
msgstr ""
"Elektronski nabavni računi so uporabni, ko dobavitelji niso zavezani izdati "
"elektronskega računa dobavitelja za vaš nakup. Kljub temu vaše obveznosti "
"zahtevajo dokument, ki ga je treba poslati v :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)` kot dokazilo o nakupu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:750
msgid ""
"To generate an electronic purchase invoice from a vendor bill, the bill must "
"be created in a purchase journal with the *Use Documents* feature enabled. "
"It is possible to modify an existing purchase journal or create a new one in "
"the following process."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje elektronskega nabavnega računa iz računa dobavitelja mora "
"biti račun ustvarjen v nabavnem dnevniku z omogočeno funkcijo *Uporabi "
"dokumente*. Mogoče je spremeniti obstoječi nabavni dnevnik ali ustvariti "
"novega v naslednjem postopku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:754
msgid ""
"To modify the existing purchase journal, or create a new purchase journal, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`. "
"Then, click the :guilabel:`New` button, and fill in the following required "
"information:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti obstoječi dnevnik nakupov ali ustvariti novega, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki`. Nato "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo` in izpolnite naslednje zahtevane podatke:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:758
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: select :guilabel:`Purchase` from the drop-down menu for "
"vendor bill journals."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta`: iz spustnega menija izberite :guilabel:`Nakup` za "
"dnevnike računov dobaviteljev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:759
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Documents`: check this field so the journal can generate "
"electronic documents (in this case the electronic purchase invoice)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabi dokumente`: označite to polje, da lahko dnevnik ustvarja "
"elektronske dokumente (v tem primeru elektronski nabavni račun)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:763
msgid "Generate an electronic purchase invoice"
msgstr "Ustvari elektronski nabavni račun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:765
msgid ""
"To generate this type of document, it is necessary to create a vendor bill "
"in Odoo. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> "
"Bills`, and click the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje te vrste dokumenta je potrebno v Odoo ustvariti račun "
"dobavitelja. To storite tako, da pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Računi` in kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:768
msgid ""
"When all of the electronic purchase invoice information is filled, select "
"the option :guilabel:`(46) Electronic Purchase Invoice` in "
"the :guilabel:`Document Type` field:"
msgstr ""
"Ko so izpolnjeni vsi podatki elektronskega nabavnega računa, izberite "
"možnost :guilabel:`(46) Elektronski nabavni račun` v polju :guilabel:`Vrsta "
"dokumenta`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:771
msgid "After the vendor bill is posted:"
msgstr "Po knjiženju računa dobavitelja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:773
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` file (Electronic Tax "
"Document) is automatically created and added to the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` (elektronski "
"davčni dokument) se samodejno ustvari in doda v pogovor."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:775
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:847
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:913
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`DTE SII Status` is set as :guilabel:`Pending to be sent`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stanje DTE SII` je nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Čaka na pošiljanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:777
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically updates the *DTE Status* every night using a scheduled "
"action. To get a response from the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)` immediately, click the :guilabel:`Send now to SII` button."
msgstr ""
"Odoo samodejno posodobi *stanje DTE* vsako noč s pomočjo načrtovanega "
"dejanja. Če želite takoj dobiti odgovor od :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)`, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Pošlji zdaj v SII`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:782
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1677
msgid "Delivery guide"
msgstr "Dobavnica"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:784
msgid ""
"To install the :guilabel:`Delivery Guide` module, go "
"to :menuselection:`Apps` and search for `Chile (l10n_cl)`. Then "
"click :guilabel:`Install` on the module :guilabel:`Chile - E-Invoicing "
"Delivery Guide`."
msgstr ""
"Za namestitev modula :guilabel:`Dobavnica` pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacije` in poiščite `Chile (l10n_cl)`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Namesti` pri modulu :guilabel:`Čile - E-izdajanje računov "
"dobavnica`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:789
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Chile - E-Invoicing Delivery Guide` has a dependency "
"with :guilabel:`Chile - Facturación Electrónica`. Odoo will install the "
"dependency automatically when the :guilabel:`Delivery Guide` module is "
"installed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Čile - E-izdajanje računov dobavnica` ima odvisnost od "
":guilabel:`Chile - Facturación Electrónica`. Odoo bo odvisnost namestil "
"samodejno, ko bo nameščen modul :guilabel:`Dobavnica`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:793
msgid ""
"The *Delivery Guide* module includes the ability to send the :abbr:`DTE "
"(Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` to :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)` and the stamp in PDF reports for deliveries."
msgstr ""
"Modul *Dobavnica* vključuje možnost pošiljanja :abbr:`DTE (Documentos "
"Tributarios Electrónicos)` na :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` "
"in žig v PDF poročilih za dostave."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:797
msgid ""
"Once all configurations have been made for :ref:`electronic invoices <chile/"
"electronic-invoice>` (e.g., uploading a valid company certificate, setting "
"up master data, etc.), delivery guides need their own :abbr:`CAFs (Folio "
"Authorization Code)`. Please refer to the :ref:`CAF documentation <chile/caf-"
"documentation>` to check the details on how to acquire the :abbr:`CAF (Folio "
"Authorization Code)` for electronic Delivery Guides."
msgstr ""
"Ko so opravljene vse konfiguracije za :ref:`elektronske račune <chile/"
"electronic-invoice>` (npr. nalaganje veljavnega certifikata podjetja, "
"nastavitev glavnih podatkov itd.), potrebujejo dobavnice svoje :abbr:`CAF "
"(Folio Authorization Code)`. Za podrobnosti o tem, kako pridobiti :abbr:`CAF "
"(Folio Authorization Code)` za elektronske dobavnice, glejte "
":ref:`dokumentacijo CAF <chile/caf-documentation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:803
msgid ""
"Verify the following important information in the :guilabel:`Price for the "
"Delivery Guide` configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Preverite naslednje pomembne podatke v konfiguraciji :guilabel:`Cena za "
"dobavnico`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:806
msgid ""
":guilabel:`From Sales Order`: delivery guide takes the product price from "
"the sales order and shows it on the document."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Iz prodajnega naloga`: dobavnica vzame ceno izdelka iz prodajnega "
"naloga in jo prikaže v dokumentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:808
msgid ""
":guilabel:`From Product Template`: Odoo takes the price configured in the "
"product template and shows it on the document."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Iz predloge izdelka`: Odoo vzame ceno, konfigurirano v predlogi "
"izdelka, in jo prikaže v dokumentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:810
msgid ":guilabel:`No show price`: no price is shown in the delivery guide."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ne prikaži cene`: v dobavnici cena ni prikazana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:812
msgid ""
"Electronic delivery guides are used to move stock from one place to another "
"and they can represent sales, sampling, consignment, internal transfers, and "
"basically any product move."
msgstr ""
"Elektronske dobavnice se uporabljajo za premik zaloge iz enega kraja na "
"drugega in lahko predstavljajo prodajo, vzorčenje, konsignacijo, interne "
"prenose in v bistvu vsak premik izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:816
msgid "Delivery guide from a sales process"
msgstr "Dobavnica iz prodajnega procesa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:819
msgid ""
"A delivery guide should **not** be longer than one page or contain more than "
"60 product lines."
msgstr ""
"Dobavnica **ne** sme biti daljša od ene strani ali vsebovati več kot 60 "
"vrstic izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:821
msgid ""
"When a sales order is created and confirmed, a delivery order is generated. "
"After validating the delivery order, the option to create a delivery guide "
"is activated."
msgstr ""
"Ko je prodajni nalog ustvarjen in potrjen, se generira naročilo za dobavo. "
"Po potrditvi naročila za dobavo se aktivira možnost za ustvarjanje dobavnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Create Delivery Guide button on a sales process."
msgstr "Gumb Ustvari dobavnico v prodajnem procesu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:828
msgid ""
"When clicking on :guilabel:`Create Delivery Guide` for the first time, a "
"warning message pops up, stating the following:"
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič kliknete na :guilabel:`Ustvari dobavnico`, se prikaže opozorilno "
"sporočilo z naslednjim besedilom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:831
msgid ""
"`No se encontró una secuencia para la guía de despacho. Por favor, "
"establezca el primer número dentro del campo número para la guía de despacho`"
msgstr ""
"`No se encontró una secuencia para la guía de despacho. Por favor, "
"establezca el primer número dentro del campo número para la guía de despacho`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:0
msgid "First Delivery Guide number warning message."
msgstr "Opozorilno sporočilo prve številke dobavnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:837
msgid ""
"This warning message means the user needs to indicate the next sequence "
"number Odoo has to take to generate the delivery guide (e.g. next "
"available :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` number), and only happens "
"the first time a delivery guide is created in Odoo. After the first document "
"has been correctly generated, Odoo takes the next available number in "
"the :abbr:`CAF (Folio Authorization Code)` file to generate the following "
"delivery guide."
msgstr ""
"To opozorilno sporočilo pomeni, da mora uporabnik navesti naslednjo "
"zaporedno številko, ki jo mora Odoo uporabiti za generiranje dobavnice (npr. "
"naslednjo razpoložljivo številko :abbr:`CAF (koda za pooblastilo folija)`), "
"in se pojavi samo prvič, ko je dobavnica ustvarjena v Odoo. Po pravilnem "
"generiranju prvega dokumenta Odoo vzame naslednjo razpoložljivo številko v "
"datoteki :abbr:`CAF (koda za pooblastilo folija)` za generiranje naslednje "
"dobavnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:843
msgid "After the delivery guide is created:"
msgstr "Po ustvarjenju dobavnice:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:845
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` file (Electronic Tax "
"Document) is automatically created and added to the :guilabel:`chatter`."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` (elektronski "
"davčni dokument) se samodejno ustvari in doda v :guilabel:`klepet`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Chatter notes of Delivery Guide creation."
msgstr "Opombe klepeta o ustvarjanju dobavnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:852
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`DTE Status` is automatically updated by Odoo with a scheduled "
"action that runs every night. To get a response from the :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` immediately, press the :guilabel:`Send now "
"to SII` button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status DTE` samodejno posodobi Odoo s predvideno akcijo, ki se "
"izvaja vsako noč. Za takojšen odgovor od :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos "
"Internos)` pritisnite gumb :guilabel:`Pošlji zdaj v SII`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:856
msgid ""
"Once the delivery guide is sent, it may then be printed by clicking on "
"the :guilabel:`Print Delivery Guide` button."
msgstr ""
"Ko je dobavnica poslana, jo lahko nato natisnete s klikom na gumb "
":guilabel:`Natisni dobavnico`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Printing Delivery Guide PDF."
msgstr "Tiskanje PDF dobavnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:862
msgid ""
"Delivery guide will have fiscal elements that indicate that the document is "
"fiscally valid when printed (if hosted in *Odoo SH* or on *On-premise* "
"remember to manually add the :guilabel:`pdf417gen` library mentioned in "
"the :ref:`Invoice PDF report section <chile/electronic-invoice-pdf-report>`)."
msgstr ""
"Dobavnica bo imela fiskalne elemente, ki pri tiskanju označujejo, da je "
"dokument fiskalno veljaven (če je gostovana v *Odoo SH* ali *On-premise*, ne "
"pozabite ročno dodati knjižnice :guilabel:`pdf417gen`, omenjene v "
":ref:`razdelku poročila PDF računa <chile/electronic-invoice-pdf-report>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:868
msgid "Electronic receipt"
msgstr "Elektronski račun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:870
msgid ""
"To install the :guilabel:`Electronic Receipt` module, go "
"to :menuselection:`Apps` and search for `Chile (l10n_cl)`. Then "
"click :guilabel:`Install` on the module :guilabel:`Chile - Electronic "
"Receipt`."
msgstr ""
"Za namestitev modula :guilabel:`Elektronski račun` pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacije` in poiščite `Chile (l10n_cl)`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Namesti` pri modulu :guilabel:`Čile - Elektronski račun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:875
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Chile - Electronic Receipt` has a dependency "
"with :guilabel:`Chile - Facturación Electrónica`. Odoo will install the "
"dependency automatically when the :guilabel:`E-invoicing Delivery Guide` "
"module is installed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Čile - Elektronski račun` ima odvisnost od :guilabel:`Chile - "
"Facturación Electrónica`. Odoo bo samodejno namestil odvisnost, ko bo "
"nameščen modul :guilabel:`E-invoicing Delivery Guide`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:879
msgid ""
"Once all configurations have been made for :ref:`electronic invoices <chile/"
"electronic-invoice>` (e.g., uploading a valid company certificate, setting "
"up master data, etc.), electronic receipts need their own :abbr:`CAFs (Folio "
"Authorization Code)`. Please refer to the :ref:`CAF documentation <chile/caf-"
"documentation>` to check the details on how to acquire the :abbr:`CAFs "
"(Folio Authorization Code)` for electronic receipts."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse konfiguracije za :ref:`elektronske račune <chile/electronic-"
"invoice>` narejene (npr. nalaganje veljavnega certifikata podjetja, "
"nastavitev osnovnih podatkov itd.), elektronski računi potrebujejo svoje "
":abbr:`CAF (kode za pooblastilo folija)`. Glejte :ref:`dokumentacijo CAF "
"<chile/caf-documentation>` za podrobnosti o tem, kako pridobiti :abbr:`CAF "
"(kode za pooblastilo folija)` za elektronske račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:885
msgid ""
"Electronic receipts are useful when clients do not need an electronic "
"invoice. By default, there is a partner in the database "
"called :guilabel:`Anonymous Final Consumer` with a generic :abbr:`RUT (Rol "
"Único Tributario)` `66666666-6` and taxpayer type of :guilabel:`Final "
"Consumer`. This partner can be used for electronic receipts or a new record "
"may be created for the same purpose."
msgstr ""
"Elektronski računi so uporabni, ko stranke ne potrebujejo elektronskega "
"računa. Privzeto je v bazi podatkov partner z imenom :guilabel:`Anonimni "
"končni potrošnik` z generičnim :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)` `66666666-"
"6` in vrsto zavezanca :guilabel:`Končni potrošnik`. Ta partner se lahko "
"uporabi za elektronske račune ali pa se lahko za isti namen ustvari nov "
"zapis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Electronic Receipt module."
msgstr "Modul elektronskih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:893
msgid ""
"Although electronic receipts should be used for final consumers with a "
"generic :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)`, it can also be used for specific "
"partners. After the partners and journals are created and configured, the "
"electronic receipts are created in the standard way as electronic invoice, "
"but the type of document :guilabel:`(39) Electronic Receipt` should be "
"selected in the invoice form:"
msgstr ""
"Čeprav bi bilo treba elektronske račune uporabljati za končne porabnike s "
"splošnim :abbr:`RUT (Rol Único Tributario)`, se lahko uporabljajo tudi za "
"določene partnerje. Ko so partnerji in dnevniki ustvarjeni in konfigurirani, "
"se elektronski računi ustvarijo na standardni način kot elektronski račun, "
"vendar je treba v obrazcu računa izbrati vrsto dokumenta :guilabel:`(39) "
"Elektronski račun`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Document type 39 for Electronic Receipts."
msgstr "Vrsta dokumenta 39 za elektronske račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:904
msgid ""
"When all of the electronic receipt information is filled, manually (or "
"automatically) proceed to validate the receipt from the sales order. By "
"default, :guilabel:`Electronic Invoice` is selected as "
"the :guilabel:`Document Type`, however in order to validate the receipt "
"correctly, make sure to edit the :guilabel:`Document Type` and change "
"to :guilabel:`Electronic Receipt`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so izpolnjeni vsi podatki elektronskega računa, ročno (ali samodejno) "
"nadaljujte s potrditvijo računa iz prodajnega naloga. Privzeto je kot "
":guilabel:`Vrsta dokumenta` izbran :guilabel:`Elektronski račun`, vendar da "
"bi račun potrdili pravilno, poskrbite, da uredite :guilabel:`Vrsto "
"dokumenta` in spremenite na :guilabel:`Elektronski račun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:909
msgid "After the receipt is posted:"
msgstr "Ko je račun knjižen:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:911
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` file (Electronic Tax "
"Document) is created automatically and added to the :guilabel:`chatter`."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka :abbr:`DTE (Documentos Tributarios Electrónicos)` (elektronski "
"davčni dokument) se samodejno ustvari in doda v :guilabel:`klepet`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Electronic Receipts STE creation status."
msgstr "Status ustvarjanja STE elektronskih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:918
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`DTE Status` is automatically updated by Odoo with a scheduled "
"action that runs every day at night. To get a response from the :abbr:`SII "
"(Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` immediately, press the :guilabel:`Send now "
"to SII` button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status DTE` samodejno posodobi Odoo s predvideno akcijo, ki se "
"izvaja vsako noč. Če želite takoj prejeti odgovor od :abbr:`SII (Servicio de "
"Impuestos Internos)`, pritisnite gumb :guilabel:`Pošlji zdaj v SII`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:922
msgid ""
"Please refer to the :ref:`DTE Workflow <chile/electronic-invoice-"
"validation>` for electronic invoices as the workflow for electronic receipt "
"follows the same process."
msgstr ""
"Glejte :ref:`potek dela DTE <chile/electronic-invoice-validation>` za "
"elektronske račune, saj potek dela za elektronski račun sledi istemu procesu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:926
msgid "Electronic export of goods"
msgstr "Elektronski izvoz blaga"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:928
msgid ""
"To install the :guilabel:`Electronic Exports of Goods` module, go "
"to :menuselection:`Apps` and search for `Chile (l10n_cl)`. Then "
"click :guilabel:`Install` on the module :guilabel:`Electronic Exports of "
"Goods for Chile`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite namestiti modul :guilabel:`Elektronski izvoz blaga`, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacije` in poiščite `Chile (l10n_cl)`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Namesti` pri modulu :guilabel:`Elektronski izvoz blaga za Čile`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:933
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Chile - Electronic Exports of Goods for Chile` has a dependency "
"with :guilabel:`Chile - Facturación Electrónica`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Čile - Elektronski izvoz blaga za Čile` je odvisen od "
":guilabel:`Čile - Facturación Electrónica`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:936
msgid ""
"Once all configurations have been made for :ref:`electronic invoices <chile/"
"electronic-invoice>` (e.g., uploading a valid company certificate, setting "
"up master data, etc.), electronic exports of goods need their "
"own :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)`. Please refer to the :ref:`CAF "
"documentation <chile/caf-documentation>` to check the details on how to "
"acquire the :abbr:`CAFs (Folio Authorization Code)` for electronic receipts."
msgstr ""
"Ko so opravljene vse konfiguracije za :ref:`elektronske račune <chile/"
"electronic-invoice>` (npr. nalaganje veljavnega certifikata podjetja, "
"nastavitev glavnih podatkov itd.), elektronski izvoz blaga potrebuje lastne "
":abbr:`CAF (kode za avtorizacijo folija)`. Glejte :ref:`dokumentacijo CAF "
"<chile/caf-documentation>`, da preverite podrobnosti o tem, kako pridobiti "
":abbr:`CAF (kode za avtorizacijo folija)` za elektronske račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:942
msgid ""
"Electronic invoices for the export of goods are tax documents that are used "
"not only for the :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)` but are also "
"used with customs and contain the information required by it."
msgstr ""
"Elektronski računi za izvoz blaga so davčni dokumenti, ki se ne uporabljajo "
"samo za :abbr:`SII (Servicio de Impuestos Internos)`, ampak se uporabljajo "
"tudi pri carini in vsebujejo podatke, ki jih ta zahteva."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:947
msgid "Contact configurations"
msgstr "Konfiguracije stikov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
msgid "Taxpayer Type needed for the Electronic Exports of Goods module."
msgstr "Vrsta davkoplačevalca, potrebna za modul Elektronski izvoz blaga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:953
msgid "Chilean customs"
msgstr "Čileanska carina"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:955
msgid ""
"When creating an electronic exports of goods invoice, these new fields in "
"the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab are required to comply with Chilean "
"regulations."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju računa za elektronski izvoz blaga so ta nova polja v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Druge informacije` potrebna za skladnost s čilenskimi predpisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/chile.rst:None
