"izpolnite polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:138
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: the name of the certificate."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime`: ime potrdila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Certificate`: upload the certificate file in PEM format. In "
"the :guilabel:`Private Key` field that appears on the screen, select an "
"existing private key or create a new one. To do so, enter a key name and "
"select :guilabel:`Create and edit`. Then, in the :guilabel:`Create Private "
"Key` wizard, upload a valid :guilabel:`Key file` and click :guilabel:`Save & "
"Close`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Potrdilo`: naložite datoteko potrdila v formatu PEM. V polju "
":guilabel:`Zasebni ključ`, ki se prikaže na zaslonu, izberite obstoječi "
"zasebni ključ ali ustvarite novega. To storite tako, da vnesete ime ključa "
"in izberete :guilabel:`Ustvari in uredi`. Nato v čarovniku "
":guilabel:`Ustvari zasebni ključ` naložite veljavno :guilabel:`Datoteko "
"ključa` in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:0
msgid "Colombian electronic invoicing credentials configured."
msgstr "Konfigurirane poverilnice za kolumbijsko elektronsko izdajanje računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:147
msgid ""
"Configure the |DIAN| environment; the |DIAN| electronic invoicing module "
"offers four different |DIAN| environments to connect with:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte okolje |DIAN|; modul za elektronsko izdajanje računov |DIAN| "
"ponuja štiri različna okolja |DIAN| za povezavo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:150
msgid ""
"**DIAN demo mode**: This environment allows to test electronic invoicing "
"workflows using a demo digital certificate. Files are created and accepted "
"automatically and are not sent to any |DIAN| environment. Every internal "
"validation can be tested. To activate it, tick the :guilabel:`DIAN Demo "
"Mode` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"**Način DIAN demo**: To okolje omogoča testiranje poteka dela za elektronsko "
"izdajanje računov z uporabo demonstracijskega digitalnega potrdila. Datoteke "
"se ustvarijo in sprejmejo samodejno ter se ne pošljejo v nobeno okolje "
"|DIAN|. Mogoče je testirati vse notranje validacije. Za aktivacijo označite "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Način DIAN demo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:156
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`DIAN Demo Mode` checkbox is hidden from view when "
"the :guilabel:`Test environment` checkbox is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Način DIAN demo` je skrito, ko je omogočeno "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Testno okolje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:159
msgid ""
"**Certification environment**: This environment is useful to pass the |DIAN| "
"certification process and obtain the *Enabled* status to invoice from Odoo. "
"To activate it, enable both the :guilabel:`Test environment` and "
"the :guilabel:`Activate the certification process` checkboxes."
msgstr ""
"**Okolje za certificiranje**: To okolje je uporabno za opravitev postopka "
"certificiranja |DIAN| in pridobitev statusa *Omogočeno* za izdajanje računov "
"iz Odoo. Za aktivacijo omogočite potrditveni polji :guilabel:`Testno okolje` "
"in :guilabel:`Aktiviraj postopek certificiranja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:162
msgid ""
"**Testing environment**: This environment allows reproducing electronic "
"invoicing flows and validations in the |DIAN| testing portal. To activate "
"it, enable only the :guilabel:`Test Environment` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"**Testno okolje**: To okolje omogoča reprodukcijo potekov dela in validacij "
"za elektronsko izdajanje računov na testnem portalu |DIAN|. Za aktivacijo "
"omogočite samo potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Testno okolje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:165
msgid ""
"**Production environment**: This environment allows generating valid "
"electronic documents. To activate it, disable both the :guilabel:`Test "
"environment` and the :guilabel:`Activate the certification process` "
"checkboxes."
msgstr ""
"**Produkcijsko okolje**: To okolje omogoča generiranje veljavnih "
"elektronskih dokumentov. Za aktivacijo onemogočite potrditveni polji "
":guilabel:`Testno okolje` in :guilabel:`Aktiviraj certifikacijski proces`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:170
msgid ""
"Do not activate :guilabel:`DIAN Demo Mode` on a production database. This "
"mode is intended for use in test environments only."
msgstr ""
"Ne aktivirajte :guilabel:`DIAN Demo Mode` v produkcijski bazi podatkov. Ta "
"način je namenjen uporabi samo v testnih okoljih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:174
msgid "In a multi-company database, each company can have its own certificate."
msgstr ""
"V večpodjetniški bazi podatkov ima lahko vsako podjetje svoj certifikat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:177
msgid ""
"For electronic invoicing configurations using the Carvajal solution, review "
"the following video: `Configuración de Facturación Electrónica - "
"Localización de Colombia <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=bzweMwTEbfY&list=PL1-aSABtP6ABxZshems3snMjx7bj_7ZsZ&index=3>`_."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracije elektronskega računa, ki uporabljajo rešitev Carvajal, si "
"oglejte naslednji videoposnetek: `Configuración de Facturación Electrónica - "
"Localización de Colombia <https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=bzweMwTEbfY&list=PL1-aSABtP6ABxZshems3snMjx7bj_7ZsZ&index=3>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:184
msgid "Automatic DIAN Enablement"
msgstr "Samodejno omogočanje DIAN"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:186
msgid ""
"Odoo automates the |DIAN| enablement process to become an electronic "
"invoicer using the `DIAN Own Software <https://micrositios.dian.gov.co/"
"sistema-de-facturacion-electronica/como-puedes-facturar-electronicamente/>`_ "
"solution, sending the required number of valid customer invoices, credit "
"notes, and debit notes to the DIAN certification environment."
msgstr ""
"Odoo avtomatizira postopek omogočanja |DIAN| za elektronsko izstavljanje "
"računov z uporabo rešitve `DIAN lastna programska oprema <https://"
"micrositios.dian.gov.co/sistema-de-facturacion-electronica/como-puedes-"
"facturar-electronicamente/>`_, s pošiljanjem zahtevanega števila veljavnih "
"računov za stranke, dobropisov in terjatvenih obremenitev v certificirno "
"okolje DIAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:191
msgid ""
"To start this process, complete the :ref:`main configuration steps for "
"electronic invoicing <localization/colombia/einvoice-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek tega postopka dokončajte :ref:`glavne konfiguracijske korake za "
"elektronsko izstavljanje računov <localization/colombia/einvoice-"
"configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:195
msgid ""
"Always run the enablement process in a **test database** to serve as the "
"environment for continued electronic invoicing testing before going to "
"production."
msgstr ""
"Postopek omogočanja vedno izvajajte v **testni zbirki podatkov**, ki bo "
"služila kot okolje za nadaljnje testiranje elektronskega izstavljanja "
"računov pred prehodom v produkcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:198
msgid ""
"To begin the process, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Colombian Electronic Invoicing` section, "
"and complete the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za začetek postopka pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se pomaknite do razdelka "
":guilabel:`Kolumbijsko elektronsko izstavljanje računov` in dokončajte "
"naslednje korake:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:201
msgid "Enable the :guilabel:`Test Environment` checkbox."
msgstr "Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Testno okolje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:202
msgid "Enable the :guilabel:`Activate Certification Process` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Aktiviraj postopek certificiranja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:203
msgid ""
"Enter the number of documents requested by the |DIAN| for each type of "
"document"
msgstr ""
"Vnesite število dokumentov, ki jih zahteva |DIAN|, za vsako vrsto dokumenta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:204
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Begin Certification Process`, then :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Začni postopek certificiranja`, nato :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:207
msgid ""
"The exact number of documents required by the |DIAN| is shown in the portal "
"when you register the operation mode."
msgstr ""
"Natančno število dokumentov, ki jih zahteva |DIAN|, je prikazano na portalu, "
"ko registrirate način delovanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:210
msgid ""
"The necessary journals, products, and required documents are automatically "
"generated and submitted to the |DIAN|'s certification environment."
msgstr ""
"Potrebni dnevniki, izdelki in zahtevani dokumenti so samodejno ustvarjeni in "
"poslani v certificirno okolje |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:213
msgid ""
"When the process is complete, click :guilabel:`Open` to review the generated "
"documents and check each document's validation status under "
"its :guilabel:`DIAN` tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko je postopek dokončan, kliknite :guilabel:`Odpri`, da pregledate "
"ustvarjene dokumente in preverite stanje validacije vsakega dokumenta na "
"zavihku :guilabel:`DIAN`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:217
msgid ""
"Confirm that the company status has changed to :guilabel:`Enabled` in the |"
"DIAN| portal before proceeding to production:"
msgstr ""
"Potrdite, da se je status podjetja spremenil v :guilabel:`Omogočeno` na "
"portalu |DIAN|, preden nadaljujete v produkcijo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:220
msgid ""
"If the status is :guilabel:`Enabled`, the process has been completed "
"successfully."
msgstr "Če je status :guilabel:`Omogočeno`, je bil postopek uspešno dokončan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:221
msgid ""
"If the company is not :guilabel:`Enabled`, repeat the process until it is "
"successfully enabled."
msgstr ""
"Če podjetje ni :guilabel:`Omogočeno`, ponovite postopek, dokler ni uspešno "
"omogočeno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:224
msgid ""
"Watch this `video <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_0j9kqL9yOU>`_ for a "
"demonstration of the process."
msgstr ""
"Za predstavitev postopka si oglejte ta `video <https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=_0j9kqL9yOU>`_."

