msgstr "Specifične davčne konfiguracije po predpisih DIAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:271
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:275
msgid "Sales journals"
msgstr "Prodajni dnevniki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:273
msgid ""
"Once the |DIAN| has assigned the official sequence and prefix for the "
"electronic invoice resolution, the sales journals related to the invoices "
"**must** be updated in Odoo. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and select an "
"existing sales journal or create a new one with the :guilabel:`Create` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Ko |DIAN| dodeli uradno zaporedje in predpono za resolucijo elektronskega "
"računa, je **treba** posodobiti prodajne dnevnike, povezane z računi, v "
"Odoo. Za to pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Journals` in izberite obstoječi prodajni dnevnik ali ustvarite novega z "
"gumbom :guilabel:`Ustvari`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:278
msgid ""
"On the sales journal form, enter the :guilabel:`Journal Name` "
"and :guilabel:`Type`, then set a unique :guilabel:`Short Code` in "
"the :guilabel:`Journals Entries` tab. Then, configure the following data in "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab:"
msgstr ""
"V obrazcu prodajnega dnevnika vnesite :guilabel:`Ime dnevnika` in "
":guilabel:`Vrsto`, nato nastavite edinstveno :guilabel:`Kratko kodo` v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Dnevniški vnosi`. Nato konfigurirajte naslednje podatke v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Napredne nastavitve`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:282
msgid ":guilabel:`Electronic invoicing`: enable UBL 2.1 (Colombia)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Elektronsko izstavljanje računov`: omogočite UBL 2.1 (Kolumbija)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:283
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Resolution`: resolution number issued by |DIAN| to the "
"company via their test set."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Resolution`: številka resolucije, ki jo je |DIAN| izdal "
"podjetju preko njihovega testnega seta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:285
msgid ":guilabel:`Resolution Date`: initial effective date of the resolution."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Resolution Date`: začetni datum veljavnosti resolucije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:286
msgid ":guilabel:`Resolution End Date`: end date of the resolution's validity."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Resolution End Date`: končni datum veljavnosti resolucije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:287
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Range of Numbering (minimum)`: first authorized invoice number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Range of Numbering (minimum)`: prva odobrena številka računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:288
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Range of Numbering (maximum)`: last authorized invoice number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obseg oštevilčenja (maksimum)`: zadnja odobrena številka računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:289
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Technical Key`: control key received from the |DIAN| portal test "
"set or from their web service in case of the production environment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tehnični ključ`: kontrolni ključ, prejet s testnega portala "
"|DIAN| ali iz njihove spletne storitve v primeru produkcijskega okolja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:292
msgid ""
"When the database is configured for the :ref:`production environment "
"<localization/colombia/einvoice-configuration>`, instead of configuring "
"these fields manually, click the :guilabel:`Reload DIAN configuration` "
"button to obtain the |DIAN| resolution information from the |DIAN| web "
"service."
msgstr ""
"Ko je zbirka podatkov konfigurirana za :ref:`produkcijsko okolje "
"<localization/colombia/einvoice-configuration>`, namesto ročnega "
"konfiguriranja teh polj kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Ponovno naloži "
"konfiguracijo DIAN`, da pridobite podatke o resoluciji |DIAN| iz spletne "
"storitve |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Reload DIAN configuration button in sale journals."
msgstr "Gumb za ponovno nalaganje konfiguracije DIAN v prodajnih dnevnikih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:301
msgid ""
"The short code and resolution of the journal **must** match the ones "
"received in the |DIAN| portal test set or from the MUISCA portal."
msgstr ""
"Kratka koda in resolucija dnevnika **morata** ustrezati tistim, ki so "
"prejeti v testnem portalu |DIAN| ali s portala MUISCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:303
msgid ""
"The :ref:`invoice sequence and prefix <localization/colombia/invoice-"
"creation>` **must** be correctly configured when the first invoice is "
"created. Odoo automatically assigns a prefix and sequence to the following "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Zaporedje in predpona računa <localization/colombia/invoice-creation>` "
"**morata** biti pravilno konfigurirana ob ustvarjanju prvega računa. Odoo "
"naslednjim računom samodejno dodeli predpono in zaporedje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:310
msgid "Purchase journals"
msgstr "Nabavni dnevniki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:312
msgid ""
"Once the |DIAN| has assigned the official sequence and prefix for the "
"*support document* related to vendor bills, the purchase journals related to "
"their supporting documents need to be updated in Odoo. The process is "
"similar to the configuration of the :ref:`sales journals <localization/"
"colombia/co-journals>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko |DIAN| dodeli uradno zaporedje in predpono za *podporni dokument*, "
"povezan z računi dobaviteljev, je treba nabavne dnevnike, povezane z "
"njihovimi podpornimi dokumenti, posodobiti v Odoo. Postopek je podoben "
"konfiguraciji :ref:`prodajnih dnevnikov <localization/colombia/co-journals>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:318
msgid ""
"For more information on support document journals using the Carvajal "
"solution, review the `Documento Soporte - Localización de Colombia video "
"<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UmYsFcD7xzE&list=PL1-"
"aSABtP6ABxZshems3snMjx7bj_7ZsZ&index=8>`_."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o dnevnikih podpornih dokumentov, ki uporabljajo rešitev "
"Carvajal, si oglejte videoposnetek `Documento Soporte - Localización de "
"Colombia <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UmYsFcD7xzE&list=PL1-"
"aSABtP6ABxZshems3snMjx7bj_7ZsZ&index=8>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:327
msgid ""
"The :doc:`chart of accounts </applications/finance/accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` is installed by default as part of the localization "
"module. The accounts are mapped automatically in taxes, default account "
"payable, and default account receivable. The chart of accounts for Colombia "
"is based on the PUC (Plan Unico de Cuentas)."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Kontni načrt </applications/finance/accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` je privzeto nameščen kot del modula za lokalizacijo. "
"Računi so samodejno preslikani v davke, privzeti konto obveznosti in "
"privzeti konto terjatev. Kontni načrt za Kolumbijo temelji na PUC (Plan "
"Unico de Cuentas)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:337
msgid ""
"The official exchange rate for Colombia is provided by the `Banco de la "
"República <https://suameca.banrep.gov.co/estadisticas-economicas/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Uradni menjalniški tečaj za Kolumbijo zagotavlja `Banco de la República "
"<https://suameca.banrep.gov.co/estadisticas-economicas/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:340
msgid "To enable automatic exchange rate updates, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za omogočanje samodejnega posodabljanja menjalniških tečajev sledite tem "
"korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:343
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Currencies` section and "
"enable :guilabel:`Automatic Currency Rates`."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se do razdelka :guilabel:`Valute` in omogočite "
":guilabel:`Samodejni menjalniški tečaji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:344
msgid ""
"Ensure that :guilabel:`[CO] Bank of the Republic` is selected as "
"the :guilabel:`Service`."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je kot :guilabel:`Storitev` izbran :guilabel:`[CO] Banka "
"republike`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:345
msgid ""
"Select an :guilabel:`Interval` for how frequently the currency rate should "
"be automatically updated."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Interval` za to, kako pogosto naj se menjalniški tečaj "
"samodejno posodablja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:349
msgid "Main workflows"
msgstr "Glavni delovni tokovi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:356
msgid ""
"The following is a breakdown of the main workflow for electronic invoices "
"with the Colombian localization:"
msgstr ""
"V nadaljevanju je razčlenitev glavnega delovnega toka za elektronske račune "
"s kolumbijsko lokalizacijo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:359
msgid "The user creates an invoice."
msgstr "Uporabnik ustvari račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:360
msgid "Odoo generates the legal XML file."
msgstr "Odoo ustvari zakonsko datoteko XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:361
msgid ""
"Odoo generates the CUFE (Invoice Electronic Code) with the electronic "
"signature."
msgstr "Odoo generira CUFE (elektronska koda računa) z elektronskim podpisom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:362
msgid "Odoo sends a notification to DIAN."
msgstr "Odoo pošlje obvestilo na DIAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:363
msgid "|DIAN| validates the invoice."
msgstr "|DIAN| preveri račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:364
msgid "|DIAN| accepts or rejects the invoice."
msgstr "|DIAN| sprejme ali zavrne račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:365
msgid "Odoo generates the PDF invoice with a QR code."
msgstr "Odoo generira račun v obliki PDF s kodo QR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:366
msgid ""
"Odoo compresses the attached document (containing the sent XML file and the "
"DIAN validation response) and the fiscal valid PDF into a :file:`.zip` file."
msgstr ""
"Odoo stisne priloženi dokument (ki vsebuje poslano datoteko XML in odgovor "
"validacije DIAN) ter fiskalno veljaven PDF v datoteko :file:`.zip`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:368
msgid ""
"The user sends the invoice (:file:`.zip` file) via Odoo to the acquirer."
msgstr "Uporabnik pošlje račun (datoteko :file:`.zip`) prek Odoo pridobitelju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:376
msgid ""
"The functional workflow taking place before an invoice validation does "
"**not** alter the main changes introduced with the electronic invoice."
msgstr ""
"Funkcionalni delovni tok, ki poteka pred validacijo računa, **ne** spremeni "
"glavnih sprememb, uvedenih z elektronskim računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:379
msgid ""
"Electronic invoices are generated and sent to both the |DIAN| and the "
"customer. These documents can be created from the sales order or manually "
"generated. To create a new invoice, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Costumers --> Invoices`, and select :guilabel:`Create`. On the invoice form, "
"configure the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"Elektronski računi so generirani in poslani tako na |DIAN| kot kupcu. Ti "
"dokumenti so lahko ustvarjeni iz prodajnega naloga ali ročno generirani. Za "
"ustvaritev novega računa pojdite na :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Costumers --> Invoices` in izberite :guilabel:`Create`. Na obrazcu računa "
"konfigurirajte naslednja polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:384
msgid ":guilabel:`Customer`: customer's information."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Customer`: podatki o kupcu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:385
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal`: journal used for electronic invoices."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Journal`: dnevnik, uporabljen za elektronske račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:386
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Electronic Invoice Type`: Select the type of document. By "
"default, :guilabel:`Factura de Venta` is selected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Electronic Invoice Type`: izberite vrsto dokumenta. Privzeto je "
"izbrana možnost :guilabel:`Factura de Venta`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:388
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Lines`: Specify the products with the correct taxes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Invoice Lines`: navedite izdelke s pravilnimi davki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:391
msgid ""
"When creating the first invoice related to an electronic invoicing journal, "
"it is required to manually change the *sequence* of the invoice to the |"
"DIAN| format: `Prefix + Sequence`."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju prvega računa, povezanega z dnevnikom elektronskega računa, "
"je treba ročno spremeniti *zaporedje* računa v obliko |DIAN|: `Predpona + "
"Zaporedje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:394
msgid "For example, format the sequence from `SETP/2024/00001` to `SETP1`."
msgstr "Na primer, oblikujte zaporedje iz `SETP/2024/00001` v `SETP1`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:396
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:227
msgid "When done, click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr "Ko končate, kliknite :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:401
msgid "Electronic invoice sending"
msgstr "Pošiljanje elektronskega računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:403
msgid ""
"After the :ref:`invoice confirmation <localization/colombia/invoice-"
"creation>`, click :guilabel:`Send`. In the wizard that appears, make sure to "
"enable the :guilabel:`DIAN` and :guilabel:`Email` checkboxes to send an XML "
"to the |DIAN| web service and the validated invoice to the client fiscal "
"email and click :guilabel:`Send`. Then:"
msgstr ""
"Po :ref:`potrditvi računa <localization/colombia/invoice-creation>` kliknite "
":guilabel:`Pošlji`. V čarovniku, ki se prikaže, poskrbite, da omogočite "
"potrditveni polji :guilabel:`DIAN` in :guilabel:`E-pošta`, da pošljete XML "
"spletni storitvi |DIAN| in potrjen račun na davčno e-pošto stranke, ter "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`. Nato:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:408
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:244
msgid "The XML document is created."
msgstr "Ustvarjen je dokument XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:409
msgid "The CUFE is generated."
msgstr "Generiran je CUFE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:410
msgid "The XML is processed synchronously by the |DIAN|."
msgstr "XML sinhronsko obdela |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:411
msgid ""
"If accepted, the file is displayed in the chatter and the email to the "
"client with the corresponding :file:`.zip` file."
msgstr ""
"Če je sprejeta, se datoteka prikaže v pogovoru in e-pošti stranki z ustrezno "
"datoteko :file:`.zip`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:None
msgid "EDI documents available in the chatter."
msgstr "Dokumenti EDI, razpoložljivi v pogovoru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:417
msgid "The :guilabel:`DIAN` tab then displays the following:"
msgstr "Zavihek :guilabel:`DIAN` nato prikaže naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:419
msgid ":guilabel:`Signed Date`: timestamp recorded of the XML creation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Podpisni datum`: zabeležena časovna značka ustvarjanja XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:420
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Status`: Status result obtained in the |DIAN| response. If the "
"invoice was rejected, the error messages can be seen here."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status`: rezultat statusa, pridobljen v odgovoru |DIAN|. Če je "
"bil račun zavrnjen, so sporočila o napakah vidna tukaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:422
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Testing Environment`: To know if the document sent was delivered "
"to the |DIAN| testing environment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Testno okolje`: da izveste, ali je bil poslani dokument "
"dostavljen v testno okolje |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:424
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Certification Process`: To know if the document was sent as part "
"of the certification process with the |DIAN|."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Postopek certificiranja`: da izveste, ali je bil dokument poslan "
"kot del postopka certificiranja z |DIAN|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:426
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Download`: To download the sent XML file, even if the |DIAN| "
"result was rejected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prenesi`: za prenos poslane datoteke XML, tudi če je bil rezultat "
"|DIAN| zavrnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:428
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fetch Attached Document`: To download the generated attached "
"document file included in the delivered :file:`.zip` file to the client."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pridobi priloženi dokument`: za prenos ustvarjene datoteke "
"priloženega dokumenta, vključene v dostavljeni datoteki :file:`.zip` stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "EDI document record available in DIAN tab."
msgstr "Zapis dokumenta EDI, razpoložljiv v zavihku DIAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:439
msgid ""
"The process for credit notes is the same as for invoices. To create a credit "
"note with reference to an invoice, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Invoices`. On the invoice, click :guilabel:`Add Credit Note`, "
"and complete the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Postopek za dobropise je enak kot za račune. Za ustvarjanje dobropisa s "
"sklicevanjem na račun pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Stranke --> Računi`. Na računu kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj dobropis` in "
"izpolnite naslednje informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:443
msgid ":guilabel:`Credit Method`: Select the type of credit method."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Metoda dobropisa`: izberite vrsto metode dobropisa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:445
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Partial Refund`: Use this option when it is a partial amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delni povračilo`: uporabite to možnost, ko gre za delni znesek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:446
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Full Refund`: Use this option if the credit note is for the full "
"amount."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Popolno povračilo`: uporabite to možnost, če je dobropis za "
"celoten znesek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:447
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Full refund and new draft invoice`: Use this option if the credit "
"note is auto-validated and reconciled with the invoice. The original invoice "
"is duplicated as a new draft."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Popolno povračilo in nov osnutek računa`: uporabite to možnost, "
"če je dobropis samodejno potrjen in usklajen z računom. Izvirni račun je "
"podvojen kot nov osnutek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:451
msgid ":guilabel:`Reason`: Enter the reason for the credit note."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Razlog`: vnesite razlog za dobropis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:452
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reversal Date`: Select if you want a specific date for the credit "
"note or if it is the journal entry date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum storniranja`: izberite, ali želite določen datum za "
"dobropis ali če je to datum knjiženja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:454
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Specific Journal`: Select the journal for your credit note or "
"leave it empty if you want to use the same journal as the original invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabi določen dnevnik`: izberite dnevnik za svoj dobropis ali "
"pustite prazno, če želite uporabiti isti dnevnik kot izvirni račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:456
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Refund Date`: If you chose a specific date, select the date for "
"the refund."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum povračila`: če ste izbrali določen datum, izberite datum za "
"povračilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:458
msgid "Once reviewed, click the :guilabel:`Reverse` button."
msgstr "Ko pregledate, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Storniraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:465
msgid ""
"The process for debit notes is similar to credit notes. To create a debit "
"note with reference to an invoice, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Customers --> Invoices`. On the invoice, click the :guilabel:`Add Debit "
"Note` button, and enter the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Postopek za terjatvene note je podoben postopku za dobropisne note. Če "
"želite ustvariti terjatveno noto s sklicevanjem na račun, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Računi`. Na računu kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj terjatveno noto` in vnesite naslednje informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:469
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:336
msgid ":guilabel:`Reason`: Type the reason for the debit note."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Razlog`: Vnesite razlog za terjatveno noto."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:470
msgid ":guilabel:`Debit note date`: Select the specific options."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum terjatvene note`: Izberite določene možnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:471
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Copy lines`: Select this option if you need to register a debit "
"note with the same lines of invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kopiraj vrstice`: Izberite to možnost, če morate registrirati "
"terjatveno noto z enakimi vrsticami kot račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:473
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Use Specific Journal`: Select the printer point for your debit "
"note, or leave it empty if you want to use the same journal as the original "
"invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabi določen dnevnik`: Izberite tiskalniško točko za vašo "
"terjatveno noto ali pustite prazno, če želite uporabiti enak dnevnik kot "
"izvirni račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:476
msgid "When done, click :guilabel:`Create Debit Note`."
msgstr "Ko končate, kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari terjatveno noto`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:481
msgid "Support document for vendor bills"
msgstr "Podporni dokument za račune dobaviteljev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:483
msgid ""
"With master data, credentials, and the purchase journal configured for "
"support documents related to vendor bills, you can start using *support "
"documents*."
msgstr ""
"Z glavnimi podatki, poverilnicami in nakupnim dnevnikom, konfiguriranim za "
"podporne dokumente, povezane z računi dobaviteljev, lahko začnete "
"uporabljati *podporne dokumente*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:486
msgid ""
"Support documents for vendor bills can be created from your purchase order "
"or manually. Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Bills` and "
"fill in the following data:"
msgstr ""
"Podporne dokumente za račune dobaviteljev lahko ustvarite iz vašega naročila "
"ali ročno. Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> "
"Računi` in izpolnite naslednje podatke:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:489
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:590
msgid ":guilabel:`Vendor`: Enter the vendor's information."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Dobavitelj`: Vnesite informacije o dobavitelju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:490
msgid ":guilabel:`Bill Date`: Select the date of the bill."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum računa`: Izberite datum računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:491
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select the journal for support documents related to the "
"vendor bills."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dnevnik`: Izberite dnevnik za podporne dokumente, povezane z "
"računi dobaviteljev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:492
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoiced Lines`: Specify the products with the correct taxes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Zaračunane vrstice`: Navedite izdelke s pravilnimi davki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:494
msgid ""
"Once reviewed, click the :guilabel:`Confirm` button. Upon confirmation, an "
"XML file is created and automatically sent to Carvajal."
msgstr ""
"Ko preverite, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Potrdi`. Po potrditvi se ustvari "
"datoteka XML in se samodejno pošlje podjetju Carvajal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:502
msgid ""
"During the XML validation, the most common errors are related to "
"missing :ref:`master data <localization/colombia/master-data>`. In such "
"cases, a validation error message is displayed and sending is blocked."
msgstr ""
"Med preverjanjem XML so najpogostejše napake povezane z manjkajočimi "
":ref:`glavnimi podatki <localization/colombia/master-data>`. V takih "
"primerih se prikaže sporočilo o napaki pri preverjanju in pošiljanje je "
"blokirano."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:506
msgid ""
"If the invoice was sent and set as *Rejected* by the |DIAN|, the error "
"messages are visible by clicking the :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(info "
"circle)` icon next to the :guilabel:`Status` field in the :guilabel:`DIAN` "
"tab. Using the reported error codes, it is possible to review solutions to "
"apply before re-sending."
msgstr ""
"Če je bil račun poslan in ga je |DIAN| nastavil kot *Zavrnjen*, so sporočila "
"o napakah vidna s klikom na ikono :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(info "
"krog)` poleg polja :guilabel:`Status` v zavihku :guilabel:`DIAN`. Z uporabo "
"sporočenih kod napak je mogoče pregledati rešitve, ki jih je treba uporabiti "
"pred ponovnim pošiljanjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Example of error messages on rejected invoices."
msgstr "Primer sporočil o napakah pri zavrnjenih računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:514
msgid ""
"After the master data or other issues are corrected, it is possible to "
"reprocess the XML again. Do so by following the :ref:`electronic invoice "
"sending <localization/colombia/send-electronic-invoice>` flow."
msgstr ""
"Ko so glavni podatki ali druge težave odpravljeni, je mogoče XML ponovno "
"obdelati. To storite tako, da sledite postopku :ref:`pošiljanja "
"elektronskega računa <localization/colombia/send-electronic-invoice>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:526
msgid "Certificado de Retención en ICA"
msgstr "Certificado de Retención en ICA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:528
msgid ""
"This report is a certification to vendors for withholdings made for the "
"Colombian Industry and Commerce (ICA) tax. The report can be found "
"under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Colombian Statements --> "
"Certificado de Retención en ICA`."
msgstr ""
"To poročilo je potrdilo dobaviteljem za zadržanja, opravljena za kolumbijski "
"davek na industrijo in trgovino (ICA). Poročilo najdete v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Kolumbijske izjave --> "
"Certificado de Retención en ICA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:532
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:547
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:562
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon to display options "
"to :guilabel:`Download Excel` and :guilabel:`Copy to Documents`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(zobnik)`, da prikažete možnosti "
"za :guilabel:`Prenesi Excel` in :guilabel:`Kopiraj v dokumente`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Certificado de Retención en ICA report in Odoo Accounting."
msgstr "Poročilo Certificado de Retención en ICA v Odoo Računovodstvu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:541
msgid "Certificado de Retención en IVA"
msgstr "Certificado de Retención en IVA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:543
msgid ""
"This report issues a certificate on the amount withheld from vendors for VAT "
"withholding. The report can be found under :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Colombian Statements --> Certificado de Retención en IVA`."
msgstr ""
"To poročilo izda potrdilo o znesku, ki je zadržan od dobaviteljev za "
"zadržanje DDV. Poročilo najdete v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročanje --> Kolumbijske izjave --> Certificado de Retención en IVA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Certificado de Retención en IVA report in Odoo Accounting."
msgstr "Poročilo Certificado de Retención en IVA v Odoo Računovodstvu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:556
msgid "Certificado de Retención en la Fuente"
msgstr "Certificado de Retención en la Fuente"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:558
msgid ""
"This certificate is issued to partners for the withholding tax that they "
"have made. The report can be found under :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Colombian Statements --> Certificado de Retención en Fuente`."
msgstr ""
"To potrdilo se izda partnerjem za davek pri viru, ki so ga opravili. "
"Poročilo najdete v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> "
"Kolumbijske izjave --> Certificado de Retención en Fuente`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/colombia.rst:None
msgid "Certificado de Retención en Fuente report in Odoo Accounting."
msgstr "Poročilo Certificado de Retención en Fuente v Odoo Računovodstvu."

