":doc:`Dokumentacija o zakonitosti in skladnosti e-fakturiranja na Hrvaškem "
"<../accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/croatia>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:48
msgid ""
"Odoo can connect to the national eRačun platform via the third-party "
"provider `mojeRačun <https://moj-eracun.hr>`_ to send and receive e-invoices."
msgstr ""
"Odoo se lahko poveže z nacionalno platformo eRačun prek ponudnika tretje "
"osebe `mojeRačun <https://moj-eracun.hr>`_ za pošiljanje in prejemanje e-"
"računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:52
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Croatia - e-invoicing` (`l10n_hr_edi`) module must "
"be :ref:`installed <general/install>` to configure e-invoicing via mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Modul :guilabel:`Hrvaška - e-izdajanje računov` (`l10n_hr_edi`) mora biti "
":ref:`nameščen <general/install>`, da lahko konfigurirate e-izdajanje "
"računov prek mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:56
msgid ""
"To use this integration, an account and `invoice package <https://portal.moj-"
"eracun.hr/podrska/cjenik/>`_ from mojeRačun are needed. The rest of this "
"documentation assumes that one has already been obtained."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo te integracije sta potrebna račun in `paket računov <https://"
"portal.moj-eracun.hr/podrska/cjenik/>`_ od mojeRačun. Preostanek te "
"dokumentacije predpostavlja, da ste ju že pridobili."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:65
msgid "Follow these steps to set up e-invoicing via mojeRačun in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Sledite tem korakom za nastavitev e-izdajanja računov prek mojeRačun v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:70
msgid "Company configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija podjetja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:72
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"down to :guilabel:`MojEracun E-invoicing`. Fill the :guilabel:`Username` "
"field with the numeric username and the :guilabel:`Password` field with the "
"password provided by mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` "
"in se pomaknite navzdol do :guilabel:`MojEracun e-izdajanje računov`. "
"Izpolnite polje :guilabel:`Uporabniško ime` z numeričnim uporabniškim imenom "
"in polje :guilabel:`Geslo` z geslom, ki ga je zagotovil mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:77
msgid ""
"Alternatively, the :guilabel:`Username` can be set to the e-mail address "
"used to register on mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Drugače lahko :guilabel:`Uporabniško ime` nastavite na e-poštni naslov, "
"uporabljen za registracijo na mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:80
msgid ""
"Ensure that the :guilabel:`Company ID (OIB or GIN)` and :guilabel:`Company "
"Business Unit (PJ)` fields are correctly filled in, matching the data used "
"to register on mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da sta polji :guilabel:`ID podjetja (OIB ali GIN)` in "
":guilabel:`Poslovna enota podjetja (PJ)` pravilno izpolnjeni in se ujemata s "
"podatki, uporabljenimi za registracijo na mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:83
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Business Software (ERP) ID` should be set to `Saodoo-001`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID poslovne programske opreme (ERP)` naj bo nastavljen na `Saodoo-"
"001`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:85
msgid ""
"Optionally, specify the :guilabel:`Incoming E-Invoices Journal` where "
"invoices received via |MER| should be created. If left unset, the default "
"purchase journal will be used."
msgstr ""
"Po želji določite :guilabel:`Dnevnik dohodno prejemljivih e-računov`, kjer "
"naj se ustvarijo računi, prejeti prek |MER|. Če ni nastavljen, se bo "
"uporabil privzeti dnevnik nabav."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:88
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`MojEracun Operating Mode` to :guilabel:`Production` to "
"send and receive invoices on the production network."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite :guilabel:`Način delovanja MojEracun` na :guilabel:`Produkcija`, "
"da pošiljate in prejemate račune v produkcijskem omrežju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:92
msgid ""
"Using the :guilabel:`Test` mode connects to a MER demo server that requires "
"separate credentials and is not relevant for most end users."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba načina :guilabel:`Test` se poveže s predstavitvenim strežnikom MER, "
"ki zahteva ločene poverilnice in ni relevanten za večino končnih uporabnikov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:95
msgid ""
"Then click :guilabel:`Activate` to activate the connection with mojeRačun."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Aktiviraj`, da aktivirate povezavo z mojeRačun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:100
msgid "Journal configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija dnevnika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:102
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals` and click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` journal to open its configuration."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki` in "
"kliknite dnevnik :guilabel:`Prodaja`, da odprete njegovo konfiguracijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:105
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Fiscalization (HR)` section, complete "
"the :guilabel:`Business premises label`, :guilabel:`Issuing device "
"label`, :guilabel:`Business premises label (refund approval)`, "
"and :guilabel:`Issuing device label (refund approval)` fields."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Fiskalizacija (HR)` izpolnite polja :guilabel:`Oznaka "
"poslovnih prostorov`, :guilabel:`Oznaka naprave za izdajanje`, "
":guilabel:`Oznaka poslovnih prostorov (odobritev vračila)` in "
":guilabel:`Oznaka naprave za izdajanje (odobritev vračila)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:109
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Business premises label` and :guilabel:`Issuing device label` "
"are used to generate invoice names. The :guilabel:`Business premises label "
"(refund approval)` and :guilabel:`Issuing device label (refund approval)` "
"fields are used to generate credit note names."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oznaka poslovnih prostorov` in :guilabel:`Oznaka naprave za "
"izdajanje` se uporabljata za ustvarjanje imen računov. Polji "
":guilabel:`Oznaka poslovnih prostorov (odobritev vračila)` in "
":guilabel:`Oznaka naprave za izdajanje (odobritev vračila)` se uporabljata "
"za ustvarjanje imen dobropisov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:116
msgid "Sending an e-invoice"
msgstr "Pošiljanje e-računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:118
msgid ""
"To send an e-invoice, follow the :ref:`standard e-invoicing <accounting/e-"
"invoicing/generation>` workflow. Be sure to select :guilabel:`by MojEracun` "
"when sending the e-invoice."
msgstr ""
"Za pošiljanje e-računa sledite :ref:`standardnemu postopku e-izdajanja "
"računov <accounting/e-invoicing/generation>`. Pri pošiljanju e-računa ne "
"pozabite izbrati :guilabel:`prek MojEracun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:121
msgid "The following invoice fields must be set before sending to mojeRačun:"
msgstr ""
"Pred pošiljanjem v mojeRačun morajo biti nastavljena naslednja polja računa:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:123
msgid ""
"**Invoice sequence:** Ensure the invoice sequence is in the format `{Journal "
"code}-{Year}-{Sequence}/{Business premises label}/{Issuing device label}`. "
"If the journal is configured :ref:`as instructed above <localizations/"
"croatia/configuration/journal>`, Odoo automatically formats invoice names to "
"fit this format."
msgstr ""
"**Zaporedje računa:** Prepričajte se, da je zaporedje računa v obliki `{Koda "
"dnevnika}-{Leto}-{Zaporedje}/{Oznaka poslovne enote}/{Oznaka naprave za "
"izdajo}`. Če je dnevnik nastavljen :ref:`kot je navedeno zgoraj "
"<localizations/croatia/configuration/journal>`, Odoo samodejno oblikuje "
"imena računov, da ustrezajo tej obliki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`KPD category`: Set the :guilabel:`KPD category` on every invoice "
"line."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kategorija KPD`: Nastavite :guilabel:`kategorijo KPD` na vsaki "
"vrstici računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:130
msgid ""
"The |KPD category| can also be set on the product record, which will then "
"automatically apply it on invoice lines when the product is used. To do so, "
"go to :menuselection:`Accounting -> Customers -> Products`, click the "
"product, and set the :guilabel:`KPD category`."
msgstr ""
"|KPD category| lahko nastavite tudi na zapisu izdelka, ki se bo nato "
"samodejno uporabil na vrsticah računa, ko se izdelek uporabi. To naredite "
"tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo -> Kupci -> Izdelki`, "
"kliknete izdelek in nastavite :guilabel:`kategorijo KPD`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:134
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Croatia: Fiscalization 2.0` tab of invoices:"
msgstr "V zavihku :guilabel:`Hrvaška: Fiskalizacija 2.0` računov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Business process type`: Set the :guilabel:`Business Process Type` "
"as appropriate. If :guilabel:`P99: Customer-defined process` is selected, "
"complete the :guilabel:`Custom Process Name` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta poslovnega procesa`: Ustrezno nastavite :guilabel:`vrsto "
"poslovnega procesa`. Če je izbrana možnost :guilabel:`P99: S strani stranke "
"določen proces`, izpolnite polje :guilabel:`Ime procesa po meri`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiscal user` and :guilabel:`Operator OIB`: The Croatian "
"government expects the user who sends the invoice to be identified via their "
"personal |OIB| number. The fiscal user defaults to the user who confirms the "
"invoice and is identified under :guilabel:`Fiscal User`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fiskalni uporabnik` in :guilabel:`OIB operaterja`: Hrvaška vlada "
"pričakuje, da je uporabnik, ki pošlje račun, identificiran s svojo osebno "
"številko |OIB|. Fiskalni uporabnik je privzeto uporabnik, ki potrdi račun, "
"in je identificiran pod :guilabel:`Fiskalni uporabnik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:143
msgid ""
"The user's |OIB| can be set on the user's contact record. To do so, follow "
"these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabnikov |OIB| lahko nastavite na kontaktnem zapisu uporabnika. To "
"naredite tako, da sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:145
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Users` and click "
"the user in the list view."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Uporabniki in podjetja --> "
"Uporabniki` in kliknite uporabnika na seznamu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:147
msgid ""
"In the user's form, click the :guilabel:`Contact` smart button to access the "
"user's :guilabel:`Contact` form."
msgstr ""
"V uporabnikovem obrazcu kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Stik`, da dostopate "
"do uporabnikovega obrazca :guilabel:`Stik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:149
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, set the :guilabel:`Personal OIB` in "
"the :guilabel:`Misc` section."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Prodaja in nakup` nastavite :guilabel:`Osebni OIB` v "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Razno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:152
msgid "Once an invoice has been sent:"
msgstr "Ko je račun poslan:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:154
msgid ""
"**Invoice fiscalization information:** The :guilabel:`Fiscalization "
"status`, :guilabel:`Fiscalization request ID`, :guilabel:`Payment amount "
"already reported to Tax Authority`, and :guilabel:`MojeRačun document "
"ElectronicId` can be viewed in the :guilabel:`Croatia: Fiscalization 2.0` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"**Informacije o fiskalizaciji računa:** :guilabel:`Status fiskalizacije`, "
":guilabel:`ID zahteve za fiskalizacijo`, :guilabel:`Znesek plačila, ki je že "
"prispel davčnemu organu`, in :guilabel:`MojeRačun dokument ElectronicId` si "
"lahko ogledate v zavihku :guilabel:`Hrvaška: Fiskalizacija 2.0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:158
msgid ""
"**Fetching status updates:** Odoo periodically checks for any updates to the "
"invoice's status (e.g., rejection by |MER|, the eRačun system, or the "
"recipient). To manually check for updates, go to "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting` dashboard, and in the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoices` (sales) journal, click the :guilabel:`MER: Fetch status` button."
msgstr ""
"**Pridobivanje posodobitev statusa:** Odoo redno preveri posodobitve statusa "
"računa (npr. zavrnitev s strani |MER|, sistema eRačun ali prejemnika). Za "
"ročno preverjanje posodobitev pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo` "
"nadzorno ploščo in v dnevniku :guilabel:`Računi kupcem` (prodaja) kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`MER: Pridobi status`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:162
msgid ""
"**Reporting a payment:** The Croatian government expects to be notified once "
"payment has been received for an invoice. To send this notification, click "
"the :guilabel:`MER: Report payments` button on the invoice form view, which "
"appears if the invoice has unreported payments."
msgstr ""
"**Poročanje o plačilu:** Hrvaška vlada pričakuje, da bo obveščena, ko bo "
"plačilo za račun prejeto. Za pošiljanje tega obvestila kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`MER: Poročaj o plačilih` v obrazcu računa, ki se prikaže, če ima "
"račun neporočana plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:167
msgid ""
"To report multiple payment notifications at once, select multiple invoices "
"from the invoice list view and click the :guilabel:`MER: Report payments` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Za poročanje o več obvestilih o plačilih hkrati izberite več računov s "
"seznama računov in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`MER: Poročaj o plačilih`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:173
msgid "Receiving e-invoices"
msgstr "Prejemanje e-računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:175
msgid ""
"Odoo periodically checks for new invoices received via mojeRačun. New "
"invoices received via mojeRačun appear in the :guilabel:`Incoming E-Invoices "
"Journal` specified in the :ref:`settings <localizations/croatia/"
"configuration/company>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo redno preveri nove račune, prejete prek mojeRačun. Novi računi, prejeti "
"prek mojeRačun, se prikažejo v :guilabel:`Dnevniku dohodnoščih e-računov`, "
"ki je naveden v :ref:`nastavitvah <localizations/croatia/configuration/"
"company>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:180
msgid "Rejecting an invoice"
msgstr "Zavrnitev računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/croatia.rst:182
msgid ""
"To reject an incoming invoice, click the :guilabel:`MER: Reject eRacun` "
"button on the invoice form view. This notifies the eRačun system and the "
"sender that the invoice is rejected."
msgstr ""
"Za zavrnitev dohodnega računa kliknite gumb :guilabel:`MER: Zavrni eRacun` v "
"obrazcu računa. To obvesti sistem eRačun in pošiljatelja, da je račun "
"zavrnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:3
msgid "Denmark"
msgstr "Danska"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:6
msgid ""
"Compliance with Danish bookkeeping requirements: data retention and integrity"
msgstr ""
"Skladnost z danskimi zahtevami za knjigovodstvo: hranjenje in celovitost "
"podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:8
msgid ""
"This page outlines how Odoo complies with the Danish Bookkeeping Act, "
"specifically regarding the storage and integrity of financial transactions "
"and receipts. Odoo recognizes the importance of adhering to Danish "
"regulations and has implemented robust measures to ensure clients' data is "
"secure and compliant."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran opisuje, kako Odoo izpolnjuje danski zakon o knjigovodstvu, posebej "
"glede shranjevanja in celovitosti finančnih transakcij ter prejemkov. Odoo "
"priznava pomen upoštevanja danskih predpisov in je uvedel robustne ukrepe za "
"zagotovitev varnosti in skladnosti podatkov strank."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:14
msgid ""
"Odoo’s registration as a digital bookkeeping system has been confirmed by "
"the Danish Business Authority under registration numbers `fob585505` and "
"`fob441967`. Customers must meet certain conditions to benefit from it, as "
"outlined below."
msgstr ""
"Registracijo sistema Odoo kot digitalnega knjigovodskega sistema je potrdila "
"danska gospodarska uprava pod registrskima številkama `fob585505` in "
"`fob441967`. Stranke morajo izpolnjevati določene pogoje, da lahko "
"izkoristijo te prednosti, kot je opisano spodaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:20
msgid "Key requirements of the Danish Bookkeeping Act"
msgstr "Ključne zahteve danskega zakona o knjigovodstvu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:22
msgid ""
"The Danish Bookkeeping Act (DBA) outlines the `requirements for digital "
"bookkeping systems <https://danishbusinessauthority.dk/requirements-digital-"
"bookkeeping-systems>`_:"
msgstr ""
"Danski zakon o knjigovodstvu (DBA) opredeljuje `zahteve za digitalne sisteme "
"knjigovodstva <https://danishbusinessauthority.dk/requirements-digital-"
"bookkeeping-systems>`_:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:25
msgid ""
"**Retain transactional data and receipts:** Store all recorded transactions "
"and receipts covered by § 3 for a minimum of five years from the end of the "
"financial year to which they pertain."
msgstr ""
"**Hranite transakcijske podatke in prejemke:** Shranjujte vse evidentirane "
"transakcije in prejemke, zajete v § 3, za najmanj pet let od konca "
"poslovnega leta, na katero se nanašajo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Ensure data integrity:** Prevent the customer from changing, backdating, "
"or deleting recorded transactions."
msgstr ""
"**Zagotovite celovitost podatkov:** Preprečite stranki spreminjanje, "
"vzvratno datiranje ali brisanje evidentiranih transakcij."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:30
msgid ""
"**Maintain data accessibility:** Store all recorded transactions in a "
"structured and machine-readable format for the required five-year period, "
"regardless of customer relationship status, bankruptcy, or dissolution."
msgstr ""
"**Vzdržujte dostopnost podatkov:** Shranjujte vse evidentirane transakcije v "
"strukturirani in strojno berljivi obliki za zahtevano petletno obdobje, ne "
"glede na status odnosa s stranko, stečaj ali razpustitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Provide decryption capabilities:** Ensure that encrypted bookkeeping data "
"and receipts can be decrypted into a structured and readable format."
msgstr ""
"**Zagotovite zmožnosti dešifriranja:** Poskrbite, da je mogoče šifrirane "
"knjigovodske podatke in prejemke dešifrirati v strukturirano in berljivo "
"obliko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:37
msgid "Odoo Compliance"
msgstr "Skladnost Odooja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:39
msgid ""
"Odoo's registration as digital standard bookkeeping systems with the Danish "
"Business Authority confirms that Odoo meets the applicable criteria for "
"digital bookkeeping systems in Denmark, in accordance with the requirements "
"of the :abbr:`DBA (Danish Bookkeeping Act)`."
msgstr ""
"Registracija sistema Odoo kot digitalnega standardnega knjigovodskega "
"sistema pri danski gospodarski upravi potrjuje, da Odoo izpolnjuje ustrezna "
"merila za digitalne knjigovodske sisteme na Danskem v skladu z zahtevami "
":abbr:`DBA (danski zakon o knjigovodstvu)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:43
msgid ""
"However, to benefit from all the required guarantees for digital bookkeeping "
"systems in Denmark, customers must meet a few conditions."
msgstr ""
"Vendar morajo stranke za izkoriščanje vseh zahtevanih jamstev za digitalne "
"knjigovodske sisteme na Danskem izpolnjevati nekaj pogojev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:47
msgid "Conditions for full DBA compliance"
msgstr "Pogoji za popolno skladnost z DBA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:49
msgid ""
"The customer uses Odoo Accounting on the Odoo SaaS platform (Odoo Online);"
msgstr "Stranka uporablja Odoo Accounting na platformi Odoo SaaS (Odoo Online);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:50
msgid ""
"The customer has an active Odoo subscription (e.g., Standard or Custom "
"Plan), or their database is managed by an officially registered `Odoo "
"Accounting Firm <https://www.odoo.com/accounting-firms>`_;"
msgstr ""
"Stranka ima aktivno naročnino Odoo (npr. Standard ali Custom Plan) ali pa "
"njeno podatkovno bazo upravlja uradno registrirana `Odoo računovodska družba "
"<https://www.odoo.com/accounting-firms>`_;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:52
msgid ""
"The customer refrains from customizations or actions intended to undermine "
"the system’s immutability, traceability, or security controls."
msgstr ""
"Stranka se vzdržuje prilagoditev ali dejanj, namenjenih spodkopavanju "
"nespremenljivosti, sledljivosti ali varnostnih kontrol sistema."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:56
msgid ""
"Customers using Odoo products outside these conditions are responsible for "
"ensuring their own compliance with the DBA."
msgstr ""
"Stranke, ki uporabljajo izdelke Odoo zunaj teh pogojev, so same odgovorne za "
"zagotavljanje lastne skladnosti z DBA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:59
msgid ""
"When the above conditions are met, the requirements of the DBA are fulfilled "
"through features and processes described in the following sections."
msgstr ""
"Ko so zgornji pogoji izpolnjeni, so zahteve DBA izpolnjene s funkcijami in "
"postopki, opisanimi v naslednjih razdelkih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:63
msgid "Immutable transaction records"
msgstr "Nespremenljivi zapisi transakcij"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:65
msgid ""
"Once transactions are recorded, they cannot be deleted through the user "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Ko so transakcije zabeležene, jih ni mogoče izbrisati prek uporabniškega "
"vmesnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:66
msgid "All modifications are logged, providing a complete audit trail."
msgstr "Vse spremembe so zabeležene, kar zagotavlja popolno revizijsko sled."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:67
msgid ""
"While historically dated entries can be made, Odoo records the creation date "
"and time of the entry."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je mogoče vnesti zgodovinsko datirane vnose, Odoo zabeleži datum in "
"čas ustvarjanja vnosa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:70
msgid "Secure document storage"
msgstr "Varno shranjevanje dokumentov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:72
msgid ""
"Receipts and digital vouchers are stored as attachments and integrated into "
"the database, ensuring they are included in backups."
msgstr ""
"Potrdila in digitalni voucher so shranjeni kot priloge in integrirani v "
"podatkovno bazo, kar zagotavlja, da so vključeni v varnostne kopije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:74
msgid "Posted documents cannot be deleted."
msgstr "Objavljenih dokumentov ni mogoče izbrisati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:75
msgid ""
"We fully support the storage of mandatory digital vouchers as defined by "
"Danish regulations."
msgstr ""
"V celoti podpiramo shranjevanje obveznih digitalnih voucherjev, kot jih "
"določajo danske predpise."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:78
msgid "Continuous data availability"
msgstr "Neprekinjena razpoložljivost podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:80
msgid ""
"Clients with active subscriptions can access all transactions and digital "
"vouchers through Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Stranke z aktivnimi naročninami lahko dostopajo do vseh transakcij in "
"digitalnih voucherjev prek Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:81
msgid ""
"Regardless of customer relations, bankruptcy, or dissolution, Odoo can "
"provide access to transaction and digital voucher details to former clients "
"for six years (see :ref:`localizations/denmark/data-lifecycle`)."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na odnose s strankami, stečaj ali razpustitev lahko Odoo zagotovi "
"dostop do podrobnosti transakcij in digitalnih voucherjev nekdanjim strankam "
"za šest let (glej :ref:`localizations/denmark/data-lifecycle`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:85
msgid "Automated data export and secure storage"
msgstr "Samodejni izvoz podatkov in varno shranjevanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:87
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting implements no automatic deletion or archival of recorded "
"transactions, so if a customer has been recording transactions for six "
"years, the six years of history are preserved in the Odoo Accounting "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Accounting ne izvaja samodejnega brisanja ali arhiviranja zabeleženih "
"transakcij, tako da če je stranka beležila transakcije šest let, je šest let "
"zgodovine ohranjene v podatkovni bazi Odoo Accounting."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:89
msgid ""
"As described in the `Odoo Cloud Hosting SLA <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-"
"sla>`_ and `Odoo Privacy Policy <https://www.odoo.com/privacy>`_, the Odoo "
"Cloud relies on immutable daily snapshot backups, which cannot be "
"individually altered or deleted, even at the customer's request, ensuring "
"their integrity."
msgstr ""
"Kot je opisano v `Odoo Cloud Hosting SLA <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-sla>`_ "
"in `Odoo Privacy Policy <https://www.odoo.com/privacy>`_, Odoo Cloud temelji "
"na nespremenljivih dnevnih varnostnih kopijah posnetkov, ki jih ni mogoče "
"posamično spremeniti ali izbrisati, niti na zahtevo stranke, kar zagotavlja "
"njihovo celovitost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:92
msgid ""
"All documents and receipts stored in a database backup are available as a "
"standard ZIP archive accompanying the SQL dump."
msgstr ""
"Vsi dokumenti in potrdila, shranjeni v varnostni kopiji podatkovne baze, so "
"na voljo kot standardni arhiv ZIP, ki spremlja SQL dump."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:98
msgid "Data lifecycle management"
msgstr "Upravljanje življenjskega cikla podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:100
msgid ""
"Odoo database backups are available in standard SQL dump formats at all "
"times and include all recorded transactions."
msgstr ""
"Varnostne kopije podatkovnih baz Odoo so vedno na voljo v standardnih "
"formatih SQL dump in vključujejo vse zabeležene transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:102
msgid ""
"The `Odoo Cloud Hosting SLA <https://www.odoo.com/cloud-sla>`_ guarantees "
"three months of backup history to all active customers. As a special "
"guarantee for Danish customers subject to the DBA and meeting the conditions "
"highlighted above the last Odoo Cloud backup retention gets increased to six "
"years as soon as they decide to terminate their Odoo Cloud subscription, in "
"order to comply with the requirements of Annex 1, 4 of Executive Order 97."
msgstr ""
"SLA za gostovanje v oblaku Odoo `Odoo Cloud Hosting SLA <https://"
"www.odoo.com/cloud-sla>`_ zagotavlja vsem aktivnim strankam tri mesece "
"zgodovine varnostnih kopij. Kot posebno jamstvo za danske stranke, ki so "
"predmet DBA in izpolnjujejo zgoraj navedene pogoje, se hrambe zadnje "
"varnostne kopije Odoo Cloud poveča na šest let, takoj ko se odločijo "
"prekiniti naročnino na Odoo Cloud, da bi izpolnili zahteve Priloge 1, 4 "
"Izvršilne odredbe 97."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:108
msgid "Decryption"
msgstr "Dešifriranje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/denmark.rst:110
msgid ""
"Odoo Accounting customer data on the Odoo Cloud is always stored in "
"encrypted form (encryption at rest at storage level). When backups are "
"retrieved, they are automatically decrypted and provided in decrypted form "
"in standard formats for the user: SQL dumps + ZIP archive of all attached "
"documents (file store)."
msgstr ""
"Podatki strank Odoo Accounting v oblaku Odoo so vedno shranjeni v šifrirani "
"obliki (šifriranje v mirovanju na ravni shranjevanja). Ko so varnostne "
"kopije pridobljene, se samodejno dešifrirajo in uporabniku zagotovijo v "
"dešifrirani obliki v standardnih formatih: SQL dumpi + arhiv ZIP vseh "
"priloženih dokumentov (shranjevanje datotek)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:3
msgid "Ecuador"
msgstr "Ekvador"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:5
msgid ""
"With the Ecuadorian localization, electronic documents can be generated "
"using XML, fiscal folio, electronic signature, and direct connection to tax "
"authority SRI."
msgstr ""
"Z ekvadorsko lokalizacijo je mogoče generirati elektronske dokumente z "
"uporabo XML, fiskalnega folija, elektronskega podpisa in neposredne povezave "
"s davčnim organom SRI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:8
msgid ""
"The supported documents are invoices, credit notes, debit notes, purchase "
"liquidations, and withholdings."
msgstr ""
"Podprti dokumenti so računi, dobropisi, bremepisi, likvidacije nakupov in "
"odtegljaji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:11
msgid ""
"The localization also includes automation to easily predict the withholding "
"tax to be applied to each purchase invoice."
msgstr ""
"Lokalizacija vključuje tudi avtomatizacijo za enostavno napovedovanje "
"odtegnjenega davka, ki se uporabi za vsak dobaviteljev račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:15
msgid ""
"`App Tour - Localización de Ecuador <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=BQOXVSDeeK8>`_"
msgstr ""
"`App Tour - Localización de Ecuador <https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=BQOXVSDeeK8>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:16
msgid ""
"`Smart Tutorial - Localización de Ecuador <https://www.odoo.com/slides/smart-"
"tutorial-localizacion-de-ecuador-170>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Smart Tutorial - Localización de Ecuador <https://www.odoo.com/slides/smart-"
"tutorial-localizacion-de-ecuador-170>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:18
msgid ""
":doc:`Documentation on e-invoicing's legality and compliance in Ecuador <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/ecuador>`"
msgstr ""
