"Simplificado)`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`ATS`. Nato naložite preneseno "
"datoteko XML v *DIMM Formularios*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:423
msgid ""
"When downloading the :abbr:`ATS (Anexo Transaccional Simplificado)` report, "
"Odoo generates a warning pop-up alerting the user if a document(s) has "
"missing or incorrect data. Nevertheless, the XML file can still be "
"downloaded."
msgstr ""
"Pri prenosu poročila :abbr:`ATS (Anexo Transaccional Simplificado)` Odoo "
"ustvari opozorilno pojavno okno, ki uporabnika obvesti, če ima dokument ali "
"dokumenti manjkajoče ali nepravilne podatke. Kljub temu je datoteko XML še "
"vedno mogoče prenesti."

