msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kratka koda`: Vnesite edinstveno 5-mestno kodo za zaporedje "
"računovodskih vnosov (npr. `PT001`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:585
msgid "Create a purchase liquidation"
msgstr "Ustvarite likvidacijo nabave"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:587
msgid ""
"Purchase liquidations, created from *purchase orders* or manually from "
"*vendor bills*, must contain the following data:"
msgstr ""
"Likvidacije nabave, ustvarjene iz *naročilnic* ali ročno iz *dobaviteljskih "
"računov*, morajo vsebovati naslednje podatke:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:591
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: Select the :guilabel:`Purchase Liquidation` journal "
"with the correct printer point."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Dnevnik`: Izberite dnevnik :guilabel:`Likvidacija nabave` s "
"pravilno točko tiskalnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:593
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Document Type`: Enter this document type: `(03) Purchase "
"Liquidation`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta dokumenta`: Vnesite to vrsto dokumenta: `(03) Likvidacija "
"nabave`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:594
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Document number`: Enter the document number (sequence). This must "
"only be entered once, and the sequence will automatically be assigned to the "
"subsequent documents."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Številka dokumenta`: Vnesite številko dokumenta (zaporedje). To "
"je treba vnesti samo enkrat, zaporedje pa bo samodejno dodeljeno naslednjim "
"dokumentom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:596
msgid ":guilabel:`Payment Method (SRI)`: Select how to pay the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Način plačila (SRI)`: Izberite način plačila računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:597
msgid ":guilabel:`Products`: Specify the product with the correct taxes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Izdelki`: Navedite izdelek s pravilnimi davki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:599
msgid "Then, validate the :guilabel:`Purchase Liquidation`."
msgstr "Nato potrdite :guilabel:`Likvidacijo nabave`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:604
msgid "Purchase withholding"
msgstr "Zadržanje pri nabavi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:606
msgid ""
"*Purchase withholdings* are electronic documents sent to the SRI once "
"they're validated. They can only be registered from a validated (posted) "
"invoice."
msgstr ""
"*Zadržanja pri nabavi* so elektronski dokumenti, poslani SRI, ko so "
"potrjeni. Registrirajo se lahko samo iz potrjenega (knjižnega) računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:609
msgid ""
"On the invoice, click :guilabel:`Add Withhold` and complete the following "
"fields in the :guilabel:`Withhold` window:"
msgstr ""
"Na računu kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj zadržanje` in izpolnite naslednja polja "
"v oknu :guilabel:`Zadržanje`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:612
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Document number`: Enter the document number (sequence). This must "
"only be entered once, and the sequence will automatically be assigned for "
"the next documents."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Številka dokumenta`: Vnesite številko dokumenta (zaporedje). To "
"je treba vnesti samo enkrat, zaporedje pa bo za naslednje dokumente "
"dodeljeno samodejno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:614
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Withhold lines`: The taxes appear automatically according to the "
"configuration of products and vendors. Review if the taxes and tax support "
"are correct. If not, edit and select the correct taxes and tax support."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrstice zadržanja`: Davki se prikažejo samodejno glede na "
"konfiguracijo izdelkov in dobaviteljev. Preverite, ali so davki in davčna "
"podpora pravilni. Če niso, uredite in izberite pravilne davke in davčno "
"podporo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:618
msgid "Then, validate the :guilabel:`Withholding`."
msgstr "Nato potrdite :guilabel:`Zadržanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:621
msgid ""
"Tax support types must be configured on the :guilabel:`Vendor Bill`. To do "
"so, go to the tax applied on the :guilabel:`Vendor Bill` and change "
"the :guilabel:`Tax Support` there."
msgstr ""
"Vrste davčne podpore morajo biti konfigurirane v :guilabel:`Dobaviteljevem "
"računu`. To storite tako, da greste na davek, ki se uporablja v "
":guilabel:`Dobaviteljevem računu`, in tam spremenite :guilabel:`Davčno "
"podporo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:624
msgid ""
"A withholding tax can be divided into two or more lines, depending on "
"whether two or more withholding percentages apply."
msgstr ""
"Davek pri zadržanju je lahko razdeljen na dve ali več vrstic, odvisno od "
"tega, ali se uporabljajo dva ali več odstotkov zadržanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:628
msgid ""
"Odoo suggests a VAT withholding of 30% with tax support 01. VAT withholding "
"of 70% can be added to a new line with the same tax support. Odoo allows it "
"if the base total matches the :guilabel:`Vendor Bill`'s total."
msgstr ""
"Odoo predlaga DDV zadržanje 30 % z davčno podporo 01. DDV zadržanje 70 % je "
"mogoče dodati v novo vrstico z enako davčno podporo. Odoo to dovoli, če se "
"osnova ujema s skupnim zneskom :guilabel:`Dobaviteljevega računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:635
msgid "Expense reimbursement"
msgstr "Povračilo stroškov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:637
msgid "Expense reimbursements apply to the following cases:"
msgstr "Povračila stroškov se uporabljajo v naslednjih primerih:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:639
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Individual`: reimbursement to an employee for miscellaneous "
"expenses (e.g., purchase liquidations)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Posameznik`: povračilo zaposlenemu za različne stroške (npr. "
"likvidacije nakupov)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:641
