"the :guilabel:`Ecuadorian Delivery Guide` (`l10n_ec_edi_stock`) module."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da :doc:`namestite </applications/general/apps_modules>` "
"modul :guilabel:`Ekvadorski dobavni list` (`l10n_ec_edi_stock`)."

