":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. V razdelku "
":guilabel:`Uvoz računovodstva` kliknite :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Uvozi` in :guilabel:`Uvozi FEC`. Nato v oknu :guilabel:`Uvoz FEC` "
"naložite datoteko FEC in kliknite :guilabel:`Uvozi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:178
msgid ""
"Importing FEC files from different years requires no particular actions or "
"computations. However, if multiple files contain RAN :dfn:`Reports à "
"Nouveaux` with the starting balance for the year, these entries are "
"automatically marked as unnecessary in Odoo and may need to be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Uvažanje datotek FEC iz različnih let ne zahteva posebnih dejanj ali "
"izračunov. Če pa več datotek vsebuje RAN :dfn:`Reports à Nouveaux` z "
"začetnim stanjem za leto, so ti vnosi samodejno označeni kot nepotrebni v "
"Odoo in jih bo morda treba izbrisati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:185
msgid "File formats"
msgstr "Oblike datotek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:188
msgid "FEC files must be in CSV format, as XML format is not supported."
msgstr "Datoteke FEC morajo biti v formatu CSV, saj format XML ni podprt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:189
msgid ""
"The FEC CSV file is a plain text file structured as a data table. The first "
"line serves as the header, defining the list of fields for each entry, and "
"each following line represents a single accounting entry without any "
"specific order."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka FEC CSV je navadna besedilna datoteka, strukturirana kot podatkovna "
"tabela. Prva vrstica služi kot glava, ki določa seznam polj za vsak vnos, "
"vsaka naslednja vrstica pa predstavlja en sam računovodski vnos brez "
"posebnega vrstnega reda."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:193
msgid "FEC files must comply with the following technical specifications:"
msgstr ""
"Datoteke FEC morajo biti skladne z naslednjimi tehničnimi specifikacijami:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:195
msgid "**Encoding**: UTF-8, UTF-8-SIG and iso8859_15."
msgstr "**Kodiranje**: UTF-8, UTF-8-SIG in iso8859_15."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:196
msgid "**Separator**: any of these: `;` or `|` or `,` or `TAB`."
msgstr "**Ločilo**: katerikoli od teh: `;` ali `|` ali `,` ali `TAB`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:197
msgid ""
"**Line terminators**: both CR+LF (`\\\\r\\\\n`) and LF (`\\\\n`) character "
"groups are supported."
msgstr ""
"**Zaključki vrstic**: podprti sta obe skupini znakov CR+LF (`\\\\r\\\\n`) in "
"LF (`\\\\n`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:198
