#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:337
msgid ""
"The account type is then flagged as :guilabel:`payable` "
"and :guilabel:`reconcilable` based on the account template."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta konta je nato označena kot :guilabel:`plačljivo` in "
":guilabel:`uskladljivo` na podlagi predloge konta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:345
msgid ""
"Journals are checked against the existing ones in Odoo to avoid duplicates, "
"even when importing multiple FEC files."
msgstr ""
"Dnevniki se preverjajo glede na obstoječe v Odoo, da se preprečijo "
"podvojitve, tudi pri uvozu več datotek FEC."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:348
msgid ""
"If a journal with the same code already exists, the existing journal is used "
"instead of creating a new one."
msgstr ""
"Če dnevnik z isto kodo že obstaja, se uporabi obstoječi dnevnik namesto "
"ustvarjanja novega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:351
msgid ""
"New journals have the prefix :guilabel:`FEC-` added to their name. For "
"example, :guilabel:`ACHATS` becomes :guilabel:`FEC-ACHATS`."
msgstr ""
"Novi dnevniki imajo predpono :guilabel:`FEC-`, dodano imenu. Na primer, "
":guilabel:`ACHATS` postane :guilabel:`FEC-ACHATS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:355
msgid ""
"Journals are *not* archived, allowing the user to manage them as desired."
msgstr ""
"Dnevniki *niso* arhivirani, kar uporabniku omogoča, da jih upravlja po želji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:360
msgid "Journal type determination"
msgstr "Določanje vrste dnevnika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:362
msgid ""
"The journal type is not specified in the format (similar to the accounts) "
"and is initially created with the default type :guilabel:`general`."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta dnevnika ni določena v formatu (podobno kot konti) in je na začetku "
"ustvarjena s privzeto vrsto :guilabel:`splošno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:365
msgid ""
"At the end of the import process, the journal type is determined based on "
"the following rules regarding related moves and accounts:"
msgstr ""
"Ob koncu postopka uvoza se vrsta dnevnika določi na podlagi naslednjih "
"pravil glede povezanih premikov in kontov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`bank`: Moves in these journals always include a line (debit or "
"credit) impacting a liquidity account."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`banka`: Premiki v teh dnevnikih vedno vključujejo vrstico (breme "
"ali dobropis), ki vpliva na konto likvidnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`cash` / :guilabel:`bank` can be interchanged, so :guilabel:`bank` "
"is assigned when this condition is met."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`gotovina` / :guilabel:`banka` se lahko zamenjata, zato je "
":guilabel:`banka` dodeljena, ko je ta pogoj izpolnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`sale`: Moves in these journals mostly have debit lines on "
"receivable accounts and credit lines on tax income accounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`prodaja`: Prenosi v teh dnevnikih imajo večinoma bremenilne "
"vrstice na kontih terjatev in dobropiše na kontih prihodkov od davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid "Sale refund journal items are debit/credit inverted."
msgstr "Postavke dnevnika dobropisov prodaje so debet/kredit obrnjene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ""
":guilabel:`purchase`: Moves in these journals mostly have credit lines on "
"payable accounts and debit lines on expense accounts."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`nakup`: Prenosi v teh dnevnikih imajo večinoma kreditne vrstice "
"na kontih obveznosti in bremenilne vrstice na kontih odhodkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid "Purchase refund journal items are debit/credit inverted."
msgstr "Postavke dnevnika dobropisov nakupa so debet/kredit obrnjene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`general`: Used for everything else."
msgstr ":guilabel:`splošno`: Uporablja se za vse ostalo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:381
msgid "A minimum of three moves is required to identify the journal type."
msgstr "Za določitev vrste dnevnika so potrebni najmanj trije prenosi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:382
msgid ""
"A threshold of 70% of the moves must meet the criteria for a journal type to "
"be determined."
msgstr ""
"Prag 70 % prenosov mora izpolnjevati merila, da se določi vrsta dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:385
msgid ""
"Suppose we are analyzing the moves that share a "
"certain :guilabel:`journal_id`."
msgstr ""
"Predpostavimo, da analiziramo prenose, ki si delijo določen "
":guilabel:`journal_id`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:388
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:418
msgid "Moves"
msgstr "Premiki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:388
msgid "Count"
msgstr "Štetje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:388
msgid "Percentage"
msgstr "Odstotek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:390
msgid "that have a sale account line and no purchase account line"
msgstr "ki imajo vrstico prodajnega konta in nimajo vrstice nakupnega konta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:392
msgid "that have a purchase account line and no sale account line"
msgstr "ki imajo vrstico nakupnega konta in nimajo vrstice prodajnega konta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:392
msgid "25%"
msgstr "25%"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:394
msgid "that have a liquidity account line"
msgstr "ki imajo vrstico konta likvidnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:394
msgid "3"
msgstr "3"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:394
msgid "**75%**"
msgstr "**75 %**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:396
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:212
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:226
msgid "**Total**"
msgstr "**Skupaj**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:396
msgid "4"
msgstr "4"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:396
msgid "100%"
msgstr "100%"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:399
msgid ""
"The journal :guilabel:`type` would be :guilabel:`bank`, because the bank's "
"move percentage (75%) exceeds the threshold (70%)."
msgstr ""
"Dnevnik :guilabel:`vrsta` bi bil :guilabel:`banka`, ker odstotek prenosov "
"banke (75 %) presega prag (70 %)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:407
msgid ""
"Each contact keeps its :guilabel:`Reference` from the :guilabel:`CompAuxNum` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Vsak stik ohrani svojo :guilabel:`Referenco` iz polja :guilabel:`CompAuxNum`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:410
msgid ""
"These fields are searchable based on previous FEC imports for fiscal/audit "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
"Ta polja so iskalna na podlagi prejšnjih uvozov FEC za fiskalne/revizijske "
"namene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:413
msgid ""
"Similar and potential duplicate contacts can be merged using the Data "
"Cleaning App."
msgstr ""
"Podobne in potencialno podvojene stike je mogoče združiti z uporabo "
"aplikacije za čiščenje podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:420
msgid ""
"Entries are posted and reconciled immediately upon submission, with "
"the :guilabel:`EcritureLet` field used to match the entries."
msgstr ""
"Vnosi so objavljeni in usklajeni takoj po predložitvi, pri čemer se za "
"ujemanje vnosov uporablja polje :guilabel:`EcritureLet`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:423
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`EcritureNum` field represents the name of the moves, but it "
"may sometimes be left empty. In such cases, the :guilabel:`PieceRef` field "
"is used instead."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`EcritureNum` predstavlja ime premikov, vendar je lahko "
"včasih prazno. V takih primerih se namesto njega uporabi polje "
":guilabel:`PieceRef`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:429
msgid "Rounding issues"
msgstr "Težave z zaokroževanjem"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:431
msgid ""
"A rounding tolerance is applied based on currency precision for debit and "
"credit amounts (i.e., 0.01 for EUR). If the difference falls under this "
"tolerance, a new line is added to the move, called :guilabel:`Import "
"rounding difference`, targeting the following accounts:"
msgstr ""
"Glede na natančnost valute za zneske v breme in dobro se uporabi toleranca "
"zaokroževanja (npr. 0,01 za EUR). Če razlika pade pod to toleranco, se "
"premiknemu doda nova vrstica z imenom :guilabel:`Import rounding "
"difference`, ki cilja na naslednje račune:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:435
msgid "`658000` Charges diverses de gestion courante, for added debits"
msgstr "`658000` Charges diverses de gestion courante, za dodane obremenitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:436
msgid "`758000` Produits divers de gestion courante, for added credits"
msgstr "`758000` Produits divers de gestion courante, za dodane dobropise"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:441
msgid "Missing move name"
msgstr "Manjkajoče ime premika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:443
msgid ""
"If the the :guilabel:`EcritureNum` field is not filled out "
"and :guilabel:`PieceRef` field is not suited to determine the move name (it "
"may be used as an accounting move line reference), it becomes impossible to "
"identify which lines should be grouped into a single move, and effectively "
"preventing the creation of balanced moves."
msgstr ""
"Če polje :guilabel:`EcritureNum` ni izpolnjeno in polje :guilabel:`PieceRef` "
"ni primerno za določitev imena premika (lahko se uporablja kot referenca "
"vrstice knjižbe), postane nemogoče prepoznati, katere vrstice je treba "
"združiti v en sam premik, kar učinkovito preprečuje ustvarjanje "
"uravnoteženih premikov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:448
msgid ""
"In such cases, a final attempt is made to group all lines by the same "
"journal and date (:guilabel:`JournalLib`, :guilabel:`EcritureDate`). If this "
"grouping generates balanced moves (sum(credit) - sum(debit) = 0), then each "
"different combination of journal and date creates a new move."
msgstr ""
"V takih primerih se izvede končni poskus združitve vseh vrstic po istem "
"dnevniku in datumu (:guilabel:`JournalLib`, :guilabel:`EcritureDate`). Če to "
"združevanje ustvari uravnotežene premike (sum(credit) - sum(debit) = 0), "
"potem vsaka različna kombinacija dnevnika in datuma ustvari nov premik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:454
msgid ""
"`ACH` + `2021/05/01` --> new move on journal `ACH` with name `20210501`."
msgstr ""
"`ACH` + `2021/05/01` --> nov premik v dnevniku `ACH` z imenom `20210501`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:456
msgid ""
"If this attempt fails, an error message is displayed, listing all the move "
"lines that are considered unbalanced."
msgstr ""
"Če ta poskus ne uspe, se prikaže sporočilo o napaki, ki navaja vse vrstice "
"premikov, ki veljajo za neuravnotežene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:462
msgid "Contact information"
msgstr "Informacije o stiku"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:464
msgid ""
"If a line includes contact information, it is copied to the accounting move "
"itself, provided the targeted journal is of type :guilabel:`payable` "
"or :guilabel:`receivable`."
msgstr ""
"Če vrstica vključuje kontaktne podatke, se ti kopirajo v sam knjigovodski "
"premik, če je ciljni dnevnik tipa :guilabel:`payable` ali "
":guilabel:`receivable`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:470
msgid "FEC Export"
msgstr "Izvoz FEC"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:472
