"izberite :guilabel:`FEC`. V oknu :guilabel:`FEC File Generation` izpolnite "
"naslednja polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:476
msgid ":guilabel:`Start Date`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Start Date`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:477
msgid ":guilabel:`End Date`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`End Date`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:478
