":guilabel:`Test File`: Enable this option to test the FEC file generation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Test File`: omogočite to možnost za preizkus ustvarjanja datoteke "
"FEC."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:479
msgid ":guilabel:`Exclude lines at 0`: Enable this option if needed."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Exclude lines at 0`: omogočite to možnost, če je potrebno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:480
msgid ":guilabel:`Excluded Journals`: Select the journal(s) to exclude."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Excluded Journals`: izberite dnevnik(-e) za izključitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:482
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Generate`."
msgstr "Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari`."

