#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:493
msgid "Liasse fiscale"
msgstr "Liasse fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:495
msgid ""
"The *liasse fiscale* (tax declaration) is a collection of standardized "
"financial documents that businesses must submit annually to the tax "
"authorities. It comprehensively summarizes the company’s financial "
"activities and determines corporate taxes."
msgstr ""
"*Liasse fiscale* (davčna napoved) je zbirka standardiziranih finančnih "
"dokumentov, ki jih morajo podjetja letno predložiti davčnim organom. Vsebuje "
"celovit povzetek finančnih dejavnosti podjetja in določa davek od dohodkov "
"pravnih oseb."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:499
msgid ""
"`Teledec <https://www.teledec.fr>`_ is a platform used to prepare and submit "
"tax declaration using data from accounting records. To synchronize your "
"accounting data stored in Odoo with Teledec and electronically send your "
"company's *liasse fiscale* to the DGFiP (Direction Générale des Finances "
"Publiques), follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"<https://www.teledec.fr> je platforma, ki se uporablja za pripravo in oddajo "
"davčne napovedi z uporabo podatkov iz računovodskih evidenc. Če želite "
"sinhronizirati računovodske podatke, shranjene v Odoo, s Teledec in "
"elektronsko poslati *liasse fiscale* vašega podjetja na DGFiP (Direction "
"Générale des Finances Publiques), sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:504
msgid ":ref:`localization/france/teledec-account`"
msgstr ":ref:`localization/france/teledec-account`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:505
msgid ":ref:`localization/france/teledec-registration`"
msgstr ":ref:`localization/france/teledec-registration`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:506
msgid ":ref:`localization/france/teledec-synchronization`"
msgstr ":ref:`localization/france/teledec-synchronization`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:511
msgid "Teledec account creation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje Teledec računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:513
msgid ""
"To create a Teledec account, access the `Teledec account creation page "
"<https://www.teledec.fr/s-enregistrer>`_ and fill in the :guilabel:`Adresse "
"e-mail` field with an email address. Choose a secure password, accept the "
"general terms and conditions by checking the box, and "
"click :guilabel:`S'enregistrer` to save. Then, enter the :abbr:`SIREN "
"(Système d'identification du répertoire des entreprises, Business Directory "
"Identification System)` number of the company."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje Teledec računa obiščite `stran za ustvarjanje Teledec računa "
"<https://www.teledec.fr/s-enregistrer>`_ in v polje :guilabel:`Adresse e-"
"mail` vnesite e-poštni naslov. Izberite varno geslo, sprejmite splošne "
"pogoje s potrditvijo polja in kliknite :guilabel:`S'enregistrer` za "
"shranjevanje. Nato vnesite številko :abbr:`SIREN (Système d'identification "
"du répertoire des entreprises, sistem identifikacije poslovnega imenika)` "
"podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:520
msgid ""
"If the account has already been created, click :guilabel:`Déjà enregistré?` "
"(Already registered)."
msgstr ""
"Če je račun že ustvarjen, kliknite :guilabel:`Déjà enregistré?` (Že "
"registrirani)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:525
msgid "Company registration and fiscal year information"
msgstr "Registracija podjetja in informacije o poslovnem letu"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:527
msgid ""
"To register the company on Teledec, go to :guilabel:`Vos entreprises` (Your "
"companies) and click :guilabel:`Enregistrer votre entreprise` (Register your "
"company). Make sure to fill in the following company information in "
"the :guilabel:`Coordonnées de l'entreprise` (Company's details) "
"and :guilabel:`Représentant légal` (Legal representative) sections:"
msgstr ""
"Za registracijo podjetja v Teledec pojdite na :guilabel:`Vos entreprises` "
"(Vaša podjetja) in kliknite :guilabel:`Enregistrer votre entreprise` "
"(Registrirajte svoje podjetje). Poskrbite, da izpolnite naslednje podatke o "
"podjetju v razdelkih :guilabel:`Coordonnées de l'entreprise` (Podatki "
"podjetja) in :guilabel:`Représentant légal` (Zakoniti zastopnik):"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:532
msgid ":guilabel:`Nom de l'entreprise`: Company's name."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nom de l'entreprise`: Ime podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:533
msgid ":guilabel:`Forme juridique`: Select the company's legal form."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Forme juridique`: Izberite pravno obliko podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:534
msgid ":guilabel:`Les comptes sont clôturés le`: Closing date."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Les comptes sont clôturés le`: Datum zaključka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:535
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Régime d'imposition, choix de la liasse`: Select the tax scheme "
"or the tax declaration option."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Régime d'imposition, choix de la liasse`: Izberite davčno shemo "
"ali možnost davčne napovedi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:537
msgid ":guilabel:`Adresse du siège social`: Head office address."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Adresse du siège social`: Naslov glavne pisarne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:538
msgid ":guilabel:`Nom du représentant légal`: Legal representative's name."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Nom du représentant légal`: Ime zakonitega zastopnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:539
msgid ":guilabel:`Agissant en qualité de`: Legal representative's function."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Agissant en qualité de`: Funkcija zakonitega zastopnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:540
msgid ":guilabel:`Numéro de téléphone`: Phone number."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Numéro de téléphone`: Telefonska številka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:542
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Sauvegarder` (Save) to display the next "
"step :guilabel:`Informations générales sur l'exercice déclaré` (General "
"information about the declared fiscal year). Then, fill in information on "
"the financial year, such as the fiscal year start and end dates or the "
"closing date and duration of the previous fiscal period. After saving, the "
"list of documents included in the *liasse fiscale* is displayed, including "
"both standard tax forms and those customized for the company’s tax "
"declaration."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Sauvegarder` (Shrani) za prikaz naslednjega koraka "
":guilabel:`Informations générales sur l'exercice déclaré` (Splošne "
"informacije o priglašenem fiskalnem letu). Nato izpolnite informacije o "
"fiskalnem letu, kot so datum začetka in konca fiskalnega leta ali datum "
"zaključka in trajanje prejšnjega fiskalnega obdobja. Po shranjevanju se "
"prikaže seznam dokumentov, vključenih v *liasse fiscale*, vključno s "
"standardnimi davčnimi obrazci in tistimi, prilagojenimi za davčno napoved "
"podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:550
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Etat` (Status) column shows the progress of the document "
"filing."
msgstr "Stolpec :guilabel:`Etat` (Status) prikazuje napredek oddaje dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:551
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Compléter` to fill out a document, "
"then :guilabel:`Sauvegarder` to save."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Izpolni`, da izpolnite dokument, nato "
":guilabel:`Shrani`, da shranite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:552
msgid ""
