#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:38
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:33
msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "Slovar"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:40
msgid "The following terms are used throughout the Guatemalan localization:"
msgstr "V guatemalski lokalizaciji se uporabljajo naslednji izrazi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:42
msgid ""
"**SAT**: *Superintendencia de Administración Tributaria* is the government "
"entity responsible for enforcing tax payments in Guatemala."
msgstr ""
"**SAT**: *Superintendencia de Administración Tributaria* je vladna "
"institucija, odgovorna za uveljavljanje plačil davkov v Gvatemali."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:44
msgid ""
"**FEL**: *Factura Electrónica en Línea* is the electronic invoicing system "
"mandated by the SAT in Guatemala, which requires businesses to issue and "
"manage electronic documents in compliance with local regulations."
msgstr ""
"**FEL**: *Factura Electrónica en Línea* je sistem elektronskega "
"računovodstva, ki ga je predpisal SAT v Gvatemali in zahteva, da podjetja "
"izdajajo in upravljajo elektronske dokumente v skladu z lokalnimi predpisi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:47
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:39
msgid ""
"**EDI**: *Electronic Data Interchange* refers to the sending of electronic "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"**EDI**: *Electronic Data Interchange* se nanaša na pošiljanje elektronskih "
"dokumentov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:48
msgid ""
"**Infile**: is the third-party organization that facilitates the interchange "
"of electronic documents between companies and the Guatemalan government."
msgstr ""
"**Infile**: je organizacija tretje osebe, ki omogoča izmenjavo elektronskih "
"dokumentov med podjetji in gvatemalsko vlado."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:50
msgid ""
"**UUID**: *Universally Unique Identifier* is a unique alphanumeric code "
"assigned by the SAT to each certified electronic document in the FEL system, "
"used for traceability and official validation."
msgstr ""
"**UUID**: *Universally Unique Identifier* je edinstven alfanumerični kod, ki "
"ga SAT dodeli vsakemu certificiranemu elektronskemu dokumentu v sistemu FEL "
"in se uporablja za sledljivost in uradno potrjevanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:53
msgid ""
"**Phrases**: Type of Phrases with specific Scenario Codes are used in the "
"Guatemalan localization to comply with the requirements of the SAT. They "
"should be added depending on the issuer regime, receiver, and operation "
"type. These phrases are used in the XML and PDF documents."
msgstr ""
"**Fraze**: Vrste fraz s specifičnimi scenarij kodo se uporabljajo v "
"guatemalski lokalizaciji za izpolnjevanje zahtev SAT. Dodati jih je treba "
"glede na režim izdajatelja, prejemnika in vrsto operacije. Te fraze se "
"uporabljajo v dokumentih XML in PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:56
msgid ""
"**Establishment Code**: A unique identifier assigned by the SAT to each "
"business establishment, which is required for electronic invoicing."
msgstr ""
"**Koda ustanove**: Edinstven identifikator, ki ga SAT dodeli vsaki poslovni "
"enoti in je potreben za elektronsko računovodstvo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:58
msgid ""
"**Quetzal**: The official currency of Guatemala, represented by the symbol "
"GTQ. This is the base currency for all financial transactions in the "
"Guatemalan localization."
msgstr ""
"**Quetzal**: Uradna valuta Gvatemale, označena s simbolom GTQ. To je osnovna "
"valuta za vse finančne transakcije v guatemalski lokalizaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:67
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the following modules to get all the "
"features of the Guatemalan localization:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Namestite <general/install>` naslednje module, da dobite vse funkcije "
"guatemalske lokalizacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:77
msgid ":guilabel:`Guatemala - Accounting`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Gvatemala - Računovodstvo`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:78
msgid "`l10n_gt`"
msgstr "`l10n_gt`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:79
msgid ""
"The default :doc:`fiscal localization package <../fiscal_localizations>`. It "
"adds accounting characteristics for the Guatemalan localization, which "
"represent the minimum configuration required for a company to operate in "
"Guatemala according to the guidelines set by the |SAT|. The module's "
"installation automatically loads the chart of accounts and taxes."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti :doc:`paket fiskalnih lokalizacij <../fiscal_localizations>`. "
"Dodaja računovodske značilnosti za gvatemalsko lokalizacijo, ki "
"predstavljajo najmanjšo zahtevano konfiguracijo za poslovanje podjetja v "
"Gvatemali v skladu s smernicami |SAT|. Namestitev modula samodejno naloži "
"kontni načrt in davke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:83
msgid ":guilabel:`Guatemala Accounting EDI`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Gvatemala računovodstvo EDI`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:84
msgid "`l10n_gt_edi`"
msgstr "`l10n_gt_edi`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:85
msgid ""
"Includes all the technical and functional requirements to generate and "
"validate :doc:`Electronics Documents <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>`, based on the technical documentation published by "
"the |SAT|. The authorized documents are :ref:`listed above <guatemala/"
"intro>`."
msgstr ""
"Vključuje vse tehnične in funkcionalne zahteve za ustvarjanje in preverjanje "
":doc:`elektronskih dokumentov <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` na podlagi tehnične dokumentacije, ki jo je objavil "
"|SAT|. Odobreni dokumenti so :ref:`navedeni zgoraj <guatemala/intro>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:91
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically installs the base module **Guatemala - Accounting** when "
"a database is installed with `Guatemala` selected as the country. However, "
"to enable electronic invoicing, the **Guatemala Accounting EDI** "
"(`l10n_gt_edi`) module needs to be manually :ref:`installed <general/"
"install>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo samodejno namesti osnovni modul **Gvatemala - Računovodstvo**, ko je "
"podatkovna baza nameščena z izbrano državo `Gvatemala`. Vendar pa je za "
"omogočanje elektronskega računovodstva treba ročno :ref:`namestiti <general/"
"install>` modul **Gvatemala računovodstvo EDI** (`l10n_gt_edi`)."

