#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:220
msgid ""
":guilabel:`GT Document Type`: Select the type of document you want to "
"create, i.e., :guilabel:`FACT - Factura Electrónica` or :guilabel:`FCAM - "
"Factura Cambiara`. By default, the document type is set to :guilabel:`FACT`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`GT vrsta dokumenta`: Izberite vrsto dokumenta, ki ga želite "
"ustvariti, npr. :guilabel:`FACT - Factura Electrónica` ali :guilabel:`FCAM - "
"Factura Cambiara`. Privzeto je vrsta dokumenta nastavljena na "
":guilabel:`FACT`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:223
msgid ":guilabel:`Due date`: To compute if the invoice is due now or later."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum valute`: Za izračun, ali je račun zapadel zdaj ali kasneje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:224
msgid ":guilabel:`Journal`: Select the sales journal."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Dnevnik`: Izberite prodajni dnevnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:225
msgid ":guilabel:`Products`: Specify the product(s) with the correct taxes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Izdelki`: Navedite izdelek(e) s pravilnimi davki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:230
msgid ""
"If you need to add a specific phrase based on the transaction, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and add the corresponding phrase "
"in :guilabel:`GT Phrases`. These phrases are used in the XML and PDF "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"Če morate dodati določeno frazo na podlagi transakcije, pojdite na zavihek "
":guilabel:`Druge informacije` in dodajte ustrezno frazo v :guilabel:`GT "
"fraze`. Te fraze se uporabljajo v dokumentih XML in PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:235
msgid ""
"If you need to add an addendum to the invoice, you can do so in "
"the :guilabel:`Terms and Conditions` field. The addendum will be included in "
"the XML document and can be used to provide additional information or notes "
"related to the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Če morate računu dodati dodatek, lahko to storite v polju :guilabel:`Pogoji "
"in določila`. Dodatek bo vključen v dokument XML in ga lahko uporabite za "
"zagotovitev dodatnih informacij ali opomb, povezanih z računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:239
msgid ""
"After the invoice confirmation, click :guilabel:`Send`. In the wizard that "
"appears, make sure to enable the :guilabel:`Send to SAT` and :guilabel:`by "
"Email` checkboxes to send the XML to the |SAT| through Infile's web service "
"and the validated invoice to the client's email, and click :guilabel:`Send`. "
"Then, the following occurs:"
msgstr ""
"Po potrditvi računa kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`. V čarovniku, ki se prikaže, "
"poskrbite, da omogočite potrditveni polji :guilabel:`Pošlji SAT` in "
":guilabel:`po e-pošti`, da pošljete XML v |SAT| prek spletne storitve Infile "
"in potrjeni račun na e-poštni naslov stranke, nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Pošlji`. Nato se zgodi naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:245
msgid "The |UUID| is generated."
msgstr "|UUID| je ustvarjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:246
msgid "The XML is processed synchronously by Infile."
msgstr "XML se sinhronsko obdela v Infile."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:248
msgid ""
"If accepted, the file is displayed in the chatter, and the email to the "
"client with the corresponding :file:`pdf` and :file:`xml` file is sent."
msgstr ""
"Če je sprejeta, se datoteka prikaže v pogovornem oknu, e-pošta stranki s "
"pripadajočima datotekama :file:`pdf` in :file:`xml` pa se pošlje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:250
msgid ""
"If the file contains errors, a warning message displays the reason(s) and "
"the email is not sent."
msgstr ""
"Če datoteka vsebuje napake, se prikaže opozorilno sporočilo z razlogi in e-"
"pošta se ne pošlje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:255
msgid "The :guilabel:`SAT` tab then displays the following:"
msgstr "Zavihek :guilabel:`SAT` nato prikaže naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:257
msgid ":guilabel:`Datetime`: Timestamp recorded of the XML creation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Datum in čas`: Zabeležena časovna značka ustvarjanja XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:258
msgid ""
":guilabel:`GT Status`: Status result obtained in the |SAT| response. If the "
"file contains errors, a warning message displays the reason(s) and the email "
"is not sent."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status GT`: Rezultat statusa, pridobljen v odgovoru |SAT|. Če "
"datoteka vsebuje napake, se prikaže opozorilno sporočilo z razlogi in e-"
"pošta se ne pošlje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:260
msgid ""
":guilabel:`UUID`: The unique identifier assigned by the |SAT| to the "
"electronic document."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`UUID`: Edinstveni identifikator, ki ga |SAT| dodeli elektronskemu "
"dokumentu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:261
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Download Certificate`: To download the sent XML file, even if the "
"|SAT| result was rejected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prenesi certifikat`: Za prenos poslane datoteke XML, tudi če je "
"bil rezultat |SAT| zavrnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:None
msgid "EDI document record available in SAT tab."
msgstr "Zapis dokumenta EDI na voljo v zavihku SAT."

