#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:492
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically performs validation checks before submission to ensure "
"compliance with GST portal requirements that must be addressed before filing."
msgstr ""
"Odoo samodejno izvede preverjanja veljavnosti pred oddajo, da zagotovi "
"skladnost z zahtevami portala GST, ki jih je treba obravnavati pred oddajo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:496
msgid "The following types of validation issues can be raised:"
msgstr "Sprožene so lahko naslednje vrste težav pri preverjanju veljavnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:498
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Apply Appropriate Tax`: :guilabel:`IGST` is not applicable for "
"intra-state transactions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabi ustrezen davek`: :guilabel:`IGST` ni primeren za "
"transakcije znotraj države."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:500
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wrong CGST/SGST on Inter-State Transactions`: :guilabel:`CGST/"
"SGST` cannot be applied on inter-state transactions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Napačen CGST/SGST pri medkrajevnih transakcijah`: :guilabel:`CGST/"
"SGST` se ne sme uporabiti pri medkrajevnih transakcijah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:502
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiscal Year Reversed Move`: Credit Notes for invoices issued in a "
