msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invalid HSN Codes`: - For products (non-services), HSN codes must "
"not begin with `99`. - For services, HSN codes must begin with `99`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Neveljavne kode HSN`: - Za izdelke (ne storitve) kode HSN se ne "
"smejo začeti z `99`. - Za storitve se morajo kode HSN začeti z `99`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:507
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Missing HSN Codes`: Some product lines do not have HSN codes for "
"journal items."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Manjkajoče kode HSN`: nekatere vrstice izdelkov nimajo kod HSN za "
"postavke dnevnika."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:509
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invalid UQC Codes`: The Unit Quantity Code (UQC) must comply with "
"Indian GST standards."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Neveljavne kode UQC`: koda enote količine (UQC) se mora ujemati z "
"indijskimi standardi GST."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:511
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Missing Document Summary`: Document summary lines are mandatory "
"for GSTR-1. This check is always marked as :guilabel:`Anomaly` initially. "
"After reviewing the summary by clicking the relevant check, it changes "
"to :guilabel:`Reviewed`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Manjkajoči povzetek dokumenta`: vrstice povzetka dokumenta so "
"obvezne za GSTR-1. Ta preverjanje je na začetku vedno označeno kot "
":guilabel:`Anomalija`. Po pregledu povzetka s klikom na ustrezno preverjanje "
"se spremeni v :guilabel:`Pregledano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:514
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Missing E-Invoice`: Some invoices are not linked to an e-invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Manjkajoči e-račun`: nekateri računi niso povezani z e-računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:515
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unlinked Unregistered Credit Notes`: Credit Notes have been "
"issued without referencing an invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nepovezani dobropisi neregistriranih`: dobropisi so bili izdani "
"brez sklicevanja na račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:518
msgid "Validation checks have four stages:"
msgstr "Preverjanja veljavnosti imajo štiri stopnje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:520
msgid ":guilabel:`To Review`: Check requires review."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Za pregled`: preverjanje zahteva pregled."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:521
msgid ":guilabel:`Reviewed`: Check has been reviewed."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Pregledano`: preverjanje je bilo pregledano."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:522
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Supervised`: Check is supervised, and a supervisor is assigned."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pod nadzorom`: preverjanje je pod nadzorom in dodeljen je "
"nadzornik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:523
msgid ":guilabel:`Anomaly`: Check has failed."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Anomalija`: preverjanje ni uspelo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:525
msgid ""
"Click on any individual check to view and resolve the corresponding issue."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na katerokoli posamezno preverjanje za ogled in reševanje ustrezne "
"težave."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:528
msgid ""
"A tax return can only be validated when all checks are in "
"the :guilabel:`Reviewed` or :guilabel:`Supervised` stage."
msgstr ""
"Davčna napoved se lahko potrdi šele, ko so vsa preverjanja v stopnji "
":guilabel:`Pregledano` ali :guilabel:`Pod nadzorom`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:531
msgid ""
"After reviewing the checks, click :guilabel:`Validate`. "
"The :guilabel:`Review` stage appears in green then."
msgstr ""
"Po pregledu preverjanj kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`. Stopnja "
":guilabel:`Pregled` se nato prikaže zeleno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:534
msgid "Click :guilabel:`GSTR-1 (IN)` to review the report."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`GSTR-1 (IN)` za pregled poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:536
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Submit`, and click :guilabel:`Push Data` in "
"the :guilabel:`Submission Instructions` window to send the report to the GST "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Predloži` in v oknu :guilabel:`Navodila za predložitev` "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji podatke`, da pošljete poročilo na portal GST."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:539
msgid ""
"During this step, GST portal credentials must be verified. As the data is "
"being sent, the :guilabel:`Send` stage in the progress bar appears orange. "
"Once the GST portal confirms receipt, the stage turns green. If an error "
"occurs, the :guilabel:`Send` stage changes to red."
msgstr ""
"Med tem korakom je treba preveriti poverilnice portala GST. Med pošiljanjem "
"podatkov se stopnja :guilabel:`Pošlji` v vrstici napredka prikaže oranžno. "
"Ko portal GST potrdi prejem, se stopnja obarva zeleno. Če pride do napake, "
"se stopnja :guilabel:`Pošlji` spremeni v rdečo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:544
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon on the "
"relevant :guilabel:`GSTR-1` line to display additional options:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(tri pike)` v ustrezni "
"vrstici :guilabel:`GSTR-1`, da prikažete dodatne možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:547
msgid ":guilabel:`Generate XLSX`: Download the GSTR-1 report as an XLSX file."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Generiraj XLSX`: Prenesi poročilo GSTR-1 kot datoteko XLSX."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:548
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reset`: Clear the current state and revert the return to the "
"initial stage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ponastavi`: Počisti trenutno stanje in vrni napoved v začetno "
"stopnjo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:550
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Check Status` to retrieve the current status from the GST "
"portal. Once the confirmation is received, the :guilabel:`Review` stage in "
"the progress bar turns green. Then, click :guilabel:`Mark as Filed` to "
"finalize and submit the return as filed."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Preveri stanje`, da pridobite trenutno stanje iz portala "
"GST. Ko prejmete potrditev, se stopnja :guilabel:`Pregled` v vrstici "
"napredka obarva zeleno. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Označi kot vloženo`, da "
"dokončate in oddate napoved kot vloženo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:555
msgid ""
"Once a return is marked as **Filed**, it cannot be reset or filed again."
msgstr ""
"Ko je napoved označena kot **Vložena**, je ni več mogoče ponastaviti ali "
"ponovno vložiti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:560
msgid "Receive GSTR-2B tax reconciliation"
msgstr "Prejem davčne uskladitve GSTR-2B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:562
msgid ""
"Select the relevant :guilabel:`GSTR-2B` report for the desired period that "
"needs to be reconciled."
msgstr ""
"Izberite ustrezno poročilo :guilabel:`GSTR-2B` za želeno obdobje, ki ga je "
"treba uskladiti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:565
msgid ""
"In the validation checks view, click :guilabel:`Fetch E-Invoice` to retrieve "
"vendor e-invoice data for the reconciliation period. The check is initially "
"marked as :guilabel:`Anomaly` and changes to :guilabel:`Reviewed` after "
"fetching. Then, click :guilabel:`Validate` to confirm and mark "
"the :guilabel:`Review` stage as green."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu preverjanj veljavnosti kliknite :guilabel:`Pridobi E-račun`, da "
"pridobite podatke o e-računih dobaviteljev za obdobje uskladitve. "
"Preverjanje je sprva označeno kot :guilabel:`Nepravilnost` in se spremeni v "
":guilabel:`Pregledano` po pridobitvi. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da "
"potrdite in označite stopnjo :guilabel:`Pregled` kot zeleno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:571
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Fetch E-Invoice` check only turns green if the e-invoice data "
"is fetched **two days after the end of the last month's reconciliation "
"period**."
msgstr ""
"Preverjanje :guilabel:`Pridobi E-račun` postane zeleno šele, če so podatki e-"
"računa pridobljeni **dva dneva po koncu obdobja uskladitve prejšnjega "
"meseca**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:574
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Fetch GSTR-2B` to retrieve all invoices from the GST "
"portal. Once the data is fetched, the :guilabel:`Fetch` stage in the "
"progress bar turns green. To view the raw report data, "
"click :guilabel:`GSTR-2B (IN)`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Pridobi GSTR-2B`, da pridobite vse račune s portala GST. "
"Ko so podatki pridobljeni, se stopnja :guilabel:`Pridobi` v vrstici napredka "
"obarva zeleno. Za ogled surovih podatkov poročila kliknite :guilabel:`GSTR-"
"2B (IN)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:578
msgid ""
"The fetched invoices are automatically matched with the E-invoices. "
"Click :guilabel:`View Bills` to see detailed matching results."
msgstr ""
"Pridobljeni računi so samodejno usklajeni z e-računi. Kliknite "
":guilabel:`Prikaži račune`, da si ogledate podrobne rezultate ujemanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:582
msgid "The :guilabel:`Match` stage indicates the reconciliation status:"
msgstr "Stopnja :guilabel:`Ujemanje` označuje stanje uskladitve:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:584
msgid "Orange: Partially matched (some bills require correction)."
msgstr "Oranžno: Delno ujemanje (nekateri računi zahtevajo popravke)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:585
msgid "Green: Fully matched (all bills reconciled)."
msgstr "Zeleno: Popolno ujemanje (vsi računi usklajeni)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:587
msgid ""
"In case of mismatches, correct the affected bills, then click the :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon to access additional options:"
msgstr ""
"V primeru neujemanja popravite prizadete račune, nato kliknite ikono "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(tri pike)`, da dostopate do dodatnih "
"možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:590
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Re-Match`: Re-run the matching process after making corrections."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ponovno ujemanje`: Znova zaženite postopek ujemanja po "
"opravljenih popravkih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:591
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reset`: Reset the reconciliation to the :guilabel:`Match` stage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ponastavi`: Ponastavite uskladitev na stopnjo "
":guilabel:`Ujemanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:593
msgid ""
"After all bills are fully matched, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis)` icon and select :guilabel:`Mark as Complete`. "
"The :guilabel:`Complete` stage in the progress bar turns green, finalizing "
"the bill reconciliation."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi računi popolnoma usklajeni, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
":guilabel:`(tri pike)` in izberite :guilabel:`Označi kot dokončano`. Stopnja "
":guilabel:`Dokončano` v vrstici napredka se obarva zeleno, s čimer je "
"uskladitev računov dokončana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:601
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/malaysia.rst:111
msgid "Tax reports"
msgstr "Davčna poročila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:606
msgid "GSTR-1 report"
msgstr "Poročilo GSTR-1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:608
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`GSTR-1` report is divided into sections. It displays "
"the :guilabel:`Base` amount, :abbr:`CGST (Central Goods and Services "
"Tax)`, :abbr:`SGST (State Goods and Service Tax)`, :abbr:`IGST (Integrated "
"Goods and Services Tax)`, and :guilabel:`CESS` for each section."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`GSTR-1` je razdeljeno na razdelke. Prikazuje "
":guilabel:`osnovni` znesek, :abbr:`CGST (centralni davek na blago in "
"storitve)`, :abbr:`SGST (državni davek na blago in storitve)`, :abbr:`IGST "
"(integrirani davek na blago in storitve)` in :guilabel:`CESS` za vsak "
"razdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-1 Report"
msgstr "Poročilo GSTR-1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:618
msgid "GSTR-2B report"
msgstr "Poročilo GSTR-2B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:620
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`GSTR-2` report is divided into sections. It displays "
"the :guilabel:`Base` amount, :abbr:`CGST (Central Goods and Services "
"Tax)`, :abbr:`SGST (State Goods and Service Tax)`, :abbr:`IGST (Integrated "
"Goods and Services Tax)`, and :guilabel:`CESS` for each section."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :guilabel:`GSTR-2` je razdeljeno na razdelke. Prikazuje znesek "
":guilabel:`Osnova`, :abbr:`CGST (Central Goods and Services Tax)`, "
":abbr:`SGST (State Goods and Service Tax)`, :abbr:`IGST (Integrated Goods "
"and Services Tax)` in :guilabel:`CESS` za vsak razdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-2B Report"
msgstr "Poročilo GSTR-2B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:630
msgid "GSTR-3B report"
msgstr "Poročilo GSTR-3B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:632
msgid "The :guilabel:`GSTR-3B` report contains different sections:"
msgstr "Poročilo :guilabel:`GSTR-3B` vsebuje različne razdelke:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:634
msgid "Details of inward and outward supply subject to a **reverse charge**;"
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti o dobavah navznoter in navzven, ki so predmet **povratnega "
"bremena**;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:635
msgid "Eligible :abbr:`ITC (Income Tax Credit)`;"
msgstr "Upravičen :abbr:`ITC (davčni kredit)`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:636
msgid "Values of **exempt**, **Nil-rated**, and **non-GST** inward supply;"
msgstr "Vrednosti **oproščenih**, **ničnih** in **ne-GST** dobav navznoter;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:637
msgid "Details of inter-state supplies made to **unregistered** persons."
msgstr "Podrobnosti o dobavah med zveznimi državami **neregistriranim** osebam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "GSTR-3B Report"
msgstr "Poročilo GSTR-3B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:643
msgid "Profit and Loss (IN) report"
msgstr "Izkaz poslovnega izida (IN)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:645
msgid ""
"This is a :guilabel:`Profit and Loss` report that displays the balances for "
"**Opening Stock** and **Closing Stock**. It helps users using Continental "
"accounting to accurately determine the cost of goods (i.e :guilabel:`Opening "
"Stock` + purchases during the period - :guilabel:`Closing Stock`)."
msgstr ""
"To je poročilo :guilabel:`Izkaz poslovnega izida`, ki prikazuje stanja za "
"**začetno zalogo** in **končno zalogo**. Pomaga uporabnikom, ki uporabljajo "
"kontinentalno računovodstvo, da natančno določijo stroške blaga (tj. "
":guilabel:`Začetna zaloga` + nabave v obdobju - :guilabel:`Končna zaloga`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "Profit and Loss report"
msgstr "Poročilo izkaza poslovnega izida"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:655
msgid "TDS/TCS threshold alert"
msgstr "Opozorilo o pragu TDS/TCS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:657
msgid ""
":abbr:`TDS (tax deducted at source)` and :abbr:`TCS (tax collected at "
"source)` are tax provisions under Indian law, triggered when transaction "
"amounts exceed specified thresholds. This alert notifies users when the "
"value of invoices or bills surpasses these limits, prompting the application "
"of the appropriate TDS/TCS."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`TDS (davek odbit pri izvoru)` in :abbr:`TCS (davek pobran pri izvoru)"
"` sta davčni določbi po indijski zakonodaji, ki se sprožita, ko zneski "
"transakcij presežejo določene pragove. To opozorilo obvesti uporabnike, ko "
"vrednost računov ali predračunov preseže te omejitve, kar sproži uporabo "
"ustreznega TDS/TCS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:662
msgid ""
"To configure Odoo to advise you on when to apply TDS/TCS, set "
"the :guilabel:`TDS/TCS section` field on the corresponding account in the "
"chart of accounts. Odoo will display a banner suggesting the TDS/TCS section "
"under which tax might be applicable when recording an invoice or bill."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti Odoo, da vas obvesti, kdaj uporabiti TDS/TCS, nastavite "
"polje :guilabel:`razdelek TDS/TCS` na ustreznem kontu v kontnem načrtu. Odoo "
"bo prikazal pasico, ki predlaga razdelek TDS/TCS, pod katerim je morda "
"primeren davek pri evidentiranju računa ali predračuna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:669
msgid "Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:670
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Indian Integration` section, enable the :guilabel:`TDS` "
"or :guilabel:`TCS` feature as required."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Indijska integracija` po potrebi omogočite funkcijo "
":guilabel:`TDS` ali :guilabel:`TCS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:672
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Chart of "
"Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Kontni načrt`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:673
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`View` on the desired account, and set the :guilabel:`TDS/"
"TCS Section` field."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ogled` na želenem kontu in nastavite polje "
":guilabel:`Oddelek TDS/TCS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:676
msgid ""
"The TDS/TCS sections are pre-configured with threshold limits. If you need "
"to modify these limits, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Taxes`. In the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, click on the  :icon:`fa-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`(internal link)` icon of the :guilabel:`Section` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Oddelki TDS/TCS so prednastavljeni s pragovnimi mejami. Če želite spremeniti "
"te meje, pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Davki`. V zavihku :guilabel:`Napredne možnosti` kliknite na ikono :icon:`fa-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`(notranja povezava)` polja :guilabel:`Oddelek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:0
msgid "TDS/TCS section modify"
msgstr "Spreminjanje oddelka TDS/TCS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:685
msgid "Applying TCS/TDS on invoices and bills"
msgstr "Uporaba TCS/TDS na računih in predračunih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:687
msgid ""
"Based on the account used on the customer invoice or vendor bill, Odoo "
"checks the TCS/TDS threshold limit. If the limit specified in "
"the :guilabel:`TCS/TDS Section` of the account is exceeded, Odoo displays an "
"alert that suggests applying the appropriate TCS/TDS. The alert will "
"disappear once the TCS/TDS is applied."
msgstr ""
"Na podlagi konta, uporabljenega na računu za stranko ali dobavitelja, Odoo "
"preveri mejno vrednost TCS/TDS. Če je presežena meja, določena v "
":guilabel:`Oddelku TCS/TDS` konta, Odoo prikaže opozorilo, ki predlaga "
"uporabo ustreznega TCS/TDS. Opozorilo bo izginilo, ko bo TCS/TDS uporabljen."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "TCS advice"
msgstr "Nasvet TCS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:695
msgid ""
"**TCS** is directly applicable in the tax on the invoice lines. To apply "
"**TDS**, click the :guilabel:`TDS Entry` smart button on the vendor bill/"
"payment. The popup window allows specifying the TDS details. Confirm the "
"entry to apply the TDS."
msgstr ""
"**TCS** se uporablja neposredno v davku na vrsticah računa. Za uporabo "
"**TDS** kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Vnos TDS` na dobaviteljevem računu/"
"plačilu. Pojavno okno omogoča določitev podrobnosti TDS. Potrdite vnos za "
"uporabo TDS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:None
msgid "TDS application"
msgstr "Uporaba TDS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:702
msgid ""
"In Odoo, the aggregate total is calculated for partners sharing the same PAN "
"number, across all company branches."
msgstr ""
"V Odooju se skupna vrednost izračuna za partnerje, ki si delijo isto "
"številko PAN, po vseh podružnicah podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:710
