#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:499
msgid "TD19 - buying goods from VAT deposit"
msgstr "TD19 - nakup blaga iz DDV skladišča"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:501
msgid ""
"Buying **goods** from a **foreign** vendor, but the **goods** are already in "
"**Italy** in a **VAT deposit**."
msgstr ""
"Nakup **blaga** od **tujega** dobavitelja, vendar je **blago** že v "
"**Italiji** v **DDV skladišču**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:504
msgid ""
"From the EU: the *buyer* integrates the invoice received with the **VAT "
