msgstr ""
"Iz EU: *kupec* dopolni prejeti račun z **DDV informacijami**, ki so "
"dolgovane v Italiji (tj. **integracija davka na računu dobavitelja**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:506
msgid ""
"Non-EU: the *buyer* sends an invoice to *themselves* (i.e., **self-"
"billing**)."
msgstr "Izven EU: *kupec* sam sebi izstavi račun (tj. **samoobračunavanje**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:508
