#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:65
msgid ""
"standard sales tax (16%): applied to most goods and services within Jordan."
msgstr ""
"standardni prometni davek (16 %): uporablja se za večino blaga in storitev v "
"Jordaniji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:66
msgid ""
"exempt transactions: for sales and services not subject to VAT, such as "
"financial services or healthcare."
msgstr ""
"oproščene transakcije: za prodajo in storitve, ki niso predmet DDV, kot so "
"finančne storitve ali zdravstvene storitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:68
msgid ""
"export tax (0%): zero-rated tax applied to goods and services exported "
"outside Jordan."
msgstr ""
"izvozni davek (0 %): davek z ničelno stopnjo, ki se uporablja za blago in "
"storitve, izvožene iz Jordanije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:75
msgid ""
"The :doc:`VAT summary <../accounting/reporting/tax_returns>` provides a "
"detailed breakdown of taxable, zero-rated, and exempt transactions. Like "
"other :doc:`financial reports <../accounting/reporting>`, the VAT summary "
"can be filtered by period, compared against other periods, and exported in "
"Excel and PDF formats, ensuring compliance with Jordanian tax laws."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Povzetek DDV <../accounting/reporting/tax_returns>` zagotavlja "
"podroben pregled obdavčljivih transakcij, transakcij z ničelno stopnjo in "
"oproščenih transakcij. Tako kot druga :doc:`finančna poročila <../accounting/"
"reporting>` je mogoče povzetek DDV filtrirati po obdobju, primerjati z "
"drugimi obdobji ter izvoziti v formatih Excel in PDF, kar zagotavlja "
"skladnost z jordansko davčno zakonodajo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:83
msgid "E-invoicing with JoFotara"
msgstr "E-izdajanje računov z JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:85
msgid ""
"E-invoicing with JoFotara is integrated with Odoo, ensuring compliance with "
"Jordanian government's technical and legal requirements for electronic "
"invoicing. The JoFotara integration in Odoo directly connects with the "
"Jordanian e-invoicing platform, allowing companies to:"
msgstr ""
"E-izdajanje računov z JoFotara je integrirano z Odoo in zagotavlja skladnost "
"s tehničnimi in pravnimi zahtevami jordanske vlade za elektronsko izdajanje "
"računov. Integracija JoFotara v Odoo se neposredno poveže s jordansko "
"platformo za e-izdajanje računov, kar podjetjem omogoča:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:89
msgid "generate compliant electronic invoices"
msgstr "ustvarjanje skladnih elektronskih računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:90
msgid "submit invoices in real time for validation"
msgstr "pošiljanje računov v realnem času za validacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:91
msgid "track invoice statuses directly within Odoo"
msgstr "spremljanje stanja računov neposredno v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:93
msgid ""
"The integration requires first creating an account with JoFotara, then "
"generating API credentials, and finally entering those credentials in your "
"Odoo database to link the two."
msgstr ""
"Integracija zahteva najprej ustvarjanje računa z JoFotara, nato ustvarjanje "
"API poverilnic in nazadnje vnos teh poverilnic v vašo podatkovno bazo Odoo "
"za povezavo med obema."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:98
msgid ""
"`Government manuals <manuals_>`_ provide instructions for creating an "
"account and generating the API credentials."
msgstr ""
"Priročniki za upravo `government manuals <manuals_>`_ vsebujejo navodila za "
"ustvarjanje računa in generiranje poverilnic API."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:109
msgid "Link Odoo to JoFotara"
msgstr "Povežite Odoo z JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:111
msgid ""
"If you don't already have an account, create one by going to the `government "
"manuals <manuals_>`_ page and following the steps in the **Procedure Manual "
"for Joining the Jordanian National Electronic Invoicing System**."
msgstr ""
"Če še nimate računa, ga ustvarite tako, da obiščete stran `government "
"manuals <manuals_>`_ in sledite korakom v **Procedure Manual for Joining the "
"Jordanian National Electronic Invoicing System**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:114
msgid ""
"Generate API credentials (Activity Number, Secret Key, and Client ID) by "
"going to the `government manuals <manuals_>`_ page and following the steps "
"in **Procedure Manual for Linking to the Jordanian National Electronic "
"Invoicing System**."
msgstr ""
"Generirajte poverilnice API (Activity Number, Secret Key in Client ID) tako, "
"da obiščete stran `government manuals <manuals_>`_ in sledite korakom v "
"**Procedure Manual for Linking to the Jordanian National Electronic "
"Invoicing System**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:117
msgid ""
"In your Odoo database, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing (Jordan)` section, enter "
