"dodajte polji :guilabel:`Stanje JoFotara` in :guilabel:`Napaka JoFotara`, da "
"v seznamskem pogledu vidite stanje pošiljanja oziroma morebitne napake."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:200
msgid ""
"There is an inherent difference in how values are approximated in Odoo and "
"ISTD due to the differing system architectures. JOD values in Odoo are "
"stored and approximated to three decimals, whereas ISTD expects values to "
"have nine decimals. As a result, an insignificant difference is inevitable "
"and arises between the values stores in Odoo and the values reported to "
"ISTD, which can have an error margin of <0.001."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja inherentna razlika v tem, kako so vrednosti približane v Odoo in "
"ISTD zaradi različnih sistemskih arhitektur. Vrednosti JOD v Odoo so "
"shranjene in približane na tri decimalna mesta, medtem ko ISTD pričakuje "
"vrednosti z devetimi decimalnimi mesti. Posledično je nepomembna razlika "
"neizogibna in nastane med vrednostmi, shranjenimi v Odoo, in vrednostmi, "
"poročanimi v ISTD, kar ima lahko mejo napake <0,001."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:209
msgid "JoFotara State"
msgstr "Stanje JoFotara"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/jordan.rst:211
