msgid "Purchases"
msgstr "Nabava"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:265
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically fetches new vendor bills from eTIMS every day. You need "
"to confirm the fetched vendor bills and send the confirmation to the KRA. To "
"confirm a vendor bill, it must be linked to one or several confirmed "
"purchase order line(s)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo samodejno pridobi nove dobaviteljeve račune iz eTIMS vsak dan. "
"Pridobljene dobaviteljeve račune morate potrditi in poslati potrditev na "
"KRA. Za potrditev dobaviteljevega računa mora biti povezan z eno ali več "
"potrjenimi vrsticami nabavnega naloga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:271
msgid ""
"In the case of purchases (not customs imports), the steps to link purchase "
"order lines with bills are the following:"
msgstr ""
"V primeru nakupov (ne carinskega uvoza) so koraki za povezavo vrstic "
"nabavnega naloga z računi naslednji:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:274
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Bills`. The vendor bill is "
"fetched from the KRA servers. The JSON file is available in the chatter of "
"the vendor bill if needed."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Računi`. "
"Dobaviteljev račun je pridobljen s strežnikov KRA. Datoteka JSON je na voljo "
"v pogovorih dobaviteljevega računa, če je potrebno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:277
msgid "Odoo looks at the :guilabel:`Tax ID` (PIN) of the vendor (partner);"
msgstr ""
"Odoo pregleda :guilabel:`Davčno številko` (PIN) dobavitelja (partnerja);"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:279
msgid "If it is unknown, a new contact (partner) is created."
msgstr "Če je neznan, se ustvari nov kontakt (partner)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:280
msgid ""
"If it is known and the branch ID is the same, Odoo uses the known contact."
msgstr "Če je znan in je ID podružnice enak, Odoo uporabi znani kontakt."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:282
msgid ""
"In the fetched bill from the KRA, select the :guilabel:`Product`. Each "
"vendor bill *must* contain a product to be confirmed and sent to eTIMS later "
"on."
msgstr ""
"V pridobljenem računu iz KRA izberite :guilabel:`Izdelek`. Vsak dobaviteljev "
"račun *mora* vsebovati izdelek, da se lahko pozneje potrdi in pošlje v eTIMS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:284
msgid ""
"Odoo checks existing purchase order lines matching the product(s) entered at "
"the previous step and the partner (if any). Click the :guilabel:`Purchase "
"Order Line` field, and select the correct related purchase order line(s) "
"matching the product(s). The quantities on the bill *must* be the same as "
"the received quantities indicated on the purchase order."
msgstr ""
"Odoo preveri obstoječe vrstice nabavnega naloga, ki se ujemajo z izdelkom(i)"
", vnesenimi v prejšnjem koraku, in partnerjem (če obstaja). Kliknite polje "
":guilabel:`Vrstica nabavnega naloga` in izberite pravilno povezano vrstico"
"(e) nabavnega naloga, ki se ujema(jo) z izdelkom(i). Količine na računu "
"*morajo* biti enake prejetim količinam, navedenim na nabavnem nalogu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:289
msgid ""
"If no existing purchase order line matches the lines of the fetched bill, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Purchase Order` and create a purchase order based on "
"the unmatched line(s). :guilabel:`Validate` the resulting stock move "
"and :guilabel:`Confirm` the bill."
msgstr ""
"Če se nobena obstoječa vrstica nabavnega naloga ne ujema z vrsticami "
"pridobljenega računa, kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari nabavni nalog` in "
"ustvarite nabavni nalog na podlagi neujemajočih se vrstic. "
":guilabel:`Potrdite` nastali premik zalog in :guilabel:`Potrdite` račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:293
msgid "Set a method in the :guilabel:`eTIMS Payment Method` field."
msgstr "Nastavite način v polju :guilabel:`Način plačila eTIMS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:294
msgid ""
"Once all steps are completed, click :guilabel:`Send to eTIMS` to send the "
"vendor bill. When the vendor bill has been confirmed on eTIMS, the **KRA "
"invoice number** can be found in the :guilabel:`eTIMS Details` tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi koraki zaključeni, kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji v eTIMS`, da "
"pošljete dobaviteljev račun. Ko je dobaviteljev račun potrjen v eTIMS, lahko "
"**številko računa KRA** najdete v zavihku :guilabel:`Podrobnosti eTIMS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:None
msgid "Bill registration steps."
msgstr "Koraki registracije računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:302
msgid "Invoicing"
msgstr "Obračun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:305
msgid "The KRA does *not* accept sales if the product is not in stock."
msgstr "KRA *ne* sprejema prodaj, če izdelek ni na zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:307
msgid "This is the **advised sales flow** in Odoo when selling:"
msgstr "To je **priporočen prodajni potek** v Odoo pri prodaji:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:309
msgid "Create a **sales order**."
msgstr "Ustvarite **prodajni nalog**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:310
msgid ":guilabel:`Validate` the delivery."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Potrdite` dobavo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:311
msgid ":guilabel:`Confirm` the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Potrdite` račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:312
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send`, and then enable :guilabel:`Send to eTIMS`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji` in nato omogočite :guilabel:`Pošlji v eTIMS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:313
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send` to send the invoice."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`, da pošljete račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:315
msgid ""
"Once the invoice has been sent and signed by the KRA, the following "
"information can be found on it:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun poslan in podpisan s strani KRA, so na njem navedene naslednje "
"informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:318
msgid "**KRA invoice number**"
msgstr "**Številka računa KRA**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:319
msgid ""
"Mandatory KRA invoice fields, such as **SCU information**, **date**, **SCU "
"ID**, **receipt number**, **item count**, **internal date**, and **receipt "
"signature**."
msgstr ""
"Obvezna polja računa KRA, kot so **podatki SCU**, **datum**, **ID SCU**, "
"**številka potrdila**, **število postavk**, **interni datum** in **podpis "
"potrdila**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:321
msgid "The **KRA tax table**"
msgstr "**Davčna tabela KRA**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:322
msgid "A unique **KRA QR code** for the signed invoice."
msgstr "Edinstvena **KRA QR koda** za podpisan račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:325
msgid "Imports"
msgstr "Uvozi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:327
msgid ""
"Customs import codes are **automatically** fetched from the KRA eTIMS API "
"servers every day. To fetch them manually, proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Carinske uvozne kode se **samodejno** pridobijo iz strežnikov KRA eTIMS API "
"vsak dan. Če jih želite pridobiti ročno, sledite naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:331
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Automation: Scheduled "
"Actions` and search for :guilabel:`KE eTIMS: Receive Customs Imports from "
"the OSCU`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Tehnično --> Avtomatizacija: "
"Načrtovana dejanja` in poiščite :guilabel:`KE eTIMS: Receive Customs Imports "
"from the OSCU`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:335
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Customs Imports` to view "
"the imported codes."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Carinski "
"uvozi`, da si ogledate uvožene kode."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:337
msgid ""
"The following steps are required to send and have **customs imports** signed "
"by the KRA:"
msgstr ""
"Za pošiljanje in podpis **carinskih uvozov** s strani KRA so potrebni "
"naslednji koraki:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:339
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Customs Imports`; The "
"customs import is fetched automatically from the KRA."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Carinski "
"uvozi`; Carinski uvoz se samodejno pridobi iz KRA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:341
msgid ""
"Match the imported item with an existing registered product in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` field (or create a product if no related product "
"exists)."
msgstr ""
"Povežite uvoženi artikel z obstoječim registriranim izdelkom v polju "
":guilabel:`Izdelek` (ali ustvarite izdelek, če povezan izdelek ne obstaja)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:343
msgid "Set a vendor in the :guilabel:`Partner` field."
msgstr "Nastavite dobavitelja v polju :guilabel:`Partner`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:344
msgid ""
"Based on the partner, match the imported item with its related purchase "
"order (see :ref:`purchase steps <kenya/purchases>`). The stock must be "
"correctly adjusted when the customs import is approved."
msgstr ""
"Na podlagi partnerja povežite uvoženi artikel z njegovim povezanim naročilom "
"(glej :ref:`korake za nakup <kenya/purchases>`). Zaloga mora biti pravilno "
"prilagojena, ko je carinski uvoz odobren."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:348
msgid ""
"If no related purchase order exists, create one and :guilabel:`Confirm` it. "
"Then, confirm the delivery by clicking :guilabel:`Receive Products`, "
"then :guilabel:`Validate` on the purchase order."
msgstr ""
"Če povezano naročilo ne obstaja, ustvarite novo in ga :guilabel:`potrdite`. "
"Nato potrdite dostavo s klikom na :guilabel:`Prejmi izdelke`, nato "
":guilabel:`Potrdi` na naročilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:352
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Match and Approve` or :guilabel:`Match and Reject`, "
"depending on the situation of the goods."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Poveži in odobri` ali :guilabel:`Poveži in zavrni`, "
"odvisno od stanja blaga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:356
msgid ""
"The JSON file received from the KRA is attached to the chatter of the "
"customs import."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka JSON, prejeta iz KRA, je priložena klepetalnici carinskega uvoza."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:359
msgid "BOM"
msgstr "BOM"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:361
msgid ""
"The KRA requires all BOMs to be sent to them. To send BOMs to eTIMS, the "
"product and its components *must* be :ref:`registered <kenya/product-"
"registration>`. To access a product's BOM, click on the product and then "
"click the :guilabel:`Bill of Materials` smart button."
msgstr ""
"KRA zahteva, da se jim pošljejo vsi BOM-i. Za pošiljanje BOM-ov v eTIMS "
"morajo biti izdelek in njegove komponente *obvezno* :ref:`registrirani "
"<kenya/product-registration>`. Za dostop do BOM-a izdelka kliknite na "
"izdelek in nato kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Kosovnica`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:365
msgid ""
"Make sure the :ref:`KRA's required fields <kenya/product-registration>` are "
"filled in the :guilabel:`KRA eTIMS details` section of "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab in the product form, and "
"click :guilabel:`Send to eTIMS`. The successful sending of the BOM is "
"confirmed in the chatter, where you can also find the sent information in an "
"attached JSON file."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so :ref:`zahtevana polja KRA <kenya/product-registration>"
"` izpolnjena v razdelku :guilabel:`KRA eTIMS podrobnosti` zavihka "
":guilabel:`Računovodstvo` v obrazcu izdelka in kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji v "
"eTIMS`. Uspešno pošiljanje BOM-a je potrjeno v klepetalnici, kjer najdete "
"tudi poslane informacije v priloženi datoteki JSON."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/kenya.rst:373
msgid ""
"The KRA does not accept credit notes with quantities or prices higher than "
"the initial invoice. When creating a credit note, a KRA reason must be "
"indicated: In the credit note form, go to the :guilabel:`eTIMS Details` tab, "
"select the :guilabel:`eTIMS Credit Note Reason`, and then select the invoice "
"number in the :guilabel:`Reversal of` field."
msgstr ""
"KRA ne sprejema dobropisov s količinami ali cenami, višjimi od začetnega "
"računa. Pri ustvarjanju dobropisa morate navesti razlog KRA: V obrazcu "
"dobropisa pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`eTIMS podrobnosti`, izberite "
":guilabel:`eTIMS razlog za dobropis` in nato izberite številko računa v "
"polju :guilabel:`Storno`."

