#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:129
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:605
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Zahteve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:131
msgid ""
"It is necessary to meet the following requirements before configuring the "
"Mexican localization modules in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Pred konfiguracijo modulov mehiške lokalizacije v Odoo je treba izpolniti "
"naslednje zahteve:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:134
msgid "Be registered in the |SAT| with a valid |RFC|."
msgstr "Biti registriran v |SAT| z veljavnim |RFC|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:135
msgid ""
"Have a `Certificado de Sello Digital / Digital Seal Certificate <https://"
"www.gob.mx/sat/acciones-y-programas/ certificado-de-sello-digital>`_ (CSD)."
msgstr ""
"Imeti `Certificado de Sello Digital / digitalni pečatni certifikat <https://"
"www.gob.mx/sat/acciones-y-programas/ certificado-de-sello-digital>`_ (CSD)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:137
msgid ""
"Choose a |PAC|. Currently, Odoo works with the following |PAC|\\s: `Solución "
"Factible <https://solucionfactible.com/contenido/productos/timbrado/"
"general#dos>`_, `Quadrum <https://cfdiquadrum.com.mx/odoo/>`_, and `SW "
"Sapien - Smarter Web <https://info.sw.com.mx/sw-smarter-odoo>`_."
msgstr ""
"Izberite |PAC|. Trenutno Odoo deluje z naslednjimi |PAC|: `Solución Factible "
"<https://solucionfactible.com/contenido/productos/timbrado/general#dos>`_, "
"`Quadrum <https://cfdiquadrum.com.mx/odoo/>`_ in `SW Sapien - Smarter Web "
"<https://info.sw.com.mx/sw-smarter-odoo>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:147
msgid ""
"After installing the correct modules, the next step is to verify that the "
"company is configured with the correct data. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies`, and select "
"the company to configure."
msgstr ""
"Po namestitvi pravilnih modulov je naslednji korak preveriti, ali je "
"podjetje konfigurirano s pravilnimi podatki. To storite tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Uporabniki in podjetja --> Podjetja` in "
"izberete podjetje za konfiguracijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:151
msgid ""
"Enter the full :guilabel:`Address` in the resulting form, "
"including: :guilabel:`ZIP` code, :guilabel:`State`, :guilabel:`Country`, and "
"|RFC| (:guilabel:`Tax ID` number)."
msgstr ""
"V prikazani obrazec vnesite celoten :guilabel:`Naslov`, vključno z: "
":guilabel:`poštno številko`, :guilabel:`Stanje`, :guilabel:`Državo` in |RFC| "
"(:guilabel:`davčno številko`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:154
msgid ""
"According to the requirements of the |CFDI| 4.0, the name of the main "
"company contact **must** match the business name registered in the |SAT|, "
"without the legal entity abbreviation. This is the same for "
"the :guilabel:`ZIP` code."
msgstr ""
"Skladno z zahtevami |CFDI| 4.0 se **mora** ime glavnega kontakta podjetja "
"ujemati s poslovnim imenom, registriranim pri |SAT|, brez okrajšave pravne "
"oblike. Enako velja za :guilabel:`poštno številko`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:159
msgid ""
"From a legal point of view, Mexican companies **must** use the local "
"currency (MXN). To use another currency, let MXN be the default currency and "
"use a :doc:`pricelist <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing>` "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"Z zakonskega vidika **morajo** mehiška podjetja uporabljati lokalno valuto "
"(MXN). Za uporabo druge valute naj bo MXN privzeta valuta in namesto tega "
"uporabite :doc:`cenik <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:163
msgid ""
"Next, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Settings`, and scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`MX Electronic invoicing` section. Under :guilabel:`Service "
"Tax Administration (SAT)`, select the :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime` that applies "
"to the company from the drop-down list, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Nato pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve` in se "
"pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`MX Elektronsko izdajanje računov`. Pod "
":guilabel:`Davčna uprava (SAT)` izberite :guilabel:`Davčni režim`, ki se "
"uporablja za podjetje, s spustnega seznama in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:168
msgid ""
"In order to test the Mexican localization, configure the company with a real "
"address within Mexico (including all fields). Add `EKU9003173C9` as "
"the :guilabel:`Tax ID` and `ESCUELA KEMPER URGATE` as the :guilabel:`Company "
"Name`. For the :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime`, use :guilabel:`General de Ley "
"Personas Morales`."
msgstr ""
"Za preskušanje mehiške lokalizacije konfigurirajte podjetje z dejanskim "
"naslovom v Mehiki (vključno z vsemi polji). Dodajte `EKU9003173C9` kot "
":guilabel:`Davčno številko` in `ESCUELA KEMPER URGATE` kot :guilabel:`Ime "
"podjetja`. Za :guilabel:`Davčni režim` uporabite :guilabel:`General de Ley "
"Personas Morales`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:176
msgid ""
"When using branches, all the invoicing information will be taken from the "
"main company except for the zip. Unless the |RFC| is set on the branch, then "
"the information will be taken directly from the branch."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi podružnic bodo vsi podatki za izdajo računov vzeti iz glavnega "
"podjetja, razen poštne številke. Razen če je |RFC| nastavljen na podružnici, "
"potem bodo podatki vzeti neposredno iz podružnice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:180
msgid ""
"Branches enable users to establish multiple brands within the same parent "
"company. Additionally, when different fiscal regimes are required for "
"invoicing purposes, it is necessary to create a branch for each regime. By "
"default, the regime is inherited from the parent company. However, if the "
"regime is explicitly set on the branch, Odoo will adopt the regime "
"applicable to that branch."
msgstr ""
"Podružnice uporabnikom omogočajo vzpostavitev več blagovnih znamk znotraj "
"istega matičnega podjetja. Poleg tega, ko so za namene izdaje računov "
"potrebni različni davčni režimi, je treba ustvariti podružnico za vsak "
"režim. Privzeto je režim podedovan od matičnega podjetja. Vendar če je režim "
"izrecno nastavljen na podružnici, bo Odoo prevzel režim, ki se uporablja za "
"to podružnico."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:191
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the **Contacts** application to access "
"contact records."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Namestite <general/install>` aplikacijo **Stiki** za dostop do zapisov "
"stikov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:193
msgid ""
"To create a contact that can be invoiced, go to "
"the :menuselection:`Contacts` app and click :guilabel:`New`. Then, enter the "
"contact name, full :guilabel:`Address` including the :guilabel:`ZIP` "
"code, :guilabel:`State`, :guilabel:`Country`, and |RFC| (:guilabel:`Tax ID`)."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje stika, ki mu lahko izdate račun, pojdite v aplikacijo "
":menuselection:`Stiki` in kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Nato vnesite ime stika, "
"celoten :guilabel:`Naslov`, vključno s :guilabel:`poštno številko`, "
":guilabel:`Stanje`, :guilabel:`Državo` in |RFC| (:guilabel:`davčno številko`)"
"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:198
msgid ""
"As with the company itself, all contacts must have their correct business "
"name registered in the |SAT|. The :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime` must also be "
"added in the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot pri samem podjetju morajo imeti vsi stiki pravilno poslovno ime, "
"registrirano pri |SAT|. :guilabel:`Davčni režim` mora biti prav tako dodan v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Prodaja in nakup`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:202
msgid ""
"Having a |RFC| (:guilabel:`Tax ID`) set but no :guilabel:`Country` "
"configured may result in incorrect invoices."
msgstr ""
"Nastavljen |RFC| (:guilabel:`Davčna številka`) brez konfigurirane "
":guilabel:`Države` lahko povzroči nepravilne račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:210
msgid ""
"In order to properly sign invoices, set the :ref:`Factor Type <l10n/mx/"
"factor-type>` and :ref:`Tax Object <l10n/mx/tax-object>` fields on sales "
"taxes."
msgstr ""
"Za pravilno podpisovanje računov nastavite polja :ref:`Vrsta faktorja <l10n/"
"mx/factor-type>` in :ref:`Davčni objekt <l10n/mx/tax-object>` pri prodajnih "
"davkih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:214
msgid ""
"RESICO ISR withholdings and some |IEPS| taxes are created automatically, but "
"the feature is not active by default. To enable it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"RESICO ISR odtegljaji in nekateri |IEPS| davki so ustvarjeni samodejno, "
"vendar funkcija privzeto ni aktivna. Za omogočanje pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Davki`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:220
msgid "Factor type"
msgstr "Vrsta faktorja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:222
msgid ""
"Both the **Factor Type** and **SAT Tax Type** fields are pre-loaded in the "
"default taxes."
msgstr ""
"Polji **Vrsta faktorja** in **Vrsta davka SAT** sta vnaprej naloženi v "
"privzetih davkih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:224
msgid ""
"For new taxes, set these fields in :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes` and click :guilabel:`New`. Set the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Type` to :guilabel:`Sales`. In the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, "
"fill :guilabel:`SAT Tax Type` and :guilabel:`Factor Type` fields."
msgstr ""
"Za nove davke nastavite ta polja v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Davki` in kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. Nastavite "
":guilabel:`Vrsto davka` na :guilabel:`Prodaja`. V zavihku "
":guilabel:`Napredne možnosti` izpolnite polji :guilabel:`Vrsta davka SAT` in "
":guilabel:`Vrsta faktorja`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:228
msgid ""
"Odoo supports four groups of :guilabel:`SAT Tax "
"Types`: :guilabel:`IVA`, :guilabel:`ISR`, :guilabel:`IEPS`, "
"and :guilabel:`Local Taxes`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo podpira štiri skupine :guilabel:`Vrst davka SAT`: :guilabel:`IVA`, "
":guilabel:`ISR`, :guilabel:`IEPS` in :guilabel:`Lokalni davki`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:231
msgid ""
"If the factor type is :guilabel:`Quota`, standard calculation methods cannot "
"be used. Instead, set the tax calculation computation to :guilabel:`Custom "
"Formula`."
msgstr ""
"Če je vrsta faktorja :guilabel:`Kvota`, standardnih metod izračuna ni mogoče "
"uporabiti. Namesto tega nastavite izračun davka na :guilabel:`Formula po "
"meri`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:235
msgid ""
"result = quantity * 6.455\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"result = količina * 6,455\n"
"\n"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:238
msgid "*quantity* = the number of items in the transaction"
msgstr "*količina* = število artiklov v transakciji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:239
msgid "*6.455* = the quota value (a fixed amount per unit)"
msgstr "*6,455* = vrednost kvote (fiksni znesek na enoto)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:240
msgid "Only per-unit quotas are supported, not quotas based on other factors"
msgstr ""
"Podprte so samo kvote na enoto, ne pa kvote, ki temeljijo na drugih "
"dejavnikih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:243
msgid ""
"Mexico manages two different kinds of 0% VAT to accommodate two scenarios:"
msgstr "Mehika upravlja dve različni vrsti 0% DDV za dva scenarija:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:245
msgid "For *0% VAT*, set the :guilabel:`Factor Type` to :guilabel:`Tasa`"
msgstr "Za *0% DDV* nastavite :guilabel:`Vrsta faktorja` na :guilabel:`Tasa`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:246
msgid "For *VAT Exempt*, set the :guilabel:`Factor Type` to :guilabel:`Exento`"
msgstr ""
"Za *DDV oproščeno* nastavite :guilabel:`Vrsta faktorja` na :guilabel:`Exento`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:249
msgid ""
"Local taxes are generated in a separate node in the XML file, these do not "
"get validated by the |PAC|."
msgstr ""
"Lokalne dajatve se ustvarijo v ločenem vozlišču v datoteki XML in jih |PAC| "
"ne preveri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:253
msgid ""
"Quotas and custom formulas require the :guilabel:`Define Taxes as Python "
"Code` module. See :doc:`Taxes <../accounting/taxes>`."
msgstr ""
"Kvote in formule po meri zahtevajo modul :guilabel:`Določi davke kot Python "
"kodo`. Glejte :doc:`Davki <../accounting/taxes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:259
msgid "Tax object"
msgstr "Davčni objekt"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:261
msgid ""
"One requirement of the CFDI 4.0 is that the resulting XML file handles the "
"breakdown of taxes of the operation in accordance with the regulation. There "
"are eight different possible values that are added in the XML file:"
msgstr ""
"Ena od zahtev CFDI 4.0 je, da rezultirajoča datoteka XML obravnava "
"razčlenitev davkov operacije v skladu s predpisi. Obstaja osem različnih "
"možnih vrednosti, ki se dodajo v datoteko XML:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:265
msgid ""
"`01`: No tax Object: This value is added automatically if the invoice line "
"doesn't contain any taxes."
msgstr ""
"`01`: Brez davčnega objekta: Ta vrednost se doda samodejno, če vrstica "
"računa ne vsebuje nobenih davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:267
msgid ""
"`02`: Tax Object: This is the default configuration of any invoice line that "
"contains taxes."
msgstr ""
"`02`: Davčni objekt: To je privzeta konfiguracija vsake vrstice računa, ki "
"vsebuje davke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:268
msgid ""
"`03`: Tax Object and doesn't require breakdown: This can only be added "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"`03`: Davčni objekt in ne zahteva razčlenitve: To je mogoče dodati samo "
"ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:269
msgid "`04`: Tax Object and doesn't have tax: This can only be added manually."
msgstr "`04`: Davčni objekt in nima davka: To je mogoče dodati samo ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:270
msgid "`05`: Tax Object, VAT for PODEBI: This can only be added manually."
msgstr "`05`: Davčni objekt, DDV za PODEBI: To je mogoče dodati samo ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:271
msgid ""
"`06`: VAT Object, No VAT forwarded: This object will be selected when there "
"is an ISR withholding and no VAT tax."
msgstr ""
"`06`: Objekt DDV, DDV se ne posreduje: Ta objekt bo izbran, če obstaja "
"zadržanje ISR in ni davka DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:273
msgid ""
"`07`: No VAT forwarded, |IEPS| breakdown: This object will be selected when "
"there is an ISR withholding, |IEPS| tax and no VAT tax."
msgstr ""
"`07`: DDV se ne posreduje, razčlenitev |IEPS|: Ta objekt bo izbran, če "
"obstaja zadržanje ISR, davek |IEPS| in ni davka DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:275
msgid ""
"`08`: No VAT forwarded, |IEPS| breakdown: This object can only be added "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"`08`: DDV se ne posreduje, razčlenitev |IEPS|: Ta objekt je mogoče dodati "
"samo ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:278
msgid ""
"Using either 01, 03, 04, or 05 will remove the tax node from the XML file."
msgstr "Uporaba 01, 03, 04 ali 05 bo odstranila vozlišče davka iz datoteke XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:281
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`IEPS breakdown` status affects the behavior of the tax "
"objects due to the missing |IEPS| when the breakdown does not happen."
msgstr ""
"Stanje :guilabel:`razčlenitve IEPS` vpliva na obnašanje davčnih objektov "
"zaradi manjkajočega |IEPS|, ko do razčlenitve ne pride."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:287
msgid "Local taxes"
msgstr "Lokalni davki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:289
msgid ""
"Local taxes (e.g., *ISH*, *Cedullar*) require a separate XML node and may "
"not follow standard tax logic."
msgstr ""
"Lokalni davki (npr. *ISH*, *Cedullar*) zahtevajo ločeno vozlišče XML in "
"morda ne sledijo standardni davčni logiki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:292
msgid ""
"When configuring a local tax, its name appears in the local tax complement. "
"The rate is treated as a withholding if negative, or carried forward if "
"positive."
msgstr ""
"Pri konfiguraciji lokalnega davka se njegovo ime pojavi v dopolnilu za "
"lokalne davke. Stopnja se obravnava kot odtegljaj, če je negativna, ali se "
"prenese naprej, če je pozitivna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:298
msgid "IEPS breakdown"
msgstr "Razčlenitev IEPS"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:300
msgid ""
"By default Odoo hides the |IEPS| in the invoices so that the subtotal on "
"which the VAT is calculated includes the amount of |IEPS|, this is to ensure "
"that Fiscal Regimes that do not require it, do not receive it."
msgstr ""
"Odoo privzeto skrije |IEPS| na računih, tako da delna vsota, na katero se "
"izračuna DDV, vključuje znesek |IEPS|. To je za zagotovitev, da davčni "
"režimi, ki tega ne zahtevajo, tega ne prejmejo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:304
msgid ""
"It is possible to make the |IEPS| visible in the XML by selecting "
"the :guilabel:`IEPS Breakdown` checkbox inside each contact on "
"the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab."
msgstr ""
"|IEPS| je mogoče narediti vidnega v XML-ju z izbiro potrditvenega polja "
":guilabel:`Razčlenitev IEPS` v vsakem stiku na zavihku :guilabel:`Prodaja in "
"nabava`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:308
msgid ""
"When using either :ref:`eCommerce invoicing <l10n/mx/ecommerce>` or "
"the :ref:`Self invoicing portal <l10n/mx/pos/portal>`, the customer will "
"have the option to decide whether or not to have the |IEPS| breakdown."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi :ref:`fakturiranja e-trgovine <l10n/mx/ecommerce>` ali "
":ref:`portala za samofakturiranje <l10n/mx/pos/portal>` bo imel stranka "
"možnost odločiti, ali želi razčlenitev |IEPS| ali ne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:315
msgid "Other tax configurations"
msgstr "Druge nastavitve davkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:317
msgid ""
"The Mexican Localization uses :doc:`cash basis taxes <../../finance/"
"accounting/taxes/cash_basis>`. When registering a payment, Odoo carries out "
"the movement of taxes from the *Cash Basis Transition Account* to the "
"account set in the :guilabel:`Definition` tab of the tax record set on the "
"invoice or bill line. For such movement, a tax base account is used: "
"(:guilabel:`899.01.99 Base Imponible de Impuestos en Base a Flujo de "
"Efectivo`) in the journal entry when reclassifying taxes. **Do not delete "
"this account**."
msgstr ""
"Mehiška lokalizacija uporablja :doc:`davke na podlagi denarnega toka <../../"
"finance/accounting/taxes/cash_basis>`. Pri registraciji plačila Odoo izvede "
"prenos davkov iz *prehodnega računa na podlagi denarnega toka* na račun, "
"določen v zavihku :guilabel:`Definicija` davčnega zapisa, določenega v "
"vrstici računa ali dobaviteljevega računa. Za tak prenos se uporablja davčni "
"osnovni račun: (:guilabel:`899.01.99 Base Imponible de Impuestos en Base a "
"Flujo de Efectivo`) v knjiženju pri prerazvrščanju davkov. **Ne izbrišite "
"tega računa**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:327
msgid "Withholdings"
msgstr "Odtegljaji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:329
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo includes withholdings with special distributions to "
"allocate VAT."
msgstr ""
"Odoo privzeto vključuje odtegljaje s posebnimi porazdelitvami za dodelitev "
"DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:331
msgid ""
"When registering an invoice, add the withholding and its corresponding VAT. "
"Both must be included on the vendor bill to ensure correct accounting. "
"Using :doc:`fiscal positions <../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions>` is "
"recommended so the cash-basis entry properly splits the distribution."
msgstr ""
"Pri registraciji računa dodajte odtegljaj in ustrezen DDV. Oba morata biti "
"vključena na dobaviteljev račun, da se zagotovi pravilno knjigovodstvo. "
"Priporočljiva je uporaba :doc:`davčnih pozicij <../accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`, da vnos na podlagi denarnega toka pravilno razdeli "
"porazdelitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:337
msgid ""
"For a lease vendor bill of `10000 MXN`, the `10.67%` lease withholding "
"corresponds to a `16% VAT 2/3 H`. Both taxes must be applied together to "
"reflect the correct accounting."
msgstr ""
"Za dobaviteljev račun za najem v višini `10000 MXN` odtegljaj za najem "
"`10,67%` ustreza `16% DDV 2/3 H`. Oba davka morata biti uporabljena skupaj, "
"da se odraža pravilno knjigovodstvo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Cash Basis entry with VAT split between paid and due."
msgstr ""
"Vnos na podlagi denarnega toka z DDV, razdeljenim med plačano in neplačano."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:344
msgid ""
"Withholdings |CFDI| is not currently supported. Consult with an accountant "
"the proper distribution."
msgstr ""
"Odtegljaji |CFDI| trenutno niso podprti. Glede ustrezne porazdelitve se "
"posvetujte s računovodjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:350
msgid ""
"To configure products, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> "
"Products`.  Open an existing product or click :guilabel:`New`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, set the :guilabel:`UNSPSC Product Category`. "
"Products and categories can be set manually, or through :doc:`a bulk import "
"<../../essentials/export_import_data>`."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo izdelkov pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Stranke --> Izdelki`. Odprite obstoječi izdelek ali kliknite "
":guilabel:`Novo`. V zavihku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` nastavite "
":guilabel:`Kategorijo izdelka UNSPSC`. Izdelke in kategorije je mogoče "
"nastaviti ročno ali prek :doc:`množičnega uvoza <../../essentials/"
"export_import_data>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:356
msgid ""
"All products need to have a |SAT| code associated with them in order to "
"prevent validation errors."
msgstr ""
"Vsi izdelki morajo imeti povezano kodo |SAT|, da se preprečijo napake pri "
"validaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:367
msgid "PAC credentials"
msgstr "Poverilnice PAC"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:369
msgid ""
"After processing your `Private Key (CSD) <https://www.sat.gob.mx/aplicacion/"
"16660/genera-y-descarga-tus-archivos-a-traves-de-la-aplicacion- certifica>`_ "
"with the |SAT|, you **must** register directly with the :ref:`PAC <l10n/mx/"
"requirements>` of your choice before you start creating invoices from Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Po obdelavi vašega `zasebnega ključa (CSD) <https://www.sat.gob.mx/"
"aplicacion/16660/genera-y-descarga-tus-archivos-a-traves-de-la-aplicacion- "
"certifica>`_ pri |SAT| se **morate** registrirati neposredno pri :ref:`PAC "
"<l10n/mx/requirements>` po vaši izbiri, preden začnete ustvarjati račune iz "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:374
msgid ""
"Once you've created your account with any of these providers, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and navigate "
"to the :guilabel:`MX Electronic invoicing` section. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Authorized Certification Provider (PAC)` section, enter the "
"name of your |PAC| with your credentials (:guilabel:`PAC username` "
"and :guilabel:`PAC password`)."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite svoj račun pri katerem koli od teh ponudnikov, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in se "
"pomaknite do odseka :guilabel:`Mehiško elektronsko fakturiranje`. V odseku "
":guilabel:`Pooblaščeni ponudnik certificiranja (PAC)` vnesite ime vašega "
"|PAC| s svojimi poverilnicami (:guilabel:`Uporabniško ime PAC` in "
":guilabel:`Geslo PAC`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Configuring PAC credentials from the Accounting settings."
msgstr "Konfiguracija poverilnic PAC v nastavitvah računovodstva."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:383
msgid ""
"To test the electronic invoicing without credentials, activate "
"the :guilabel:`MX PAC test environment` checkbox, and "
"select :guilabel:`Solucion Factible` as the :guilabel:`PAC`. It is not "
"required to add a username or password for a test environment."
msgstr ""
"Za testiranje elektronskega izdajanja računov brez poverilnic aktivirajte "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Testno okolje MX PAC` in izberite "
":guilabel:`Solucion Factible` kot :guilabel:`PAC`. Za testno okolje ni "
"potrebno dodati uporabniškega imena ali gesla."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:390
msgid ".cer and .key certificates"
msgstr "Certifikati .cer in .key"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:392
msgid ""
"The `digital certificates of the company <https://www.gob.mx/tramites/ficha/"
"certificado-de-sello-digital/SAT139>`_ must be uploaded within "
"the :guilabel:`Certificates` section. To do so, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --> Certificates and Keys`."
msgstr ""
"`Digitalni certifikati podjetja <https://www.gob.mx/tramites/ficha/"
"certificado-de-sello-digital/SAT139>`_ morajo biti naloženi v razdelek "
":guilabel:`Certifikati`. Za to pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> "
"Splošne nastavitve --> Certifikati in ključi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:397
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Manage your certificates`, click the :icon:`fa-right-"
"arrow` :guilabel:`Keys` link to access the :guilabel:`Keys` list view. "
"Click :guilabel:`Create`, upload the digital :guilabel:`Key file` "
"(:file:`.key` file), add a :guilabel:`Name` to the key, and enter "
"the :guilabel:`Private key password`."
msgstr ""
"Pod :guilabel:`Upravljajte svoje certifikate` kliknite povezavo :icon:`fa-"
"right-arrow` :guilabel:`Ključi`, da dostopate do seznamskega pogleda "
":guilabel:`Ključi`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari`, naložite digitalno "
":guilabel:`Datoteko ključa` (datoteka :file:`.key`), dodajte :guilabel:`Ime` "
"ključu in vnesite :guilabel:`Geslo zasebnega ključa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:402
msgid ""
"From :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --> Certificates and "
"Keys`, select :guilabel:`Certificates` to access the :guilabel:`Certificate` "
"list view. Click :guilabel:`Create`, upload the "
"digital :guilabel:`Certificate` (:file:`.cer` file), add a :guilabel:`Name` "
"to the certificate, and select the :guilabel:`Private Key` created on the "
"previous step from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Iz :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Splošne nastavitve --> Certifikati in "
"ključi` izberite :guilabel:`Certifikati`, da dostopate do seznamskega "
"pogleda :guilabel:`Certifikat`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari`, naložite "
"digitalni :guilabel:`Certifikat` (datoteka :file:`.cer`), dodajte "
":guilabel:`Ime` certifikatu in iz spustnega menija izberite "
":guilabel:`Zasebni ključ`, ustvarjen v prejšnjem koraku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:409
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Certificate Password` and :guilabel:`Public Key` fields "
"on :guilabel:`Certificate` records are optional."
msgstr ""
"Polji :guilabel:`Geslo certifikata` in :guilabel:`Javni ključ` v zapisih "
":guilabel:`Certifikat` sta neobvezni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:413
msgid ""
"In order to test the electronic invoicing, the following |SAT| test "
"certificates are provided:"
msgstr ""
"Za testiranje elektronskega izdajanja računov so na voljo naslednji testni "
"certifikati |SAT|:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:415
msgid ":download:`Certificate <mexico/certificate.cer>`"
msgstr ":download:`Certifikat <mexico/certificate.cer>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:416
msgid ":download:`Certificate Key <mexico/certificate.key>`"
msgstr ":download:`Ključ certifikata <mexico/certificate.key>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:417
msgid "**Password**: ``12345678a``"
msgstr "**Geslo**: ``12345678a``"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:427
msgid ""
"The invoicing process in Odoo is based on `Annex 20 <http://"
"omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/anexo_20.htm>`_ version 4.0 of "
"electronic invoicing of the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"Postopek izdajanja računov v Odoo temelji na `Prilogi 20 <http://"
"omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/anexo_20.htm>`_, različica 4.0 "
"elektronskega izdajanja računov |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:436
msgid ""
"To start invoicing from Odoo, a customer invoice must be created using "
"the :doc:`standard invoicing flow <../accounting/customer_invoices>`."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek izdajanja računov iz Odoo je treba ustvariti račun za stranko z "
"uporabo :doc:`standardnega poteka izdajanja računov <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:439
msgid ""
"While the document is in draft mode, changes can be made to it, some fields "
"take values previously set on the sale order or the contact."
msgstr ""
"Dokler je dokument v osnutku, je mogoče vnašati spremembe, nekatera polja "
"prevzamejo vrednosti, predhodno nastavljene v prodajnem nalogu ali stiku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:442
msgid "The fields that need to be reviewed are:"
msgstr "Polja, ki jih je treba pregledati, so:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:444
msgid "CFDI to public."
msgstr "CFDI za javnost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:445
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1534
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:446
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1532
msgid "Payment Policy"
msgstr "Politika plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:447
msgid "Payment Method (If Payment Policy is not set as |PPD|)"
msgstr "Način plačila (če politika plačila ni nastavljena na |PPD|)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:450
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Usage`, :guilabel:`Payment Policy` and :guilabel:`Payment Method` "
"can be previously set on a sale order and/or can be set on the contact for "
"every invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporaba`, :guilabel:`Politika plačila` in :guilabel:`Način "
"plačila` se lahko predhodno nastavijo v prodajnem nalogu in/ali se lahko "
"nastavijo pri stiku za vsak račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:453
msgid ""
"The payment policy is a selectable field on the invoice and can be manually "
"set to the required policy, however if no policy is selected, Odoo will "
"compute an automatic policy based on the following general rules:"
msgstr ""
"Politika plačila je izbirno polje na računu in se lahko ročno nastavi na "
"zahtevano politiko, vendar če politika ni izbrana, bo Odoo izračunal "
"samodejno politiko na podlagi naslednjih splošnih pravil:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:457
msgid ""
"The value will be set to |PUE| if the due date in which the payment is "
"expected is within the current month, in case the date is outside the "
"current month, the policy will be set to |PPD| instead."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost bo nastavljena na |PUE|, če je rok plačila v tekočem mesecu, v "
"primeru, da je datum zunaj tekočega meseca, bo politika nastavljena na |PPD|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:462
msgid ""
"If the payment policy is not selected and |PPD| policy is expected, either "
"select an invoice :guilabel:`Due Date` on a different month than the current "
"one, or choose :guilabel:`Payment terms` that imply changing the due month "
"(i.e., :guilabel:`30 Days`, or :guilabel:`15 Days`, as long as they fall on "
"the next month)."
msgstr ""
"Če politika plačila ni izbrana in je pričakovana politika |PPD|, bodisi "
"izberite :guilabel:`Datum valute` računa v drugem mesecu kot je trenutni, "
"ali izberite :guilabel:`Plačilni pogoji`, ki pomenijo spremembo meseca "
"valute (npr. :guilabel:`30 dni` ali :guilabel:`15 dni`, če padejo v "
"naslednji mesec)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:467
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Confirm` in the customer invoice, click "
"the :guilabel:`Send` button to process the invoice with the government. Make "
"sure that the :guilabel:`CFDI` checkbox is marked."
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na :guilabel:`Potrdi` v računu kupca kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Pošlji`, da obdelate račun pri državnem organu. Poskrbite, da je "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`CFDI` označeno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "CFDI Checkbox"
msgstr "Potrditveno polje CFDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:473
msgid ""
"After receiving the signed document back from the government, "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` field appears on the document, and the XML file "
"appears both in the |CFDI| tab and attached in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Po prejemu podpisanega dokumenta od vlade se na dokumentu pojavi polje "
":guilabel:`Fiskalna mapa`, datoteka XML pa se prikaže v zavihku |CFDI| in je "
"priložena v klepetu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:477
msgid ""
"If an email address is configured on the customer contact record, marking "
"the :guilabel:`by Email` and :guilabel:`CFDI` checkboxes sends both the XML "
"and PDF files together."
msgstr ""
"Če je na kontaktu stranke nastavljen e-poštni naslov, označitev polj "
":guilabel:`po e-pošti` in :guilabel:`CFDI` pošlje datoteki XML in PDF skupaj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:480
msgid "To download the PDF file locally, click the :guilabel:`Print` button."
msgstr "Za lokalni prenos datoteke PDF kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Natisni`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:483
msgid ""
"When clicking :guilabel:`Update SAT`, the :guilabel:`SAT status` field on "
"the invoice will confirm if the XML file is **Validated** in the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete :guilabel:`Posodobi SAT`, polje :guilabel:`Stanje SAT` na računu "
"potrdi, ali je datoteka XML **Potrjena** v |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:486
msgid ""
"On a testing environment, the message :guilabel:`Not Found` will always come "
"up."
msgstr ""
"V testnem okolju se bo vedno prikazalo sporočilo :guilabel:`Ni najdeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:489
msgid ""
"If the partner does not contain the :guilabel:`Country` or :guilabel:`Zip` "
"the invoicing is assumed as a |CFDI| to public and the invoicing will be "
"addressed to the generic customer. If however, these fields are left empty "
"and the user unticks the :guilabel:`CFDI to public` checkbox, a pop-up will "
"appear blocking the operation."
msgstr ""
"Če partner ne vsebuje :guilabel:`Država` ali :guilabel:`Poštna številka`, se "
"obračunavanje obravnava kot |CFDI| javnosti in bo naslovljeno na splošno "
"stranko. Če pa so ta polja prazna in uporabnik odznači potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`CFDI za javnost`, se prikaže pojavno okno, ki blokira operacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:499
msgid ""
"While an invoice is a document type \"I\" (Ingreso), a credit note is a "
"document type \"E\" (Egreso)."
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko je račun vrsta dokumenta \"I\" (Ingreso), je dobropis vrsta "
"dokumenta \"E\" (Egreso)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:501
msgid ""
"An addition to the :doc:`standard flow for credit notes <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/credit_notes>` is that, as a requirement of the |SAT|, "
"there has to be a relation between a credit note and an invoice through the "
"fiscal folio."
msgstr ""
"Dodatek k :doc:`standardnemu postopku za dobropisna <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/credit_notes>` je, da mora kot zahteva |SAT| obstajati "
"povezava med dobropisi in računom prek fiskalnega folija."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:505
msgid ""
"Because of this requirement, the field :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` adds this "
"relation with a `01|`, followed by the fiscal folio of the "
"original :abbr:`UUID (universally unique identifier)`."
msgstr ""
"Zaradi te zahteve polje :guilabel:`Izvor CFDI` doda to povezavo z `01|`, ki "
"mu sledi fiskalni folio izvirnega :abbr:`UUID (univerzalni enolični "
"identifikator)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:509
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` field to be automatically added, use "
"the :guilabel:`Add Credit Note` button from the invoice, instead of creating "
"it manually."
msgstr ""
"Da bi bilo polje :guilabel:`Izvor CFDI` samodejno dodano, uporabite gumb "
":guilabel:`Dodaj dobropis` iz računa, namesto da ga ustvarite ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:512
msgid ""
"Generally credit notes reverse the main sales account defined in the "
"journal, but it is also possible to globally assign an account to all credit "
"notes. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Settings` and set the :guilabel:`Credit notes` account under "
"the :guilabel:`Default Accounts` section."
msgstr ""
"Dobropisi običajno stornirajo glavni prodajni konto, določen v dnevniku, "
"vendar je mogoče tudi globalno dodeliti konto vsem dobropisom. To storite "
"tako, da odprete :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve` in nastavite konto :guilabel:`Dobropisi` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Privzeti konti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:518
msgid ""
"On the default configuration, the credit notes account is set "
"as :guilabel:`402.01.01 Returns, discounts or bonuses over sales and/or "
"services at the general rate`."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je konto za dobropise nastavljen kot :guilabel:`402.01.01 Vračila, "
"popusti ali bonusi pri prodaji in/ali storitvah po splošni stopnji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:526
msgid ""
"Vendor bills have to have a fiscal folio for reports and payments to work "
"correctly, if the vendor bill was created by the purchase app or added "
"manually, just add the XML file of the invoice on the chatter **As a log "
"note** and the fiscal folio will be updated accordingly, keep in mind that "
"the bill **Must be in draft state** for the update to happen."
msgstr ""
"Računi dobaviteljev morajo imeti fiskalno mapo, da poročila in plačila "
"delujejo pravilno. Če je bil račun dobavitelja ustvarjen prek aplikacije za "
"nakup ali dodan ročno, samo dodajte datoteko XML računa v klepet **Kot "
"dnevniški zapis** in fiskalna mapa bo ustrezno posodobljena. Upoštevajte, da "
"mora biti račun **V osnutku**, da se posodobitev izvede."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:532
msgid ""
"When clicking :guilabel:`Update SAT`, the :guilabel:`SAT status` field on "
"the invoice will confirm if the XML file is **Validated** by the |SAT|, this "
"is also true for vendor bills."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete :guilabel:`Posodobi SAT`, bo polje :guilabel:`Status SAT` na "
"računu potrdilo, ali je datoteko XML **potrdil** |SAT|. To velja tudi za "
"dobaviteljeve račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:536
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/vendor_bills`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/vendor_bills`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:543
msgid ""
"The module :guilabel:`EDI for Mexico (Advanced Features)` "
"(`l10n_mx_edi_extended`) must be installed on the database to complete "
"the :guilabel:`Address Issued` field on the sales journal. This ensures that "
"all invoices from that sales journal, as well as :ref:`global invoices <l10n/"
"mx/global-invoice>`, use the correct zipcode when generating the CFDI."
msgstr ""
"Modul :guilabel:`EDI za Mehiko (Napredne funkcije)` (`l10n_mx_edi_extended`) "
"mora biti nameščen v bazi podatkov, da se izpolni polje :guilabel:`Naslov "
"izdaje` v prodajnem dnevniku. To zagotavlja, da vsi računi iz tega "
"prodajnega dnevnika, kot tudi :ref:`globalni računi <l10n/mx/global-invoice>"
"`, pri ustvarjanju CFDI uporabljajo pravilno poštno številko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:548
msgid ""
"To invoice within a company under different time zones with the same user, a "
"system parameter must be created to ensure the correct time zone is applied "
"when invoicing, as the user's time zone is used by default."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izdajati račune v podjetju pod različnimi časovnimi pasovi z istim "
"uporabnikom, je treba ustvariti sistemski parameter za zagotovitev uporabe "
"pravilnega časovnega pasu pri izdajanju računov, saj se privzeto uporablja "
"uporabnikov časovni pas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:552
msgid ""
"To do so, enable :doc:`developer mode <../../general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new parameter with the key "
"`l10n_mx_edi_tz_XX` where `XX` is the ID of the journal, and set the desired "
"time zone as the value, for example, “America/Tijuana”."
msgstr ""
"To omogočite tako, da vključite :doc:`razvijalski način <../../general/"
"developer_mode>` in pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Tehnično --> "
"Sistemski parametri`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite nov parameter "
"s ključem `l10n_mx_edi_tz_XX`, kjer je `XX` ID dnevnika, in nastavite želeno "
"časovno območje kot vrednost, na primer „America/Tijuana\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:565
msgid "Payment policy"
msgstr "Politika plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:567
msgid ""
"One addition of the Mexican localization is the :guilabel:`Payment Policy` "
"field. `According to the SAT documentation <https://www.sat.gob.mx/consultas/"
"92764/comprobante-de-recepcion-de-pagos>`_, there are two types of payments:"
msgstr ""
"Ena od dodatkov mehiške lokalizacije je polje :guilabel:`Politika plačila`. "
"`Glede na dokumentacijo SAT <https://www.sat.gob.mx/consultas/92764/"
"comprobante-de-recepcion-de-pagos>`_ obstajata dve vrsti plačil:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:571
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PUE` (Pago en una Sola Exhibición/Payment in a Single Exhibition)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PUE` (Pago en una Sola Exhibición/Plačilo v enkratnem prikazu)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:572
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PPD` (Pago en Parcialidades o Diferido/Payment in Installements "
"or Deferred)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PPD` (Pago en Parcialidades o Diferido/Plačilo v obrokih ali "
"odloženo)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:575
msgid ""
"Payment Complements are only generated if the policy of the invoice is set "
"to |PPD|, please note that it is a requirement to set the :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method` to something different than **99 - Por definir**."
msgstr ""
"Dopolnila plačil se ustvarijo samo, če je politika računa nastavljena na "
"|PPD|. Upoštevajte, da je zahteva, da nastavite :guilabel:`Način plačila` na "
"nekaj drugega kot **99 - Por definir**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Example of an invoice with the PUE requirements."
msgstr "Primer računa z zahtevami PUE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:582
msgid ""
"If the invoice has a due date outside the current month, it will default to |"
"PPD|."
msgstr ""
"Če ima račun datum valute zunaj tekočega meseca, bo privzeto nastavljen na "
"|PPD|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Example of an invoice with the PPD requirements."
msgstr "Primer računa z zahtevami PPD."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:590
msgid "Payment flow"
msgstr "Potek plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:592
msgid ""
"In both cases, the payment process in Odoo :doc:`is the same <../accounting/"
"payments>`, the main difference being payments related to |PPD| invoices, by "
"law, need to be sent to the government as a document type \"P\" (Pago)."
msgstr ""
"V obeh primerih je postopek plačila v Odoo :doc:`enak <../accounting/"
"payments>`, glavna razlika pa je, da morajo biti po zakonu plačila, povezana "
"s |PPD| računi, poslana vladi kot vrsta dokumenta \"P\" (Pago)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:596
msgid ""
"If a payment is related to a |PUE| invoice, it can be registered through the "
"payment popup, and be associated with the corresponding invoice. To do so, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices`, and "
"select an invoice. Then, click the :guilabel:`Pay` button to open the "
"payment popup, set the :guilabel:`Payment Way` and any other fields, and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Payment`."
msgstr ""
"Če je plačilo povezano z |PUE| računom, ga lahko registrirate prek pojavnega "
"okna za plačilo in ga povežete z ustreznim računom. Za to pojdite v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Računi` in izberite račun. "
"Nato kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Plačaj`, da odprete pojavno okno za plačilo, "
"nastavite :guilabel:`Način plačila` in vsa druga polja ter kliknite "
":guilabel:`Ustvari plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:603
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:604
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/bank/reconciliation`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/bank/reconciliation`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:606
msgid ""
"While this process is the same for PPD invoices, the addition of creating "
"an :doc:`electronic document <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` means some additional requirements are needed to "
"correctly send the document to the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je ta postopek enak za PPD račune, dodatek ustvarjanja "
":doc:`elektronskega dokumenta <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` pomeni, da so potrebne nekatere dodatne zahteve za "
"pravilno pošiljanje dokumenta |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:610
msgid ""
"From a legal perspective, PPD invoices **must** include the "
"specific :guilabel:`Payment Way` that the payment was received. Because of "
"this, the :guilabel:`Payment Way` field **cannot** be set as :guilabel:`To "
"Define`, thus the field will become invisible when selecting it."
msgstr ""
"Z zakonskega vidika **morajo** PPD računi vključevati določen "
":guilabel:`Način plačila`, s katerim je bilo plačilo prejeto. Zaradi tega "
"polja :guilabel:`Način plačila` **ni mogoče** nastaviti kot :guilabel:`Za "
"določiti`, zato bo polje postalo nevidno, ko ga izberete."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:615
msgid ""
"If a bank account number is required, add it in the :guilabel:`Accounting` "
"tab of a customer's contact record."
msgstr ""
"Če je potrebna številka bančnega računa, jo dodajte v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Računovodstvo` kontaktnega zapisa stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:617
msgid ""
"The exact configurations are in the `Anexo 20 of the SAT <http://"
"omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/anexo_20.htm>`_. Usually, "
"the :guilabel:`Bank Account` needs to be 10 or 18 digits for transfers, 16 "
"for credit or debit cards."
msgstr ""
"Natančne konfiguracije so v `Anexo 20 SAT <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/anexo_20.htm>`_. Običajno mora biti "
":guilabel:`Bančni račun` 10 ali 18 mestni za prenose, 16 za kreditne ali "
"debetne kartice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:622
msgid ""
"If a fully-reconciled payment is related to an invoice with "
"a :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`, the :guilabel:`Update Payments` appears. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Update Payments` button to send the **payment complement** "
"XML file to the government automatically and display it in the |CFDI| tab in "
"both the invoice and the payment."
msgstr ""
"Če je popolnoma usklajeno plačilo povezano z računom s :guilabel:`Fiscal "
"Folio`, se prikaže :guilabel:`Posodobi plačila`. Kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Posodobi plačila`, da samodejno pošljete XML datoteko **dopolnila "
"plačila** vladi in jo prikažete v zavihku |CFDI| tako na računu kot na "
"plačilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:628
msgid ""
"While it is a bad fiscal practice, the |PUE| payments can also be sent to "
"the government, however it is required to click :guilabel:`Force CFDI` in "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab for this."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je to slaba davčna praksa, je mogoče |PUE| plačila poslati tudi "
"vladi, vendar je za to potrebno klikniti :guilabel:`Prisili CFDI` v zavihku "
":guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:631
msgid ""
"Similar to an invoice or credit note, the PDF and XML can be sent to the "
"final customer. To do so, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon "
"to open the actions drop-down menu and select :guilabel:`Send receipt by "
"email` from the payment view."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot račun ali dobropis lahko PDF in XML pošljete končnemu kupcu. Za "
"to kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(zobnik)`, da odprete spustni "
"meni dejanj, in v prikazu plačila izberite :guilabel:`Pošlji potrdilo po e-"
"pošti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:635
msgid ""
"Regardless of whether the payment was created with or without "
"reconciliation, it is possible to download the payment PDF from "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab on the invoice by clicking the :guilabel:`print` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali je bilo plačilo ustvarjeno z uskladitvijo ali brez nje, "
"je mogoče PDF plačila prenesti iz zavihka :guilabel:`CFDI` na računu s "
"klikom na gumb :guilabel:`natisni`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Example of the print button on the CFDI tab."
msgstr "Primer gumba za tiskanje v zavihku CFDI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:645
msgid "Invoice cancellations"
msgstr "Preklici računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:647
msgid ""
"It is possible to cancel the EDI documents sent to the |SAT|. According to "
"the `Reforma Fiscal 2022 <https://www.sat.gob.mx/consultas/91447/nuevo-"
"esquema-de-cancelacion>`_, since January 1st, 2022, there are two "
"requirements for this:"
msgstr ""
"Možno je preklicati EDI dokumente, poslane v |SAT|. V skladu z `Reforma "
"Fiscal 2022 <https://www.sat.gob.mx/consultas/91447/nuevo-esquema-de-"
"cancelacion>`_ obstajata od 1. januarja 2022 za to dve zahtevi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:651
msgid "All cancellation requests require a *cancellation reason*."
msgstr "Vse zahteve za preklic zahtevajo *razlog za preklic*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:652
msgid ""
"After 24 hours from the invoice creation, the client must be asked to "
"approve the cancellation. If there is no response within 72 hours, the "
"cancellation is processed automatically."
msgstr ""
"Po 24 urah od izdaje računa je potrebno stranko zaprositi za odobritev "
"preklica. Če v 72 urah ni odziva, se preklic obdela samodejno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:655
msgid ""
"Invoice cancellations are updated automatically on Odoo but can take some "
"time, to check the status of the cancellation just press "
"the :guilabel:`Update SAT` button."
msgstr ""
"Preklici računov se v Odoo posodobijo samodejno, vendar to lahko traja nekaj "
"časa. Za preverjanje statusa preklica preprosto pritisnite gumb "
":guilabel:`Posodobi SAT`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:658
msgid "Invoice cancellations can be made for one of the following reasons:"
msgstr "Preklice računov je mogoče opraviti iz enega od naslednjih razlogov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:660
msgid "01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related document)"
msgstr "01 - Račun izdan z napakami (z povezanim dokumentom)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:661
msgid "02 - Invoice issued with errors (no replacement)"
msgstr "02 - Račun izdan z napakami (brez zamenjave)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:662
msgid "03 - The operation was not carried out"
msgstr "03 - Operacija ni bila izvedena"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:663
msgid "04 - Nominative operation related to the global invoice"
msgstr "04 - Nominativna operacija povezana s skupnim računom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:665
msgid ""
"To initiate a cancellation, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --"
"> Invoices`, select the posted invoice to cancel, and "
"click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. Then, refer to the :ref:`l10n/mx/01-"
"invoice-cancellation` or :ref:`l10n/mx/02-03-04-invoice-cancellation` "
"sections, depending on the cancellation reason."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek razveljavitve pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Kupci --> Računi`, izberite knjiženi račun za razveljavitev in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Zahtevaj razveljavitev`. Nato se sklicujte na razdelek :ref:`l10n/"
"mx/01-invoice-cancellation` ali :ref:`l10n/mx/02-03-04-invoice-"
"cancellation`, odvisno od razloga za razveljavitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:671
msgid ""
"Alternatively, request a cancellation from the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Cancel` on the line item."
msgstr ""
"Alternativno lahko zahtevate razveljavitev na zavihku :guilabel:`CFDI` s "
"klikom na :guilabel:`Razveljavi` pri postavki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:675
msgid ""
"If a cancellation is requested on a locked period, the CFDI will be "
"cancelled but not the accounting entry."
msgstr ""
"Če je razveljavitev zahtevana v zaklenjenem obdobju, bo CFDI razveljavljen, "
"vendar ne knjigovodski vnos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:677
msgid ""
"If the client rejects the cancellation, the invoice cancellation line item "
"is removed from the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab."
msgstr ""
"Če stranka zavrne razveljavitev, je postavka razveljavitve računa "
"odstranjena iz zavihka :guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:683
msgid "Cancellation reason 01"
msgstr "Razlog za razveljavitev 01"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:685
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Request CFDI Cancellation` pop-up window, "
"select :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related document)` "
"from the :guilabel:`Reason` field and click :guilabel:`Create Replacement "
"Invoice` to create a new draft invoice. This new draft invoice replaces the "
"previous invoice, along with the related |CFDI|."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Zahtevaj razveljavitev CFDI` izberite "
":guilabel:`01 - Račun izdan z napakami (z povezanim dokumentom)` iz polja "
":guilabel:`Razlog` in kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari nadomestni račun`, da "
"ustvarite nov osnutek računa. Ta novi osnutek računa nadomesti prejšnji "
"račun skupaj s povezanim |CFDI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:689
msgid ":guilabel:`Confirm` the draft and :guilabel:`Send` the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Potrdite` osnutek in :guilabel:`pošljite` račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:690
msgid ""
"Return to the initial invoice (i.e., the invoice from which you first "
"requested the cancellation). Notice the :guilabel:`Substituted By` field "
"appears with a reference to the new replacement invoice."
msgstr ""
"Vrnite se na začetni račun (tj. račun, iz katerega ste prvič zahtevali "
"razveljavitev). Opazite, da se prikaže polje :guilabel:`Nadomeščeno z` s "
"sklicevanjem na novi nadomestni račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:693
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`. In the :guilabel:`Request CFDI "
"Cancellation` pop-up window, the :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors "
"(with related document)` option is automatically selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Reason` field."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Zahtevaj razveljavitev`. V pojavnem oknu "
":guilabel:`Zahtevaj razveljavitev CFDI` je možnost :guilabel:`01 - Račun "
"izdan z napakami (z povezanim dokumentom)` samodejno izbrana v polju "
":guilabel:`Razlog`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:696
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr "Klikněte na :guilabel:`Potvrdit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:698
msgid ""
"The invoice cancellation is then generated with a reason line item in "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab."
msgstr ""
"Razveljavitev računa je nato ustvarjena s postavko razloga v zavihku "
":guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Canceled invoice line item in the CFDI tab."
msgstr "Postavka razveljavitve računa v zavihku CFDI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:704
msgid ""
"When using the :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related "
"document)` cancellation reason, the `04|` prefix appears in "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` field. This is an internal prefix used by Odoo "
"to complete the cancellation and **does not** mean that the cancellation "
"reason was :guilabel:`04 - Nominative operation related to the global "
"invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi razloga za razveljavitev :guilabel:`01 - Račun izdan z napakami "
"(z povezanim dokumentom)` se v polju :guilabel:`Davčna mapa` pojavi predpona "
"`04|`. To je interna predpona, ki jo uporablja Odoo za dokončanje "
"razveljavitve, in **ne** pomeni, da je bil razlog za razveljavitev "
":guilabel:`04 - Nominativna operacija povezana s skupnim računom`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:712
msgid "Cancellation reasons 02, 03, and 04"
msgstr "Razlogi za razveljavitev 02, 03 in 04"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:714
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Request CFDI Cancellation` pop-up window, select the "
"desired cancellation :guilabel:`Reason` and :guilabel:`Confirm` the "
"cancellation."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Zahtevaj razveljavitev CFDI` izberite želeni "
":guilabel:`Razlog` za razveljavitev in :guilabel:`Potrdite` razveljavitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:717
msgid ""
"Upon doing so, the invoice cancellation is generated with a reason line item "
"in the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab."
msgstr ""
"Pri tem je razveljavitev računa ustvarjena s postavko razloga v zavihku "
":guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:721
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`SAT Status` goes back to **Validated** it could be due to "
"one of these three reasons:"
msgstr ""
"Če se :guilabel:`Status SAT` vrne na **Potrjeno**, je lahko to posledica "
"enega od teh treh razlogov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:724
msgid ""
"The invoice is labeled as *No Cancelable* in the `SAT Website <https://"
"www.sat.gob.mx/home>`_. due to the fact that it has a valid related "
"document: Either another invoice linked with the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` "
"field or a Payment Complement. If so, you need to cancel any other related "
"document first."
msgstr ""
"Račun je na `spletni strani SAT <https://www.sat.gob.mx/home>`_ označen kot "
"*Ni mogoče preklicati*, ker ima veljaven povezan dokument: bodisi drug "
"račun, povezan s poljem :guilabel:`Izvor CFDI`, bodisi dopolnilo plačila. Če "
"je tako, morate najprej preklicati vse druge povezane dokumente."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:728
msgid ""
"The cancellation request is still being processed by the |SAT|. If so, wait "
"a few minutes and try again."
msgstr ""
"Zahteva za preklic se še vedno obdeluje s strani |SAT|. Če je temu tako, "
"počakajte nekaj minut in poskusite znova."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:730
msgid ""
"The final customer needs to reject or accept the cancellation request in "
"their `Buzón Tributario <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/BuzonTributario/Paginas/"
"servicios_disponibles.html>`_. This can take up to 72 hours and, in case "
"that the cancellation requests gets rejected, you will need to repeat the "
"process again."
msgstr ""
"Končni kupec mora zavrniti ali sprejeti zahtevo za preklic v svojem `Buzón "
"Tributario <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/BuzonTributario/Paginas/"
"servicios_disponibles.html>`_. To lahko traja do 72 ur in v primeru, da je "
"zahteva za preklic zavrnjena, boste morali postopek ponoviti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:736
msgid ""
"`Tool to validate Mexican Electronic Documents (CFDI) status <https://"
"verificacfdi.facturaelectronica.sat.gob.mx/>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Orodje za preverjanje statusa mehiških elektronskih dokumentov (CFDI) "
"<https://verificacfdi.facturaelectronica.sat.gob.mx/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:739
msgid ""
"For the cancellation reasons **02**, **03** and **04**, "
"the :guilabel:`Create Replacement Invoice` button is replaced by "
"a :guilabel:`Confirm` button that requests the cancellation immediately."
msgstr ""
"Pri razlogih za preklic **02**, **03** in **04** je gumb :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"nadomestni račun` zamenjan z gumbom :guilabel:`Potrdi`, ki takoj zahteva "
"preklic."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:742
msgid ""
"Both the current :guilabel:`State` and :guilabel:`Cancellation Reason` can "
"be found in the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab."
msgstr ""
"Tako trenutno :guilabel:`Stanje` kot tudi :guilabel:`Razlog za preklic` "
"najdete v zavihku :guilabel:`CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Old invoice with CFDI Origin."
msgstr "Stari račun s CFDI Origin."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:751
msgid "Payment cancellations"
msgstr "Preklici plačil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:753
msgid ""
"To cancel :ref:`payment complements <l10n/mx/payment-flow>`, go to "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab of the related invoice and click :guilabel:`Cancel` "
"on the line of the payment complement."
msgstr ""
"Za preklic :ref:`dopolnil plačil <l10n/mx/payment-flow>` pojdite v zavihek "
":guilabel:`CFDI` povezanega računa in kliknite :guilabel:`Prekliči` v "
"vrstici dopolnila plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:756
msgid ""
"Like with invoices, go to the payment and click :guilabel:`Update SAT` in "
"order to change the :guilabel:`SAT Status` and :guilabel:`Status` "
"to :guilabel:`Cancelled`."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot pri računih pojdite na plačilo in kliknite :guilabel:`Posodobi "
"SAT`, da spremenite :guilabel:`Status SAT` in :guilabel:`Stanje` v "
":guilabel:`Preklicano`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:760
msgid ""
"Just like invoices, when creating a new payment complement, it is possible "
"to add the relation of the original document, by adding a `04|` plus the "
"fiscal folio in the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` field."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako kot pri računih je ob ustvarjanju novega dopolnila plačila mogoče "
"dodati povezavo izvirnega dokumenta z dodajanjem `04|` ter fiskalnega folia "
"v polje :guilabel:`CFDI Origin`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:764
msgid ""
"This action cancels the invoice and marks the :guilabel:`Reason` "
"as :guilabel:`01 - Invoice issued with errors (with related document)`."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje prekliče račun in označi :guilabel:`Razlog` kot :guilabel:`01 - "
"Račun izdan z napakami (s povezanim dokumentom)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:770
msgid "Invoicing special use cases"
msgstr "Fakturiranje posebnih primerov uporabe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:775
msgid "CFDI relations"
msgstr "Povezave CFDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:777
msgid ""
"Sometimes it is needed to relate the current document to previously signed "
"CFDIs, to do so just fill the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` field on the invoice "
"indicating a relation, there are 7 possible values:"
msgstr ""
"Včasih je potrebno trenutni dokument povezati s prej podpisanimi CFDI, za to "
"preprosto izpolnite polje :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` na računu s povezavo, "
"možnih je 7 vrednosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:780
msgid "01: Nota de crédito"
msgstr "01: Nota de crédito"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:781
msgid "02: Nota de débito de los documentos relacionados"
msgstr "02: Nota de débito de los documentos relacionados"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:782
msgid "03: Devolución de mercancía sobre facturas o traslados previos"
msgstr "03: Devolución de mercancía sobre facturas o traslados previos"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:783
msgid "04: Sustitución de los CFDI previos"
msgstr "04: Sustitución de los CFDI previos"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:784
msgid "05: Traslados de mercancias facturados previamente"
msgstr "05: Traslados de mercancias facturados previamente"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:785
msgid "06: Factura generada por los traslados previos"
msgstr "06: Factura generada por los traslados previos"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:786
msgid "07: CFDI por aplicación de anticipo"
msgstr "07: CFDI por aplicación de anticipo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:789
msgid ""
"The format is: Origin Type|UUID1, UUID2, ...., UUIDn where more than one "
"Origin Type can be added."
msgstr ""
"Oblika je: Vrsta izvora|UUID1, UUID2, ...., UUIDn, kjer je mogoče dodati več "
"kot eno vrsto izvora."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:793
msgid "Here is an example with two relations:"
msgstr "Tukaj je primer z dvema relacijama:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:800
msgid "The first section has relation type **04** with **1 UUID**"
msgstr "Prvi razdelek ima vrsto relacije **04** z **1 UUID**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:801
msgid "The second section has relation type **07** with **2 UUIDs**"
msgstr "Drugi razdelek ima vrsto relacije **07** z **2 UUID**"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:803
msgid "Additionally any combination is also visible on the signed PDF."
msgstr "Dodatno je katerakoli kombinacija vidna tudi v podpisanem PDF-ju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Example of the PDF with 3 relations."
msgstr "Primer PDF-ja s 3 relacijami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:813
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Main Currency` in Mexico is MXN. While this is mandatory for "
"all Mexican companies, it is possible to send and receive invoices (and "
"payments) in different currencies. To enable the use of :doc:`multicurrency "
"<../accounting/get_started/multi_currency>`, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Currencies`, and "
"set :guilabel:`[MX] Bank of Mexico` as the :guilabel:`Service` in "
"the :guilabel:`Automatic Currency Rates` section. Then, set "
"the :guilabel:`Interval` field to the frequency you wish to update the "
"exchange rates."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Glavna valuta` v Mehiki je MXN. Čeprav je to obvezno za vsa "
"mehiška podjetja, je mogoče pošiljati in prejemati račune (in plačila) v "
"različnih valutah. Za omogočanje uporabe :doc:`več valut <../accounting/"
"get_started/multi_currency>` pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Valute` in nastavite :guilabel:`[MX] Mehiška centralna "
"banka` kot :guilabel:`Storitev` v razdelku :guilabel:`Samodejni menjalniški "
"tečaji`. Nato nastavite polje :guilabel:`Interval` na pogostost, s katero "
"želite posodabljati menjalne tečaje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:820
msgid ""
"This way, the XML file of the document will have the correct exchange rate, "
"and the total amount, in both the foreign currency and in MXN."
msgstr ""
"Na ta način bo datoteka XML dokumenta vsebovala pravilen menjalni tečaj in "
"skupni znesek v tuji valuti in v MXN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:823
msgid ""
"It is highly recommended to use separate :doc:`bank accounts for each "
"currency <../accounting/bank/foreign_currency>`."
msgstr ""
"Močno priporočamo uporabo ločenih :doc:`bančnih računov za vsako valuto <../"
"accounting/bank/foreign_currency>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:827
msgid ""
"The only currencies that automatically update their exchange rate daily are: "
"USD, EUR, GBP, JPY and CNY."
msgstr ""
"Edine valute, ki samodejno posodabljajo svoj menjalni tečaj dnevno, so: USD, "
"EUR, GBP, JPY in CNY."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:835
msgid ""
"By law, electronic documents sent to the government cannot have negative "
"lines, as this can trigger errors. Therefore, when using :doc:`Gift Cards "
"<../../sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards>` or :doc:`Loyalty "
"Programs <../../sales/sales/products_prices/loyalty_discount>`, the "
"subsequent negative lines will be translated in the XML as if they were "
"regular :doc:`Discounts <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing/>`."
msgstr ""
"Po zakonu elektronski dokumenti, poslani vladi, ne smejo vsebovati "
"negativnih vrstic, saj lahko to povzroči napake. Zato se pri uporabi "
":doc:`darilnih kartic <../../sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards>"
"` ali :doc:`programov zvestobe <../../sales/sales/products_prices/"
"loyalty_discount>` naslednje negativne vrstice v XML-ju prevedejo, kot da so "
"običajni :doc:`popusti <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/pricing/>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:842
msgid ""
"In order to set this up, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales --> Products --> "
"Products` and create a product `Discounts`, make sure that it has a "
"valid :guilabel:`Tax` (usually :guilabel:`IVA` at `16%`)."
msgstr ""
"Za nastavitev tega pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodaja --> Izdelki --> "
"Izdelki` in ustvarite izdelek `Popusti`, pri čemer se prepričajte, da ima "
"veljaven :guilabel:`Davek` (običajno :guilabel:`IVA` pri `16%`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:846
msgid ""
"After this, create and sign the invoice via |CFDI|, and add the `Discounts` "
"product at the bottom. In the XML, Odoo will distribute the discount between "
"the lines evenly, while any math differences will be added in a rounding "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Po tem ustvarite in podpišite račun prek |CFDI| ter dodajte izdelek "
"`Popusti` na dno. V XML-ju bo Odoo enakomerno razdelil popust med vrstice, "
"medtem ko bodo vse matematične razlike dodane v izdelek zaokroževanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:851
msgid ""
"A `Discount` and `UNSPSC Product Category` for each product variant related "
"to :guilabel:`Gift Cards` or :guilabel:`Loyalty Programs` have to be created."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako različico izdelka, povezano z :guilabel:`Darilnimi karticami` ali "
":guilabel:`Programi zvestobe`, je treba ustvariti `Popust` in `Kategorijo "
"izdelka UNSPSC`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:857
msgid "Down payments"
msgstr "Akontacije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:859
msgid ""
"A common practice in Mexico is the usage of :doc:`down payments <../../sales/"
"sales/invoicing/down_payment>`. It's usage primarily consists of cases where "
"you receive a payment for a good or service where either the product or the "
"price (or both) has not been fully determined."
msgstr ""
"Pogosta praksa v Mehiki je uporaba :doc:`akontacij <../../sales/sales/"
"invoicing/down_payment>`. Njihova uporaba se predvsem nanaša na primere, ko "
"prejmete plačilo za blago ali storitev, pri katerih izdelek ali cena (ali "
"oboje) še nista popolnoma določena."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:864
msgid ""
"The |SAT| allows two different ways to handle this process: both of them "
"involve linking all invoices to each other with the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"|SAT| omogoča dva različna načina obravnave tega postopka: oba vključujeta "
"povezovanje vseh računov drug z drugim s poljem :guilabel:`Izvor CFDI`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:868
msgid "For this process, the :doc:`Sales <../../sales>` app must be installed."
msgstr ""
"Za ta postopek mora biti nameščena aplikacija :doc:`Prodaja <../../sales>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:871
msgid ""
"`The official documentation for registration of down payments in Mexico "
"<http://http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/documentos/"
"GuiaAnexo311221.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Uradna dokumentacija za registracijo akontacij v Mehiki <http://http://"
"omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/documentos/GuiaAnexo311221.pdf>"
"`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:877
msgid ""
"First, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales --> Products --> Products` to "
"create a product `Anticipo` and configure it. The :guilabel:`Product Type` "
"must be :guilabel:`Service`, and use the :guilabel:`UNSPSC "
"Category` :guilabel:`84111506 Servicios de facturación`."
msgstr ""
"Najprej pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodaja --> Izdelki --> Izdelki`, da "
"ustvarite izdelek `Anticipo` in ga konfigurirate. :guilabel:`Vrsta izdelka` "
"mora biti :guilabel:`Storitev` in uporabite :guilabel:`kategorijo UNSPSC` "
":guilabel:`84111506 Servicios de facturación`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:881
msgid ""
"Then, go to :menuselection:`Sales --> Settings --> Invoicing --> Down "
"Payments`, and add the *Anticipo* product as the default."
msgstr ""
"Nato pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodaja --> Nastavitve --> Fakturiranje --> "
"Akontacije` in dodajte izdelek *Anticipo* kot privzetega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:887
msgid "Method A"
msgstr "Metoda A"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:889
msgid ""
"This method consists of creating a down payment invoice, creating a invoice "
"for the total amount, and finally, creating a credit note for the total of "
"the down payment."
msgstr ""
"Ta metoda vključuje ustvarjanje predračuna za akontacijo, ustvarjanje računa "
"za celotni znesek in nazadnje ustvarjanje dobropisa za znesek akontacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:892
msgid ""
"First, create a sales order with the total amount, and create a down payment "
"from it (either using a percentage or fixed amount). Then, sign the document "
"via CFDI, and register the payment."
msgstr ""
"Najprej ustvarite prodajni nalog s celotnim zneskom in iz njega ustvarite "
"akontacijo (z uporabo odstotka ali fiksnega zneska). Nato podpišite dokument "
"prek CFDI in registrirajte plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:895
msgid ""
"When the time comes for the customer to get the final invoice, create it "
"again from the same sales order. In the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` popup, "
"select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice`. Make sure to delete the line that "
"contains the product *Anticipo*."
msgstr ""
"Ko pride čas, da stranka prejme končni račun, ga znova ustvarite iz istega "
"prodajnega naloga. V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari račun` izberite "
":guilabel:`Redni račun`. Poskrbite, da izbrišete vrstico, ki vsebuje izdelek "
"*Anticipo*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:900
msgid ""
"When using down payments with the Mexican localization, make sure that "
"the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` of the products are :guilabel:`Ordered "
"quantities`. Otherwise a customer credit note will be created."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi akontacij z mehiško lokalizacijo se prepričajte, da je "
":guilabel:`Pravilnik za zaračunavanje` izdelkov nastavljen na "
":guilabel:`Naročene količine`. V nasprotnem primeru bo ustvarjen dobropis "
"stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:904
msgid ""
"Then, copy the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` from the down payment invoice, and "
"paste it into the :guilabel:`CDFI Origin` of the final invoice, adding the "
"prefix `07|` before the value and sign the document via |CFDI|."
msgstr ""
"Nato kopirajte :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` iz računa za akontacijo in ga "
"prilepite v :guilabel:`CDFI Origin` končnega računa, pri čemer dodajte "
"predpono `07|` pred vrednost, in podpišite dokument prek |CFDI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:908
msgid ""
"Finally, create a credit note for the first invoice. Copy "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` from the final invoice, and paste it in "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` of the credit note, adding the prefix `07|`. "
"Then, sign the document via |CFDI|."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje ustvarite dobropis za prvi račun. Kopirajte :guilabel:`Fiscal "
"Folio` iz končnega računa in ga prilepite v :guilabel:`CFDI Origin` "
"dobropisa, pri čemer dodajte predpono `07|`. Nato podpišite dokument prek "
"|CFDI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:912
msgid ""
"With this, all electronic documents are linked to each other. The final step "
"is to fully pay the new invoice. At the bottom of the new invoice, you can "
"find the credit note in the :guilabel:`Outstanding credits` - add it as "
"payment. Finally, register the remaining amount with the :guilabel:`Pay` "
"popup."
msgstr ""
"S tem so vsi elektronski dokumenti med seboj povezani. Zadnji korak je "
"popolno plačilo novega računa. Na dnu novega računa lahko najdete dobropis v "
":guilabel:`Neporavnani dobropisi` - dodajte ga kot plačilo. Nazadnje "
"registrirajte preostali znesek s pojavnim oknom :guilabel:`Plačaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:917
msgid ""
"In the sales order, all three documents should appear as \"In Payment\"."
msgstr ""
"V prodajnem nalogu bi se morali vsi trije dokumenti prikazati kot \"V "
"plačilu\"."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:920
msgid "Method B"
msgstr "Metoda B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:922
msgid ""
"Another, simpler way to fulfill |SAT| requirements involves creating only "
"the down payment invoice, and a second invoice for the remnant. This method "
"involves the fact that negative lines are treated as discounts."
msgstr ""
"Drug, enostavnejši način za izpolnjevanje zahtev |SAT| vključuje ustvarjanje "
"samo računa za akontacijo in drugega računa za ostanek. Ta metoda temelji na "
"dejstvu, da se negativne vrstice obravnavajo kot popusti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:926
msgid ""
"For this, follow the same process as :ref:`Method A <l10n-mx/down-payment-"
"method-a>`, up until the creation of the final invoice. Do not delete the "
"line that contains the *Anticipo* and instead rename the other "
"products :guilabel:`Description` to include the text `CFDI por remanente de "
"un anticipo`. Don't forget to add the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` of the down "
"payment invoice in the :guilabel:`CDFI Origin` of the final invoice, adding "
"the prefix `07|`."
msgstr ""
"V ta namen sledite istemu postopku kot pri :ref:`Metoda A <l10n-mx/down-"
"payment-method-a>`, vse do ustvarjanja končnega računa. Ne izbrišite "
"vrstice, ki vsebuje *Anticipo*, temveč preimenujte :guilabel:`Opis` drugih "
"izdelkov tako, da vključuje besedilo `CFDI por remanente de un anticipo`. Ne "
"pozabite dodati :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio` računa za akontacijo v "
":guilabel:`CDFI Origin` končnega računa, pri čemer dodajte predpono `07|`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:932
msgid "Finally, sign the final invoice via |CFDI|."
msgstr "Nazadnje podpišite končni račun prek |CFDI|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:937
msgid "Addendas and complements"
msgstr "Dodatki in dopolnila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:939
msgid ""
"Addendas and complements can be included in the XML. To add one, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Addendas & Complementos "
"(MX)` and :guilabel:`New` to enter the code to be injected. Additional "
"fields beyond standard Odoo may be required."
msgstr ""
"V XML je mogoče vključiti dodatke in dopolnila. Za dodajanje pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Addendas & Complementos "
"(MX)` in izberite :guilabel:`Novo`, da vnesete kodo, ki bo vstavljena. Poleg "
"standardnih polj Odoo so lahko zahtevana dodatna polja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:944
msgid ""
"This section might require technical knowledge and may risk adding technical "
"debt; it is recommended to ask your account manager for the best technical "
"advice."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek lahko zahteva tehnično znanje in lahko povzroči dodatek tehnične "
"dolga; priporočljivo je, da pri upravljavcu svojega računa zaprosite za "
"najboljši tehnični nasvet."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:947
msgid ""
"Once the desired nodes are created, they can be selected on each contact to "
"make them appear on every invoice addressed to that contact. By default, all "
"the selected nodes will be added automatically on every invoice."
msgstr ""
"Ko so želena vozlišča ustvarjena, jih je mogoče izbrati pri vsakem stiku, da "
"se prikažejo na vsakem računu, naslovljenem na ta stik. Privzeto bodo vsa "
"izbrana vozlišča samodejno dodana na vsak račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:951
msgid ""
"It is also possible to just select the nodes as needed on every invoice by "
"selecting the :guilabel:`Other info` tab and then selecting the desired "
"nodes from :guilabel:`Addendas & Complementos`"
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je tudi preprosto izbrati vozlišča po potrebi na vsakem računu tako, "
"da izberete zavihek :guilabel:`Druge informacije` in nato izberete želena "
"vozlišča iz :guilabel:`Addendas & Complementos`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:956
msgid "It is possible to add more than one per contact or per invoice."
msgstr "Mogoče je dodati več kot enega na stik ali račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:961
msgid "XML reader"
msgstr "Bralnik XML"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:963
msgid ""
"In certain occasions, such as when you are creating invoices in another "
"software or in the |SAT| directly, you would want to upload the invoices in "
"Odoo. The XML Reader allows you to retrieve the data from an XML file. To do "
"this, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Invoices` "
"and, in the list view, click the :guilabel:`Upload` button to select any "
"number of XML files, and draft invoices will be automatically created. This "
"can work also by dragging the files from your computer and dropping them in "
"the view."
msgstr ""
"V določenih primerih, na primer ko ustvarjate račune v drugi programski "
"opremi ali neposredno v |SAT|, bi morda želeli račune naložiti v Odoo. "
"Bralnik XML vam omogoča pridobivanje podatkov iz datoteke XML. Za to se "
"pomaknite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Računi` in v "
"seznamskem pogledu kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Naloži`, da izberete poljubno "
"število datotek XML, osnutki računov pa bodo samodejno ustvarjeni. To deluje "
"tudi tako, da datoteke povlečete iz računalnika in jih spustite v pogled."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:970
msgid ""
"The draft invoices will retrieve the :guilabel:`Customer information` (if it "
"doesn't exist, new ones will be created), the :guilabel:`Product Lines` "
"(only if products with the same name already exist) and will calculate all "
"taxes and additional fields exclusive to the Mexican Localization. The "
"import information will appear in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Osnutki računov bodo pridobili :guilabel:`Informacije o stranki` (če ne "
"obstajajo, bodo ustvarjene nove), :guilabel:`Vrstice izdelkov` (samo če "
"izdelki z istim imenom že obstajajo) in izračunali bodo vse davke in dodatna "
"polja, značilna za mehiško lokalizacijo. Informacije o uvozu se bodo "
"prikazale v klepetu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:976
msgid ""
"Depending on where the invoice was created, XML files could have different "
"values from the total calculated in Odoo. **Always** double-check any "
"document uploaded this way."
msgstr ""
"Glede na to, kje je bil račun ustvarjen, lahko datoteke XML vsebujejo "
"različne vrednosti od skupnega zneska, izračunanega v Odoo. **Vedno** "
"ponovno preverite vse dokumente, naložene na ta način."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:979
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer Invoices` created this way will be able to create "
"**payment complements** and to be canceled at any time. If you use "
"the :guilabel:`Print` button, the PDF document will have all the "
"corresponding information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Računi za stranke`, ustvarjeni na ta način, bodo omogočali "
"ustvarjanje **dopolnil plačila** in bodo lahko kadarkoli prekličani. Če "
"uporabite gumb :guilabel:`Natisni`, bo dokument PDF vseboval vse ustrezne "
"informacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:983
msgid "This can be done for :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` too."
msgstr "To lahko storite tudi za :guilabel:`Račune dobaviteljev`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:986
msgid ""
"To retrieve the :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`, drag and drop XML files as a log "
"note in the chatter for previously created draft invoices."
msgstr ""
"Za pridobitev :guilabel:`Davčnega folija` povlecite in spustite datoteke XML "
"kot dnevniški zapis v klepetu za predhodno ustvarjene osnutke računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:992
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1533
msgid "CFDI to public"
msgstr "CFDI za javnost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:994
msgid ""
"The Mexican government requires that any goods or services that are sold "
"must be backed up by an invoice. If the customer does not require an invoice "
"or has no |RFC|, a *CFDI to Public* has to be created also known as a "
"\"nominative\" invoice."
msgstr ""
"Mehka vlada zahteva, da mora biti vsako blago ali storitev, ki se proda, "
"podprta z računom. Če stranka ne potrebuje računa ali nima |RFC|, je treba "
"ustvariti *CFDI za javnost*, znan tudi kot \"nominativni\" račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:998
msgid "A contact must be created and it must have a particular name."
msgstr "Ustvariti je treba stik in imeti mora določeno ime."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1000
msgid ""
"If  the :guilabel:`CFDI to Public` checkbox in either a sales order or an "
"invoice is checked, the final XML will override the data in the invoice "
"contact and will add the following characteristics:"
msgstr ""
"Če je v prodajnem nalogu ali računu označeno potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`CFDI za javnost`, bo končni XML prepisal podatke v stiku računa "
"in dodal naslednje značilnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1003
msgid ""
"|RFC|: **XAXX010101000** if it is a national customer or **XEXX010101000** "
"if it is a foreign customer"
msgstr ""
"|RFC|: **XAXX010101000**, če gre za nacionalno stranko, ali "
"**XEXX010101000**, če gre za tujo stranko"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1005
msgid ":guilabel:`ZIP` code: The same code of the company"
msgstr "Poštna številka :guilabel:`ZIP`: enaka koda kot pri podjetju"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1006
msgid ":guilabel:`Usage`: S01 - Without Fiscal Effects"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uporaba`: S01 - Brez davčnih učinkov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "CFDI to Public Checkbox"
msgstr "Potrditveno polje CFDI za javnost"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1011
msgid ""
"If the final customer doesn't share any details, create a "
"generic :guilabel:`Customer`. The name cannot be `PUBLICO EN GENERAL` or an "
"error will be triggered (it can be, for example, `CLIENTE FINAL`)."
msgstr ""
"Če končna stranka ne deli nobenih podrobnosti, ustvarite splošno "
":guilabel:`Stranko`. Ime ne sme biti `PUBLICO EN GENERAL`, sicer bo sprožena "
"napaka (lahko je na primer `CLIENTE FINAL`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1016
msgid ""
"By default sending the invoice is not allowed if the partner does not have "
"either the *Country* or *Zip code* set, however this is not required if "
"the :guilabel:`CFDI to public` checkbox is active."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto pošiljanje računa ni dovoljeno, če partner nima nastavljene niti "
"*države* niti *poštne številke*, vendar to ni zahtevano, če je potrditveno "
"polje :guilabel:`CFDI za javnost` aktivno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1021
msgid ""
"`Regla 2.7.1.21 Expedición de comprobantes en operaciones con el público en "
"general <https://www.sat.gob.mx/articulo/90959/regla-2.7.1.21>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Regla 2.7.1.21 Expedición de comprobantes en operaciones con el público en "
"general <https://www.sat.gob.mx/articulo/90959/regla-2.7.1.21>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1027
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1465
msgid "Global invoice"
msgstr "Skupinski račun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1029
msgid ""
"If by the end of a certain period of time (that can vary from daily to "
"bimonthly, depending of your company's legal needs and preferences) and the "
"customer still has sales that weren't marked as regular invoices or "
"individual *CFDI to Public* invoices, the |SAT| allows for the creation of a "
"single invoice that can contain all operations, known as a *global invoice*."
msgstr ""
"Če do konca določenega časovnega obdobja (ki se lahko razlikuje od dnevnega "
"do dvotedenskega, odvisno od zakonskih potreb in preferenc vašega podjetja) "
"ima stranka še vedno prodaje, ki niso bile označene kot redni računi ali "
"posamezni računi *CFDI javnosti*, |SAT| omogoča izdelavo enega samega "
"računa, ki lahko vsebuje vse operacije, znanega kot *globalni račun*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1035
msgid ""
"For this process, the :doc:`Sales <../../sales/sales>` app must be installed."
msgstr ""
"Za ta postopek mora biti nameščena aplikacija :doc:`Prodaja <../../sales>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1038
msgid ""
"`Guía de llenado del CFDI global <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/documentos/GuiallenadoCFDIglobal311221.pdf>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Guía de llenado del CFDI global <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/documentos/GuiallenadoCFDIglobal311221.pdf>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1044
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Global Invoice Serie` is specific to each branch or company "
"and is used to define the sequence of global invoices. To configure it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`, and navigate "
"to the :guilabel:`MX Electronic invoicing` section. The :guilabel:`Global "
"Invoice Serie` field can be found within the :guilabel:`Service Tax "
"Administration (SAT)` section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Globalna serija računov` je specifična za vsako podružnico ali "
"podjetje in se uporablja za določitev zaporedja globalnih računov. Za "
"nastavitev pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve` in se pomaknite do razdelka :guilabel:`MX Elektronsko izdajanje "
"računov`. Polje :guilabel:`Globalna serija računov` najdete v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Davčna uprava storitev (SAT)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Accounting setting with an MX company."
msgstr "Računovodska nastavitev s podjetjem MX."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1053
msgid "The default sequence for every company/branch is `GINV/`"
msgstr "Privzeto zaporedje za vsako podjetje/podružnico je `GINV/`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1056
msgid "Sales flow"
msgstr "Potek prodaje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1058
msgid ""
"First, create a dedicated journal in :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Journals` to maintain a separate sequence that is used for "
"global invoices, which function as orders when they are created."
msgstr ""
"Najprej ustvarite namenski dnevnik v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Dnevniki`, da ohranite ločeno zaporedje, ki se uporablja "
"za globalne račune, ki delujejo kot naročila, ko so ustvarjeni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1062
msgid ""
"Then, make sure that all the sales orders that need to be signed have the "
"following configurations:"
msgstr ""
"Nato se prepričajte, da imajo vsi prodajni nalogi, ki jih je treba "
"podpisati, naslednje konfiguracije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1064
msgid ":guilabel:`CFDI to Public` checkbox enabled"
msgstr "Potrjeno potrditveno polje :guilabel:`CFDI to Public`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1065
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Status` marked as :guilabel:`To Invoice`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Stanje računa` označeno kot :guilabel:`Za izdajo računa`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1067
msgid ""
"After this, go to :menuselection:`Sales --> To Invoice --> Orders to "
"Invoice`, select all relevant sales orders and press :guilabel:`Create "
"Invoices`. Make sure to disable the :guilabel:`Consolidated Billing` "
"checkbox and click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Po tem pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodaja --> Za izdajo računa --> Naročila "
"za izdajo računa`, izberite vsa ustrezna prodajna naročila in pritisnite "
":guilabel:`Ustvari račune`. Prepričajte se, da onemogočite potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`Konsolidirano obračunavanje` in kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"osnutek računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1071
msgid ""
"Odoo will redirect to a list of invoices. Select all of them and in "
"the :icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Actions` drop-down menu "
"select :guilabel:`Post entries`. Select all posted invoices again and go "
"back to the  :icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Actions` drop-down menu to "
"select :guilabel:`Create Global Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo vas bo preusmeril na seznam računov. Izberite vse in v spustnem meniju "
":icon:`fa-gear` :guilabel:`Dejanja` izberite :guilabel:`Objavi vnose`. "
"Ponovno izberite vse objavljene račune in se vrnite v spustni meni :icon:`fa-"
"gear` :guilabel:`Dejanja`, kjer izberite :guilabel:`Ustvari globalni račun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1076
msgid ""
"In the wizard, select the :guilabel:`Periodicity` indicated by a "
"professional accountant and press :guilabel:`Create`. All invoices should be "
"signed under the same XML file, with the same :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`."
msgstr ""
"V čarovniku izberite :guilabel:`Periodičnost`, ki jo je navedel pooblaščeni "
"računovodja, in pritisnite :guilabel:`Ustvari`. Vsi računi morajo biti "
"podpisani v isti datoteki XML z istim :guilabel:`Fiscal Folio`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1081
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Show` in the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab to display a list with "
"all related invoices."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Prikaži` na zavihku :guilabel:`CFDI`, da prikažete "
"seznam vseh povezanih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1082
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Cancel` in the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab to cancel the global "
"invoice in both the |SAT| and Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Prekliči` na zavihku :guilabel:`CFDI`, da prekličete "
"globalni račun v |SAT| in Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1086
msgid ""
"Global invoices created this way won't have a **PDF** in them as their "
"information is already within Odoo and is not to be seen by a customer."
msgstr ""
"Globalni računi, ustvarjeni na ta način, ne bodo imeli **PDF**, saj so "
"njihove informacije že v Odoo in niso namenjene strankam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1092
msgid "Electronic accounting (reporting)"
msgstr "Elektronsko računovodstvo (poročanje)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1094
msgid ""
"For Mexico, `Electronic Accounting <https://www.sat.gob.mx/aplicacion/42150/"
"envia-tu-contabilidad-electronica>`_ refers to the obligation to keep "
"accounting records and entries through electronic means, and to enter "
"accounting information on a monthly basis, through the |SAT| website."
msgstr ""
"Za Mehiko se `elektronsko računovodstvo <https://www.sat.gob.mx/aplicacion/"
"42150/envia-tu-contabilidad-electronica>`_ nanaša na obveznost vodenja "
"računovodskih evidenc in vnosov v elektronski obliki ter mesečnega vnosa "
"računovodskih informacij prek spletnega mesta |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1099
msgid "It consists of three main XML files:"
msgstr "Sestoji iz treh glavnih datotek XML:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1101
msgid "The updated list of the chart of accounts that is currently in use"
msgstr "Posodobljen seznam kontnega načrta, ki je trenutno v uporabi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1102
msgid ""
"A monthly trial balance, plus a closing entry report, also known as: *Trial "
"Balance Month 13*"
msgstr ""
"Mesečno poskusno bilanco plus poročilo o končnih vnosih, znano tudi kot: "
"*poskusna bilanca mesec 13*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1103
msgid ""
"An export of the journal entries in the general ledger (optional except in "
"the case of a compulsory audit)"
msgstr ""
"Izvoz vnosov dnevnika v glavno knjigo (neobvezno, razen v primeru obvezne "
"revizije)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1106
msgid ""
"The resulting XML files follow the requirements of the `Anexo Técnico de "
"Contabilidad Electrónica 1.3 <https://www.gob.mx/cms/uploads/attachment/file/"
"151135/Anexo24_05012015.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"Nastale datoteke XML sledijo zahtevam `Anexo Técnico de Contabilidad "
"Electrónica 1.3 <https://www.gob.mx/cms/uploads/attachment/file/151135/"
"Anexo24_05012015.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1109
msgid ""
"In addition to this, it is possible to generate the `DIOT <https://"
"www.sat.gob.mx/declaracion/74295/presenta-tu-declaracion-informativa-de-"
"operaciones-con- terceros-(diot)->`_: a report of vendors' journal entries "
"that involve IVA taxes that can be exported in a TXT file."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega je mogoče generirati `DIOT <https://www.sat.gob.mx/declaracion/"
"74295/presenta-tu-declaracion-informativa-de-operaciones-con- terceros-"
"(diot)->`_: poročilo o vnosih dnevnika dobaviteljev, ki vključujejo davke "
"IVA in jih je mogoče izvoziti v datoteko TXT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1115
msgid "In order to use these reports, the following modules must be installed:"
msgstr "Za uporabo teh poročil morajo biti nameščeni naslednji moduli:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1117
msgid ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican Localization Reports` `l10n_mx_reports`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican Localization Reports` `l10n_mx_reports`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1118
msgid ":guilabel:`Mexico - Month 13 Trial Balance` `l10n_mx_reports_closing`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Mexico - Month 13 Trial Balance` `l10n_mx_reports_closing`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1119
msgid ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican XML Polizas Export` `l10n_mx_xml_polizas`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican XML Polizas Export` `l10n_mx_xml_polizas`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1121
msgid ""
"The *chart of accounts* and the *Trial Balance Month 13* reports can be "
"found in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Trial Balance`. The "
"*DIOT* report can be found in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Tax Report`."
msgstr ""
"Poročila *kontni načrt* in *Poskusna bilanca mesec 13* najdete v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Poskusna bilanca`. Poročilo "
"*DIOT* najdete v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Davčno "
"poročilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1126
msgid ""
"The specific characteristics and obligations of the reports that you send "
"might change according to your fiscal regime. Always contact your accountant "
"before sending any documents to the government."
msgstr ""
"Posebne značilnosti in obveznosti poročil, ki jih pošiljate, se lahko "
"spremenijo glede na vaš davčni režim. Vedno se posvetujte s svojim "
"računovodjem, preden pošljete kakršne koli dokumente državi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1135
msgid ""
"The :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` "
"in Mexico follows a specific pattern based on |SAT|'s' `Código agrupador de "
"cuentas <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/fichas_tematicas/buzon_tributario/"
"Documents/codigo_agrupador.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Kontni načrt <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` v Mehiki "
"sledi posebnemu vzorcu, ki temelji na |SAT|-ovem `Código agrupador de "
"cuentas <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/fichas_tematicas/buzon_tributario/"
"Documents/codigo_agrupador.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1139
msgid ""
"It is possible to create any account, as long as it respects |SAT|'s "
"encoding group: the pattern is `NNN.YY.ZZ` or `NNN.YY.ZZZ`."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je ustvariti katerikoli račun, če spoštuje |SAT|-ovo skupino "
"kodiranja: vzorec je `NNN.YY.ZZ` ali `NNN.YY.ZZZ`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1143
msgid "Some examples are `102.01.99` or `401.01.001`."
msgstr "Nekateri primeri so `102.01.99` ali `401.01.001`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1145
msgid ""
"When a new account is created in :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Chart of Accounts`, with the |SAT| encoding group pattern, "
"the correct grouping code appears in :guilabel:`Tags`, and the account "
"appears in the *COA* report."
msgstr ""
"Ko je nov račun ustvarjen v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Kontni načrt` z vzorcem skupine kodiranja |SAT|, se "
"pravilna koda združevanja pojavi v :guilabel:`Oznakah` in račun se pojavi v "
"poročilu *COA*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1149
msgid ""
"Once all accounts are created, make sure the correct :guilabel:`Tags` are "
"added as these mark the nature of the account."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi računi ustvarjeni, preverite, ali so dodane pravilne "
":guilabel:`Oznake`, saj te označujejo naravo računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1153
msgid ""
"It is not advised use any pattern that ends a section with a 0 (such as "
"`100.01.01`, `301.00.003` or `604.77.00`). This triggers errors in the "
"report. By default Odoo will mark the accounts as yellow if the numbering "
"will cause issue later on, this is to prevent reports from providing "
"inaccurate data."
msgstr ""
"Ni priporočljivo uporabljati katerega koli vzorca, ki se konča z 0 (kot so "
"`100.01.01`, `301.00.003` ali `604.77.00`). To povzroči napake v poročilu. "
"Odoo bo privzeto označil račune z rumeno, če bo oštevilčenje kasneje "
"povzročilo težave, to je preprečevanje poročil pred zagotavljanjem netočnih "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1158
msgid ""
"Once everything is set up, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --"
"> Trial Balance`, and click the :guilabel:`COA SAT (XML)` button to generate "
"an XML file containing all of the accounts. This XML file is ready to upload "
"to the |SAT| website."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vse nastavljeno, pojdite v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročanje --> Poskusna bilanca` in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`COA SAT (XML)`, "
"da ustvarite datoteko XML, ki vsebuje vse račune. Ta datoteka XML je "
"pripravljena za nalaganje na spletno stran |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1167
msgid ""
"The trial balance reports the initial balance, credit, and total balance of "
"your accounts, provided that you added their correct :ref:`encoding group "
"<l10n_mx/chart-of-accounts>`."
msgstr ""
"Poskusna bilanca prikazuje začetno stanje, dobropis in skupno stanje vaših "
"računov, če ste dodali njihovo pravilno :ref:`skupino kodiranja <l10n_mx/"
"chart-of-accounts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1170
msgid ""
"To generate an XML file of the trial balance, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Trial Balance`, select the "
"date, and click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(action menu)`, then "
"select :guilabel:`SAT (XML)`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti datoteko XML poskusne bilance, pojdite v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Poskusna bilanca`, izberite "
"datum in kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(meni dejanj)`, nato izberite "
":guilabel:`SAT (XML)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Trial balance report."
msgstr "Poročilo poskusne bilance."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1178
msgid "Odoo does not generate the *Balanza de Comprobación Complementaria*."
msgstr "Odoo ne ustvari *Balanza de Comprobación Complementaria*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1183
msgid "Month 13"
msgstr "Mesec 13"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1185
msgid ""
"An additional report is the *Month 13*: a closing balance sheet that shows "
"any adjustments or movements made in the accounting to close the year."
msgstr ""
"Dodatno poročilo je *Mesec 13*: zaključna bilanca stanja, ki prikazuje vse "
"prilagoditve ali gibanja v računovodstvu za zaprtje leta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1188
msgid ""
"To generate this XML document, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Accounting --> Journal Entries`, and create a new document. Here, add all "
"amounts to modify, and balance the debit and/or credit of each one."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti ta dokument XML, pojdite v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Računovodstvo --> Knjižbe` in ustvarite "
"nov dokument. Tukaj dodajte vse zneske za spremembo in uskladite breme in/"
"ali dobropis vsakega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1192
msgid ""
"After this is done, go to the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and check "
"the :guilabel:`Month 13 Closing` field. If needed, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Trial Balance` and select "
"the date :guilabel:`Month 13`, where it is possible to see the the total "
"amount of the year, plus all the additions of the journal entry. To generate "
"the XML file, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(action menu)`, then "
"select :guilabel:`SAT (XML)`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to končano, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Druge informacije` in "
"označite polje :guilabel:`Zaprtje meseca 13`. Po potrebi pojdite v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Poskusna bilanca` in "
"izberite datum :guilabel:`Mesec 13`, kjer je mogoče videti skupni znesek "
"leta in vse dodatke knjižbe. Če želite ustvariti datoteko XML, kliknite "
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(meni dejanj)`, nato izberite :guilabel:`SAT (XML)"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1203
msgid ""
"By law, all transactions in Mexico must be recorded digitally. Since Odoo "
"automatically creates all the underlying journal entries of all invoices and "
"payments, simply exporting the general ledger complies with |SAT|'s audits "
"and/or tax refunds."
msgstr ""
"Po zakonu morajo biti vse transakcije v Mehiki zabeležene digitalno. Ker "
"Odoo samodejno ustvari vse osnovne knjižbe vseh računov in plačil, preprosto "
"izvažanje glavne knjige ustreza |SAT|-ovim revizijam in/ali vračilom davka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1208
msgid ""
"The report can be filtered by period or by journal, depending on the need."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo je mogoče filtrirati po obdobju ali po dnevniku, odvisno od potrebe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1210
msgid ""
"To create the XML, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"General Ledger`, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(action menu)`, then "
"click :guilabel:`XML (Polizas)`. Then, select among four :guilabel:`Export` "
"types:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti XML, pojdite v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročanje --> Glavna knjiga`, kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(meni "
"dejanj)`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`XML (Polizas)`. Nato izberite med štirimi "
"vrstami :guilabel:`Izvoza`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1214
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax audit`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Davčna revizija`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1215
msgid ":guilabel:`Audit certification`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Certifikat revizije`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1216
msgid ":guilabel:`Return of goods`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vračilo blaga`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1217
msgid ":guilabel:`Compensation`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Kompenzacija`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1219
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Tax audit` or :guilabel:`Audit certification`, add "
"the :guilabel:`Order Number` provided by the |SAT|. For :guilabel:`Return of "
"goods` or :guilabel:`Compensation`, add the :guilabel:`Process Number`, also "
"provided by the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"Za :guilabel:`Davčno revizijo` ali :guilabel:`Certifikat revizije` dodajte "
":guilabel:`Številko naročila`, ki jo zagotovi |SAT|. Za :guilabel:`Vračilo "
"blaga` ali :guilabel:`Kompenzacijo` dodajte :guilabel:`Številko postopka`, "
"ki jo prav tako zagotovi |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1224
msgid ""
"To see this report without sending it, use `ABC6987654/99` for "
"the :guilabel:`Order Number` or `AB123451234512` for the :guilabel:`Process "
"Number`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled tega poročila brez pošiljanja uporabite `ABC6987654/99` za "
":guilabel:`Številko naročila` ali `AB123451234512` za :guilabel:`Številko "
"postopka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1230
msgid "DIOT report"
msgstr "Poročilo DIOT"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1232
msgid ""
"The DIOT (Declaración Informativa de Operaciones con Terceros / *Informative "
"Declaration of Operations with Third Parties*) is an additional obligation "
"with the |SAT|, where the current status of creditable and non-creditable "
"payments, withholdings, import taxes, and refunds of VAT from your vendor "
"bills are provided to the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"DIOT (Declaración Informativa de Operaciones con Terceros / *Informativna "
"izjava o poslih s tretjimi osebami*) je dodatna obveznost do |SAT|, kjer se "
"|SAT| predloži trenutno stanje plačil, ki se lahko odštejejo in ne morejo "
"odšteti, odtegljaji, uvozne dajatve in povračila DDV iz računov dobaviteljev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1238
msgid "Since July 2025 the new 2025 version of the report is available."
msgstr "Od julija 2025 je na voljo nova različica poročila za leto 2025."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1240
msgid ""
"Unlike other reports, the |DIOT| is uploaded to a website provided by the |"
"SAT| that contains the A-29 form. In Odoo, you can download the records of "
"your transactions as a TXT file that can be uploaded to the form, avoiding "
"direct capture of this data."
msgstr ""
"Za razliko od drugih poročil se |DIOT| naloži na spletno stran, ki jo "
"zagotavlja |SAT| in vsebuje obrazec A-29. V Odoo lahko prenesete zapise "
"svojih transakcij kot datoteko TXT, ki jo je mogoče naložiti v obrazec, s "
"čimer se izognete neposrednemu zajemanju teh podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1244
msgid ""
"The transactions file contains the total amount of the payments registered "
"in vendor bills, broken down into the corresponding types of IVA. "
"The :guilabel:`VAT`, :guilabel:`Country` and :guilabel:`Type of operation` "
"fields are mandatory for all vendors."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka transakcij vsebuje skupni znesek plačil, registriranih na računih "
"dobaviteljev, razčlenjenih na ustrezne vrste IVA. Polja :guilabel:`DDV`, "
":guilabel:`Država` in :guilabel:`Vrsta poslovanja` so obvezna za vse "
"dobavitelje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1248
msgid ""
"To download the |DIOT| report as a TXT file, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reports --> Tax Return`. Select the "
"desired month, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(action menu)`, and "
"select :guilabel:`DIOT (TXT)`."
msgstr ""
"Za prenos poročila |DIOT| kot datoteke TXT pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročila --> Davčna napoved`. Izberite "
"želeni mesec, kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(meni dejanj)` in izberite "
":guilabel:`DIOT (TXT)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1252
msgid ""
"In case new taxes are created on the database, there are two types of tags, "
"the tags containing **tax** must go into the tax distribution and the ones "
"with the base name go on the base of the tax. All lines of a VAT tax "
"**must** containing at least one tax grid."
msgstr ""
"V primeru, da so v zbirki podatkov ustvarjeni novi davki, obstajata dve "
"vrsti oznak: oznake, ki vsebujejo **tax**, morajo iti v razporeditev davka, "
"oznake z osnovnim imenom pa v osnovo davka. Vse vrstice davka DDV **morajo** "
"vsebovati vsaj eno davčno mrežo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "DIOT (TXT) download button."
msgstr "Gumb za prenos DIOT (TXT)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1260
msgid ""
"It is required to fill in the :guilabel:`Type of Operation` field in "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab of each vendor to prevent validation errors. "
"Make sure that foreign customers have their :guilabel:`Country` set."
msgstr ""
"Za preprečitev napak pri preverjanju je treba izpolniti polje "
":guilabel:`Vrsta poslovanja` v zavihku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` vsakega "
"dobavitelja. Prepričajte se, da imajo tuji kupci nastavljeno "
":guilabel:`Državo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "DIOT information on a vendor contact."
msgstr "Podatki DIOT na kontaktu dobavitelja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1267
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`87 - Global Operations` will cause the final TXT file "
"to merge all vendors that are part of the global operations under one "
"generic VAT: *XAXX010101000*."
msgstr ""
"Izbira :guilabel:`87 - Globalna poslovanja` bo povzročila, da bo končna "
"datoteka TXT združila vse dobavitelje, ki so del globalnih poslovanja, pod "
"eno splošno identifikacijsko številko za DDV: *XAXX010101000*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1273
msgid "External trade"
msgstr "Zunanja trgovina"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1275
msgid ""
"The external trade is a complement to a regular invoice that adds certain "
"values in both the XML and PDF, to invoices with a foreign customer "
"according to `SAT regulations <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/"
"Paginas/complemento_comercio_exterior.htm>`_, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Zunanja trgovina je dodatek k običajnemu računu, ki doda določene vrednosti "
"v XML in PDF računom s tujimi kupci v skladu s `predpisi SAT <http://"
"omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/"
"complemento_comercio_exterior.htm>`_, kot so:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1279
msgid "The specific address of the receiver and the sender"
msgstr "Natančen naslov prejemnika in pošiljatelja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1280
msgid ""
"The addition of a :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` that identifies the type of "
"product"
msgstr "Dodajanje :guilabel:`Tarifne frakcije`, ki identificira vrsto izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1281
msgid ""
"The correct :doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms` (International "
"Commercial Terms)"
msgstr ""
"Pravilni :doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/incoterms` (mednarodni "
"trgovinski pogoji)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1282
msgid ""
"And more, such as the *certificate of origin* and *special units of measure*"
msgstr "In več, kot je *potrdilo o izvoru* in *posebne merske enote*"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1284
msgid ""
"This allows the correct identification of exporters and importers, in "
"addition to expanding the description of the merchandise sold."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča pravilno identifikacijo izvoznikov in uvoznikov, poleg razširitve "
"opisa prodanega blaga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1287
msgid ""
"Since January 1, 2018, external trade is a requirement for taxpayers who "
"carry export operations of type A1. While the current CFDI is 4.0, the "
"external trade is currently on version 2.0."
msgstr ""
"Od 1. januarja 2018 je zunanja trgovina zahteva za davčne zavezance, ki "
"izvajajo izvozne operacije tipa A1. Medtem ko je trenutni CFDI 4.0, je "
"zunanja trgovina trenutno na različici 2.0."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1291
msgid ""
"In order to use this feature, the :guilabel:`EDI for Mexico (Advanced "
"Features)` `l10n_mx_edi_extended` module must be installed."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo te funkcije mora biti nameščen modul :guilabel:`EDI za Mehiko "
"(napredne funkcije)` `l10n_mx_edi_extended`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1295
msgid ""
"Before installing, make sure your business needs to use this feature. "
"Consult your accountant first, if needed, before installing any modules."
msgstr ""
"Pred namestitvijo se prepričajte, da vaše podjetje potrebuje to funkcijo. "
"Najprej se posvetujte s svojim računovodjem, če je potrebno, preden "
"namestite kakršne koli module."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1298
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`CFDI to public` checkbox must be ticked when creating foreign "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje :guilabel:`CFDI za javnost` mora biti označeno pri "
"ustvarjanju tujih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1306
msgid ""
"To configure your company contact for external trade, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`, remove the "
"default :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` filter, and select "
"your :guilabel:`Company` name. While the CFDI 4.0 requirements require "
"adding a valid :guilabel:`ZIP` code in the company contact record, the "
"external trade complement adds the requirement that the :guilabel:`City` and "
"the :guilabel:`State` must also be valid. All three fields must coincide "
"with the `Official SAT Catalog for Carta Porte <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/catalogos_emision_cfdi_complemento_ce.htm>`_, or "
"it will produce an error."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo kontakta vašega podjetja za zunanjo trgovino pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Stranke`, odstranite privzeti "
"filter :guilabel:`Računi strankam` in izberite ime vašega "
":guilabel:`Podjetja`. Medtem ko zahteve CFDI 4.0 zahtevajo dodajanje "
"veljavne :guilabel:`poštne številke` v zapis kontakta podjetja, dodatek za "
"zunanjo trgovino dodaja zahtevo, da morata biti tudi :guilabel:`Mesto` in "
":guilabel:`Stanje` veljavna. Vsa tri polja se morajo ujemati z `uradnim "
"katalogom SAT za Carta Porte <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/"
"Paginas/catalogos_emision_cfdi_complemento_ce.htm>`_, sicer bo prišlo do "
"napake."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1316
msgid ""
"Add the :guilabel:`City` and :guilabel:`State` in the company's *contact "
"record*, not in the company record itself."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte :guilabel:`Mesto` in :guilabel:`Stanje` v *zapis kontakta* podjetja, "
"ne v sam zapis podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1319
msgid ""
"On the contact record, the optional fields :guilabel:`Locality` "
"and :guilabel:`Colony Code` can also be filled. These two fields also have "
"to coincide with the data in the |SAT|."
msgstr ""
"V zapisu kontakta je mogoče izpolniti tudi neobvezni polji "
":guilabel:`Lokaliteta` in :guilabel:`Koda kolonije`. Tudi ti dve polji se "
"morata ujemati s podatki v |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1322
msgid ""
"To configure the contact data for a foreign receiving client, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers`, and select the "
"foreign client's contact. The contact must have the following fields "
"completed to avoid errors:"
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo kontaktnih podatkov tujega prejemnega odjemalca pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Stranke` in izberite kontakt "
"tujega odjemalca. Kontakt mora imeti izpolnjena naslednja polja, da se "
"izognete napakam:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1326
msgid ""
"The entire company :guilabel:`Address`, including a valid :guilabel:`ZIP` "
"code and the foreign :guilabel:`Country`."
msgstr ""
"Celoten :guilabel:`Naslov` podjetja, vključno z veljavno :guilabel:`poštno "
"številko` in tujo :guilabel:`državo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1328
msgid ""
"The foreign :guilabel:`RFC` (tax identification number), in the correct "
"format (for example: Colombia `123456789-1`)"
msgstr ""
"Tuji :guilabel:`RFC` (davčna identifikacijska številka) v pravilni obliki "
"(na primer: Kolumbija `123456789-1`)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1330
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, to activate the :guilabel:`Needs "
"external trade?` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Prodaja in nabava` označite potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`Potrebuje zunanjo trgovino?`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1334
msgid ""
"In the resulting XML and PDF files, the :guilabel:`VAT` is automatically "
"replaced by the generic VAT for abroad transactions: `XEXX010101000`."
msgstr ""
"V nastalih datotekah XML in PDF se :guilabel:`DDV` samodejno nadomesti z "
"generičnim DDV za tuje transakcije: `XEXX010101000`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1340
msgid ""
"All products involved with external trade have four additional fields that "
"are required, two of which are exclusive to external trade."
msgstr ""
"Vsi izdelki, vključeni v zunanjo trgovino, imajo štiri dodatna polja, ki so "
"obvezna, dve od njih sta izključno za zunanjo trgovino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1343
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Reference` of the product must be set in "
"the :guilabel:`General Information` tab."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Referenca` izdelka mora biti nastavljena v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Splošne informacije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1344
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Weight` of the product in the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab must "
"be more than `0`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Teža` izdelka v zavihku :guilabel:`Zaloga` mora biti več kot `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1345
msgid ""
"The `correct  <https://www.ventanillaunica.gob.mx/vucem/"
"Clasificador.html>`_ :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` of the product must be set "
"in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab for external trade."
msgstr ""
"`Pravilna <https://www.ventanillaunica.gob.mx/vucem/Clasificador.html>`_ "
":guilabel:`Tarifna frakcija` izdelka mora biti nastavljena v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Računovodstvo` za zunanjo trgovino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1347
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab must be set and "
"correspond to the :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` for external trade."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` na zavihku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` mora biti "
"nastavljeno in se mora ujemati s :guilabel:`Tarifno frakcijo` za zunanjo "
"trgovino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Required external trade product fields."
msgstr "Zahtevana polja izdelka za zunanjo trgovino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1354
msgid ""
"If the UoM code of the :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` is `01`, the "
"correct :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` is `kg`."
msgstr ""
"Če je koda mer. enote :guilabel:`Tarifne frakcije` `01`, je pravilna "
":guilabel:`UMT Aduana` `kg`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1356
msgid ""
"If the UoM code of the :guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` is `06`, the "
"correct :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` is `Units`."
msgstr ""
"Če je koda mer. enote :guilabel:`Tarifne frakcije` `06`, je pravilna "
":guilabel:`UMT Aduana` `Units`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1362
msgid ""
"Before creating an invoice, it is important to take into account that "
"external trade invoices require converting product prices into a foreign "
"currency such as USD. Therefore, :doc:`multicurrency <../accounting/"
"get_started/multi_currency>` **must** be enabled with the foreign currency "
"activated in the :guilabel:`Currencies` section. The "
"correct :guilabel:`Service` to run is :guilabel:`[MX] Bank of Mexico`. To "
"convert product prices, create a :doc:`pricelist <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/prices/pricing>` in the foreign currency."
msgstr ""
"Pred ustvarjanjem računa je pomembno upoštevati, da računi za zunanjo "
"trgovino zahtevajo pretvorbo cen izdelkov v tujo valuto, kot je USD. Zato "
"**mora** biti omogočena :doc:`več-valutnost <../accounting/get_started/"
"multi_currency>` z aktivirano tujo valuto v razdelku :guilabel:`Valute`. "
"Pravilna :guilabel:`Storitev` za zagon je :guilabel:`[MX] Bank of Mexico`. "
"Za pretvorbo cen izdelkov ustvarite :doc:`cenik <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/prices/pricing>` v tuji valuti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1369
msgid ""
"Then, with the correct exchange rate set up in :menuselection:`Accounting --"
"> Settings --> Currency`, set the :guilabel:`Incoterm` and the "
"optional :guilabel:`Certificate Source` fields in the "
"invoice's :guilabel:`Other Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Nato z ustreznim menjalnim tečajem, nastavljenim v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> Valuta`, nastavite polja "
":guilabel:`Incoterm` in izbirno :guilabel:`Vir certifikata` na zavihku "
":guilabel:`Druge informacije` računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1374
msgid ""
"While not mandatory, the information will be more complete "
"if :guilabel:`CFDI to public` is also active."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav ni obvezno, bodo informacije popolnejše, če je aktivna tudi možnost "
":guilabel:`CFDI javnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1377
msgid ""
"Finally, confirm the invoice with the same process as a regular invoice, and "
"click the :guilabel:`Send` button to sign it via CFDI."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu potrdite račun z enakim postopkom kot pri običajnem računu in "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Pošlji`, da ga podpišete prek CFDI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1385
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Point of sale <../../sales/point_of_sale>` adaptation of the "
"Mexican Localization enables the creation of invoices that comply with the |"
"SAT| requirements directly from the **POS register**, with the added benefit "
"of creating receipt tickets that allow *self-invoicing* in a special portal "
"and creating global invoices."
msgstr ""
"Prilagoditev :doc:`Prodajna točka <../../sales/point_of_sale>` mehiške "
"lokalizacije omogoča ustvarjanje računov, ki ustrezajo zahtevam |SAT| "
"neposredno iz **blagajne Prodajne točke**, z dodatno prednostjo ustvarjanja "
"potrdil, ki omogočajo *samoobračunavanje* v posebnem portalu, in ustvarjanja "
"globalnih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1393
msgid "Point of sale flow"
msgstr "Potek prodajne točke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1395
msgid ""
"On top of the standard :ref:`Point of Sale configuration <pos/use/"
"settings>`, the Mexican localization requires each payment method to be "
"configured with a correct :guilabel:`Payment Way` as well as a :guilabel:`Re-"
"invoicing account` to handle the accounting for invoices with the invoicing "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Poleg standardne :ref:`konfiguracije prodajne točke <pos/use/settings>` "
"mehxiška lokalizacija zahteva, da je vsak način plačila konfiguriran s "
"pravilnim :guilabel:`Načinom plačila` ter :guilabel:`Računom za ponovno "
"izdajo računov` za obravnavo računovodstva za račune s portalom za izdajanje "
"računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1401
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo creates pre-configured payment methods for cash, credit "
"card, and debit card and assigns the :guilabel:`402.04.01 Re-invoicing` "
"account as default for re-invoicing."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto Odoo ustvari vnaprej konfigurirane načine plačila za gotovino, "
"kreditno kartico in debit kartico ter dodeli račun :guilabel:`402.04.01 Re-"
"invoicing` kot privzeti za ponovno izdajo računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1404
msgid ""
"While selling on the **Point of Sale**, click the :guilabel:`Customer` "
"button to either create or select a customer. Here it is possible to review "
"customer invoicing information (such as the |RFC| or :guilabel:`Fiscal "
"Regime`) and even modify it directly inside the session."
msgstr ""
"Med prodajo v **Prodajni točki** kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Stranka`, da "
"ustvarite ali izberete stranko. Tukaj je mogoče pregledati informacije o "
"izdajanju računov stranke (kot sta |RFC| ali :guilabel:`Davčni režim`) in "
"jih celo neposredno spremeniti znotraj seje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1408
msgid ""
"After selecting a customer, tick the :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Invoice` checkbox. This opens a menu to select "
"the :guilabel:`Usage` and to define if it is an invoice to the public. Click "
"confirm, select the payment method, and then click validate to complete the "
"order. The PDF is then downloaded and it is possible to send the invoice via "
"mail to the final customer alongside the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Po izbiri stranke označite potrditveno polje :icon:`fa-file-text-o` "
":guilabel:`Račun`. To odpre meni za izbiro :guilabel:`Uporabe` in za "
"določitev, ali gre za račun za javnost. Kliknite potrditev, izberite način "
"plačila in nato kliknite potrdi, da dokončate naročilo. PDF se nato prenese "
"in račun je mogoče poslati po e-pošti končni stranki skupaj z računi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1415
msgid ""
"To create invoices from orders, go to the :guilabel:`Orders` menu, select "
"the order, click :guilabel:`Load Order`, and tick the :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Invoice` checkbox. This opens the same menu for "
"the :guilabel:`Usage` and :guilabel:`CFDI to Public`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti račune iz naročil, pojdite na meni :guilabel:`Naročila`, "
"izberite naročilo, kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži naročilo` in označite "
"potrditveno polje :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Račun`. To odpre isti "
"meni za :guilabel:`Uporabo` in :guilabel:`CFDI javnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Invoice Configuration for Point of Sale."
msgstr "Konfiguracija računa za prodajno točko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1422
msgid ""
"To sign a credit note automatically, tick the :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Invoice` checkbox when processing a :ref:`refund <pos/use/"
"refund>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite avtomatsko podpisati dobropis, ob obdelavi :ref:`dobropisa <pos/"
"use/refund>` označite potrditveno polje :icon:`fa-file-text-o` "
":guilabel:`Račun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1426
msgid ""
"Credit notes for returned products will contain the relation "
"type :guilabel:`03 - Devolución de mercancía sobre facturas o traslados "
"previos`."
msgstr ""
"Dobropisi za vrnjene izdelke bodo vsebovali vrsto relacije :guilabel:`03 - "
"Devolución de mercancía sobre facturas o traslados previos`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1430
msgid ""
"In the Mexican localization, positive and negative lines in a **POS** "
"session cannot be mixed."
msgstr ""
"V mehiški lokalizaciji pozitivnih in negativnih vrstic v seji **POS** ni "
"mogoče mešati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1432
msgid ""
"If a |SAT| validation error occurs customer will get a :doc:`Pro-Forma "
"invoice <../../sales/sales/invoicing/proforma>` instead."
msgstr ""
"Če pride do napake pri preverjanju |SAT|, bo stranka namesto tega prejela "
":doc:`predračun <../../sales/sales/invoicing/proforma>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1438
msgid "Self-invoicing portal"
msgstr "Portal za samoizdajanje računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1440
msgid ""
"If the final customer is not sure if they want to have their invoice "
"generated at the exact moment of the sale, it is possible to give them the "
"option of creating a receipt with either a QR code or a URL. To do so, "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Če končna stranka ni prepričana, ali želi, da se račun ustvari točno v "
"trenutku prodaje, ji je mogoče ponuditi možnost ustvarjanja računa s QR kodo "
"ali URL-jem. To storite tako:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1444
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration`."
msgstr "Pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Konfiguracija`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1445
msgid "Select the :guilabel:`Point of Sale`."
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Prodajna točka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1446
msgid "Scroll to the :guilabel:`Bills & Receipts` section."
msgstr "Pomaknite se do odseka :guilabel:`Računi in potrdila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1447
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Self-service invoicing`."
msgstr "Omogočite :guilabel:`Samopoštretno izdajanje računov`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1448
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Print` field to :guilabel:`QR code`, :guilabel:`URL`, "
"or :guilabel:`QR code + URL`."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite polje :guilabel:`Natisni` na :guilabel:`QR koda`, :guilabel:`URL` "
"ali :guilabel:`QR koda + URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1451
msgid ""
"Customers who scan this QR code or follow the URL will access to a menu "
"where they can add their fiscal information, including the *Usage* and "
"*Fiscal Regime* once they enter the five digit code that is also provided on "
"the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Stranke, ki skenirajo to QR kodo ali sledijo URL-ju, bodo dostopale do "
"menija, kjer lahko dodajo svoje davčne informacije, vključno z *uporabo* in "
"*davčnim režimom*, ko vnesejo petmestno kodo, ki je prav tako navedena na "
"potrdilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1455
msgid ""
"On the journal entries of the session, the previously selected **Re-"
"invoicing account** will be used to handle reversals of the sales entries "
"when invoices are requested as well as be used as a sales account for the "
"new invoices."
msgstr ""
"Pri knjiženju seje bo prejšnji izbrani **Račun za ponovno izdajo** "
"uporabljen za obravnavo stornacij prodajnih vnosov, ko so zahtevani računi, "
"in kot prodajni račun za nove račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1460
msgid ":doc:`../../sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1467
msgid ""
"As with regular sales orders, global invoices can also be created from the "
"POS register."
msgstr ""
"Kot pri običajnih prodajnih naročilih lahko tudi skupne račune ustvarite iz "
"blagajne."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1469
msgid ""
"For this, make sure not to select a customer or the invoice option in the "
"payment menu and go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`. "
"There, select all the orders to invoice, click :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` and select :guilabel:`Create Global Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Za to se prepričajte, da v meniju plačila ne izberete stranke ali možnosti "
"za izdajo računa, in pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> "
"Naročila --> Naročila`. Tam izberite vsa naročila za izdajo računa, kliknite "
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in izberite :guilabel:`Ustvari globalni "
"račun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1473
msgid ""
"Like with sales orders, choose the correct :guilabel:`Periodicity` and "
"press :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"Kot pri prodajnih nalogih izberite pravilno :guilabel:`Periodičnost` in "
"pritisnite :guilabel:`Ustvari`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1475
msgid ""
"This attaches an XML file to each of the selected orders. The XML files can "
"be downloaded by going to the :guilabel:`CFDI` tab. If needed, it is "
"possible to cancel the invoice from the same tab."
msgstr ""
"To priloži datoteko XML vsakemu izbranem naročilu. Datoteke XML je mogoče "
"prenesti tako, da greste na zavihek :guilabel:`CFDI`. Po potrebi je mogoče "
"račun preklicati z istega zavihka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1478
msgid ""
"If eventually any of the orders that are part of the global invoice need to "
"be addressed to a customer, it is still possible to send an invoice by "
"opening the POS register, clicking the :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(drop-down "
"menu)`, then click :guilabel:`Orders`. Change the :guilabel:`All active "
"orders` filter to :guilabel:`Paid`, select the order, and click "
"the :icon:`fa-file-text-o` :guilabel:`Invoice` button."
msgstr ""
"Če je treba kateri koli naročili, ki je del skupnega računa, na koncu "
"poslati kupcu, je še vedno mogoče poslati račun tako, da odprete blagajno, "
"kliknete :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`(spustni meni)`, nato kliknete "
":guilabel:`Naročila`. Spremenite filter :guilabel:`Vsa aktivna naročila` v "
":guilabel:`Plačano`, izberite naročilo in kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-file-text-"
"o` :guilabel:`Račun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1485
msgid ""
"Global invoices, just as regular invoices, can only be grouped by physical "
"address. That is determined by the address set on the POS invoice journal, "
"so when attempting to invoice two addresses a warning will come up to warn "
"the user of the error."
msgstr ""
"Globalne račune, enako kot običajne račune, je mogoče združevati samo po "
"fizičnem naslovu. To določa naslov, nastavljen v dnevniku računov POS, zato "
"se pri poskusu izdaje računa za dva naslova prikaže opozorilo, ki uporabnika "
"opozori na napako."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1494
msgid ""
"The eCommerce adaptation of the Mexican Localization provides and extra step "
"to create invoices that comply with the |SAT| requirements "
"on :doc:`eCommerce  <../../websites/ecommerce>` by retrieving the customer "
"data after the **Checkout** and even allowing for the signature of "
"**automatic invoices** after the payment is processed, as well as sending "
"customers the files via email and granting them access to retrieve their PDF "
"file from their own customer portal."
msgstr ""
"Prilagoditev eCommerce mehiške lokalizacije zagotavlja dodaten korak za "
"ustvarjanje računov, ki ustrezajo zahtevam |SAT| na :doc:`eCommerce  <../../"
"websites/ecommerce>`, tako da pridobi podatke o stranki po **zaključku "
"nakupa** in celo omogoča podpisovanje **samodejnih računov** po obdelavi "
"plačila, pa tudi pošiljanje datotek strankam po e-pošti in odobritev dostopa "
"do datoteke PDF z njihovega portala za stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1503
msgid "eCommerce flow"
msgstr "Potek eCommerce"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1505
msgid ""
"During the regular checkout process, a new :guilabel:`Invoicing Info` step "
"appears, where it is possible to request an invoice or not. "
"If :guilabel:`No` is selected, a **CFDI to Public** is created,. "
"If :guilabel:`Yes` is selected, the :guilabel:`RFC`, :guilabel:`Fiscal "
"Regime`, and :guilabel:`Usage` are required in order to get all information "
"in the sales order, where its status will change to :guilabel:`To Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Med običajnim postopkom zaključka nakupa se pojavi nov korak "
":guilabel:`Informacije za izdajo računa`, kjer je mogoče zahtevati račun ali "
"ne. Če je izbrano :guilabel:`Ne`, se ustvari **CFDI za javnost**. Če je "
"izbrano :guilabel:`Da`, so :guilabel:`RFC`, :guilabel:`Davčni režim` in "
":guilabel:`Uporaba` potrebni za pridobitev vseh informacij v prodajnem "
"nalogu, kjer se bo status spremenil v :guilabel:`Za izdajo računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1511
msgid ""
"Additionally the customer can decide whether or not to request :ref:`IEPS "
"Breakdown <l10n/mx/ieps-breakdown>`."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega se lahko stranka odloči, ali bo zahtevala :ref:`razčlenitev IEPS "
"<l10n/mx/ieps-breakdown>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1515
msgid ""
"Make sure to add a :guilabel:`UNSPSC code` to the :ref:`shipping product "
"<ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da dodate :guilabel:`kodo UNSPSC` :ref:`izdelku za dostavo "
"<ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1518
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Automatic Invoicing` is enabled "
"in :menuselection:`Settings --> Website --> Invoicing`, the electronic "
"document will be signed automatically."
msgstr ""
"Če je :guilabel:`Samodejno izdajanje računov` omogočeno v "
":menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Spletna stran --> Izdajanje računov`, bo "
"elektronski dokument samodejno podpisan."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1526
msgid ""
"The **Sales** app contains fields that make invoicing easier, while the "
"fields themselves do not change the sales behavior, they are directly copied "
"when creating an invoice."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija **Prodaja** vsebuje polja, ki olajšajo izdajanje računov, medtem "
"ko sama polja ne spreminjajo vedenja prodaje, se neposredno kopirajo pri "
"ustvarjanju računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1529
msgid "The copied fields are:"
msgstr "Kopirana polja so:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1531
msgid "Payment Way"
msgstr "Način plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1536
msgid ""
"Additionally, it is possible to get a preview of the invoice for validation "
"purposes with the customer by installing the :doc:`pro-forma module <../../"
"sales/sales/invoicing/proforma>`. This module adds the mentioned fields to "
"the sale order as well as:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega je mogoče pridobiti predogled računa za namene preverjanja s "
"stranko z namestitvijo :doc:`modula pro-forma <../../sales/sales/invoicing/"
"proforma>`. Ta modul prodajnemu nalogu doda omenjena polja kot tudi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1540
msgid "Product code"
msgstr "Koda izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1541
msgid "Unit code"
msgstr "Koda enote"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1542
msgid "Fiscal regime"
msgstr "Davčni režim"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1547
msgid "Subscriptions"
msgstr "Naročnine"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1549
msgid ""
"While handling subscriptions, all the sales fields are used to create the "
"recurrent invoices. These are automatically signed and sent via email with "
"the PDF and XML attached with no additional manual actions required."
msgstr ""
"Pri upravljanju naročnin se vsa prodajna polja uporabljajo za ustvarjanje "
"ponavljajočih se računov. Ti so samodejno podpisani in poslani po e-pošti s "
"priloženim PDF in XML brez potrebnih dodatnih ročnih dejanj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1554
msgid ""
"All invoices generated by the subscription app will always be automatically "
"signed with no exceptions."
msgstr ""
"Vsi računi, ustvarjeni z aplikacijo za naročnine, bodo vedno samodejno "
"podpisani brez izjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1560
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "Zaloga"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1565
msgid "Customs numbers"
msgstr "Carinske številke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1567
msgid ""
"A *customs declaration* (Pedimento Aduanero) is a fiscal document that "
"certifies that all contributions to the fiscal entity (the |SAT|) have been "
"paid for, including the import/export of goods."
msgstr ""
"*Carinska deklaracija* (Pedimento Aduanero) je davčni dokument, ki potrjuje, "
"da so bili plačani vsi prispevki davčnemu organu (|SAT|), vključno z uvozom/"
"izvozom blaga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1571
msgid ""
"According to the `Annex 20 <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/"
"Paginas/anexo_20.htm>`_ of CFDI 4.0, in documents where the invoiced goods "
"come from a first-hand import operation, the :guilabel:`Customs Number` "
"field needs to be added to all lines of products involved with the "
"operation, as does the date of the document."
msgstr ""
"V skladu z `Prilogo 20 <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/"
"anexo_20.htm>`_ standarda CFDI 4.0 mora biti v dokumentih, kjer fakturirano "
"blago izvira iz neposredne uvozne operacije, polje :guilabel:`Customs "
"Number` dodano vsem vrsticam izdelkov, vključenih v operacijo, kot tudi "
"datum dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1577
msgid ""
"To do so, the :guilabel:`Odoo Mexico Localization for Stock/Landing` "
"`l10n_mx_edi_landing` module must be installed, in addition to "
"the :doc:`Inventory <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory>`, :doc:`Purchase "
"<../../inventory_and_mrp/purchase>`, and :doc:`Sales <../../sales/sales>` "
"apps."
msgstr ""
"Za to je treba namestiti modul :guilabel:`Mehiška lokalizacija Odoo za "
"zalogo/pristajanje` `l10n_mx_edi_landing` poleg aplikacij :doc:`Zaloga <../"
"../inventory_and_mrp/inventory>`, :doc:`Nabava <../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"purchase>` in :doc:`Prodaja <../../sales/sales>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1582
msgid ""
"Do not confuse this feature with external trade. The customs numbers are "
"directly related to importing goods, while the external trade complement is "
"related to exporting. Consult your accountant first if this feature is "
"needed before doing any modifications."
msgstr ""
"Ne zamenjujte te funkcije z zunanjo trgovino. Carinske številke so "
"neposredno povezane z uvozom blaga, medtem ko je dodatek za zunanjo trgovino "
"povezan z izvozom. Pred kakršnimi koli spremembami se najprej posvetujte s "
"svojim računovodjo, če je ta funkcija potrebna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1589
msgid ""
"In order to track the correct customs number for a specific invoice, Odoo "
"uses :doc:`landed costs <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"inventory_valuation/landed_costs>`. Go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and in the :guilabel:`Valuation` section, make "
"sure that :guilabel:`Landed Costs` is activated."
msgstr ""
"Za sledenje pravilne carinske številke za določen račun Odoo uporablja "
":doc:`dodatne stroške <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/"
"landed_costs>`. Pojdite na :menuselection:`Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve` in v razdelku :guilabel:`Vrednotenje` se prepričajte, da so "
":guilabel:`Dodatni stroški` aktivirani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1595
msgid ""
"It is recommended to add a :guilabel:`Default Journal` to automatically fill "
"the mandatory :guilabel:`Journal` field on landed costs even though landed "
"costs that only add customs numbers without adding :guilabel:`Additional "
"Costs` do not create journal entries."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je dodati :guilabel:`Default Journal`, da se samodejno izpolni "
"obvezno polje :guilabel:`Journal` pri pristajaliških stroških, čeprav "
"pristajališki stroški, ki dodajajo samo carinske številke brez dodajanja "
":guilabel:`Additional Costs`, ne ustvarijo knjiženj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1599
msgid ""
"Configure the **goods-type** products that hold the customs numbers. To do "
"so, create the products and complete these three requirements:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte izdelke tipa **blago**, ki vsebujejo carinske številke. To "
"storite tako, da ustvarite izdelke in izpolnite te tri zahteve:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1602
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tracking` **must** be set to either :guilabel:`By Lots` "
"or :guilabel:`By Unique Serial Number` but **not** :guilabel:`By Quantity`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tracking` **mora** biti nastavljen bodisi na :guilabel:`By Lots` "
"ali :guilabel:`By Unique Serial Number`, vendar **ne** na :guilabel:`By "
"Quantity`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1604
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` **must** be set to :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` **mora** biti nastavljena na "
":guilabel:`Delivered quantities`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1605
msgid ""
":doc:`Valuation by lots/serial numbers <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"inventory_valuation/valuation_by_lots>` **must** be enabled."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Vrednotenje po serijah/serijskih številkah <../../inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/inventory_valuation/valuation_by_lots>` **mora** biti omogočeno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1608
msgid ""
"This will make the field :guilabel:`Customs invoicing` available on "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. Enable the field to use customs numbers with "
"this product."
msgstr ""
"To bo omogočilo polje :guilabel:`Customs invoicing` v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Accounting`. Omogočite polje za uporabo carinskih številk s tem "
"izdelkom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1611
msgid ""
"It is important to make sure the product has a :guilabel:`Product Category` "
"and has the following configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Pomembno je preveriti, da ima izdelek :guilabel:`Product Category` in ima "
"naslednjo konfiguracijo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1614
msgid ":guilabel:`Costing Method`: Either :guilabel:`FIFO` or :guilabel:`AVCO`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Metoda obračuna stroškov`: bodisi :guilabel:`FIFO` ali "
":guilabel:`AVCO`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1615
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Inventory Valuation`: Either :guilabel:`Periodic` "
"or :guilabel:`Perpetual`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Inventory Valuation`: Bodisi :guilabel:`Periodic` ali "
":guilabel:`Perpetual`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1618
msgid ""
"The feature works regardless of whether the :doc:`inventory valuation <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>` is set to "
"either :guilabel:`Periodic (at closing)` or :guilabel:`Perpetual (at "
"invoicing)`."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija deluje ne glede na to, ali je :doc:`vrednotenje zalog <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>` nastavljeno na "
":guilabel:`Periodično (ob zaključku)` ali :guilabel:`Neprekinjeno (ob izdaji "
"računa)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Storable products general configuration."
msgstr "Splošna konfiguracija skladiščnih izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Storable product category configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija kategorije skladiščnih izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1629
msgid "Purchase and sales flow"
msgstr "Tok nabave in prodaje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1631
msgid ""
"After configuring the product, follow the standard :doc:`purchase flow "
"<../../inventory_and_mrp/purchase>`."
msgstr ""
"Po konfiguraciji izdelka sledite standardnemu :doc:`toku nabave <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1634
msgid ""
"Create a purchase order from :menuselection:`Purchase --> Orders --> "
"Purchase Order`. Then, confirm the order to display a :guilabel:`Receipt` "
"smart button. Click the :guilabel:`Receipt` smart button "
"and :guilabel:`Validate` the receipt."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite naročilnico na :menuselection:`Nakup --> Naročila --> "
"Naročilnica`. Nato potrdite naročilo, da se prikaže pametni gumb "
":guilabel:`Prejem`. Kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Prejem` in "
":guilabel:`potrdite` prejem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1638
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Operations --> Landed Costs`, and create "
"a new record. In the :guilabel:`Transfer`, add the receipt that was just "
"validated, and add the :guilabel:`Customs number`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Inventory --> Operations --> Landed Costs` in "
"ustvarite nov zapis. V :guilabel:`Transfer` dodajte ravnokar potrjen prejem "
"in dodajte :guilabel:`Customs number`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1643
msgid ""
"While it is possible to add costs related to the customs number at this "
"stage of the process, it is highly recommended to create a landed cost from "
"a vendor bill from your customs agent. Learn more about :doc:`Landed Costs "
"here <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/landed_costs>`."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je mogoče na tej stopnji postopka dodati stroške, povezane s carinsko "
"številko, je zelo priporočljivo ustvariti dodatne stroške iz dobaviteljevega "
"računa vašega carinskega zastopnika. Več o tem izveste v :doc:`Dodatnih "
"stroških tukaj <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/"
"landed_costs>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1649
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customs number` field is not editable once it is set, and "
"cannot be repeated, however it is possible to fix the number on the lot or "
"serial number later by selecting a different landed cost."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Customs number` ni več uredljivo, ko je nastavljeno, in ga "
"ni mogoče ponoviti, vendar je mogoče pozneje popraviti številko na seriji "
"ali serijski številki z izbiro drugačnih pristajaliških stroškov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Customs number on a landed costs Inventory record."
msgstr "Carinska številka na zapisih pristajalne ocene v zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1656
msgid ""
"The customs number assigned to a specific lot or serial number can be found "
"on the its registry on :menuselection:`Inventory --> Products --> Lots/"
"Serial Numbers`. The :guilabel:`L10N Mx Edi Landed Cost` field can be edited "
"at any time to fix any mistakes that could have occurred when registering "
"the landed cost. Editing the :guilabel:`L10N Mx Edi Landed Cost` field "
"automatically updates the :guilabel:`Customs number` and the name of the lot "
"or serial number."
msgstr ""
"Carinsko številko, dodeljeno določeni seriji ali serijski številki, najdete "
"v njenem registru na :menuselection:`Inventory --> Products --> Lots/Serial "
"Numbers`. Polje :guilabel:`L10N Mx Edi Landed Cost` je mogoče urediti "
"kadarkoli za popravek morebitnih napak, ki bi se lahko pojavile pri "
"registraciji pristajaliških stroškov. Urejanje polja :guilabel:`L10N Mx Edi "
"Landed Cost` samodejno posodobi :guilabel:`Customs number` in ime serije ali "
"serijske številke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1662
msgid ""
"Next, create a sales order and confirm it. Click the :guilabel:`Delivery` "
"smart button that appears, and carefully review the assigned lots/serial "
"numbers to make sure they are the desired values, after "
"that :guilabel:`Validate` the delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Nato ustvarite prodajni nalog in ga potrdite. Kliknite pametni gumb "
":guilabel:`Dostava`, ki se prikaže, ter pazljivo preglejte dodeljene šarže/"
"serijske številke, da se prepričate, da gre za želene vrednosti, nato pa "
":guilabel:`potrdite` dobavnico."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1666
msgid ""
"Finally, :ref:`create an invoice from the sales order <accounting/inv-"
"process/so>`, and confirm it. The invoice lines are created according to the "
"distribution of the delivery order, in cases where more than one customs "
"number were selected, Odoo will split the invoice lines by quantity and "
"customs numbers."
msgstr ""
"Končno :ref:`ustvarite račun iz prodajnega naloga <accounting/inv-process/so>"
"` in ga potrdite. Vrstice računa so ustvarjene v skladu z razporeditvijo "
"naročilnice. V primerih, ko je bila izbrana več kot ena carinska številka, "
"bo Odoo razdelil vrstice računa po količini in carinskih številkah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Customs number on confirmed sales order product."
msgstr "Carinska številka na izdelku potrjenega prodajnega naloga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1679
msgid ""
"A `Carta Porte <https://www.sat.gob.mx/portal/public/tramites/complemento-"
"carta-porte>`_ is a bill of lading: a document that states the type, "
"quantity, and destination of goods being carried."
msgstr ""
"`Carta Porte <https://www.sat.gob.mx/portal/public/tramites/complemento-"
"carta-porte>`_ je tovorni list: dokument, ki navaja vrsto, količino in cilj "
"prevoza blaga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1682
msgid ""
"On July 17th, 2024, version 3.1 of this |CFDI| was implemented for all "
"transportation providers, intermediaries, and owners of goods. Odoo is able "
"to generate a document type \"T\" (Traslado), which, unlike other documents, "
"is created in a delivery order instead of an invoice or payment."
msgstr ""
"17. julija 2024 je bila za vse prevoznike, posrednike in lastnike blaga "
"uvedena različica 3.1 tega |CFDI|. Odoo lahko ustvari dokument tipa \"T\" "
"(Traslado), ki se za razliko od drugih dokumentov ustvari v dobavnici "
"namesto na računu ali plačilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1686
msgid ""
"Odoo can create XML and PDF files with (or without) ground transport, and "
"can process materials that are treated as *Dangerous Hazards*."
msgstr ""
"Odoo lahko ustvari datoteke XML in PDF z (ali brez) cestnega prevoza in "
"lahko obdeluje materiale, ki so obravnavani kot *nevarne snovi*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1689
msgid ""
"In order to print the PDF, the delivery order must be signed by the "
"government and then it can be printed using the :guilabel:`Print Carta "
"Porte` button on the delivery order."
msgstr ""
"Za tiskanje PDF mora biti dobavnica podpisana s strani vlade, nato pa jo je "
"mogoče natisniti z uporabo gumba :guilabel:`Natisni Carta Porte` na "
"dobavnici."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1693
msgid ""
"The PDF file contains a QR code to verify the CCP code for the authorities."
msgstr "Datoteka PDF vsebuje kodo QR za preverjanje kode CCP pri organih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1695
msgid ""
"In order to transport goods between warehouses, the logistic route must "
"contain a **Delivery** type of operation."
msgstr ""
"Za prevoz blaga med skladišči mora logistična pot vsebovati operacijo tipa "
"**Dostava**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1699
msgid ""
":doc:`Inter-warehouse replenishment <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Medskladiščno dopolnjevanje zalog <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/replenishment/resupply_warehouses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1703
msgid ""
"In order to use this feature, the :guilabel:`Mexico - Electronic Delivery "
"Guide` `l10n_mx_edi_stock` module must be installed."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo te funkcije je treba namestiti modul :guilabel:`Mehika - "
"elektronski dobavni vodnik` `l10n_mx_edi_stock`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1706
msgid ""
"Additionally, it is necessary to have the :doc:`Inventory <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` and :doc:`Sales <../../sales/sales>` apps "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega je treba namestiti aplikaciji :doc:`Zaloga <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory>` in :doc:`Prodaja <../../sales/sales>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1710
msgid ""
"Odoo does not support Carta Porte type document type \"I\" (Ingreso), air, "
"train or marine transport."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ne podpira tipa dokumenta Carta Porte \"I\" (Ingreso), zračnega, "
"vlačnega ali pomorskega prevoza."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1713
msgid ""
"Consult your accountant first if this feature is needed before doing any "
"modifications."
msgstr ""
"Če potrebujete to funkcijo, se pred kakršnimi koli spremembami posvetujte s "
"svojim računovodjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1718
msgid ""
"Odoo manages two different types of CFDI type \"T\". Both can be created "
"from either :doc:`incoming shipments or delivery orders <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo upravlja dve različni vrsti CFDI tipa \"T\". Obe je mogoče ustvariti iz "
":doc:`dohodnih pošiljk ali naročil dobave <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1722
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No Federal Highways` is used when the :guilabel:`Distance to "
"Destination` is `less than 30 km <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/cartaporte/"
"Paginas/documentos/PreguntasFrecuentes_Autotransporte.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Brez zveznih avtocest` se uporablja, ko je :guilabel:`Razdalja do "
"cilja` `manjša od 30 km <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/cartaporte/Paginas/"
"documentos/PreguntasFrecuentes_Autotransporte.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1725
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Federal Transport` is used when the :guilabel:`Distance to "
"Destination` exceeds 30 km."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zvezni prevoz` se uporablja, ko :guilabel:`Razdalja do cilja` "
"presega 30 km."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1727
msgid ""
"For No Federal Highways, no other configuration is required beyond the "
"standard requirements of regular invoicing (the |RFC| of the customer, the "
"UNSPSC code, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Za ne-zvezne ceste ni potrebna nobena dodatna konfiguracija poleg "
"standardnih zahtev rednega računovodstva (|RFC| stranke, koda UNSPSC itd.)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1730
msgid ""
"For *Federal Transport*, several configurations have to be added to "
"contacts, vehicle setups, and products. Those configurations are then "
"included in the XML and PDF files."
msgstr ""
"Za *Zvezni prevoz* je treba kontaktom, nastavitvam vozil in izdelkom dodati "
"več konfiguracij. Te konfiguracije so nato vključene v datoteke XML in PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1734
msgid "Contacts and vehicles"
msgstr "Kontakti in vozila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1736
msgid ""
"Like the external trade feature, the :guilabel:`Address` in both the company "
"and the final customer must be complete. The :guilabel:`ZIP` "
"code, :guilabel:`City`, and :guilabel:`State` must coincide with the "
"`Official SAT Catalog for Carta Porte <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/"
"tramitesyservicios/Paginas/catalogos_emision_cfdi_complemento_ce.htm>`_."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot pri funkciji zunanje trgovine mora biti :guilabel:`Naslov` v "
"podjetju in pri končnem kupcu popoln. :guilabel:`Poštna številka`, "
":guilabel:`Mesto` in :guilabel:`Stanje` se morajo ujemati z `uradnim "
"katalogom SAT za Carta Porte <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/"
"Paginas/catalogos_emision_cfdi_complemento_ce.htm>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1742
msgid "The :guilabel:`Locality` field is optional for both addresses."
msgstr "Polje :guilabel:`Locality` je izbirno za oba naslova."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1745
msgid ""
"The origin address used for the delivery guide is set "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Warehouses`. While this "
"is set as the company address by default, you can change it to your correct "
"warehouse address."
msgstr ""
"Naslov izvora, uporabljen za dobavni list, je nastavljen v "
":menuselection:`Zaloga --> Konfiguracija --> Skladišča`. Čeprav je ta "
"privzeto nastavljen kot naslov podjetja, ga lahko spremenite v pravilen "
"naslov skladišča."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1749
msgid ""
"This feature requires the use of :doc:`Fleet <../../hr/fleet/new_vehicle>` "
"to manage vehicles. The vehicle setup is managed directly on the vehicle, "
"and all the required fields are only visible after checking "
"the :guilabel:`L10N Mx Is Freight Vehicle` field."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija zahteva uporabo :doc:`Voznega parka <../../hr/fleet/new_vehicle>"
"` za upravljanje vozil. Nastavitev vozila se upravlja neposredno na vozilu, "
"vsa zahtevana polja pa so vidna šele po označitvi polja :guilabel:`L10N Mx "
"Is Freight Vehicle`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1753
msgid ""
"Checking the :guilabel:`L10N Mx Is Freight Vehicle` field displays "
"the :guilabel:`MX Parameters` tab where the mandatory fields are required to "
"create a correct delivery guide. Additionally the vehicle **must** contain "
"a :guilabel:`License Plate`, a :guilabel:`Model Year`, and "
"a :guilabel:`Driver`."
msgstr ""
"Označitev polja :guilabel:`L10N Mx Is Freight Vehicle` prikaže zavihek "
":guilabel:`MX Parameters`, kjer so obvezna polja potrebna za ustvarjanje "
"pravilnega dobavnega lista. Poleg tega **mora** vozilo vsebovati "
":guilabel:`License Plate`, :guilabel:`Model Year` in :guilabel:`Driver`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1758
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Vehicle Plate Number` and :guilabel:`Number Plate` fields "
"must contain between 5 and 7 characters."
msgstr ""
"Polji :guilabel:`Vehicle Plate Number` in :guilabel:`Number Plate` morata "
"vsebovati med 5 in 7 znakov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1761
msgid ""
"The main driver of the vehicle is set directly on the :guilabel:`Driver` "
"field, and it is possible to add more vehicle operators in "
"the :guilabel:`Intermediaries` section. The only mandatory fields for driver "
"contacts are the :guilabel:`VAT` and :guilabel:`Operator License`."
msgstr ""
"Glavni voznik vozila je nastavljen neposredno v polju :guilabel:`Driver`, "
"dodatne voznike vozila pa je mogoče dodati v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Intermediaries`. Edini obvezni polji za stike voznikov sta "
":guilabel:`VAT` in :guilabel:`Operator License`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Delivery guide vehicle configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija vozila za dobavni list."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1769
msgid ""
"If the vehicle is rented or more intermediaries are required, it is possible "
"to add them in the :guilabel:`Intermediaries` field."
msgstr ""
"Če je vozilo najeto ali so potrebni dodatni posredniki, jih je mogoče dodati "
"v polje :guilabel:`Intermediaries`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1775
msgid ""
"Similar to regular invoicing, all products must have a :guilabel:`UNSPSC "
"category`. In addition to this, there are two extra configurations for "
"products involved in delivery guides:"
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot pri rednem izdajanju računov morajo imeti vsi izdelki "
":guilabel:`kategorijo UNSPSC`. Poleg tega obstajata dve dodatni "
"konfiguraciji za izdelke, vključene v dobavne liste:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1778
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Product Type` must be set as :guilabel:`Storable Product` for "
"stock movements to be created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta izdelka` mora biti nastavljena kot :guilabel:`Izdelek za "
"skladiščenje`, da se ustvarijo premiki zaloge."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1780
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab, the :guilabel:`Weight` field must be more "
"than `0`."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Zaloga` mora biti polje :guilabel:`Weight` večje od `0`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1783
msgid ""
"Creating a delivery guide of a product with the :guilabel:`Weight` set to "
"`0` will trigger an error. As the :guilabel:`Weight` is immediately stored "
"in the delivery order, it is then necessary to return the products and "
"recreate the delivery order (and delivery guide) with the correct values."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje dobavnega lista za izdelek s poljem :guilabel:`Weight`, "
"nastavljenim na `0`, bo sprožilo napako. Ker je :guilabel:`Weight` takoj "
"shranjena v dobavnem nalogu, je nato potrebno vrniti izdelke in ponovno "
"ustvariti dobavni nalog (in dobavni list) s pravilnimi vrednostmi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1789
msgid "Sales and inventory flow"
msgstr "Prodajni in zalogi tok"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1791
msgid ""
"To create a delivery guide, first create and confirm a sales order "
"from :menuselection:`Sales --> Sales Order`. Click the :guilabel:`Delivery` "
"smart button that is generated, and :guilabel:`Validate` the transfer."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje dobavnega lista najprej ustvarite in potrdite prodajni nalog "
"iz :menuselection:`Sales --> Sales Order`. Kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Delivery`, ki je ustvarjen, in :guilabel:`Validate` prenos."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1795
msgid ""
"After the status is set to :guilabel:`Done`, you can edit the transfer, and "
"select the :guilabel:`Transport Type` in the :guilabel:`Additional Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko je stanje nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Končano`, lahko uredite prenos in "
"izberete :guilabel:`Vrsta prevoza` v zavihku :guilabel:`Dodatne informacije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1798
msgid ""
"If using the :guilabel:`No Federal Highways` :guilabel:`Transport Type`, "
"save the transfer, and then click :guilabel:`Generate Delivery Guide`. The "
"resulting XML can be found in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate :guilabel:`Brez zveznih avtocest` :guilabel:`Vrsta prevoza`, "
"shranite prenos in nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari dobavni list`. Nastali "
"XML najdete v pogovornem oknu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1802
msgid ""
"Other than the :guilabel:`UNSPSC` on all products, delivery guides that "
"use :guilabel:`No Federal Highways` do not require any special configuration "
"to be sent to the government, as they are a type \"T\" CFDI with no delivery "
"guide complement."
msgstr ""
"Poleg :guilabel:`UNSPSC` na vseh izdelkih dobavni listi, ki uporabljajo "
":guilabel:`No Federal Highways`, ne zahtevajo nobene posebne konfiguracije "
"za pošiljanje vladi, saj so vrsta \"T\" CFDI brez dodatka dobavnega lista."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1806
msgid ""
"If using the :guilabel:`Federal Transport` :guilabel:`Transport Type`, "
"the :guilabel:`Vehicle Setup` is displayed to be selected. "
"The :guilabel:`Gross vehicle weight` is taken from the :guilabel:`Vehicle "
"setup` configuration where it is possible to add additional :guilabel:`Extra "
"weight` to account for the drivers and luggage."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate :guilabel:`Federal Transport` :guilabel:`Transport Type`, je "
"prikazan :guilabel:`Vehicle Setup` za izbiro. :guilabel:`Gross vehicle "
"weight` je vzeta iz konfiguracije :guilabel:`Vehicle setup`, kjer je mogoče "
"dodati dodatno :guilabel:`Extra weight` za upoštevanje voznikov in prtljage."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1812
msgid ""
"Odoo will calculate the :guilabel:`Gross vehicle weight` with the following "
"formula:"
msgstr "Odoo bo izračunal :guilabel:`Gross vehicle weight` s sledečo formulo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1814
msgid ""
"Gross vehicle weight = Vehicle weight + (Weight + Extra Weight) / 1000\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Gross vehicle weight = Vehicle weight + (Weight + Extra Weight) / 1000\n"
"\n"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1817
msgid ""
"Every delivery requires a value in :guilabel:`Distance to Destination (KM)` "
"greater than `0`. Finally, enter the :guilabel:`Delivery Date` and "
"click :guilabel:`Generate Delivery Guide`."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka dobava zahteva vrednost v :guilabel:`Distance to Destination (KM)`, "
"večjo od `0`. Nazadnje vnesite :guilabel:`Delivery Date` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Generate Delivery Guide`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1821
msgid ""
"By default the :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` is filled and represents the time "
"at which the shipment leaves the warehouse and the :guilabel:`Delivery Date` "
"is the time that the shipment is expected to arrive at its destination. "
"These values are declared in both the XML and PDF."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je izpolnjen :guilabel:`Scheduled Date` in predstavlja čas, ko "
"pošiljka zapusti skladišče, :guilabel:`Delivery Date` pa je čas, ko naj bi "
"pošiljka prispela na cilj. Te vrednosti so navedene tako v XML kot v PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1826
msgid "Dangerous hazards"
msgstr "Nevarne snovi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1828
msgid ""
"Certain values in the :guilabel:`UNSPSC Category` are considered in the "
"`official SAT catalog <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/"
"complemento_carta_porte.htm>`_ as *dangerous hazards*. These categories need "
"additional considerations when creating a delivery guide "
"with :guilabel:`Federal Transport`."
msgstr ""
"Določene vrednosti v :guilabel:`kategoriji UNSPSC` so v `uradnem katalogu "
"SAT <http://omawww.sat.gob.mx/tramitesyservicios/Paginas/"
"complemento_carta_porte.htm>`_ obravnavane kot *nevarne snovi*. Te "
"kategorije zahtevajo dodatne ukrepe pri ustvarjanju dobavnega lista z "
":guilabel:`Zveznim prevozom`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1833
msgid ""
"First, select the product from :menuselection:`Inventory --> Products --> "
"Products`. Then, in the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab, fill "
"the :guilabel:`Hazardous Material Designation Code` and :guilabel:`Hazardous "
"Packaging` fields with the correct code from the |SAT| catalog."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite izdelek iz :menuselection:`Zaloga --> Izdelki --> Izdelki`. "
"Nato v zavihku :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` izpolnite polji :guilabel:`Koda za "
"označevanje nevarnih snovi` in :guilabel:`Embalaža nevarnih snovi` s "
"pravilno kodo iz kataloga |SAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:None
msgid "Delivery guide hazardous material product required fields."
msgstr "Obvezna polja izdelka z nevarnimi snovmi na dobavnem listu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1841
msgid ""
"There exists the possibility that a :guilabel:`UNSPSC Category` may or may "
"not be a dangerous hazard (for example *01010101*). If it is not dangerous, "
"enter `0` in the :guilabel:`Hazardous Material Designation Code` field."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja možnost, da :guilabel:`kategorija UNSPSC` je ali pa ni nevarna snov "
"(na primer *01010101*). Če ni nevarna, vnesite `0` v polje :guilabel:`Koda "
"za označevanje nevarnih snovi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1845
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`MX Parameters`, complete the :guilabel:`Environment Insurer` "
"and :guilabel:`Environment Insurance Policy` as well. After this, continue "
"with the regular process to create a delivery guide."
msgstr ""
