"podatke vnesete v svoje zapise."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Partner identification type."
msgstr "Vrsta identifikacije partnerja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:389
msgid ""
"Additional to the basic information in your products, for the Peruvian "
"localization, the UNSPC Code on the product is a required value to be "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"Poleg osnovnih informacij o vaših izdelkih je za peruansko lokalizacijo koda "
"UNSPC na izdelku zahtevana vrednost, ki jo je treba konfigurirati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "UNSPC Code on products."
msgstr "Koda UNSPC na izdelkih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:402
msgid "EDI Elements"
msgstr "Elementi EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:404
msgid ""
"Once you have configured your master data, the invoices can be created from "
"your sales order or manually. Additional to the basic invoice information "
"described on :doc:`our page about the invoicing process <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/overview>`, there are a couple of fields required as part "
"of the Peru EDI:"
msgstr ""
"Ko ste konfigurirali svoje osnovne podatke, lahko račune ustvarite iz "
"svojega prodajnega naloga ali ročno. Poleg osnovnih informacij o računu, "
"opisanih na :doc:`naši strani o postopku izdajanja računov <../accounting/"
"customer_invoices/overview>`, je kot del peruanskega EDI potrebnih še nekaj "
"polj:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:409
msgid ""
"**Document type**: The default value is “Factura Electronica” but  you can "
"manually change the document type if needed and select Boleta for example."
msgstr ""
"**Vrsta dokumenta**: Privzeta vrednost je \"Factura Electronica\", vendar "
"lahko po potrebi ročno spremenite vrsto dokumenta in izberete na primer "
"Boleta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Invoice document type field on invoices."
msgstr "Polje vrste dokumenta računa na računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:415
msgid ""
"**Operation type**: This value is required for Electronic Invoice and "
"indicates the transaction type, the default value is “Internal Sale” but "
"another value can be selected manually when needed, for example Export of "
"Goods."
msgstr ""
"**Vrsta operacije**: Ta vrednost je zahtevana za elektronski račun in "
"označuje vrsto transakcije. Privzeta vrednost je \"Internal Sale\", vendar "
"je mogoče po potrebi ročno izbrati drugo vrednost, na primer Export of Goods."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Invoice operation type field on invoices."
msgstr "Polje vrste operacije računa na računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:422
msgid ""
