"Ko preverite, da so vse informacije na vašem računu pravilne, lahko "
"nadaljujete s potrditvijo. To dejanje registrira knjigovodsko knjiženje in "
"sproži potek dela elektronskega računa za pošiljanje v OSE in SUNAT. Na vrhu "
"računa se prikaže naslednje sporočilo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Sending of EDI Invoice in blue."
msgstr "Pošiljanje EDI računa v modrem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:440
msgid ""
"Asynchronous means that the document is not sent automatically after the "
"invoice has been posted."
msgstr "Asinhrono pomeni, da dokument ni poslan samodejno po knjiženju računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:445
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:532
msgid "Electronic Invoice Status"
msgstr "Status elektronskega računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:447
msgid ""
"**To be Sent**: Indicates the document is ready to be sent to the OSE, this "
"can be done either automatically by Odoo with a *cron* that runs every hour, "
"or the user can send it immediately by clicking on the button “Sent now”."
msgstr ""
"**Za poslati**: Označuje, da je dokument pripravljen za pošiljanje v OSE. To "
"lahko Odoo opravi samodejno s *cronom*, ki se izvaja vsako uro, ali pa lahko "
"uporabnik dokument pošlje takoj s klikom na gumb »Pošlji zdaj«."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Send EDI manually."
msgstr "Ročno pošlji EDI."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:454
msgid ""
"**Sent**: Indicates the document was sent to the OSE and was successfully "
"validated. As part of the validation a ZIP file is downloaded and a message "
"is logged in the chatter indicating the correct Government validation."
msgstr ""
"**Poslano**: Označuje, da je bil dokument poslan v OSE in uspešno potrjen. V "
"okviru potrditve se prenese datoteka ZIP in v pogovornem oknu se zabeleži "
"sporočilo, ki potrjuje pravilno državno potrditev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Message on chatter when the invoice is valid."
msgstr "Sporočilo v pogovornem oknu, ko je račun veljaven."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:461
msgid ""
"In case there is a validation error the Electronic Invoice status remains in "
"“To be sent” so the corrections can be made and the invoice can be sent "
"again."
msgstr ""
"V primeru napake pri potrjevanju ostane stanje elektronskega računa na »Za "
"poslati«, zato je mogoče opraviti popravke in račun ponovno poslati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:465
msgid ""
"One credit is consumed each time that you send a document for validation, in "
"this sense if an error is detected on an invoice and you send it one more "
"time, two credits are consumed in total."
msgstr ""
"En kredit je porabljen vsakič, ko pošljete dokument v potrditev. To pomeni, "
"da če je na računu odkrita napaka in ga pošljete še enkrat, sta v celoti "
"porabljena dva kredita."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:470
msgid "Common Errors"
msgstr "Pogoste napake"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:472
msgid ""
"There are multiple reasons behind a rejection from the OSE or the SUNAT, "
"when this happens Odoo sends a message at the top of the invoice indicating "
"the error details and in the most common cases a hint to fix the issue."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja več razlogov za zavrnitev s strani OSE ali SUNAT. Ko se to zgodi, "
"Odoo pošlje sporočilo na vrh računa, ki navaja podrobnosti napake, v "
"najpogostejših primerih pa tudi namig za odpravo težave."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:476
msgid "If a validation error is received, you have two options:"
msgstr "Če prejmete napako pri potrjevanju, imate dve možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:478
msgid ""
"In case the error is related to master data on the partner, customer or "
"taxes, you can simply apply the change on the record (example customer "
"identification type) and once it is done click on the Retry button."
msgstr ""
"Če je napaka povezana z matičnimi podatki o partnerju, stranki ali davkih, "
"lahko preprosto spremenite zapis (na primer vrsto identifikacije stranke) in "
"ko je to opravljeno, kliknite gumb Poskusi znova."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:481
msgid ""
"If the error is related to some data recorded on the invoice directly "
"(Operation type, missing data on the invoice lines), the correct solution is "
"to reset the invoice to Draft, apply the changes, and then send the invoice "
"again to the SUNAT for another validation."
msgstr ""
"Če je napaka povezana s kakšnimi podatki, zabeleženimi neposredno na računu "
"(vrsta operacije, manjkajoči podatki v vrsticah računa), je pravilna "
"rešitev, da račun ponastavite na Osnutek, opravite spremembe in nato račun "
"ponovno pošljete v SUNAT za novo potrditev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "List of common errors on invoices."
msgstr "Seznam pogostih napak na računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:488
msgid ""
"For more detail please refert to `Common errors in SUNAT <https://"
"www.nubefact.com/codigos-error-sunat/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti si oglejte `Pogoste napake v SUNAT <https://"
"www.nubefact.com/codigos-error-sunat/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:492
msgid "Invoice PDF Report"
msgstr "Poročilo računa v PDF"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:494
msgid ""
"After the invoice is accepted and validated by the SUNAT, the invoice PDF "
"report can be printed. The report includes a QR code, indicating the invoice "
"is a valid fiscal document."
msgstr ""
"Ko SUNAT račun sprejme in potrdi, je mogoče natisniti poročilo računa v PDF. "
"Poročilo vključuje kodo QR, ki označuje, da je račun veljaven davčni "
"dokument."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Invoice PDF report."
msgstr "Poročilo računa v PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:501
msgid "IAP Credits"
msgstr "Krediti IAP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:503
msgid ""
"Odoo’s Electronic IAP offers 1000 credits for free, after these credits are "
"consumed in your production database, your company must buy new credits in "
"order to process your transactions."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Electronic IAP ponuja 1000 kreditov brezplačno. Ko so ti krediti "
"porabljeni v vaši produkcijski bazi podatkov, mora vaše podjetje kupiti nove "
"kredite, da lahko obdela svoje transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:506
msgid ""
"Once you run out of credits a red label is displayed at the top of the "
"invoice indicating that additional credits are required, you can easily buy "
"them by accessing the link provided in the message."
msgstr ""
"Ko porabite vse kredite, se na vrhu računa prikaže rdeča oznaka, ki "
"označuje, da so potrebni dodatni krediti. Enostavno jih lahko kupite tako, "
"da dostopate do povezave, navedene v sporočilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Buying credits in the IAP."
msgstr "Nakup kreditov v IAP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:513
msgid ""
"In the IAP service includes packages with different pricing based on the "
"number of credits. The price list in the IAP is always displayed in EUR."
msgstr ""
"Storitev IAP vključuje pakete z različnimi cenami glede na število kreditov. "
"Cenik v IAP je vedno prikazan v EUR."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:517
msgid "Special Use cases"
msgstr "Posebni primeri uporabe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:520
msgid "Cancellation process"
msgstr "Postopek preklica"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:522
msgid ""
"Some scenarios require an invoice cancellation, for example, when an invoice "
"was created by mistake. If the invoice was already sent and validated by the "
"SUNAT, the correct way to proceed is by clicking on the button Request "
"Cancellation:"
msgstr ""
"Nekateri scenariji zahtevajo preklic računa, na primer, ko je bil račun "
"ustvarjen pomotoma. Če je bil račun že poslan in potrjen s strani SUNAT, je "
"pravilen način nadaljevanja s klikom na gumb Zahtevaj preklic:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Request invoice cancellation button."
msgstr "Gumb za zahtevo po preklicu računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:529
msgid "In order to cancel an invoice, please provide a cancellation Reason."
msgstr "Za preklic računa navedite razlog za preklic."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:534
msgid ""
"**To Cancel**:  Indicates the cancellation request is ready to be sent to "
"the OSE, this can be done either automatically by Odoo with a *cron* that "
"runs every hour, or the user can send it immediately by clicking on the "
"button “Send now”. Once it is sent, a cancellation ticket is created, as a "
"result the next message and CDR File are logged in the chatter:"
msgstr ""
"**Za preklic**: Označuje, da je zahtevek za preklic pripravljen za "
"pošiljanje na OSE. To se lahko izvede samodejno prek Odoo *cron* opravila, "
"ki se izvaja vsako uro, ali pa uporabnik lahko zahtevek pošlje takoj s "
"klikom na gumb »Pošlji zdaj«. Ko je poslan, se ustvari zahtevek za preklic "
"in v pogovor se zabeležita naslednje sporočilo in datoteka CDR:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Cancellation CDR sent by the SUNAT."
msgstr "CDR za preklic, poslan s strani SUNAT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:542
msgid ""
"**Cancelled**: Indicates the cancellation request was sent to the OSE and "
"was successfully validated. As part of the validation a ZIP file is "
"downloaded and a message is logged in the chatter indicating the correct "
"Government validation."
msgstr ""
"**Preklican**: Označuje, da je bil zahtevek za preklic poslan na OSE in "
"uspešno potrjen. Kot del potrditve se prenese datoteka ZIP in v pogovor se "
"zabeleži sporočilo, ki označuje pravilno vladno potrditev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Invoice after cancellation."
msgstr "Račun po preklicu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:550
msgid "One credit is consumed on each cancellation request."
msgstr "Pri vsakem zahtevku za preklic se porabi en kredit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:555
msgid ""
"When creating exportation invoices, take into account the next "
"considerations:"
msgstr "Pri ustvarjanju računov za izvoz upoštevajte naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:557
msgid "The Identification type on your customer must be Foreign ID."
msgstr "Vrsta identifikacije pri vašem kupcu mora biti Tuji ID."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:558
msgid "Operation type in your invoice must be an Exportation one."
msgstr "Vrsta operacije na vašem računu mora biti izvozna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:559
msgid "The taxes included in the invoice lines should be EXP taxes."
msgstr "Davki, vključeni v vrstice računa, morajo biti davki EXP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:565
msgid "Advance Payments"
msgstr "Predplačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:568
msgid ""
"Because the SUNAT does not allow negative in filings, a workaround is "
"required when reporting down payments."
msgstr ""
"Ker SUNAT ne dovoljuje negativnih vrednosti v prijavah, je pri poročanju o "
"plačilih vnaprej potrebna rešitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:571
msgid "Open the sales order requiring a down payment."
msgstr "Odprite prodajni nalog, ki zahteva plačilo vnaprej."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:572
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create Invoice` and select :guilabel:`Down payment "
"(percentage)` or :guilabel:`Down payment (fixed amount)`. Enter the amount, "
"then click :guilabel:`Create Draft`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari fakturo` in izberite :guilabel:`Plačilo vnaprej "
"(odstotek)` ali :guilabel:`Plačilo vnaprej (fiksni znesek)`. Vnesite znesek, "
"nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari osnutek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:574
msgid ""
"Check that all information is correct. If yes, click :guilabel:`Confirm`. If "
"not, make the necessary changes before confirming."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, ali so vse informacije pravilne. Če so, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Potrdi`. Če niso, pred potrditvijo opravite potrebne spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:576
msgid ""
"Navigate back to the sales order and click :menuselection:`Create Invoice --"
"> Regular Invoice --> Create Draft` to proceed with invoice creation."
msgstr ""
"Vrnite se na prodajni nalog in kliknite :menuselection:`Ustvari fakturo --> "
"Redna faktura --> Ustvari osnutek`, da nadaljujete z ustvarjanjem fakture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:578
msgid ""
"From the invoice, remove the section separation *and* the down payment "
"invoice line by clicking the :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(trash bin)` "
"icon, and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Iz fakture odstranite ločitev razdelka *in* vrstico fakture plačila vnaprej "
"tako, da kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(koš za smeti)` in "
":guilabel:`Potrdi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Removing invoice lines and section."
msgstr "Odstranjevanje vrstic fakture in razdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:584
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, click :guilabel:`Credit Note`, then :guilabel:`Reverse`, and "
"finally remove all invoice lines by clicking the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash bin)` icon. The invoice should be clear of any product."
msgstr ""
"Ko je potrjeno, kliknite :guilabel:`Dobropis`, nato :guilabel:`Storniraj` in "
"na koncu odstranite vse vrstice fakture tako, da kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-"
"trash-o` :guilabel:`(koš za smeti)`. Faktura naj ne vsebuje nobenega izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:587
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. Click the :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(bars)` icon, enter a description (e.g., `Down Payment`), "
"and input the :guilabel:`Price`. Click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-bars` "
":guilabel:`(palice)`, vnesite opis (npr. `Plačilo vnaprej`) in vnesite "
":guilabel:`Ceno`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Adding down payment description."
msgstr "Dodajanje opisa plačila vnaprej."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:593
msgid ""
"After issuing the credit note and if not done automatically, reconcile it "
"with the final invoice."
msgstr ""
"Po izdaji dobropisa in če še ni bilo izvedeno samodejno, ga uskladite z "
"končnim računom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:594
msgid ""
"The final invoice's remaining balance **must** be paid with a regular "
"payment transaction."
msgstr ""
"Preostalo stanje končnega računa **mora** biti plačano z običajno plačilno "
"transakcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:597
msgid "Detraction Invoices"
msgstr "Računi z odbitkom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:599
msgid ""
"When creating invoices that is subject to Detractions, take into account the "
"next considerations:"
msgstr "Pri ustvarjanju računov, ki so predmet odbitkov, upoštevajte naslednje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:601
msgid ""
"All the products included in the invoice must have these fields configured:"
msgstr ""
"Vsi izdelki, vključeni v račun, morajo imeti konfigurirani naslednji polji:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Detraction fields on products."
msgstr "Polji za odbitek pri izdelkih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:606
msgid "Operation type in your invoice must be ``1001``"
msgstr "Vrsta operacije na vašem računu mora biti ``1001``"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:0
msgid "Detraction code on invoices."
msgstr "Koda odbitka na računih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:612
msgid "Credit Notes"
msgstr "Dobropisi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:614
msgid ""
"When a correction or refund is needed over a validated invoice, a credit "
"note must be generated, for this just click on the button “Add Credit Note”, "
"a part of the Peruvian localization you need to prove a Credit Reason "
"selecting one of the options in the list."
msgstr ""
"Ko je potrebna popravek ali vračilo potrjenega računa, je treba ustvariti "
"dobropis. To storite tako, da kliknete gumb „Dodaj dobropis“. Kot del "
"peruške lokalizacije morate dokazati razlog za dobropis z izbiro ene od "
"možnosti na seznamu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Add Credit Note from invoice."
msgstr "Dodaj dobropis iz računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:622
msgid ""
"When creating your first credit Note, select the Credit Method: Partial "
"Refund, this allows you to define the credit note sequence."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju prvega dobropisa izberite način dobropisa: delno vračilo. To "
"vam omogoča, da določite zaporedje dobropisa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:625
msgid "By default the Credit Note is set in the document type:"
msgstr "Privzeto je dobropis nastavljen v vrsti dokumenta:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Credit Note document type."
msgstr "Vrsta dokumenta dobropis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:630
msgid ""
"To finish the workflow please follow the instructions on :doc:`our page "
"about Credit Notes <../accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes>`."
msgstr ""
"Za končanje postopka sledite navodilom na :doc:`naši strani o dobropisih <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:634
msgid ""
"The EDI workflow for the Credit notes works in the same way as the invoices."
msgstr "Potek dela EDI za dobropise deluje enako kot za račune."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:637
msgid "Debit Notes"
msgstr "Debetni zapiski"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:639
msgid ""
"As part of the Peruvian localization, besides creating credit notes from an "
"existing document you can also create debit Notes. For this just use the "
"button “Add Debit Note”."
msgstr ""
"Kot del peruške lokalizacije lahko poleg ustvarjanja dobropisov iz "
"obstoječega dokumenta ustvarite tudi bremepise. To storite tako, da "
"uporabite gumb „Dodaj bremepiš“."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:642
msgid "By default the Debit Note is set in the document type."
msgstr "Privzeto je bremepiš nastavljen v vrsti dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:647
msgid "Electronic delivery guide 2.0"
msgstr "Elektronski spremni list 2.0"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:649
msgid ""
"The *Guía de Remisión Electrónica* (GRE) is an electronic document generated "
"by the shipper to support the transportation or transfer of goods from one "
"place to another, such as a warehouse or establishment. In Odoo, there are "
"several configuration steps needed before you can successfully use this "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"*Guía de Remisión Electrónica* (GRE) je elektronski dokument, ki ga ustvari "
"pošiljatelj za podporo prevozu ali prenosu blaga z enega kraja na drugega, "
"na primer skladišče ali objekt. V Odooju je potrebnih več konfiguracijskih "
"korakov, preden lahko uspešno uporabite to funkcijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:654
msgid ""
"The use of the *guía de remisión electrónica* electronic document is "
"mandatory and required by |SUNAT| for taxpayers who need to transfer their "
"products, except those under the *Single Simplified Regime* (régimen único "
"simplificado or RUS)."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba elektronskega dokumenta *guía de remisión electrónica* je obvezna in "
"jo zahteva |SUNAT| za davkoplačevalce, ki morajo prenašati svoje izdelke, "
"razen tistih pod *enotnim poenostavljenim režimom* (régimen único "
"simplificado ali RUS)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:659
msgid "Delivery guide types"
msgstr "Vrste spremnih listov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:662
msgid "Sender"
msgstr "Pošiljatelj"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:664
msgid ""
"The *Sender* delivery guide type is issued when a sale is made, a service is "
"rendered (including processing), goods are assigned for use, or goods are "
"transferred between premises of the same company and others."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta spremnega lista *pošiljatelj* se izda, ko je opravljena prodaja, "
"izvedena storitev (vključno s predelavo), dodeljeno blago za uporabo ali "
"preneseno blago med prostori istega podjetja in drugimi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:668
msgid ""
"This delivery guide is issued by the owner of the goods (i.e., the sender) "
"at the beginning of the shipment. The sender delivery guide is supported in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Ta spremni list izda lastnik blaga (tj. pošiljatelj) ob začetku pošiljke. "
"Spremni list pošiljatelja je podprt v Odooju."

