"trgovine**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:949
msgid ""
":ref:`Client account registration <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-"
"access>`;"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Registracija klientovega računa <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-"
"access>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:950
msgid ":ref:`Automatic invoice <ecommerce/handling/invoices>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`Samodejni račun <ecommerce/handling/invoices>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:951
msgid ""
":doc:`../../websites/ecommerce/configuration/products`: Set "
"the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` to :guilabel:`Ordered quantities` and "
"define the desired :guilabel:`Customer taxes`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../websites/ecommerce/configuration/products`: Nastavite "
":guilabel:`Pravila izdajanja računov` na :guilabel:`Naročene količine` in "
"določite želene :guilabel:`Davke kupcev`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:953
msgid ":doc:`../payment_providers`;"
msgstr ":doc:`../payment_providers`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:954
msgid ""
":doc:`../../websites/ecommerce/shipping`: For each shipping method, set "
"the :guilabel:`Provider` field to :guilabel:`Fixed Price`. Then, set "
"a :guilabel:`Fixed Price` amount greater than `0.00` (not zero), as the "
"shipping method price is added to the invoice line."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../websites/ecommerce/shipping`: Za vsako metodo pošiljanja "
"nastavite polje :guilabel:`Ponudnik` na :guilabel:`Fiksna cena`. Nato "
"nastavite znesek :guilabel:`Fiksna cena`, ki je večji od `0.00` (ne nič), "
"saj se cena načina pošiljanja doda v vrstico računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:959
msgid ""
"`Mercado Pago <https://www.mercadopago.com/>`_ is an online payment provider "
"supported in Odoo that covers several countries, currencies, and payment "
"methods in Latin America."
msgstr ""
"`Mercado Pago <https://www.mercadopago.com/>`_ je ponudnik spletnih plačil, "
"ki ga podpira Odoo in pokriva več držav, valut in načinov plačila v Latinski "
"Ameriki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:961
msgid ""
"Make sure to define a :guilabel:`Sales Price` on the :guilabel:`Delivery "
"Product` of the shipping method to prevent errors when validating the "
"invoice with |SUNAT|."
msgstr ""
"Poskrbite, da na :guilabel:`Izdelku za dostavo` načina pošiljanja določite "
":guilabel:`Prodajno ceno`, da preprečite napake pri potrjevanju računa z "
"|SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:963
msgid ""
"To offer free delivery, manually remove the :guilabel:`Delivery Product`, or "
"at least use `$0.01` (one cent) for the invoice to be validated with SUNAT."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ponuditi brezplačno dostavo, ročno odstranite :guilabel:`Izdelek "
"za dostavo` ali pa vsaj uporabite `$0.01` (en cent), da bo račun potrjen z "
"SUNAT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:967
msgid ""
":doc:`Set up the Mercado Pago payment provider. <../payment_providers/"
"mercado_pago>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Nastavite ponudnika plačil Mercado Pago. <../payment_providers/"
"mercado_pago>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:972
msgid ""
"Once the :ref:`configurations <peru-ecommerce-configuration>` are all set, "
"fiscal input fields will be available during the checkout process for signed-"
"in customers."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse :ref:`nastavitve <peru-ecommerce-configuration>` nastavljene, bodo "
"med postopkom zaključka nakupa na voljo davčna vnosna polja za prijavljene "
"stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:975
msgid ""
"When customers enter their fiscal data at checkout and complete a successful "
"purchase, the invoice is generated with the corresponding |EDI| elements. "
"The document type (Boleta/Factura) is selected based on their tax ID (RUC/"
"DNI). The invoice must then :ref:`be sent to the OSE and the SUNAT <peru-"
"electronic-invoice-status>`. By default, all published invoices are sent "
"once a day through a scheduled action, but you can also send each invoice "
"manually if needed."
msgstr ""
"Ko stranke ob zaključku nakupa vnesejo svoje davčne podatke in uspešno "
"dokončajo nakup, se ustvari račun z ustreznimi elementi |EDI|. Vrsta "
"dokumenta (Boleta/Factura) se izbere na podlagi njihove davčne številke (RUC/"
"DNI). Račun je nato :ref:`treba poslati OSE in SUNAT <peru-electronic-"
"invoice-status>`. Privzeto se vsi objavljeni računi pošljejo enkrat na dan "
"prek načrtovane akcije, vendar lahko vsak račun po potrebi pošljete tudi "
"ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:981
msgid ""
"Once the invoice is validated with |SUNAT|, customers can download the .zip "
"file with the CDR, XML, and PDF files directly from the customer portal by "
"clicking the :guilabel:`Download` button."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun potrjen z |SUNAT|, lahko stranke prenesejo datoteko .zip z "
"datotekami CDR, XML in PDF neposredno iz portala za stranke s klikom na gumb "
":guilabel:`Prenesi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:990
msgid "Permanent inventory reports: |PLE| 12.1 and |PLE| 13.1"
msgstr "Poročila o stalni zalogi: |PLE| 12.1 in |PLE| 13.1"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:992
msgid ""
"Odoo can produce two permanent inventory reports as `.txt` files for "
"Peruvian accounting: |PLE| 12.1 and |PLE| 13.1. All inventory transactions "
"made need to be reported."
msgstr ""
"Odoo lahko ustvari dve poročili o stalni zalogi kot datoteki `.txt` za "
"perujsko računovodstvo: |PLE| 12.1 in |PLE| 13.1. Prijaviti je treba vse "
"opravljene transakcije zalog."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:995
msgid ""
"|PLE| 12.1 **only tracks inventory in physical units**, focusing on the "
"inflow and outflow of goods for effective management and planning."
msgstr ""
"|PLE| 12.1 **sledi samo zalogi v fizičnih enotah**, s poudarkom na prilivi "
"in odlivi blaga za učinkovito upravljanje in načrtovanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:998
msgid ""
"|PLE| 13.1 tracks **both physical quantities and monetary values of "
"inventory**, providing a comprehensive view for tax and management purposes."
msgstr ""
"|PLE| 13.1 sledi **tako fizičnim količinam kot denarnim vrednostim zaloge**, "
"kar zagotavlja celovit pregled za davčne in upravljavske namene."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1001
msgid ""
"Both reports must be maintained semi-annually (January-June and July-"
"December), with monthly transaction details reported within these periods. "
"The submission deadlines are October 1st for the first semester and April "
"1st for the second semester, in accordance with the *Resolución de "
"Superintendencia N° 169-2015*."
msgstr ""
"Obe poročili je treba voditi polletno (januar–junij in julij–december), pri "
"čemer se mesečni podatki o transakcijah poročajo znotraj teh obdobij. Roki "
"za oddajo so 1. oktober za prvo polletje in 1. april za drugo polletje v "
"skladu z *Resolución de Superintendencia N° 169-2015*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1009
msgid ""
"Before generating the |PLE| 12.1 or |PLE| 13.1 reports, make sure "
"the :guilabel:`Peru - Stock Reports` (`l10n_pe_reports_stock`) module is "
"installed, then update the fields for:"
msgstr ""
"Pred ustvarjanjem poročil |PLE| 12.1 ali |PLE| 13.1 poskrbite, da je "
"nameščen modul :guilabel:`Peru - Stock Reports` (`l10n_pe_reports_stock`), "
"nato pa posodobite polja za:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1012
msgid ":ref:`Products <peru/reports-ple-products>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Izdelki <peru/reports-ple-products>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1013
msgid ":ref:`Warehouses <peru/reports-ple-warehouses>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Skladišča <peru/reports-ple-warehouses>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1014
msgid ":ref:`Inventory transfers <peru/reports-ple-transfers>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Prenosi zaloge <peru/reports-ple-transfers>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1021
msgid ""
"Several configurations related to the product or product category are "
"necessary for |PLE| reporting:"
msgstr ""
"Za poročanje |PLE| je potrebnih več konfiguracij, povezanih z izdelkom ali "
"kategorijo izdelka:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1023
msgid ""
"**Type of existence**: For all products needing |PLE| reporting, go to the "
"product record's :guilabel:`Accounting` tab and select the :guilabel:`Type "
"of Existence` according to |SUNAT|'s table 5 for inventory reporting."
msgstr ""
"**Vrsta obstoja**: Za vse izdelke, ki potrebujejo poročanje |PLE|, pojdite "
"na zavihek :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` v zapisu izdelka in izberite "
":guilabel:`Vrsta obstoja` v skladu s tabelo 5 |SUNAT| za poročanje o zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1027
msgid ""
"**Automatic inventory valuation**: For storable goods (:dfn:`products with "
"tracked inventory`), use :doc:`automatic inventory valuation <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>`. Once "
"automatic inventory valuation is enabled, this valuation method can be "
"enabled for a product's product category."
msgstr ""
"**Samodejno vrednotenje zalog**: Za blago za skladiščenje (:dfn:`izdelki s "
"sledeno zalogo`) uporabite :doc:`samodejno vrednotenje zalog <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>`. Ko je "
"samodejno vrednotenje zalog omogočeno, je ta metoda vrednotenja lahko "
"omogočena za kategorijo izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1032
msgid ""
"**Costing method:** Storable goods must use a :doc:`costing method <../../"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>` **other** "
"than :guilabel:`Standard Price`, as the journal entries generated from stock "
"moves are used to populate the |PLE| reports."
msgstr ""
"**Metoda obračunavanja stroškov:** Blago za skladiščenje mora uporabljati "
":doc:`metodo obračunavanja stroškov <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"inventory_valuation/cheat_sheet>` **drugo** kot :guilabel:`Standardna cena`, "
"saj se kontne postavke, ustvarjene iz premikov zalog, uporabljajo za "
"zapolnjevanje |PLE| poročil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1040
msgid "Warehouses"
msgstr "Skladišča"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1042
msgid ""
"When :doc:`setting up a warehouse <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses>`, the :guilabel:`Annex "
"Establishment Code` field must be filled. This code acts as a unique ID for "
"each warehouse and should only be a numeric combination, containing between "
"4 to 7 digits."
msgstr ""
"Pri :doc:`vzpostavljanju skladišča <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"warehouses_storage/inventory_management/warehouses>` je treba izpolniti "
"polje :guilabel:`Koda dodatka ustanova`. Ta koda deluje kot enolični "
"identifikator za vsako skladišče in mora biti samo numerična kombinacija, ki "
"vsebuje od 4 do 7 številk."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1050
msgid "Inventory transfers"
msgstr "Prenosi zaloge"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1052
msgid ""
"Transferring inventory is a key process captured in the |PLE| 12.1 and |PLE| "
"13.1 reports. :doc:`Inventory transfers <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations>` include both incoming and outgoing "
"shipments."
msgstr ""
"Prenašanje zaloge je ključni proces, zajet v poročilih |PLE| 12.1 in |PLE| "
"13.1. :doc:`Prenosi zaloge <../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/daily_operations>` vključujejo tako dohodne kot odhodne "
"pošiljke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1056
msgid ""
"When validating an inventory transfer (either on a warehouse receipt or "
"delivery order), select the :guilabel:`Type of Operation (PE)` performed "
"according to |SUNAT|'s table 12 for permanent inventory reporting."
msgstr ""
"Pri potrjevanju prenosa zaloge (bodisi ob skladnem prejemu bodisi dobavnici) "
"izberite :guilabel:`Vrsta operacije (PE)`, izvedene v skladu s tabelo 12 "
"|SUNAT| za poročanje o stalni zalogi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1061
msgid "Generate a .txt file for permanent inventory Kardex reports"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje datoteke .txt za poročila Kardex stalne zaloge"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1063
msgid ""
"|PLE| 12.1 and 13.1 come as two separate books. The books need to be "
"downloaded in `.txt` file format from Odoo, and then they should be "
"submitted to the |SUNAT| |PLE| software."
msgstr ""
"|PLE| 12.1 in 13.1 sta dve ločeni knjigi. Knjige je treba prenesti v formatu "
"`.txt` iz Odoo in nato poslati v programsko opremo |SUNAT| |PLE|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1066
msgid ""
"On the :ref:`Inventory Valuation Report <inventory/product_management/"
"valuation-report>`, click the :guilabel:`PLE Reports` button. Then, select "
"the :guilabel:`Period` and choose a report to export: either "
"the :guilabel:`PLE 12.1` or :guilabel:`PLE 13.1`. Odoo generates a `.txt` "
"file for the chosen report."
msgstr ""
"V :ref:`Poročilu o vrednotenju zalog <inventory/product_management/valuation-"
"report>` kliknite gumb :guilabel:`PLE poročila`. Nato izberite "
":guilabel:`Obdobje` in izberite poročilo za izvoz: bodisi :guilabel:`PLE "
"12.1` ali :guilabel:`PLE 13.1`. Odoo ustvari datoteko `.txt` za izbrano "
"poročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:None
msgid "Export Buttons selection"
msgstr "Izbira gumbov za izvoz"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:1075
msgid ""
"Only a download of the report in `.txt` format is available. There is no "
"preview or visualization available within Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo je samo prenos poročila v formatu `.txt`. V Odoo ni na voljo "
"predogleda ali vizualizacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:3
