msgstr ""
"Kode ATC so ključne za generiranje poročil :ref:`BIR 2307 <localizations/"
"philippines/reports/bir2307>`, :ref:`localizations/philippines/reports/"
"sawt_qap`. Te kode zagotavljajo skladnost z regulativnimi zahtevami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:85
msgid ""
"To configure a withholding tax, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, select the tax, and fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Philippines ATC` (Alphanumeric Tax Code) field under "
"the :guilabel:`Philippines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo davka pri viru pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Davki`, izberite davek in izpolnite polje "
":guilabel:`Filipini ATC` (alfanumerična davčna koda) pod zavihkom "
":guilabel:`Filipini`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:97
msgid "2550Q"
msgstr "2550Q"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:99
msgid ""
"The **BIR Form 2550Q** summarizes sales, purchases, output VAT, input VAT, "
"and the resulting VAT payable or refundable for the period."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec **BIR Form 2550Q** povzema prodajo, nakupe, izhodni DDV, vstopni DDV "
"ter rezultat plačljivega ali povračljivega DDV za obdobje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:102
msgid ""
"To access it, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax "
"Report`, click :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report`, and "
"select :guilabel:`2550Q (PH)`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Davčno "
"poročilo`, kliknite :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Poročilo` in izberite "
":guilabel:`2550Q (PH)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:108
msgid "SAWT and QAP"
msgstr "SAWT in QAP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:110
msgid ""
"To access these reports, navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Reporting --> Tax Report`, click :icon:`fa-book` :guilabel:`Report`, and "
"select :guilabel:`SAWT & QAP (PH)`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do teh poročil pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročanje --> Davčno poročilo`, kliknite :icon:`fa-book` "
":guilabel:`Poročilo` in izberite :guilabel:`SAWT & QAP (PH)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:113
msgid ""
"**Summary of Alphalist of Withholding Taxes (SAWT)**: Displays all customer "
"invoices that have sales withholding taxes applied. This export is used as a "
"supporting document for forms **1701Q**, **1701**, **1702Q**, and **1702**."
msgstr ""
"**Summary of Alphalist of Withholding Taxes (SAWT)**: Prikazuje vse račune "
"strankam, pri katerih so bili uporabljeni davki pri obdavčenju na viru od "
"prodaje. Ta izvoz se uporablja kot podporni dokument za obrazce **1701Q**, "
"**1701**, **1702Q** in **1702**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:116
msgid ""
"**Quarterly Alphalist of Payees (QAP)**: Includes all vendor bills that have "
"purchase withholding taxes applied. This export is used as a supporting "
"document for forms **1601EQ** and **1604E**."
msgstr ""
"**Quarterly Alphalist of Payees (QAP)**: Vključuje vse račune dobaviteljev, "
"pri katerih so bili uporabljeni davki pri obdavčenju na viru od nakupov. Ta "
"izvoz se uporablja kot podporni dokument za obrazca **1601EQ** in **1604E**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:121
msgid ""
"The generated file is based on the specific **period** selected in the "
"calendar report filter. For example, while the **1601EQ** is a quarterly "
"report, `.DAT` files are submitted monthly. Make sure to filter "
"by :guilabel:`Month` and select the appropriate month before exporting."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjena datoteka temelji na določenem **obdobju**, izbranem v filtru "
"koledarskega poročila. Na primer, medtem ko je **1601EQ** četrtletno "
"poročilo, se datoteke `.DAT` predložijo mesečno. Pred izvozom poskrbite, da "
"filtrirate po :guilabel:`Mesecu` in izberete ustrezen mesec."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:125
msgid ""
"Both SAWT and QAP reports can be exported in `.DAT` format, which is "
"compatible with the BIR :abbr:`Alpha (Alphalist Data Entry and Validation)` "
"module. To do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Poročili SAWT in QAP je mogoče izvoziti v obliki `.DAT`, ki je združljiva z "
"modulom BIR :abbr:`Alpha (Alphalist Data Entry and Validation)`. Za to "
"sledite naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:128
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:159
msgid "Make sure to filter by the appropriate month."
msgstr "Poskrbite, da filtrirate po ustreznem mesecu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:129
msgid ""
"On the report page, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon and "
"select :guilabel:`Export SAWT & QAP`."
msgstr ""
"Na strani poročila kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(zobnik)` in "
"izberite :guilabel:`Izvozi SAWT & QAP`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:131
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`DAT Export Options` window, choose the "
"relevant :guilabel:`Attachment For (e.g., 1601EQ)` and "
"click :guilabel:`Export`."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Možnosti izvoza DAT` izberite ustrezno vrednost "
":guilabel:`Priponka za (npr. 1601EQ)` in kliknite :guilabel:`Izvozi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:137
msgid "SLSP"
msgstr "SLSP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:139
msgid ""
"The **SLSP (Summary lists of sales and purchases)** is an electronic "
"schedule required from VAT‑registered taxpayers listing sales and purchase "
