"sledite naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:160
msgid ""
"On the report page, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon and "
"select :guilabel:`Export SLSP`."
msgstr ""
"Na strani poročila kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`zobnik` in "
"izberite :guilabel:`Export SLSP`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:162
msgid "In the :guilabel:`DAT Export Options` window, click :guilabel:`Export`."
msgstr "V oknu :guilabel:`DAT Export Options` kliknite :guilabel:`Export`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:167
msgid "BIR 2307"
msgstr "BIR 2307"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:169
msgid ""
"The **BIR 2307**, or *Certificate of Creditable Tax Withheld at Source*, can "
"be generated for :guilabel:`vendor bills` that include expanded withholding "
"taxes."
msgstr ""
"**BIR 2307** ali *Potrdilo o davku, odtetem pri viru*, se lahko ustvari za "
":guilabel:`dobaviteljeve račune`, ki vključujejo razširjene davke pri viru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:172
msgid "To generate a BIR 2307 report:"
msgstr "Za ustvarjanje poročila BIR 2307:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:174
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Bills` and select one or "
"multiple vendor bills from the list view."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Računi` in "
"izberite enega ali več dobaviteljevih računov s seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:176
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, and select :guilabel:`Download BIR "
"2307 XLS`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in izberite :guilabel:`Download "
"BIR 2307 XLS`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:177
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`BIR 2307 Report` window, review the selection and "
"click :guilabel:`Generate`."
msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`BIR 2307 Report` preglejte izbiro in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Generate`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:180
msgid ""
"The XLS file generates records **only** for bill lines with **expanded "
"withholding taxes** applied."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka XLS ustvari zapise **samo** za vrstice računov z **razširjenimi "
"davki pri viru**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:184
msgid ""
"Odoo does not generate the BIR 2307 PDF report natively. The exported "
"`Form_2307.xls` file must be converted to BIR DAT or PDF format."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ne ustvarja poročila BIR 2307 v obliki PDF samodejno. Izvoženo datoteko "
"`Form_2307.xls` je treba pretvoriti v obliko BIR DAT ali PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:201
