msgstr "Plačila s čekom"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:240
msgid ""
"The Philippines check print layout adheres to the **New Check Design "
"Standards and Specifications** (CICS OM No. 23-040)."
msgstr ""
"Filipinska postavitev čeka ustreza **novim standardom in specifikacijam "
"zasnove čekov** (CICS OM št. 23-040)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/philippines.rst:243
msgid ""
"To use check payments, :ref:`activate the check payment option <accounting/"
"pay-checks/activate-methods>`, then, in the :guilabel:`Check Layout` field, "
