msgstr ""
":doc:`../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts`: vnaprej določena "
"struktura, usklajena s predpisi Savdske Arabije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:60
msgid ""
