#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"Standard VAT (15%): The prevailing rate applied to the majority of goods and "
"services supplied within the Kingdom."
msgstr ""
"Standardni DDV (15 %): Prevladujoča stopnja, uporabljena za večino blaga in "
"storitev, dobavljenih v kraljevini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"The supplier charges 15% VAT on the sale (Output VAT) and is generally "
"entitled to deduct the VAT paid on its business purchases (Input VAT)."
msgstr ""
"Dobavitelj zaračuna 15 % DDV od prodaje (izhodni DDV) in je na splošno "
"upravičen do odbitka DDV, plačanega pri svojih poslovnih nakupih (vstopni "
"DDV)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:87
msgid ""
"Most commercial sales, retail goods, telecommunication services, non-exempt "
"private education, and non-exempt private healthcare."
msgstr ""
"Večina komercialne prodaje, maloprodajnega blaga, telekomunikacijskih "
"storitev, neoprostega zasebnega izobraževanja in neoprostenega zasebnega "
"zdravstva."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"Zero-rated VAT (0%): These are taxable supplies where the rate of tax "
"applied is 0%."
msgstr ""
"DDV z ničelno stopnjo (0 %): To so obdavčljive dobave, pri katerih je "
"uporabljena stopnja davka 0 %."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"The supplier charges no VAT on the sale, but, critically, is fully entitled "
"to recover the input VAT paid on costs related to making those supplies."
msgstr ""
"Dobavitelj ne zaračuna DDV od prodaje, vendar je – kar je ključnega pomena – "
"v celoti upravičen do povračila vstopnega DDV, plačanega za stroške v zvezi "
"s temi dobavami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:92
msgid ""
"Exports: Supplies of goods and services to a non-:abbr:`GCC (Gulf "
"Cooperation Council)` resident or for consumption outside the Kingdom."
msgstr ""
"Izvoz: Dobave blaga in storitev nerezidentu :abbr:`GCC (Sveta za sodelovanje "
"v Zalivu)` ali za porabo zunaj kraljevine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:94
msgid ""
"International transport: Services for the international transport of "
"passengers and goods, and related services."
msgstr ""
"Mednarodni prevoz: Storitve mednarodnega prevoza potnikov in blaga ter "
"povezane storitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:96
msgid ""
"Specific goods: Supplies of qualifying medicines and qualifying medical "
"equipment, as specified by ZATCA/Ministry of Health."
msgstr ""
"Določeno blago: Dobave ustreznih zdravil in ustrezne medicinske opreme, kot "
"jih določita ZATCA/Ministrstvo za zdravje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:98
msgid ""
"Residential property: First supply of a new residential building/property to "
"a Saudi citizen, up to a value of SAR 1,000,000 (subject to specific "
"conditions)."
msgstr ""
"Stanovanjske nepremičnine: Prva dobava nove stanovanjske zgradbe/"
"nepremičnine savdijskemu državljanu do vrednosti 1.000.000 SAR (pod "
"določenimi pogoji)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:100
msgid ""
"Investment metals: Qualifying gold, silver, and platinum of 99% purity or "
"higher (supplied for investment)."
msgstr ""
"Investicijske kovine: Ustrezno zlato, srebro in platina čistosti 99 % ali "
"več (dobavljeno za naložbe)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"Exempt transactions: These transactions fall outside the scope of VAT, "
"meaning they are not subject to the tax."
msgstr ""
"Oproščeni posli: Ti posli ne spadajo na področje DDV, kar pomeni, da niso "
"predmet obdavčitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"The supplier does not charge any VAT on the sale and is not entitled to "
"recover the input VAT paid on costs related to making these supplies "
"(resulting in an unrecoverable cost)."
msgstr ""
"Dobavitelj ne zaračuna DDV od prodaje in ni upravičen do povračila vstopnega "
"DDV, plačanega za stroške v zvezi s temi dobavami (kar povzroči nepovraten "
"strošek)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:109
msgid ""
"Financial services: interest on loans, provision of credit, operations of "
"current/deposit/savings accounts, issuance or transfer of money or "
"securities, and life insurance."
msgstr ""
"Finančne storitve: obresti od posojil, odobravanje kreditov, poslovanje "
"tekočih/depozitnih/varčevalnih računov, izdaja ali prenos denarja ali "
"vrednostnih papirjev ter življenjsko zavarovanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:112
msgid "Real estate: bare rental (leasing) of residential property."
msgstr "Nepremičnine: goli najem (zakup) stanovanjske nepremičnine."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"Import VAT: VAT is levied on goods brought into the Kingdom from a "
"non-:abbr:`GCC (Gulf Cooperation Council)` country."
msgstr ""
"Uvozni DDV: DDV se obračuna od blaga, vnesenega v kraljevino iz države, ki "
"ni članica :abbr:`GCC (Sveta za sodelovanje v Zalivu)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:0
msgid ""
"VAT is typically calculated at the standard rate (15%) and is paid to the "
"Customs Authority at the point of importation."
msgstr ""
"DDV se običajno izračuna po standardni stopnji (15 %) in se plača carinskim "
"organom ob uvozu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:120
msgid ""
"When assigning :doc:`discounts <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/"
"discounts>` to invoices, assign a 15% tax on the line containing a global "
"discount to comply with ZATCA rules."
msgstr ""
"Pri dodeljevanju :doc:`popustov <../../sales/sales/products_prices/prices/"
"discounts>` na računih dodelite 15-odstotni davek v vrstici, ki vsebuje "
"globalni popust, da upoštevate pravila ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:124
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:128
msgid "Reverse charge mechanism (RCM)"
msgstr "Mehanizem prenesene davčne obveznosti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:126
msgid ""
"Description: Mechanism that shifts the responsibility for accounting for VAT "
"from the non-resident supplier to the resident recipient of the goods or "
"services."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Mehanizem, ki prenese odgovornost za obračunavanje DDV z "
"nerezidentnega dobavitelja na rezidentnega prejemnika blaga ali storitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:128
msgid ""
"Mechanism: The VAT-registered recipient must calculate and account for the "
"VAT (as both output VAT and input VAT) in their :ref:`VAT return <accounting/"
"tax-returns/vat-report>`. This typically results in a net zero effect on the "
"VAT return, provided the input tax is fully deductible."
msgstr ""
"Mehanizem: Prejemnik, registriran za DDV, mora izračunati in obračunati DDV "
"(tako kot izhodni DDV kot tudi vhodni DDV) v svojem :ref:`obračunu DDV "
"<accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>`. To običajno povzroči neto ničelni "
"učinek na obračun DDV, pod pogojem, da je vstopni davek v celoti odbitni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:131
msgid ""
"Application: Primarily used for B2B supplies of services from a non-resident "
"supplier to a VAT-registered business in Saudi Arabia."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba: Primarno se uporablja za B2B dobave storitev od dobavitelja "
"nerezidenta poslovnemu subjektu, registriranemu za DDV v Savdski Arabiji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:139
msgid ""
"There are two available methods for calculating withholding tax: gross and "
"deducted."
msgstr "Na voljo sta dve metodi za izračun davka pri viru: bruto in odbitna."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:141
msgid ""
"Gross withholding: This is the primary configuration, where the withholding "
"amount is calculated in addition to the bill total. For example, if the "
"total bill is entered as 115 SAR, the system calculates the base plus "
"Withholding Tax (WHT) without reducing the payment amount."
msgstr ""
"Bruto davek pri viru: To je primarna konfiguracija, kjer se znesek davka pri "
"viru izračuna dodatno k skupnemu znesku računa. Na primer, če je skupni "
"znesek računa vnesen kot 115 SAR, sistem izračuna osnovo plus davek pri viru "
"(WHT) brez zmanjšanja zneska plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:144
msgid ""
"Deducted withholding: It reduces the payable amount by the withholding "
"amount directly, meaning the total payment reflects the deduction upfront. "
"This affects how the accounting entries and payable lines are booked."
msgstr ""
"Odtegnjen davčni odtegljaj: Zmanjša znesek, ki ga je treba plačati, za "
"znesek davčnega odtegljaja neposredno, kar pomeni, da skupno plačilo vnaprej "
"odraža odbitek. To vpliva na način knjiženja računovodskih vnosov in vrstic "
"za plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:149
msgid ""
"Deducted withholding taxes are not enabled by default. To activate it, go to "
"Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes and enable the relevant withholding "
"tax."
msgstr ""
"Odbitni davki pri viru niso privzeto omogočeni. Za aktivacijo pojdite v "
"Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Davki in omogočite ustrezni davek pri "
"viru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:152
msgid ""
"The following Withholding Tax (WHT) configurations are preloaded and "
"available for use:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednje konfiguracije davka pri viru (WHT) so vnaprej naložene in na voljo "
"za uporabo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:154
msgid ""
"5% Withholding Tax: Applied on payments for rent, dividends, technical and "
"consulting services, air and maritime freight, as well as interest, "
"insurance, and reinsurance premiums."
msgstr ""
"5% davek pri viru: Uporablja se pri plačilih za najemnino, dividende, "
"tehnične in svetovalske storitve, letalski in pomorski prevoz ter obresti, "
"zavarovanja in pozavarovanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:156
msgid ""
"15% Withholding Tax: Applies to royalties and other general service payments "
"made to non-residents."
msgstr ""
"15% davek pri viru: Velja za avtorske honorarje in druga splošna plačila za "
"storitve nerezidentom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:158
msgid ""
"20% Withholding Tax: Reserved for management fees and specific high-value "
"service payments."
msgstr ""
"20% davek pri viru: Rezerviran za upravljavske pristojbine in določena "
"plačila za storitve visoke vrednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:165
msgid ""
"The :ref:`VAT and Withholding Return <accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` "
"provide a detailed breakdown of taxable, zero-rated, exempt, and withholding "
"transactions. Like other financial reports, the :guilabel:`VAT` "
"and :guilabel:`Withholding Return` can be filtered by period, compared "
"against other periods, and exported in Excel and PDF formats, ensuring "
"compliance with Saudi Arabia tax laws."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Obračun DDV in davka pri viru <accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` "
"zagotavlja podroben razčlen obdavčljivih, ničnih stopenj, oproščenih in "
"transakcij z davkom pri viru. Tako kot druga finančna poročila je mogoče "
":guilabel:`DDV` in :guilabel:`obračun davka pri viru` filtrirati po obdobju, "
"primerjati z drugimi obdobji in izvoziti v formatih Excel in PDF, kar "
"zagotavlja skladnost z davčno zakonodajo Savdske Arabije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:176
msgid ""
"To ensure proper integration with :ref:`ZATCA <localizations/saudi-arabia/"
"zatca>`, the following fields are required on the :ref:`company record "
"<general/companies/company>`:"
msgstr ""
"Za zagotovitev pravilne integracije z :ref:`ZATCA <localizations/saudi-"
"arabia/zatca>` so v :ref:`zapisu podjetja <general/companies/company>` "
"zahtevana naslednja polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company Name`, limited to a maximum of 63 characters to comply "
"with ZATCA requirements."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Název společnosti`, omezeno na maximálně 63 znaků pro splnění "
"požadavků ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:181
msgid ""
"All relevant :guilabel:`Address` fields, including "
"the :guilabel:`District`, :guilabel:`Building Number`, and :guilabel:`Plot "
"Identification`"
msgstr ""
"Vsa ustrezna polja :guilabel:`naslova`, vključno z :guilabel:`okrožjem`, "
":guilabel:`številko stavbe` in :guilabel:`identifikacijo parcele`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:183
msgid ":guilabel:`Identification Scheme`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Shema identifikacije`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:185
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax Identification Number`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Davčna identifikacijska številka`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:186
msgid ":guilabel:`Commercial Registration Number`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Poslovna registracijska številka`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:187
msgid ":guilabel:`Momra License`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Licenca Momra`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:188
msgid ":guilabel:`MLSD License`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Licenca MLSD`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:189
msgid ":guilabel:`700 Number`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Številka 700`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:190
msgid ":guilabel:`Sagia License`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Licenca Sagia`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:192
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT Number`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Številka DDV`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:193
msgid ":guilabel:`Currency` must be set to :guilabel:`SAR`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Valuta` mora biti nastavljena na :guilabel:`SAR`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:196
msgid ""
"All fields must be completed accurately to avoid rejection "
"during :ref:`ZATCA onboarding <localizations/saudi-arabia/zatca>`."
msgstr ""
"Vsa polja morajo biti izpolnjena natančno, da se prepreči zavrnitev med "
":ref:`registracijo v ZATCA <localizations/saudi-arabia/zatca>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:200
msgid ""
"The same configuration applies to all relevant :doc:`contact <../../"
"essentials/contacts>` forms."
msgstr ""
"Enaka konfiguracija velja za vse ustrezne obrazce :doc:`stikov <../../"
"essentials/contacts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:205
msgid "Branches configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija podružnic"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:207
msgid ""
"Set up your company :ref:`branches <general/branches>` in compliance "
"with :ref:`ZATCA rules <localizations/saudi-arabia/company-contacts>`."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite :ref:`podružnice <general/branches>` vašega podjetja v skladu s "
":ref:`pravili ZATCA <localizations/saudi-arabia/company-contacts>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:211
msgid ""
"On the branch contact form, enter the same :guilabel:`VAT Number` as the "
"parent company and enter the branch :guilabel:`Commercial Registration "
"Number (CRN)` in the :guilabel:`Identification Scheme` field."
msgstr ""
"V obrazcu stika podružnice vnesite enak :guilabel:`davčni številki` kot pri "
"matičnem podjetju in vnesite :guilabel:`registracijsko številko podružnice "
"(CRN)` v polje :guilabel:`Identifikacijska shema`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:216
msgid ""
"Either use the parent company’s sales journal to follow a centralized "
"billing system model, or onboard a new branch-specific journal to set up a "
"multi-threaded system with parallel invoice processing."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite bodisi prodajni dnevnik matičnega podjetja za centralizirani model "
"obračunavanja bodisi registrirajte nov dnevnik, specifičen za podružnico, za "
"vzpostavitev večnitnega sistema z vzporednim obdelavo računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:225
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:244
msgid ""
"Invoices can be issued in different languages to meet regional or customer-"
"specific requirements at two levels:"
msgstr ""
"Računi se lahko izdajo v različnih jezikih za izpolnitev regionalnih ali "
"strank specifičnih zahtev na dveh ravneh:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:228
msgid ""
"Customer level: To assign a preferred language to a customer, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers` "
"or :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Customers`, and open the "
"relevant customer form.  In the :guilabel:`Language` field, update the "
"language. All documents are then automatically generated in the selected "
"language for that customer."
msgstr ""
"Raven stranke: Če želite stranki dodeliti prednostni jezik, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Stranke --> Stranke` ali "
":menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> Naročila --> Stranke` in odprite ustrezen "
"obrazec stranke. V polju :guilabel:`Jezik` posodobite jezik. Vsi dokumenti "
"se nato za to stranko samodejno ustvarijo v izbranem jeziku."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:234
msgid ""
"Saudi Arabia's VAT regulations require :guilabel:`Tax Invoices` "
"and :guilabel:`Simplified Tax Invoices` (along with corresponding credit "
"notes or debit notes) to be in Arabic, mandatorily. Invoices can be "
"bilingual, including English."
msgstr ""
"Predpisi o DDV v Savdski Arabiji zahtevajo, da so :guilabel:`davčni računi` "
"in :guilabel:`poenostavljeni davčni računi` (skupaj z ustreznimi "
"dobropisnimi ali bremepisi) obvezno v arabščini. Računi so lahko dvojezični, "
"vključno z angleščino."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:238
msgid ""
"Company level: To add Arabic as a secondary language to meet Saudi Arabia "
"VAT regulations:"
msgstr ""
"Raven podjetja: Če želite dodati arabščino kot sekundarni jezik za "
"izpolnitev predpisov o DDV v Savdski Arabiji:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:240
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:253
msgid ""
"For :guilabel:`Tax Invoices`: Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, in the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` section."
msgstr ""
"Za :guilabel:`Davčne račune`: Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, v razdelek :guilabel:`Računi kupcem`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:242
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:255
msgid ""
"For Point of Sale receipts: Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and navigate to the :guilabel:`Bills & "
"Receipts` section."
msgstr ""
"Za potrdila prodajne točke: Pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodajna točka --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in pojdite v razdelek :guilabel:`Računi in "
"potrdila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:245
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:258
msgid ""
"Then, enable the :guilabel:`Gulf Cooperation Council Format` option, "
"and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Nato omogočite možnost :guilabel:`Oblika Sveta za sodelovanje v Zalivu` in "
":guilabel:`Shranite`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:250
msgid "Electronic invoicing with ZATCA"
msgstr "Elektronsko fakturiranje z ZATCA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:252
msgid ""
"The ZATCA e-invoicing system is designed to streamline and digitize the "
"invoicing process for businesses operating in Saudi Arabia."
msgstr ""
"Sistem e-fakturiranja ZATCA je zasnovan za poenostavitev in digitalizacijo "
"postopka fakturiranja za podjetja, ki delujejo v Savdski Arabiji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:255
msgid ""
"ZATCA Phase 2 employs a clearance e-invoicing model for Business-to-Business "
"(B2B) transactions. Conversely, for Business-to-Consumer (B2C) transactions, "
"Odoo generates a QR code and subsequently reports these transactions to the "
"Fatoora reporting endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Faza 2 ZATCA uporablja model potrjevanja e-fakturiranja za transakcije med "
"podjetji (B2B). Nasprotno, za transakcije med podjetjem in potrošnikom (B2C) "
"Odoo ustvari kodo QR in nato te transakcije poroča končni točki Fatoora za "
"poročanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:259
msgid ""
"In a B2B scenario, a :guilabel:`Tax Invoice` is issued, whereas in a B2C "
"scenario, a :guilabel:`Simplified Tax Invoice` is generated."
msgstr ""
"V scenariju B2B se izda :guilabel:`davčni račun`, medtem ko se v scenariju "
"B2C ustvari :guilabel:`poenostavljen davčni račun`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:263
msgid ""
"`ZATCA e-invoicing page <https://zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/Pages/"
"default.aspx>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Stran ZATCA e-fakturiranje <https://zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/Pages/"
"default.aspx>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:268
