"the :guilabel:`ZATCA API mode` is set to :guilabel:`Production`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` "
"in v razdelku :guilabel:`Elektronsko izdajanje računov za Savdsko Arabijo` "
"zagotovite, da je :guilabel:`Način ZATCA API` nastavljen na "
":guilabel:`Produkcija`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:367
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:598
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Enter the OTP` window, enter the 6-digit :guilabel:`OTP` "
"retrieved from the Fatoora Portal under the Production Environment. Then "
