msgstr ""
"V oknu :guilabel:`Vnesite OTP` vnesite 6-mestno :guilabel:`OTP`, pridobljeno "
"s portala Fatoora v produkcijskem okolju. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:370
msgid "Invoice synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija računov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:380
msgid "Each :guilabel:`Sales` journal must be onboarded separately."
msgstr "Vsak dnevnik :guilabel:`Prodaja` mora biti vklopljen ločeno."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:382
msgid ""
"If a sales journal is no longer needed as a ZATCA solution unit, make sure "
"to revoke it in your Fatoora portal. To do so, click :guilabel:`View List of "
"Solutions And Devices`, select the relevant solution and device "
"under :guilabel:`Revoke CSID`, then click :guilabel:`Revoke` "
"and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Če dnevnik prodaje ni več potreben kot enota rešitve ZATCA, ga ne pozabite "
"preklicati na portalu Fatoora. To storite tako, da kliknete "
":guilabel:`Prikaži seznam rešitev in naprav`, izberete ustrezno rešitev in "
"napravo pod :guilabel:`Prekliči CSID`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Prekliči` in "
":guilabel:`Potrdi`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:388
msgid ""
"Once the API mode is switched to :guilabel:`Production` and an invoice is "
"submitted to ZATCA, it cannot be changed back to :guilabel:`Sandbox` "
"or :guilabel:`Simulation (Pre-Production)`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je način API preklopljen na :guilabel:`Produkcija` in je račun poslan v "
"ZATCA, ga ni več mogoče spremeniti nazaj na :guilabel:`Peskovnik` ali "
":guilabel:`Simulacija (pred-produkcija)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:390
msgid ""
"OTP’s generated from either the Fatoora Simulation or Production portal "
"expire after 60 minutes and need to be regenerated."
msgstr ""
"OTP-ji, generirani bodisi s portala Fatoora Simulation bodisi Production, "
"potečejo po 60 minutah in jih je treba ponovno generirati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:396
msgid "Invoice submission to ZATCA"
msgstr "Pošiljanje računov v ZATCA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:398
msgid ""
"After submitting the invoice to ZATCA, a structured response message is "
"returned by the API in the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Po pošiljanju računa v ZATCA API v pogovoru vrne strukturirano sporočilo z "
"odgovorom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:402
msgid ""
"[202] BR-KSA-F-13 : [BR-KSA-F-13] - Please recheck Other Seller/Buyer ID "
"(BT-29 or BT-46) as it contains an invalid value."
msgstr ""
"[202] BR-KSA-F-13 : [BR-KSA-F-13] - Preverite drugi ID prodajalca/kupca (BT-"
"29 ali BT-46), saj vsebuje neveljavno vrednost."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:405
msgid "Common codes that can be received:"
msgstr "Pogoste kode, ki jih lahko prejmete:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:411
msgid "Action"
msgstr "Dejanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:412
msgid ":guilabel:`200 – Action Successful`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`200 – Dejanje uspešno`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:413
msgid "No action required."
msgstr "Ni potrebno nobeno dejanje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:414
msgid ":guilabel:`202 – Action Successful (with Warnings)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`202 – Dejanje uspešno (z opozorili)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:415
msgid ""
"Share the warnings with the solution provider to correct them as soon as "
"possible."
msgstr "Opozorila delite s ponudnikom rešitve, da jih čim prej popravi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:416
msgid ""
"Warnings are temporarily accepted but may become rejections in the future."
msgstr ""
"Opozorila so začasno sprejeta, vendar se lahko v prihodnosti spremenijo v "
"zavrnitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:417
msgid ""
"Frequent warnings may trigger investigation, education, or auditing by ZATCA."
msgstr ""
"Pogosta opozorila lahko sprožijo preiskavo, izobraževanje ali revizijo s "
"strani ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:418
msgid ":guilabel:`303 – Clearance Switched Off`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`303 – Preverjanje izklopljeno`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:419
msgid "Submit the invoice through the reporting flow instead of clearance."
msgstr "Pošljite račun prek postopka poročanja namesto preverjanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:420
msgid ":guilabel:`400 – Action Failed (Rejected)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`400 – Dejanje ni uspelo (zavrnjeno)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:421
msgid "Review the detailed error message, correct the issue, and resubmit."
msgstr ""
"Preglejte podrobno sporočilo o napaki, odpravite težavo in znova pošljite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:422
msgid ":guilabel:`401 – Unauthorized`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`401 – Nepooblaščeno`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:423
msgid "Check the authentication certificate and secret key."
msgstr "Preverite overjitveno potrdilo in skrivni ključ."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:424
msgid "Correct the credentials and resubmit."
msgstr "Popravite poverilnice in znova pošljite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:425
msgid ":guilabel:`413 – Payload Too Large (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`413 – Vsebina prevelika (račun ni bil prejet)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:426
msgid "Reduce the invoice payload size and resend."
msgstr "Zmanjšajte velikost vsebine računa in znova pošljite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:427
msgid ":guilabel:`429 – Too Many Requests (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`429 – Preveč zahtev (račun ni bil prejet)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:428
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:430
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:432
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:434
msgid "Resend the invoice."
msgstr "Znova pošljite račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:429
msgid ":guilabel:`500 – Internal Server Error (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`500 – Notranja napaka strežnika (račun ni bil prejet)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:431
msgid ":guilabel:`503 – Service Unavailable (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`503 – Storitev ni na voljo (račun ni bil prejet)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:433
msgid ":guilabel:`504 – Request Timed Out (Invoice Not Received)`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`504 – Časovna omejitev zahteve je potekla (račun ni bil prejet)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:436
msgid ""
"The color of the message displayed in the chatter after an invoice is "
"confirmed and submitted indicates the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Barva sporočila, prikazanega v pogovornem zavihku po potrditvi in pošiljanju "
"računa, označuje naslednje informacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:439
msgid ""
"Green: invoice successfully accepted - The invoice is fully compliant and "
"has been successfully validated by ZATCA."
msgstr ""
"Zelena: račun uspešno sprejet - Račun je popolnoma skladen in ga je ZATCA "
"uspešno preveril."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:441
msgid ""
"Yellow: invoice accepted with warnings - The invoice is legally valid but "
"was accepted with a warning. The issue should be reviewed and corrected for "
"future submissions."
msgstr ""
"Rumena: račun sprejet z opozorili - Račun je pravno veljaven, vendar je bil "
"sprejet z opozorilom. Težavo je treba pregledati in odpraviti za prihodnje "
"predložitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:443
msgid ""
"Red: invoice was rejected - The invoice was not accepted by ZATCA and is not "
"legally valid. It must be corrected and resubmitted."
msgstr ""
"Rdeča: račun je bil zavrnjen - ZATCA računa ni sprejel in ni pravno "
"veljaven. Popraviti ga je treba in znova poslati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:446
msgid ""
"If the invoice is rejected, an error message is displayed in the invoice’s "
"chatter. Correct the underlying issue described in the message description "
"in the invoice or company settings. Then, to resubmit the invoice, "
"click :guilabel:`Retry`."
msgstr ""
"Če je račun zavrnjen, se v pogovornem dnevniku računa prikaže sporočilo o "
"napaki. Popravite osnovni problem, opisan v sporočilu, v računu ali "
"nastavitvah podjetja. Nato račun ponovno predložite s klikom na "
":guilabel:`Poskusi znova`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:451
msgid ""
"Invoices rejected by ZATCA remain in a :guilabel:`Rejected` state and are "
"not considered legally valid."
msgstr ""
"Računi, ki jih ZATCA zavrne, ostanejo v stanju :guilabel:`Zavrnjeno` in niso "
"veljavni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:453
msgid ""
"In case of any incidents, technical errors, or emergency matters that "
"prevent the generation of e-invoices/e-receipts, notify `ZATCA <https://"
"zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/FailureNotifications/Pages/"
"VerifyTaxpayer.aspx>`_. Once the issue has been resolved, contact ZATCA "
"again using the same communication channel. For specific failure scenarios, "
"refer to the steps outlined in `ZATCA's guidelines (page 45) <https://"
"zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/Introduction/Guidelines/Documents/E-"
"Invoicing_Detailed__Guideline.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"V primeru kakršnih koli incidentov, tehničnih napak ali nujnih zadev, ki "
"preprečujejo ustvarjanje e-računov/e-potrdil, obvestite `ZATCA <https://"
"zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/FailureNotifications/Pages/VerifyTaxpayer.aspx>"
"`_. Ko je težava odpravljena, stopite v stik z ZATCA znova prek istega "
"komunikacijskega kanala. Za posebne scenarije napak si oglejte korake, "
"opisane v `smernicah ZATCA (stran 45) <https://zatca.gov.sa/en/E-Invoicing/"
"Introduction/Guidelines/Documents/E-Invoicing_Detailed__Guideline.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:462
msgid "QR code verification"
msgstr "Preverjanje kode QR"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:464
msgid ""
"To verify the QR Code on the invoice, scan it using the official `ZATCA app "
"<https://zatca.gov.sa/en/AboutUs/ZATCAApps/Pages/default.aspx>`_."
msgstr ""
"Za preverjanje kode QR na računu jo skenirajte s pomočjo uradne `aplikacije "
"ZATCA <https://zatca.gov.sa/en/AboutUs/ZATCAApps/Pages/default.aspx>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:467
msgid ""
"Once in the app, click :guilabel:`Services`. In the :guilabel:`E-Invoice "
"Validation` section, click :guilabel:`Start Service`. Then, begin scanning "
"the invoices' QR codes."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste v aplikaciji, kliknite :guilabel:`Storitve`. V razdelku "
":guilabel:`Preverjanje veljavnosti e-računa` kliknite :guilabel:`Začni "
"storitev`. Nato začnite skenirati kode QR računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:471
msgid ""
"The QR verification output does not display a currency symbol. The invoice "
