"Invoicing_Detailed__Guideline.pdf>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:513
msgid "Retention"
msgstr "Zadrževanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:515
msgid ""
"Retention is an amount temporarily held by the customer, defined by the "
"commercial contract, to ensure the quality and completion of the work. It is "
"usually a percentage of the invoice value (e.g., 5-10%) and serves as "
"security against future defects; it is ultimately paid back to the "
"contractor once the warranty period expires."
msgstr ""
"Zadrževanje je znesek, ki ga stranka začasno zadrži, določen s trgovinsko "
"pogodbo, za zagotovitev kakovosti in dokončanja dela. Običajno je to "
"odstotek vrednosti računa (npr. 5-10 %) in služi kot varnost pred "
"prihodnjimi napaka­mi; na koncu se plača nazaj izvajalcu, ko poteče "
"garancijsko obdobje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:520
msgid ""
"For ZATCA, the commonly applied rule is that VAT is calculated based on the "
"full invoice amount, even if the customer withholds a portion as retention. "
"ZATCA advises taxpayers to first determine the tax position, specifically "
"whether the retention amount reduces the taxable amount or not. Tax position "
"depends on contractual terms."
msgstr ""
"Za ZATCA se običajno uporablja pravilo, da se DDV izračuna na podlagi "
"celotnega zneska računa, tudi če kupec zadrži del zneska kot varščino. ZATCA "
"davčnim zavezancem svetuje, da najprej določijo davčni položaj, natančneje "
"ali znesek varščine zmanjšuje obdavčljiv znesek ali ne. Davčni položaj je "
"odvisen od pogodbenih določb."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:525
msgid ""
"The Odoo retention workflow ensures, through tax position, that the "
"retention amount does not reduce the taxable amount."
msgstr ""
"Odoo-jev postopek za varščino zagotavlja prek davčnega položaja, da znesek "
"varščine ne zmanjšuje obdavčljivega zneska."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:529
msgid ""
"Any negative tax (e.g., -20%) configured with the :guilabel:`Is Retention` "
"checkbox enabled has no impact on the UBL 2.1. It only applies when this "
"retention tax is used in conjunction with a generic tax (e.g., 15%) on the "
"invoice line and represents a percentage of that invoice line. For example, "
"if a taxpayer wants to retain 20% of the invoiced goods, both the 15% tax "
"and the -20% retention tax would be applied to the invoice line."
msgstr ""
"Vsak negativni davek (npr. -20 %), nastavljen s potrjenim potrditvenim "
"poljem :guilabel:`Je varščina`, nima vpliva na UBL 2.1. Uporablja se le, ko "
"se ta davek varščine uporabi skupaj s splošnim davkom (npr. 15 %) v vrstici "
"računa in predstavlja odstotek te vrstice računa. Na primer, če želi davčni "
"zavezanec zadržati 20 % zaračunanega blaga, bi se na vrstico računa "
"uporabila tako davek 15 % kot davek varščine -20 %."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:535
msgid ""
"Within this same tax position, retention can also be applied at the invoice "
"level as an separate negative invoice line using a 0% (Not Subject to VAT) "
"tax rate."
msgstr ""
"V okviru istega davčnega položaja se lahko varščina uporabi tudi na ravni "
"računa kot ločena negativna vrstica računa z uporabo davčne stopnje 0 % (Ne "
"podleže DDV)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:539
msgid ""
"Adding either a negative tax with :guilabel:`Is Retention` enabled and a "
"generic tax on the invoice line, or a separate negative invoice line with a "
"0% (:guilabel:`Not Subject to VAT`) tax rate at the invoice level, usually "
"indicates that VAT has been paid on the full taxable amount. Therefore, the "
"final invoice for releasing the retention amount does not qualify as "
"a :guilabel:`Tax Invoice` and should not be submitted to ZATCA."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje negativnega davka z omogočeno možnostjo :guilabel:`Je zadrževanje` "
"in splošnim davkom v vrstici računa ali ločena negativna vrstica računa z "
"davčno stopnjo 0% (:guilabel:`Ni predmet DDV`) na ravni računa običajno "
"nakazuje, da je bil DDV plačan od celotnega obdavčljivega zneska. Zato "
"končni račun za sprostitev zneska zadrževanja ne ustreza opredelitvi "
":guilabel:`Davčni račun` in ga ni treba predložiti ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:544
msgid ""
"The 0% (Not Subject to VAT) tax is already preconfigured according to ZATCA "
"rules; do not modify it."
msgstr ""
"Davek 0 % (Ne podleže DDV) je že vnaprej nastavljen v skladu s pravili "
"ZATCA; ne spreminjajte ga."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:548
msgid ""
"When creating a new retention tax, create a :guilabel:`Retention` tax group "
"and assign it to this newly created retention tax to comply with ZATCA rules."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju novega davka varščine ustvarite davčno skupino "
":guilabel:`Varščina` in jo dodelite na novo ustvarjenemu davku varščine v "
"skladu s pravili ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:550
msgid ""
"To add the :guilabel:`Retention Amount` as a note on the invoice line, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a note` to comply with ZATCA rules. For example - "
"Retention Amount: `[retention amount] SAR`"
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati :guilabel:`Znesek varščine` kot opombo v vrstico računa, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj opombo` v skladu s pravili ZATCA. Na primer – "
"Znesek varščine: `[znesek varščine] SAR`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:556
msgid "Generated documents"
msgstr "Ustvarjeni dokumenti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:558
msgid ""
"Once an invoice is submitted, a UBL 2.1 XML file is generated and sent to "
"ZATCA API endpoints. For auditability, this XML file is stored in the "
"chatter. To display it, click the :icon:`fa-"
"paperclip` :guilabel:`(attachments)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Ko je račun oddan, se ustvari datoteka UBL 2.1 XML in pošlje na API končne "
"točke ZATCA. Zaradi revizije je ta datoteka XML shranjena v klepetu. Če jo "
"želite prikazati, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-paperclip` :guilabel:`(priloge)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:562
msgid ""
"Additionally, the invoice PDF generated when using :guilabel:`Send` is "
"displayed in the chatter. Both the XML and PDF files are permanently "
"attached to the invoice and cannot be deleted to ensure compliance with "
"ZATCA regulations."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega je PDF računa, ustvarjen pri uporabi :guilabel:`Pošlji`, prikazan "
"v klepetu. Obe datoteki XML in PDF sta trajno priloženi računu in jih ni "
"mogoče izbrisati, da se zagotovi skladnost s predpisi ZATCA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:567
msgid ""
"Successfully ZATCA-submitted invoices can only be reset to draft "
"in :ref:`Sandbox <localizations/saudi-arabia/sandbox>` or :ref:`Simulation "
"(Pre-Production) <localizations/saudi-arabia/simulation>` modes."
msgstr ""
"Račune, uspešno oddane v ZATCA, je mogoče ponastaviti v osnutek samo v "
"načinih :ref:`Peskovnik <localizations/saudi-arabia/sandbox>` ali "
":ref:`Simulacija (predprodukcija) <localizations/saudi-arabia/simulation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:572
msgid ""
"To automatically generate a PDF/A-3 with the embedded UBL 2.1, "
"click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite samodejno ustvariti PDF/A-3 z vdelano datoteko UBL 2.1, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Pošlji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:582
