#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:41
msgid ""
"Default Spain-specific taxes are created automatically when "
"the :guilabel:`Spanish - Accounting (PGCE 2008) (l10n_es)` module is "
"installed, and tax reports are available when installing the "
"module :guilabel:`Spain - Accounting (PGCE 2008) (l10n_es_reports)`. Each "
"tax impacts the Spain-specific **tax reports (Modelo)**, available by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Statements Reports: Tax "
"Report`."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti španski davki so ustvarjeni samodejno, ko je nameščen modul "
":guilabel:`Spain - Accounting (PGCE 2008) (l10n_es)`, davčna poročila pa so "
"na voljo po namestitvi modula :guilabel:`Spain - Accounting (PGCE 2008) "
"(l10n_es_reports)`. Vsak davek vpliva na španska **davčna poročila (Modelo)"
"**, dostopna prek :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Poročila: "
"Davčno poročilo`."

