#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:44
msgid "Sales and purchase tax report"
msgstr "Poročilo o DDV pri prodaji in nabavi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:46
msgid ""
"To generate a sales and purchase tax report, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Report`. Select a "
"specific time or time range on the tax report, and "
"click :guilabel:`VAT-202-01 (xlsx)` for purchase tax "
"and :guilabel:`VAT-202-02 (xlsx)` for sales tax."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje poročila o DDV pri prodaji in nabavi pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Davčno poročilo`. Izberite "
"določen čas ali časovno obdobje v davčnem poročilu in kliknite "
":guilabel:`VAT-202-01 (xlsx)` za DDV pri nabavi in :guilabel:`VAT-202-02 "
"(xlsx)` za DDV pri prodaji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "Thai purchase and sales taxes reports"
msgstr "Tajska poročila o DDV pri nabavi in prodaji"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:54
msgid "Withholding PND tax report"
msgstr "Poročilo o davku pri viru PND"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:56
msgid ""
"PND report data displays the summarized amounts of the applicable "
"**withholding corporate income tax returns (domestic)** from vendor bills "
"under the :guilabel:`PND53 (TH)` and :guilabel:`PND3 (TH)` tax reports. It "
"is installed by default with the Thai localization."
msgstr ""
"Podatki poročila PND prikazujejo zbrane zneske veljavnih **napovedi davka "
"pri viru od dohodka pravnih oseb (domači)** iz računov dobaviteljev pod "
"davčnimi poročili :guilabel:`PND53 (TH)` in :guilabel:`PND3 (TH)`. Nameščeno "
"je privzeto s tajsko lokalizacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "PND tax reports"
msgstr "Davčna poročila PND"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:64
msgid ""
"Withholding corporate income tax returns (domestic) is the tax used in case "
"the company has withheld the tax from “**Personal (PND3)**” or “**Corporate "
"(PND53)**” services provided such as rental, hiring, transportation, "
"insurance, management fee, consulting, etc."
msgstr ""
"Napoved davka pri viru od dohodka pravnih oseb (domači) je davek, ki se "
"uporablja v primeru, ko je podjetje zadržalo davek od storitev »**fizičnih "
"oseb (PND3)**« ali »**pravnih oseb (PND53)**«, kot so najem, zaposlovanje, "
"prevoz, zavarovanje, stroški upravljanja, svetovanje itd."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:68
msgid ""
"The PND tax report allows users to generate a CSV file for bills to upload "
"on the `RDprep for Thailand e-Filling application <https://efiling.rd.go.th/"
"rd-cms/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo o davku PND uporabnikom omogoča ustvarjanje datoteke CSV za račune "
"za nalaganje v `aplikacijo RDprep za elektronsko oddajo na Tajskem <https://"
"efiling.rd.go.th/rd-cms/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:71
msgid ""
"To generate a PND CSV file, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --"
"> Tax Report`, select a specific time or time range on the tax report, and "
"click :guilabel:`PND3` or :guilabel:`PND53`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje datoteke PND CSV pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> "
"Poročanje --> Davčno poročilo`, izberite določen čas ali časovno obdobje v "
"davčnem poročilu in kliknite :guilabel:`PND3` ali :guilabel:`PND53`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:74
msgid ""
"This generates the :file:`Tax Report PND3.csv` and :file:`Tax Report "
"PND53.csv` files that lists all the vendor bill lines with the applicable "
"withholding tax."
msgstr ""
"To ustvari datoteki :file:`Tax Report PND3.csv` in :file:`Tax Report "
"PND53.csv`, ki navajata vse vrstice računov dobaviteljev z veljavnim davkom "
"pri viru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "PND3 and PND53 CSV files"
msgstr "Datoteke CSV PND3 in PND53"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:81
msgid ""
"Odoo cannot generate the PND or PDF report or **withholding tax "
"certificate** directly. The generated :file:`Tax Report PND3.csv` "
"and :file:`Tax Report PND53.csv` files must be exported to an external tool "
"to convert them into a **withholding PND** report or a **PDF** file."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ne more neposredno ustvariti poročila PND ali PDF ali **potrdila o "
"davku pri viru**. Ustvarjeni datoteki :file:`Tax Report PND3.csv` in "
":file:`Tax Report PND53.csv` je treba izvoziti v zunanji program, da ju "
"pretvorite v poročilo **PND o davku pri viru** ali datoteko **PDF**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:86
msgid "Tax invoice"
msgstr "Davčni račun"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:88
msgid ""
"The **tax invoice PDF** report can be generated from Odoo through the "
"**Invoicing** module. Users have the  option to print PDF reports for normal "
"invoices and tax invoices. To print out **tax invoices**, users can click "
"on :guilabel:`Print Invoices` in Odoo. Regular invoices can be printed as "
"**commercial invoices** by clicking on :menuselection:`Cog button (⚙️) --> "
"Print --> Commercial Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Poročilo **davčni račun PDF** lahko ustvarite v Odoo prek modula "
"**Fakturiranje**. Uporabniki lahko natisnejo poročila PDF za običajne račune "
"in davčne račune. Za tiskanje **davčnih računov** lahko uporabniki kliknejo "
":guilabel:`Print Invoices` v Odoo. Običajne račune lahko natisnete kot "
"**komercialne račune** s klikom na :menuselection:`Cog button (⚙️) --> "
"Print --> Commercial Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "Commercial invoice printing"
msgstr "Tiskanje komercialnega računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:98
msgid "Headquarter/Branch number settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve številke sedeža/podružnice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:100
msgid ""
"You can inform a company's **Headquarters** and **Branch number** in the "
"**Contacts** app. Once in the app, open the **contact form** of the company "
"and under the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab:"
msgstr ""
"Podatke o **sedežu** in **številki podružnice** podjetja lahko vnesete v "
"aplikaciji **Stiki**. Ko odprete aplikacijo, odprite **obrazec stika** "
"podjetja in pod zavihkom :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:103
msgid ""
"If the contact is identified as a branch, input the **Branch number** in "
"the :guilabel:`Company ID` field."
msgstr ""
"Če je stik opredeljen kot podružnica, vnesite **številko podružnice** v "
"polje :guilabel:`Company ID`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:105
msgid ""
"If the contact is a **Headquarters**, leave the :guilabel:`Company ID` field "
"**blank**."
msgstr "Če je stik **sedež**, pustite polje :guilabel:`Company ID` **prazno**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "Company Headquarter/Branch number"
msgstr "Številka sedeža/podružnice podjetja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:111
msgid ""
"This information is used in the **tax invoice** PDF report and PND **tax "
"report** export."
msgstr ""
"Te informacije se uporabijo v poročilu PDF **davčni račun** in izvozu "
"**davčnega poročila** PND."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:114
msgid "PromptPay QR code on invoices"
msgstr "Koda QR PromptPay na računih"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:116
msgid ""
"The **PromptPay QR code** is a QR code that can be added to invoices to "
"allow customers to pay their bills using the PromptPay-supported bank mobile "
"application. The QR code is generated based on the **invoice amount** and "
"one of the following **merchant information**:"
msgstr ""
"**Koda QR PromptPay** je koda QR, ki jo lahko dodate računom, da strankam "
"omogočite plačilo računov prek mobilne aplikacije banke, ki podpira "
"PromptPay. Koda QR se ustvari na podlagi **zneska računa** in ene od "
"naslednjih **informacij o trgovcu**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:120
msgid "Ewallet ID"
msgstr "ID e-denarnice"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:121
msgid "Merchant Tax ID"
msgstr "Davčna ID trgovca"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:122
msgid "Mobile Number"
msgstr "Številka mobilnega telefona"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:131
msgid "PromptPay QR bank account configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija bančnega računa PromptPay QR"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:133
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Contacts --> Configuration --> Bank Accounts` and "
"select the bank account for which you want to activate PromptPay QR. Set "
"the :guilabel:`Proxy Type` and fill in the :guilabel:`Proxy Value` field "
"depending on the chosen type."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Contacts --> Configuration --> Bank Accounts` in "
"izberite bančni račun, za katerega želite aktivirati PromptPay QR. Nastavite "
":guilabel:`Proxy Type` in izpolnite polje :guilabel:`Proxy Value` glede na "
"izbrani tip."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:139
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Include Reference` checkbox doesn't work for PromptPay QR "
"codes."
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Include Reference` ne deluje za kode QR "
"PromptPay."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:None
msgid "PromptPay bank account configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija bančnega računa PromptPay"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:150
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Journals`, open the "
"bank journal, then fill in the :guilabel:`Account Number` "
"and :guilabel:`Bank` under the :guilabel:`Journal Entries` tab."
msgstr ""
"Odprite :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> Dnevniki`, odprite "
"bančni dnevnik in nato izpolnite :guilabel:`Številka računa` in "
":guilabel:`Banka` pod zavihkom :guilabel:`Vknjižbe`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:157
msgid "Issue invoices with PromptPay QR code"
msgstr "Izdaja računov s QR kodo PromptPay"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/thailand.rst:165
msgid ""
"Ensure that the :guilabel:`Recipient Bank` is the one you configured, as "
