#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:351
msgid ""
"The e-Ledger is an electronic system that enables businesses to digitally "
"store and submit their accounting records to the government for tax and "
"regulatory compliance. In Odoo, users can generate the e-Ledger as a zipped "
"CSV file and report company records seamlessly through the Nilvera "
"integration."
msgstr ""
"e-Glavna knjiga je elektronski sistem, ki podjetjem omogoča digitalno "
"shranjevanje in predložitev njihovih računovodskih evidenc vladi za davčno "
"in regulativno skladnost. V Odoo lahko uporabniki ustvarijo e-Glavno knjigo "
"kot stisnjeno CSV datoteko in brezhibno poročajo podatke podjetja prek "
"integracije Nilvera."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:356
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> General Ledger`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Poročanje --> Glavna knjiga`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:357
msgid "Click the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Actions`) icon."
msgstr "Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`Dejanja`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:358
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Generate e-Ledger` to generate the file and download it to "
"your computer."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari e-Glavno knjigo`, da ustvarite datoteko in jo "
"prenesete na svoj računalnik."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:363
msgid "Manage e-Dispatch files"
msgstr "Upravljajte datoteke e-Odpreme"

