msgstr "Ustvarite datoteke e-Odpreme"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:368
msgid ""
"The e-Dispatch is an electronic document that replaces traditional paper "
"delivery notes, allowing businesses to digitally issue, transmit, and track "
"shipment details for goods in transit. In Odoo, users can generate e-"
"Dispatch documents as XML and upload them through the Nilvera integration, "
"ensuring compliant and traceable delivery operations."
msgstr ""
"e-Odpremnica je elektronski dokument, ki nadomešča tradicionalne papirne "
"dobavnice in podjetjem omogoča digitalno izdajanje, prenos in sledenje "
"podrobnosti pošiljk blaga v tranzitu. V Odoo lahko uporabniki ustvarijo "
"dokumente e-Odpreme kot XML in jih naložijo prek integracije Nilvera, kar "
"zagotavlja skladne in sledljive dobavne operacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:373
msgid "Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Operations --> Deliveries`."
msgstr "Pojdite na :menuselection:`Zaloga --> Operacije --> Dobave`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:374
msgid "Open an existing delivery order or create a new one."
msgstr "Odprite obstoječe dobavno naročilo ali ustvarite novo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:375
msgid ""
"Once a :guilabel:`Delivery Address` is selected, fill in the necessary "
