#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:390
msgid "Mandatory compliance information"
msgstr "Obvezne informacije o skladnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:392
msgid ""
"The following rules are mandatory for all users of the Türkiye localization "
"integration. Compliance with these requirements is essential for the legal "
"validity of e-Documents issued through the |GİB| via Nilvera."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja pravila so obvezna za vse uporabnike integracije turške "
"lokalizacije. Skladnost s temi zahtevami je bistvena za pravno veljavnost e-"
"dokumentov, izdanih prek |GİB| preko Nilvera."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:397
msgid "Document numbering structure"
msgstr "Struktura številčenja dokumentov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:399
msgid ""
"All generated invoices and dispatch documents must follow a specific "
"numbering structure: `three alphanumeric characters` + `document year` + "
"`sequential number`."
msgstr ""
"Vsi ustvarjeni računi in odpremni dokumenti morajo slediti določeni "
"strukturi številčenja: `tri alfanumerični znaki` + `leto dokumenta` + "
"`zaporedna številka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:403
msgid "INV/2025/00001"
msgstr "INV/2025/00001"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:405
msgid ""
"The numbering must be unique, sequential, and continuous. Each document must "
"have a distinct identifier."
msgstr ""
"Številčenje mora biti edinstveno, zaporedno in neprekinjeno. Vsak dokument "
"mora imeti poseben identifikator."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:407
msgid ""
"Once a file has been submitted, even if it returns an error, the same "
"sequence number cannot be used; a new document must be created."
msgstr ""
"Ko je datoteka oddana, tudi če vrne napako, iste zaporedne številke ni "
"mogoče uporabiti; ustvariti je treba nov dokument."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:411
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/sequence`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/customer_invoices/sequence`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:412
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/vendor_bills/sequence`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/vendor_bills/sequence`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:415
msgid "Sequential number gaps"
msgstr "Vrzeli v zaporednih številkah"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:417
msgid ""
"If a sequence number is skipped, the previous missing numbers must be issued "
"within 7 days."
msgstr ""
"Če je zaporedna številka preskočena, je treba prejšnje manjkajoče številke "
"izdati v 7 dneh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:420
msgid ""
"If INV/2025/00002 is issued before INV/2025/00001, INV/2025/00001 must be "
"issued within 7 days."
msgstr ""
"Če je INV/2025/00002 izdan pred INV/2025/00001, mora biti INV/2025/00001 "
"izdan v 7 dneh."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:423
msgid "No sequence number can remain unissued beyond this period."
msgstr "Nobena zaporedna številka ne sme ostati neizdana po tem obdobju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:426
msgid "Discount rules"
msgstr "Pravila za popuste"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:428
msgid ""
"Global discounts (discounts shown as a separate invoice line) cannot be "
"issued."
msgstr ""
"Globalnih popustov (popusti, prikazani kot ločena vrstica računa) ni mogoče "
"izdati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:429
msgid ""
"All discounts must be applied at the product line level within the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Vsi popusti morajo biti uporabljeni na ravni postavke izdelka znotraj računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:432
msgid "e-Ledger compliance"
msgstr "Skladnost z e-Ledger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/turkiye.rst:434
msgid ""
