#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:41
msgid ""
"The UAE fiscal localisation provides a fully configured accounting setup "
"aligned with national VAT and corporate tax regulations. It includes a "
"localised chart of accounts, VAT-compliant tax groups, standard journals, "
"fiscal year configurations, and reporting features that ensure accuracy and "
"compliance with the Federal Tax Authority (FTA)."
msgstr ""
"Davčna lokalizacija ZAE zagotavlja popolnoma konfigurirano računovodsko "
"nastavitev, usklajeno z nacionalnimi predpisi o DDV in davku od dohodkov "
"pravnih oseb. Vključuje lokalizirani kontni načrt, davčne skupine, skladne z "
"DDV, standardne dnevnike, konfiguracije poslovnega leta in funkcije "
"poročanja, ki zagotavljajo točnost in skladnost s Zvezno davčno upravo (FTA)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:46
msgid ""
"The UAE localization package provides the following key features to ensure "
"compliance with local fiscal and accounting regulations:"
msgstr ""
"Paket lokalizacije za ZAE zagotavlja naslednje ključne funkcije za "
"zagotavljanje skladnosti z lokalnimi davčnimi in računovodskimi predpisi:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:49
msgid ""
":ref:`Chart of accounts <localizations/uae/coa>`: a predefined structure "
"aligned with UEA accounting standards"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Kontni načrt <localizations/uae/coa>`: vnaprej določena struktura, "
"usklajena s standardi računovodstva ZAE"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:51
msgid ""
":ref:`Taxes <localizations/uae/taxes>`: preconfigured tax groups and "
"templates based on UAE VAT rules"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Davki <localizations/uae/taxes>`: vnaprej konfigurirane davčne skupine "
"in predloge na podlagi pravil DDV ZAE"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:53
msgid ""
":doc:`../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions`: automated tax adjustments to "
"handle local and cross-border transactions"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions`: samodejne davčne prilagoditve "
"za obravnavo lokalnih in čezmejnih transakcij"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:55
msgid ""
":ref:`VAT return <localizations/uae/tax-return>`: structured according to "
"the UAE VAT return format, as issued by the :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax "
"Authority)`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`DDV obračun <localizations/uae/tax-return>`: strukturiran v skladu z "
"obliko DDV obračuna ZAE, kot ga izdaja :abbr:`FTA (Zvezna davčna uprava)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:57
msgid ""
":ref:`Corporate Tax Report <localizations/uae/corporate-tax-report>`: "
"structured according to the UAE Corporate Tax Report, as issued by "
"the :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax Authority)`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Poročilo o davku od dohodkov pravnih oseb <localizations/uae/corporate-"
"tax-report>`: strukturirano v skladu s poročilom o davku od dohodkov pravnih "
"oseb ZAE, kot ga izdaja :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax Authority)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:65
msgid ""
"The UAE :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` is aligned with :abbr:`IFRS (International Financial "
"Reporting Standards)` and :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax Authority)` tax "
"requirements. This includes classified accounts for assets, liabilities, "
"equity, income, and expenses, as well as separate accounts for VAT payable "
"and VAT receivable."
msgstr ""
"Kontni načrt ZAE :doc:` <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` je "
"usklajen z :abbr:`IFRS (mednarodnimi standardi računovodskega poročanja)` in "
"davčnimi zahtevami :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax Authority)`. To vključuje "
"razvrščene račune za sredstva, obveznosti, kapital, prihodke in odhodke ter "
"ločene račune za plačljiv in terjatev DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:70
msgid ""
"This structure ensures compatibility with UAE reporting obligations, VAT, "
"and corporate income tax filings."
msgstr ""
"Ta struktura zagotavlja združljivost z obveznostmi poročanja v ZAE, DDV in "
"prijav davka od dohodkov pravnih oseb."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:78
msgid ""
"The UAE localization includes preconfigured VAT rates and :doc:`taxes <../"
"accounting/taxes>` as defined by the :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax Authority)`:"
msgstr ""
"Lokalizacija za ZAE vključuje vnaprej konfigurirane stopnje DDV in "
":doc:`davke <../accounting/taxes>`, kot jih določa :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax "
"Authority)`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"Standard VAT (5%): The prevailing VAT rate applied to most taxable goods and "
"services supplied within the UAE."
msgstr ""
"Standardni DDV (5 %): Veljavna stopnja DDV, ki se uporablja za večino "
"obdavčljivega blaga in storitev, dobavljenih v ZAE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"The supplier charges 5% VAT on the sale (Output VAT). VAT-registered "
"businesses may generally recover the VAT paid on eligible business purchases "
"(Input VAT)."
msgstr ""
"Dobavitelj zaračuna 5 % DDV od prodaje (izhodni DDV). Podjetja, registrirana "
"za DDV, lahko na splošno povrnejo DDV, plačan za upravičene poslovne nakupe "
"(vstopni DDV)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"Zero-Rated VAT (0%): Taxable supplies on which VAT is applied at a rate of "
"0%."
msgstr ""
"DDV po ničelni stopnji (0 %): Obdavčljive dobave, za katere se uporablja DDV "
"po stopnji 0 %."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"No VAT is collected on the sale, but the supplier remains fully entitled to "
"recover input VAT related to making these supplies."
msgstr ""
"Pri prodaji se ne pobira DDV, vendar dobavitelj ohrani polno pravico do "
"povračila vstopnega DDV, povezanega s temi dobavami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:95
msgid "Exports of goods and services (subject to qualifying conditions)"
msgstr "Izvoz blaga in storitev (pod pogoji za izpolnjevanje pogojev)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:96
msgid "International transport and related services"
msgstr "Mednarodni prevoz in z njim povezane storitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:97
msgid "Designated sectors such as specific healthcare and education services"
msgstr ""
"Določeni sektorji, kot so specifične zdravstvene in izobraževalne storitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:98
msgid "First supply of residential property (subject to conditions)"
msgstr "Prva dobava stanovanjske nepremičnine (pod pogoji)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"Exempt VAT: Supplies that fall outside the taxable category and are not "
"subject to VAT."
msgstr ""
"Oproščen DDV: Dobave, ki ne spadajo v kategorijo obdavčljivih in niso "
"predmet DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"The supplier does not charge VAT and cannot recover input VAT on costs "
"related to exempt activities."
msgstr ""
"Dobavitelj ne zaračuna DDV in ne more povrniti vstopnega DDV na stroške, "
"povezane z oprostnimi dejavnostmi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:105
msgid ""
"Financial services: Interest on loans, bank account operations, and life "
"insurance (when no explicit fee is charged)."
msgstr ""
"Finančne storitve: obresti na posojila, bančne operacije in življenjsko "
"zavarovanje (kadar se ne zaračuna izrecna pristojbina)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:107
msgid ""
"Local passenger transport: Taxis, buses, metro services, and domestic "
"flights within the UAE."
msgstr ""
"Lokalni prevoz potnikov: taksiji, avtobusi, storitve metroja in domači "
"poleti v ZAE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid "Import VAT: VAT that is applied to goods imported into the UAE."
msgstr "Uvozni DDV: DDV, ki se uporablja za blago, uvoženo v ZAE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"Import VAT is recorded at the applicable rate (generally 5%). In UAE VAT "
"reporting, only the VAT amount is declared; the import base amount is not "
"required in the tax report."
msgstr ""
"Uvozni DDV se evidentira po veljavni stopnji (običajno 5 %). V poročanju o "
"DDV v ZAE se navaja samo znesek DDV; osnova za uvoz ni zahtevana v davčnem "
"poročilu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"Applied when recording customs-import transactions or imports recognized "
"through the VAT return."
msgstr ""
"Uporablja se pri evidentiranju carinskih uvoznih transakcij ali uvozov, "
"priznanih prek napovedi za DDV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:0
msgid ""
"Out of Scope: Transactions that fall outside the scope of UAE VAT "
"legislation."
msgstr ""
"Zunaj obsega: Transakcije, ki ne spadajo na področje uporabe zakonodaje o "
"DDV v ZAE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:117
msgid "Transactions entirely outside the UAE"
msgstr "Transakcije v celoti zunaj ZAE"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:118
msgid "Internal accounting adjustments"
msgstr "Interne računovodske prilagoditve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:119
msgid "Certain government-mandated transfers"
msgstr "Določeni prenosi, ki jih nalaga vlada"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:122
msgid ""
"These taxes can be applied directly to products or managed dynamically "
"through fiscal positions."
msgstr ""
"Te davke je mogoče uporabiti neposredno za izdelke ali jih upravljati "
"dinamično prek davčnih položajev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:130
msgid ""
"Description: Mechanism that transfers the obligation to account for VAT from "
"the non-resident supplier to the UAE VAT-registered recipient."
msgstr ""
"Opis: Mehanizem, ki prenaša obveznost obračunavanja DDV z nerezidentnega "
"dobavitelja na prejemnika, registriranega za DDV v ZAE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:132
msgid ""
"Mechanism: The recipient declares VAT as both output VAT and input VAT in "
"the VAT return. This typically results in a net-zero impact when fully "
"recoverable."
msgstr ""
"Mehanizem: Prejemnik v davčni napovedi za DDV navede DDV kot izhodni DDV in "
"vhodni DDV. To običajno povzroči neto ničelni vpliv, če je v celoti "
"povrnitljiv."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:134
msgid ""
"Application: Commonly used for imported services and cross-border B2B "
"transactions where the supplier has no UAE VAT registration."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba: Pogosto se uporablja za uvožene storitve in čezmejne transakcije "
"B2B, kjer dobavitelj nima registracije za DDV v ZAE."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:140
msgid "VAT return (VAT201)"
msgstr "Napoved za DDV (VAT201)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:142
msgid ""
"The UAE :ref:`VAT Return report <accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` "
"includes:"
msgstr ""
"Poročilo :ref:`Napoved za DDV v ZAE <accounting/tax-returns/vat-report>` "
"vključuje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:144
msgid "Output VAT"
msgstr "Izhodni DDV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:145
msgid "Input VAT"
msgstr "Vhodni DDV"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:146
msgid "Reverse charge VAT"
msgstr "DDV po sistemu obrnjenega davčnega bremena"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:147
msgid "Zero-rated and exempt sales"
msgstr "Prodaja z ničelno stopnjo in oproščena prodaja"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:150
msgid ""
"The report structure follows the official :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax "
"Authority)` format and can be exported in both Excel and PDF formats for "
"manual submission."
msgstr ""
"Struktura poročila sledi uradni obliki :abbr:`FTA (Federal Tax Authority)` "
"in jo je mogoče izvoziti v oblikah Excel in PDF za ročno predložitev."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:156
msgid "Corporate tax report"
msgstr "Poročilo o davku od dohodkov pravnih oseb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:158
msgid ""
"The UAE Corporate Tax Report helps companies prepare for compliance with "
"local corporate tax regulations. The report is found "
"under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Corporate Tax Report` and "
"includes:"
msgstr ""
"Poročilo o davku od dohodkov pravnih oseb v ZAE pomaga podjetjem pri "
"pripravi na skladnost z lokalnimi predpisi o davku od dohodkov pravnih oseb. "
"Poročilo najdete v :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Corporate "
"Tax Report` in vključuje:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:162
msgid "Net profit"
msgstr "Neto dobiček"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:163
msgid "Exempt income"
msgstr "Oproščeni dohodek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:164
msgid "Allowable deductions"
msgstr "Dopustni odbitki"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:165
msgid "Adjustments for non-deductible (disallowed) expenses"
msgstr "Prilagoditve za neodbitne (nedovoljene) stroške"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:166
msgid "Corporate tax amount"
msgstr "Znesek davka od dohodkov pravnih oseb"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:168
msgid ""
"As part of this report, users can set :ref:`exempt income <localizations/uae/"
"exempt-income-accounts>`, :ref:`allowable deductions <localizations/uae/"
"allowable-deductions-accounts>`, and :ref:`disallowed expenses accounts "
"<localizations/uae/disallowed-expenses>`."
msgstr ""
"Kot del tega poročila lahko uporabniki nastavijo :ref:`oščete dohodke "
"<localizations/uae/exempt-income-accounts>`, :ref:`dopuščene odbitke "
"<localizations/uae/allowable-deductions-accounts>` in :ref:`račune za "
"nedopuščene stroške <localizations/uae/disallowed-expenses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:174
msgid ""
"No default fiscal categories, disallowed expenses, allowable deduction "
"accounts, or exempt income accounts are configured. Users must classify them "
"manually according to their tax situation."
msgstr ""
"Privzete davčne kategorije, nedopuščeni stroški, računi za dopuščene odbitke "
"ali računi za oščete dohodke niso konfigurirani. Uporabniki jih morajo ročno "
"razvrstiti v skladu s svojo davčno situacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:180
msgid "Exempt income accounts"
msgstr "Računi za oščete dohodke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:182
msgid ""
"Exempt income generally refers to revenue that is not subject to corporate "
"tax under UAE rules. Examples may include:"
msgstr ""
"Oščeti dohodki na splošno pomenijo prihodke, ki v skladu s predpisi ZAE niso "
"predmet davka od dohodkov pravnih oseb. Primeri lahko vključujejo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:185
msgid "Dividends received from qualifying shareholdings"
msgstr "Dividende, prejete iz kvalificiranih deležev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:186
msgid "Capital gains on the sale of qualifying shares"
msgstr "Kapitalski dobički pri prodaji kvalificiranih deležev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:188
msgid ""
"To classify exempt income, navigate to the :doc:`chart of accounts <../"
"accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>`, open the relevant account, and "
"assign the tag :guilabel:`Corporate Tax Report – Exempted Income Accounts`. "
"Tagging these accounts ensures that exempt income is reported accurately "
"without being included in the taxable base."
msgstr ""
"Za razvrstitev oščetih dohodkov pojdite na :doc:`kontni načrt <../accounting/"
"get_started/chart_of_accounts>`, odprite ustrezen račun in dodelite oznako "
":guilabel:`Poročilo o davku od dohodkov pravnih oseb – Računi za oščete "
"dohodke`. Označevanje teh računov zagotavlja, da so oščeti dohodki točno "
"poročani, ne da bi bili vključeni v obdavčljivo osnovo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:196
msgid "Allowable deductions accounts"
msgstr "Računi za dopuščene odbitke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:198
msgid ""
"Allowable deductions are expenses that are incurred solely for business "
"purposes. Examples include:"
msgstr ""
"Dopuščeni odbitki so stroški, ki nastanejo izključno v poslovne namene. "
"Primeri vključujejo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:201
msgid "Employee salaries and benefits"
msgstr "Plače in ugodnosti kadra"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:202
msgid "Office rent, utilities, and professional services"
msgstr "Najemnina pisarne, režijski stroški in strokovne storitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:204
msgid ""
"To classify allowable deductions, navigate to the :doc:`chart of accounts "
"<../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>`, open the relevant expense "
"account, and assign the tag :guilabel:`Corporate Tax Report – Allowable "
