#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:111
msgid ""
"The :doc:`chart of accounts (COA) <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` for the United States localization, in Odoo, follows the "
"standard |GAAP| structure, with accounts grouped into seven main categories, "
"with corresponding numeric values that prefix individual journal entries:"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Kontni načrt <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` za "
"lokalizacijo Združenih držav v Odoo sledi standardni strukturi |GAAP|, z "
"računi, razvrščenimi v sedem glavnih kategorij, s pripadajočimi številčnimi "
"vrednostmi, ki so predpona posameznih dnevniških vnosov:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:121
msgid ""
"**Equity**: the amount of money that is returned to a company's shareholders "
"if all of the assets were liquidated and all of the company's debt was paid "
"off in the case of liquidation. Equity is indicated by the journal code "
"labeled (or beginning) with :guilabel:`3` or :guilabel:`9`."
msgstr ""
"**Kapital**: znesek denarja, ki je vrnjen delničarjem podjetja, če bi bila "
"vsa sredstva likvidirana in bi bil ves dolg podjetja poplačan v primeru "
"likvidacije. Kapital je označen s kodo dnevnika, ki je označena (ali se "
"začne) z :guilabel:`3` ali :guilabel:`9`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:137
msgid ""
"Predefined accounts are included in Odoo, as part of the |CoA| that is "
"installed with the US localization package. The accounts listed below are "
"preconfigured to perform certain operations within Odoo. It is recommended "
"to **not** delete these accounts; however, if changes are needed, rename the "
"accounts instead."
msgstr ""
"Vnaprej določeni računi so vključeni v Odoo kot del |CoA|, ki je nameščen z "
"lokalizacijskim paketom za ZDA. Spodaj navedeni računi so vnaprej "
"konfigurirani za izvajanje določenih operacij v Odoo. Priporočljivo je, da "
"teh računov **ne** izbrišete; če pa so potrebne spremembe, račune "
"preimenujte."

