#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:434
msgid ""
"European accounting frameworks include appropriation of profit in the "
"generic |P&L| statement. Under |GAAP| accounting standards, the |P&L| "
"statement summarizes performance only. As a result, the US report does not "
"include *Allocations and Withdrawals*."
msgstr ""
"Evropski računovodski okviri vključujejo razporeditev dobička v splošnem "
"|P&L| izkazu. Po računovodskih standardih |GAAP| izkaz |P&L| povzema samo "
"uspešnost. Posledično ameriški izkaz ne vključuje *Rezervacij in dvigov*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:454
msgid ""
"Using checks is still a common payment practice in the US. Be sure the *US "
"Checks Layout* (`l10n_us_check_printing`) module for the US localization "
"is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba čekov je v ZDA še vedno pogosta plačilna praksa. Prepričajte se, da "
"je modul *US Checks Layout* (`l10n_us_check_printing`) za ameriško "
"lokalizacijo :ref:`nameščen <general/install>`."

