msgstr ":guilabel:`Print Blank Check (Bottom) - US`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:472
msgid ""
"Optionally set a :guilabel:`Check Top Margin` and :guilabel:`Check Left "
"Margin`, if required."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi nastavite :guilabel:`Check Top Margin` in :guilabel:`Check Left "
"Margin`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:477
msgid ""
"Pre-printed check formats (non-blank checks) require pre-printed paper from "
"a third-party vendor. `Pre-printed checks from checkdepot.net <https://"
"checkdepot.net/collections/odoo-checks>`_ are recommended."
msgstr ""
"Vnaprej natisnjeni formati čekov (ne-prazni čeki) zahtevajo vnaprej "
"natisnjeno papir tretje osebe. Priporočeni so `vnaprej natisnjeni čeki iz "
"checkdepot.net <https://checkdepot.net/collections/odoo-checks>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:483
msgid ""
"Use one of the blank check formats to print the information of the check ad-"
"hoc when needed. This requires the use of both :abbr:`MICR (Magnetic Ink "
"Character Recognition)` ink or toner complying with the standards for check "
"printing, as well as `check quality paper <https://checkdepot.net/"
"collections/blank-check-paper/products/top-format-blank-check-paper-"
"cdt164>`_. Other information, such as the company name, bank account, and "
"check number, is printed when creating the blank check."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite enega od formatov praznih čekov za tiskanje informacij čeka ad-hoc "
"po potrebi. To zahteva uporabo tako :abbr:`MICR (Magnetic Ink Character "
"Recognition)` črnila ali tonerja, ki ustreza standardom za tiskanje čekov, "
"kot tudi `papirja kakovosti čekov <https://checkdepot.net/collections/blank-"
"check-paper/products/top-format-blank-check-paper-cdt164>`_. Druge "
"informacije, kot so ime podjetja, bančni račun in številka čeka, se "
"natisnejo pri ustvarjanju praznega čeka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:498
msgid ""
"The **Payroll** app is responsible for calculating an employee's pay, taking "
"into account all work, vacation, and sick time, benefits, and deductions. "
"The **Payroll** app pulls information from the **Attendances**, "
"**Timesheets**, **Time Off**, **Employees** and **Expenses** apps, to "
"calculate the worked hours and compensation for each employee."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija **Plačni seznam** je odgovorna za izračun plače kadra ob "
"upoštevanju vsega dela, dopusta in bolniškega staleža, ugodnosti in "
"odbitkov. Aplikacija **Plačni seznam** povleče informacije iz aplikacij "
"**Prisotnosti**, **Časovnice**, **Odsotnost**, **Kader** in **Stroški**, da "
"izračuna opravljene ure in nadomestilo za vsakega kadra."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:503
msgid ""
"When using an external payroll provider, such as *ADP*, it is necessary to "
"export the various payroll-related data, such as work entries, repayment of "
"expenses, taxes, commissions, and any other relevant data, so the data can "
"be uploaded into the payroll provider, who then issues the actual paychecks "
"or directly deposits the funds into an employee's bank account."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi zunanjega ponudnika plač, kot je *ADP*, je potrebno izvoziti "
"različne podatke, povezane s plačami, kot so vnosi dela, povračila stroškov, "
"davki, provizije in vsi drugi relevantni podatki, da se lahko podatki "
"naložijo v ponudnika plač, ki nato izdela dejanske plačne čeke ali "
"neposredno nakaže sredstva na bančni račun zaposlenega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:508
msgid ""
"In order to export the payroll data, the work entries must first be "
"validated and correct. Refer to the :doc:`work entries <../../hr/payroll/"
"work_entries>` documentation for more information regarding validating work "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Za izvoz podatkov o plačah je treba najprej potrditi in popraviti vnose "
"dela. Za več informacij o potrjevanju vnosov dela glejte dokumentacijo "
":doc:`vnosi dela <../../hr/payroll/work_entries>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:512
msgid ""
"Once work entries are validated, the information can be :ref:`exported to "
"ADP <l10n_us/adp>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vnosi dela potrjeni, je informacije mogoče :ref:`izvoziti v ADP "
"<l10n_us/adp>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:514
msgid ""
"After payments have been issued to employees, payslips can be processed into "
"batches, validated, and posted to the corresponding accounting journals to "
"keep all financial records in Odoo current."
msgstr ""
"Ko so plačila izdana zaposlenim, je plačilne liste mogoče obdelati v "
"serijah, potrditi in knjiti v ustrezne računovodske dnevnike, da bodo vsi "
"finančni zapisi v Odoo posodobljeni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:520
msgid ""
"It is important to have the **Employees** app installed, and all employee "
"information populated. Several fields in both the :ref:`employee records "
"<l10n_us/payroll-employee-records>`, as well as in an :ref:`employee "
"contracts <l10n_us/payroll-employee-contracts>`, are necessary to properly "
"process the employee's pay. Ensure the following fields are filled out in "
"their respective places."
msgstr ""
"Pomembno je, da je aplikacija **Kader** nameščena in da so izpolnjeni vsi "
"podatki o zaposlenih. Za pravilno obdelavo plače zaposlenega je potrebnih "
"več polj v :ref:`zapisih zaposlenih <l10n_us/payroll-employee-records>` kot "
"tudi v :ref:`pogodbah o zaposlitvi <l10n_us/payroll-employee-contracts>`. "
"Preverite, da so naslednja polja izpolnjena na ustreznih mestih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:528
msgid "Employee records"
msgstr "Zapisi kadra"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:530
msgid ""
"In each employee record, there is various information the **Payroll** app "
"requires to properly process payslips, including various banking, tax, and "
"work information."
msgstr ""
"V vsakem zapisu zaposlenega so različne informacije, ki jih aplikacija "
"**Plačni seznam** zahteva za pravilno obdelavo plačnih list, vključno z "
"različnimi bančnimi, davčnimi in delovnimi podatki."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:533
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :menuselection:`Employees app` and select an employee record "
"to view the sections of the employee form that directly affect *Payroll*:"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`aplikacijo Kader` in izberite zapis zaposlenega, "
"da si ogledate dele obrazca zaposlenega, ki neposredno vplivajo na *Plačni "
"seznam*:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:536
msgid ":guilabel:`Work Information` tab:"
msgstr "Zavihek :guilabel:`Work Information`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:538
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Address`: indicates where the employee is located, including "
"the state, which affects the tax calculations."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Work Address`: označuje, kje se zaposleni nahaja, vključno z "
"državo, kar vpliva na izračune davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:540
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours`: determines how pay is calculated, and determines "
"if an employee earns overtime."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours`: določa, kako se izračuna plača, in določa, ali "
"zaposleni zasluži nadure."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:543
msgid ":guilabel:`Private Information` tab:"
msgstr "Zavihek :guilabel:`Zasebne informacije`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:545
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:579
msgid ""
":guilabel:`SSN No`: the last four digits of the employee's Social Security "
"Number (SSN) appears on payslips."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Št. SSN`: zadnje štiri številke zaposlenikovega socialnovarstvene "
"številke (SSN) se prikazujejo na plačilnih listih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:547
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bank Account Number`: the bank account associated with the NACHA "
"payment file."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Številka bančnega računa`: bančni račun, povezan z NACHA plačilno "
"datoteko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:549
msgid ":guilabel:`HR Settings` tab:"
msgstr "Zavihek :guilabel:`Nastavitve kadrov`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:551
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Federal Tax Filing Status`: the tax status an employee uses for "
"Payroll tax calculations, which can be different from their state status."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status davčne prijave na zvezni ravni`: davčni status, ki ga "
"zaposleni uporablja za izračun davkov iz plačnega seznama in se lahko "
"razlikuje od njegovega statusa v državi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:553
msgid ""
":guilabel:`State Tax Filing Status`: the tax status an employee uses for "
"their state portion of the Payroll tax calculation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Status davčne prijave za državo`: davčni status, ki ga zaposleni "
"uporablja za državni del izračuna davkov iz plačnega seznama."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:555
msgid ""
":guilabel:`W-2 Form`: a US tax form indicating the summary of wages, taxes, "
"and benefits paid to an employee during a tax period (typically one year)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obrazec W-2`: ameriški davčni obrazec, ki prikazuje povzetek "
"plač, davkov in ugodnosti, plačanih zaposlenemu v davčnem obdobju (običajno "
"eno leto)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:557
msgid ""
":guilabel:`W-4 Form`: an IRS form that helps outline the amount of federal "
"taxes to withhold for an employee, which is paid to the IRS by the company."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obrazec W-4`: obrazec IRS, ki pomaga določiti znesek zveznih "
"davkov, ki jih je treba odtegniti za zaposlenega in jih podjetje nakaže IRS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:563
msgid "Employee contracts"
msgstr "Pogodbe z zaposlenimi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:565
msgid ""
"Additionally, there is information that is found in an employee contract "
"that also affects the **Payroll** app."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega se v pogodbi o zaposlitvi nahajajo informacije, ki prav tako "
"vplivajo na aplikacijo **Plačni seznam**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:568
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :menuselection:`Employees app --> Employees --> Contracts` "
"and select a contract record to view the sections of a contract that "
"directly affect *Payroll*:"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Kader --> Kader --> Pogodbe` in "
"izberite zapis pogodbe, da si ogledate razdelke pogodbe, ki neposredno "
"vplivajo na *Plačni seznam*:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:571
msgid ":guilabel:`General Information`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Splošne informacije`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:573
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salary Structure Type: United States: Employee`: defines when the "
"employee is paid, their working schedule, and the work entry type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta strukture plače: Združene države: Zaposleni`: določa, kdaj "
"je zaposleni plačan, njegov delovni urnik in vrsto vnosa dela."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:575
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry source`: determines how work entries are calculated."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vir vnosa dela`: določa, kako se izračunavajo vnosi dela."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:577
msgid ":guilabel:`Salary Information` tab:"
msgstr "Zavihek :guilabel:`Informacije o plači`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:581
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage type`: determines how the employee is paid, wether a Fixed "
"wage (salary) or Hourly wage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta plače`: določa, kako je zaposleni plačan, bodisi s fiksno "
"plačo (mesečno) ali urno postavko."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:583
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule Pay`: defines how often the employee is paid, "
"either :guilabel:`Annually`, :guilabel:`Semi-"
"annually`, :guilabel:`Quarterly`, :guilabel:`Bi-"
"monthly`, :guilabel:`Monthly`, :guilabel:`Semi-monthly`, :guilabel:`Bi-"
"weekly`, :guilabel:`Weekly`, or :guilabel:`Daily`. In the US, Semi-monthly "
"(24 payments a year) or bi-weekly (26 payments a year) are the most common."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Razpored plačila`: določa, kako pogosto je zaposleni plačan, "
"bodisi :guilabel:`Letno`, :guilabel:`Polletno`, :guilabel:`Četrtletno`, "
":guilabel:`Dvomesečno`, :guilabel:`Mesečno`, :guilabel:`Polmesečno`, "
":guilabel:`Štirinajstdnevno`, :guilabel:`Tedensko` ali :guilabel:`Dnevno`. V "
"ZDA sta najpogostejša polmesečna (24 plačil na leto) ali štirinajstdnevna "
"(26 plačil na leto) plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:587
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage, Yearly, and Monthly cost`: used to show the total cost of "
"an employee. It is recommended to populate the :guilabel:`Yearly` wage "
"first, as it auto-populates the other fields."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Plača, letni in mesečni stroški`: uporabljeno za prikaz skupnih "
"stroškov zaposlenega. Priporočljivo je najprej izpolniti polje "
":guilabel:`Letno`, saj samodejno izpolni ostala polja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:590
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pre-tax benefits`: populate this section according to the "
"employee's selections. Pre-tax benefits decrease the gross wage, which "
"lowers the base amount that is taxed. These are displayed at the beginning "
"of the payslip."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ugodnosti pred obdavčitvijo`: izpolnite ta razdelek v skladu z "
"izbirami zaposlenega. Ugodnosti pred obdavčitvijo znižujejo bruto plačo, kar "
"zmanjšuje osnovni znesek, ki se obdavčuje. Te so prikazane na začetku "
"plačilnega lista."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:593
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Post-tax benefits`: these benefits are deductions made *after* "
"taxes are calculated. These appear towards the end of the payslip before the "
"net amount is displayed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ugodnosti po obdavčitvi`: te ugodnosti so odbitki, ki se izvedejo "
"*po* izračunu davkov. Prikazane so proti koncu plačilnega lista, preden je "
"prikazan neto znesek."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:597
msgid ":doc:`Employees documentation <../../hr/employees/new_employee>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Dokumentacija kadrov <../../hr/employees/new_employee>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:602
msgid "Export work entries to ADP"
msgstr "Izvozi vnose dela v ADP"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:607
msgid ""
"In order to create a report that can be uploaded to ADP, there are some "
"initial configuration steps that must be completed first."
msgstr ""
"Da ustvarite poročilo, ki ga je mogoče naložiti v ADP, je treba najprej "
"končati nekaj začetnih konfiguracijskih korakov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:610
msgid ""
"First, ensure the *United States - Payroll - Export to ADP* "
"(`l10n_us_hr_payroll_adp`) module is :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Najprej se prepričajte, da je modul *United States - Payroll - Export to "
"ADP* (`l10n_us_hr_payroll_adp`) :ref:`nameščen <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:613
msgid ""
"Then, the company **must** have an *ADP Code* entered in the company "
"settings. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Enter the :guilabel:`ADP Code` in "
"the :guilabel:`US Localization` section."
msgstr ""
"Nato **mora** imeti podjetje v nastavitvah podjetja vneseno *kodo ADP*. To "
"storite tako, da se pomaknete na :menuselection:`aplikacija Plačni "
"seznam --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. Vnesite :guilabel:`kodo ADP` v "
"razdelek :guilabel:`Lokalizacija ZDA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:617
msgid ""
"Next, work entry types **must** have the correct ADP code listed in the "
"*External Code* field for each work entry type that is being referenced."
msgstr ""
"Nato **morajo** imeti tipi vnosov dela v polju *Zunanja koda* navedeno "
"pravilno kodo ADP za vsak tip vnosa dela, na katerega se sklicuje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:620
msgid ""
"Lastly, every employee **must** have an *ADP Code* entered on their employee "
"form. To do so, navigate to :menuselection:`Employees app`, select an "
"employee record, and open the :guilabel:`HR Settings` tab. Enter "
"the :guilabel:`ADP Code` in the :guilabel:`ADP Information` section."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje **mora** imeti vsak zaposleni v obrazcu zaposlenega vneseno *kodo "
"ADP*. To storite tako, da se pomaknete na :menuselection:`aplikacija Kader`, "
"izberete zapis zaposlenega in odprete zavihek :guilabel:`Nastavitve kadrov`. "
"Vnesite :guilabel:`kodo ADP` v razdelek :guilabel:`Informacije ADP`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:624
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`ADP Code` code is how ADP identifies that particular "
"employee, and is typically a six-digit number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Koda ADP` je način, kako ADP identificira dooločenega "
"zaposlenega, in je običajno šestmestna številka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:628
msgid ":ref:`payroll/new-work-entry`"
msgstr ":ref:`payroll/new-work-entry`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:629
msgid ":doc:`../../hr/employees/new_employee`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../hr/employees/new_employee`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:632
msgid "Export data"
msgstr "Izvozi podatke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:634
msgid ""
"Once :doc:`work entries <../../hr/payroll/work_entries>` have been verified, "
"the information can be exported to a CSV file, which can then be uploaded "
"into ADP."
msgstr ""
"Ko so :doc:`vnosi dela <../../hr/payroll/work_entries>` preverjeni, je "
"mogoče informacije izvoziti v datoteko CSV, ki jo je nato mogoče naložiti v "
"ADP."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:637
msgid ""
"To export the data, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting --"
"> United States: ADP Export`, then click :guilabel:`New`. Next, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Start Date` and :guilabel:`End Date` for the work entries "
"using the calendar pop-over."
msgstr ""
"Za izvoz podatkov se pomaknite na :menuselection:`aplikacija Plačni "
"seznam --> Poročanje --> Združene države Amerike: izvoz ADP` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Novo`. Nato vnesite :guilabel:`Začetni datum` in "
":guilabel:`Končni datum` za vnose dela s pomočjo pojavnega okna s koledarjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:641
msgid ""
"Then, enter a :guilabel:`Batch ID` in the corresponding field. The "
"recommendation for this field is to enter the date in a `YY-MM-DD` format, "
"followed by any other characters to distinguish that specific batch, such as "
"a department name, or any other defining characteristics for the batch."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite :guilabel:`ID serije` v ustrezno polje. Priporočilo za to polje "
"je, da vnesete datum v obliki `YY-MM-DD`, ki mu sledijo drugi znaki za "
"razlikovanje te določene serije, kot je ime oddelka ali druge značilnosti "
"serije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:645
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Batch Description` in the corresponding field. This "
"should be short and descriptive, but distinct from the :guilabel:`Batch "
"Name`."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite :guilabel:`Opis serije` v ustrezno polje. To mora biti kratko in "
"opisno, vendar različno od :guilabel:`Imena serije`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:648
msgid ""
"Ensure the correct company populates the :guilabel:`Company` field. Change "
"the selected company with the drop-down menu, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je v polje :guilabel:`Podjetje` vneseno pravo podjetje. "
"Po potrebi spremenite izbrano podjetje s spustnim menijem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:651
msgid ""
"Lastly, add the employee's work entry information to the list. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` and an :guilabel:`Add: Employee` pop-up window "
"loads. The list can be :doc:`filtered <../../essentials/search>` to find the "
"employees to add to the list."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu dodajte informacije o delovnih vnosih zaposlenega na seznam. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` in naloži se pojavno okno "
":guilabel:`Dodaj: Zaposleni`. Seznam je mogoče :doc:`filtrirati <../../"
"essentials/search>`, da najdete zaposlene, ki jih želite dodati na seznam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:656
msgid ""
"Process the data export in multiple groups instead of in one large group "
"that contains all employees. This helps to meaningfully differentiate the "
"batches and makes processing more tenable, overall. The most common ways to "
"group employees is by department, or by wage type (hourly or salaried)."
msgstr ""
"Obdelujte izvoz podatkov v več skupinah namesto v eni veliki skupini, ki "
"vsebuje vse zaposlene. To pomaga pri smiselnem razlikovanju serij in splošno "
"olajša obdelavo. Najpogostejša načina grupiranja zaposlenih sta po oddelku "
"ali po vrsti plače (urna ali fiksna)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:661
msgid ""
"Select the employees to add to the list by ticking the box to the left of "
"their name. Once all desired employees have been selected, click "
"the :guilabel:`Select` button in the lower-left corner, and the employees "
"appear in the list."
msgstr ""
"Izberite zaposlene, ki jih želite dodati na seznam, tako da označite polje "
"levo od njihovega imena. Ko so vsi želeni zaposleni izbrani, kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Izberi` v spodnjem levem kotu in zaposleni se prikažejo na "
"seznamu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:665
msgid ""
"To create the CSV file, click the :guilabel:`Generate` button in the top-"
"left corner."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje datoteke CSV kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Generiraj` v zgornjem "
"levem kotu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:670
msgid "ACH - electronic transfers"
msgstr "ACH - elektronska nakazila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:672
msgid ""
"Automated Clearing House (ACH) payments are a modern way to transfer funds "
"electronically between bank accounts, replacing traditional paper-based "
"methods. |ACH| payments are commonly used for direct deposits, bill "
"payments, and business transactions."
msgstr ""
"Plačila Automated Clearing House (ACH) so sodoben način elektornskega "
"prenosa sredstev med bančnimi računi, ki nadomestiča tradicionalne papirne "
"metode. |ACH| plačila se pogosto uporabljajo za neposredna nakazila, plačila "
"računov in poslovne transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:677
msgid "Receive ACH payments: payment provider integration"
msgstr "Prejem plačil ACH: integracija ponudnika plačil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:679
msgid ""
"|ACH| payments are supported by *Authorize.net* and *Stripe* payment "
"integrations in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Plačila |ACH| podpirata integraciji plačil *Authorize.net* in *Stripe* v "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:682
msgid ""
":ref:`Setting up Authorize.net for ACH payments (Odoo) <authorize/"
"ach_payments>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Nastavitev Authorize.net za plačila ACH (Odoo) <authorize/ach_payments>"
"`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:683
msgid ""
"`Authorize.net's ACH payment processing for small businesses documentation "
"<https://www.authorize.net/resources/blog/2021/ach-payments-for-small-"
"businesses.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentacija Authorize.net za procesiranje plačil ACH za mala podjetja "
"<https://www.authorize.net/resources/blog/2021/ach-payments-for-small-"
"businesses.html>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:685
msgid ""
":doc:`Setting up Stripe for ACH payments (Odoo) <../payment_providers/"
"stripe>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Nastavitev Stripe za plačila ACH (Odoo) <../payment_providers/stripe>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:686
msgid ""
"`Stripe's ACH Direct Debit documentation <https://docs.stripe.com/payments/"
"ach-debit>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Dokumentacija Stripe za ACH Direct Debit <https://docs.stripe.com/payments/"
"ach-debit>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:691
msgid "Send payments: NACHA files"
msgstr "Pošiljanje plačil: datoteke NACHA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:693
msgid ""
"Odoo can generate a National Automated Clearing House Association (NACHA) "
"compatible |ACH| file to send to a company's bank. For each individual "
"*Bank* journal that the company wishes to pay vendors with, a |NACHA| "
"configuration section needs to be filled out on the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo lahko ustvari datoteko |ACH|, združljivo z National Automated Clearing "
"House Association (NACHA), za pošiljanje banki podjetja. Za vsak posamezen "
"dnevnik *Banka*, s katerim želi podjetje plačevati dobaviteljem, je treba v "
"podatkovni bazi Odoo izpolniti konfiguracijski razdelek |NACHA|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:700
msgid ""
"First, navigate to the :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> "
"Journals`. Open the bank journal and click into the :guilabel:`Outgoing "
"Payments` tab."
msgstr ""
"Najprej pojdite v :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Dnevniki`. Odprite bančni dnevnik in kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Odhodna "
"plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"NACHA (National Automated Clearing House Association) configuration settings "
"on Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijske nastavitve NACHA (National Automated Clearing House "
"Association) v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:707
msgid ""
"The following |NACHA| configuration information is normally provided by the "
"company's financial institution once they have been approved to send "
"payments via their account."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje konfiguracijske informacije |NACHA| običajno zagotovi finančna "
"institucija podjetja, ko je odobreno za pošiljanje plačil prek svojega "
"računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:710
msgid ""
"Under the section labeled, :guilabel:`NACHA configuration` are the fields "
"required to generate a |NACHA| compatible |ACH| file to send to a company's "
"bank. First, enter the routing number of the financial institution in the "
"field labeled, :guilabel:`Immediate Destination`. This information is widely "
"available on the Internet and generally varies by bank location. This number "
"is usually provided during the initial account setup."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku z oznako :guilabel:`Konfiguracija NACHA` so polja, potrebna za "
"ustvarjanje datoteke |ACH|, združljive z |NACHA|, za pošiljanje banki "
"podjetja. Najprej vnesite usmeritveno številko finančne institucije v polje "
"z oznako :guilabel:`Immediate Destination`. Ta informacija je široko "
"dostopna na internetu in se običajno razlikuje glede na lokacijo banke. Ta "
"številka je običajno zagotovljena med začetno nastavitvijo računa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:716
msgid ""
"Next, enter the registered name of the financial institution in the field "
"called, :guilabel:`Destination`. This information is provided by the bank or "
"credit union."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite registrirano ime finančne ustanove v polje z imenom "
":guilabel:`Destinacija`. Te informacije zagotovi banka ali kreditna unija."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:719
msgid ""
"Following the :guilabel:`Destination` field is the :guilabel:`Immediate "
"Origin` field. Enter the 9-digit company ID or Employer Identification "
"Number (EIN) into this field. This information is provided by the financial "
"institution."
msgstr ""
"Za poljem :guilabel:`Destination` sledi polje :guilabel:`Immediate Origin`. "
"V to polje vnesite 9-mestno ID podjetja ali davčno številko delodajalca (EIN)"
". To informacijo zagotovi finančna institucija."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:723
msgid ""
"Next, enter the :guilabel:`Company Identification` number, which is a 10-"
"digit number made from combining the 9-digit company ID or Employer "
"Identification Number (EIN), along with an additional number at the start of "
"the sequence. This number is often a `1`. Check with the financial "
"institution should this first number differ to verify that it is correct, as "
"this number is provided for |ACH| approved accounts."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite številko :guilabel:`Company Identification`, ki je 10-mestna "
"številka, sestavljena iz kombinacije 9-mestnega ID-ja podjetja ali davčne "
"številke delodajalca (EIN) skupaj z dodatno številko na začetku zaporedja. "
"Ta številka je pogosto `1`. Preverite s finančno institucijo, če se ta prva "
"številka razlikuje, da preverite, ali je pravilna, saj je ta številka "
"zagotovljena za račune, odobrene za |ACH|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:729
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Originating DFI Identification` number next, which "
"should contain an assigned 8-digit number from the financial institution."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite številko :guilabel:`Originating DFI Identification`, ki naj "
"vsebuje dodeljeno 8-mestno številko finančne institucije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:733
msgid ""
"Enter the numerical values in this section *exactly* as the company's "
"financial institution (e.g. bank or credit union) has provided them, "
"otherwise risk failing a successful |NACHA| configuration in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite številčne vrednosti v tem razdelku *natančno* tako, kot jih je "
"zagotovila finančna institucija podjetja (npr. banka ali kreditna unija), "
"sicer tvegate neuspešno konfiguracijo |NACHA| v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"NACHA settings with the standard entry class code drop-down menu highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve NACHA s poudarjenim spustnim menijem za kodo razreda standardnega "
"vnosa."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:740
msgid ""
"Two options are available for the next field: :guilabel:`Standard Entry "
"Class Code`. Select the drop-down menu to the right of the field and pick "
"either :guilabel:`Corporate Credit or Debit (CCD)` or :guilabel:`Prearranged "
"Payment and Deposit (PPD)`. Again, this information is provided by the "
"financial institution. By default :guilabel:`Corporate Credit or Debit "
"(CCD)` is selected."
msgstr ""
"Za naslednje polje sta na voljo dve možnosti: :guilabel:`Koda razreda "
"standardnega vnosa`. Izberite spustni meni na desni strani polja in izberite "
"bodisi :guilabel:`Korporativni kredit ali debet (CCD)` bodisi "
":guilabel:`Vnaprej dogovorjeno plačilo in polog (PPD)`. Tudi te informacije "
"zagotovi finančna ustanova. Privzeto je izbrano :guilabel:`Korporativni "
"kredit ali debet (CCD)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:745
msgid ""
"Finally, the last option is for :guilabel:`Generated Balanced Files`. Tick "
"the checkbox to the right of the field to enable :guilabel:`Generated "
"Balanced Files`. Consult the company's accountant or financial adviser to "
"make an informed decision for this field."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje je zadnja možnost za :guilabel:`Ustvarjene uravnotežene datoteke`. "
"Označite potrditveno polje na desni strani polja, da omogočite "
":guilabel:`Ustvarjene uravnotežene datoteke`. Posvetujte se z računovodjo "
"ali finančnim svetovalcem podjetja, da sprejmete premišljeno odločitev za to "
"polje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:749
msgid ""
"Manually save the configuration by clicking the :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(cloud upload)` icon, or navigate away from this screen "
"to auto-save. The configuration is now complete."
msgstr ""
"Ročno shranite konfiguracijo s klikom na ikono :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` "
":guilabel:`(prenos v oblak)` ali zapustite ta zaslon za samodejno "
"shranjevanje. Konfiguracija je zdaj dokončana."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:755
msgid "Create batch payment"
msgstr "Ustvari paketno plačilo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:757
msgid "Now, record each payment in Odoo using the |NACHA| payment method."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj v Odoo zabeležite vsako plačilo z uporabo plačilnega načina |NACHA|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:760
msgid ""
":ref:`Register Payments in Odoo <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Evidentiranje plačil v Odoo <accounting/payments/from-invoice-bill>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:763
msgid ""
"Be aware of the cut-off time for same-day payments. Either the file needs to "
"have a future date associated with each payment or the file needs to be sent "
"prior to the cut-off, if the dates included in it match today's date. "
"Consult the financial institution for the exact cut-off time for their "
"processing of same-day payments."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte mejni čas za plačila isti dan. Datoteka mora imeti prihodnji "
"datum, povezan z vsakim plačilom, ali pa jo je treba poslati pred mejnim "
"časom, če se datumi v njej ujemajo z današnjim datumom. Za natančen mejni "
"čas obdelave plačil isti dan se posvetujte s finančno institucijo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:768
msgid ""
"Once all the payments to be included in the |NACHA| |ACH| file have been "
"made, a batch payment needs to be made from the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Action` menu."
msgstr ""
"Ko so izvedena vsa plačila, ki naj bih bila vključena v datoteko |NACHA| "
"|ACH|, je treba ustvariti paketno plačilo iz menija :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Dejanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:771
msgid ""
"To create the batch payments, access the payments page, by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Payments`. Select all the "
"payments that should be included in the |NACHA| |ACH| file, by ticking the "
"checkboxes to the far-left of the rows."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje paketnih plačil odprite stran s plačili tako, da se pomaknete "
"na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Plačila`. Izberite vsa "
"plačila, ki naj bodo vključena v datoteko |NACHA| |ACH|, tako da označite "
"potrditvena polja na skrajni levi strani vrstic."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid ""
"On the payments screen, the action menu is highlighted with create a batch "
"payment\n"
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Na zaslonu plačil je označen meni dejanj z izbrano možnostjo ustvari paketno "
"plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:780
msgid ""
"All payments in the batch **must** share the same |NACHA| payment method."
msgstr "Vsa plačila v paketu **morajo** imeti isto plačilno metodo |NACHA|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:782
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to the batched payment (:menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Vendors --> Batch Payments`). Click into the payment recently created and "
