#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1089
msgid "XML (same base) with U.S. data rules"
msgstr "XML (ista osnova) s pravili za podatke v ZDA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1090
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "Primeri"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1091
msgid "SEPA Credit Transfer (Europe), SWIFT MX messages"
msgstr "SEPA Credit Transfer (Evropa), sporočila SWIFT MX"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1092
msgid "Fedwire ISO 20022, CHIPS ISO 20022"
msgstr "Fedwire ISO 20022, CHIPS ISO 20022"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1093
msgid "Differences"
msgstr "Razlike"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1094
msgid "Global fields and formats"
msgstr "Globalna polja in formati"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1095
msgid ""
"Trimmed or modified to fit U.S. needs (e.g., ABA routing numbers instead of "
"IBANs)"
msgstr ""
"Prirezano ali prilagojeno potrebam ZDA (npr. številke usmerjanja ABA namesto "
"IBAN)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1098
msgid ""
"It is recommended to use the generic ISO20022 for *international* transfers, "
"and use the U.S. ISO20022 for *domestic* transfers."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je uporabiti splošni ISO20022 za *mednarodne* prenose in "
"ameriški ISO20022 za *domače* prenose."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1104
msgid ""
"First, :ref:`create <accounting/vendor_bills/creation>` and :ref:`confirm "
"<accounting/vendor_bills/bill-confirmation>` a vendor bill. Then, click "
"the :guilabel:`Pay` button, and a :guilabel:`Pay` pop-up window loads. Using "
"the drop-down menu, select :guilabel:`ISO20022` in the :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method` field, then click :guilabel:`Create Payment`."
msgstr ""
"Najprej :ref:`ustvarite <accounting/vendor_bills/creation>` in "
":ref:`potrdite <accounting/vendor_bills/bill-confirmation>` račun "
"dobavitelja. Nato kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Plačaj` in naloži se pojavno okno "
":guilabel:`Plačaj`. V spustnem meniju izberite :guilabel:`ISO20022` v polju "
":guilabel:`Način plačila`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "The Pay pop-up window configured for ISO20022."
msgstr "Pojavno okno Plačaj, konfigurirano za ISO20022."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1112
msgid ""
"A green :guilabel:`In Payment` banner now appears on the vendor bill. Next, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Vendors --> Payments`, and tick "
"the checkbox next to the payment that was paid using ISO20022 file to select "
"it. Click :guilabel:`Create Batch`, then click :guilabel:`Validate` on the "
"batch form. Once validated, the batch payment moves to the :guilabel:`Sent` "
"stage, and the U.S. ISO20022 XML file is created and added to the chatter. "
"The XML file can be downloaded and used to initiate a bank payment."
msgstr ""
"Na računu dobavitelja se zdaj prikaže zelen napis :guilabel:`V plačilu`. "
"Nato pojdite na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Dobavitelji --> Plačila` "
"in odkljukajte potrditveno polje poleg plačila, ki je bilo plačano z "
"datoteko ISO20022, da ga izberete. Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari paket`, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi` na obrazcu paketa. Ko je potrjen, se paketno "
"plačilo premakne v fazo :guilabel:`Poslano` in datoteka XML ameriškega "
"ISO20022 je ustvarjena ter dodana v pogovor. Datoteko XML je mogoče prenesti "
"in uporabiti za začetek bančnega plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "A batch payment with the XML file in the chatter."
msgstr "Paketno plačilo z datoteko XML v pogovoru."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1122
msgid ""
"Once the XML file is created, the following steps occur **outside** of the "
"Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Ko je datoteka XML ustvarjena, se naslednji koraki zgodijo **zunaj** baze "
"podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1124
msgid ""
"Log into the bank's online portal or payment system. Most banks that support "
"ISO 20022 have a special section for `file uploads` or `import payments`. "
"Upload the XML ISO 20022 file created by Odoo (ending in `.xml`) and upload "
"it to the bank system."
msgstr ""
"Prijavite se v spletni portal banke ali plačilni sistem. Večina bank, ki "
"podpirajo ISO 20022, ima poseben razdelek za `nalaganje datotek` ali `uvoz "
"plačil`. Naložite datoteko XML ISO 20022, ki jo je ustvaril Odoo (končnica "
"`.xml`), v bančni sistem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1128
msgid ""
"The bank checks the XML file by reading the file and making sure all details "
"(accounts, amounts, etc.) are valid. The list of payments appears inside the "
"file. Review and confirm the information, then click `Approve` or `Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Banka preveri datoteko XML tako, da prebere datoteko in se prepriča, da so "
"vsi podatki (računi, zneski itd.) veljavni. Seznam plačil se prikaže v "
"datoteki. Preglejte in potrdite informacije, nato kliknite `Odobri` ali "
"`Pošlji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_states.rst:1132
msgid ""
"The bank processes each payment in the file and transfers the funds to the "
"recipients."
msgstr "Banka obdela vsako plačilo v datoteki in prenese sredstva prejemnikom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:3
msgid "Uruguay"
msgstr "Urugvaj"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:14
msgid ""
"With the Uruguayan localization, you can generate electronic documents with "
"its XML, fiscal folio, electronic signature and connection to tax authority "
"Dirección General Impositiva (DGI) through Uruware."
msgstr ""
"Z urugvajsko lokalizacijo lahko ustvarite elektronske dokumente z XML-jem, "
"davčno številko, elektronskim podpisom in povezavo do davčnega organa "
"Dirección General Impositiva (DGI) prek Uruware."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:20
msgid ""
":guilabel:`e-Invoice`, :guilabel:`e-Invoice Credit Note`, :guilabel:`e-"
"Invoice Debit Note`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`e-račun`, :guilabel:`dobropis e-računa`, :guilabel:`breme e-"
"računa`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:21
msgid ""
":guilabel:`e-Ticket`, :guilabel:`e-Ticket Credit Note`, :guilabel:`e-Ticket "
"Debit Note`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`e-zahtevek`, :guilabel:`dobropis e-zahtevka`, :guilabel:`breme e-"
"zahtevka`;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:22
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Export e-Invoice`, :guilabel:`Export e-Invoice Credit "
"Note`, :guilabel:`Export e-Invoice Debit Note`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izvozni e-račun`, :guilabel:`dobropis izvoznega e-računa`, "
":guilabel:`breme izvoznega e-računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:25
msgid ""
"The localization requires an Uruware account, which enables users to "
"generate electronic documents within Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Lokalizacija zahteva račun Uruware, ki uporabnikom omogoča ustvarjanje "
"elektronskih dokumentov v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:29
msgid ""
":doc:`Documentation on e-invoicing's legality and compliance in Uruguay <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/uruguay>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dokumentacija o zakonitosti in skladnosti e-računov v Urugvaju <../"
"accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/uruguay>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:35
msgid "The following terms are used throughout the Uruguayan localization:"
msgstr "Naslednji izrazi se uporabljajo v urugvajski lokalizaciji:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:37
msgid ""
"**DGI**: *Dirección General Impositiva* is the government entity responsible "
"for enforcing tax payments in Uruguay."
msgstr ""
"**DGI**: *Dirección General Impositiva* je vladna organizacija, odgovorna za "
"izvajanje plačil davkov v Urugvaju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:40
msgid ""
"**Uruware**: is the third-party organization that facilitates the "
"interchange of electronic documents between companies and the Uruguayan "
"government."
msgstr ""
"**Uruware**: je zunanja organizacija, ki omogoča izmenjavo elektronskih "
"dokumentov med podjetji in urugvajsko vlado."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:42
msgid ""
"**CAE**: *Constancia de Autorización de Emisión* is a document requested "
"from the tax authority's website to enable electronic invoice issuance."
msgstr ""
"**CAE**: *Constancia de Autorización de Emisión* je dokument, zahtevan na "
"spletni strani davčnega organa, ki omogoča izdajanje elektronskih računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:51
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the following modules to get all the "
"features of the Uruguayan localization:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Namestite <general/install>` naslednje module, da dobite vse funkcije "
"urugvajske lokalizacije:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:61
msgid ":guilabel:`Uruguay - Accounting`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Urugvaj - Računovodstvo`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:62
msgid "`l10n_uy`"
msgstr "`l10n_uy`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:63
msgid ""
"The default :doc:`fiscal localization package <../fiscal_localizations>`. It "
"adds accounting characteristics for the Uruguayan localization, which "
"represent the minimum configuration required for a company to operate in "
"Uruguay according to the guidelines set by the |DGI|. The module's "
"installation automatically loads: chart of accounts, taxes, documents types, "
"and tax supported types."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti :doc:`paket fiskalne lokalizacije <../fiscal_localizations>`. Doda "
"računovodske značilnosti za urugvajsko lokalizacijo, ki predstavljajo "
"minimalno konfiguracijo, potrebno za delovanje podjetja v Urugvaju v skladu "
"s smernicami, ki jih določa |DGI|. Namestitev modula samodejno naloži: "
"kontni načrt, davke, vrste dokumentov in podprte vrste davkov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:68
msgid ":guilabel:`Uruguay Accounting EDI`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uruguay Accounting EDI`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:69
msgid "`l10n_uy_edi`"
msgstr "`l10n_uy_edi`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:70
msgid ""
"Includes all the technical and functional requirements to generate and "
"validate :doc:`Electronics Documents <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>`, based on the technical documentation published by "
"the |DGI|. The authorized documents are :ref:`listed above <uruguay/intro>`."
msgstr ""
"Vključuje vse tehnične in funkcionalne zahteve za generiranje in validacijo "
":doc:`elektronskih dokumentov <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"electronic_invoicing>` na podlagi tehnične dokumentacije, ki jo je objavil "
"|DGI|. Odobreni dokumenti so :ref:`našteti zgoraj <uruguay/intro>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:76
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically installs the base module **Uruguay - Accounting** when a "
"database is installed with `Uruguay` selected as the country. However, to "
"enable electronic invoicing, the **Uruguay Accounting EDI** (`l10n_uy_edi`) "
"module needs to be manually :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo samodejno namesti osnovni modul **Uruguay - Accounting**, ko je baza "
"podatkov nameščena z izbrano državo `Uruguay`. Vendar pa je za omogočanje "
"elektronskega izdajanja računov potrebno ročno :ref:`namestiti <general/"
"install>` modul **Uruguay Accounting EDI** (`l10n_uy_edi`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tax ID`: enter the identification number for the selected "
"taxpayer type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Davčna številka`: Vnesite identifikacijsko številko za izbrano "
"vrsto davkoplačevalca."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`DGI Main Branch Code`: this is part of the XML when creating an "
"electronic document. If this field is not set, all electronic documents will "
"be rejected."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`DGI Main Branch Code`: to je del XML pri ustvarjanju "
"elektronskega dokumenta. Če to polje ni nastavljeno, bodo vsi elektronski "
"dokumenti zavrnjeni."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:93
msgid "To find the :guilabel:`DGI Main Branch Code`, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za iskanje :guilabel:`DGI Main Branch Code` sledite tem korakom:"

