"odootest.ucfe.com.uy/Gestion/>`_ ali `produkcijskem portalu <https://"
"prod6109.ucfe.com.uy/Gestion/>`_ Uruware:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:145
