"Use the account credentials in the email to log in to the to the "
"corresponding (`test <https://odootest.ucfe.com.uy/Gestion/>`_ or "
"`production <https://prod6109.ucfe.com.uy/Gestion/>`_) portal."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite poverilnice računa iz e-poštnega sporočila za prijavo v ustrezen "
"(`testni <https://odootest.ucfe.com.uy/Gestion/>`_ ali `produkcijski "
"<https://prod6109.ucfe.com.uy/Gestion/>`_) portal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:149
msgid ""
"In Uruware's portal, the following steps are needed to be able to issue "
"invoices from Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Na portalu Uruware so potrebni naslednji koraki, da lahko izdajate račune iz "
"Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:151
msgid "Complete and correct the company's information."
msgstr "Dopolnite in popravite podatke o podjetju."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:152
msgid "Add your digital certificate."
msgstr "Dodajte svoje digitalno potrdilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:153
msgid ""
"Add your :abbr:`CAEs (Constancia de Autorización para Emisión)` for each "
"document-type you plan to issue."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte svoje :abbr:`CAE (Constancia de Autorización para Emisión)` za vsako "
"vrsto dokumenta, ki ga nameravate izdati."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:155
msgid ""
"Configure the format of the PDF to be printed and sent to your customers."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte obliko zapisa PDF, ki bo natisnjen in poslan vašim strankam."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:158
msgid ""
"Be sure to configure two accounts, one for testing and one for production. "
"The certificate is needed in both environments, but :abbr:`CAEs (Constancia "
"de Autorización para Emisión)` are only needed in production."
msgstr ""
"Poskrbite, da konfigurirate dva računa, enega za testiranje in enega za "
"produkcijo. Potrdilo je potrebno v obeh okoljih, vendar so :abbr:`CAE "
"(Constancia de Autorización para Emisión)` potrebni samo v produkciji."

