msgid ""
"The following modules are installed automatically with the Uzbek "
"localization:"
msgstr "Z uzbekistansko lokalizacijo se samodejno namestijo naslednji moduli:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:21
msgid "Uzbekistan - Accounting"
msgstr "Uzbekistan - Accounting"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:22
msgid "l10n_uz"
msgstr "l10n_uz"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:23
msgid ""
"Default fiscal localization package for Uzbekistan. Includes the chart of "
"accounts and core accounting configuration aligned with local requirements."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti paket davčne lokalizacije za Uzbekistan. Vključuje kontni načrt in "
"osnovno računovodsko konfiguracijo, usklajeno z lokalnimi zahtevami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:25
msgid "Uzbekistan - Accounting Reports"
msgstr "Uzbekistan - Accounting Reports"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:26
msgid "l10n_uz_reports"
msgstr "l10n_uz_reports"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:27
msgid ""
"Provides localized financial reports, including the balance sheet and profit "
"and loss statement based on an |IFRS|-style structure."
msgstr ""
"Zagotavlja lokalizirane finančne poročila, vključno z bilanco stanja in "
"izkazom poslovnega izida na podlagi strukture |IFRS|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:35
msgid ""
"The Uzbekistan localization assists companies in meeting local accounting "
"requirements by providing a structured and compliant accounting setup. It "
"contains the following core components:"
msgstr ""
"Uzbekistanska lokalizacija pomaga podjetjem izpolnjevati lokalne "
"računovodske zahteve z zagotavljanjem strukturirane in skladne računovodske "
"nastavitve. Vsebuje naslednje ključne komponente:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:38
msgid ""
":ref:`Taxes <localizations/uz/taxes>`: preconfigured tax rates, including "
"standard 12% VAT, zero-rated export, and exempt options"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Davki <localizations/uz/taxes>`: vnaprej konfigurirane davčne stopnje, "
"vključno s standardnim 12% DDV, izvozom z ničelno stopnjo in možnostmi "
"oprostitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:40
msgid ""
":ref:`Chart of accounts <localizations/uz/coa>`: preconfigured structure "
"aligned with Uzbek standards"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Kontni načrt <localizations/uz/coa>`: vnaprej konfigurirana struktura, "
"usklajena z uzbekistanskimi standardi"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:42
msgid ""
":ref:`Financial reports <localizations/uz/taxes>`: |IFRS|-style balance "
"sheet and profit and loss reports with a tag-based linking of accounts to "
"report lines"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Finančna poročila <localizations/uz/taxes>`: bilanca stanja in izkaz "
"poslovnega izida v slogu |IFRS| z označevalno povezavo računov z vrsticami "
"poročila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:50
msgid "The Uzbek localization includes preconfigured sales and purchase taxes:"
msgstr ""
"Uzbekistanska lokalizacija vključuje vnaprej konfigurirane prodajne in "
"nabavne davke:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:52
msgid ""
"**Standard VAT (12%):** This standard VAT is applied to most goods and "
"services. The supplier charges 12% VAT on the sale (VAT output) and is "
"generally entitled to deduct the VAT paid on business purchases (VAT input)."
msgstr ""
"**Standardni DDV (12%):** Ta standardni DDV se uporablja za večino blaga in "
"storitev. Dobavitelj zaračuna 12% DDV od prodaje (izhodni DDV) in je "
"načeloma upravičen do odbitka DDV, plačanega pri poslovnih nakupih (vhodni "
"DDV)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:57
msgid ""
"Most commercial sales and general supply of goods and services within "
"Uzbekistan use the **Standard VAT (12%)** tax."
msgstr ""
"Večina komercialnih prodaj in splošne dobave blaga in storitev v Uzbekistanu "
"uporablja davek **Standardni DDV (12%)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:60
msgid ""
"**Export VAT (0%):** The export tax is applied on taxable supplies where the "
"VAT rate applied is 0%. The supplier does not charge VAT on the sale."
msgstr ""
"**Izvozni DDV (0%):** Izvozni davek se uporablja za obdavčljive dobave, kjer "
"je uporabljena stopnja DDV 0%. Dobavitelj ne zaračuna DDV na prodajo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:64
msgid ""
"Exports of goods and services to customers outside Uzbekistan use the "
"**Export VAT (0%)** tax."
msgstr ""
"Izvoz blaga in storitev strankam zunaj Uzbekistana uporablja davek **Izvozni "
"DDV (0%)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:66
msgid ""
"**Exempt transactions (0%):** The exempt tax applies to transactions that "
"fall outside the scope of VAT and are not subject to tax."
msgstr ""
"**Oproščene transakcije (0%):** Davek za oprostitev se uporablja za "
"transakcije, ki ne spadajo v obseg DDV in niso predmet obdavčitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:70
msgid ""
"Transactions that are legally exempt from VAT under local regulations, such "
"as essential food products (meat, fish, potatoes, rice), pharmaceuticals, "
"and financial/insurance services, use the **Exempt transactions (0%)** tax."
msgstr ""
"Transakcije, ki so po lokalnih predpisih zakonsko oproščene DDV, kot so "
"osnovni živilski izdelki (meso, ribe, krompir, riž), farmacevtski izdelki "
"ter finančne/zavarovalne storitve, uporabljajo davek **Oproščene transakcije "
"(0%)**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:79
msgid ""
"The Uzbek :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` is preconfigured according to Uzbek accounting standards "
"and requirements. When :ref:`creating new accounts <chart-of-account/"
"create>`, it is important to use :ref:`account tags <localizations/uz/tags>`."
msgstr ""
"Uzbeški :doc:`kontni načrt <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` je "
"vnaprej konfiguriran v skladu z uzbeškimi računovodskimi standardi in "
"zahtevami. Pri :ref:`ustvarjanju novih kontov <chart-of-account/create>` je "
"pomembno uporabiti :ref:`oznake kontov <localizations/uz/tags>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:86
msgid "Account tags"
msgstr "Oznake kontov"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:88
msgid ""
"The Uzbek localization uses account tags to determine where accounts appear "
"in :ref:`financial reports <localizations/uz/financial-reports>`. Each tag "
"links the account to a specific report line."
msgstr ""
"Uzbeška lokalizacija uporablja oznake kontov za določanje, kje se računi "
"pojavijo v :ref:`finančnih poročilih <localizations/uz/financial-reports>`. "
"Vsaka oznaka poveže račun z določeno vrstico poročila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:92
msgid ""
"Accounts that use the tag :guilabel:`BS Line 0120: Right-of-Use Assets` "
"appear on the balance sheet on the :guilabel:`[0120] - Right-of-Use Assets` "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Računi, ki uporabljajo oznako :guilabel:`BS Line 0120: Right-of-Use Assets`, "
"se pojavijo v bilanci stanja v vrstici :guilabel:`[0120] - Right-of-Use "
"Assets`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:96
msgid ""
"If no tag is assigned, the account behaves as an off-balance sheet account "
"and does not appear on the balance sheet or the profit and loss statement."
msgstr ""
"Če oznaka ni dodeljena, se račun obnaša kot izvenbilančni račun in se ne "
"pojavi v bilanci stanja ali izkazu poslovnega izida."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:104
msgid ""
"The following reports have been tailored to meet the needs of businesses "
"using the Uzbek localization:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednja poročila so prilagojena potrebam podjetij, ki uporabljajo uzbeško "
"lokalizacijo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:108
msgid "Profit and loss statement"
msgstr "Izkaz poslovnega izida"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uzbekistan.rst:110
msgid ""
"These reports follow an |IFRS|-style structure, as per the Uzbek reporting "
"requirements. They are built using a :ref:`tag <localizations/uz/tags>`-"
"based mapping system:"
msgstr ""
"Ta poročila sledijo strukturi v slogu |IFRS|, v skladu z uzbeškimi zahtevami "
"za poročanje. Zgrajena so z uporabo sistema preslikave, ki temelji na "
