msgstr ":ref:`Bančno nakazilo <payment_providers/bank_payments/wire_transfer>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:0
msgid ""
"Odoo displays your payment information with a payment reference. You have to "
"approve the payment manually once it has been received in your bank account."
msgstr ""
"Odoo prikaže vaše podatke o plačilu s plačilno referenco. Plačilo morate "
"ročno odobriti, ko je prejeto na vašem bančnem računu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:0
msgid ":ref:`SEPA Direct Debit <payment_providers/bank_payments/sdd>`"
msgstr ":ref:`SEPA direktna bremenitev <payment_providers/bank_payments/sdd>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:0
msgid ""
"Customers can make a bank transfer to register a SEPA Direct Debit mandate "
"and allow their account to be charged directly for future payments."
msgstr ""
"Stranke lahko opravijo bančno nakazilo za registracijo mandata SEPA direktne "
"bremenitve in dovolijo neposredno bremenitev svojega računa za prihodnja "
"plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:229
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/inperson_payments.rst:3
msgid "In-person payments"
msgstr "Plačila v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:0
msgid ":ref:`Pay on Site <payment_providers/inperson_payments/pay_on_site>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Plačilo na kraju samem <payment_providers/inperson_payments/"
"pay_on_site>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:0
msgid ""
"Customers can reserve products online and pay when collecting their orders "
"in store."
msgstr ""
"Stranke lahko rezervirajo izdelke na spletu in plačajo ob prevzemu naročila "
"v trgovini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:0
msgid ""
":ref:`Cash on Delivery <payment_providers/inperson_payments/"
"cash_on_delivery>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Plačilo po povzetju <payment_providers/inperson_payments/"
"cash_on_delivery>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:0
msgid "Customers can pay for their orders upon delivery."
msgstr "Stranke lahko plačajo za svoja naročila ob dostavi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:239
msgid "Enabling a payment provider"
msgstr "Omogočanje ponudnika plačil"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:241
msgid ""
"To add a new payment provider and make its related payment methods available "
"to your customers, proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati novega ponudnika plačil in uporabnikom omogočiti sorodne "
"načine plačila, sledite naslednjim korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:244
msgid ""
"Go to the payment provider's website, create an account, and make sure you "
"have the API credentials requested for third-party use. These are necessary "
"for Odoo to communicate with the payment provider."
msgstr ""
"Obiščite spletno mesto ponudnika plačil, ustvarite račun in se prepričajte, "
"da imate pridobljene poverilnice API, potrebne za uporabo s strani tretjih "
"oseb. Te so potrebne, da lahko Odoo komunicira s ponudnikom plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:247
msgid ""
"In Odoo, navigate to the :guilabel:`Payment providers` by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Payment "
"Providers`, :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Payment "
"Providers`, or :menuselection:`Sales --> Configuration --> Payment "
"Providers`."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo pojdite na :guilabel:`Ponudniki plačil` prek menija "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Nastavitve --> Ponudniki plačil`, "
":menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Nastavitve --> Ponudniki plačil` ali "
":menuselection:`Prodaja --> Nastavitve --> Ponudniki plačil`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:250
msgid "Select the provider and configure the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab."
msgstr "Izberite ponudnika in konfigurirajte zavihek :guilabel:`Poverilnice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:251
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:62
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:45
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:99
