msgstr "Nastavite polje :guilabel:`Stanje` na :guilabel:`Omogočeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:254
msgid ""
"The fields available in the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab depend on the "
"payment provider. Refer to the :ref:`related documentation "
"<payment_providers/supported_providers>` for more information."
msgstr ""
"Polja, ki so na voljo v zavihku :guilabel:`Poverilnice`, so odvisna od "
"ponudnika plačil. Za več informacij si oglejte :ref:`sorodno dokumentacijo "
"<payment_providers/supported_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:257
msgid ""
"Once you have enabled the payment provider, it is automatically published on "
"your website. If you wish to unpublish it, click the :guilabel:`Published` "
"button. Customers cannot make payments through an unpublished provider, but "
"they can still manage :dfn:`(delete and assign to a subscription)` their "
"existing tokens linked to such a provider."
msgstr ""
"Ko omogočite ponudnika plačil, je ta samodejno objavljen na vaši spletni "
"strani. Če ga želite umakniti iz objave, kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Objavljeno`. Uporabniki ne morejo izvajati plačil prek "
"neobjavljenega ponudnika, lahko pa še vedno upravljajo :dfn:`(brišejo in "
"dodelijo naročnini)` svoje obstoječe žetone, povezane s takim ponudnikom."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:265
msgid "Test mode"
msgstr "Preskusni način"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:268
msgid ""
"We recommend using the test mode on a **duplicate** or a **test** database "
"to avoid potential issues with invoice numbering."
msgstr ""
"Priporočamo uporabo testnega načina na **duplikatu** ali **testni** bazi "
"podatkov, da se izognete morebitnim težavam s številčenjem računov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:271
msgid ""
"To try a payment provider without affecting live transactions, set "
"the :guilabel:`State` field in the payment provider form to :guilabel:`Test "
"mode`. Then, enter the **provider's dedicated test or sandbox credentials** "
"in the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab. Each payment provider has its own "
"separate test account or environment for this purpose."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preskusiti ponudnika plačil, ne da bi to vplivalo na žive "
"transakcije, nastavite polje :guilabel:`Stanje` v obrazcu ponudnika plačil "
"na :guilabel:`Testni način`. Nato vnesite **namenjena testna ali peskovniška "
"poverila ponudnika** v zavihek :guilabel:`Poverila`. Vsak ponudnik plačil "
"ima za ta namen svoj ločen testni račun ali okolje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:277
msgid ""
"By default, the payment provider remains **unpublished** in test mode so "
"that it's not visible to visitors."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto ponudnik plačil ostane **neobjavljen** v testnem načinu, tako da ni "
"viden obiskovalcem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:285
msgid ""
"Each payment provider is related to a list of supported payment methods; the "
"methods listed in the :guilabel:`Payment methods` field in "
"the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab of the payment provider form are the ones "
"that have been activated. To activate or deactivate a payment method for a "
"provider, click :guilabel:`Enable Payment Methods`, then click the toggle "
"button of the related method."
msgstr ""
"Vsak ponudnik plačil je povezan s seznamom podprtih načinov plačila; načini, "
"navedeni v polju :guilabel:`Načini plačila` v zavihku :guilabel:`Nastavitve` "
"obrazca ponudnika plačil, so tisti, ki so bili aktivirani. Če želite "
"aktivirati ali deaktivirati način plačila za ponudnika, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Omogoči načine plačila` in nato kliknite gumb za preklop pri "
"sorodnemu načinu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:291
msgid ""
"To view the complete list of supported payment methods, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Payment "
"Methods`, :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Payment Methods`, "
"or :menuselection:`Sales --> Configuration --> Payment Methods`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled celotnega seznama podprtih načinov plačila pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Načini plačila`, "
":menuselection:`Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> Načini plačila` ali "
":menuselection:`Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Načini plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:294
msgid ""
"Payment methods are displayed on the ecommerce website based on their "
"sequence order. To reorder them, drag and drop the payment methods into the "
"desired order in the :guilabel:`Payment Methods` list."
msgstr ""
"Načini plačila so na spletni strani prikazani glede na vrstni red zaporedja. "
"Če jih želite preurediti, povlecite in spustite načine plačila v želeni "
"vrstni red na seznamu :guilabel:`Načini plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:299
msgid "Icons and brands"
msgstr "Ikone in blagovne znamke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:301
msgid ""
"The icons displayed next to the payment method on your website are either "
"the icons of the brands activated for the payment method or, if there aren't "
"any, the icons of the payment methods themselves. To modify "
"them, :ref:`access the list of payment methods <payment_providers/"
"payment_methods>`, then click the relevant one."
msgstr ""
"Ikone, prikazane poleg načina plačila na vaši spletni strani, so bodisi "
"ikone blagovnih znamk, aktiviranih za način plačila, ali, če jih ni, ikone "
"samih načinov plačila. Če jih želite spremeniti, :ref:`odprite seznam "
"načinov plačila <payment_providers/payment_methods>`, nato kliknite "
"ustreznega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:306
msgid ""
"To modify a payment method's icon, hover your mouse over the image in the "
"upper-right corner of the payment method's form and click the :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` (:guilabel:`pencil`) icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti ikono načina plačila, premaknite miško nad sliko v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu obrazca načina plačila in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` (:guilabel:`svinčnik`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:309
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Brands` tab to view the brands that have been "
"activated for the payment method. The brands and their related icons are "
"displayed based on their sequence order; to reorder them, drag and drop them "
"into the desired order. To modify a brand's icon, select the brand, then, in "
"the popup window that opens, hover the mouse over the image in the upper-"
"right corner and click the :icon:`fa-pencil` (:guilabel:`pencil`) icon."
msgstr ""
"Izberite zavihek :guilabel:`Blagovne znamke`, da si ogledate blagovne "
"znamke, ki so bile aktivirane za način plačila. Blagovne znamke in njihove "
"povezane ikone so prikazane glede na vrstni red zaporedja; če jih želite "
"preurediti, jih povlecite in spustite v želeni vrstni red. Če želite "
"spremeniti ikono blagovne znamke, izberite blagovno znamko, nato v pojavnem "
"oknu, ki se odpre, postavite miško nad sliko v zgornjem desnem kotu in "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-pencil` (:guilabel:`svinčnik`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:316
msgid "Advanced configuration"
msgstr "Napredna konfiguracija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:318
msgid "To further configure payment methods, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za dodatno konfiguracijo načinov plačila sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:321
msgid ""
":ref:`Access the list of payment methods <payment_providers/"
"payment_methods>` and click the relevant one."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odprite seznam načinov plačila <payment_providers/payment_methods>` in "
"kliknite ustreznega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:323
msgid ""
"Go to the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab and adjust the features as needed."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Konfiguracija` in po potrebi prilagodite "
"funkcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:326
msgid ""
"Each payment method is preconfigured in a way that aligns with the payment "
"providers' behavior and their integration with Odoo. Any change to this "
"configuration may result in errors and should be tested on a duplicate or "
"test database first."
msgstr ""
"Vsak način plačila je vnaprej konfiguriran na način, ki je usklajen z "
"obnašanjem ponudnikov plačil in njihovo integracijo z Odoo. Vsaka sprememba "
"te konfiguracije lahko povzroči napake in jo je treba najprej preizkusiti v "
"podvojeni ali testni podatkovni bazi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:329
msgid ""
"Modifications to the payment method's configuration only work to the extent "
"of the method's and provider's capabilities. For example, "
"adding :ref:`countries <payment_providers/currencies_countries>` for a "
"payment method only supported in one country or enabling :ref:`tokenization "
"<payment_providers/tokenization>` for a method linked to a provider that "
"does not support it will not produce the intended results."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe konfiguracije načina plačila delujejo le v obsegu zmožnosti načina "
"in ponudnika. Na primer, dodajanje :ref:`držav <payment_providers/"
"currencies_countries>` za način plačila, ki je podprt samo v eni državi, ali "
"omogočanje :ref:`tokenizacije <payment_providers/tokenization>` za način, "
"povezan s ponudnikom, ki tega ne podpira, ne bo dalo želenih rezultatov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:338
msgid "Tokenization"
msgstr "Tokenizacija"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:340
msgid ""
":ref:`If the payment provider supports this feature <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>`, customers can save their payment method details for "
"later. To enable this feature, go to the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab of "
"the selected payment provider and enable :guilabel:`Allow Saving Payment "
"Methods`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Če ponudnik plačil podpira to funkcijo <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>`, lahko uporabniki shranijo podrobnosti svojega načina "
"plačila za kasnejšo uporabo. Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, pojdite na "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Nastavitve` izbranega ponudnika plačil in omogočite "
":guilabel:`Dovoli shranjevanje načinov plačila`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:345
msgid ""
"In this case, a **payment token** is created in Odoo to be used as a payment "
"method for subsequent payments without the customer having to enter their "
"payment method details again. This is particularly useful for the eCommerce "
"conversion rate and subscriptions that use recurring payments."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru se v Odoo ustvari **plačilni žeton**, ki se uporabi kot način "
"plačila za nadaljnja plačila, ne da bi moral uporabnik ponovno vnesti "
"podatke o načinu plačila. To je še posebej uporabno za stopnjo konverzije "
"eCommerce in naročnine, ki uporabljajo ponavljajoča se plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:350
msgid ""
"To add or delete their saved payment method details, customers can "
"click :guilabel:`Manage payment methods` in the :ref:`customer portal <users-"
"portal-payment-methods>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želijo uporabniki dodati ali izbrisati svoje shranjene podrobnosti načina "
"plačila, lahko kliknejo :guilabel:`Upravljaj načine plačila` v "
":ref:`uporabniškem portalu <users-portal-payment-methods>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:353
msgid "PCI DSS and Attestation of Compliance"
msgstr "PCI DSS in potrdilo o skladnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:355
msgid ""
"Odoo is not `PCI <https://www.pcisecuritystandards.org>`_ DSS-certified "
"because it does not store cardholder data or process payments. Instead, it "
"outsources tokenization and payment to :ref:`external payment providers "
"<payment_providers/online_providers>`, which means that as an Odoo customer, "
"you only need to complete the minimal Self-Assessment Questionnaire (SAQ) "
"with the provider to obtain the Attestation of Compliance (AoC) and achieve "
"PCI compliance. Odoo should not be mentioned as a payment processor or a "
"third-party service provider in the :abbr:`SAQ (Self-Assessment "
"Questionnaire)`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ni `PCI <https://www.pcisecuritystandards.org>`_ DSS-certificiran, ker "
"ne shranjuje podatkov o imetnikih kartic in ne obdeluje plačil. Namesto tega "
"zaupa tokenizacijo in plačilo :ref:`zunanjim ponudnikom plačil "
"<payment_providers/online_providers>`, kar pomeni, da morate kot uporabnik "
"Odoo izpolniti le minimalen vprašalnik za samopreverjanje (SAQ) pri "
"ponudniku, da pridobite potrdilo o skladnosti (AoC) in dosežete skladnost s "
"PCI. Odoo ne sme biti naveden kot procesor plačil ali ponudnik storitev "
"tretje osebe v :abbr:`SAQ (vprašalniku za samopreverjanje)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:366
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:71
msgid "Manual capture"
msgstr "Ročno zajemanje"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:368
msgid ""
":ref:`If the payment provider supports this feature <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>`, you can authorize and capture payments in two steps "
"instead of one. To enable this feature, go to the :guilabel:`Configuration` "
"tab of the selected payment provider and enable :guilabel:`Capture Amount "
"Manually`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Če ponudnik plačil podpira to funkcijo <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>`, lahko avtorizirate in zajamete plačila v dveh korakih "
"namesto v enem. Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, pojdite na zavihek "
":guilabel:`Konfiguracija` izbranega ponudnika plačil in omogočite "
":guilabel:`Ročno zajemi znesek`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:373
msgid ""
"When you authorize a payment, the funds are reserved on the customer's "
"payment method but not immediately charged. They are charged when you "
"manually capture the payment later on. You can also void the authorization "
"to cancel it and release the reserved funds. Capturing payments manually is "
"helpful in many situations:"
msgstr ""
"Ko avtorizirate plačilo, so sredstva rezervirana na plačilnem sredstvu "
"stranke, vendar niso takoj zaračunana. Zaračunana so, ko pozneje ročno "
"zajamete plačilo. Avtorizacijo lahko tudi razveljavite, s čimer prekličete "
"rezervacijo in sprostite rezervirana sredstva. Ročno zajemanje plačil je "
"koristno v številnih situacijah:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:378
msgid ""
"Receive the payment confirmation and wait until the order is shipped to "
"capture the payment."
msgstr ""
"Prejmite potrditev plačila in počakajte, da je naročilo odpremljeno, preden "
"zajamete plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:379
msgid ""
"Review and verify that orders are legitimate before the payment is completed "
"and the fulfillment process starts."
msgstr ""
"Preglejte in preverite, ali so naročila zakonita, preden je plačilo "
"zaključeno in se začne postopek izpolnitve."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:381
msgid ""
"Avoid potentially high refund fees for refunded payments: payment providers "
"will not charge you for voiding an authorization."
msgstr ""
"Izognite se potencialno visokim stroškom vračila za vračila plačil: "
"ponudniki plačil vam ne bodo zaračunali za razveljavitev avtorizacije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:383
msgid ""
"Hold a security deposit to return later, minus any deductions (e.g., in case "
"of damages)."
msgstr ""
"Zadržite varščino za poznejše vračilo, zmanjšano za morebitne odbitke (npr. "
"v primeru škode)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:385
msgid ""
"To capture the payment after it was authorized, go to the related sales "
"order or invoice and click the :guilabel:`Capture Transaction` button. To "
"release the funds, click the :guilabel:`Void Transaction` button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zajeti plačilo po avtorizaciji, pojdite na povezani prodajni nalog "
"ali račun in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Zajemi transakcijo`. Če želite "
"sprostiti sredstva, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Razveljavi transakcijo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:390
msgid ""
"Some payment providers support capturing only part of the authorized amount. "
"The remaining amount can then be either captured or voided. These providers "
"have the value **Full and partial** in the :ref:`table above "
"<payment_providers/online_providers>`. The providers that only support "
"capturing or voiding the total amount have the value **Full only**."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri ponudniki plačil podpirajo zajemanje samo dela avtoriziranega "
"zneska. Preostali znesek je nato mogoče bodisi zajeti bodisi razveljaviti. "
"Ti ponudniki imajo v :ref:`zgornji tabeli <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>` vrednost **Polno in delno**. Ponudniki, ki podpirajo samo "
"zajemanje ali razveljavitev celotnega zneska, imajo vrednost **Samo polno**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:394
msgid ""
"The funds are likely not reserved forever. After a certain time, they may be "
"automatically released back to the customer's payment method. Refer to your "
"payment provider's documentation for the exact reservation duration."
msgstr ""
"Sredstva verjetno niso rezervirana za vedno. Po določenem času so lahko "
"samodejno sproščena nazaj na plačilno sredstvo stranke. Za natančno trajanje "
"rezervacije glejte dokumentacijo vašega ponudnika plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:397
msgid ""
":doc:`payment_providers/adyen` and :doc:`payment_providers/stripe` allow to "
"capture payments manually directly from their website interface."
msgstr ""
":doc:`payment_providers/adyen` in :doc:`payment_providers/stripe` omogočata "
"ročno zajemanje plačil neposredno iz vmesnika njune spletne strani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:405
msgid ""
"If your payment provider supports this feature, you can refund payments "
"directly from Odoo. It does not need to be enabled first. To refund a "
"customer payment, navigate to it and click the :guilabel:`Refund` button."
msgstr ""
"Če vaš ponudnik plačil podpira to funkcijo, lahko vračila plačil izvajate "
"neposredno iz Odoo. Ni ga treba najprej omogočiti. Če želite vrniti plačilo "
"stranke, pojdite nanj in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Vračilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:410
msgid ""
"Some payment providers support refunding only part of the amount. The "
"remaining amount can then optionally be refunded, too. These providers have "
"the value **Full and partial** in the :ref:`table above <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>`. The providers that only support refunding the total "
"amount have the value **Full only**."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri ponudniki plačil podpirajo vračilo samo dela zneska. Preostali "
"znesek je nato po želji mogoče prav tako vrniti. Ti ponudniki imajo v "
":ref:`zgornji tabeli <payment_providers/online_providers>` vrednost **Polno "
"in delno**. Ponudniki, ki podpirajo samo vračilo celotnega zneska, imajo "
"vrednost **Samo polno**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:414
msgid ""
":doc:`payment_providers/adyen` and :doc:`payment_providers/stripe` allow to "
"refund payments directly from their website interface."
msgstr ""
":doc:`payment_providers/adyen` in :doc:`payment_providers/stripe` omogočata "
"vračila plačil neposredno iz vmesnika njune spletne strani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:420
msgid "Express checkout"
msgstr "Ekspresna blagajna"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:422
msgid ""
":ref:`If the payment provider supports this feature <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>`, you can allow customers to use the :guilabel:`Google "
"Pay` and :guilabel:`Apple Pay` buttons and pay their eCommerce orders in one "
"click. When they use one of these buttons, customers go straight from the "
"cart to the confirmation page without filling out the contact form. They "
"just have to validate the payment on Google's or Apple's payment form."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Če ponudnik plačil podpira to funkcijo <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>`, lahko strankam omogočite uporabo gumbov "
":guilabel:`Google Pay` in :guilabel:`Apple Pay` ter plačilo naročil e-"
"trgovine z enim klikom. Ko uporabijo enega od teh gumbov, stranke pridejo "
"naravnost iz košarice na stran s potrditvijo, ne da bi izpolnile kontaktni "
"obrazec. Plačilo morajo samo potrditi na plačilnem obrazcu Google ali Apple."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:428
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, go to the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab of the "
"selected payment provider and enable :guilabel:`Allow Express Checkout`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, pojdite na zavihek "
":guilabel:`Konfiguracija` izbranega ponudnika plačil in omogočite "
":guilabel:`Dovoli ekspresno blagajno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:432
msgid ""
"All prices shown on the express checkout payment form always include taxes."
msgstr ""
"Vse cene, prikazane na plačilnem obrazcu ekspresne blagajne, vedno "
"vključujejo davke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:439
msgid ""
"You can adapt the payment provider's availability by specifying "
"the :guilabel:`Maximum amount` allowed and modifying "
"the :guilabel:`Currencies` and :guilabel:`Countries` in "
"the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab."
msgstr ""
"Razpoložljivost ponudnika plačil lahko prilagodite tako, da določite "
":guilabel:`Največji znesek` in spremenite :guilabel:`Valute` in "
":guilabel:`Države` v zavihku :guilabel:`Konfiguracija`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:444
msgid ""
"To display an availability report for payment providers and payment methods, "
"and to help diagnose potential availability issues on the payment form, "
"enable the :ref:`developer-mode`, then click the :icon:`fa-bug` "
"(:guilabel:`bug`) icon next to the :guilabel:`Choose a payment method` "
"heading on the payment form. The report includes a list of enabled payment "
"providers and payment methods, reasons for any payment providers or methods "
"not being available, if applicable, and a list of supported providers for "
"each payment method."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati poročilo o razpoložljivosti ponudnikov plačil in "
"plačilnih metod ter pomagati pri diagnosticiranju morebitnih težav z "
"razpoložljivostjo na plačilnem obrazcu, omogočite :ref:`developer-mode`, "
"nato kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-bug` (:guilabel:`napaka`) poleg naslova "
":guilabel:`Izberite plačilno metodo` na plačilnem obrazcu. Poročilo "
"vključuje seznam omogočenih ponudnikov plačil in plačilnih metod, razloge za "
"morebitno nedostopnost ponudnikov plačil ali metod, če je primerno, in "
"seznam podprtih ponudnikov za vsako plačilno metodo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:454
msgid "Currencies and countries"
msgstr "Valute in države"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:456
msgid ""
"All payment providers have a different list of available currencies and "
"countries. They serve as a first filter during payment operations, i.e., the "
"payment methods linked to the payment provider are not available for "
"selection if the customer's currency or country is not in the supported "
"list. As there might be errors, updates, and unknowns in the lists of "
"available currencies and countries, adding or removing a payment provider's "
"supported currencies or countries is possible."
msgstr ""
"Vsi ponudniki plačil imajo različen seznam razpoložljivih valut in držav. "
"Služijo kot prvi filter med plačilnimi operacijami, kar pomeni, da plačilne "
"metode, povezane s ponudnikom plačil, niso na voljo za izbiro, če valuta ali "
"država stranke ni na seznamu podprtih. Ker so lahko v seznamih "
"razpoložljivih valut in držav napake, posodobitve in neznanke, je mogoče "
"dodajati ali odstranjevati podprte valute ali države ponudnika plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:464
msgid ""
":ref:`Payment methods <payment_providers/payment_methods>` also have their "
"own list of available currencies and countries that serves as another filter "
"during payment operations."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Načini plačila <payment_providers/payment_methods>` imajo tudi svoj "
"seznam razpoložljivih valut in držav, ki služi kot dodaten filter med "
"plačilnimi operacijami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:466
msgid ""
"If the list of supported currencies or countries is empty, it means the list "
"is too long to be displayed, or Odoo does not have information on that "
"payment provider. The payment provider remains available, even though it is "
"possible the payment will be refused at a later stage should the country or "
"currency not be supported."
msgstr ""
"Če je seznam podprtih valut ali držav prazen, to pomeni, da je seznam "
"predolg za prikaz ali da Odoo nima informacij o tem ponudniku plačil. "
"Ponudnik plačil ostane na voljo, čeprav je možno, da bo plačilo v kasnejši "
"fazi zavrnjeno, če država ali valuta nista podprti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:474
msgid "Maximum amount"
msgstr "Najvišji znesek"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:476
msgid ""
"You can restrict the :guilabel:`Maximum Amount` that can be paid with the "
"selected provider. Leave the field to `0.00` to make the payment provider "
"available regardless of the payment amount."
msgstr ""
"Lahko omejite :guilabel:`Najvišji znesek`, ki ga je mogoče plačati z "
"izbranim ponudnikom. Pustite polje na `0.00`, da bo ponudnik plačil na voljo "
"ne glede na znesek plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:480
msgid ""
"This feature is not intended to work on pages that allow the customer to "
"update the payment amount, e.g., the **Donation** snippet and the "
"**Checkout** page when paid :doc:`shipping methods <../websites/ecommerce/"
"shipping>` are enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija ni namenjena uporabi na straneh, ki uporabniku omogočajo "
"posodobitev zneska plačila, npr. vdelani element **Donacija** in stran "
"**Blagajna**, ko so omogočeni plačljivi :doc:`načini dostave <../websites/"
"ecommerce/shipping>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:487
msgid "Payment journal"
msgstr "Plačilni dnevnik"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:489
msgid ""
"A :doc:`payment journal <accounting/bank>` must be defined for the payment "
"provider to record the payments on an **outstanding account**. By default, "
"the :guilabel:`Bank` journal is added as the payment journal for all payment "
"providers. To modify it, go to the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab of the "
"selected payment provider and select another :guilabel:`Payment journal`."
msgstr ""
"Za ponudnika plačil mora biti določen :doc:`plačilni dnevnik <accounting/"
"bank>`, da se plačila zabeležijo na **odprtem računu**. Privzeto je dnevnik "
":guilabel:`Banka` dodan kot plačilni dnevnik za vse ponudnike plačil. Če ga "
"želite spremeniti, pojdite na zavihek :guilabel:`Konfiguracija` izbranega "
"ponudnika plačil in izberite drug :guilabel:`Plačilni dnevnik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:495
msgid "The payment journal must be a :guilabel:`Bank` journal."
msgstr "Plačilni dnevnik mora biti dnevnik :guilabel:`Banka`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:496
msgid "The same journal can be used for several payment providers."
msgstr "Isti dnevnik se lahko uporablja za več ponudnikov plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:497
msgid ""
"Payment journals must only be configured if the :doc:`Invoicing or "
"Accounting app <accounting>` is installed."
msgstr ""
"Plačilne dnevnike je treba konfigurirati samo, če je nameščena "
":doc:`aplikacija Fakturiranje ali Računovodstvo <accounting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:501
msgid "Accounting perspective"
msgstr "Računovodsko gledišče"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:503
msgid ""
"From an accounting perspective, there are two types of online payment "
"workflows: the payments that are directly deposited into your bank account "
"and follow the usual :doc:`reconciliation <accounting/bank/reconciliation>` "
"workflow, and those coming from third-party :ref:`online payment providers "
"<payment_providers/online_providers>` and require you to follow another "
"accounting workflow. For these payments, you need to consider how you want "
"to record your payments' journal entries. We recommend you ask your "
"accountant for advice."
msgstr ""
"Z računovodskega vidika obstajata dve vrsti spletnih plačilnih tokov: "
"plačila, ki so neposredno vplačana na vaš bančni račun in sledijo običajnemu "
"poteku :doc:`uskladitve <accounting/bank/reconciliation>`, in tista, ki "
"prihajajo od zunanjih :ref:`ponudnikov spletnih plačil <payment_providers/"
"online_providers>` in od vas zahtevajo, da sledite drugemu računovodskemu "
"poteku. Za ta plačila morate razmisliti, kako želite beležiti knjigovodske "
"vnose svojih plačil. Priporočamo, da se posvetujete s svojim računovodjem."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:510
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Bank Account` defined for the :ref:`payment "
"journal <payment_providers/journal>` is used, but you can also specify "
"an :ref:`outstanding account <accounting/journals/outstanding-accounts>` for "
"each payment provider to separate the provider's payments from other "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto se uporabi :guilabel:`Bančni račun`, določen za :ref:`dnevnik "
"plačil <payment_providers/journal>`, lahko pa za vsakega ponudnika plačil "
"določite tudi :ref:`predhodni račun <accounting/journals/outstanding-"
"accounts>`, da ločite plačila ponudnika od drugih plačil."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers.rst:None
msgid "Define an outstanding account for a payment provider."
msgstr "Določite odprt račun za ponudnika plačil."

