#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:3
msgid "Adyen"
msgstr "Adyen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Adyen <https://www.adyen.com/>`_ is a Dutch company that offers several "
"online payment possibilities."
msgstr ""
"`Adyen <https://www.adyen.com/>`_ je nizozemsko podjetje, ki ponuja več "
"možnosti spletnega plačevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:9
msgid ""
"Adyen is more focused on enterprise customers and may require a minimum "
"number of transactions and a minimum processed volume."
msgstr ""
"Adyen je bolj osredotočen na poslovne stranke in lahko zahteva najmanjše "
"število transakcij ter najmanjši obseg obdelave."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:15
msgid "Adyen configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija Adyen"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:17
msgid ""
"Create an Adyen account if necessary and log into your `Adyen Customer Area "
"<https://ca-live.adyen.com/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi ustvarite račun Adyen in se prijavite v `območje za stranke Adyen "
"<https://ca-live.adyen.com/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:21
msgid ""
"Log into your **Test account** to try the integration without charging "
"customers. Switch to your **Live account** once you are ready to accept "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Prijavite se v svoj **testni račun**, da preizkusite integracijo brez "
"zaRAčunavanja strankam. Preklopite na svoj **dejanski račun**, ko ste "
"pripravljeni sprejemati plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:24
msgid ""
"`Contact the Adyen support team <https://docs.adyen.com/platforms/quickstart-"
"guide/support#contact-adyen-support>`_ to enable the **Multiple partial "
"capture** feature."
msgstr ""
"`Obrnite se na Adyenovo podporno ekipo <https://docs.adyen.com/platforms/"
"quickstart-guide/support#contact-adyen-support>`_, da omogočite funkcijo "
"**Večkratnega delnega zajema**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:26
msgid ""
"In the Adyen Customer Area, go to :menuselection:`Developers --> API "
"credentials` and click the relevant API credential user name in the list or "
"click :icon:`fa-plus-circle` :guilabel:`Create new credential` to create a "
"new one."
msgstr ""
"V območju za stranke Adyen pojdite na :menuselection:`Razvijalci --> "
"Poverilnice API` in kliknite ustrezno uporabniško ime poverilnice API na "
"seznamu ali kliknite :icon:`fa-plus-circle` :guilabel:`Ustvari novo "
"poverilnico`, da ustvarite novo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:29
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Server settings` section, click :guilabel:`Generate API "
"key`, then click the :icon:`fa-copy` (:guilabel:`Copy API key`) icon and "
"save the value for the :ref:`payment_providers/adyen/configure_odoo` step."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Server settings` kliknite :guilabel:`Generate API "
"key`, nato kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-copy` (:guilabel:`Copy API key`) in "
"shranite vrednost za korak :ref:`payment_providers/adyen/configure_odoo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:32
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Client settings` section, click :guilabel:`Generate client "
"key`, then click the :icon:`fa-copy` (:guilabel:`Copy client key`) icon and "
"save the value for the :ref:`payment_providers/adyen/configure_odoo` step."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Nastavitve odjemalca` kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"ključ odjemalca`, nato kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-copy` (:guilabel:`Kopiraj "
"ključ odjemalca`) in shranite vrednost za korak :ref:`payment_providers/"
"adyen/configure_odoo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:35
msgid ""
"Enter your Odoo database URL in the :guilabel:`Add allowed origins` field, "
"then click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite URL svoje zbirke podatkov Odoo v polje :guilabel:`Dodaj dovoljene "
"izvore`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:37
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save changes` at the bottom of the page."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani spremembe` na dnu strani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:38
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Developers --> Webhooks` in the left menu and "
"click :icon:`fa-plus-circle` :guilabel:`Create new webhook`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Razvijalci --> Webhooks` v levem meniju in "
"kliknite :icon:`fa-plus-circle` :guilabel:`Ustvari nov webhook`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:40
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Create new webhook` popup, click :guilabel:`Add` on "
"the :guilabel:`Standard webhook` line."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari nov webhook` kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj` v "
"vrstici :guilabel:`Standardni webhook`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:42
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Webhook generation` form, in the :guilabel:`Server "
"configuration` section, enter your Odoo database :guilabel:`URL` followed by "
"`/payment/adyen/notification`."
msgstr ""
"V obrazcu :guilabel:`Ustvarjanje webhooka` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Konfiguracija strežnika` vnesite :guilabel:`URL` svoje zbirke "
"podatkov Odoo, ki mu sledi `/payment/adyen/notification`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:44
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Security` section, click :guilabel:`Generate` "
"under :guilabel:`HMAC`, then click the :icon:`fa-copy` (:guilabel:`Copy HMAC "
"to the clipboard`) icon and save the value for the :ref:`payment_providers/"
"adyen/configure_odoo` step."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Varnost` kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari` pod "
":guilabel:`HMAC`, nato kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-copy` (:guilabel:`Kopiraj "
"HMAC v odložišče`) in shranite vrednost za korak :ref:`payment_providers/"
"adyen/configure_odoo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:47
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save configuration` at the bottom of the page."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani konfiguracijo` na dnu strani."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:48
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Developers --> API URLs`, then copy "
"the :guilabel:`Prefix` and save the value for the :ref:`payment_providers/"
"adyen/configure_odoo` step."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Razvijalci --> URL-ji API`, nato kopirajte "
":guilabel:`Predpono` in shranite vrednost za korak :ref:`payment_providers/"
"adyen/configure_odoo`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:56
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:76
