"<authorize-import-template>`."
msgstr ""
"Odprite besedilno datoteko, izberite :guilabel:`All`, kopirajte podatke in "
"jih prilepite v list :guilabel:`Report 2 Download` v :ref:`predlogi za uvoz "
"v Excelu <authorize-import-template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:116
msgid ""
"Transit lines are automatically filled in and updated in "
"the :guilabel:`transit for report 1` and :guilabel:`transit for report 2` "
"sheets of the :ref:`Excel import template <authorize-import-template>`. Make "
"sure all entries are present, and **if not**, copy the formula from "
"previously filled-in lines of the :guilabel:`transit for report 1` "
"or :guilabel:`2` sheets and paste it into the empty lines."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice prehoda so samodejno izpolnjene in posodobljene v listih "
":guilabel:`transit for report 1` in :guilabel:`transit for report 2` v "
":ref:`predlogi za uvoz v Excelu <authorize-import-template>`. Prepričajte "
"se, da so vsi vnosi prisotni in **če niso**, kopirajte formulo iz predhodno "
"izpolnjenih vrstic listov :guilabel:`transit for report 1` ali :guilabel:`2` "
"in jo prilepite v prazne vrstice."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:123
msgid ""
"To get the correct closing balance, **do not remove** any line from the "
"Excel sheets."
msgstr ""
"Za pravilno končno stanje **ne odstranjujte** nobene vrstice iz Excelovih "
"listov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:126
msgid "Import into Odoo"
msgstr "Uvoz v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:128
msgid "To import the data into Odoo:"
msgstr "Za uvoz podatkov v Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:130
msgid "Open the :ref:`Excel import template <authorize-import-template>`."
msgstr "Odprite :ref:`predlogo za uvoz v Excelu <authorize-import-template>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:131
msgid ""
"Copy the data from the :guilabel:`transit for report 2` sheet and use *paste "
"special* to only paste the values in the :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` "
"sheet."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte podatke iz lista :guilabel:`transit for report 2` in uporabite "
"*posebno lepljenje*, da prilepite samo vrednosti v list :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Import to CSV`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:133
msgid ""
"Look for *blue* cells in the :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` sheet. These are "
"chargeback entries without any reference number. As they cannot be imported "
"as such, go to :menuselection:`Authorize.Net --> Account --> Statements --> "
"eCheck.Net Settlement Statement`."
msgstr ""
"Poiščite *modre* celice v listu :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV`. To so vnosi "
"povratnih bremenitev brez referenčne številke. Ker jih kot takih ni mogoče "
"uvoziti, pojdite na :menuselection:`Authorize.Net --> Account --> "
"Statements --> eCheck.Net Settlement Statement`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:136
msgid "Look for :guilabel:`Charge Transaction/Chargeback`, and click it."
msgstr "Poiščite :guilabel:`Charge Transaction/Chargeback` in kliknite nanj."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:137
msgid ""
"Copy the invoice description, paste it into the :guilabel:`Label` cell of "
"the :guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` sheet, and add `Chargeback /` before the "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte opis računa, ga prilepite v celico :guilabel:`Label` lista "
":guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV` in pred opis dodajte `Chargeback /`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:139
msgid ""
"If there are multiple invoices, add a line into the :ref:`Excel import "
"template <authorize-import-template>` for each invoice and copy/paste the "
"description into each respective :guilabel:`Label` line."
msgstr ""
"Če obstaja več računov, dodajte vrstico v :ref:`predlogo za uvoz Excel "
"<authorize-import-template>` za vsak račun in kopirajte/prilepite opis v "
"vsako ustrezno vrstico :guilabel:`Label`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:144
msgid ""
"For **combined chargeback/returns** in the payouts, create a new line in "
"the :ref:`Excel import template <authorize-import-template>` for each "
"invoice."
msgstr ""
"Za **kombinirane povratne bremenitve/vračila** v izplačilih ustvarite novo "
"vrstico v :ref:`predlogi za uvoz Excel <authorize-import-template>` za vsak "
"račun."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:0
msgid "Chargeback description"
msgstr "Opis povratne bremenitve"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:152
msgid ""
"Next, delete *zero transaction* and *void transaction* line items, and "
"change the format of the :guilabel:`Amount` column in the :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Import to CSV` sheet to *Number*."
msgstr ""
"Nato izbrišite vrstice *ničelna transakcija* in *razveljavljena transakcija* "
"ter spremenite obliko stolpca :guilabel:`Amount` v listu :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Import to CSV` v *Število*."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:154
msgid ""
"Go back to :menuselection:`eCheck.Net Settlement Statement --> Search for a "
"Transaction` and search again for the previously used batch settlements "
"dates."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite nazaj na :menuselection:`eCheck.Net Settlement Statement --> Search "
"for a Transaction` in znova poiščite predhodno uporabljene datume poravnav "
"paketov."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:156
msgid ""
"Verify that the batch settlement dates on eCheck.Net match the related "
"payments' dates found in the :guilabel:`Date` column of the :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Import to CSV`."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, ali se datumi poravnav paketov na eCheck.Net ujemajo z datumi "
"povezanih plačil, ki jih najdete v stolpcu :guilabel:`Date` v "
":guilabel:`Odoo Import to CSV`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:158
msgid ""
"If it does not match, replace the date with the one from eCheck.Net. Sort "
"the column by *date*, and make sure the format is `MM/DD/YYYY`."
msgstr ""
"Če se ne ujema, zamenjajte datum z datumom iz eCheck.Net. Razvrsti stolpec "
"po *datumu* in se prepričajte, da je oblika `MM/DD/YYYY`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:160
msgid ""
"Copy the data - column headings included - from the :guilabel:`Odoo Import "
"to CSV` sheet, paste it into a new Excel file, and save it using the CSV "
"format."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte podatke - vključno z naslovi stolpcev - iz lista :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Import to CSV`, jih prilepite v novo datoteko Excel in jo shranite v obliki "
"CSV."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:162
msgid ""
"Open the Accounting app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Journals`, "
"tick the :guilabel:`Authorize.Net` box, and click :menuselection:`Favorites "
"--> Import records --> Load file`. Select the CSV file and upload it into "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Odprite aplikacijo Računovodstvo, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Configuration --> Journals`, označite polje "
":guilabel:`Authorize.Net` in kliknite :menuselection:`Favorites --> Import "
"records --> Load file`. Izberite datoteko CSV in jo naložite v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/authorize.rst:167
msgid ""
"List of `eCheck.Net return codes <https://support.authorize.net/"
"knowledgebase/Knowledgearticle/?code=000001293>`_"
msgstr ""
"Seznam `kod za vračila eCheck.Net <https://support.authorize.net/"
"knowledgebase/Knowledgearticle/?code=000001293>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:11
msgid "Wire transfer"
msgstr "Bančno nakazilo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:13
msgid ""
"The **Wire Transfer** payment method allows you to provide payment "
"instructions to customers, such as your bank details and a reference to "
"include with the payment. These instructions are displayed after the "
"customer selects :guilabel:`Wire Transfer` as the payment method and clicks "
"the :guilabel:`Pay now` button at the end of the checkout process on your "
"ecommerce website or on the customer portal."
msgstr ""
"Plačilna metoda **Bančno nakazilo** vam omogoča, da strankam zagotovite "
"navodila za plačilo, kot so podatki o vaši banki in sklic, ki ga je treba "
"navesti pri plačilu. Ta navodila so prikazana, ko stranka izbere "
":guilabel:`Bančno nakazilo` kot plačilno metodo in na koncu postopka nakupa "
"na vaši spletni trgovini ali na portalu za stranke klikne gumb "
":guilabel:`Plačaj zdaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:20
msgid ""
"While this method is widely accessible and requires minimal setup, it is not "
"efficient process-wise. It is recommended to set up a :doc:`payment provider "
"<../payment_providers>` instead."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je ta metoda široko dostopna in zahteva minimalno nastavitev, ni "
"učinkovita s procesnega vidika. Priporočljivo je namestiti :doc:`payment "
"provider <../payment_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:23
msgid ""
"Online orders remain in the :guilabel:`Quotation sent` (i.e., unpaid order) "
"stage until you receive the payment and manually :guilabel:`Confirm` the "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Spletna naročila ostanejo v fazi :guilabel:`Quotation sent` (tj. neplačano "
"naročilo), dokler ne prejmete plačila in ročno :guilabel:`Confirm` naročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:26
msgid "To configure **Wire Transfer**, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za konfiguracijo **Bančnega nakazila** sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:28
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the Wire Transfer payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Navigate to the Wire Transfer payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:29
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:84
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Configuration` tab, select whether the memo "
"or :guilabel:`Communication` to be displayed alongside the payment "
"instructions should be:"
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku :guilabel:`Konfiguracija` izberite, ali naj bo opomba ali "
":guilabel:`sporočilo`, prikazano skupaj z navodili za plačilo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:32
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Based on Document Reference`: the sales order or invoice number"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Na podlagi sklica dokumenta`: številka prodajnega naloga ali "
"računa"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:33
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:88
msgid ":guilabel:`Based on Customer ID`: the customer identifier"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Na podlagi ID-ja stranke`: identifikator stranke"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:35
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Enable QR codes` to activate QR code payments."
msgstr "Omogočite :guilabel:`Enable QR codes`, da aktivirate plačila s QR kodo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:38
#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:93
msgid ""
":doc:`Additional accounting setup <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"epc_qr_code>` is required to use QR codes."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Dodatna nastavitev računovodstva <../accounting/customer_invoices/"
"epc_qr_code>` je potrebna za uporabo QR kod."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:41
msgid ""
"Define the payment instructions in the :guilabel:`Messages` tab. If :doc:`a "
"bank account <../accounting/bank>` has already been defined, the account "
"number is automatically added to the default message generated by Odoo. You "
"can also add it afterward and update the message by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Reload pending message`."
msgstr ""
"Določite navodila za plačilo v zavihku :guilabel:`Messages`. Če je :doc:`a "
"bank account <../accounting/bank>` že določen, se številka računa samodejno "
"doda privzetemu sporočilu, ki ga ustvari Odoo. Lahko ga dodate tudi pozneje "
"in posodobite sporočilo s klikom na :guilabel:`Reload pending message`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:48
msgid ""
"The **Wire transfer** payment method can serve as a template for other "
"payment methods that are processed manually, such as checks. :ref:`Access "
"the Wire Transfer payment method <payment_providers/payment_methods>`, then "
"duplicate it if needed and rename it accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Plačilna metoda **Bančno nakazilo** lahko služi kot predloga za druge "
"plačilne metode, ki se obdelujejo ročno, kot so čeki. :ref:`Dostopajte do "
"plačilne metode Bančno nakazilo <payment_providers/payment_methods>`, jo po "
"potrebi podvojite in ustrezno preimenujte."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:55
msgid "SEPA Direct Debit"
msgstr "SEPA direktna bremenitev"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:59
msgid ""
"SEPA (Single Euro Payments Area) is a payment-integration initiative of the "
"European Union that facilitates standardized and simplified electronic "
"payments in euros across participating countries."
msgstr ""
"SEPA (enotno območje plačil v evrih) je plačilna pobuda Evropske unije, ki "
"olajša standardizirana in poenostavljena elektronska plačila v evrih med "
"sodelujočimi državami."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:62
msgid ""
"SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) is a payment provider that allows future payments to "
"be collected from customers' bank accounts based on a signed :ref:`SEPA "
"Direct Debit mandate <accounting/batch_sdd/sdd_mandates>`. This is "
"particularly useful for recurring payments based on a :doc:`subscription </"
"applications/sales/subscriptions>`."
msgstr ""
"SEPA direktna obremenitev (SDD) je ponudnik plačil, ki omogoča pobiranje "
"prihodnjih plačil z bančnih računov strank na podlagi podpisanega "
":ref:`mandata za SEPA direktno obremenitev <accounting/batch_sdd/"
"sdd_mandates>`. To je še posebej uporabno za ponavljajoča se plačila na "
"podlagi :doc:`naročnine </applications/sales/subscriptions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:68
msgid ""
"To use the SEPA Direct Debit (SDD) payment provider and create :ref:`SEPA "
"Direct Debit mandates <accounting/batch_sdd/sdd_mandates>`:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti ponudnika plačil SEPA direktna obremenitev (SDD) in "
"ustvariti :ref:`mandate za SEPA direktno obremenitev <accounting/batch_sdd/"
"sdd_mandates>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:71
msgid "The invoice being paid must be for an amount in euros."
msgstr "Račun, ki se plačuje, mora biti za znesek v evrih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:72
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`SEPA Direct Deposit (SDD)` feature must be enabled, and the "
"company's :guilabel:`Creditor Identifier` must be defined in "
"the :ref:`Accounting or Invoicing settings <accounting/batch_sdd/sepa-"
"configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija :guilabel:`SEPA direktna obremenitev (SDD)` mora biti omogočena in "
":guilabel:`identifikator upnika` podjetja mora biti določen v "
":ref:`nastavitvah računovodstva ali fakturiranja <accounting/batch_sdd/sepa-"
"configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:81
msgid "To configure **SEPA Direct Debit**, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Za konfiguracijo **SEPA direktne obremenitve** sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:83
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the SEPA Direct Debit payment provider <payment_providers/"
"supported_providers>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pojdite na ponudnika plačil SEPA direktna obremenitev "
"<payment_providers/supported_providers>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:90
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Enable QR codes` check box to activate QR code "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Omogoči QR kode`, da aktivirate "
"plačila z QR kodo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:96
msgid ""
"Edit the default payment instructions in the :guilabel:`Messages` tab to "
"include your **bank account number**. These instructions are displayed at "
"the end of the checkout process on your ecommerce website or on the customer "
"portal."
msgstr ""
"Uredite privzeta navodila za plačilo v zavihku :guilabel:`Sporočila`, da "
"vključite svojo **številko bančnega računa**. Ta navodila se prikažejo na "
"koncu postopka plačila na vaši spletni trgovini ali na portalu za stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:102
msgid ""
"Leave the :guilabel:`Currencies` field set to the default :guilabel:`EUR` "
"tag to ensure |sdd| is only available for payments in euros."
msgstr ""
"Pustite polje :guilabel:`Valute` nastavljeno na privzeto oznako "
":guilabel:`EUR`, da zagotovite, da je |sdd| na voljo samo za plačila v evrih."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:104
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Bank Account` defined for the :guilabel:`Payment Journal` "
"must be a valid IBAN."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bančni račun`, določen za :guilabel:`Plačilni dnevnik`, mora biti "
"veljaven IBAN."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:107
msgid ""
"You can also test SEPA direct debit payments using "
"the :ref:`payment_providers/test-mode`."
msgstr ""
"Plačila SEPA Direct Debit lahko testirate tudi z uporabo "
":ref:`payment_providers/test-mode`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:110
msgid "Online payments with |sdd|"
msgstr "Spletna plačila z |sdd|"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:112
msgid ""
"Customers selecting |sdd| as a payment method are prompted to enter their "
"IBAN to complete the :ref:`SEPA Direct Debit mandate <accounting/batch_sdd/"
"sdd_mandates>`."
msgstr ""
"Stranke, ki izberejo |sdd| kot način plačila, so pozvane, da vnesejo svoj "
"IBAN za dokončanje :ref:`SEPA Direct Debit mandata <accounting/batch_sdd/"
"sdd_mandates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:115
msgid ""
"The |sdd| mandate is then automatically created in :guilabel:`Draft` based "
"on the provided IBAN. To validate the information, customers must confirm "
"each new mandate with a successful bank transfer of the expected amount "
"**using the specified payment reference (communication)** defined in "
"the :ref:`SEPA Direct Debit payment provider's form <sdd/configuration>`. "
"Once this initial payment is received and :doc:`reconciled <../accounting/"
"bank/reconciliation>`, the mandate is automatically validated and updated to "
"the :guilabel:`Active` status. Once a mandate is active, it is reused for "
"all subsequent payments made with the |sdd| payment method. You can then "
"collect them by :ref:`uploading them to your online banking interface "
"<accounting/batch_sdd/XML>`."
msgstr ""
"Mandat |sdd| se nato samodejno ustvari v stanju :guilabel:`Osnutek` na "
"podlagi vnešenega IBAN-a. Za potrditev podatkov morajo stranke potrditi vsak "
"nov mandat z uspešnim bančnim nakazilom pričakovanega zneska **z navedeno "
"plačilno referenco (sporočilom)**, ki je opredeljena v :ref:`obrazcu "
"ponudnika plačil SEPA Direct Debit <sdd/configuration>`. Ko je to začetno "
"plačilo prejeto in :doc:`usklajeno <../accounting/bank/reconciliation>`, se "
"mandat samodejno potrdi in posodobi na stanje :guilabel:`Aktiven`. Ko je "
"mandat aktiven, se ponovno uporabi za vsa nadaljnja plačila z načinom "
"plačila |sdd|. Nato jih lahko poberete tako, da jih :ref:`naložite v svoj "
"vmesnik spletnega bančništva <accounting/batch_sdd/XML>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:125
msgid ":doc:`../accounting/payments/batch_sdd`"
msgstr ":doc:`../accounting/payments/batch_sdd`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:128
msgid ""
"Mandates are automatically :ref:`closed <accounting/batch_sdd/close-revoke-"
"mandate>` 36 months after the date of the last collection."
msgstr ""
"Mandati so samodejno :ref:`zapreti <accounting/batch_sdd/close-revoke-"
"mandate>` 36 mesecev po datumu zadnjega pobiranja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/bank_payments.rst:130
msgid ""
"|sdd| is also available as a payment method through other providers, such "
"as :doc:`adyen`, :doc:`buckaroo`, and :doc:`stripe`. In these cases, |sdd| "
"mandates are handled externally by the payment provider."
msgstr ""
"|sdd| je na voljo tudi kot način plačila prek drugih ponudnikov, kot so "
":doc:`adyen`, :doc:`buckaroo` in :doc:`stripe`. V teh primerih ponudnik "
"plačil zunaj obravnava mandate |sdd|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:3
msgid "Buckaroo"
msgstr "Buckaroo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Buckaroo <https://www.buckaroo.eu/>`_ is a Dutch-based company that offers "
"several online payment possibilities."
msgstr ""
"<https://www.buckaroo.eu/>`_ je podjetje na Nizozemskem, ki ponuja več "
"možnosti spletnega plačevanja."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:11
msgid "Configuration on Buckaroo Plaza"
msgstr "Konfiguracija na Buckaroo Plaza"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:13
msgid ""
"Log into `Buckaroo Plaza <https://plaza.buckaroo.nl>`_, go "
"to :menuselection:`My Buckaroo --> Websites` and select the :guilabel:`Push "
"settings` tab."
msgstr ""
"Prijavite se v `Buckaroo Plaza <https://plaza.buckaroo.nl>`_, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`My Buckaroo --> Websites` in izberite zavihek "
":guilabel:`Push settings`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:15
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Enable Push Response` check box in "
"the :guilabel:`Delayed and Push responses` section."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Enable Push Response` v razdelku "
":guilabel:`Delayed and Push responses`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/buckaroo.rst:17
msgid ""
"Enter the URL of your Odoo database, followed by `/payment/buckaroo/webhook` "
"in both the :guilabel:`Push URI Success/Pending` and :guilabel:`Push URI "
