msgstr "Demo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/demo.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo's **Demo Payment Provider** allows you to test business flows involving "
"online transactions without requiring real banking credentials."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Demo ponudnik plačil** vam omogoča testiranje poslovnih procesov, ki "
"vključujejo spletne transakcije, brez potrebe po pravih bančnih poverilnicah."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/demo.rst:15
msgid "Switch the state to :guilabel:`Test Mode`."
msgstr "Preklopite stanje na :guilabel:`Testni način`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/demo.rst:18
msgid "Payment outcome"
msgstr "Rezultat plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/demo.rst:20
msgid ""
"Upon checkout or when paying a bill online, you can choose the payment "
"outcome when using the demo payment provider. To do so, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Status` drop-down menu and select the desired outcome."
msgstr ""
"Pri zaključku nakupa ali plačevanju računa na spletu lahko izberete rezultat "
"plačila pri uporabi demo ponudnika plačil. To storite tako, da kliknete "
"spustni meni :guilabel:`Stanje plačila` in izberete želeni rezultat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/demo.rst:None
msgid "Payment status outcomes."
msgstr "Rezultati stanja plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/demo.rst:29
msgid "Transaction state"
msgstr "Stanje transakcije"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/demo.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you selected :guilabel:`Pending` as **payment outcome**, you can change "
"the state of the transaction straight from its form view. To access a "
"transaction's form view, activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and go to :menuselection:`Accounting / Website --> Configuration --> "
"Payment Transactions`. Then, change the status of a transaction by clicking "
"on the state bar (:guilabel:`Draft, Pending, Authorized, Confirmed, "
"Cancelled, Error`)."
msgstr ""
"Če ste kot **rezultat plačila** izbrali :guilabel:`V teku`, lahko spremenite "
"stanje transakcije neposredno iz njenega obrazca. Za dostop do obrazca "
"transakcije aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>` in pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Računovodstvo / Spletna stran --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Plačilne transakcije`. Nato spremenite status transakcije s klikom na "
"vrstico stanja (:guilabel:`Osnutek, V teku, Odobreno, Potrjeno, Preklicano, "
"Napaka`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/demo.rst:None
msgid "Transaction's status bar."
msgstr "Vrstica stanja transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:3
msgid "DPO Pay"
msgstr "DPO Pay"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:5
msgid ""
"`DPO Pay <https://dpogroup.com/>`_ is a payment provider based in Africa "
"that operates across multiple countries on the continent."
msgstr ""
"Podjetje `DPO Pay <https://dpogroup.com/>`_ je ponudnik plačilnih storitev s "
"sedežem v Afriki, ki posluje v več državah na celini."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:11
msgid "DPO Pay account creation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje računa DPO Pay"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:13
msgid ""
"`Fill in the DPO Pay onboarding form <https://dpo-pay-network.odoo.com/"
"form>`_ and upload the required documents."
msgstr ""
"`Izpolnite obrazec za registracijo DPO Pay <https://dpo-pay-network.odoo.com/"
"form>`_ in naložite zahtevane dokumente."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:15
msgid ""
"Agree to the :guilabel:`Terms and Conditions` and click :guilabel:`Submit`."
msgstr ""
"Sprejmite :guilabel:`Pogoje in določila` ter kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:16
msgid ""
"DPO Pay creates a test account based on the submitted information and sends "
"you an email containing your login credentials for the `DPO portal <https://"
"portal.dpopay.com>`_ and the :ref:`test credentials <payment_providers/test-"
"mode>` to enter in :ref:`Odoo <payment_providers/dpo/configure_odoo>` if you "
"want to try DPO Pay without affecting live transactions."
msgstr ""
"DPO Pay ustvari testni račun na podlagi predloženih informacij in vam pošlje "
"e-pošto s prijavnimi podatki za `portal DPO <https://portal.dpopay.com>`_ in "
":ref:`testnimi poverilnicami <payment_providers/test-mode>`, ki jih lahko "
"vnesete v :ref:`Odoo <payment_providers/dpo/configure_odoo>`, če želite "
"preizkusiti DPO Pay, ne da bi to vplivalo na dejanske transakcije."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:21
msgid ""
"Once DPO has verified the information and documents, they will transition "
"your test account to a live account and send another email containing your "
"live credentials to configure in :ref:`Odoo <payment_providers/dpo/"
"configure_odoo>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko DPO preveri informacije in dokumente, bodo vaš testni račun spremenili v "
"dejanski račun in poslali še eno e-pošto z vašimi dejanskimi poverilnicami "
"za konfiguracijo v :ref:`Odoo <payment_providers/dpo/configure_odoo>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:30
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider DPO Pay <payment_providers/add_new>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pojdite do ponudnika plačilnih storitev DPO Pay <payment_providers/"
"add_new>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:31
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Service ID` and :guilabel:`Company Token` fields with "
"the :ref:`information received from DPO Pay <payment_providers/dpo/"
"configure_dashboard>`."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite polji :guilabel:`ID storitve` in :guilabel:`Žeton podjetja` z "
":ref:`informacijami, prejetimi od DPO Pay <payment_providers/dpo/"
"configure_dashboard>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:33
msgid "Configure the remaining options to your liking."
msgstr "Preostale možnosti konfigurirajte po svoji želji."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:34
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`State` field to :guilabel:`Enabled` (or :guilabel:`Test "
"Mode` if you are trying DPO Pay as a :ref:`test <payment_providers/test-"
"mode>`)."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Stanje` nastavite na :guilabel:`Omogočeno` (ali "
":guilabel:`Testni način`, če preizkušate DPO Pay kot :ref:`test "
"<payment_providers/test-mode>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/dpo.rst:38
msgid ""
"All `payment methods supported by DPO Pay <https://dpogroup.com/Payment-"
"methods>`_ are grouped under the :guilabel:`Card / Mobile` payment method. "
"When they select this payment method, customers are redirected to a DPO Pay "
"page where they can select their preferred payment method. To enable or "
"disable specific payment options, contact `DPO Pay support <https://"
"dpogroup.com/contact-us/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Vse `plačilne metode, ki jih podpira DPO Pay <https://dpogroup.com/Payment-"
"methods>`_, so združene pod plačilno metodo :guilabel:`Kartica / Mobilnik`. "
"Ko stranke izberejo to plačilno metodo, so preusmerjene na stran DPO Pay, "
"kjer lahko izberejo želeno plačilno metodo. Za omogočanje ali onemogočanje "
"določenih plačilnih možnosti se obrnite na `podporo DPO Pay <https://"
"dpogroup.com/contact-us/>`_."

