msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`API Individual Integration Key` section, copy "
"the :guilabel:`Client Key` and :guilabel:`Secret Key`, and save them for "
"the :ref:`Odoo configuration step <payment_providers/toss_payments/"
"configure_odoo>`."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`API Individual Integration Key` kopirajte "
":guilabel:`Client Key` in :guilabel:`Secret Key` ter ju shranite za "
":ref:`korak konfiguracije Odoo <payment_providers/toss_payments/"
"configure_odoo>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/tosspayments.rst:29
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Webhook` menu and click :guilabel:`Register "
"Webhook`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na meni :guilabel:`Webhook` in kliknite :guilabel:`Register Webhook`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/tosspayments.rst:30
msgid "Enter a name to help identify the webhook."
msgstr "Vnesite ime, ki bo pomagalo prepoznati webhook."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/tosspayments.rst:31
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`URL` field, enter your Odoo database's URL, followed by `/"
"payment/toss-payments/webhook` (e.g., `https://example.odoo.com/payment/toss-"
"payments/webhook`)."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`URL` vnesite URL vaše Odoo podatkovne baze, ki mu sledi `/"
"payment/toss-payments/webhook` (npr. `https://example.odoo.com/payment/toss-"
"payments/webhook`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/tosspayments.rst:36
msgid ""
"You can also copy the :guilabel:`Webhook URL` from the Toss Payments form in "
"Odoo and paste it."
msgstr ""
"Lahko tudi kopirate :guilabel:`Webhook URL` iz obrazca Toss Payments v Odoo "
"in ga prilepite."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/tosspayments.rst:39
msgid ""
"Ensure the :guilabel:`PAYMENT_STATUS_CHANGED` event is enabled, then save "
"the webhook settings."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je dogodek :guilabel:`PAYMENT_STATUS_CHANGED` omogočen, "
"nato shranite nastavitve webhooka."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/tosspayments.rst:47
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Toss Payments <payment_providers/"
"add_new>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pojdite na ponudnika plačil Toss Payments <payment_providers/add_new>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/tosspayments.rst:48
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Client Key` and :guilabel:`Secret Key` fields with "
"the information saved at the step :ref:`payment_providers/toss_payments/"
"configure_dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite polji :guilabel:`Client Key` in :guilabel:`Secret Key` z "
"informacijami, shranjenimi v koraku :ref:`payment_providers/toss_payments/"
"configure_dashboard`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/tosspayments.rst:51
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`State` field to :guilabel:`Enabled` (or :guilabel:`Test "
"Mode` if you are trying Toss Payments as a :ref:`test <payment_providers/"
"test-mode>`)."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite polje :guilabel:`Stanje` na :guilabel:`Enabled` (ali "
":guilabel:`Test Mode`, če preizkušate Toss Payments kot :ref:`test "
"<payment_providers/test-mode>`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:3
msgid "Worldline"
msgstr "Worldline"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Worldline <https://worldline.com/>`_ is a France-based company and the "
"world's fourth largest payment provider."
msgstr ""
"`Worldline <https://worldline.com/>`_ je podjetje s sedežem v Franciji in "
"četrti največji ponudnik plačil na svetu."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:9
msgid "Settings in Worldline"
msgstr "Nastavitve v Worldline"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:14
msgid "Create an API user"
msgstr "Ustvari API uporabnika"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:16
msgid ""
"It is recommended to set up an **API user** to create transactions from Odoo "
"to ensure that your Worldline configuration remains safe even if credentials "
"are compromised. Additionally, API users do not require frequent password "
"updates like regular accounts."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je nastaviti **API uporabnika** za ustvarjanje transakcij iz "
"Odoo, da zagotovite, da vaša konfiguracija Worldline ostane varna, tudi če "
"so poverila ogrožena. Poleg tega API uporabniki ne zahtevajo pogostega "
"posodabljanja gesla kot običajni računi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:20
msgid "To create an **API user**, proceed as follows:"
msgstr "Za ustvaritev **API uporabnika** nadaljujte na sledeči način:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:22
msgid ""
"Log into your `Worldline Merchant Portal <https://merchant-portal.worldline-"
"solutions.com/>`_, click the :icon:`fa-th` (:guilabel:`menu`) icon, and "
"select :guilabel:`Back Office`."
msgstr ""
"Prijavite se v vaš `Worldline Merchant Portal <https://merchant-"
"portal.worldline-solutions.com/>`_, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-th` "
"(:guilabel:`menu`) in izberite :guilabel:`Back Office`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:24
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` and click on :guilabel:`New "
"User`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Configuration --> Users` in kliknite na "
":guilabel:`New User`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:25
msgid "Configure the following fields:"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte naslednja polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:27
msgid ""
"Specify a :guilabel:`UserID`, :guilabel:`User's name`, :guilabel:`E-mail "
"address`, and :guilabel:`Timezone` of your choice."
msgstr ""
"Določite :guilabel:`ID uporabnika`, :guilabel:`Ime uporabnika`, :guilabel:`E-"
"poštni naslov` in :guilabel:`Časovni pas` po vaši izbiri."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:29
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Profile` field to :guilabel:`Admin`."
msgstr "Nastavite polje :guilabel:`Profil` na :guilabel:`Skrbnik`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:30
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Special user for API`."
msgstr "Omogočite :guilabel:`Poseben uporabnik za API`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:33
msgid ""
"If you have already set up a user, make sure it is activated without any "
"error."
msgstr ""
"Če ste že nastavili uporabnika, se prepričajte, da je aktiviran brez napak."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:34
msgid ""
"To test the payment flow with Worldline, use their `test environment "
"<https://merchant-portal.preprod.worldline-solutions.com/>`_ together with "
"the :ref:`test mode <payment_providers/test-mode>`."
msgstr ""
"Za preizkus plačilnega poteka z Worldline uporabite njihovo `testno okolje "
"<https://merchant-portal.preprod.worldline-solutions.com/>`_ skupaj z "
":ref:`testnim načinom <payment_providers/test-mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:41
msgid "Set up Worldline for Odoo"
msgstr "Nastavitev Worldline za Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:43
msgid "Worldline must now be configured to accept payments from Odoo."
msgstr "Worldline mora biti zdaj konfiguriran za sprejemanje plačil iz Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:45
msgid ""
"From your merchant portal, go to :menuselection:`Developer --> Payment API` "
"and click on :guilabel:`Generate API key`. Copy the :guilabel:`API key ID` "
"and the :guilabel:`Secret API key` and save them for :ref:`later <wordline/"
"odoo-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Na svojem trgovskem portalu pojdite na :menuselection:`Razvijalec --> API za "
"plačila` in kliknite :guilabel:`Generiraj API ključ`. Kopirajte "
":guilabel:`ID API ključa` in :guilabel:`Skrivni API ključ` ter ju shranite "
"za :ref:`pozneje <wordline/odoo-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:48
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Developer --> Webhooks` and click "
"on :guilabel:`Generate webhook keys`. Copy the :guilabel:`Webhook ID` and "
"the associated :guilabel:`Secret webhook key` and save them for :ref:`later "
"<wordline/odoo-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Razvijalec --> Webhooks` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Generiraj webhook ključe`. Kopirajte :guilabel:`ID webhooka` in "
"pripadajoči :guilabel:`Skrivni webhook ključ` ter ju shranite za "
":ref:`pozneje <wordline/odoo-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add webhook endpoint`, enter your Odoo database's URL "
"followed by `/payment/worldline/webhook` in the :guilabel:`Endpoint url` "
"field, and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj končno točko webhooka`, vnesite URL vaše Odoo "
"podatkovne baze, ki mu sledi `/payment/worldline/webhook` v polje "
":guilabel:`URL končne točke`, in :guilabel:`Potrdite`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:0
msgid "For example: `https://example.odoo.com/payment/worldline/webhook`."
msgstr "Na primer: `https://example.odoo.com/payment/worldline/webhook`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:58
msgid "Settings in Odoo"
msgstr "Nastavitve v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:60
msgid "To set up Worldline in Odoo:"
msgstr "Za nastavitev Worldline v Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:62
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Worldline <payment_providers/"
"add_new>` and change its state to :guilabel:`Enabled`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pojdite do ponudnika plačil Worldline <payment_providers/add_new>` in "
"spremenite njegovo stanje na :guilabel:`Omogočeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/worldline.rst:64
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab, enter the :guilabel:`PSPID` of your "
"Worldline account and fill in the :guilabel:`API Key`, :guilabel:`API "
"Secret`, :guilabel:`Webhook Key`, and :guilabel:`Webhook Secret` with the "
"values you saved at the step :ref:`Set up Worldline for Odoo <worldline/set-"
"up>`."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Poverilnice` vnesite :guilabel:`PSPID` vašega Worldline "
"računa in izpolnite :guilabel:`API ključ`, :guilabel:`API skrivnost`, "
":guilabel:`Webhook ključ` in :guilabel:`Webhook skrivnost` z vrednostmi, ki "
"ste jih shranili pri koraku :ref:`Nastavitev Worldline za Odoo <worldline/"
"set-up>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:3
msgid "Xendit"
msgstr "Xendit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:5
msgid ""
"`Xendit <https://www.xendit.co>`_ is an Indonesian-based payment solution "
"provider that covers several Southeast Asian countries. It allows businesses "
"to accept credit cards as well as several local payment methods."
msgstr ""
"`Xendit <https://www.xendit.co>`_ je indonezijski ponudnik plačilnih "
"rešitev, ki pokriva več držav jugovzhodne Azije. Podjetjem omogoča "
"sprejemanje kreditnih kartic ter več lokalnih plačilnih metod."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:10
msgid ""
"Credit card payments are processed through Odoo, while all other payment "
"methods are handled via Xendit's website."
msgstr ""
"Plačila s kreditnimi karticami se obdelujejo v Odoo, medtem ko se vse druge "
"plačilne metode upravljajo prek spletne strani Xendit."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:12
msgid ""
"Xendit supports card payment tokenization, provided the customer has "
"requested Merchant Initiated Transaction (MIT) from `Xendit Support <https://"
"www.xendit.co/en/contact/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Xendit podpira tokenizacijo plačil s karticami, pod pogojem da je stranka "
"zahtevala transakcijo, ki jo sproži trgovec (MIT), od `podpore Xendit "
"<https://www.xendit.co/en/contact/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:18
msgid "Configuration on the Xendit Dashboard"
msgstr "Konfiguracija na nadzorni plošči Xendit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:20
msgid ""
"`Create a Xendit account <https://dashboard.xendit.co/register/1?"
"referral_code=odooid&countr_code=ID>`_ if necessary and log in to the "
"`Xendit Dashboard <https://dashboard.xendit.co>`_."
msgstr ""
"Če je potrebno, `ustvarite račun Xendit <https://dashboard.xendit.co/"
"register/1?referral_code=odooid&countr_code=ID>`_ in se prijavite v "
"`nadzorno plošč Xendit <https://dashboard.xendit.co>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:23
msgid ""
"Check your account mode in the top left corner of the page. Use "
"the :guilabel:`Test Mode` to try the integration without charging your "
"customers. Switch to :guilabel:`Live Mode` once you are ready to accept "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Preverite način svojega računa v zgornjem levem kotu strani. Uporabite "
":guilabel:`testni način` za preizkus integracije brez obremenitve strank. "
"Preklopite na :guilabel:`način v živo`, ko ste pripravljeni sprejemati "
"plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:26
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration: Settings` in the left part of the "
"application page. In the :guilabel:`Developers` section, click `API Keys "
"<https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#api-keys>`_."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Konfiguracija: Nastavitve` na levi strani "
"aplikacijske strani. V razdelku :guilabel:`Razvijalci` kliknite `API ključi "
"<https://dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#api-keys>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Generate Secret Key`. In the popup box, enter "
"any :guilabel:`API key name`, select :guilabel:`Write` for "
"the :guilabel:`Money-in Products` permission and :guilabel:`None` for all "
"other permissions then click :guilabel:`Generate key`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Generiraj skrivni ključ`. V pojavnem oknu vnesite "
"poljubno :guilabel:`ime API ključa`, izberite :guilabel:`Pisanje` za "
"dovoljenje :guilabel:`Izdelki za denar` in :guilabel:`Nič` za vsa ostala "
"dovoljenja, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Generiraj ključ`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:32
msgid ""
"Confirm your password to display your API key. Copy or download the key and "
"**save this information securely for later**. This is the only time the API "
"key can be viewed or downloaded."
msgstr ""
"Potrdite svoje geslo, da prikažete API ključ. Kopirajte ali prenesite ključ "
"in **te podatke varno shranite za pozneje**. To je edini čas, ko je mogoče "
"API ključ pregledati ali prenesti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:35
msgid ""
"Once completed, scroll down the page to the `Webhooks <https://"
"dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks>`_ section to generate the "
"webhook token."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate, se pomaknite navzdol po strani do razdelka `Webhooks <https://"
"dashboard.xendit.co/settings/developers#webhooks>`_, da generirate žeton "
"webhook."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:38
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Webhook verification token`, click :guilabel:`View Webhook "
"Verification Token`, then confirm your password to display the token. Save "
"it for later."
msgstr ""
"Pod :guilabel:`žeton za preverjanje webhooka` kliknite :guilabel:`Prikaži "
"žeton za preverjanje webhooka`, nato potrdite svoje geslo, da prikažete "
"žeton. Shranite ga za pozneje."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:40
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Webhook URL` section, enter your Odoo database's URL, "
"followed by `/payment/xendit/webhook` (e.g., `https://example.odoo.com/"
"payment/xendit/webhook`) in the field :guilabel:`Invoices paid` and click "
"the :guilabel:`Test and save` button next to it."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`URL webhooka` vnesite URL svoje podatkovne baze Odoo, "
"ki mu sledi `/payment/xendit/webhook` (npr. `https://example.odoo.com/"
"payment/xendit/webhook`) v polje :guilabel:`Plačani računi` in kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Preizkusi in shrani` poleg njega."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:43
msgid ""
"To allow recurring payments for credit cards, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration: Payment Channels` in the left part of the "
"application page. Then, hover your mouse over the :guilabel:`Visa, "
"Mastercard, JCB, Amex` channel, click :guilabel:`View Details`, and "
"enable :guilabel:`Recurring Payments` by toggling the related switch."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti ponavljajoča se plačila za kreditne kartice, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Konfiguracija: Plačilni kanali` na levi strani aplikacijske "
"strani. Nato premaknite miško nad kanal :guilabel:`Visa, Mastercard, JCB, "
"Amex`, kliknite :guilabel:`Prikaži podrobnosti` in omogočite "
":guilabel:`Ponavljajoča se plačila` s preklopom ustreznega stikala."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:51
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Xendit <payment_providers/add_new>` "
"and change its state to :guilabel:`Enabled`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pojdite na ponudnika plačil Xendit <payment_providers/add_new>` in "
"spremenite njegovo stanje na :guilabel:`Omogočeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:53
msgid ""
"Fill in the :guilabel:`Secret Key` and :guilabel:`Webhook Token` fields with "
"the information saved at the step :ref:`payment_providers/xendit/"
"configure_dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite polji :guilabel:`Skrivni ključ` in :guilabel:`Žeton webhooka` s "
"podatki, shranjenimi v koraku :ref:`payment_providers/xendit/"
"configure_dashboard`."

